NK053('i)001:1: // ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka s+ya n+ao pi ka
NK053('i)001:2: sa mya k+si d+d+ha nam h+aa gu h+ya t+ai ka
NK053('i)001:5: // dpal khrag 'thung chen po'i sgrub thabs yang dag grub
NK053('i)001:6: pa zhes bya ba'i gsang 'grel chen po bzhugs so
NK053('i)001:17: rgya gar dang bod skad do //
NK053('i)001:19: ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka no pi ka sanyaka sid+d+hi n+aa ma ma h+aa gu h+ya t+aika /
NK053('i)001:21: rtogs pa bdag gi dang thugs rje gzhan gyi dapala
NK053('i)001:22: nyon mongs pa khraga dang 'dra ba rtogs na ye
NK053('i)001:23: shes su 'thunga ba'i gong na gzhan med pas chena
NK053('i)001:24: po'i mchog thun mong gi sgrub thabas /
NK053('i)001:25: chos nyid yang dag pa rang la rang chas su
NK053('i)001:26: grub pa zhesa bya ba gab pa dang sbas pa'i
NK053('i)001:27: gasnga ba de'i don 'grela pa chena po /
NK053('i)001:29: bdud bzhi bcoma ye shes lnga dang ldana gnyis med
NK053('i)001:30: du 'adsa pa'i zhi ba'i lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis
NK053('i)001:31: khro bo'i lha lnga bcu rtsa brgyad dbyer med 'abra
NK053('i)001:32: ba'i lha tshogas mang ba la lus ngag yid gsum
NK053('i)001:33: mos pa dang gus pas phyag 'atshala lo //
NK053('i)001:34: zhe sdang gdug pa ste zhe sdang ma spangs gnas
NK053('i)001:35: su dag pa badz+ra he ru kas lus ngag yid
NK053('i)001:36: gsum khro bo'i cha lugs can ru tra 'khor bcas
NK053('i)001:38: kun tu bzang po'i shes rab kyi thugas rje ma
NK053('i)001:39: 'gags par thabas kyisa khro rgyal dpal chen po mchoga
NK053('i)001:40: tu sprul nas // spyir phrin las bzhi las bye
NK053('i)001:41: brag tu draga po'i thabas kyis gduga pa can ru
NK053('i)001:42: tra lta bu 'jomas par madzada pa //
NK053('i)001:43: rtogs pa bdag thugs rje gzhan gyi dapala gong na
NK053('i)001:44: gzhan med pas chena po he ni chos sku mtshon
NK053('i)001:45: dang bral ru ni longs sku chen po ka ni
NK053('i)001:46: phrin las sprul pa ste dom sku gsum la phyag
NK053('i)001:47: 'atshala lo // bshad par dam bca' ba ni /
NK053('i)001:48: gdul bya 'gro ba'i mgona po rdo rje semas dpa' ste //
NK053('i)001:49: gdul bya skyong ba posa ni ched du bstan te rnama par gsungas pa'i //
NK053('i)001:50: rgyuda 'jiga rten las 'adsa mdo chena po dang //
NK053('i)001:51: he ru ka yi gala po lasa bsdus bsdus nas //
NK053('i)001:52: sgrub thabas rtsa ba 'grel pa lag tu blangs pa'i cho ga rgya chena po 'di //
NK053('i)001:53: bla ma gong ma gong ma'i lunga gisa bashada para bya'o //
NK053('i)001:54: rgyud las bsdus pa'i rtsa ba 'di dgos 'dod tshang
NK053('i)001:55: bas dpe yida bzhina gyi nor bu rina po che
NK053('i)001:56: dang 'dra'o // dper na zab pas mtsho dang 'dra
NK053('i)001:57: gsal bas na miga dang 'dra ba gsal bar ston
NK053('i)001:58: pa skara khunga lta bu ste //
NK053('i)001:59: rjod byed tshig tu nyung la brjod bya la dona chena por ston pa kun gyi gzhi ma //
NK053('i)001:60: bskyed pa ma h+aa rdzogas pa a nu rdzogs chen a ti rnama gsuma gzhi ma ru //
NK053('i)001:61: yang dag gruba pa'i rtsa ba theg pa dman pa la gasnga ba rgya che ba'i 'grela pa 'di //
NK053('i)001:62: rgyud 'dus mado'am gal po che'am sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor
NK053('i)001:63: la sogs bskyed rdzogs gsum la snanga ba'i rjod byed
NK053('i)001:65: ma lusa par 'grel pa 'dira bsdusa nas gadmas ngaga tu bsgrigs te //
NK053('i)001:66: badga 'dra slob dpon pad+ma 'byunga gansa kyis //
NK053('i)001:67: lha srasa khri srong lde'u btsan dona du brtsam pa yina //
NK053('i)001:69: spyir bshad thabs man ngag gi spyi khog tu bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:70: bye brag tu bstan pa ste /
NK053('i)001:72: mdora na yang dag gruba pa la //
NK053('i)001:78: don man ngag gis rdzogas para bya ba la //
NK053('i)001:79: yo byada gnyisa shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin du
NK053('i)001:80: dbye ba'am thabs dang shes rab gnyis la longas spyod
NK053('i)001:81: pasa // dkyila 'khora dgu yisa gtan la dabba //
NK053('i)001:82: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang gcig /
NK053('i)001:84: gzugs brnyan gyi dal dang gsum /
NK053('i)001:85: mchod rdzas la brten pa'i dal dang bzhi /
NK053('i)001:86: dbang bskur ba'i dal dang lnga /
NK053('i)001:87: ting nge 'dzin gyi dal dang drug /
NK053('i)001:88: lhun gyis grub pa'i dal dang bdun /
NK053('i)001:89: thugs kyi phrin las kyi dal dang brgyad /
NK053('i)001:90: dngos grub blang ba'i dal dang dagu'o //
NK053('i)001:91: skabas sbyor bco brgyad para matshamas bzunga //
NK053('i)001:92: dpal chen po'i rang bzhin bstan pa'i skabs dang gcig /
NK053('i)001:93: lung bstan pa slob ma'i skabs dang gnyis /
NK053('i)001:94: sgrub pa po rnams kyi brtul zhugs kyi khyad par dang dam tshig bstan pa'i skabs dang gsum /
NK053('i)001:95: slob ma snod dang mi ldan pa la slob dpon
NK053('i)001:96: gyis bstan na gnyis ka dmyal bar 'gro ba'i skabs
NK053('i)001:97: dang bzhi / yo byad dang rdzas dang sa gzhi brtags pa'i skabs dang lnga /
NK053('i)001:98: phyi nang gi mchod pa bya zhing mtshams bcad dang ma tram mnan pa'i skabs dang drug /
NK053('i)001:99: dkyil 'khor bri zhing rdzas bkod de mchod rdzas byin gyis brlabs pa'i skabs dang bdun /
NK053('i)001:100: slob dpon mnyes par byas nas slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa'i skabs dang brgyad /
NK053('i)001:101: rigs kyi yum brten cing byin gyis brlab cing sbyor ba'i lung bstan pa dang dgu /
NK053('i)001:102: slob dpon gyis slob ma snod dang ldan pa la
NK053('i)001:103: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi dbang sbyin pa'i skabs
NK053('i)001:104: dang bcu / slob mas sgrub pa'i dam tshig la
NK053('i)001:105: gnas shing bsnyen sgrub gzhung bzhin du bya ba'i skabs
NK053('i)001:106: dang bcu / dang bcu gcig / nye ba'i bsnyen
NK053('i)001:107: pa'i phyir zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor ting nge 'dzin rnam
NK053('i)001:108: gsum la sogs pa bskyed rdzogs kyi cho ga bya
NK053('i)001:110: sgrub pa bya ba'i phyir khro bo'i lha bskyed pa'i
NK053('i)001:111: thabs khyad par du bstan pa'i skabs dang bcu gsum
NK053('i)001:112: / ye shes kyi he ru ka spyan drangs shing
NK053('i)001:113: mchod pa'i cho ga bstan pa'i skabs dang bcu bzhi
NK053('i)001:114: / / sgrub rdzas bsgral ba'i man ngag bstan pa'i skabs dang bco lnga /
NK053('i)001:115: bar chad kyi bgegs nyams kyi phyag rgyas bsad cing zil gyis mnan pa'i skabs dang bcu drug /
NK053('i)001:116: dngos grub blang zhing sgrub pa chen po'i dus bstan pa'i skabs dang bcu bdun /
NK053('i)001:117: dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo bar bstan pa'i skabs dang bco brgyad do //
NK053('i)001:118: lung dgu dang bcas lung dgu ni /
NK053('i)001:119: lta ba yang dag ma nor bar gtan la dbab pa'i lung dang gcig /
NK053('i)001:120: sgrub pa rdzas kyi lung dang gnyis /
NK053('i)001:121: dur khrod bdag po ma tram mnan pa'i lung dang gsum /
NK053('i)001:122: dam rdzas dang mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i lung dang bzhi /
NK053('i)001:123: dam tshig dbang gi lung dang lnga /
NK053('i)001:124: yi ge 'khor lo bsnyen pa'i lung dang drug /
NK053('i)001:125: thugs rjes khams gsum bsgral ba'i lung dang bdun /
NK053('i)001:126: mdzad pa phrin las kyi lung dang brgyad /
NK053('i)001:127: bgegs chen mnan pa'i lung dang dagu'o //
NK053('i)001:129: 'chad thabs rgyan lngas spyi khog bstan //
NK053('i)001:130: dmigs pa'i yul dang sgrub par byed pa'i thabs //
NK053('i)001:131: grub pa'i 'bras bu yin te rnam pa gsum //
NK053('i)001:132: bsdus pa'i don ni yin par 'dod //
NK053('i)001:134: 'di nyams su len pa'i gang zag skyes bu blo dang ldan pa dag ni /
NK053('i)001:135: ci dang ci'i bya ba thams cad la /
NK053('i)001:136: shes bzhin gyi rtog pa sngon du gtong ba'i bdag nyid can yin te /
NK053('i)001:142: don gong ma lngas ni man ngag gi mdzes par byed pa'i rgyan /
NK053('i)001:144: bshad thabs kyi yan lag man ngag gi spyi khog tsam du shes par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:145: dgos mi dgos ci rigs su brtag par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:146: bye brag tu bstan na gsum /
NK053('i)001:149: grub pa'i 'bras bu ste 'og ma'i don gsum pos 'di ltar /
NK053('i)001:150: bsgrub par bya ba'am dmigs par bya ba'i yul ni gang /
NK053('i)001:152: sgrub par byed pa'i thabs ni gang /
NK053('i)001:154: bsgrubs pa'i 'bras bu ni gang zhig thob snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:156: dmigs par bya ba'i yul ni /
NK053('i)001:157: zhi ba dpal rdo rje sems dpa' de nyid khros pa dpal chen po'i rang bzhin no //
NK053('i)001:158: sgrub par byed pa'i thabs ni rnam pa gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:162: chos sku longs sku sprul sku sku gsum dang ldan
NK053('i)001:163: pa'i bdag nyid dpal rdo rje sems dpa' de nyid
NK053('i)001:164: las / gdul bya khro bo la mos pa la
NK053('i)001:165: dpal chen po'i rang bzhin du bstan nas mchog thun
NK053('i)001:166: mong gi dngos grub thob pa'o //
NK053('i)001:169: de la thog mar dmigs par bya ba'i yul /
NK053('i)001:170: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' dpal khrag 'thung chen po'i
NK053('i)001:171: rang bzhin ste ji lta bu zhig gi sgo nas
NK053('i)001:176: zhes bya ba yan chad kyi tshig bzhi po 'di la /
NK053('i)001:179: lan gnyis su bshad thabs dkyus gcig la tshig zur gnyis par ston te /
NK053('i)001:180: bdag gzhan gyi don mthar phyin par dmigs par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:181: dkyil 'khor drug gi ngo bor ril por sangs rgyas par bstan pa'o /
NK053('i)001:183: 1 / de la bdag gzhan gyi don mthar phyin par bstan pa'i phyir na /
NK053('i)001:184: yang dag grub pa gcig pu nyid //
NK053('i)001:185: sangs rgyas bde chen kun 'dus pa //
NK053('i)001:186: rnal 'byor zab mo sku gsum rdzogs //
NK053('i)001:187: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog bde //
NK053('i)001:189: de la chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa'i sgo nas yang dag /
NK053('i)001:191: de la blo bur gyi sgrib pa sprin dang 'dra ba dwangs shing byang bar byas te /
NK053('i)001:192: nam mkha'i dbyings dag pa dang 'dra bas na yang dag /
NK053('i)001:194: de rtogs pa'i sgo nas grub pa /
NK053('i)001:196: rig pa'i ye shes kyis chos kyi dbyings rnam par dag pa'i don rtogs pa la grub pa /
NK053('i)001:198: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med par gyur pa la gciga pu nyid /
NK053('i)001:200: de ni phyogs bcu na bzhugs shing dus gsum du
NK053('i)001:201: gshegs pa'i sangs rgyas chos kyi longs spyod dang skyid
NK053('i)001:202: pa ma lus pa nyams su myong ba kun gyi
NK053('i)001:203: rang bzhin yin par bstan pa'i sgo nas /
NK053('i)001:204: sangsa rgyas bde chena kuna 'dus pa //
NK053('i)001:206: chos thams cad kyi de bzhin nyid mnyam pa nyid la snyoms par zhugs shing /
NK053('i)001:207: de las mi g.yo bas rnala 'byor zaba mo //
NK053('i)001:210: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK053('i)001:211: sprul pa'i sku dang sku gsum rdzogs par mnga' ba'i sgo nas sku gsuma rdzogas /
NK053('i)001:213: ye shes dang thugs rjes gzhan don nam mkha'i khams
NK053('i)001:214: su khyab par 'gro zhing don mdzad par ston pa'i
NK053('i)001:215: phyir mkha'a 'gro / zhes gsungs pa yin no //
NK053('i)001:219: brtags na dben pa'i phyir sgyu ma /
NK053('i)001:221: de ltar yang cis mngon na /
NK053('i)001:223: mi rtog dbyings las thugs rje'i chags pas bzhengs //
NK053('i)001:224: cis 'dul der snang yid bzhin rin chen sku //
NK053('i)001:225: gdul bya thabs kyi spyod pas kun 'dul yang //
NK053('i)001:226: btags pa tsam snang brjod med chos kyi dbyings //
NK053('i)001:228: chos kyi dbyings skye ba med pa'i rgyu las thugs rje rkyen gyis bskyed pas ni /
NK053('i)001:229: rgyu rkyen las skyes zhes bya /
NK053('i)001:230: ji ltar 'dul ba de ltar snang bas /
NK053('i)001:232: gdul bya thabs kyi spyod pas re 'dod skong bas ni /
NK053('i)001:234: btags pa tsam du snang gis /
NK053('i)001:235: yang dag par na sku gsung thugs kyi ngo bo la brjod du med pas ni /
NK053('i)001:238: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga mi spong bar spyod pas bde la /
NK053('i)001:239: lha chen po ru tra la ltos na /
NK053('i)001:240: de ltar spyod kyang nyon mongs pa'i mtshan mas mi gos pas na mchoga go //
NK053('i)001:241: klong du gyur pa'i gdengs dang ldan pas ni bde ba'o //
NK053('i)001:244: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' de nyid /
NK053('i)001:245: dpal khrag 'thung chen por gsal bas /
NK053('i)001:246: chos kyi dbyings ye ji bzhin yang dag pa de /
NK053('i)001:247: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis rtogs te /
NK053('i)001:249: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med par gyur pa /
NK053('i)001:251: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas kun gyi rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:252: chos nyid mnyam pa nyid kyi rnal 'byor la snyoms par zhugs shing /
NK053('i)001:253: de las mi g.yo bas sku gsum rdzogs par mnga' bas /
NK053('i)001:254: nyid kyi don phun sum tshogs par lhun gyis grub la /
NK053('i)001:255: ye shes dang thugs rjes 'khor ba ma stongs kyi bar du /
NK053('i)001:256: nam mkha'i mtha' gtugs pa'i sems can gyi rjes su khyab par 'gro zhing /
NK053('i)001:257: sku gsung thugs sgyu ma lta bus /
NK053('i)001:258: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga la zhen cing spyod pa rnams la thabs de nyid kyis 'dul zhing /
NK053('i)001:259: de nyid kyang 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i bde ba
NK053('i)001:260: mchog la spyod cing nyon mongs pa'i mtshan mas mi
NK053('i)001:261: gos par gzhan gyi don mthar phyin par mdzad pa
NK053('i)001:262: de lta bu la dmigs so //
NK053('i)001:265: 2 / de la dkyil 'khor drug gi ngo bor ril sangs rgyas pa ni gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:266: yang dag grub pa gcig pu nyid //
NK053('i)001:267: sangs rgyas bde chen kun 'dus pa //
NK053('i)001:268: rnal 'byor zab mo sku gsum rdzogs //
NK053('i)001:269: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog bde //
NK053('i)001:270: zhes bya ba gsungs pa la /
NK053('i)001:278: yul rang rgyud du snang ngo //
NK053('i)001:282: rna ba'i sna yi lce yi lus kyi kun gzhi'i
NK053('i)001:283: nyon mongs pa can gyi yid kyi rnam shes so
NK053('i)001:284: // de nyid phung po lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:286: 'du shes tshor ba rnam shes 'du byed kyi phung po'o //
NK053('i)001:287: nyon mongs pa lnga zhe sdang /
NK053('i)001:291: phrag dog dang bcas nas snang ngo //
NK053('i)001:292: yul ni 'byung ba chen po lnga'o //
NK053('i)001:298: de lta bas na gzung 'dzin du rang ka mar gyur pa'o //
NK053('i)001:299: de la sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:300: sems can las logs nas mi 'tshol te /
NK053('i)001:301: yul sems can nyid rang grol du 'gro ba rigs drug rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas su bstan te /
NK053('i)001:302: de la yang dag zhes bya /
NK053('i)001:303: rnam shes las sems can gyi lus kyi rnam par shes pa chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes te /
NK053('i)001:304: snang ba thams cad yang dag pa'i chos nyid las ma g.yos pa'i ngang las /
NK053('i)001:305: gzugs snang thams cad rnam par snang mdzad de gti
NK053('i)001:306: mug rang byung chen po ye shes kyi skur gsal
NK053('i)001:307: tsam na yang dag zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:309: lus kyi rnam shes gzugs phung rnam snang mdzad //
NK053('i)001:310: gti mug rang byung yang dag bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:313: sems can gyi rnam shes na /
NK053('i)001:314: sems can kun gyi kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa me long lta bu'i ye shes de /
NK053('i)001:315: dbyings de nyid la dngos po med kyang /
NK053('i)001:316: rang bzhin gyi 'od gsal zhing khyab par rtogs nas /
NK053('i)001:317: chos kyi skur rtogs nas sems so ma yin par
NK053('i)001:318: rnam par shes pa'i phung po rdo rje sems dpa'
NK053('i)001:320: zhe sdang rang byung chen po ye shes kyi skur gsal ba la grub pa zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:322: kun gzhi'i rnam shes mi bskyod rdo rje sems //
NK053('i)001:323: zhe sdang rang byung grub pa bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:328: sems can gyi nyon mongs pa'i yid mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes te /
NK053('i)001:329: dbyings ma 'gags pa rang byung gi rig pa yin la /
NK053('i)001:330: de spros pa dang bral te chos kyi sku gcig
NK053('i)001:331: tu gyur par ro myong ba ni tshor ba'i phung
NK053('i)001:333: nga rgyal rang byung chen po ye shes kyi skur gsal ba la gcig pu nyid ces bya'o //
NK053('i)001:335: nyon mongs rnam shes tshor ba rin chen 'byung //
NK053('i)001:336: nga rgyal rang byung gcig pu bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:338: sangsa rgyas bde chena zhes bya ba /
NK053('i)001:340: gzugs la sogs pa snang ba'i dbang po yid dmigs pa la zhugs pas gzugs gcod /
NK053('i)001:342: sems can gyi yid kyi rnam par shes pa so sor rtog pa'i ye shes te /
NK053('i)001:343: sems can ye nas sangs rgyas te /
NK053('i)001:344: spros pa dang bral ba'i bde ba chen po'i dbyings la yang dag pa'i shes rab kyis bltas na /
NK053('i)001:346: rang gi mtshan nyid so sor ma 'dres par chos
NK053('i)001:347: nyid las ye shes kyi bye brag tu sangs rgyas
NK053('i)001:349: sems can gyi phung po na /
NK053('i)001:350: 'du shes kyi phung po snang ba mtha' yas te /
NK053('i)001:351: 'dod chags rang byung chen po'i ye shes kyi skur gsal ba la sangs rgyas bde chen zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:353: yid kyi rnam shes 'du shes snang mtha' yas //
NK053('i)001:354: 'dod chags rang byung sangs rgyas bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:360: sems can gyi kun gzhi'i rnam par shes pa stong pa nyid kyii ye shes te /
NK053('i)001:361: chos nyid la dngos po dang mtshan ma med par gsal ba'i dbyings su ril 'dus pas /
NK053('i)001:362: dug lnga rang byung gi ye shes te /
NK053('i)001:363: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po nyid do //
NK053('i)001:365: kun gzhi'i rnam shes rang byung dpal chen nyid //
NK053('i)001:366: dug lnga rang byung kun 'dus bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:368: rnala 'byor zaba mo zhes bya ba /
NK053('i)001:370: mig rna ba sna lce lus kyi rnam shes te /
NK053('i)001:371: sems can gyi sgo lnga bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes te /
NK053('i)001:372: chos nyid zab mo nam mkha' dang 'dra ba de /
NK053('i)001:373: ma 'gags pa'i ye shes su gsal ba'i rtags /
NK053('i)001:374: snang srid ye shes kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK053('i)001:376: sangs rgyas par 'dris shing goms par 'du bas /
NK053('i)001:378: 'du byed kyi phung po don yod grub pa ste /
NK053('i)001:380: phrag dog rang byung chen po ye shes kyi skur gsal ba la rnal 'byor zab mo zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:382: sgo lnga'i rnam shes 'du byed don yod grub //
NK053('i)001:383: phrag dog rang byung rnal 'byor bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:387: gong ma'i don de sgrub pa po nyid kyi rgyud la sbyar na /
NK053('i)001:388: shes pa ye thog ma nas ma bcos par bzhag ste /
NK053('i)001:389: yul drug mig gi yul du gzugs sogs 'gre dri ro sgra reg spyi dang drug po la /
NK053('i)001:391: shes pa drug gis ma bzung bar /
NK053('i)001:392: rtog pa med cing spros pa dang bral ba chos
NK053('i)001:393: nyid zab mo nam mkha' ltar rtogs pa ni chos
NK053('i)001:394: kyi sku'o // phung po lnga rigs lnga ye shes lngar shar bas /
NK053('i)001:395: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa la longs spyod pas longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'o //
NK053('i)001:396: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga gang snang yang skyon med
NK053('i)001:397: cing rol par snang bas sprul pa'i sku rdzogs so
NK053('i)001:398: // de ltar yin par cis mngon zhe na /
NK053('i)001:399: byang chub sems rmad du byung ba las /
NK053('i)001:400: bcom ldan 'das rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas la /
NK053('i)001:401: rnam par thar pa'i lam du mnga' /
NK053('i)001:403: sems dpa' chen po nyon cig /
NK053('i)001:405: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la /
NK053('i)001:406: rnam par thar pa'i lam ma nor ba lnga yod de /
NK053('i)001:414: ye nas dag pa chos kyi sku //
NK053('i)001:415: lhun gyis rdzogs pas longs spyod rdzogs //
NK053('i)001:416: cir snang rol ba sprul pa'i sku //
NK053('i)001:419: rtog med mnyam nyid chos kyi sku //
NK053('i)001:420: gzung bas mi zin chu zla 'dra //
NK053('i)001:421: a li ka li thabs shes rab /
NK053('i)001:427: chos dbyings ye shes rnam snang mdzad //
NK053('i)001:428: mnyam nyid ye shes rdo rje nyi ma la //
NK053('i)001:429: rin 'byung so sor rtog pa'i ye shes gar dbang phyug /
NK053('i)001:430: snang ba mtha' yas rta mchog bya ba nan tan gyi ye shes yin no //
NK053('i)001:431: ye shes lnga yi bdag nyid ni //
NK053('i)001:432: zhi ba rdo rje sems dpa' bde ba che //
NK053('i)001:433: khros pa badz+ra he ru ka khrag 'thung me long lta bu'i ye shes so //
NK053('i)001:435: de ltar ni byung zhing snang bar rang byung gi ye shes kyis shes te /
NK053('i)001:436: de yang dge slong sook+sha de bas lta ba la bzlas te gsungs pa /
NK053('i)001:437: kun 'bral ji yang ma spangs pa //
NK053('i)001:438: rdzogs pa chen po'i lta ba yin //
NK053('i)001:439: don rnams lhun gyis grub pa ni //
NK053('i)001:440: bya bral rdzogs chen sgom pa yin //
NK053('i)001:441: bden pa'i lha yang grub pas na //
NK053('i)001:442: sngags kyi lha ni mthu byin che //
NK053('i)001:445: stong min stong bral gnyis su med //
NK053('i)001:446: zab mo nyid la bsgom pa ni //
NK053('i)001:447: dbu ma la yang mi gnas te //
NK053('i)001:448: phyag rgya chen po lha yi tshul //
NK053('i)001:453: shes rab kyis g.yang sa chod par byas la /
NK053('i)001:454: ting nge 'dzin gyis nyams bag tu blangs na /
NK053('i)001:456: yab thabs kyi phyag rgya dpal chen rang bzhin yin lugs /
NK053('i)001:457: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK053('i)001:458: de'i yum 'byung ba chen po gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:459: mkha' 'gro sgyu ma bde mchog bde //
NK053('i)001:461: de yang 'byung ba la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:464: de la snyigs ma'i 'byung ba ni /
NK053('i)001:465: da ltar sems can gyis btags pa'i 'byung ba lnga'o //
NK053('i)001:467: de nyid rang grol du ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro ma drug gi rang bzhin du sangs rgyas te /
NK053('i)001:468: de yang ji ltar sangs rgyas zhe na /
NK053('i)001:469: snyigs ma'i 'byung ba rtog bcas kyi sems dang 'byung ba nam mkha' ltar snang ba nyid /
NK053('i)001:470: rtog med du ye nas ma bcos par chos kyi
NK053('i)001:471: sku'i ngang du gsal zhing kun la khyab bdal bas
NK053('i)001:472: sems dang 'byung ba nam mkha' snang ba ston pa'i
NK053('i)001:473: yum kun tu bzang mo rdo rje rigs kyi mkha'a
NK053('i)001:474: 'gro ma rdo rje dbyings phyug mar snang la rang
NK053('i)001:475: bzhin med par sangs rgyas so //
NK053('i)001:477: sems can rtog bcas kyi sha dang rus pa ltar snang ba rtog med du gsal bas /
NK053('i)001:478: sha rus ltar snang ba ril bskyed rten byed pas yum sangs rgyas spyan te /
NK053('i)001:479: de bzhin rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:480: snyigs ma'i 'byung ba sems can gyi rtog bcas kyi khrag dang chu ltar snang ba /
NK053('i)001:481: rtog med du gsal bas thugs rje rlan sdud m+aa ma k+ai ste /
NK053('i)001:482: rin po che rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:483: snyigs ma'i 'byung ba sems can gyi rtog bcas kyi
NK053('i)001:484: drod dang mer snang ba rtog med du gsal bas
NK053('i)001:485: / thugs rjes smin cing brtas byed yum gos dkar mo ste /
NK053('i)001:486: pad+ma rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:487: snyigs ma'i 'byung ba rtog bcas kyi dbugs dang rlung ltar snang ba /
NK053('i)001:488: thugs rjes yang zhing g.yo byed 'degs par byed pas /
NK053('i)001:489: yum dam tshig sgrol ma ste /
NK053('i)001:490: las kyi rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:491: snyigs ma'i 'byung ba lnga ril sems can gyi rtog
NK053('i)001:492: bcas kyi bkrag dang mdangs dbugs kyis bsdus pa rtog
NK053('i)001:493: med chos nyid du gsal bas /
NK053('i)001:494: 'gro ba dang 'ong ba dang gnas pa kun gyi
NK053('i)001:495: gzhi khros pa'i dus na yum kro ti shwa ri
NK053('i)001:496: ma ste / de ltar 'byung ba chen po lnga
NK053('i)001:497: po 'di la 'khor 'das thams cad mi gnas pa
NK053('i)001:498: ma ste / dang / des ma bskyed pa gang yang med de /
NK053('i)001:499: 'byung ba lnga yang don gyi rigs kyi yum lnga /
NK053('i)001:500: yum lnga po yang kun tu bzang mo de nyid kro ti shwa ri ma zhes bya ste /
NK053('i)001:501: yum de'i mkha' chos kyi dbyings kyi gzhal yas khang /
NK053('i)001:502: skyon gyis ma gos pa pad+ma ge sar gyi klong
NK053('i)001:503: du rigs lnga ye shes lnga po de nyid dpal
NK053('i)001:504: chen po ye shes kyi thig le dkyil 'khor dang
NK053('i)001:505: bcas pa yang / yum gyi mkha' 'dir sngar yang mya ngan las 'das /
NK053('i)001:506: da ltar bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas gzugs sku zhal gnyis pa yang /
NK053('i)001:507: yum gyi mkha' 'di dang dbyer med par bzhugs /
NK053('i)001:508: slad kyi byon pa'i sangs rgyas ril yang mkha' 'dir brgyud de byon pas /
NK053('i)001:509: 'on kyang chos nyid yum gyi mkha' 'di ni rgyal ba ril gyi gdung la /
NK053('i)001:512: ye shes tha dad par rol pas yum gyi mkha' 'o //
NK053('i)001:513: de ltar yang cis mngon zhe na /
NK053('i)001:515: snyigs ma'i 'byung ba lnga ni sems can gyis btags pa'i 'byung ba ste //
NK053('i)001:516: de nyid gnyis med rang bzhin gyis dag dwangs ma'i 'byung ba lnga //
NK053('i)001:517: ma bcos don gyis rigs kyi mkha' 'gro ma //
NK053('i)001:518: 'byung ba chen po lnga nyid kro ti shwa ri'i mkha' //
NK053('i)001:520: rmad du byung ba las kyang /
NK053('i)001:521: 'byung ba chen po lnga ni sku lnga lhun gyis rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor nyid do //
NK053('i)001:522: chen po lnga'i dwangs ma ni /
NK053('i)001:523: byang chub kyi sems rmad du byung ba thig le nyag gcig nyod do //
NK053('i)001:524: dwangs ma de gsal ba'i snying po ni /
NK053('i)001:525: shin tu brtag dka' ba de nyid ye shes te thugs nyid du gyur pa nyid do //
NK053('i)001:528: 'byung ba chen po lnga bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:529: yin te 'gro ba sems can kun la yang 'byung
NK053('i)001:530: ba lnga las lus 'di grub pas rang bzhin gnas
NK053('i)001:533: de la sgyu ma zhes pa la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:535: 'byung ba lnga po 'di dang 'dis bskyed pa'i sems
NK053('i)001:536: can kun mi rtag pa tsam du kun rdzob sgyu
NK053('i)001:537: mar mthong la / de bas gsang sngags khyad che ste /
NK053('i)001:538: lhar bsgyur nas snang la rang bzhin med pa tsam sgyu mar mthong la /
NK053('i)001:539: de bas kyang rdzogs pa chen po khyad che ste /
NK053('i)001:540: gzhi la gnyis med du lhun grub sgyu mar mthong zhing spyod pas /
NK053('i)001:541: rim pas spags shing khyad yod pas shes rab kyis
NK053('i)001:542: g.yang sa chod pas thag chod byas nas ting nge
NK053('i)001:543: 'dzin la longs spyod par shes na /
NK053('i)001:544: ji ltar 'dod par dbang bsgyur bas na sgyu ma'o //
NK053('i)001:545: de yang nam mkha' che las /
NK053('i)001:546: sgyu ma lhun grub yul la rol //
NK053('i)001:549: rang bzhin gcig tu ma nges par //
NK053('i)001:550: ji ltar bltas pas de ltar snang //
NK053('i)001:553: sgyu ma zhes pa 'byung ba lnga nyid chos nyid
NK053('i)001:554: kun tu bzang mo'i mkha' klong rnam par dag pa
NK053('i)001:555: / skye ba med pa'i mkha' las /
NK053('i)001:556: skye ba'i cho 'phrul ji lta bu'i ngo bor yang shar zhing ji ltar snang yang snang ste /
NK053('i)001:557: zhi ba'i lha mo lta bu dang /
NK053('i)001:558: khro bo mo lta bu dang /
NK053('i)001:559: gnod sbyin mo lta bu dang /
NK053('i)001:560: rigs drug rdzogs pa'i yum bud med la sogs pa'i cha lugs su yang shar zhing snang ste /
NK053('i)001:562: ci yang med pa las sgyu ma'i mkhan pos ci
NK053('i)001:563: la yang sgyu ma'i gzugs su bsgyur du gtub pa
NK053('i)001:565: don chos nyid yum gyi mkha' skye ba med pa'i don rtogs na /
NK053('i)001:566: rtags rig pa'i ye shes skye ba'i cho 'phrul ji ltar yang snang ngo //
NK053('i)001:568: rang gi ngo bos yongs bsgyur na //
NK053('i)001:569: bud med kun gyi sgyu mas 'grub //
NK053('i)001:570: sna tshogs sgyu ma'i phyag rgya 'di //
NK053('i)001:571: mkha' 'gro ma zhes brdar bstan to //
NK053('i)001:573: shes rab dang ting 'dzin yo byad gnyis la longs spyod pa'i rnal 'byor pas /
NK053('i)001:577: chos nyid yum gyi mkha' klong 'di las bskyed la /
NK053('i)001:578: spyan drangs shing bzhugs su gsol na yang /
NK053('i)001:579: chos nyid yum gyi mkha' 'di las spyan drangs shing
NK053('i)001:580: chos nyid yum gyi mkha' 'di'i ngang la bzhugs su
NK053('i)001:581: gsol / mchod pa 'bul zhing ar+g+ham sbreng na yang /
NK053('i)001:582: chos nyid yum gyi mkha' 'dir sbreng /
NK053('i)001:583: bsod nams spel zhing tshe dgug na yang /
NK053('i)001:584: yum gyi mkha' 'dir spel zhing dgug /
NK053('i)001:585: slob ma byin gyis brlabs shing dbang bskur na yang /
NK053('i)001:586: yum 'di'i mkha' nas byin gyis brlabs shing dbang bskur /
NK053('i)001:587: dgra bgegs dgug cing bsgral na yang /
NK053('i)001:588: chos nyid yum gyi mkha' 'dir dgug cing bsgral /
NK053('i)001:589: de la ji ltar spyad cing snang ba yang /
NK053('i)001:590: de nyid la dngos po dang mtshan mar mi 'dzin cing /
NK053('i)001:591: skye 'gag tu mi dmigs pa'i shes rab kyis bzung ba ni /
NK053('i)001:595: gang ltar bde ba spyod pa'i mchog /
NK053('i)001:596: mtshan mar mi 'dzin bde ba'i lam //
NK053('i)001:599: mtha' drug las thag lta bas gcod pa'o //
NK053('i)001:600: lung dgu las snang srid sangs rgyas mkha' 'gro'i lung
NK053('i)001:601: ste lta ba yang dag ma nor bar gtan la
NK053('i)001:603: yo byad gnyis las shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin gnyis ka'o //
NK053('i)001:604: dal dgu las dang po rang bzhiin gyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK053('i)001:605: skabs sbyor bco brgyad las dang po dpal chen po'i rang bzhin bstan pa'i skabs so //
NK053('i)001:607: sgrub par byed pa'i thabs la rnam pa gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:609: thabs kyi ngo bo bstan pa'o /
NK053('i)001:611: 1 / thabs kyi yan lag la don lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:612: snod ji lta bu la bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:618: snod ji lta bu zhig la 1bstan snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:619: skabs sbyor bco brgyad la gnyis pa lung bstan pa slob ma'i skabs /
NK053('i)001:620: shes rab kyis ni blo phyes nas //
NK053('i)001:621: nges par brtags pa'i sa gzhi la //
NK053('i)001:622: bla mas nges pa'i lung 'di bstan //
NK053('i)001:624: shesa raba ni rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:629: blo la yang rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:637: snod rnam pa bzhi'i blo kha dbye ste /
NK053('i)001:639: mnyan pa'i shes rab la brtson pas /
NK053('i)001:640: snod dug can dang 'dra ba'i blo kha dbye /
NK053('i)001:641: bsam pa'i shes rab la nan tan du gyur pas /
NK053('i)001:642: snod khas sbubs dang 'dra ba'i blo kha dbye /
NK053('i)001:643: sgom pa'i shes rab la sbyangs pas /
NK053('i)001:644: snod 'phred nyal dag 'dra ba'i blo kha dbye /
NK053('i)001:645: gsang ba'i shes rab la gnas na gsang thub cing barlinga pas /
NK053('i)001:646: snod zhabs rdol dang 'dra ba'i blo kha dbye /
NK053('i)001:647: de ltar shes rab rnam pa bzhis /
NK053('i)001:648: snod rnam pa bzhi'i blo kha phyes nasa /
NK053('i)001:649: ngasa para ba rtag pa ni bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:650: rigs nges par brtag pa dang /
NK053('i)001:651: yul nges par brtag pa dang /
NK053('i)001:652: dad pa nges par brtag pa dang /
NK053('i)001:653: shes rab nges par brtag pa'o //
NK053('i)001:654: de la dang por rigs nges par brtag ste /
NK053('i)001:656: rje rigs las nges par skyes pa'o //
NK053('i)001:658: rigs bzang bas ngo tsha la 'dzem /
NK053('i)001:659: de nas yul nges par brtag pa ni /
NK053('i)001:660: snod mi gzhi bzang pos ngan pa'i las mi byed
NK053('i)001:661: cing ngo tsha shes pas bzang po'i las nges par
NK053('i)001:662: byed pa'o // de nas dad pa nges par brtag pa ni /
NK053('i)001:663: lus dang srog la yang mi phongs par chos phyir nges par gtong sems yod pa'o //
NK053('i)001:664: de nas shes rab nges par brtag pa ni /
NK053('i)001:665: gang bstan pa'i don nges par shes shing rtogs par nges pa'o //
NK053('i)001:666: de ni dper na sa gzhi gshin pa nges par brtags pa la /
NK053('i)001:667: sa bon gang btab pa 'bras bu nges par dus su 'byung ba dang 'dra bar /
NK053('i)001:668: snod nges par brtag pa'i slob ma sa gzhi gshin pa dang 'dra ba la /
NK053('i)001:669: gang zag kun nas blar gyur pa'i bla ma rdo rje slob dpon gyis /
NK053('i)001:670: ngesa pa'i don gyi gsang rgyud kyi bcud blangs pa'i man ngag /
NK053('i)001:672: nges pa'i lunga gi sgrub thabs /
NK053('i)001:675: bla na med pa'i byang chub kyi 'bras bu thob par bya ba'i phyir bstan to //
NK053('i)001:677: de la thog mar 2dam tshig bstan pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:679: gsang sngags kyi mtha' drug las dang po gzhi dam tshig ston /
NK053('i)001:680: yo byad gnyis las shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin gnyis pa'o //
NK053('i)001:681: skabs sbyor gsum pa sgrub pa po rnams brtul zhugs
NK053('i)001:682: kyi khyad par dang dam tshig bstan pa'i skabs so
NK053('i)001:683: // snum pa yi ni dam tshig dang //
NK053('i)001:686: snum pa yi ni zhes bya ba /
NK053('i)001:687: dper na snum gyis lus skye ba'i bcud dam gzhir gyur pa dang 'dra bar /
NK053('i)001:688: de bzhin du dam tshig snum lta bu la brten nas /
NK053('i)001:689: rnam par byang ba'i phyogs kyi dge ba thams cad skye bar 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:691: gzhi 'dzin dam tshig snum 'dra rin po che //
NK053('i)001:692: ma rig tha rgod ko khengs lta bu brtul //
NK053('i)001:693: yang dag don ston sems dang chos su 'dres //
NK053('i)001:694: lus dang srog la bab kyang dam tshig mchog mi spong //
NK053('i)001:695: de la gnas na rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen por 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:697: de yang gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i lugs kyis gzhi dam tshig gis bzung ba'i lung bstan te /
NK053('i)001:699: dama tshiga ces bya ba la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:704: bsrung bar sems pa'i rgyun ma chad pa'o //
NK053('i)001:706: bsrung bya de la 'da' bar bya ba ma yin la /
NK053('i)001:707: de las 'das na tshig par dam tshig ces bya'o //
NK053('i)001:711: byang chub sems kyi dam tshig go //
NK053('i)001:712: de la rtsa ba gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:713: sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig go //
NK053('i)001:715: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK053('i)001:716: spyi dang 'dren dang dam tshig dbang //
NK053('i)001:717: shes rgyud 'grol dang nyams chag skong //
NK053('i)001:718: man ngag lung gi slo dpon rnams //
NK053('i)001:724: ngan sems dang dpya sems tsam yang mi bskyed par bya ba yin na /
NK053('i)001:726: gnod pa dngos su byed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:727: 'khu zhing ldog pa lta ci smos te /
NK053('i)001:729: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon lam dang pha dang /
NK053('i)001:730: mig gi 'bras bu bas kyang lhag cing /
NK053('i)001:731: sangs rgyas bzhin du bkur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:732: bla ma'i bka' zur yang mi bcag pa dang /
NK053('i)001:733: mnyes pa rnam pa gsum rab shes rab rgyud /
NK053('i)001:735: tha ma zang zing nor gyis mnyes par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:736: bla ma des phog pa'i lha dang srung ma mi spang zhing /
NK053('i)001:739: mched dang lcam dral la rdo rje'i spun dang ming sring du blta zhing /
NK053('i)001:740: brtse gdung breng ma chad par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:741: de la gsung gi dam tshig ni /
NK053('i)001:742: yi dam lha yi sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun mi bcag pa ste /
NK053('i)001:743: de yang sngags la bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:744: rgyu ma nor brtsa ba'i sngags yi ge h+aum lta bu dang /
NK053('i)001:745: bskyed pa'i sngags badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:746: badz+ra sa ha kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:748: bzlas pa las kyi sngags ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:750: bskul ba phrin las kyi sngags h'u h'u bi shwa sogs khro bo 'chol bar spro ba /
NK053('i)001:753: phyag rgya la yang bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:754: gtso bo'i sku'i phyag rgya lha sku dang /
NK053('i)001:755: gzungs ma dam tshig gi phyag rgya yum bsgom pa dang /
NK053('i)001:756: thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' bsgom zhing bzlas pa byed pa chos kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK053('i)001:757: 'od zer phar 'phro tshur 'du las kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK053('i)001:758: de la rnal 'byor pas nyams bag du bya ba'i dus nas /
NK053('i)001:759: bdag lha yab yum gnyis su med pa'i skur gsal
NK053('i)001:760: ba ra bsgom pa ni bdag gi de kho na
NK053('i)001:761: nyid dang / thugs kar ye shes sems dpa' la
NK053('i)001:762: thugs phyag mtshan la bzlas pa'i yi ges mtshan par
NK053('i)001:763: bsam pa ni thugs phyag mtshan gyi de kho na
NK053('i)001:764: nyid dang / nyid dang / bzlas pa'i yi ge
NK053('i)001:765: las 'od byung bar bsam zhing bzlas pa ni bzlas
NK053('i)001:766: brjod kyi de kho na nyid dang /
NK053('i)001:767: bdun gyi nam mkha' ye shes sems dpa' gsal ba ni lha'i de kho na nyid dang /
NK053('i)001:768: de dang gnyis 'phro 'du bya zhing bzlas pa bya ba ni 'phro 'du'i de kho na nyid dang /
NK053('i)001:769: de kho na nyid lnga dang ldan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:771: rab kyis chu bo'i rgyun bzhin mi bcad /
NK053('i)001:772: 'bring gis zhag re la nyin stong mtshan stong dang mchod pa re /
NK053('i)001:774: tha ma bas zla ba re re la /
NK053('i)001:778: bsnyen pa dang mchod pa gzhung bzhin du bya'o //
NK053('i)001:784: zla ba ra ba bzhi la bsnyen mchod re re bya'o //
NK053('i)001:785: tha ma de yang ma grub na lo re la
NK053('i)001:786: dam bcas pa'i bsnyen mchod re re 'grub tshad du
NK053('i)001:787: bya'o // de ma grub na gsung gi dam tshig nyams par 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:790: sgrub pa'i dus gsang ba dang /
NK053('i)001:791: sgrub pa'i gnas gsang ba dang /
NK053('i)001:795: dkyil 'khor gsang ba 'di 'dra ba zhig zhal phye bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:796: cho ga gsang ba 'di tshug byed bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:797: phyag rgya gsang ba 'di ltar 'cha' bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:798: sngags gsang ba 'di skad zlos bya ba'o //
NK053('i)001:802: dpon mched kyi ngan skyon dang /
NK053('i)001:803: ma legs pa'i skyon thams cad gsang ba'o //
NK053('i)001:804: gsang bar gnyer gtad pa ni /
NK053('i)001:805: slob dpon gyis gnyer bsgo ba'i gsang tshig rnams so //
NK053('i)001:806: 'di rnams gsongs shig gsung ba lta bu'o //
NK053('i)001:809: dam tshig mchog ni 'dir bzung ba //
NK053('i)001:811: bla ma spun mched grogs yi dam lha srung dang //
NK053('i)001:812: gsung gi dam tshig sngags dang phyag rgya thugs kyi dam tshig gsang tshig rnams //
NK053('i)001:814: dbang rgyud man ngag gnang ba'i bla ma bkur dang /
NK053('i)001:815: yi dam lha srung mi spang grogs bzhi la byams pa dang //
NK053('i)001:816: sngags gsum dang phyag rgya bzhi rgyun mi bcad cing gsang bcu spel mi bya //
NK053('i)001:817: 'di ni rtsa ba'i dam tshig yin //
NK053('i)001:819: yan lag gi dam tshig la yang lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:820: mi spang ba'i dam tshig lnga dang /
NK053('i)001:821: dang du blang ba lnga dang /
NK053('i)001:826: gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg pa 'di yi gzhung gis //
NK053('i)001:827: mi spang ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK053('i)001:828: gti mug chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes chos sku dang /
NK053('i)001:829: zhe sdang me long lta bu'i ye shes ngo bo nyid sku dang /
NK053('i)001:830: nga rgyal mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes longs sku dang /
NK053('i)001:831: 'dod chags so sor rtog pa'i ye shes gsang ba'i sku dang /
NK053('i)001:832: phrag dog bya ba grub pa'i ye shes sprul sku dang lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:833: ye gdod ma nas sku rnam pa lnga 'am ye
NK053('i)001:834: shes lnga'i ngo bo yin pas mi spang ba dang
NK053('i)001:835: / dang du blang ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK053('i)001:836: dri chen rnam par snang mdzad kyi dam rdzas ye shes chos dbyings dang /
NK053('i)001:837: byang chub sems rdo rje sems dpa'i dam rdzas ye shes me long lta bu dang /
NK053('i)001:838: sha chen rin chen 'byung ldan ye shes mnyam nyid dang /
NK053('i)001:839: rak+ta snang ba mtha' yas ye shes sor rtog dang /
NK053('i)001:840: dri chu don grub ye shes bya grub lnga ni /
NK053('i)001:841: rigs lnga ye shes lnga yi ngo bo yin pas na mi dor bar bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:842: spyad par bya ba'i dam tshig lnga ni /
NK053('i)001:843: pad+ma'i rigs kyi dam tshig sbyor ba dang /
NK053('i)001:844: rdo rje'i rigs kyi dam tshig sgrol ba dang /
NK053('i)001:845: rin po che'i rigs kyi dam tshig ma byin par len pa dang /
NK053('i)001:846: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dam tshig rdzun du smra ba dang /
NK053('i)001:847: las kyi rigs kyi dam tshig tshig rlang por smra
NK053('i)001:848: ba lnga ni gong du bstan pa bzhin spyod pa
NK053('i)001:849: yin pas spyad par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:850: shes par bya ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK053('i)001:851: phung po lnga rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas /
NK053('i)001:852: gzugs kyi phung po rnam snang /
NK053('i)001:853: rnam par shes pa'i phung po mi bskyod pa /
NK053('i)001:855: 'du shes phung po snang ba mtha' yas /
NK053('i)001:856: 'du byed kyi phung po don yod grub pa'o //
NK053('i)001:857: 'byung ba lnga rigs kyi yum lnga /
NK053('i)001:858: nam mkha' rdo rje dbyings phyug mar /
NK053('i)001:863: rnam par shes pa brgyad sems dpa' brgyad /
NK053('i)001:864: mig gi rnam shes sa yi snying po /
NK053('i)001:865: rna ba'i rnam shes nam mkha'i snying po /
NK053('i)001:866: sna'i rnam shes spyan ras gzigs /
NK053('i)001:868: mig gi dbang po byams pa /
NK053('i)001:869: rna ba'i dbang po sgrib sel /
NK053('i)001:871: lce yi dbang po 'jam dpal lo //
NK053('i)001:873: mig gi yul gzugs l+aa s+ye ma /
NK053('i)001:874: rna ba'i yul sgra m+aa l+ye ma /
NK053('i)001:876: lce'i yul ro n+ai rti ma /
NK053('i)001:880: 'byung ba ma nges pa gan+d+he ma'o //
NK053('i)001:881: khams dang skye mched gzhan yang lha dang lha mor shes pa ste /
NK053('i)001:882: lus kyi reg pa sgo ba rnam par rgyal ba /
NK053('i)001:886: yul sgo ma rtag par ma yin pa lcags kyu ma /
NK053('i)001:887: chad par ma yin pa zhags pa ma /
NK053('i)001:888: bdag tu ma yin pa lcags sgrog ma /
NK053('i)001:889: mtshan mar ma yin pa dril bu ma'o //
NK053('i)001:890: nyon mongs pa drug thub pa drug go //
NK053('i)001:891: bsgrub par bya ba'i dam tshig ni /
NK053('i)001:897: phyi nang snod bcud ril ye nas ma bcos par rigs lngar lhun gyis grub pa'o //
NK053('i)001:899: mi spang ba dang dang du blang //
NK053('i)001:900: spyad par bya dang shes pa dang //
NK053('i)001:901: bsgrub par bya ba'i dam tshig gis //
NK053('i)001:902: chos dang sems su 'dres pa na //
NK053('i)001:903: de las mi 'da' dam tshig yin //
NK053('i)001:905: byang chub sems kyi dam tshig ni /
NK053('i)001:906: chos thams cad kyi srog ni dam tshig /
NK053('i)001:907: dam tshig gi srog lta ba /
NK053('i)001:910: man gang gi srog sgom pa /
NK053('i)001:911: sgom pa'i srog ma yengs pa /
NK053('i)001:912: ma yengs pa'i srog gdengs su gyur pa ste /
NK053('i)001:913: gdengs su gyur pa'i dus na /
NK053('i)001:914: dam tshig thams cad 'di bzhir 'dus par bstan te /
NK053('i)001:915: sems nyid skye med yin pas med pa dang /
NK053('i)001:916: rol pa ma 'gags pas phyal ba dang /
NK053('i)001:917: thig le nyag gcig tu 'dus pas gcig pu nyid dang /
NK053('i)001:918: ye nas lhun gyis grub pa dang bzhir la bazla'o //
NK053('i)001:920: dang po gsang sngags kyi sgor nges par 'jug par 'dod pa rnams kyis /
NK053('i)001:921: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon don du gnyer nas /
NK053('i)001:922: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor du dam tshig tshul bzhin du blangs nas /
NK053('i)001:924: 'das na tshig cing brlag par 'gyur pas /
NK053('i)001:926: gang nyams pa de ma thag tu bskang zhing gso ba'i cho ga bya zhes /
NK053('i)001:927: gsang ba'i rgyud sde dang grub pa thob pa'i bla ma rnams kyis gsungs so //
NK053('i)001:931: dam tshig rjes su gtsang sbra bsdu //
NK053('i)001:934: gatsanga dang 3zhes bya bas bstan te /
NK053('i)001:935: de la gtsang sbra ni rnam pa gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:936: pho nya'i gtsang sbra thun mong gi sid+d+hi la mi dmigs par mchog gi don du gnyer ba dang /
NK053('i)001:937: sbyor ba'i gtsang sbra yum gyi mkha' gsang byin gyis barloba pa la sogs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:938: zas gcig tu za ba'i gtsang sbra'o //
NK053('i)001:939: zas mthun pas dam rdzas bdud rtsi lnga la gtsang dme med pa'i don yin te bshad gsung ngo //
NK053('i)001:942: gtsang sbra gsum du shes bya zhing //
NK053('i)001:943: rigs dang rin ngor mi blta ba //
NK053('i)001:944: pho nya'i gtsang sbra dang po yin //
NK053('i)001:945: dper na rgyal po'i pho nya ni /
NK053('i)001:946: las gang la btang ba der rang gi rigs kyi
NK053('i)001:947: ngor dang gzhan gyi rigs kyi ngor mi lta bar
NK053('i)001:949: 'dir yang rnal 'byor pas bsnyen pa'i brtul zhugs byed
NK053('i)001:950: pa ni bya ba gzhan dang rang gi rigs dang
NK053('i)001:951: rin ngor mi lta bar don sgrub pa'o //
NK053('i)001:952: gnyis pa sbyor ba yin par 'dod //
NK053('i)001:953: zas gcig tu ni za ba nyid //
NK053('i)001:954: gtsang sbra gsum pa yin par 'dod //
NK053('i)001:955: gtsang sbra 'di dag rab bskyongs pas //
NK053('i)001:956: gtsang ma dag pa'i rim thob na //
NK053('i)001:959: gtsang sbra gsum la gnas par bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:964: lta ba ngan pa rnams 'jigas shing skrag pa la gsang bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:965: dad pa yod pa'i sngags pas /
NK053('i)001:967: dang por bla ma rdo rje slob dpon la /
NK053('i)001:968: gong ma lta bu'i dam tshig dang /
NK053('i)001:969: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:970: brtul zhugs tshul bzhin du mnod do //
NK053('i)001:973: dben pa'i gnas su bla ma la //
NK053('i)001:974: dam tshig dbang gi brtul zhugs blang //
NK053('i)001:977: bsnyen sgrub kyi brtul zhugsa te /
NK053('i)001:979: thig le zla gam gcig pu ru //
NK053('i)001:980: dmigs rten mngon par bzhag nas su //
NK053('i)001:981: sems nyid gnas par ma gyur bar //
NK053('i)001:982: bzlas pa mthar dbyung sbyin bsreg bya //
NK053('i)001:984: man+dala thig le gcig pa dang /
NK053('i)001:986: yi dam gyi lha'i sku gzugs ris su bris pa'am
NK053('i)001:987: lugs su blugs pa'am 'bur du gtod pa legs par
NK053('i)001:988: byas pas / man+dala du bzhugs su gsol la /
NK053('i)001:989: de'i spyan sngar rnal 'byor pa 'dug ste /
NK053('i)001:991: bsod nams bsags pa'i las byas nas /
NK053('i)001:992: yi dam gyi lha bsgom par bya ba yang /
NK053('i)001:994: khams kyi ngo bo thams cad dang //
NK053('i)001:995: de bzhin srog dang rtsol las byung //
NK053('i)001:996: rang gi lha yi cha byad du //
NK053('i)001:997: sgrub pa'i phyag rgya rab tu byang //
NK053('i)001:999: yi dam gyi lha bsgom pa yang /
NK053('i)001:1000: don dam dang kun rdzob gnyis kyi sgo nas te /
NK053('i)001:1006: chos nyid ma byung ma skyes pa /
NK053('i)001:1007: ye nas dag pa'i ngo bo nyid du gsal bas /
NK053('i)001:1008: nyon mongs pa ril chos nyid mi rtog pa'i ngang du brtul te /
NK053('i)001:1009: ci la'ang mi rtog mi sems te /
NK053('i)001:1010: chos nyid stong pa nyid du gsal pas /
NK053('i)001:1011: rang gi shes rgyud dag par sbyang ba dang /
NK053('i)001:1012: de'i ngang ngam shugs las srog gang na gnas pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1014: rlung phyi rgyu dbugs kyi rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:1016: dpal khrag 'thung chen po'i ting nge 'dzin zhi khro'i cha byad cana du bsgom par bya ba yang /
NK053('i)001:1017: sngar gyi sku gzung ji lta ba bzhin du bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:1018: de la gsal bar gyur pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1019: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing bstims nas /
NK053('i)001:1020: sku gzugs la mchod pa byas nas /
NK053('i)001:1021: bzlas pa'ang de nyid kyi spyan sngar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1022: bsnyen pa la sems 'byongs par gyur pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1023: rab tu dben pa'i gnas su /
NK053('i)001:1024: rnal 'byor pa chen po'i spyod pa shin tu'ang chen por spyad de /
NK053('i)001:1025: zhi ba'i rgyan dag cha lugs dbu rgyan stod g.yogs la sogs dang /
NK053('i)001:1026: khro bo'i rgyan dang mtshan mas dur khrod kyi chas
NK053('i)001:1027: brgyad la sogs kyis rang gi lus la legs par
NK053('i)001:1028: brgyan nas / bzlas pa drag tu bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1029: de ni bsnyen pa dag nye ba'i bsnyen pa'i man ngag ste /
NK053('i)001:1030: dus de nyid du zas lnga sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga /
NK053('i)001:1031: bza' zhing rtog pa dang dbral lo //
NK053('i)001:1032: de ltar brtul zhugs spyad na lhas byin gyis barloba cing /
NK053('i)001:1033: 'go ba'i byin rlabs kyi mtshan ma 'byung ngo //
NK053('i)001:1036: brtul zhugs de daga gong du bsgomas par byas la /
NK053('i)001:1037: de nasa gdod sgrub pa nyamsa su lena pa bsnyen sgrub la 'jug par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1039: de dag goms nas nyams su blang //
NK053('i)001:1041: snod dang 5mi ldan pa la bstan na nyes dmigs ji lta bu 'byung snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:1042: skabs sbyor bzhi pa slob ma snod dang mi ldan
NK053('i)001:1043: pa la slob dpon gyis bstan na gnyis ka dmyal
NK053('i)001:1045: blo zhan shes rab chung bas ni //
NK053('i)001:1047: phung byed gnyis ka bsregs pas na //
NK053('i)001:1048: de bas gzhan du bstan pa min //
NK053('i)001:1050: de la blo zhana pas ni /
NK053('i)001:1051: rmad du byung ba'i spyod pa la 'jug mi nus /
NK053('i)001:1053: gsang sngags kyi dgongs pa 'og ma las spags pa'i don dang mi ldan zhing /
NK053('i)001:1055: 'di'i don bsgrub kyanga 'grub para mi 'gyur te /
NK053('i)001:1056: gal te bsgrubs su zin na yang phung bar byed do //
NK053('i)001:1057: 'jig rten 'dir yang nad mang zhing tshe thung la /
NK053('i)001:1058: phyi mar dmyal bar ltung nas /
NK053('i)001:1059: slob dpon dang slob bu gnyis ka bsregas dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal ba dang /
NK053('i)001:1060: sgrib pa la stsogs pa yi dwags kyi sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar 'gyur basa na /
NK053('i)001:1061: gong ma lta bu'i sgrub pa po /
NK053('i)001:1063: brtul zhugs can gyi sgrub pa po las ma gtogs pa /
NK053('i)001:1066: shes rab chung ba la bstana cing bshad para bya ba ma yin no //
NK053('i)001:1069: 2 / thabs kyi ngo bo bstan pa la don bzhis bstan te /
NK053('i)001:1070: phun sum tshogs pa bzhi dang ldan pas sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1071: rdzas brtag cing btsal ba dang /
NK053('i)001:1072: sa gzhi brtag cing sa chog bya bar bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1073: phrin las kyi rim par bsgrub pa chen po'i gzhung bsrang ba'o //
NK053('i)001:1074: de la 1phun sum tshogs pa bzhi dang ldan pas sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pa bstan pa yang /
NK053('i)001:1076: dkyus gcig pa la zur gnyis par ston te /
NK053('i)001:1077: spyi'i man ngag gi sdom bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1078: khyad par du dgos pa'i sgos gdab pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1079: de la spyi'i man ngag gi sdom bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:1080: skabs sbyor lnga pa yo byad rdzas dang sa gzhi brtag par bstan pa'i skabs /
NK053('i)001:1081: phun sum tshogs pa bzhir ldan nas //
NK053('i)001:1082: zhes pas bstan pa la don bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:1087: de la lta ba phun sum tshogs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:1089: dri ma spangs pa'i man ngag bshad do //
NK053('i)001:1091: sbyor sgrol gnyis kyi man ngag bshad /
NK053('i)001:1093: zhi khro gnyis kyi man ngag bshad /
NK053('i)001:1097: byang chub sems kyi dam tshig bshad de /
NK053('i)001:1099: lta ba spyod pa mthar phyin cing //
NK053('i)001:1100: phrin las dam tshig ldan par bsgrub //
NK053('i)001:1102: khyad par du dgos pa'i sgos gdab pa ni gang snyam pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1103: phun sum tshogsa pa bzhir ldan nas //
NK053('i)001:1104: zhes gsungs pa la don bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:1105: shes pa phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1107: gnas phun sum tshogs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1108: yo byad phun sum tshogs pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1109: de la shes pa phun sum tshogs pa la yang bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:1110: rdo rje slob dpon lung dang man ngag shes pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1111: yum mi 'khrug sbyor ba'i sgyu rtsal shes pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1112: ging g.yog gtsug lag gi brda' shes pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1113: 'khor las dang phyag rgya'i brda' shes pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1114: de la slob dpon lung dang man ngag shes pa la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:1119: mngon par shes pa lnga dang ldan zhing /
NK053('i)001:1120: shes bya rig pa'i gnas lnga bzo rig pa /
NK053('i)001:1124: nang don rig pa la mkhas pa'i ma h+aa pan+di ta chen po'o //
NK053('i)001:1126: tan+t+ra sde bco brgyad sku'i rgyud sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor /
NK053('i)001:1127: gsung gi rgyud zla gsang thig le /
NK053('i)001:1128: thugs kyi rgud gsang ba 'dus pa /
NK053('i)001:1129: phrin las kyi rgyud karma m+aa le /
NK053('i)001:1130: yon tan gyi rgyud phreng ba dam pa la sogs /
NK053('i)001:1131: he ru ka rol pa'i rgyud /
NK053('i)001:1132: dbang rgyas rta mchog rol pa /
NK053('i)001:1135: phur pa gsang rgyud rol pa /
NK053('i)001:1139: dam tshig sa ma ya bkod pa rgyal po /
NK053('i)001:1140: ye shes rngam pa glog gi rgyud /
NK053('i)001:1142: rnam snang sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba dang 'jam dpal sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba /
NK053('i)001:1143: rdo rje sems dpa' sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba gsang ba snying po'o //
NK053('i)001:1144: la mkhas par sbyangs shing shes pa ste /
NK053('i)001:1145: de ni lung la mkhas pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1147: sgrub thabs 'di nyid kyi rgyud dang /
NK053('i)001:1150: yum mi 'khrug sbyor ba'i sgyu rtsal shes pa ni /
NK053('i)001:1151: sbyor thabs kyi gtsug lag la mkhas par shes pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1152: ging g.yog gtsug lag gi brda' shes pa ni /
NK053('i)001:1156: 'khor las dang phyag rgya'i bda' shes pa ni /
NK053('i)001:1157: phyag rgya dang las kyi go rim la mkhas pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1159: rgyal po sgom shes pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1162: ging sgrol shes pa dang bzhi /
NK053('i)001:1164: 'khor phun sum tshogs pa la yang bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:1169: de la dgyes pa bskyed pa'i 'khor ni /
NK053('i)001:1170: 'phral du bla ma ji ltar dgyes pa bskyed par
NK053('i)001:1171: byed pa'i gzugs ma rigs ngan ma yin zhing rigs
NK053('i)001:1172: bzang ba dang bzhin gzugs bzang ba dang tshul shes
NK053('i)001:1173: ba'o // mchod pa stob pa'i 'khor ni /
NK053('i)001:1174: kha tshar med pa'i byan po byan mo dang bgos dang 'gyed la mkhas pa'i phyag tshangs pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1176: dam tshig gtsor 'dzin cing bsgo ba'i bka' nyan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1178: phyi nang gi las byed do //
NK053('i)001:1179: de kun kyang skyon drug rnam par spangs nas /
NK053('i)001:1180: mi byed pa bdun dang ldan pa ma yin pa la ni /
NK053('i)001:1181: tshig zur dang man+dala gyi zur yang bstan par lung las ma gsungs so //
NK053('i)001:1186: bka' sdod phyi rol na gnas pa'i 'khor /
NK053('i)001:1188: gnas phun sum tshogs pa la yang bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:1189: ting nge 'dzin ye shes mchog gi gnas dang /
NK053('i)001:1190: bkra shis dag pa'i gnas dang /
NK053('i)001:1191: yid du 'ong zhing nyams dga' ba'i gnas dang /
NK053('i)001:1192: bsgrub pa dus kyi gnas so //
NK053('i)001:1193: de la ting nge 'dzin ye shes mchog gi gnas ni /
NK053('i)001:1195: gang bstan pa'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas nus pa /
NK053('i)001:1196: de la snang stong dbyer med kyi man ngag bstan pa'i gnas yin /
NK053('i)001:1197: bkra shis dag pa'i gnas ni /
NK053('i)001:1198: sngon 'phags pa'i zhabs kyis bcag pa rdo rje'i gdan lta bu dang /
NK053('i)001:1199: sngar bsgrubs te dngos grub thob pa mang po byung ba'i gnas so //
NK053('i)001:1200: yid du 'ong zhing nyams dga' ba'i gnas ni /
NK053('i)001:1202: me tog dang 'bras bur ldan pa'i ri //
NK053('i)001:1203: dga' zhing yid 'ong dben gnas su //
NK053('i)001:1204: ngang pa dang bzhad pa bya rgod sgra 'byin pa //
NK053('i)001:1205: sgrub pa'i gnas su bshad pa yin //
NK053('i)001:1207: bsgrub pa dus kyi gnas ni /
NK053('i)001:1208: dus gang du btab pa'i sar dus 'di tsa na bsgrub par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1210: yid du 'ong bas nyams dga' ba dang /
NK053('i)001:1211: sngon bsgrubs pas bkra shis pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1212: zhabs kyis bcag pas byin che ba dang /
NK053('i)001:1213: rigs dang mthun pas sgrub thag nye ba'o //
NK053('i)001:1214: yo byad phun sum tshogs pa la yang bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:1215: 'tsho ba zas kyi yo byad dang /
NK053('i)001:1216: rkyen bzlog sman gyi yo byad dang /
NK053('i)001:1217: sgrub pa rdzas kyi yo byad dang /
NK053('i)001:1218: mchod pa rdzas kyi yo byad do //
NK053('i)001:1219: de la 'tsho ba zas kyi yo byad ni /
NK053('i)001:1220: bsgrub pa'i dus kyi kha zas ldab bur spags te sta gon la gnas par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1221: rkyen bzlog sman gyi yo byad ni /
NK053('i)001:1222: nad 'du ba rnam pa bzhi la /
NK053('i)001:1223: gang dang gang phan pa'i sman dang /
NK053('i)001:1224: sman pa mkhas pa yang sta gon la gnas par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1225: sgrub pa rdzas kyi yo byad ni /
NK053('i)001:1227: dngos grub bsgrub pa'i sgrub rdzas dang /
NK053('i)001:1228: dbang bskur ba'i dbang rdzas dang /
NK053('i)001:1229: rmad du byung ba'i dam rdzas tshang ba'o //
NK053('i)001:1230: mchod pa rdzas kyi yo byad ni /
NK053('i)001:1231: phyi nang gi mchod rdzas thams cad do //
NK053('i)001:1233: kham phor ri mo bri ba'i rdzas thod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1234: snang ba 'od dang bcas pa'i rdzas /
NK053('i)001:1238: spyad pa yo byad kyi rdzas so //
NK053('i)001:1240: de yang phun sum tshogs pa bzhi po 'di la yang man ngag tu gdams pa /
NK053('i)001:1241: slob dpon kyang phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi dbang nges par thob cing /
NK053('i)001:1242: lung dang man ngag yod pa /
NK053('i)001:1243: yon tan brgyad dang ldan pas bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1245: sngags dang phyag rgya ting nge 'dzin la gnas pa'i dbang mnos pas /
NK053('i)001:1246: sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las dang ldan pa'i yon tan dang /
NK053('i)001:1247: bka' dag cing gsang ba'i dbang thob pas /
NK053('i)001:1248: 'bras bu la rmongs pa med pa'i yon tan dang /
NK053('i)001:1249: dam tshig gtsang zhing sgrub pa la brtson pas /
NK053('i)001:1250: lha dang srung ma nye ba'i yon tan dang /
NK053('i)001:1251: sgom sgrub sran che zhing mthu rtsal dang ldan pas /
NK053('i)001:1252: bgegs kyis mi tshugs pa'i yon tan dang /
NK053('i)001:1253: rkyen thub cing dgos pa zab pas /
NK053('i)001:1254: bar chad mi 'byung ba'i yon tan dang /
NK053('i)001:1255: gnyid dang chang dad chung bas /
NK053('i)001:1256: las mthar phyin pa'i yon tan dang /
NK053('i)001:1257: snying rje che zhing 'khor la brtse bas /
NK053('i)001:1258: kun gyis bkur zhing basngagasa pa'i yon tan dang /
NK053('i)001:1259: dgongs pa rgya che zhing snyan khung yangs pas /
NK053('i)001:1260: ya ga dang phra mas mi tshugs pa dang brgyad do //
NK053('i)001:1261: gzugs ma mtshan bzang sum cu tshang zhing dad pa che bas bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1262: su cu ni lus dang ngag dang yid la bcu bcu ste sum cu'o //
NK053('i)001:1263: yang na mtshan bzang sum cu ni //
NK053('i)001:1266: yan lag rdzogs dang zha grum med //
NK053('i)001:1267: dbyibs legs mdog sdug lus mnyen dang //
NK053('i)001:1268: seng+ge'i sked skabs dri zhim dang //
NK053('i)001:1269: rgyab nas dgye la mdun nas rgu //
NK053('i)001:1270: smin dkyus ring dang rnam bcu'o //
NK053('i)001:1272: ngag snyan ngag dal tshig 'bru gsal //
NK053('i)001:1273: brda dag mi bden rdzun mi smra //
NK053('i)001:1274: phra ma zhe gcod tshig mi rtsub //
NK053('i)001:1275: gsang thub sngags bzlos tshig ni btsun //
NK053('i)001:1278: brnab sems gnod sems log mi lta //
NK053('i)001:1279: mi stong sems brjid re dogs med //
NK053('i)001:1280: g.yo med sgyu med rku sems med //
NK053('i)001:1281: gzhan gyis kha mi 'drong pa'i yon tan dang bcu'o //
NK053('i)001:1282: slob ma skyon drug spangs pa ste /
NK053('i)001:1283: nyan pa dang dge ba'i phyogs la brtson 'grus chung ba lus kyi skyon dang /
NK053('i)001:1284: bzlas pa la gtam smra ba sogs ngag gi skyon dang /
NK053('i)001:1285: bsam pa la zhe 'gras pa yid kyi skyon dang /
NK053('i)001:1286: bag zon chung zhing brjed ngas pa dam tshig gi skyon dang /
NK053('i)001:1287: gnyid dang chang dad che ba ting nge 'dzin gyi skyon dang /
NK053('i)001:1288: sgom sgrub la skyo dub che ba dad pa'i skyon dang drug spangs pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1289: mi phyed pa bdun dang ldan par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1290: rtogs pas chos nyid dang mi phyed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1291: dam tshig ma nyams pas yi dam gyi lha dang mi phyed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1292: dad pa dang sri zhu che bas slob dpon dang mi phyed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1293: brtse gdung che bas mched lcam dang mi phyed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1294: brtul zhugs che bas dam rdzas dang mi phyed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1295: tan gan la brtson pas gzugs ma dang mi phyed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1296: snying rje che bas sems can dang mi phyed pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1297: ting nge 'dzin gsal zhing sgom sran che bas dngos grub dang mi phyed pa /
NK053('i)001:1298: sgom pa la sran tshugs pas blo la thang lhod
NK053('i)001:1299: med par brtan pas ting nge 'dzin dang mi phyed
NK053('i)001:1300: pa'o // gnas dben zhing nyams dga' la rgyu srong la ma bab pa /
NK053('i)001:1303: kham phor tshal bu brgyad dbus kyi gnam zhal dang dgu ri mor bris pa'i rdzas dang /
NK053('i)001:1304: snang ba'i 'od dang bcas pa'i rdzas mar me dgu dang /
NK053('i)001:1305: mdzes par 'khor bar bzhag pa'i rdzas dam rdzas gzhan dang /
NK053('i)001:1306: dmigs rten mngon par bkram pa'i rdzas ris su bris pa'am lugs 'bur gang yod dang /
NK053('i)001:1307: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rnam pa lnga /
NK053('i)001:1319: sha rnam pa lnga mi sha /
NK053('i)001:1325: rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dang /
NK053('i)001:1332: sgrub pa zhing gi rdzas dang /
NK053('i)001:1338: spyad pa'i yo byad lnga sha /
NK053('i)001:1344: 'di rnams kun ldab bur bsogs te /
NK053('i)001:1346: dkyil 'khor chen po'i cho ga brtsam par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1348: slob dpon dang ni slob bu dang //
NK053('i)001:1349: gnas dang yo byad ldan gyur nas //
NK053('i)001:1350: bsgrub pa'i las la 'jug bya ba //
NK053('i)001:1351: nges par rab tu brtags te bya //
NK053('i)001:1353: dang po sgrub pa po brtags shing 'bru bdam ste /
NK053('i)001:1354: slob ma snod mi gzhi bzang po btsal lo //
NK053('i)001:1356: slob mas slob dpon ma brtags na slob ma'i bdud du 'ong bas /
NK053('i)001:1357: slob ma ma brtags na slob ma ngan pa dang 'phrad na slob dpon gyi bdud du 'ong /
NK053('i)001:1358: gzungs ma ma brtags na gzugs ma mi ngan dang 'phrad na sgrub pa po'i bdud du 'ong /
NK053('i)001:1359: gnas ma brtags na 'dre bo cher drags pa'am bar chad kyi bdud du 'ong bas /
NK053('i)001:1360: shin tu brtag cing btsal ba gal che'o //
NK053('i)001:1362: rjes 2 brtag cing btsal ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:1363: rdzas dang sa gzhi brtag pa der //
NK053('i)001:1366: sa gzhi brtag pa gnyis las /
NK053('i)001:1369: rdzas brtag cing btsal ba'i thabs 'byung ste /
NK053('i)001:1371: bsnyen pa rdzogs pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK053('i)001:1373: rdzas mchog mtshan ldan brtags te btsal //
NK053('i)001:1374: rdzas bzhi gang la brtags te sbyar //
NK053('i)001:1377: de la rdzas brtag pa la don bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:1378: bkra shis gtsang ma'i rdzas dang /
NK053('i)001:1380: sgrub pa mchog gi rdzas dang /
NK053('i)001:1381: bsgral ba zhing gi rdzas so //
NK053('i)001:1382: de la bkra shis gtsang ma'i rdzas ni /
NK053('i)001:1385: rje'u rigs la stsogs pa'i rigs btsun pa /
NK053('i)001:1389: skra bung ba ltar gnag cing lcang lor 'dug pa /
NK053('i)001:1390: so tshag dam pa swo dung swo 'khor ba /
NK053('i)001:1392: mchu bim pa ltar dmar zhing pad+ma'i dbyibs su 'dug
NK053('i)001:1393: pa de mtshan dang ldan zhing bkra shis pa'i rdzas
NK053('i)001:1394: so // dag pa lha yi rdzas ni /
NK053('i)001:1402: skra mtshams nas sna'i rtse mor sme ba bdun chags pa /
NK053('i)001:1403: de ni skye ba bdun du mir skyes pa'i rtags yin pas /
NK053('i)001:1404: bkra shis la sgrub pa'i rdzas su basngagasa so //
NK053('i)001:1405: sgrub pa mchog gi rdzas ni /
NK053('i)001:1406: skyes pa gzhon nu dpa' rtsal can rab tu barlinga
NK053('i)001:1407: ba de 'khrug pa la g.yul du mtshon rnon pos
NK053('i)001:1408: bsad pa'am / rigs bzang mtshan ldan ma glo bur du shi ba ste /
NK053('i)001:1409: de yang sgrub pa'i rdzas so //
NK053('i)001:1410: bsgral ba zhing gi rdzas la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:1411: bsgral zhing bshad pa'i rdzas dang /
NK053('i)001:1412: gdul bya bsgral ba'i rdzas so //
NK053('i)001:1413: bsgral zhing bshad pa'i rdzas ni /
NK053('i)001:1419: shel lug nag lug smug dang /
NK053('i)001:1420: tsa ra ra pho la stsogs pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1421: des bde gshegs dam can thugs dam bskang zhing sor gzhug pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1422: sgrub pa po rnams bzang zhing rol pa'i rdzas so //
NK053('i)001:1423: gdul bya bsgral ba'i rdzas ni /
NK053('i)001:1426: rdo rje slob dpon gyi sgos dgra /
NK053('i)001:1428: dam las log pa zhes bya /
NK053('i)001:1429: dam la 'khus pa ste gsang ba snod ngan la spel ba /
NK053('i)001:1430: sgrub pa'i 'du bar 'ong nas gshe ba /
NK053('i)001:1431: yongs la gnod pa'i jag dpon lta bu /
NK053('i)001:1432: dam dgra zhes bya ba ste bzlog pa mkhan lta bu /
NK053('i)001:1433: mi dge ba kho na la spyod pa ngan pa'i ngang tshul can /
NK053('i)001:1435: dmigs kyis btsal zhing mngon du bsgral lo //
NK053('i)001:1436: de ltar brtag pa'i gong gi rdzas /
NK053('i)001:1440: dag pa lha yi rdzas te snga ma gsum po gang yang rung ba de /
NK053('i)001:1441: nges par gson gshin gyi dus su brtags la /
NK053('i)001:1443: gong 'og gi gnas gang rnyed der /
NK053('i)001:1444: sgrub pa po rnams 'dus shing 'tshogs nas man+dala byas shing rdzas tshogs par byas te /
NK053('i)001:1445: rdo rje rgyal po slob dpon yab yum stan bde ba la gnas shing /
NK053('i)001:1446: sbyor ba tshul bzhin du byas shing /
NK053('i)001:1451: dpal chen pos byin gyis brlabs shing gsang ba'i dbang bskur bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1452: dang por de nas bgegs 'jug pa'i gnas lngar spyi gtsug ltag pa'i bdud sgo /
NK053('i)001:1456: yang byang chub sems dkar dmar kyi thig le bya zhing /
NK053('i)001:1457: h'u phata sarba ma ra ya s+t+wam pa k+aa ra h'u h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:1458: ces brjod pas byang chub sems h'u du gsal ba las /
NK053('i)001:1459: khro chung zhal gsum la phyag drug pa re rer gyur te /
NK053('i)001:1460: gong gi gnas lngar bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:1462: de nas yang bzlas pa de nyid kyis lus kun
NK053('i)001:1463: la yang khro chung mang po gtams par bsgom mo
NK053('i)001:1464: // de nas rgyal thebs karma ging gsum gyi lag pa g.yas kun tu /
NK053('i)001:1468: lag pa g.yon pa gsum du /
NK053('i)001:1470: khro bo gshin rje gshed dang /
NK053('i)001:1472: ta ki r+aa dza gsum du byin gyis brlabs pa
NK053('i)001:1473: re re lag tu bskur te pho nyar gtong ngo
NK053('i)001:1475: rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen po yis //
NK053('i)001:1476: dur khrod kyi rdzas mchog bam ma nyams pa //
NK053('i)001:1477: thed rol dang god kar ma song ba /
NK053('i)001:1478: blangs te bsgrub par bya ba yang //
NK053('i)001:1479: rgyud bzang rigs btsun mtshan dang ldan //
NK053('i)001:1480: gtsang zhing bkra shis yid du 'ong dus tshod rab 'bring tha ma la //
NK053('i)001:1481: dus la babs pas ro blang dus //
NK053('i)001:1482: bdag nyid dpal chen yab yum gyis //
NK053('i)001:1483: rgyal thebs karma ging gsum la //
NK053('i)001:1484: gong bzhin dbang bskur gnas lngar bsrung ba byas nas ni //
NK053('i)001:1485: lag cha bskur te pho nyar mngag /
NK053('i)001:1487: de nas mngag pa'i pho nya de gsum gyis /
NK053('i)001:1489: ma dang a las nyi ma dang zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:1490: 'gro drug gi sems can ma rig pa'i 'khrul dong mun pa dang 'dra ba na 'dug pa la /
NK053('i)001:1491: rig pa'i ye shes nyi zla'i 'od zer lta bus
NK053('i)001:1492: 'khor ba'i bag chags sprin dang na bun 'dra ba
NK053('i)001:1495: gom pa'i stabs khro bo'i stang stabs kyis 'gro bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1497: srid pa rgyu mchog bam chen de //
NK053('i)001:1498: rnal 'byor dbang phyug dngos grub rdzas /
NK053('i)001:1499: kha t+w+aam mtshon cha thogs nas su //
NK053('i)001:1500: dpal chen khro bo'i ting 'dzin gyis /
NK053('i)001:1501: khams gsum zil gyis gnon pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:1502: nyi zla'i spyan gyis btsal bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1504: de nas rdzas yod pa'i sa der phyin pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1505: khro bo'i stang stabs gdengs shing phyogs bcur blta zhing /
NK053('i)001:1506: rdo rje'i 'gros kyis lan gsum du bskor /
NK053('i)001:1507: rdo rje dang kha t+w+aam kha gsor zhing /
NK053('i)001:1508: cang te'u bkrol te 'di skad brjod do //
NK053('i)001:1509: sa phyogs 'di na gnas pa'i gdon bgegs thams cad ma gnas par dengs shig /
NK053('i)001:1510: gal te mi 'gro bar gyur na yang rdo rje
NK053('i)001:1511: gnod sbyin drag pos khyed kyi lus sems kyi rgyud
NK053('i)001:1512: thal ba bzhin du brlag par 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:1513: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK053('i)001:1515: ro'i gshed du gyur pa za 'dre zhon srung drag tu bskrad do //
NK053('i)001:1519: rdo rje me 'od kyi gur du 'khrigs par bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:1523: gzugs med khams te khams gsum dbang du bsdu ba dang //
NK053('i)001:1526: 'og klu'i srid pa ste srid gsum zil gyis gnon pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:1527: rdo rje 'gros kyis btsal bar bya //
NK053('i)001:1531: rdo rje sa la brdab pas /
NK053('i)001:1532: gshin rje'i khang pa dang grong khyer bcom par bsgom zhing /
NK053('i)001:1533: ha ha ru lu ru lu h'u phata //
NK053('i)001:1534: ces brjod cing phata dral lo //
NK053('i)001:1536: gong gi gshin rje gshed du bsgom pa'i phur pas /
NK053('i)001:1537: bam gyi ltag khung du btab pas /
NK053('i)001:1538: 'chi bdag gi lag nas 'phrogs shing bgegs drag po dang phral bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:1540: lag pa g.yas g.yon la dpa' bo 'bru lnga +aahmh'u
NK053('i)001:1541: s+aa h+aa las ye shes lnga'i 'od zer gyis dug
NK053('i)001:1542: lnga dpyis phyung / skye ba'i sgo rtsad nas bcad par bsam zhing /
NK053('i)001:1545: gshin rje'i khang khyim gzhom pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:1546: kha t+w+aam rdo rje sa la brdab //
NK053('i)001:1547: 'chi bdag gshed dang dbral ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:1548: gshin rje gshed po'i phur pas gdab //
NK053('i)001:1549: dug lnga skye ba'i rtsad bcad phyir //
NK053('i)001:1550: lag pa la dpal bo 'bru lngar byin gyis brlabs pa de /
NK053('i)001:1551: rdo rje sder mos blang bar bya //
NK053('i)001:1554: ro yi gshed dang dbral ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:1555: seng ldeng phur bu sor brgyad po //
NK053('i)001:1556: stobs po che yi skur bsgom la //
NK053('i)001:1557: stobs po che rang gi gsang sngags brgya ni rtsa brgyad bzlas /
NK053('i)001:1558: gson gyi bdud dang gshin gyi lcags //
NK053('i)001:1560: gzugs dang mtshan mar bcas nas ni //
NK053('i)001:1561: phur bus btab ste ro shun dril //
NK053('i)001:1562: ro'i khung bur mnan te ro stod gzir //
NK053('i)001:1563: phrin las rnam bzhis gzir gnon bya //
NK053('i)001:1566: tak+ki r+aa dza bsgom pa'i phur pa 'dril zhing /
NK053('i)001:1567: sum b+ha ni la sogs pa'i sngags brjod pas /
NK053('i)001:1568: ro'i lus la 'khril shing phyir 'breng ba la sogs pa rnams ril bcings shing btags par bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:1570: phyis kyi gdon rnams brlag pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:1571: ta ki r+aa dzas bcings shing btags //
NK053('i)001:1574: de khog pa yi ge b+h+r+aumhls gzhal yas khang du bskyed la /
NK053('i)001:1575: der rdzogs pa'i tshul gyis lha bskyed /
NK053('i)001:1576: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing gnyis su med par bstims nas /
NK053('i)001:1579: 'byung ba dang lhar gsal bar byas la /
NK053('i)001:1580: de gsum dbyer med par byas te /
NK053('i)001:1581: gang du 'gro ba'i gnas sgrub khang der /
NK053('i)001:1582: pho brang dkyil 'khor gzhal yas khang du bsgom pa de /
NK053('i)001:1583: rlung gi dkyil 'khor gyis bskyod par bsam zhing /
NK053('i)001:1584: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:1586: ro de nyid dngos por gsal bas /
NK053('i)001:1587: dbang po rnam pa lnga mig rna ba sna lce
NK053('i)001:1588: lus las 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i lha mor 'phro
NK053('i)001:1589: bar bsam pa'am / ro de nyid yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che lta bur bsam pa'am /
NK053('i)001:1590: ro de nyid ru tra'i ngo bor bsam pa gang yang rung ste /
NK053('i)001:1591: dang po las kyi karmasa bkug /
NK053('i)001:1592: rgyal thebs kyis byin gyis rlob /
NK053('i)001:1593: ging gis phra men mas 'dzin tshul bya zhing /
NK053('i)001:1594: ru lu ru lu h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:1595: ru lu ru lu sarba m+aa ra ya s+ya'e na ya /
NK053('i)001:1597: uts+tshash+ta ya h'u h'u phata phata /
NK053('i)001:1599: ro de nyid 'dod yon gyi yid bzhin no bu'am ru ta'am gang la mos par bsam la /
NK053('i)001:1600: cang te'u yang drag tu brdung ngo //
NK053('i)001:1602: las kyi karmasa khyer nas ni //
NK053('i)001:1603: mkha' 'gro'i dam rdzas yin pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:1607: rdo rje rgyal po yab yum la sogs pas /
NK053('i)001:1608: ye shes las grub pa'i pho nya sgo ba yan chad dang /
NK053('i)001:1609: las las grub pa'i pho nya dbang phyug ma dang /
NK053('i)001:1610: rang dang 'brel ba'i lha srung pho nyas /
NK053('i)001:1611: tshe 'das pa de'i rnam shes tshogs brgyad dang /
NK053('i)001:1612: 'dod yon gyi rdzas su bcas pa dgug go //
NK053('i)001:1613: de nas sgrub khang gi sgor phyin pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1614: nang na 'dug pa sgrub pa po kun gyis kyang //
NK053('i)001:1615: ru tra ma tram sa ma ya /
NK053('i)001:1616: e dam sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:1617: a la la hoh zhes brjod do //
NK053('i)001:1618: sgo'i drung du phyin pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1620: h'u bcu'i rgyas btab la bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:1622: gnas su phyin nas mtshams kyang bcad //
NK053('i)001:1623: sgrom du bcug la rgya yis gdab //
NK053('i)001:1624: bka' bsgo phyogs bcings bsrung bar bya //
NK053('i)001:1626: 'o na ji ltar spyad pa'i rdzas bzhi dang /
NK053('i)001:1628: gzhon zhing na tshod la bab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1629: rigs bzang mtshan ldan ma drug dang /
NK053('i)001:1630: spyad du 'os pa rigs pa dang sbyar te /
NK053('i)001:1631: thabs gong ltar byas te blang ngo //
NK053('i)001:1633: seng ge dkar po'i sha la mi 'bag pa rdo rje slob dpon gyi bam mi bsha' ba dang /
NK053('i)001:1634: stag gi god sha la mi 'bag pa gzhan gyis byas pa'i rdzas mgo bral ba'am /
NK053('i)001:1635: snying dang rkang lag brag pa'am /
NK053('i)001:1636: bya spang khwa yis phyes pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1637: gangs kyi thigs chu mi btung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:1643: lhog ro la sogs mi blang ngo /
NK053('i)001:1644: ming btags pa'i nor la mi 'bag pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1645: dmen dang ngan pas zin pa'i klu'i the rol mdzer ro //
NK053('i)001:1646: 'di ni bsgrub pa'i rdzas brtag cing /
NK053('i)001:1647: sta gon la gnas par bya ba'i rim pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1649: sa 3gzhi brtag cing sa chog bstan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:1652: khyad par can gyi gnas btsal zhing brtag pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1653: sa yi chog ga'i rim pa bstan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1654: de la khyad par can gyi gnas btsal zhing brtags pa ni /
NK053('i)001:1656: zhi ba'i dgon gnas lha yi gnas //
NK053('i)001:1657: ri bo chen po 'dus pa'i rtse //
NK053('i)001:1658: gangs dkar shel gyis gtams pa'i 'dabs //
NK053('i)001:1659: seng chen 'dra ba'i gnas su bya //
NK053('i)001:1662: khro bo'i dgon gnas srin po'i gnas //
NK053('i)001:1663: ri bo chen po btsan po'i ngos //
NK053('i)001:1664: brag dmar gtams pa'i dkyil ngos la //
NK053('i)001:1665: stag dred 'khra ba'i gnas su bya //
NK053('i)001:1668: ma mo'i dgon gnas dur khrod gnas //
NK053('i)001:1669: shin tu dben pa'i sa phyogs su //
NK053('i)001:1670: gsar rnying ro yi 'du sa na //
NK053('i)001:1671: gcan gzan dang dur bya rnams 'du sar bya //
NK053('i)001:1674: rdo rje rigs kyi gnas mchog ni //
NK053('i)001:1675: dur khrod dang ni lha rten dang //
NK053('i)001:1676: ma mo'i khyim dang yid 'ong du //
NK053('i)001:1677: der ni sa yi cho ga bya //
NK053('i)001:1679: gnas de lta bu rnyed kyang /
NK053('i)001:1685: rigs bsdus pa dang drug gi gnam sa brtag pa'am /
NK053('i)001:1687: spyir brtag pa gnas brtag ste 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad 'dra ba'am /
NK053('i)001:1689: bar snang bdud rtsi 'bab pa 'dra ba der bya /
NK053('i)001:1690: bar snang la ri chag gang tsam med cing /
NK053('i)001:1691: lung pa'i mdo lho phyogs su zug pa ni sbom pa /
NK053('i)001:1692: phu byang phyogs su bltas pa ni phra ba /
NK053('i)001:1693: de ni gshin rje'i mdung gi phog sa yin pas mi rung /
NK053('i)001:1694: sa gzhi yang gcan gzan gyi sder mos brad pa'am /
NK053('i)001:1695: yug sa mo'i mchi ma'i rjes 'dra bas mi rung ngo //
NK053('i)001:1697: skye bo yongs kyis mig mang gis blta sa /
NK053('i)001:1698: kha mang gi gleng ba'i sa yin pa dang /
NK053('i)001:1699: lha 'dre gdug pa can gyi rgyu srang la ma bab pa /
NK053('i)001:1700: rgyal po dang blon po zhang blon gdug pa can gyi mig la ma bab pa ma yin pa /
NK053('i)001:1701: rab tu nyams dga' ba btsal ba ni /
NK053('i)001:1702: sa gzhi brtag pa zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1704: gnas der sa'i cho ga'i rim pa brtsam par bya ba ste /
NK053('i)001:1712: sa yi lha mo dpang por bzhag pa dang bdun no //
NK053('i)001:1714: dang 1 po sa bslang bar bya ste /
NK053('i)001:1715: cho ga rnam pa gsum gyis gsung yig 'bru'i cho ga /
NK053('i)001:1716: thugs phyag mtshan gyi cho ga /
NK053('i)001:1717: sku yongs su rdzogs pa'i cho ga bdag nyid dpal chen rdo rje sems dpa'i skur bskyed la /
NK053('i)001:1740: snying po lnga chu'i snying po lan tsh+wa /
NK053('i)001:1743: shing gi snying po bu ram /
NK053('i)001:1744: me tog snying po sbrang rtsi dang /
NK053('i)001:1750: bkang ba'i gtor ma byas la /
NK053('i)001:1751: sngags drug phyag rgya drug gis byin gyis brlabs pa bden pa brdar te /
NK053('i)001:1752: sa bdag lha klu 'khor bdud dang btsan dang rma dang mathe'u rang dang bcas //
NK053('i)001:1753: gtor ma dam pa 'di bzhes pa //
NK053('i)001:1754: bdag gis bsnyen sgrub ma thon bar //
NK053('i)001:1755: khyed la gnas 'di bdag g.yar gyis //
NK053('i)001:1756: ci bde bar ni gnang du gsol //
NK053('i)001:1758: sa bdag lha klu spyi la bslang ngo //
NK053('i)001:1759: khyad par du sa'i lha mo la bslang ste /
NK053('i)001:1761: 'og gi phyogs na dbang bsgyur bzhugs so 'tshal //
NK053('i)001:1762: sa yi lha mo brtan ma 'og phyogs skyong //
NK053('i)001:1763: sa 'di bslang ba'i ched du spyan 'dren na //
NK053('i)001:1764: 'gro ba'i don phyir khyod kyis g.yar du gsol //
NK053('i)001:1765: e h+ye hi pri thi de bi h'u /
NK053('i)001:1766: dzahmh'u bam hoh de ba su pra ti b+he ga sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:1767: sa yi lha mo 'khor bcas la phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK053('i)001:1768: spyir sa gzhi dge zhing bkra shis par mdzad du gsol /
NK053('i)001:1769: rigs 'dul ba'i phrin las kyis ni sa bdag gi rigs 'dul bar mdzad du gsol lo //
NK053('i)001:1770: phyogs skyong ba'i phrin las kyis ni 'og gi phyogs skyong bar mdzad du gsol lo //
NK053('i)001:1771: pri thi de b+ai b+he ga sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:1773: skyob pa sangs rgyas thams cad kyis //
NK053('i)001:1774: spyod pa'i tshul dag khyad par gyi //
NK053('i)001:1775: sa dang pha rol phyi pa la //
NK053('i)001:1776: lha mo khyod ni dpang du gyur //
NK053('i)001:1778: lag pa lan gsum sa la brdab pas /
NK053('i)001:1779: sa gzhi gas te sa yi lha mo byon par bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:1780: de nas mchod pa rnam pa lnga phul nas /
NK053('i)001:1781: gtsang zhing gtsang mar sbyar ba yi //
NK053('i)001:1782: lha rdzas dam pa'i bsil mngar chab //
NK053('i)001:1783: sa yi lha mo brtan ma 'khor bcas la //
NK053('i)001:1784: bdag cag dad pas 'bul lags kyis //
NK053('i)001:1785: sa rin bstsal phyir bzhes su gsol //
NK053('i)001:1786: sa bdag lha klu la sogs mthu chen rnams //
NK053('i)001:1787: sgrub pa mchog la de ring nged zhugs kyis //
NK053('i)001:1788: sa glud rin chen gtor ma 'di khyer la //
NK053('i)001:1789: bgegs tshogs sa yi bdag po sa bdag rnams //
NK053('i)001:1790: nga rgyal gdug rtsub la sogs zhi nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:1791: bdag can rnams la sa 'di g.yar du gsol //
NK053('i)001:1793: sa dang pha rol phyin pa la //
NK053('i)001:1794: dbang gyur lha mo chen mo ni //
NK053('i)001:1795: sku mdog ser mo rgyan gyis brgyan //
NK053('i)001:1796: bzhin sdug mdzes pa'i cha byad can //
NK053('i)001:1797: phyag g.yas skyabs sbyin phyag rgya la //
NK053('i)001:1798: g.yon na gser gyi bum pa bsnams //
NK053('i)001:1799: kun gyi dbang gyur phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK053('i)001:1801: sa yi lha mos dga' ba'i mdangs phyung nas //
NK053('i)001:1802: rnal 'byor bka' stsol ji ltar bgyi //
NK053('i)001:1804: de la bdag gis 'di skad brjod //
NK053('i)001:1805: sh+aakya seng ge skyob pa yis //
NK053('i)001:1806: ji ltar bdud kyi sde bcom pa //
NK053('i)001:1807: de bzhin bdag kyang bdud sde las //
NK053('i)001:1808: rgyal bar bya phyir dkyil 'khor bri //
NK053('i)001:1810: sa yi lha mo dga' ba'i yid kyis /
NK053('i)001:1811: bdag la 'di skad gnang bar bsgom /
NK053('i)001:1812: khyod ni slob dpon dam pa yin //
NK053('i)001:1813: sems can don byos dkyil 'khor bris //
NK053('i)001:1814: de skad zer nas sa yi lha mo sa la slar thim par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:1815: de nas sa 2brtag par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:1816: sa khru gang tsam mar brkos te /
NK053('i)001:1817: pra bzang na gter lta bu'am /
NK053('i)001:1818: rin po che sna lnga lta bu dang 'phrad la /
NK053('i)001:1819: ngan par gyur na ro lnga'i mtshan ma sa ro gseg ma /
NK053('i)001:1823: srog chags kyi ro rus pa /
NK053('i)001:1825: ngan na sa de nas spo ba'am /
NK053('i)001:1826: phrin las bzhi'i sbyin bsreg bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1827: de nas sa der gter 3gzhug par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:1828: kham sa'i bum pa so btang ba'i nang du nyi shu rtsa lnga'i rdzas gong ltar kyis bkang la /
NK053('i)001:1830: sa yi lha mo 'khor dang bcas //
NK053('i)001:1831: sngon gyi rgyal ba rnams kyi bka' //
NK053('i)001:1832: byang chub sems kyi gter bum 'di //
NK053('i)001:1834: de nas sas bkang la 'thas par bcag go //
NK053('i)001:1835: de nas sa 4sbyang bar bya ste /
NK053('i)001:1838: thugs ka nas 'phros te de'i 'od zer gyis dngos por snang ba ril po /
NK053('i)001:1841: kham las chus bkrus te dag par byas nas /
NK053('i)001:1842: as chos nyid stong pa nyid du bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:1843: sa gzhi dal mnyam zhing dri sna lnga'i chus gtor ro //
NK053('i)001:1844: de nas bgegs 5bskrad par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:1845: bdag nyid skad cig ma'i ting nge 'dzin gyis zhe sdang rdo rje'i ting nge 'dzin du bsgyur la /
NK053('i)001:1846: mig gnyis nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor du bsam la bzlog cing /
NK053('i)001:1847: lag pa gnyis rdo rje dril bu bsil te /
NK053('i)001:1848: rkang pa h'u las rdo rjer bsgoms nas rdo rje'i 'gros bya zhing /
NK053('i)001:1850: sa phyogs 'di la gnas pa yi //
NK053('i)001:1851: lha klu gnod sbyin dri za dang //
NK053('i)001:1852: 'byung po sha za srin po'i tshogs //
