NK053('i)001:1853: gang dag gnas pa myur du song //
NK053('i)001:1854: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i bka' byung nas //
NK053('i)001:1855: gang dag mi 'gro de rnams la //
NK053('i)001:1856: rdo rje rab tu 'bar ba yis //
NK053('i)001:1857: mgo nas brgyab pas rkang par 'gems //
NK053('i)001:1858: gzhi rdo rjer gyur pa dang bgegs bskrad par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:1861: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK053('i)001:1863: de nas sa gzung 6bar bya ste /
NK053('i)001:1864: seng ldeng gi phur pa gcig khro bo bdud rtsi 'khyil par byin gyis brlabs la /
NK053('i)001:1866: bde bar gshegs pa'i dgongs rgyud la //
NK053('i)001:1867: rnal 'byor rig pa'i rtsal sbyong gis //
NK053('i)001:1868: bsnyen sgrub ma thon bar dag tu //
NK053('i)001:1869: khro bo chen pos bzung du gsol //
NK053('i)001:1871: de nas sa'i lha mo dpang 7por bzhag ste /
NK053('i)001:1872: sngon bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pas /
NK053('i)001:1873: rdo rje'i gdan drung du bdud sde bzhi phung po'i bdud /
NK053('i)001:1877: brtul zhing chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'ang sa gzhi rin po che'i steng du mdzad pa yin pas /
NK053('i)001:1878: bdag cag rnal 'byor pa rnams kyang de bzhin gshegs
NK053('i)001:1879: pa'i dgongs pa la shes rab kyi rtsal sbyong bas
NK053('i)001:1880: / sa'i lha mo'i mkhyen pa dang dpang dam pa mdzad du gsol lo //
NK053('i)001:1882: bdud kyi sde dang dpung bcom zhing //
NK053('i)001:1883: de ring bdag gis bdud las ni //
NK053('i)001:1884: rgyal bar byas nas dkyil 'khor bri //
NK053('i)001:1886: lag pa sa la brdab pas /
NK053('i)001:1887: sa'i lha mo sku lte ba phyed nub tsam byung ste /
NK053('i)001:1888: bdag gis sngar dge ba ci bsags pa yang brjod cing /
NK053('i)001:1889: da yang de bzhin gyis la /
NK053('i)001:1890: sems can gyi don du dkyil 'khor chen po bzhengs
NK053('i)001:1891: su gsol cig pa'i gnang ba stsol bar bsgom mo
NK053('i)001:1892: // de nas dur khrod kyi sa la stegs bu
NK053('i)001:1893: lus mtshon pa'i rtags su 'dom gang gru bzhir brtsigs
NK053('i)001:1894: te me long lta bur bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1895: de nas 'jig rten pa'i sa bdag lha klu kun la yang bden pa brdar te /
NK053('i)001:1896: phud dang barngana pa byin te sa bslang ngo //
NK053('i)001:1898: gnas dang sa gzhi brtag pa der //
NK053('i)001:1899: bslang dang brtag dang sbyong ba dang //
NK053('i)001:1900: bgegs bskrad sa gzung dpang por bzhag /
NK053('i)001:1901: 'jig rten sa bdag lha klu la //
NK053('i)001:1902: sa rin btsal te sa bslang ngo //
NK053('i)001:1904: de yan chad du gnas dang sa gzhi sta gon la gnas par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:1907: don bzhis bstan pa'i tha ma phrin las 4kyi rim pa bstan pa la /
NK053('i)001:1909: mtshams gcod pa'i phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:1910: ma tram mnan pa'i phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:1911: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bri zhing rdzas dgod pa'i phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:1912: thams cad byin gyis brlab pa'i phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:1913: slob mar dbang bskur ba'i phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:1914: lha mnyes par bya ba'i phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:1915: dngos grub dbang gi phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:1916: las kyi lhag ma'i phrin las so /
NK053('i)001:1918: 1 / de la mtshams gcod pa'i phrin las la don gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:1921: nang mtshams gcod pa'i rim pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1922: de dag kyang gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:1923: skabs sbyor drug pa phyi nang gi mchod pa bya
NK053('i)001:1924: zhing mtshams bcad pa ma tram mnan pa'i skabs so
NK053('i)001:1925: // dkyil 'khor dgu las gnyis pa mtshams kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK053('i)001:1926: mtha' drug las bzhi pa spyod pa'o //
NK053('i)001:1927: yo byad gnyis las thabs ting nge'o //
NK053('i)001:1928: lung dgu las ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa las kyi lung ngo //
NK053('i)001:1929: gsum pa ma tram mnan pa'i lung dang /
NK053('i)001:1930: dur khrod kyi lung du yang 'agro'o //
NK053('i)001:1931: 'byung por gtor ma btang nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:1932: gsang ba'i don gyi las rnams bya //
NK053('i)001:1934: dang po phyi mtshams gcod pa'i dus su /
NK053('i)001:1935: bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:1936: man+dala legs par brtsigs pa las /
NK053('i)001:1937: dri sna lnga'i chag chag stsol nas /
NK053('i)001:1938: der 'bru sna lnga'i tshom bu bkod de /
NK053('i)001:1939: me tog gi gcal du phreng ba bris nas /
NK053('i)001:1940: mchod pa rnam pa lnga dang /
NK053('i)001:1941: gtor ma rnams bzang por bshams te /
NK053('i)001:1942: bdag dang 'khor rnams khrus dang bsangs gtor dag par byas la /
NK053('i)001:1943: dkon mchog gsum la skyabs su gsol zhing /
NK053('i)001:1944: rang rang gi yi dam gyi lha'i skur dran pa bskyed de /
NK053('i)001:1946: thugs ka'am smin mtshams nas yi ge e /
NK053('i)001:1955: las rin po che'i ri rab /
NK053('i)001:1958: b+h+r+aum rnams las 'byung ba rim brtsegs kyi steng du /
NK053('i)001:1959: rin po che'i gzhal yas khang 'byams yas pa /
NK053('i)001:1960: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan dang ldan par bsgoms te /
NK053('i)001:1961: rang rang thugs rje'i stobs dang ldan par byas nas /
NK053('i)001:1965: btang snyoms bzhis 'gro ba'i don bya bar bsams te /
NK053('i)001:1966: rang rang gi yi dam gyi lha'i snying po brjod nas /
NK053('i)001:1975: las kyi bya bas bde bar gshegs pa so so'i pho brang nas bzhengs su gsol te /
NK053('i)001:1976: spyan drangs nas nyi zla'i gdan la bzhugs pa la /
NK053('i)001:1977: phyi nang gi mchod pa rnam pa lngas mchod pa 'bul /
NK053('i)001:1980: mgron po yon tan gyi mgron mchod pa /
NK053('i)001:1981: 'gro ba rigs drug snying rje'i mgron la bsngo ba /
NK053('i)001:1982: rang gi lha mgon dang phan gnod byed pa la bsngo ba /
NK053('i)001:1983: lan chags kyi mgron la bsngo ba dang /
NK053('i)001:1984: 'phral gyi rkyen bgegs la bsngo ba'o //
NK053('i)001:1985: gtor ma yang ye shes rnam pa lnga'i bye brag
NK053('i)001:1986: gis mchod pa phyi rgyal mtshan 'phan gdugs bla bre
NK053('i)001:1987: lhab lhub phye ma phur ma /
NK053('i)001:1989: gsang ba'i sbyor sgrol gyi mchod par sprul te byin gyis brlabs la /
NK053('i)001:1991: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK053('i)001:1992: phyogs gcig tu ma nges par sgo'i gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin rgyal po gtor ma 'di //
NK053('i)001:1993: yo byad rgyu rkyen rten 'brel tshogs pa'i nus mthu las //
NK053('i)001:1994: don chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i byin rlabs dang //
NK053('i)001:1995: yon tan dkon mchog rin chen spags te che ba dang /
NK053('i)001:1996: snying po phyag rgya nges pa'i dam tshig dang //
NK053('i)001:1997: bdag gi shes rab smon lam ting 'dzin gyis //
NK053('i)001:1998: kun bzang mchod sprin gur gum gyi spang ri /
NK053('i)001:2007: cang shes kyi rta pho sogs ye shes lngas brgyan 'di //
NK053('i)001:2008: bdag gi mchod gnas sri zhu'i mgron gyur pa //
NK053('i)001:2009: bla med dkon mchog gsum dang yi dam lha //
NK053('i)001:2010: dus gsum bder gshegs rgyal ba yab yum dang //
NK053('i)001:2011: byang chub sems dpa' lcam sems ma brgyad /
NK053('i)001:2014: nyan thos dgra bcom 'phags pa bzhugs kun la //
NK053('i)001:2015: nam mkha'i mtha' klas gter chen zad med gyur pa 'di //
NK053('i)001:2016: mchod gnas gong ma bla ma rnams kyi pho brang du //
NK053('i)001:2017: kun bzang la sogs mchod pa'i sprin gyis gtibs shing rgyas gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:2019: sri zhu'i mgron du gyur pa la /
NK053('i)001:2022: khyad par gyi sdig pa dang chag nyams bshags pa
NK053('i)001:2023: bgyid pas bdag cag sgrub pa po rnams kyi sgrib
NK053('i)001:2024: pa sbyong zhing byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:2025: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub nod cing mchis pas /
NK053('i)001:2027: dngos grub la gnod par byed pa'i dgra bgegs thams
NK053('i)001:2028: cad mi rtog pa'i ye shes chen po'i ngang du
NK053('i)001:2031: me tog la rten 'brel gyi snying po ye d+harma bzlas la dbul bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2032: de nas yon tan gyi mgron la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:2035: spyi'i mgron la gtor ma gcig byin gyis brlabs la bsngo ba /
NK053('i)001:2036: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK053('i)001:2037: gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin rgyal po 'di //
NK053('i)001:2038: mchod gnas yon tan dpung gnyen mgron gyur pa //
NK053('i)001:2039: tshangs pa brgya byin rgyal chen rigs bzhi yul 'khor srung /
NK053('i)001:2044: phyogs skyong bcu gcig dri za /
NK053('i)001:2079: r+aa hu la dang rgyu skar nyi shu brgyad //
NK053('i)001:2081: snar ma sogs gnod sbyin sde dpon phan tsi ka sogs 'phrog ma bu lnga brgya dang bcas //
NK053('i)001:2082: ma h+aa ka la lcam lha mo dral mgon po la sogs te //
NK053('i)001:2083: gtsang rigs mgon po bdun cu g.yog 'khor dang bcas pa dang //
NK053('i)001:2084: rnal 'byor nang gi srung ma ma lus la //
NK053('i)001:2085: chos dbyings mtha' klas mchod sbyin 'dis khyab par bsngosa pas //
NK053('i)001:2086: so so'i dbang po lngar 'dod yon lngas tshim /
NK053('i)001:2088: rab tu tshims nas yongs su mnyes gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:2090: yon tan gyi mgron du gyur pa thams cad la /
NK053('i)001:2091: mchod pa 'bul zhing bshags pa bgyid pas /
NK053('i)001:2092: bdag cag sgrub pa po rnams gsang ba mchog gi
NK053('i)001:2093: sgrub pa gnyen po 'di lta bu zhig bgyid pas
NK053('i)001:2094: / de la bar du gcod pa'i dgra bgegs kyi sbyor ba ngan pa rgyud bcad de /
NK053('i)001:2095: sngon gyi thugs dam sngar sangs rgyas las zhal gyis bzhes pa bzhin du /
NK053('i)001:2096: phyi'i dgra bgegs nang du mi gtong ba dang /
NK053('i)001:2097: nang gi dngos grub phyi mi gtong ba'i mtshams kyi phrin las lhun gyis grub par mdzad du gsol /
NK053('i)001:2099: de nas khyad par gyi mgron rgyal chen sde bzhi mchod la phrin las bcol ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:2100: gnas kyi phyi rol du tho bzhi shar du tho zla gam dkar po /
NK053('i)001:2102: nub tu zlum po dmar po /
NK053('i)001:2103: byang ngu zur gsum ljang gu /
NK053('i)001:2106: byang du gru bzhi ljang gu gsung /
NK053('i)001:2109: b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i gzhal yas khang pad+ma'i gdan dang bcas par bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:2111: mchod pa rnam pa lnga bshams la /
NK053('i)001:2112: sngags drug gis byin gyis brlabs la mchod cing phrin las bcol ba /
NK053('i)001:2114: ri rab gling bzhi'i phyogs phyogs nas //
NK053('i)001:2115: gsang bdag phyag na rdo rje'i mthus //
NK053('i)001:2116: mthu chen rgyal po sde bzhi rnams //
NK053('i)001:2117: bdag cag re ba bskang ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:2119: mtshams kyi las mchog mdzad du gsol //
NK053('i)001:2121: mchod pa rnam pa lnga dang gtor ma re re 'bul zhing phrin las bcol ba ni /
NK053('i)001:2123: 'jig rten gyi phyogs bzhi skyong ba'i dam tshig can //
NK053('i)001:2124: mthu chen rgyal po sde bzhi rnams //
NK053('i)001:2125: so so'i bgegs rigs shar dri za /
NK053('i)001:2129: chos skyong longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK053('i)001:2131: rigs bzhi'i kha dog so sor gsal //
NK053('i)001:2136: rang rtags lha yi mtshan ma togs //
NK053('i)001:2141: phyi rol skyong ba'i rdzu 'phrul can //
NK053('i)001:2142: bdag cag rnal 'byor rtsal sbyong gis //
NK053('i)001:2143: rang rang 'khor rnams thub par mdzod //
NK053('i)001:2145: gtor ma re re btang zhing phrin las so sor bcol lo //
NK053('i)001:2146: de nas bsod nams kyi tshigs spel zhing sdug bsngal zhi bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:2147: snying rje'i mgron 'gro ba yongs la sbyin gtor gcig btang ste /
NK053('i)001:2148: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK053('i)001:2149: gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin rgya chen 'di //
NK053('i)001:2150: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga ru byin brlabs te //
NK053('i)001:2151: snying rje'i bu gnyen mchod gnas mgron gyur pa //
NK053('i)001:2155: drod gsher skyes bsdus pa'i rigs drug lha mi lha min byol song yi dwags dmyal ba /
NK053('i)001:2157: 'dod pa'i longs spyod char bzhin 'byung gyur te //
NK053('i)001:2158: bye brag tu yang lha rnams 'pho ltung sdug bsngal rab zhi nas //
NK053('i)001:2159: dge bcu bsam gtan ting nge 'dzin ldan zhing //
NK053('i)001:2160: nyan thos byang chub 'bras bu thob gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:2161: lha min gnod pa 'thad rtsod gdug rtsub bral gyur te //
NK053('i)001:2162: byams ldan dga' tshal byang chub thob gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:2163: mi rnams 'dod pa phun sum tshogs gyur te //
NK053('i)001:2164: brgyad dang bcu drug gnod pa rnams dang bral //
NK053('i)001:2165: 'di la mchan rnying ma dag pa mang yang don /
NK053('i)001:2166: nang gi sdug bsngal skye rgan na 'chi bzhi /
NK053('i)001:2167: phyi'i sdug bsngal med pa mi rnyed /
NK053('i)001:2171: 'jig rten chos brgyad kyi re dogs bcas bshad 'dug /
NK053('i)001:2172: gzhung tshig bab pa yongs grags ltar /
NK053('i)001:2173: me sbrul sha za glang chen btson //
NK053('i)001:2174: chom rkun seng ge rgya mtsho'i rlabs //
NK053('i)001:2175: rgyal po'i chad pa dgra gdon mdze //
NK053('i)001:2176: bshes bral dbul phongs gnam lcags thog /
NK053('i)001:2177: don nyams la sogs 'jigs pa ni //
NK053('i)001:2178: brgyad tshan gnyis zhes gsungs pa ltar gang yin dpyad /
NK053('i)001:2179: yang dag gnas dang byang chub thob gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:2180: byol song gcig la gcig za la sogs pa'i //
NK053('i)001:2181: gnod pa'i sdug bsngal de dag yongs mi 'byung //
NK053('i)001:2182: bag yangs lha mi'i bde 'gro thob gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:2183: yi dwags rnams la zas skom la sogs pa //
NK053('i)001:2184: thogs pa med pa 'di las 'byung gyur te //
NK053('i)001:2185: yi dwags sgrib pa rnam gsum phyi nang sgos khur /
NK053('i)001:2187: bde 'gro thar lam myur du thob gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:2188: sems can dmyal ba'i sdug bsngal gang dang gang //
NK053('i)001:2189: tsha grang brgyad brgyad la sogs mi bzad sna tshogs la //
NK053('i)001:2190: thugs rje'i bsod nams 'di yi byin rlabs kyis //
NK053('i)001:2191: sdug bsngal de dag myur du zhi gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:2192: de nas rang gi lha mgon dang phan gnod byed pa kun la yang /
NK053('i)001:2193: gtor ma gcig bsngo zhing phrin las bcol te /
NK053('i)001:2194: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi'o //
NK053('i)001:2195: gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin rgyal po 'di //
NK053('i)001:2196: las dang thugs rjes 'brel pa'i lha mgon mgron //
NK053('i)001:2202: srog lha dam tshig lha dang dgra lha nor lha dang //
NK053('i)001:2204: grogs rogs mdzad pa'i lha mgon ma lus la //
NK053('i)001:2205: gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin 'dis khyab pas //
NK053('i)001:2206: so so'i dbang po'i spyod yul tshims nas mnyes gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:2207: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK053('i)001:2208: gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin rgyal po 'di //
NK053('i)001:2209: gang na gnas pa'i yul bdag khyim mtshes mgron //
NK053('i)001:2210: lha klu mkhar gyi rtse lha yul lha la sogs pa'i //
NK053('i)001:2211: so so'i rig sngags 'chang ba'i sa bdag ma lus la //
NK053('i)001:2212: gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin 'dis khyab pas //
NK053('i)001:2213: rab tu tshims nas kun kyang mnyes gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:2215: bdag cag gi stong grogs dang khyud mnyam rogs mdzod cig /
NK053('i)001:2217: lan chags dang bral zhing lan chags kyi bgegs zhi bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:2218: sngon gyi lan chags 'ded pa'i mgron la gtor ma gcig bsngosa te /
NK053('i)001:2219: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK053('i)001:2220: gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin rgyal po 'di //
NK053('i)001:2221: tshe rabs sngon nas lan chags mgron gyur pa //
NK053('i)001:2222: sa'am 'on te mkha' la 'khod pa yi //
NK053('i)001:2223: dus ma yin par 'byung bas 'byung po gshin rje gnod sbyin la sogs pa'i //
NK053('i)001:2224: stong phrag brgyad cu dag las gang gnod pa //
NK053('i)001:2226: gtan med pa'i glud gtor 'dis khyab pas //
NK053('i)001:2227: bu lon khyer cig lan chags bral gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:2229: bdag cag gi bu lon dang /
NK053('i)001:2230: sngon gyi lan chags rnying khrin snying chags zhen pa /
NK053('i)001:2231: thams cad 'dis khyer bar gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:2233: bar chad mi 'byung bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:2234: 'phral gyi rkyen bgegs la gtor ma gcig bsngosa te /
NK053('i)001:2235: dkon mchog gsum la phyag 'tshal skyabs su mchi //
NK053('i)001:2236: gtan pa med pa'i mchod sbyin rgyal po 'di //
NK053('i)001:2237: gtor ma cha gcig mchod dang rtsa ba'i rkyen bgegs mgron //
NK053('i)001:2238: tshe rabs las dang 'phral gyi rkyen dbang gi gnod
NK053('i)001:2239: pa ni sa gnyan rlog shing gnyan gcod lta bus
NK053('i)001:2241: nyams pa'i chad pa rbod gtong mthu la sogs //
NK053('i)001:2242: tshe srog bsod nams nor zas la gnod cing gtses pa rnams //
NK053('i)001:2243: bden brdar dang mchod sbyin byin brlabs 'dis dgrol te //
NK053('i)001:2244: 'phral du zhi nas yun du byang gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:2246: bdag cag la gnod pa ma byed cig /
NK053('i)001:2248: de ltar gtor ma bgyi zhing phrin las so sor bcol ba ni /
NK053('i)001:2249: phyi gtor dang phyi mtshams kyi phrin las so //
NK053('i)001:2250: de nas bar mtshams la 'jug par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:2254: dang po dam sri mnan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:2255: sgo nas gcal ba'i phyi rol du 'dom gang sar /
NK053('i)001:2256: brub khung gru gsum khru gang thur du brkos te /
NK053('i)001:2257: de'i kha la me ri bris pa gcig tu byas /
NK053('i)001:2258: dur khrod kyi thod skam mtshan ngan dum bu drug
NK053('i)001:2259: bdun brgyad dgu pa lta bu la sbyi bor rdo
NK053('i)001:2260: rje rgya gram la 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad par bris
NK053('i)001:2261: te zhes 'khor lo'i lte bar rgya gram de'i dbus
NK053('i)001:2263: 'khor lo'i rtsibs bcu la h'u bcu bris te /
NK053('i)001:2264: gsung yang brgyad bri gnyis steng 'og tu bsgom /
NK053('i)001:2266: gro ga'am shing shun la dam sri'i ling ga gzugs dang /
NK053('i)001:2267: ya ma dam sri s+t+wam pa ni m+aa ra ya ni nan /
NK053('i)001:2268: ces bya ba phag pa'i khrag gis bris la /
NK053('i)001:2269: thod pa dang gzugs su bcas pa brub khung du bcug la /
NK053('i)001:2270: bdag nyid zhe sdang rdo rje'am /
NK053('i)001:2271: las kyi rgyal po he ru ka'i skur bskyed de /
NK053('i)001:2272: ye shes las grub pa'i pho nya sgo ba yan chad dang /
NK053('i)001:2273: las las grub pa'i pho nya dbang phyug ma dang /
NK053('i)001:2274: rang dang 'brel ba'i pho nyas rang gi chos skyong bye brag pa dam sri dgug go //
NK053('i)001:2275: dzahmh'u bam hoh phyag rgya bzhis gzugs ling+ga la gnyis su med par bstims te /
NK053('i)001:2276: skud pa dkar nag khar nag gis bcings /
NK053('i)001:2277: gu gul nag po gyis bdug /
NK053('i)001:2280: dug gis dpal la byug pa'i phur pa gcig khro
NK053('i)001:2281: bo mi g.yo mgon po'i skur bsgoms la gdab ste
NK053('i)001:2283: dur khrod chen po'i gnas dag tu //
NK053('i)001:2284: sprul pa'i rbod gtong chen po dang //
NK053('i)001:2285: za byed chen po'i rngams stabs kyis //
NK053('i)001:2286: gnon pa'i las rnams dus la bab //
NK053('i)001:2287: h'u mdzad mi g.yo mgon po h'u gi +aar+ya a tsa la //
NK053('i)001:2288: sprul pa'i 'od zer rngam pa'i mdangs dang ldan //
NK053('i)001:2289: shangs nas h'u dang zhal nas phata kyi sgra chen 'brug ltar sgrogs //
NK053('i)001:2290: dur khrod bgegs kyi tshogs la +aar+ya a tsa la //
NK053('i)001:2293: b+han+d+ha b+han+d+ha k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2295: sngar gyi ling+ga gzugs thod par gzhug la /
NK053('i)001:2298: dong kha bsrub la mnan par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:2300: ri rab chen po'i rmangs su sba //
NK053('i)001:2301: gshin rje'i rgyal po ya ma r+aa dza'i zas su sbyin //
NK053('i)001:2302: chu srin 'bar ba'i kha ru bardzonga //
NK053('i)001:2304: bdun rgyud rigs ni brlag 'gyur na //
NK053('i)001:2305: nam yang ldang bar mi nus te //
NK053('i)001:2306: byang chub sems ni skyes na gtong //
NK053('i)001:2308: phrin las rnam bzhi'i bro dang /
NK053('i)001:2309: zhi ba nas brtsams te drag po la gtad do //
NK053('i)001:2310: sum b+ha ni la sogs pa bya /
NK053('i)001:2311: de nas smon lam gdab ste /
NK053('i)001:2312: hoh dur khrod mchog gi gnas /
NK053('i)001:2314: khro bdag chen po sh+r+ai he ru ka'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bsgrub pa'i gnas 'dir /
NK053('i)001:2315: ding nub dbu btsugs nas nam ma byung gi bar du /
NK053('i)001:2316: ya ma dam sri la sogs 'dul bar mdzad du gsol /
NK053('i)001:2318: de nas sgo byang gdags te /
NK053('i)001:2320: lha lha min gnyis rgyud gcig tu bsdus nas lam
NK053('i)001:2321: rgyud lnga la dbang byed pa'i bdag po gshin rje
NK053('i)001:2322: chos kyi rgyal po'i sku gzugs ma he glang rgod
NK053('i)001:2323: la chibs pa / phyag g.yas khram shing g.yon na sbrul zhags can bris pa der bskyed la /
NK053('i)001:2326: gtor mas mnyes par byas la /
NK053('i)001:2329: gsang chen lhun grub pho brang nas //
NK053('i)001:2330: las kyi gshin rje'i bdag po la //
NK053('i)001:2333: de bzhin rig 'dzin sgrub pa po //
NK053('i)001:2334: bka' gsang gzhung chen 'di bsgrub cing //
NK053('i)001:2335: yang dag don la nges 'jug na //
NK053('i)001:2336: 'di dag nor bu rin chen de //
NK053('i)001:2337: 'di la gnod cing bar gcod pa'i //
NK053('i)001:2338: lha klu gnod sbyin bdud btsan dmu rgyal po the'u rang ste lha srin sde brgyad 'byung po kun //
NK053('i)001:2339: chos rgyal khyod kyi 'khor dang g.yog lags kyis //
NK053('i)001:2340: rgyu 'bras rnam par smin pa'i chos shod la //
NK053('i)001:2341: gsang ba mchog gi rnal 'byor pa //
NK053('i)001:2342: bdag cag rnams kyis bla med 'bras bu ma thob par //
NK053('i)001:2343: phyi sgo'i sa 'di yan chad lha srin bar gcod byed pa /
NK053('i)001:2345: dpal chen mi pham bka' ma 'da' //
NK053('i)001:2346: bdag cag ye nas gnyis su med //
NK053('i)001:2347: phyi rol skyong ba'i mu ran la //
NK053('i)001:2348: rdo rje'i g.yar dam thub par mdzod //
NK053('i)001:2349: ya ma ra tsa gshin rje rgyal po /
NK053('i)001:2352: zhes brjod la gtor ma byin la /
NK053('i)001:2353: bar chad bsrung ba'i gnyer bsgo bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2354: de dag la ci'i phyir 'byung po'i gtor ma zhes bya zhe na /
NK053('i)001:2355: gsang ba bas kyang ches gsang ba /
NK053('i)001:2356: yang gsang thugs kyi sgrub pa'i dus 'dir /
NK053('i)001:2357: rgyal po chen po bzhi la sogs pa'i mgron de rnams kun /
NK053('i)001:2358: dus 'dir 'byung zhing bar chad byed du 'ong bas na 'byung po ste /
NK053('i)001:2359: de dag dang po nas drag po bya ba ma
NK053('i)001:2360: yin par zhi ba'i las kyis dam la btags shing
NK053('i)001:2361: gtor ma byin nas phrin las bcol ba dang /
NK053('i)001:2362: bden pas bka' bsgo la btang ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:2363: gtor ma rnams so so'i longs spyod du byin nas /
NK053('i)001:2365: lan chags kyi mgron la sogs pa bkye ba la /
NK053('i)001:2370: zhes bya ba'i don ni bsdu ba'i don to //
NK053('i)001:2372: mtshams la sogs pa bsdu ba ste /
NK053('i)001:2374: gasnga ba'i don gyi las rnams bya //
NK053('i)001:2376: nang mtshams bcad pa'i rim pa la don gnyis /
NK053('i)001:2377: mtshams bcad pa'i phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:2378: sngon du 'gro ba'i phrin las so //
NK053('i)001:2379: de yang don gyis bar 'dir sgrub pa po gsar ba rnams dbye bsal bya ste /
NK053('i)001:2380: sngar ma 'dres pa rnams sgor phyung ste /
NK053('i)001:2382: sngar 'dres pa rnams rnying pa nang du 'du zhing 'tshogs nas /
NK053('i)001:2383: mtshams kyi phrin las la 'jug pa la /
NK053('i)001:2386: bdag nyid chen po'i mtshams dang /
NK053('i)001:2387: khro bo'i sdang mig gi mtshams dang /
NK053('i)001:2388: rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi mtshams dang /
NK053('i)001:2389: 'gros dang stangs stabs kyi mtshams dang /
NK053('i)001:2390: ra ba dang gur gyi mtshams dang /
NK053('i)001:2392: de la rang bzhin gyi mtshams ni /
NK053('i)001:2394: rnam par rtog pa bgegs yin te //
NK053('i)001:2395: bgegs ni rang gi sems las byung //
NK053('i)001:2396: sems la rang bzhin med shes na //
NK053('i)001:2397: gzhan na bgegs zhes bya ba med //
NK053('i)001:2399: sems kyis sems la brtags pa dang //
NK053('i)001:2400: sems la rang bzhin nam dngos po /
NK053('i)001:2402: chos nyid rnam par mi rtog par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:2404: rtog pa thams cad chos nyid mi rtog pa'i ngang du nub pas /
NK053('i)001:2405: rtog pa'i bgegs ming yang med par stong pa nyid du gyur pa de ni /
NK053('i)001:2406: bka' rang bzhin gyi mtshams so //
NK053('i)001:2407: yang dag lta ba'i mtshams zhes kyang bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2408: de la bdag nyid chen po'i mtshams ni /
NK053('i)001:2409: ci la'ang mi rtog pa'i chos nyid stong pa nyid kyi ngang de las /
NK053('i)001:2411: yi ge h'u mthing ka 'od 'bar ba gcig tu gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:2413: rdo rje rtse lnga pa gcig tu bsam /
NK053('i)001:2417: bdag nyid dpal rdo rje sems dpa' sku mdog mthing ka zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa /
NK053('i)001:2418: phyag g.yas na gser gyi rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK053('i)001:2419: g.yon gser gyi dril bu dkur brten pa /
NK053('i)001:2420: zhi ba'i rgyan dar gyi chas gos lnga dang rin po che'i rgyan brgyad gyis spud pa /
NK053('i)001:2422: dbu la rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas rdzogs pa /
NK053('i)001:2423: gdan seng ge pad+ma nyi zla'i gdan la /
NK053('i)001:2424: zhabs mnyam pa'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa /
NK053('i)001:2425: rdo rje sems dpa'i de'i thugs ka na nyi ma'i
NK053('i)001:2426: steng na yi ge h'u dmar po 'od 'bar ba
NK053('i)001:2428: de gcig pu kho nar yang ma zad de /
NK053('i)001:2429: rnal 'byor pa thams cad kyang rang rang gi yi dam gyi lhar gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:2431: cod pan lta bur bde gshegs rigs lngar bsgom na //
NK053('i)001:2432: dper na sangs rgyas kyis kyang gnod mi nus //
NK053('i)001:2433: 'jigs las lhag pa'i bgegs rnams med //
NK053('i)001:2434: da lta ci smos de bzhin bstan pa tsam gyis bgegs gzhan pham mo //
NK053('i)001:2436: gong gi lha'i ting 'dzin rim par bsgom zhing gsal la mi 'gyur bas gnas nas /
NK053('i)001:2437: 'dzin pa med par chos nyid du rtogs pa la ni bgegs kyis mi tshugs so //
NK053('i)001:2438: khro bo sdang mig gi mtshams ni /
NK053('i)001:2439: thugs ka'i yi ge h'u dmar po las 'od 'phros 'dus pas rdo rjer gyur /
NK053('i)001:2440: rdo rje de 'phros shing 'dus pa las /
NK053('i)001:2444: zhal gsum la phyag drug pa /
NK053('i)001:2445: sku mthing nag gcig tu gyur te /
NK053('i)001:2446: mdun gyi bar snang la bzhugs pa la /
NK053('i)001:2447: bdag gis lcags kyus phyag rgyas bcings te /
NK053('i)001:2448: badz+ra ak+sho b+h+ya h'u am ku sha dzah zhes brjod pas /
NK053('i)001:2449: bdag gi thugs ka nas 'od zer khro bo ak+sho
NK053('i)001:2450: b+h+ya la phog pas thugs dam bskul te 'od zer
NK053('i)001:2451: gyis bkug nas bdag rdo rje sems dpa' la thim
NK053('i)001:2452: pa las / dbyer med par khrugs kyis 'dres pa dang /
NK053('i)001:2454: don chos nyid zhi ba'i rtags sems dpa' yi ni skyil krung gis //
NK053('i)001:2455: nyi zla pad+ma 'jam pa'i stan la 'dug nas ni //
NK053('i)001:2456: bag tsam khros pa zhe sdang rdo rje'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK053('i)001:2457: 'dir gnas nas gnas srung rnam par bsgom //
NK053('i)001:2460: khro bo zhe sdang rdo rje sku mdog mthing skya me tog spang rgyan 'dra ba'am /
NK053('i)001:2461: rgya gar gyi ban+d+hu ka'i me tog 'dra ba /
NK053('i)001:2462: zhal gsum la phyag drug pa /
NK053('i)001:2468: tha ma na lcags kyu bsnams pa gcig bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:2469: rgyan zhi khro'i rgyan cha spel ma /
NK053('i)001:2470: mche ba cung zad gtsigs par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:2472: ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor du gyur pa'i mig
NK053('i)001:2473: gis phyogs kun tu bltas pas ye shes kyi me
NK053('i)001:2475: bgegs dang 'byung po thams cad tshig cing bsreg par bsam la /
NK053('i)001:2477: g.yas pa'i spyan zur bzlog pa las //
NK053('i)001:2478: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bsam par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2479: gu lang dbang chen nye dbang dang //
NK053('i)001:2480: nyi zla gshin rje tshangs par bcas //
NK053('i)001:2481: thams cad ma lus bsreg par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2482: ma sur+ya man+da la h'u ram /
NK053('i)001:2485: a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du gyur pa'i mig gis phyogs mtshams kun tu bltas pas /
NK053('i)001:2486: gong du bsregs pa de dag la bdud rtsi'i chu
NK053('i)001:2487: rgyun babs te slar gsos te kho'i sdug bsngal zhi
NK053('i)001:2488: bar bsam la / yang rgyud las /
NK053('i)001:2489: g.yon pa'i spyan zur bzlog pa las //
NK053('i)001:2490: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor bsam par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2491: gu lang dbang chen nye dbang dang //
NK053('i)001:2492: nyi zla gshin rje tshangs par bcas //
NK053('i)001:2493: thams cad ma lus zhi bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2494: a tsan+d+ra man+da la h'u a zhes 'byung ngo //
NK053('i)001:2496: zhe sdang rdo rje'i mtshams zhes kyang bya /
NK053('i)001:2497: khro bo sdang mig gi mtshams zhes kyang bya /
NK053('i)001:2498: 'bar ba'i rgyal po'i mtshams zhes kyang bya /
NK053('i)001:2499: de la rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi mtshams ni /
NK053('i)001:2501: yang dag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:2502: gsang ba'i dam can so so nas //
NK053('i)001:2503: gdul ba las ni ma gtogs pa //
NK053('i)001:2504: kun kyang re ba bskangs zin gyis //
NK053('i)001:2505: da lta nyid du so sor dengs //
NK053('i)001:2506: ci ste bka' las 'das gyur na //
NK053('i)001:2507: rdo rje 'dzin rgyal zhe sdang rdo rje khros nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:2508: rdo rje'i mtshon chen 'bar ba yis //
NK053('i)001:2509: thal ba bzhin du brlag par bya //
NK053('i)001:2511: zhe sdang rdo rje'i thugs ka yi ge h'u ljang
NK053('i)001:2512: khu las rdo rje gnod sbyin sku mdog ljang nag
NK053('i)001:2514: g.yon sdigs mdzub can grangs med par spro zhing sngags brjod do //
NK053('i)001:2515: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya /
NK053('i)001:2516: na mash+tsa tsan+da badz+ra p+aa na ye /
NK053('i)001:2517: phyag na rdo rje gtum po la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:2518: ma h+aa yak+sha se n+aa pa ta ye /
NK053('i)001:2519: gnod sbyin gyi sde dpon chen po la /
NK053('i)001:2520: na mahs man+ta k+aa ya w+aa k+tsit+ta badz+r+aa n+aam /
NK053('i)001:2521: thams cad sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i rang bzhin la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:2522: na mo badz+ra kro d+ha ya /
NK053('i)001:2523: rdo rje khro bo la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:2524: ma h+aa damsh+tat+ka b+hee ra w+aa ya /
NK053('i)001:2525: mche ba chen po rnon po khros pa'i cha byad can /
NK053('i)001:2526: a si ral gri mu sa la /
NK053('i)001:2529: dgra s+t+wa zhags pa lag na 'dzin /
NK053('i)001:2532: a mri ta kun+da li bdud rtsi 'khyil ba /
NK053('i)001:2533: kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK053('i)001:2538: bkug pa mdun du gnas par gyis /
NK053('i)001:2550: tshal pa thong cig tshal pa thong cig /
NK053('i)001:2556: bgegs thams cad kyi bdag po /
NK053('i)001:2558: ma h+aa ga na pa ti /
NK053('i)001:2559: tshogs kyi bdag po chen po /
NK053('i)001:2560: dz+ai bi t+aan+ta ka ra ya srog myos nas shi la khad par gyis shig /
NK053('i)001:2563: khro bo mang pos bgegs rnams phyogs bcur bskrad par bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:2564: 'gros dang stangs stabs kyi mtshams ni /
NK053('i)001:2565: zhe sdang rdo rje stan las langs nas /
NK053('i)001:2566: sems nyid nga rgyal dang bcas pas h'u zhes brjod cing /
NK053('i)001:2567: lag pa g.yas pa bsgreng te /
NK053('i)001:2568: thabs kyi rang bzhin rdo rje gsor zhing /
NK053('i)001:2570: shes rab kyi rang bzhin dril bu bsil nas /
NK053('i)001:2571: rdo rje'i 'phros kyis lus brjid bag dang bcas pas yongs su bskor bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2572: de nas stangs stabs kyis sdang ba bgegs thams cad bskrad par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:2573: rkang pa rdo rje'i 'gros kyis 'gro ste /
NK053('i)001:2574: stangs stabs re re'i mdun du /
NK053('i)001:2576: gom pa gsum gsum byas nas /
NK053('i)001:2577: shar du dri zar lta ba nas /
NK053('i)001:2578: byang shar dbang ldan gyi bar du stangs stabs bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2579: he ru ka'i gal po nas /
NK053('i)001:2580: g.yas brkyang shar ba g.yon brkyang lho //
NK053('i)001:2581: zlum po nub la gru bzhi byang //
NK053('i)001:2582: mtshams ni rdo rjes 'gros bskor nas //
NK053('i)001:2583: sa gzhi rdo rjer byin gyis brlabs //
NK053('i)001:2585: sa gzhi thams cad rdo rje'i ram du bsgom /
NK053('i)001:2586: rang bzhin du byin gyis brlabs par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2587: ra ba dang gur gyi mtshams ni /
NK053('i)001:2588: bdag nyid zhe sdang rdo rje kyi shangs kyi rlung sgrom nas /
NK053('i)001:2589: h'u las gyur pa'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa la sogs pa'i mtshon cha rdo rje /
NK053('i)001:2594: lnga ye shes kyi 'od zer bskal pa'i me 'bar ba lta bu dang bcas pa 'phros shing /
NK053('i)001:2595: bgegs la sogs pa lus rdul du lo 'dabs ser bas brtsogs pa bzhin nyigs nyigs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:2596: phyogs bcur bskrad par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:2597: slar 'dus pa'i dus na rdo rje la sogs pa mtshon cha rnam pa lnga'i rim pa /
NK053('i)001:2601: phyogs mtshams gur la sogs te /
NK053('i)001:2604: a cang yang ces srid pa'i rlung yang mi thar ba'i nang na /
NK053('i)001:2605: rnal 'byor pa rnams dgongs pa bag yangs su spyod par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:2606: de la sngags tshig 'dis don 'grub par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:2610: badz+ra dz+wa la badz+ra h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2611: b+h+r+aum h'u b+h+r+aum t+r+aam b+h+r+aum h+r+ai b+h+r+aum h+aa b+h+aum /
NK053('i)001:2612: rim bzhin 'khor lo rdo rje rin chen pad+ma rgya gram bcas kyi thog /
NK053('i)001:2614: mtshon cha 'byung zhing byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:2615: mtshon cha re re'i rab dang gur du bya ba ni 'di skad du /
NK053('i)001:2617: nga yi dkyil 'khor brtag bya'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:2618: khro rgyal byin rlabs las byung ba'i //
NK053('i)001:2619: mtshon cha rnam pa sna tshogs kyis //
NK053('i)001:2620: dkyil 'khor rim pa tshul bzhin srung //
NK053('i)001:2622: steng yang rdo rje'i bla re la //
NK053('i)001:2624: phyogs mtshams rdo rjes gtams pa la //
NK053('i)001:2625: rdo rje'i mtshams las ma 'da' zhig /
NK053('i)001:2626: h'u badz+ra badz+ra rak+sha h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2631: rgya gram gyis mtshams bcad de /
NK053('i)001:2636: t+r+aam badz+ra ka la ru pa sha h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2638: s+w+aa badz+ra ma h+aa ro sha khang+ga h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2640: h+aa badz+ra karma sa t+wo ha ha h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2644: rdo rje'i 'gros dang stang stabs dang //
NK053('i)001:2645: nang rim nas rdo rje 'khor lo ral gri dang //
NK053('i)001:2646: dbyug to rgya gram rnam pa lngas //
NK053('i)001:2647: steng 'og phyogs mtshams kun rim pa bzhin du bcad byas nas //
NK053('i)001:2648: ci yang mi gnas shing bgegs kyis cis mi shig /
NK053('i)001:2650: de nas srung ba'i 'khor lo'i mtshams ni /
NK053('i)001:2651: zhe sdang rdo rje'i thugs ka nas /
NK053('i)001:2653: h'u k+aa ra badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2655: mdun du khro bo h'u k+aa ra /
NK053('i)001:2656: zhal gsum mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK053('i)001:2657: phyag drug pa phyag g.yas g.yon dang po gnyis h'u gi phyag rgya byang chub mchog gi phyag rgya /
NK053('i)001:2659: g.yas rdo rje dang g.yon dril bu 'dzin pa /
NK053('i)001:2660: g.yas g.yon bar ma gnyis na lcags kyu dang ral gri 'dzin pa /
NK053('i)001:2661: g.yas g.yon 'og ma gnyis na dgra s+t+wa dang zhags pa bsnams pa /
NK053('i)001:2662: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng na /
NK053('i)001:2663: zhabs g.yon bskum g.yas brkyang ba /
NK053('i)001:2664: smin mtshams kyi khro gnyer dang /
NK053('i)001:2665: sdang mig dang spyan rtsa dmar ba /
NK053('i)001:2666: bskal pa'i me 'bar ba'i klong na /
NK053('i)001:2667: dper na zhe sdang rdo rje rgyal po la h'u
NK053('i)001:2668: k+aa ra blon po bka' nod pa'i tshul du bsam
NK053('i)001:2669: nas / de la bka' stsal pa /
NK053('i)001:2675: khro bo nyid kyis zungs la non cig /
NK053('i)001:2676: gri h+na pa ya gri h+na pa ya h'u /
NK053('i)001:2677: 'khor rnams kyis zungs la non cig /
NK053('i)001:2678: a na ya hoh dgra bgegs zungs la khrid de shog /
NK053('i)001:2680: bid+ya r+aa dza ya rig pa'i rgyal po /
NK053('i)001:2683: khro bo gnod mdzes zhal gcig phyag brgyad par gsang 'dus nas bshad do //
NK053('i)001:2685: phyogs bcur khro bo bcu'i gdan things shig par bka' stsal pa dang /
NK053('i)001:2686: h'u k+aa ra yi thugs ka nas /
NK053('i)001:2687: t+aa ki r+aa dza ma h+aa kro ta h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2689: khro bo t+aa ki r+aa dza sku mdog dmar smug /
NK053('i)001:2692: h'u k+aa ra las t+aa ki r+aa dzar blon po las mi bka' nod pa'i tshul du bsam te /
NK053('i)001:2693: de la phyogs bcu khro bo bcu'i gdan things shig par bka' stsal pa dang /
NK053('i)001:2694: t+aa ki r+aa dzas sum+b+ha ni'i sngags dang /
NK053('i)001:2695: shar du in+d+ra ye dri za pho mo //
NK053('i)001:2705: nub tu ba ru na ya /
NK053('i)001:2719: khro bo t+aa ki r+aa dzas phyogs skyong ba bcu
NK053('i)001:2720: g.yon pa'i lcags kyus bzung g.yas pa'i tho bas brdungs
NK053('i)001:2721: te / rdo rje'i brag dang nyi ma'i steng du /
NK053('i)001:2722: zhe sdang gi rtags pho kha sbub /
NK053('i)001:2723: 'dod chags kyi rtags mo gan rkyal du /
NK053('i)001:2725: mo mgo g.yon du mgo mjug tu bsnol te gdan du btings nas /
NK053('i)001:2726: t+aa ki r+aa dzas h'u k+aa ra la zhus pa /
NK053('i)001:2727: gdan gting lags so bcom ldan khro rgyal gtso //
NK053('i)001:2728: gdug pa'i tshogs rnams ma lus 'dul ba dang //
NK053('i)001:2729: zhe sdang rdo rje'i thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas //
NK053('i)001:2730: khro bo'i sprul pa phyogs bcur dgye ru gsol //
NK053('i)001:2732: t+aa k+ai r+aa dza h'u k+aa ra'i thugs kar thim nas mi snang bar gyur to //
NK053('i)001:2733: h'u k+aa ra yang zhe sdang rdo rje'i thugs kar thim nas mi snang bar gyur to //
NK053('i)001:2734: de nas seng ldeng gi phur pa bcu la zhe
NK053('i)001:2735: sdang rdo rje'i thugs ka nas yi ge h'u bcu
NK053('i)001:2736: spros te / phur pa bcu la thim pa las /
NK053('i)001:2737: phur pa'i dngos po bsregs nas /
NK053('i)001:2738: yi ge h'u bcur gyur pa las /
NK053('i)001:2739: h'u h'u k+aa ra h'u mdzad badz+ra rdo rje ma h+aa kro d+ha khro bo chen po h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2740: steng du phyogs skyong lha'i steng du h'u k+aa ra /
NK053('i)001:2741: h'u bi dza ya badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2742: shar dri za'i steng rnam par rgyal ba /
NK053('i)001:2743: h'u n+ai la dan+da badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2744: shar lho me lha'i steng dbyug pa sngon po /
NK053('i)001:2745: h'u ya m+aan+ta ka badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2746: lhor gshin rje'i steng gshin rje gshed /
NK053('i)001:2747: h'u +aar+ya a tsa la badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2748: lhoo nub srin po'i steng mi g.yo mgon po /
NK053('i)001:2749: h'u h+ya g+r+ai wa badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2751: h'u a pa ra tsit+ta badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2752: nub byang rlung lha'i steng 'dod pa'i rgyal po /
NK053('i)001:2753: h'u a mri ta kun+da l+ai badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2754: byang gnod sbyin steng bdud rtsi 'khyil ba /
NK053('i)001:2755: h'u tree lo kya bi dza ya badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2756: byang shar bgegs kyi steng khams gsum rnam rgyal /
NK053('i)001:2757: h'u ma h+aa ba la badz+ra ma h+aa kro ta h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2758: 'og sa bdag steng du stobs po che /
NK053('i)001:2760: ye shes kyi khro bo bcu sku stod zhal gsum phyag drug pa /
NK053('i)001:2761: phyag mtshan sna tshogs bsnams pa /
NK053('i)001:2762: sku smad lcags kyi phur pa zur gsum pa /
NK053('i)001:2764: sku mdog mthing nag la gzugs rags pa /
NK053('i)001:2765: dbu skra kham nag ral pa zur gsum gyen du 'greng ba /
NK053('i)001:2766: zhal gsum nas phata kyi sgra sgrog pa /
NK053('i)001:2767: spyan gsum sdang mig tu gzigs shing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK053('i)001:2768: sprul dang thod pa'i phreng bas mdzes par brgyan pa /
NK053('i)001:2769: bskal pa'i me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na /
NK053('i)001:2770: ye shes kyi 'od zer 'phro zhing 'khrug par bsams te /
NK053('i)001:2771: phyogs bcur rim pa bzhin bsgoms nas /
NK053('i)001:2772: seng ldeng phur pa de la gu gul gyis bdug pa dang /
NK053('i)001:2773: yungs kar gyis dbang bskur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:2775: rang bzhin gyi gnas nas spyan drangs shing dbyer med par bstim pa dang /
NK053('i)001:2778: bstod pa yan chad man ngag las shes par byas nas /
NK053('i)001:2779: rgyas par las byang ltar bya /
NK053('i)001:2780: bsdus pa ting nge 'dzin gyis bya /
NK053('i)001:2781: badz+ra kro ta k+ai li k+ai la ya h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2782: ces brgya rtsa brgyad kyis lhag par mthu bskyed nas /
NK053('i)001:2783: de nas bdud rtsi 'khyil ba bdag gi mdun du bkug ste /
NK053('i)001:2784: bdud rtsi 'khyil ba la rdo rje'i tho ba gtad de /
NK053('i)001:2785: phur pa gdab par bskul ba ni /
NK053('i)001:2786: rdo rje bdud rtsi 'khyil ba rgya chen po //
NK053('i)001:2787: gang zhig mnan pa'i mchog rnams la //
NK053('i)001:2788: khro rgyal 'bar ba bcu'i phur pa k+ai la yas //
NK053('i)001:2789: phyogs mtshams gdon rnams non par mdzod //
NK053('i)001:2791: bdud rtsi 'khyil bas rdo rje sder mo'i sngags /
NK053('i)001:2792: g+ha g+ha phur bu 'dril g+h+aa ta ya g+h+aa ta ya phur bus gdab tho bas brdung /
NK053('i)001:2793: sarba dush+ta snang bar byed pa thams cad /
NK053('i)001:2797: phur bus spyi bo nas gdab tho bas brdung /
NK053('i)001:2798: sarba p+aa bam sdig pa thams cad phata phata /
NK053('i)001:2799: h'u h'u h'u badz+ra k+ai la ya /
NK053('i)001:2801: badz+ra d+ha ro adz+ny+aa pa ya ti /
NK053('i)001:2802: rdo rje 'dzin gyi bka' nyon cig /
NK053('i)001:2803: sarba big+h+nam bgegs thams cad k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta
NK053('i)001:2804: badz+ra k+ai la ya sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje
NK053('i)001:2805: phur bu gdab / h'u h'u phata phata phata /
NK053('i)001:2806: ces brjod cing rim pas btab pas /
NK053('i)001:2807: phyogs skyong ba bcu thal phyung nas nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la dbal nus par bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:2808: de nas bdud rtsi 'khyil bas zhe sdang rdo rje la /
NK053('i)001:2809: tho ba gtad pa nyid kyis bdud rtsi 'khyil ba byang gnod sbyin la btab bo //
NK053('i)001:2810: de la phyogs skyong bcu ni bgegs thams cad kyi rgyal po yin la /
NK053('i)001:2811: de rnams gdan du bting pas /
NK053('i)001:2813: rgyal po btson du bzung na /
NK053('i)001:2815: bgegs phra mo gzhan gyis kyang bar chad byed nus par mi 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:2816: de yan chad du mtshams bcad nas /
NK053('i)001:2817: sngon du 'gro ba'i phrin las la don gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:2818: bsnyen pa sngon du 'gro ba'i phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:2819: sta gon gyi phrin las so //
NK053('i)001:2820: de la bsnyen pa sngon du 'gro ba'i phrin las ni /
NK053('i)001:2821: gong 'og tu bstan pa'i man ngag las shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2822: gong du rdzas sa gzhi mtshams sogs yin /
NK053('i)001:2824: sta gon la gnas pa'i phrin las la lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:2830: de la dkyil 'khor sta gon la gnas par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:2831: chu lci ba kha chu 'o ma mar te /
NK053('i)001:2832: ba byung rnam lngas legs byug ste /
NK053('i)001:2833: me long gi gsal ngos ltar 'jam pa mkhreg pa dkyil mtho bar byas la /
NK053('i)001:2834: dri sna lnga'i gong ltar chus legs par byug par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2835: de nas nyungs kar la rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi sngags bzlas la /
NK053('i)001:2836: dbus dang phyogs mtshams su gtor te bgegs bskrad par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2837: de nas lha sta gon la gnas par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:2838: bdag nyid chos nyid ye nas dag pa'i ngo bo las /
NK053('i)001:2839: rdzogs pa'i tshul du bskyed pa'am /
NK053('i)001:2840: h'u bzhis bskyed pa gang yang rung bas /
NK053('i)001:2841: bdag nyid rdo rje gnod sbyin las kyi lhar gsal bar byas la /
NK053('i)001:2842: de nas bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga'i lde gus man+dala
NK053('i)001:2843: la thig le lha'i grangs dang mnyam par bya zhing
NK053('i)001:2844: / rtsa ba'i snying po rnams lan bzhi bzhi brjod par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2845: de nas me tog gi tshom bu lha'i grangs dang mnyam par du dgram zhing /
NK053('i)001:2846: so sor bskyed pa'i snying po rnams lan bzhi bzhi brjod par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2847: de nas ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:2850: phyag dang mchod pa la sogs pa bya ste /
NK053('i)001:2851: tshig 'dis gsol ba gdab par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2853: kun la khyab bdag me long lta bu'i ye shes bdag nyid can //
NK053('i)001:2854: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' dang //
NK053('i)001:2855: yum chen kun tu bzang mo gnyis //
NK053('i)001:2856: deng nub bdag la dgongs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:2857: thugs brtser ldan pa'i dgongs pa can //
NK053('i)001:2858: khyed rnams la ni mchod pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:2859: rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor bzang po sang bri yis //
NK053('i)001:2860: byin yis brlab par mdzad du gsol //
NK053('i)001:2862: gnyis med ye shes las byung ba'i //
NK053('i)001:2863: bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad dang //
NK053('i)001:2864: yum chen sangs rgyas spyan dang gnyis //
NK053('i)001:2865: deng nub bdag la sogs man chad 'gre ste /
NK053('i)001:2866: de bzhin du sgo ba la thug pa yan chad bya ste //
NK053('i)001:2869: mnyam nyid ye shes bcom ldan rin chen 'byung ldan yum chen m+aa ma k+ai deng nub sogs /
NK053('i)001:2870: sor rtog ye shes bcom ldan snang ba mtha' yas yum chen na bza' dkar mo deng nub sogs /
NK053('i)001:2871: bya grub ye shes bcom ldan don yod grub pa yum chen dam tshig sgrol ma deng nub sogs /
NK053('i)001:2872: de nas rgyas par so so'am /
NK053('i)001:2874: tshogs brgyad gnas dag las byang chub sems dpa' brgyad rnams dang //
NK053('i)001:2875: yul brgyad dag pa'i sems ma brgyad //
NK053('i)001:2877: rtag chad mu bzhi gnas dag pa'i //
NK053('i)001:2878: sgo bzhi khro chen bzhi rnams dang //
NK053('i)001:2879: tshad med rnam bzhi sgo ma bzhi //
NK053('i)001:2881: 'di ltar sbyar na 'grig min gzigs par zhu /
NK053('i)001:2882: ye shes kyi lha rnams bdag dang slob mar bcas
NK053('i)001:2883: pa la zhal gzigs shing thugs la dgongs par brtag
NK053('i)001:2884: go // de nas slob dpon sta gon la gnas par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:2885: rgyal thebs dang karmasa nub phyogs su man+dala legs par byas te /
NK053('i)001:2886: dri sna lngas byug cing me tog gi gcal bkrams nas /
NK053('i)001:2887: de'i steng du ras dang dar la sogs pa bting la /
NK053('i)001:2888: der bla ma spyan drangs shing bzhugs su gsol nas /
NK053('i)001:2889: dza gad phyag tu bzhugs nas /
NK053('i)001:2891: gang dbang dang man ngag 'dod pa de byin gyis brlab par mdzad du gsol /
NK053('i)001:2893: rdzas dang yo byad sta gon la gnas par bya ba la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:2895: de la rdzas la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:2898: de kun spyi 'og nas ji skad smos pa bzhin du bsags par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:2899: khyad par du dbang bskur ba'i rdzas /
NK053('i)001:2900: bum pa sta gon la gnas par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:2901: rgyu gser ram dngul gyi bum pa tshad dang ldan pa /
NK053('i)001:2902: bre gang yan chad shong ba /
NK053('i)001:2907: de la bum pa nag nog ra ri med pa gnyis la /
NK053('i)001:2908: gcig rnam bum la tshon rtsi bzang pos rigs lnga'i phyag mtshan rdo rje /
NK053('i)001:2914: gcig las bum la ni rdo rje rgya gram bri'o //
NK053('i)001:2915: de la dbang bskur ba'i bum pa byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:2917: nyungs kar la rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi sngags bzlas te gtor nas bgegs bskrad do //
NK053('i)001:2918: de nas bdag gi thugs ka nas yi ge a dkar po gcig byung ste /
NK053('i)001:2919: bum pa'i dngos po sbyangs nas /
NK053('i)001:2920: chos nyid stong pa nyid du gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:2921: de'i gang la yi ge mum gcig tu gsal ba las spro bsdu byas pas /
NK053('i)001:2922: gser gyi dril bu gcig tu gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:2926: yum kun tu bzang mo mtshan dang dpe byad dang ldan pa gcig bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:2929: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud dang bcas /
NK053('i)001:2932: sgo bzhi dang bcas pa so so'i gdan dag bcas pa gcig tu bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:2933: de'i nang du sman lnga dang /
NK053('i)001:2936: rin po che sna lnga dang /
NK053('i)001:2938: bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga'i chu blugs te /
NK053('i)001:2939: de nas bdag gi thugs ka nas /
NK053('i)001:2941: yum gyi mkha' la bstim pa ni /
NK053('i)001:2944: ta t+aa la sogs pa gang yang rung ba bkod de /
NK053('i)001:2945: rdzas rnams so sor 'od du zhu ba las /
NK053('i)001:2947: h'u badz+ra d+h+rika la sogs brjod pas /
NK053('i)001:2948: bud+d+ha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi sku yum gyi mkha' la gsal bar bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:2949: shing tsan+dana la sogs pa la yal ga dang lo
NK053('i)001:2950: ma me tog 'bras bur ldan pas bum pa'i kha
NK053('i)001:2951: brgyan no // man+dala gyi dbus su bzhugs su gsol nas /
NK053('i)001:2952: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing bstim pa dang /
NK053('i)001:2954: phyag dang mchod pas mchod de /
NK053('i)001:2958: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlab bo //
NK053('i)001:2959: las byang nas 'byung ba bzhin bya'o //
NK053('i)001:2960: de nas las kyi bum pa byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:2961: bum pa b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang du gsal ba'i nang du /
NK053('i)001:2962: ma las nyi ma'i steng du yi ge h'u gi 'phro 'du las /
NK053('i)001:2963: badz+ra yak+sha big+h+nana ta krit+ta h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:2965: rdo rje gnod sbyin sku mdog ljang gu /
NK053('i)001:2968: zhabs brkyang bskum gyis bzhugs pa /
NK053('i)001:2969: dur khrod kyi rgyan dang ldan pa gcig bskyed la /
NK053('i)001:2970: de la phyag rgya bzhis spyan drangs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:2973: phyag dang mchod pas mchod do //
NK053('i)001:2974: gong gi snying po badz+ra yak+sha brgya brtsa brgyad bzlas so //
NK053('i)001:2982: zhes dus drug tu lan bdun bdun bzlas shing bum pa'i mthun bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:2984: dbang rdzas dang yo byed la sogs pa /
NK053('i)001:2985: gong 'og tu smros pa kun kyang /
NK053('i)001:2986: lta gon la tshogs par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:2988: de nas slob ma sta gon la gnas par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:2990: slob ma sta gon du gnas pa la don bcu bdun te /
NK053('i)001:2991: dang po bsre bsnan gyi sta gon man+dala bshams pa dang /
NK053('i)001:2992: gnyis pa slob ma nang du 'bod pa /
NK053('i)001:2993: gsum pa slob mas drug rnam dag bya ba /
NK053('i)001:2994: bzhi pa slob dpon gyis sems bskyed cing slob mas khas blang ba /
NK053('i)001:2996: drug pa mig phye bar zhu ba /
NK053('i)001:2998: brgyad pa me tog bor ba /
NK053('i)001:2999: dgu pa gsang mtshan gdags pa /
NK053('i)001:3000: bcu pa swo shing gi cho ga /
NK053('i)001:3001: bcu gcig pa bsrung skud gdags pa /
NK053('i)001:3002: bcu gnyis pa snying po dpog cing phreng ba gtad pa /
NK053('i)001:3003: bcu gsum pa ku sha gding ba /
NK053('i)001:3004: bcu bzhi pa rdo rje'i gral du bzhad pa /
NK053('i)001:3005: bco lnga pa gtang rag btang ba /
NK053('i)001:3006: bcu drug pa mchod pa gzhung bsrang ba /
NK053('i)001:3007: bcu bdun pa rmi lam brtag pa'o //
NK053('i)001:3008: dang po man+dala bshams pa ni /
NK053('i)001:3009: karma las dang bya ba la mkhas pas /
NK053('i)001:3010: shar ngos su man+dala legs par byas te /
NK053('i)001:3011: ba byung rnam pa lngas byug pa'i ko ba tsam du byas nas /
NK053('i)001:3012: gnyis pa slob ma nang du 'bod pa /
NK053('i)001:3013: de nas slob ma dbang dang man ngag gi snod du rung ba brtag pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3014: sgrub pa po sngar dam ma 'dres pa rnams phyir phyes la mig ras kyis bkag /
NK053('i)001:3015: 'dres pa rnams nang du bos pa 'di skad du brjod par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:3016: kye kye rigs kyi bu tshur gshegs //
NK053('i)001:3017: khyod ni theg pa chen po'i gsang sngags kyi rigs //
NK053('i)001:3018: gsang sngags zab mo'i snod yin pas //
NK053('i)001:3019: gsang sngags cho ga zab mo 'di //
NK053('i)001:3020: khyod la yang dag bshad par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:3021: rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas 'das pa dang //
NK053('i)001:3022: de bzhin gang dag ma byon dang //
NK053('i)001:3023: da ltar bzhugs pa'i rdzogs sangs rgyas //
NK053('i)001:3024: de dag kun gyis gsang sngags kyi //
NK053('i)001:3025: cho ga zab mo 'di mkhyen pas //
NK053('i)001:3026: sngon byung yang dang po byang chub shing drung du //
NK053('i)001:3027: thams cad mkhyen pa'i chos sku brnyes //
NK053('i)001:3028: gsang sngags lta spyod zab mo 'dis //
NK053('i)001:3029: skyobs pa rdo rje sems dpa' des //
NK053('i)001:3030: bdud sde shin tu mi bzad pa'i //
NK053('i)001:3031: dpung chen dag kyang de yis bcom //
NK053('i)001:3032: de bas kun mkhyen thob pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:3033: bu yi blo gros dus 'dir bya //
NK053('i)001:3035: gsum pa slob mas drug rnam dag bya ba la /
NK053('i)001:3036: dang po phyag 'tshal ba'i yan lag ni /
NK053('i)001:3037: de nas slob ma rnams kyis 'di skad du brjod do //
NK053('i)001:3038: dkon mchog gsum dang yi dam lha //
NK053('i)001:3039: dus gsum bder gshegs thams cad dang //
NK053('i)001:3040: pho brang zhi khro'i lha tshogs la //
NK053('i)001:3041: lus ngag yid gsum phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:3042: 'jig rten 'di na gnyen sdug gang bas kyang //
NK053('i)001:3043: lhag pa'i 'dren ston bla ma rin po che //
NK053('i)001:3044: yon tan mang po 'byung ba'i mdzod mnga' ba //
NK053('i)001:3045: slob dpon lha gnyen dpal la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:3046: tshe rabs sngon tshe gong nas 'phro mthud pa'i //
NK053('i)001:3047: dus 'dir dam tshig gcig pas rdo rje'i rgyan //
NK053('i)001:3048: 'di dang phyi ma gnyis ka mi 'bral ba'i //
NK053('i)001:3049: rdo rje'i mched lcam tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:3050: gnyis pa skyabs su 'gro ba'i yan lag ni /
NK053('i)001:3051: sangs rgyas chos dang dge 'dun dang //
NK053('i)001:3052: dus gsum bder gshegs thams cad dang //
NK053('i)001:3053: yi dam lha dang bla ma la //
NK053('i)001:3054: rtag tu bdag ni skyabs su mchi'o //
NK053('i)001:3055: thugs rje che dang ldan pa yi //
NK053('i)001:3056: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK053('i)001:3057: dkyil 'khor bzhugs pa'i lha rnams la //
NK053('i)001:3058: rtag tu bdag ni skyabs su mchi //
NK053('i)001:3059: khyad par rdo rje slob dpon dang //
NK053('i)001:3061: byang chub rdo rje lcam dral la //
NK053('i)001:3062: rtag tu bdag ni skyabs su mchi'o //
NK053('i)001:3063: gsum pa mchod pa 'bul ba'i yan lag /
NK053('i)001:3064: dkon mchog bla ma lha tshogs 'khor bcas la //
NK053('i)001:3065: lus ngag yid gsum longs spyod 'khor dang bcas //
NK053('i)001:3066: dngos su 'byor dang yid kyis rnam sprul pa'i //
NK053('i)001:3067: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rgya mtshos mchod //
NK053('i)001:3068: bzhi pa sdig pa bshags pa'i yan lag /
NK053('i)001:3069: tshe rabs thog ma med pa'i sngon rol nas //
NK053('i)001:3070: da lta'i lus 'di blangs pa phan chad du //
NK053('i)001:3071: sdig sgrib bsags pa ma lus thams cad dang //
NK053('i)001:3072: dam tshigs nyams par gyur pa mthol lo bshags //
NK053('i)001:3073: lnga pa rjes su yi rang ba /
NK053('i)001:3074: thams cad ye rdzogs lha yi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:3075: sngon nas da lta yan chod rnal 'byor pas //
NK053('i)001:3076: dge ba'i las rnams rdzogs par bgyis pa la //
NK053('i)001:3077: de dag kun la rjes su yi rang ngo //
NK053('i)001:3078: drug pa byin rlabs zhu ba ni /
NK053('i)001:3079: bdag cag 'khor ba'i sems can rnams //
NK053('i)001:3080: ma rig rmongs pa'i bag chags kyis //
NK053('i)001:3082: thugs rjes byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK053('i)001:3083: de skad ces brjod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3084: bzhi pa slob dpon gyis sems bskyed cing /
NK053('i)001:3087: gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:3088: bla med 'bras bu bsgrub pa dang //
NK053('i)001:3089: bde gshegs dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:3090: byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:3093: bdag kyang dus 'di phan chad nas //
NK053('i)001:3094: byang chub snying po'i bar du ni //
NK053('i)001:3095: bla ma'i bka' bzhin bsgrub lags kyis //
NK053('i)001:3096: sman pa tshul bzhin dpog tu gsol //
NK053('i)001:3102: badz+ra yak+sha kro ta ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:3103: ces bdud rtsi byin gyis brlabs la /
NK053('i)001:3105: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs dang yan lag bcas //
NK053('i)001:3106: mi 'da' ma grub bar du bsrung ngo zhes //
NK053('i)001:3107: yang nas yang du dam bca' byas pa 'di //
NK053('i)001:3108: lus dang srog la bab kyang ma btang shig /
NK053('i)001:3111: rtsa ba dang yan lag gis bsdus pa'i dam tshig phog la /
NK053('i)001:3114: ji snyed sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK053('i)001:3115: byang chub sems dang rdo rje 'dzin //
NK053('i)001:3116: de bzhin sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor pa //
NK053('i)001:3117: de dag la ni snying ring na //
NK053('i)001:3118: rdo rje yak+sha gnod sbyin gyis //
NK053('i)001:3119: khyod kyi snying la bzhos te btung //
NK053('i)001:3121: snying la yang dag gnas pa yi //
NK053('i)001:3122: 'di ni sems can dmyal ba'i chu //
NK053('i)001:3123: dam tshig nyams na sreg par byed //
NK053('i)001:3124: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ni //
NK053('i)001:3126: i dan te na ra kan /
NK053('i)001:3127: sa ma ya ya kyi h'u /
NK053('i)001:3129: bdud rtsi h'u du gyur pa blangs te lce la bzhag pas /
NK053('i)001:3130: h'u kho'i snying khar zhugs te /
NK053('i)001:3131: slob ma'i shes pa h'u du byin brlabs so //
NK053('i)001:3132: drug pa mig dbye bar zhu ba /
NK053('i)001:3135: ma rig mig gi ling thog gis //
NK053('i)001:3136: shin tu mdongs par gyur lags pas //
NK053('i)001:3137: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK053('i)001:3138: nyon mongs sgrib pa bsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:3142: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i sems can rnams //
NK053('i)001:3143: bu khyod kyis ni mi shes pa'i //
NK053('i)001:3144: ma rig pa yi ling thog rnams //
NK053('i)001:3145: bde gshegs dgongs pas bsal bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:3150: brgyad pa me tog dor ba /
NK053('i)001:3153: dus gsum bder gshegs rgyal ba kun gyi thugs //
NK053('i)001:3154: rdo rje sems dpa' yi dam lha mchog 'di //
NK053('i)001:3155: rtse gcig sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor zab mo'i thugs //
NK053('i)001:3156: da lta nyid du bdag la dpog tu gsol //
NK053('i)001:3157: zhes brjod de me tog bor ro //
NK053('i)001:3158: de nas slob ma mdun du bzhag la /
NK053('i)001:3159: slob dpon gyi thugs ka'i zla ba la h'u yig sngon po /
NK053('i)001:3162: slob ma'i lus la thim pas /
NK053('i)001:3163: ye shes kyi 'od zer ram yig 'bar ba'i rang
NK053('i)001:3164: bzhin gyis nye bar len pa'i bag chags ngan pa
NK053('i)001:3165: / bud shing dang 'dra ba bsregs sbyangs nas /
NK053('i)001:3166: sems mar me lta bur gsal ba las dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i snying pos h'u badz+ra d+h+rika /
NK053('i)001:3167: slob ma dpal rdo rje sems dpa' ci 'dra bar byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:3168: de las yi ge +aahmh'u 'bru gsum gyis sku gsung
NK053('i)001:3169: thugs rdo rje'i rang bzhin du byin gyis brlab pa
NK053('i)001:3171: dpal ldan rdo rje sku gsung thugs 'chang ba //
NK053('i)001:3172: rdo rje mi phyed sku gsung thugs dang ldan //
NK053('i)001:3173: deng bdag lha mchog sku gsung thugs 'dzin pa //
NK053('i)001:3174: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub khyod la sbyin //
NK053('i)001:3175: ye shes lnga sarba ta th+aa ga ta de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi /
NK053('i)001:3176: k+aa ya w+aaka tsit+ta badz+ra sku gsung thugs rdo rje'i /
NK053('i)001:3179: bdud rtsi lce la lan gsum du bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:3180: thig le gnas bzhir bya'ang gsungs /
NK053('i)001:3181: de nas me tog blangs te spyi bor bzhag nas /
NK053('i)001:3182: sngon tshe tshe rabs grangs med nas /
NK053('i)001:3183: dag pa'i las kyis bsten pa'i lha //
NK053('i)001:3184: yi dam lha mchog dam pa 'di //
NK053('i)001:3185: da lta nyid du khyod la dbab //
NK053('i)001:3187: lha'i snying po dang phyag rgyas dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:3188: dgu pa gsang mtshan gdags pa /
NK053('i)001:3189: bar 'dir gsang ba'i mtshan bris la /
NK053('i)001:3190: med na gsang mtshan yang gdags te /
NK053('i)001:3191: 'di ni rdo rje ming gi dbang //
NK053('i)001:3192: mtshan mchog 'dis ni dbang bskur bas //
NK053('i)001:3193: sangs rgyas zhing du grags pa yi //
NK053('i)001:3196: rdo rje che ge mo zhes gdags so //
NK053('i)001:3197: bcu pa so shing dang khyor chu byin pa /
NK053('i)001:3198: de nas so shing gi cho ga bya ba ste /
NK053('i)001:3199: shing u dum b+aa ra la sogs pa'i dri zhim po la /
NK053('i)001:3201: sor bcu gnyis pa'i tshad du byas pa la /
NK053('i)001:3202: ya yo med cing 'bu srin gyis ma zos pa la /
NK053('i)001:3203: dris byug ste bdud rtsi'i chu bkrus pa la /
NK053('i)001:3204: rtse mo la u dum w+aa ra dang /
NK053('i)001:3205: a shwa tha'i me tog bcings pa yin te /
NK053('i)001:3207: zhes byin gyis brlabs la byin te /
NK053('i)001:3208: shar phyogs su kha bltas la so shing baca'o //
NK053('i)001:3210: man+dala steng du so shing bor du stsal //
NK053('i)001:3211: de'i tshe gar yo brtag par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:3212: de nas gdong pa dang lag pa las kyi bum pa'i chus bkrus te /
NK053('i)001:3213: h+r+ai bi shud+ha d+har+m+aa sarba p+aa pam ni tsa s+ya
NK053('i)001:3214: shwa d+ha ya sarba bi kalpa la a ba na
NK053('i)001:3215: ya h'u / zhes chu khyor ba gsum 'thung du gzhug /
NK053('i)001:3216: bcu gcig pa srung skud gdags pa /
NK053('i)001:3217: de nas srug skud dmar po la /
NK053('i)001:3218: bud+d+ha mee tri rak+sha rak+sha sarba na h'u a ham /
NK053('i)001:3219: zhes dpung pa la gdags shing mdud pa gsum gsum bya'o //
NK053('i)001:3220: bcu gnyis pa snying po dpog pa dang phreng ba gtad la /
NK053('i)001:3221: de nas snying po dpog par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:3222: 'das dang ma byon da lta dus gsum lha //
NK053('i)001:3223: dus gsum bde gshegs thugs kyi snying po 'di //
NK053('i)001:3224: da lta nyid du khyod la dpog par bya //
NK053('i)001:3226: ces bya ba la sogs kyis dpog /
NK053('i)001:3229: rig pa srog gis 'brel ba'i phreng thag la //
NK053('i)001:3230: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba'i phreng ba brgyus //
NK053('i)001:3231: rtse gcig lha dang 'grogs pa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK053('i)001:3232: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bsgrub par bya //
NK053('i)001:3234: bcu gsum pa ku sha gding ba /
NK053('i)001:3236: +aahmh'u gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs pa'i r+ts+wa ku sha'i gdan 'ding zhing sbyin par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:3237: bcu bzhi pa rdo rje'i gral du bzhag pa /
NK053('i)001:3238: de nas yang rdo rje'i gral du bzhag pa ni /
NK053('i)001:3239: rtsa ba sku gsung thugs kyi dam tshig dang //
NK053('i)001:3240: bsnyen sgrub rnam bzhi bsnyen cing sgrub pa dang //
NK053('i)001:3241: yi dam lha mchod 'dzab bsnyen bgrang ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:3242: dam tshig rdo rje'i gral du mchis par gnang //
NK053('i)001:3244: zhes tshul 'di lta bu 'di ni rnal 'byor pa re re la bya ba yin te /
NK053('i)001:3245: sngar ma 'dres pa rnams dang dam tshig bsre ba yin la /
NK053('i)001:3246: 'dres pa rnams la bsnan pa yin te /
NK053('i)001:3248: gsang ba'i las la 'jug pa'i dus //
NK053('i)001:3249: ma 'dres pa yi mched lcam la //
NK053('i)001:3250: bsre zhing mnan pa ma byas na //
NK053('i)001:3251: bde gshegs rgyal ba'i thugs dang 'gal //
NK053('i)001:3254: bco lnga pa gtang rag btang ba /
NK053('i)001:3255: de nas slob ma rnams kyis /
NK053('i)001:3256: yi dam lha dang slob dpon la /
NK053('i)001:3257: rang rang gsang mtshan nas brjod do /
NK053('i)001:3260: dza gad thogs la gtang rag btag pa /
NK053('i)001:3261: dam tshig dbang dang shes rgyud lung ston cing //
NK053('i)001:3262: tshe 'di nyid la 'bras bu mthar phyin pa'i //
NK053('i)001:3263: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon rin po che //
NK053('i)001:3264: bka' drin rjes su dran phyir gtang rag gtong //
NK053('i)001:3266: bcu drug pa mchod pa gzhung bsrung ba /
NK053('i)001:3267: de nas mchod pa gzhung bzhin du bshams la /
NK053('i)001:3270: sgrub pa po rnams rang rang gi yi dam lhar bsgom zhing snying po bzlas /
NK053('i)001:3271: gong ltar rgyu lnga bsgral ba'i sha 'bras bu'i bskang bshags bya /
NK053('i)001:3272: tshogs kyis mchod pa'i rjes la /
NK053('i)001:3273: lha dang slob dpon rig 'dzin srung ma mchod /
NK053('i)001:3275: khyad par du dam tshig can du gyur pa'i mgron la /
NK053('i)001:3276: gtor ma dang lhag ma bsdus te phul nas /
NK053('i)001:3277: phrin las drug tu bcol te /
NK053('i)001:3278: sngon dpal chen po'i spyan sngar khas blangs shing dam bcas pa bzhin /
NK053('i)001:3279: bsnyen sgrub zab mo 'di la do nub zhugs nas /
NK053('i)001:3280: nam ma thon gyi bar du /
NK053('i)001:3281: phyi'i dgra bgegs nang du mi gtong ba dang /
NK053('i)001:3282: nang gi dngos grub phyir mi gtong zhing dgra bgegs
NK053('i)001:3283: kyi bar chad ci yang mi 'byung bar mdzad du
NK053('i)001:3284: gsol // zhes byas la las bcol lo //
NK053('i)001:3285: bcu bdun pa rmi lam brtags pa /
NK053('i)001:3286: de nas nyal te rmi lam brtag par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:3287: rmi lam ngan na spog pa'i cho ga bya'o //
NK053('i)001:3288: de la sngon du 'gro ba'i rim pas /
NK053('i)001:3289: bsod nams kyi tshogs bsags pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3291: phyi nang gi mtshams bcad pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3292: sta gon la gnas pa'i rim pas sgrub pa po
NK053('i)001:3293: dbang dang dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar bya'o
NK053('i)001:3297: 2 / de la ma tram mnan pa'i phrin las gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:3298: de nas dur khrod bdag po dag /
NK053('i)001:3299: phyag rgya che dang ldan par ni //
NK053('i)001:3300: ci rigs su ni las rnams bya //
NK053('i)001:3302: de ltar sngon du 'gro ba'i las song nas /
NK053('i)001:3303: dur khrod kyi bdag po mnan pa ston pa /
NK053('i)001:3306: de la dur khroda ces pa la bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:3311: de la lta ba'i dur khrod ni /
NK053('i)001:3312: snang srid thams cad dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa'i chos kyi sku /
NK053('i)001:3313: rang byung gi ye shes chen po'i klong de las /
NK053('i)001:3316: kun gzhi chos kyi dbyings kyi dur la /
NK053('i)001:3317: rnam par shes pa'i tshogs ni khrod do //
NK053('i)001:3319: ma tram gi khog pa nyid dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad du gyur pa ste /
NK053('i)001:3326: de yang khams gsum 'di nyid la /
NK053('i)001:3327: bdud ma tram ru tra dbang che zhing rtsal drags pa de'i khung bcad na /
NK053('i)001:3329: sngon ji ltar byung ba'i gleng gzhi bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3330: sngon ji ltar btul ba'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK053('i)001:3331: da lta 'dul ba'i thabs bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3332: btul nas gzhal yas khang du bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:3333: phrin las rnam pa bzhis 'khor yan chad dbang du bsdus te spobs pa med par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:3335: de la 1dang po sngon ji ltar byung ba'i gleng gzhi ni /
NK053('i)001:3336: sngon bskal pa grangs med pa /
NK053('i)001:3337: gang g+aa'i klung gi bye ma snyed /
NK053('i)001:3338: brgya dgu bcu 'das pa'i pha rol du /
NK053('i)001:3340: bskal pa'i ming ni gdul dka' ba /
NK053('i)001:3341: 'jig rten gyi ming ni 'byung dka' ba zhes pa der /
NK053('i)001:3342: sangs rgyas 'jig rten srid pa'i sgron ma zhes bya ba 'byung ba'i dus de'i tshe /
NK053('i)001:3343: slob dpon gyi ming ni rgyal ba'i 'khor lo zhes bya ba thub dka' gzhon nu zhes kyang bya /
NK053('i)001:3345: slob ma dge slong thar pa nag po zhes bya ba zhig yod pa la /
NK053('i)001:3346: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i don ni /
NK053('i)001:3352: man ngag ste gsang sngags kyi mtha' drug tu bsdus te bstan pa las /
NK053('i)001:3353: slob mas de ltar ma rtogs te /
NK053('i)001:3354: bdag dang bdag gir rang ka mar rtog pa'i dbang gis /
NK053('i)001:3357: sems ni gdug par gyur to //
NK053('i)001:3359: gab pa'i gsang ba chos nyid kyi don rang la rang chas su yod pa ma rtogs par /
NK053('i)001:3360: sbas pa'i gsang ba sbyor sgrol rang ka ma la mngon par 'chel ba'i dbang gis /
NK053('i)001:3361: srid pa'i sa bon rtsub mos 'phangs nas /
NK053('i)001:3362: dmyal ba tsha grang gi gnas su bskal pa stong
NK053('i)001:3363: phrag bcu gnyis su sdug bsngal nyams su myong ba
NK053('i)001:3364: byas so // der las kyi sgrib pa khad kyis srab nas /
NK053('i)001:3365: yi dwags kyi gnas su skyes te /
NK053('i)001:3366: der bskal pa stong phrag drug tu sdug bsngal nyams su myong bar byas so //
NK053('i)001:3367: de nas las kyi rnam par smin pa khang kyis srab nas /
NK053('i)001:3368: sngon gyi las kyi srid pas mtshams sbyar nas /
NK053('i)001:3369: yab dbang phyug chen po ma h+aa de ba dang /
NK053('i)001:3370: yum u ma de wa'i bur skyes te /
NK053('i)001:3371: bdud ru tra rab tu khro zhing gtum pa /
NK053('i)001:3372: gdug pa can 'jigs pa'i gzugs cir yang sprul nus pa /
NK053('i)001:3375: kha rlangs kyis gzhan la gnod cing thams cad skyi bung zhes byed par skyes te /
NK053('i)001:3376: ru tra des klu'i ris dang /
NK053('i)001:3377: lha ma yin gyi ris dang /
NK053('i)001:3378: lha'i ris 'bras bu che ba man chad dbang du bsdus shing 'dar yed yed btang ba /
NK053('i)001:3379: kho'i gnas khang dur khrod chen po'i gnas rab tu 'jigs shing skyi g.ya' ba'i gnas na /
NK053('i)001:3380: dur khrod chen po'i khang pa /
NK053('i)001:3381: thod pa tshar gsum las brtsigs pa la sogs pa'i nang na /
NK053('i)001:3382: ro gsar rnying mang pos gtams shing /
NK053('i)001:3383: sha khrag rus pa rul bal myags mnam pa'i nang de na /
NK053('i)001:3384: ru tra de dang las kyis bstun pa'i yum srin mo kro ti shwa ri ma zhes bya ba /
NK053('i)001:3385: rab tu gdug cing mi bsrun pa dang gnyis khyo shug tu gnas so //
NK053('i)001:3387: ru tra de dang las kyis bstun pa'i 'khor /
NK053('i)001:3388: srin mo tsa su ra mu ka /
NK053('i)001:3389: n+aa ga su ra mu ka /
NK053('i)001:3401: hri ra ha ya mu ka /
NK053('i)001:3417: nyi shu rtsa brgyad dngos dbang phyug ma'o //
NK053('i)001:3418: lha chen po la sogs khyoo nyer brgyad dang bcas /
NK053('i)001:3421: phyi rol gyi 'khor na gnas so //
NK053('i)001:3422: de ni ru tra de'i bdag 'dzin las gyur pa'i 'khor ro //
NK053('i)001:3423: gzhan yang gnas de'i grwa bzhin /
NK053('i)001:3424: srin mo ro ga ma dang /
NK053('i)001:3427: re ma ti dang bzhi gnas so //
NK053('i)001:3428: ru tra'i khrag rus pa drod dbugs nang gi 'byung ba bzhi las sprul pa'i 'khor ro //
NK053('i)001:3430: gnas de'i shar sgo na rta /
NK053('i)001:3433: byang sgo na khyi dang bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:3434: de ni ru tra'i rtag chad bdag mtshan bzhi las sprul pa'i 'khor ro //
NK053('i)001:3445: 'di rnams ru tra'i tshogs brgyad kyi yul brgyad las sprul pa'i 'khor ro //
NK053('i)001:3446: 'di rnams sed+ha ma brgyad kyi ma'o //
NK053('i)001:3448: sring mo la ma ge ri /
NK053('i)001:3449: kha 'da' ro ha ru pi ni /
NK053('i)001:3456: 'di rnam par shes pa sgo lnga'i rnam shes /
NK053('i)001:3462: de rnams la dbang bsgyur te /
NK053('i)001:3464: steng lha bar mi 'og klu ste srid gsum la dbang bsgyur zhing /
NK053('i)001:3465: 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad du /
NK053('i)001:3466: rang rang gi cha lugs 'jigs par byed pa /
NK053('i)001:3467: gdug byed kyi mtshon cha sna tshogs thogs nas /
NK053('i)001:3468: rngam pa'i nga ro sgra skad sna tshogs par sgrogs shing /
NK053('i)001:3470: nga ro dri dang kha rlangs sna bug g.yas g.yon
NK053('i)001:3471: nas tsha grang gi nad kyis thams cad skyi bung
NK053('i)001:3472: zhes pa / rab tu 'jigs pa'i rlung nag dang
NK053('i)001:3473: grang ba dang tsha ba'i dug gis phyogs bcu kun
NK053('i)001:3474: tu sems can kun khams 'khrugs par byed pa /
NK053('i)001:3475: nad bzhi brgya rtsa bzhis 'debs par byed pa /
NK053('i)001:3476: myos shing nyams par byed pa /
NK053('i)001:3477: dus ma yin pa'i dus dang /
NK053('i)001:3478: bskal pa ma yin pa'i bskal pa cher gtor bar byed pa /
NK053('i)001:3479: phyir bcud nam mkha' dang 'byung bzhi'i 'jig rten gsum la khyab cing 'khrug par byed pa /
NK053('i)001:3480: nang du sems can thams cad kyi lus ngag yid gsum la khyab cing 'khrug par byed do //
NK053('i)001:3482: daga ces bya ba'i sgra ni mang po la snyegs pa ste /
NK053('i)001:3484: ru tra la brgyad yod de /
NK053('i)001:3485: ma tram ka ru tra dang /
NK053('i)001:3486: kha tram kha ru tra dang /
NK053('i)001:3487: a ka ra sha ru tra /
NK053('i)001:3493: de la ma tram ka ru tra ni /
NK053('i)001:3494: phyi'i yul la dngos por bltas shing mtshan mar rang rgyud bzung ba las byung ste /
NK053('i)001:3495: snod kyi 'jig rten dang sems can ril gyi lus la khyab par gnas so //
NK053('i)001:3496: kha tram kha ru tra ni /
NK053('i)001:3497: sems can thams cad kyi nang sems la ngar 'dzin
NK053('i)001:3498: cing rtag chad gnyis su lta ba'i phyin ci log
NK053('i)001:3499: gi rtog pa las skyes te /
NK053('i)001:3500: bcud kyi 'jig rten gyi sems can gyi sems la khyab par gnas so //
NK053('i)001:3501: a kar sha ru tra ni /
NK053('i)001:3502: thams cad las la rgyu 'bras med cing /
NK053('i)001:3503: mtha' chad par lta ba las skyes te /
NK053('i)001:3504: sems can thams cad kyi ngag la khyab par gnas so //
NK053('i)001:3505: khams gsum gyi bgegs thams cad kyang 'di las skyes te /
NK053('i)001:3506: de ltar lus ngag yid gsum la /
NK053('i)001:3507: phyin ci log tu rtog pa'i sgrib pa stug po ni /
NK053('i)001:3508: thar pa mya ngan las 'das pa'i bar du gcod pa'i bdud chen po ste /
NK053('i)001:3509: las las skyes pa'i bgegs gzhan yang der 'jug go //
NK053('i)001:3510: de la ni ru tra rnam pa gsum zhes bya ste /
NK053('i)001:3511: dngos po bdud ma tram ka ru tra /
NK053('i)001:3512: zhes bya ba de yin no //
NK053('i)001:3515: srid pa gsum gyi srog dbugs la dbang byed do //
NK053('i)001:3517: srid pa bar ma do'i gshin ril gyi bla sems la gnas so //
NK053('i)001:3519: sems can ril gyi lus la khyab par gnas so //
NK053('i)001:3521: sems can ril gyi rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pa la gnas so //
NK053('i)001:3522: dngos 'di bzhis sems can ril gyi srid dang dbang thang srog dbugs thams cad la dbang byed do //
NK053('i)001:3523: de dag kun gyi phyag brnyan dam sri ru tra ste /
NK053('i)001:3524: chos dkar po dang dben ril khyab par rgyu zhing gnas so //
NK053('i)001:3526: 'dir bdud ma tram ka ru tra 'khor dang bcas pa gtum bag langs te /
NK053('i)001:3527: 'khor dang bcas pa g.yos te lha'i yul du phyin pas /
NK053('i)001:3528: lha'i dbang po brgya byin 'khor nye dbang sum cu rtsa gnyis dang bcas pa skrags te /
NK053('i)001:3529: nyen cing nyam thag nas tshangs pa'i drung du nye bar song nas /
NK053('i)001:3530: khyed ni srid pa thams cad kyi bdag po 'jig
NK053('i)001:3531: rten gsum la mnga' mdzad pa'i mthu bo che yin
NK053('i)001:3532: pas bdag gi skyabs mdzod cig /
NK053('i)001:3533: ces byas te skyabs su song nas /
NK053('i)001:3534: tshangs pas srin po 'bar ba'i gzugs su sprul nas rgol bas ru tra ma thub pas /
NK053('i)001:3535: de nas tshangs pas khyab 'jug la skyabs su song bas /
NK053('i)001:3536: khyab 'jug gis 'khor lo nag po'i rdzu 'phrul gyis rgol bas kyang ma thub bo //
NK053('i)001:3539: lha'i dbang po brgya byin dang bcas pa rnams kyis /
NK053('i)001:3540: lha chen po ma h+aa de ba la skyabs su song bas /
NK053('i)001:3541: bar pa drag po'i rdzu 'phrul gyis brgal bar byas kyang ma thub /
NK053('i)001:3542: de nas de rnams bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la skyabs su song bas /
NK053('i)001:3543: skyabs de btsan par gyur to //
NK053('i)001:3544: de ltar las kyi ru tra gdug pa can des /
NK053('i)001:3546: lha ma yin gyi ris dang /
NK053('i)001:3551: 'bras bu che man chad dbang du bsdus so //
NK053('i)001:3553: sngon tshe 'das pa'i dang po la //
NK053('i)001:3554: sangs rgyas srid pa'i sgron ma byung //
NK053('i)001:3555: slob dpon rgyal ba 'khor lo yis //
NK053('i)001:3556: slob ma dge slong nag po la //
NK053('i)001:3557: gsang sngags mtha' drug bstan pa la //
NK053('i)001:3558: don de gdengs du ma gyur cing //
NK053('i)001:3559: log pa'i lung du spyad pa yis //
NK053('i)001:3560: dmyal ba yi dwags kha 'khor nas //
NK053('i)001:3561: tha mar las kyi srin por skyes /
NK053('i)001:3562: khams gsum 'khrugs pa'i bdud du gyur //
NK053('i)001:3564: da ni de sngon ji ltar 2btul ba'i gleng gzhi brjod de /
NK053('i)001:3565: de yang bud ka la yi sgras drangs nas /
NK053('i)001:3566: gang du yang 'gro zhes bya ste /
NK053('i)001:3567: dge slong nag po 'khor dang bcas pa de /
NK053('i)001:3570: thar pas sngon yi dam gyi lha rdo rje sems dpa' la brten pa'i stobs kyis /
NK053('i)001:3571: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' thams cad
NK053('i)001:3572: mkhyen pa'i spyan rnam par dag pas gzigs te thugs
NK053('i)001:3573: rje chen pos gdul bar dgongs nas yum rdo rje
NK053('i)001:3574: dbyings phyug ma lus dang grib ma'i tshul du bskyed
NK053('i)001:3575: nas / gnyis su med pa'i rol par spyad pa'i
NK053('i)001:3576: gsang ba se gol gyi sgras phyogs bcu dus gsum
NK053('i)001:3577: gyi sangs rgyas thams cad chos kyi sku las gzugs
NK053('i)001:3578: kyi skur bzhengs su gsol nas /
NK053('i)001:3579: sangs rgyas thams cad kyis gdan tshogs gcig tu bka' bgro ba mdzad de /
NK053('i)001:3581: kye kye 'dus pa'i tshogs chen dag /
NK053('i)001:3582: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba'i //
NK053('i)001:3583: da ltar dus 'dir byung ba'i ru tra ste //
NK053('i)001:3584: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab la //
NK053('i)001:3585: bdag nyid chen po rtag pa rang rgyud par bzung ba yis //
NK053('i)001:3586: khro bo'i tshul du sngon byung ba'i //
NK053('i)001:3587: dus de tshe sems can thams cad kun //
NK053('i)001:3588: shin tu khro drag gtum pa yis //
NK053('i)001:3589: ru tra de 'o dod 'bod cing ngan song du ltung bar 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:3590: mi bzod chen po'i sdug bsngal te //
NK053('i)001:3591: dug gsum mtha' la mngon zhen pa'i //
NK053('i)001:3592: ji lta ba yi thabs kyis gdul //
NK053('i)001:3594: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs dang /
NK053('i)001:3597: las kyi rigs la sogs pa gang gis kyang thul bar ma gyur nas /
NK053('i)001:3599: ru tra ni rdo rje'i rigs kyis thul cig par lung bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3600: dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i thugs su stsol nas /
NK053('i)001:3601: sangs rgyas thams cad dpal rdo rje sems dpa' yab
NK053('i)001:3602: yum gyi ba spu'i bu gar bsdus te sku'i dbyig
NK053('i)001:3603: tu brgyud / rdo rje'i lam du phyung /
NK053('i)001:3605: byang chub sems las yi ge h'u du gsal /
NK053('i)001:3606: h'u de las dpal he ru'i skur bskyed de /
NK053('i)001:3607: dpal he ru ka 'jigs byed ye shes kyi sku la /
NK053('i)001:3608: dur khrod kyi rgyan gyis gsibs pa /
NK053('i)001:3610: gdugs byed kyi mtshon cha phyag na bsnams pa zhig /
NK053('i)001:3611: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi ngo bor gar bzhengs te /
NK053('i)001:3612: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum gyi rol pa
NK053('i)001:3613: chen po rgyan du dpa' chen po bzhugs su gsol
NK053('i)001:3614: nas / ru tra srid pa gsum gyi bdag po gdul ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:3615: dpal chen nga rgyal chen po'i skur bstan te /
NK053('i)001:3616: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nyid nas /
NK053('i)001:3617: khro bo dbang phyug ma mngon du phyung ste /
NK053('i)001:3618: gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems sprin las /
NK053('i)001:3619: khro bo 'chol ba'i dmag phyung nas /
NK053('i)001:3620: srin po ru tra skyams ling la song pa'i shul du /
NK053('i)001:3621: srin po'i gnas su ye shes kyi lha'i dmag drangs te /
NK053('i)001:3622: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po nyid kyis dur khrod kyi gnas der byon te /
NK053('i)001:3623: srin po'i khang khyim ni ye shes kyi gzhal yas khang du byin gyis brlabs /
NK053('i)001:3624: dri chen dri chu rak+ta sogs 'khor ba'i 'dam rdzas
NK053('i)001:3625: thams cad ye shes kyi bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs
NK053('i)001:3626: te rol / khro bo 'chol ba'i dmag gis srin
NK053('i)001:3627: po'i phyi 'khor na yod pa'i 'dod khams kyi dbang
NK053('i)001:3628: phyug chen po khyo shug dang bcas pa /
NK053('i)001:3629: dregs pa can rnams btul te /
NK053('i)001:3632: la la mngag pa dang pho nyar byas so //
NK053('i)001:3633: de'i chung ma dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad po dbang du bsdus te /
NK053('i)001:3634: zil gyis mnan te gzir ba dang /
NK053('i)001:3635: dbang phyug ma rnams kyis dpal chen po la so so'i srog gi snying po phul ba dang /
NK053('i)001:3636: dpal chen pos kyang dam la btags te /
NK053('i)001:3637: gsang ba'i snying po dam tshig rna bar bshug blugs pa las /
NK053('i)001:3638: shar gyi dbang phyug ma bdun gyis ma ltar byams par khas blangs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3639: lho'i bdun gyis sring mo ltar brtse ba dang /
NK053('i)001:3640: nub kyi bdun gyis mdza' mo ltar gdung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:3641: byang gi bdun gyis bran mo ltar las byed par rnam pa bzhir khas blangs te /
NK053('i)001:3642: dpal chen pos dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:3648: ming gi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK053('i)001:3649: khyo ming chung ma la btags te /
NK053('i)001:3650: mi'i srin po'i chung ma yin pas mi srin mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3651: de bzhin tshangs pa'i chung ma la tshangs ma dang /
NK053('i)001:3652: lha chen po'i la 'khrug ma dang /
NK053('i)001:3654: gzhon nu gdong drug gi gzhon nu mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3655: brgya byin gyi dbang mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3656: lha gsang ba'i dmar mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3657: nyi ma'i bdud rtsi mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3658: zla ba'i zhi ba mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3659: be con gyi be con mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3661: za byed kyi za ba mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3662: dga' byed kyi dga' byed mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3663: stobs bzang gi ra ro khrag 'thung myos ma dang /
NK053('i)001:3664: gshin rje'i sring mo gcig pu spyod ma dang /
NK053('i)001:3666: nor srung gi grub mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3668: gsod byed kyi gsod byed chen mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3671: gshin rje'i rgan byed mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3672: dbang ldan gyi sna tshogs mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3673: chu lha'i chu lha mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3674: ma h+aa k+aa la'i nag mo chen mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3675: ra mgo dmar ser gyi ra mgo dmar ser mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3676: srin bum sna'i bum sna sngo nag chen mo dang /
NK053('i)001:3677: d+ha sha g+h+ri ba'i gsus 'dzin ma rnams su btags so //
NK053('i)001:3678: rdzas kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK053('i)001:3679: lag tu las kyi rdo rje rtse gsum pa re re byin no //
NK053('i)001:3680: zas kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK053('i)001:3681: bka' yi pham phab kha chus btab te byin no //
