NK053('i)001:3682: gnas kyi dbang bskur ba ni /
NK053('i)001:3683: dkyil 'khor mu ran la bzhag nas las kyi gnyer bsgo ba ni /
NK053('i)001:3684: dam tshig gi bya ra bar bzhag ste phyi rabs
NK053('i)001:3685: kyi rnal 'byor pa gang dam tshig gzhung du srung
NK053('i)001:3686: ba de'i 'go zhing stongs grogs su bya ba dang
NK053('i)001:3687: / phrin las rnam pa bzhi la sogs pa'i las gang yang grub par bya bar dam bcas so //
NK053('i)001:3688: gang dam tshig mi bsrung zhing gzhung du mi spyod pa /
NK053('i)001:3689: lta spyod log par spyod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3690: khyad par du tshom bu mched sgrub pa'i nang du /
NK053('i)001:3691: rgyal ba dang bla ma'i bka' las nyams pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3692: rtsa ba dang yan lag gi dam tshig nyams pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3693: spyir sdig la mi 'dzem sgos srog la 'tshe bas srog las nyams pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3694: spyir chos rtags mi byed sgos tha mal gyi rtags tshul byed pa rtags las nyams pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3695: 'di rnams chos su gang 'dzud par byed pa de la ni /
NK053('i)001:3696: dam tshig gi chad pas bcad de gnyer bskos te bzhag go dbang mos kyang dam bcas so //
NK053('i)001:3697: de ni dregs pa khyo shug btul zhing dam la btags pa'i gleng gazhi'o //
NK053('i)001:3698: de nas dpal chen pos dur khrod kyi bdag po'i gnas kyi nang du byon te gzigs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3699: dur khrod kyi ma mo bzhi la ma chags thabs kyi sbyor ba mdzad pa las /
NK053('i)001:3700: gsang ba'i ma mo chen mo bzhi byung ste /
NK053('i)001:3701: dkar mo nyi ma'i mig gcig pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3702: ser mo glog gi bang can ma dang /
NK053('i)001:3703: sngon mo rlung gi shugs can ma dang /
NK053('i)001:3704: nag mo klu 'dul ma dang bzhi byung ste /
NK053('i)001:3705: yab lha'i shas che bas bkra shis la nyams dga' 'o //
NK053('i)001:3706: ma gnod sbyin mo shas che bas /
NK053('i)001:3710: bsad bcad la dga' ba bzhi byung ba las /
NK053('i)001:3711: dpal chen pos ma dang bur bcas pa dbang du bsdus dam la btags pas /
NK053('i)001:3712: so so'i srog gi snying po phul te /
NK053('i)001:3713: dam tshig legs nyes kyi las gong bzhin du bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:3714: khyad par du sbyor sgrol gnyis kyi bya rar bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:3715: de nas sgo bzhir byon te /
NK053('i)001:3716: rta dang phag la sogs pa bzhi la ma chags
NK053('i)001:3717: thabs kyi sbyor ba mdzad lhums su yi ge dzahmh'u
NK053('i)001:3718: bam hohbazhi bzhag pa las sgom chen mo bzhi byung
NK053('i)001:3719: ste / yab lha'i shas che bas /
NK053('i)001:3720: lus kyang lha'i skur byung ba mkhyen pa dang rig par ldan /
NK053('i)001:3721: ma byol song gi shas che bas /
NK053('i)001:3722: so so'i mgo brnyan rta phag seng khyi du yang byung ngo //
NK053('i)001:3723: de nas de'i nang rol du byon pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3725: stag la sogs pa la ma chags thabs kyi sbyor ba mdzad pa las /
NK053('i)001:3726: lhums su he brgyad bzhag pa las phra men seng ge'i mgo can dang /
NK053('i)001:3727: stag gi mgo la sogs pa brgyad byung ste /
NK053('i)001:3730: ma srin gyi shas che bas so so'i mgo brnyan du yang byung ba yin no //
NK053('i)001:3731: de nas nang rol du byon nas gzigs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3732: bdud dang srin po'i bu mo srin mo ko'u r+ai
NK053('i)001:3733: la sogs pa brgyad la ma chags thabs kyi sbyor
NK053('i)001:3734: ba mdzad de / lhums su ha brgyad bzhag pa las sras khro mo brgyad byung ste /
NK053('i)001:3735: yab lha'i shas che bas lung kyang lhar byung la /
NK053('i)001:3736: mkhyen pa dang rig par yang ldan //
NK053('i)001:3737: ma srin gyi shas che bas /
NK053('i)001:3740: sdang mig glog tu 'gyu ba byung ngo //
NK053('i)001:3741: de nas dpal chen po ru tra'i cha lugs su bsgyur nas /
NK053('i)001:3742: ru tra'i chung ma srin mo kro ti shwa ri ma'i gam du byon pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3744: ngam zhing ngo mtshar ba'i tshig e ma'o //
NK053('i)001:3745: bdag gi grogs po ru tra 'dra na /
NK053('i)001:3746: de bas kyang ngo mtshar zhing dpa' brjid che'o //
NK053('i)001:3748: de nas de la ma chags thabs kyi sbyor ba mdzad de /
NK053('i)001:3756: zhal gsum phyag drug pa zhig byung ste /
NK053('i)001:3757: de ni gsang ba'i he ru ka zhes bya ste /
NK053('i)001:3759: lus kyang lha'i skur byung la mkhyen pa dang rig par dang yang ldan /
NK053('i)001:3760: ma srin gyi shas che bas /
NK053('i)001:3763: ral pa gyen du 'khyil par byung ba yin no //
NK053('i)001:3764: de nas bdud ru tra 'khor srin po dang gshin
NK053('i)001:3765: rje la sogs pa dur khrod kyi ma mo bdud
NK053('i)001:3766: dang bcas pas / rang gi snying po /
NK053('i)001:3767: ma h+aa rak+sha ru lu ru lu ma ma b+h+yo b+h+yo /
NK053('i)001:3770: zhes pa bzlog shing 'ongs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3771: rang gi gnas khro bo'i gzhal yas khang du bsgyur ba de nyid kyis skrag cing dngangs nas /
NK053('i)001:3773: ru lu ru lu zhes bsdus pas /
NK053('i)001:3775: dpal chen pos ru tra'i snying po de /
NK053('i)001:3776: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:3777: zhes bya bar byin gyis brlabs te bzlas pas /
NK053('i)001:3778: ru tra'i 'khor kun dpal chen po'i 'khor du gyur nas /
NK053('i)001:3779: ru tra'i shin tu yang gzi byin nyams pa las /
NK053('i)001:3780: dpal chen pos sras la sgra cig pa'i lung stsal ba dang /
NK053('i)001:3781: sras badz+ra he ru kas 'di sgrol cig par thugs su gsol nas /
NK053('i)001:3782: sku gsum mtshon rtags kha t+w+aam kha rtse gsum pa cig ru tra'i sked par brgyab pas /
NK053('i)001:3783: 'jig rten gyi khams 'dir phyi gan rkyal du 'gyel te /
NK053('i)001:3784: de nas ru tra der bsgral lo //
NK053('i)001:3785: lus dang sems ma nyams pa zhig 'phral du dam tshig la bkod de /
NK053('i)001:3786: byang chub sems dpa'i chos kyi rgyal po zhes bya bar ming btags te /
NK053('i)001:3787: 'jig rten gyi srung ma chos skyong du dbang bskur nas bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:3790: ru tra de'i rnam par shes pa /
NK053('i)001:3795: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs la sbyor mtshams su 'phangs nas sras kyi dam par bskyed /
NK053('i)001:3796: ma 'ongs pa'i dus su zhing khams de bzhin gshegs
NK053('i)001:3797: pa thal ba'i mtshan gyis brgyan pa zhes bya bar
NK053('i)001:3799: zhes bya bar lung bstan to //
NK053('i)001:3803: sangs rgyas kyi theg pa thun mong las ni /
NK053('i)001:3806: theg pa chen po thun mong ma yin pa gsang sngags las ni /
NK053('i)001:3807: thams cad sprul pa yin yang nyes skyon med do //
NK053('i)001:3809: 'dir dngos dang sprul pa gnyis ka yin par shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:3810: de la dur khrod kyi bdag po de'i ro nyal thabs gan rkyal te /
NK053('i)001:3811: mgo lho nub kyi mtshams su bstan /
NK053('i)001:3812: rkang pa byang shar gyi mtshams su bstan nas /
NK053('i)001:3813: ro lho yi 'dzam bu gling du bor nas sa gzhir gyur pa ni /
NK053('i)001:3814: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad du gyur te /
NK053('i)001:3815: de la phyi dur khrod kyi gnas phyed dang brgyad ni /
NK053('i)001:3816: dur khrod bsil ba'i tshal phyed du bartsi'o //
NK053('i)001:3824: nang dur khrod kyi gnas phyed dang brgyad la /
NK053('i)001:3825: yan lag lnga ro stod ro smad nang rol /
NK053('i)001:3826: nang rol la pha'i rgyu med pas phyed du brtsi /
NK053('i)001:3827: gsang ba dur khrod kyi gnas rnam shes tshogs brgyad la /
NK053('i)001:3829: der dregs pa'i lha brgyad dbang phyug chen po sogs bsgral /
NK053('i)001:3830: ro'i srung mar srin mo ko'u r+ai ma brgyad bzhag /
NK053('i)001:3831: de'i gnas rten du rang byung gi mchod rten re re bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:3832: de'i khog pa gzhal yas khang du byin gyis brlabs so //
NK053('i)001:3833: dbang po rnam pa lnga 'dod yon gyi lha mo lngar byin gyis brlabs so //
NK053('i)001:3834: dngos gzhi bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga bdud rtsi chen por byin gyis brlabs so //
NK053('i)001:3844: thal chen las drag po bsgrub pa'i gdug rdzas su byin gyis brlabs so //
NK053('i)001:3845: dur khrod kyi chas brgyad bgo ba'i gos gsum /
NK053('i)001:3848: dpal gyi chas brgyad du byin gyis brlabs /
NK053('i)001:3849: ru tra'i 'khor thams cad dbang du bsdus shing /
NK053('i)001:3850: srog gi snying po blangs nas dam tshig phog ste /
NK053('i)001:3851: gsang sngags srung mar dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:3852: de ni sgrub pa'i dur khrod do //
NK053('i)001:3854: khams gsum 'khrul pa'i bdud chen po //
NK053('i)001:3855: dpal ldan rdo rje sems dpa' yis //
NK053('i)001:3856: sangs rgyas thams cad bsdu bar byas //
NK053('i)001:3857: nas zhi bar bstan pas 'dul ma yin //
NK053('i)001:3858: khro bor gyur nas bdud de bsgral //
NK053('i)001:3859: bsgrub pa'i gnas su byin brlabs te //
NK053('i)001:3860: bsgral ba'i rdzas la longs spyod mdzad //
NK053('i)001:3862: de la da lta gdul ba'i thabs 3bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:3865: de gang gis gdul snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:3866: phyag rgya che dang ldan par ni //
NK053('i)001:3868: de la lta bas gdul ba ni /
NK053('i)001:3869: shes rab kyis g.yang sa bcad pa ste /
NK053('i)001:3870: ma tram ka ru tra ni /
NK053('i)001:3871: phyi'i yul la dngos por bzung las byung bas /
NK053('i)001:3872: snod kyi 'jig rten dang lus la rang bzhin med par shes pas /
NK053('i)001:3873: ma tram ka ru tra don gyis btul lo //
NK053('i)001:3874: kha tram ka ru tra ni /
NK053('i)001:3875: nang gi sems la bdag tu 'dzin pa las skyes pa yang /
NK053('i)001:3876: sems la phyin ci log gi rtog pa med de /
NK053('i)001:3877: sems nyid stong par shes pas /
NK053('i)001:3878: kha tram kha ru tra don gyis btul lo //
NK053('i)001:3879: a kar sha ru tra ni /
NK053('i)001:3880: mtha' chad par lta ba las gyur pa yang /
NK053('i)001:3881: kun rdzob tu chos thams cad rten 'brel sgyu mar snang bas /
NK053('i)001:3882: lha'i phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor mngon du snang la /
NK053('i)001:3883: de nyid sgyu ma'i cho 'phrul rgyun mi chad par shes pas /
NK053('i)001:3884: a kar sha ru tra don gyis btul lo //
NK053('i)001:3885: de la spyod par gdul ba ni /
NK053('i)001:3886: las dang bya bas 'bras bu yod par bya ba ste /
NK053('i)001:3887: de la don dgus bstan te /
NK053('i)001:3888: gdul ba'i gnyen po gang yin pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3889: rgyu ci las byung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:3890: rkyen ci las gyur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:3893: las skal gyi spyod pa ci byed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3894: ma btul na skyon ci yod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3895: btul ba la yon tan ci yod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3896: rnal 'byor pa ji lta bas gdul bar bstan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:3897: de la gdul ba'i dngos po gang yin pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:3898: gdul bya'i sngon du byung ba'i gleng gzhi gong du bshad pas shes par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:3900: bdud ma tram ka ru tra gdug pa can de sngon ltar bden na /
NK053('i)001:3901: dpal chen pos bsgral zin na da lta gdul zhing bsgral ci dgos /
NK053('i)001:3902: sngon ma btul na ni da mnan yang mi non no //
NK053('i)001:3904: de yang gdul zhing mnan dgos te /
NK053('i)001:3905: de yang bdud ru tra yang 'khor ba'i sa bon rtsub mo dang ldan pa yin pas /
NK053('i)001:3906: sha khrag thig pa re re lus pa las kyang /
NK053('i)001:3907: bag chags ngan pa langs shing rnal 'byor sgrub pa po'i bar gcod du 'ongs pas /
NK053('i)001:3908: de mnan te da lta yang rnal 'byor pa bdag nyid kyang /
NK053('i)001:3909: sku gsum ye shes kyi sprul pa yin te /
NK053('i)001:3910: dper na pha tshab bus byas pa'am /
NK053('i)001:3911: rjes las khol gyis byas pa dang 'dra'o //
NK053('i)001:3912: da lta gdul ba'i dngos po gang yin pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:3914: mi snang ba gnyis su sems par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:3916: gsang sngags kyi mtha' drug la ma zhugs shing don dang mi ldan par spyod pa ste /
NK053('i)001:3917: de thabs kyis gdul zhing 'khor ba'i g.yang sar mi btang ba'o //
NK053('i)001:3918: de la dngos por mi snang ba ni /
NK053('i)001:3919: sngags pa gsang sngags kyi mtha' drug dang mi ldan pa ste /
NK053('i)001:3920: sngags pa lta ba log pa ni //
NK053('i)001:3921: ru tra kun gyi ded dpon yin //
NK053('i)001:3923: dam nyams shing dman pa'i lta bas bgegs kyi gnas su skyes pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3924: des bsgrub shing rdzas su spyad pa'i gnas bor ba de ni /
NK053('i)001:3925: dam srir song nas rnal 'byor sgrub po thams cad la dus der 'jug tu 'ong ste /
NK053('i)001:3926: de sa bon rtsub mos btab pa gdug pa'i dbal can yin pas /
NK053('i)001:3927: de'i rgyud la ru tra rnam pa gsum char tshang bas /
NK053('i)001:3929: de yang rgyud las gsungs pas /
NK053('i)001:3930: sems dpa' rdo rjes smras pa /
NK053('i)001:3931: sems dpa' chen po gsang ba'i bdag po nyon cig /
NK053('i)001:3932: log pa'i dka' thub drag po can gyi sems can 'di ni /
NK053('i)001:3933: legs pa'i rgyu rkyen las ni ma byung gis /
NK053('i)001:3934: nyes pa'i rgyu rkyen las byung ste /
NK053('i)001:3936: gzung 'dzin gyi rtog pa las byung ngo //
NK053('i)001:3938: gsang ba'i bka' zab mo spyad nyes pa las byung ngo //
NK053('i)001:3940: nyon mongs pa lngar smin ni //
NK053('i)001:3942: 'khor ba'i rigs can de gdol pa can gyi 'byung por btags so //
NK053('i)001:3943: las skal gyi spyod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:3944: chags sdang gi spyod pa chen po la zhen pa'o //
NK053('i)001:3946: lha dang mi'i srid pa brlag ste /
NK053('i)001:3947: kha lo log par bsgyur nas /
NK053('i)001:3948: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams stong ste /
NK053('i)001:3949: 'khor ba ni lte chad du lus la /
NK053('i)001:3950: sangs rgyas ni gnyen ris su lus nas /
NK053('i)001:3951: sems can la mi phan pa'i skyon yod /
NK053('i)001:3953: dug gsum rtsa nas bcad de /
NK053('i)001:3955: 'khor ba chos nyid du gyur te /
NK053('i)001:3956: sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams dag par byas pa'i yon tan yod do //
NK053('i)001:3958: de la rnal 'byor pa ji lta bus 'dul ba ni /
NK053('i)001:3959: gsang sngags kyi mtha' drug rdzogs shing /
NK053('i)001:3960: yo byad gnyis la longs spyod par shes pas gdul te /
NK053('i)001:3961: de yang rnal 'byor pa rnams sku gsum phyag rgya
NK053('i)001:3962: bzhi dang ldan par bsgom pa'i stobs kyis 'dul ba
NK053('i)001:3963: dang / dur khrod kyi bdag po dngos por dgug cing 'dul ba'o //
NK053('i)001:3964: de la sku gsum phyag rgya bzhi bsgom pa yang /
NK053('i)001:3965: dang po kho bo sngon byung gi gleng gzhi brjod par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:3966: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba'i //
NK053('i)001:3967: bdag nyid chen por brtag pa yi //
NK053('i)001:3968: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab la //
NK053('i)001:3969: 'di'i tshig rkang pa gnyis gong du go rim dkrug
NK053('i)001:3970: 'dug kyang gzhung gzhan nas 'di ltar 'byung bas sor
NK053('i)001:3971: bzhag byas / go don yang gdul bya gdul byed
NK053('i)001:3972: so sor 'grel chog pa 'dra snyam pas phyi rabs
NK053('i)001:3974: 'gro ba'i tshul du sngon byung ba //
NK053('i)001:3975: de tshe sems can thams cad ni //
NK053('i)001:3976: shin tu khro gtum gdug par gyur //
NK053('i)001:3977: shin tu khro gtum gdug pa yis //
NK053('i)001:3981: de bzhin nyid de mi rtog pa dang /
NK053('i)001:3982: kun tu snang ste 'od kyi ting 'dzin dang /
NK053('i)001:3983: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin h'u du gsal ba'o //
NK053('i)001:3984: h'u de las e 'phros shing mched pa las snang
NK053('i)001:3985: srid ril e gru gsum mtha' dang dbus med pa
NK053('i)001:3986: 'od zer mthing ka 'khrugs shing 'khyil bar bsgom mo
NK053('i)001:3987: // de'i dbus su ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor lte ba yar lta zhig bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:3988: de'i steng h'u mthing nag 'bar ba de gsal bar bsgom la /
NK053('i)001:3991: shin tu khro gtum gdug pa la //
NK053('i)001:3992: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK053('i)001:3993: shes rab thabs kyi ngo bo yis //
NK053('i)001:3994: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK053('i)001:3995: khro bo'i tshul 'chang khros pa yis //
NK053('i)001:3996: srid pa gsum dag sreg byed na //
NK053('i)001:3997: sangs rgyas thams cad khros pa yis /
NK053('i)001:3998: khams gsum ma lus smos ci dgos //
NK053('i)001:4000: phyag rgya bzhi dang ldan pa'i stobs kyis /
NK053('i)001:4001: h'u bzhis ting nge 'dzin gyi rtsal sbyangs te /
NK053('i)001:4002: de la h'u brjod pa dang pos ni /
NK053('i)001:4003: bdag gi ba'i rgyud yi ge h'u 'od du 'bar bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:4005: de las 'od zer bskal pa'i me dpung lta bu phyogs bcur 'phro ba'o //
NK053('i)001:4007: de las sprul pa mang po 'phros pas ma rungs pa'i tshogs kun btul lo //
NK053('i)001:4009: sprul pa de dag kun slar 'dus pa las /
NK053('i)001:4010: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:4012: bdag nyid dpal chen sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:4017: g.yas g.yon dang po rdo rjes dung chen dkrugs shing rngub pa /
NK053('i)001:4018: g.yas 'og ma brgyad na ko'u r+ai ma brgyad /
NK053('i)001:4019: g.yon 'og ma brgyad na phra men ma brgyad /
NK053('i)001:4021: sku la dur khrod kyi chas brgyad dang ldan pa /
NK053('i)001:4022: thugs ka na nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du a dkar la 'tsher ba gcig dang /
NK053('i)001:4023: h'u dmar la dwangs pa zhig brtsegs mar bsgom pa ni /
NK053('i)001:4024: gtso bo'i sku phyag rgya chen po'o //
NK053('i)001:4026: badz+ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:4028: yum kro ti sh+aa ri ma sku lhag gis gsal ba ni /
NK053('i)001:4029: yum dang mi 'bral ba dam tshig gi phyag rgya'o //
NK053('i)001:4030: de nas yab yum gnyis su med pa'i 'phro 'du las /
NK053('i)001:4031: khro bo dang khro mo dpag tu med pa'i 'phro 'du mang pos /
NK053('i)001:4034: khro bo bcu dang koo seng sgo ma dang bcas par bsgom pa ni /
NK053('i)001:4036: de tsam na don chos nyid mnyam pa nyid las mi 'da' ba ni /
NK053('i)001:4037: zhi ba chos kyi phyag rgya'o //
NK053('i)001:4038: de ltar gsal bas bskul ba /
NK053('i)001:4039: gdul dka' ma lus gdul ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:4040: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs //
NK053('i)001:4041: dam tshig la sdang rnam sbyor phyir //
NK053('i)001:4042: du khrod gar gyi phyag rgyar gsal //
NK053('i)001:4045: chos nyid mi g.yo phyag rgya chen po'i ngang //
NK053('i)001:4046: chos kyi sku las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:4047: sems can thams cad khro ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:4048: rdo rje yang ni khro bar bya //
NK053('i)001:4050: dur khrod kyi bdag po dngos por dgug cing bsgral ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:4051: ci rigs su ni las rnams bya //
NK053('i)001:4056: sngar bla ma'i dbang dag gdams ngag thob pa'i rjes la /
NK053('i)001:4057: rang rig pa'i rtsal dang ldan pa des lag tu blang ba'i rim pa la /
NK053('i)001:4061: dus dang gnas skabs kyi spyir shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4068: de la khyad par gyi las ni /
NK053('i)001:4070: khyad par gyi las la don bcu drug go //
NK053('i)001:4074: bzhi pa dam la bzhag pa /
NK053('i)001:4075: lnga pa zil gyis mnan pa /
NK053('i)001:4077: bdun pa 'gyel ba la sha zan gtod cing bardzi ba /
NK053('i)001:4078: brgyad pa ma tram khog pa sgo'i tshul du phye ba /
NK053('i)001:4079: dgu pa khog pa dngos kha phye ba /
NK053('i)001:4080: bcu pa sras su bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:4081: bcu gcig pa khog pa gzhal yas khang du bya ba /
NK053('i)001:4082: bcu gnyis pa gtor ma byin te sgo srung du gnyer bsgo ba /
NK053('i)001:4083: bcu gsum pa ma tram gnas spar chos rgyal la gtang rag btang ba /
NK053('i)001:4084: bcu bzhi pa sgo 'byed gcod dang mtshams gcod pa /
NK053('i)001:4085: bco lnga pa ma mo brgyad spyan drangs pa /
NK053('i)001:4086: bcu drug pa phra men ma bsgom pa'o //
NK053('i)001:4087: dang po gzugs bri ba ni /
NK053('i)001:4088: dur khrod kyi bdag po ma tram gi gzugs /
NK053('i)001:4089: thal chen gyis ri mor bris la /
NK053('i)001:4090: de'i snying gar yi ge tri zhes bri'o //
NK053('i)001:4092: ma tram ka ru tra pre ta dz+wa la ya /
NK053('i)001:4094: dur khrod kyi bdag po ma tram ka ru tra mdog thal skya /
NK053('i)001:4096: lus ri rab bas kyang che ba /
NK053('i)001:4097: 'khor ma mo bdun dang bcas par bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:4099: de la 'jig rten pa'i ru tra drag po rang gi gnas nas dgug pa /
NK053('i)001:4102: nag mo ru tra gdul pa dang //
NK053('i)001:4103: ma tram thams cad mnan pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:4104: 'byung po mang po bdag la gson //
NK053('i)001:4105: dbang phyug chen po dregs pa can //
NK053('i)001:4106: 'tshe ba'i bdag po tshe dang srog /
NK053('i)001:4107: thugs rje'i ngang dang shes rab dang //
NK053('i)001:4108: thabs la mkhas pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK053('i)001:4109: 'gro ba thams cad bskyab mdzad phyir //
NK053('i)001:4110: bdud dang gshin rje 'khor bcas kun //
NK053('i)001:4111: gnyis med rol pa'i phyag rgya yis //
NK053('i)001:4112: thugs rje'i lcags kyus dgug par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4113: dzahmh'u bam hoh ma tram ka ru tra dzahdzahmh'u /
NK053('i)001:4114: kha tram ga ru tra dzahdzahmh'u /
NK053('i)001:4117: bdag nyid dpal chen kyi thugs ka dang /
NK053('i)001:4119: gsang ba'i gnas thams cad nas /
NK053('i)001:4120: khro bo dang khro mo dang dzahmh'u bam hoh phyag rgya bzhi dang bcas par 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:4121: ma tram ka ru tra 'khor sprul pa dang bcas pa mdun du bkug par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:4125: ma tram gi ni rnam shes te //
NK053('i)001:4126: nges par gzugs la phab nas ni //
NK053('i)001:4127: las la bab pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK053('i)001:4128: dus la bab po sa ma ya //
NK053('i)001:4129: sarba sa ma ye he sa ti s+t+wam //
NK053('i)001:4131: gzugs dang bcas pa'i bskyed pa la bstim mo //
NK053('i)001:4132: bzhi pa dam la bzhag pa /
NK053('i)001:4133: de nas bdag nyid lha'i skur nga rgyal bskyed cing /
NK053('i)001:4135: zhes yun ring du brjod pa'i rjes la /
NK053('i)001:4136: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka tri sha ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:4138: dam tshig nyan par gyur par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4139: de nas lag pa g.yon pa'i mdzub mo thugs kar bsgreng ste /
NK053('i)001:4140: mthe bong gis gung mo mnan te /
NK053('i)001:4141: srin lag dang mthe chung gnyis yid tsam sgur por byas nas ma mo brgyad la dam brdar /
NK053('i)001:4142: he brgyad dri sh+ya hohs ma ya s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:4144: lnga pa zil gyis mnan pa /
NK053('i)001:4145: g.yas pa'i mthe bong dang srin lag rtse sprad pa'i
NK053('i)001:4146: bar du mi ro sked pa nas bzung ste phyar
NK053('i)001:4147: / sor mo gzhan bsgreng ste tri shu la'i tshul du byas la 'di skad do //
NK053('i)001:4149: shar phyogs lam sgo'i 'jig rten na //
NK053('i)001:4150: 'byung po gtum po nga rgyal can //
NK053('i)001:4151: khyod kyi sgrub pa kun la sgrib //
NK053('i)001:4152: yang dag shes rab ye shes kyis //
NK053('i)001:4153: khungs brtag rtsad bcad bdag la 'byung //
NK053('i)001:4154: bdag 'dzin bdag gi rtog pa ni //
NK053('i)001:4155: bdag med stong pa'i tho bas gzhom //
NK053('i)001:4157: gnas ngan len pa'i ded dpon byed //
NK053('i)001:4158: de nyid bdag nyid yin pas na //
NK053('i)001:4159: bdag med tho ba'i zhabs kyis gzhom //
NK053('i)001:4160: sa man+ta ma h+aa shu dz+ny+aa ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra mung+ga re +aa ko ta ya h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:4162: ma tram 'khor dang bcas pa 'dar phril gyi song nas /
NK053('i)001:4163: gzi byin dang bral te 'dug par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:4167: ma tram bya ba'i sdig chen khyod //
NK053('i)001:4168: sngon yang dpal chen he ru kas //
NK053('i)001:4169: bsgral nas dur khrod chen por mdzad //
NK053('i)001:4170: da yang rnal 'byor dbang phyug gis //
NK053('i)001:4171: bsgral nas dur khrod chen por bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4172: 'gro ba'i bdag po tshe dang srog /
NK053('i)001:4173: gson po dag la bar gcod cing //
NK053('i)001:4174: bdud dang gshin rje dbang phyug che //
NK053('i)001:4175: gzhom zhing bsad pa'i gnyen po ni //
NK053('i)001:4176: 'jam dpal sku sprul khro bo'i mchog /
NK053('i)001:4177: srid gsum mthar byed rngams pa des /
NK053('i)001:4178: kha t+w+aam thod dbyug mi bzad pas //
NK053('i)001:4179: gshin rje bcom nas gsad par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4180: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra
NK053('i)001:4181: sarba dush+tam sa ma ya mu tra pra ban tsakra
NK053('i)001:4182: ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:4184: kha t+w+aam sked par brgyab pas /
NK053('i)001:4185: gyad kyis sdong khog bsgyur ba bzhin sngo hrangs kyis gan rkyal du 'gyel bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:4186: bdun pa 'gyel ba la gzan gtod cing bardzi ba /
NK053('i)001:4188: ro bdag drag po chen po ni //
NK053('i)001:4189: ro yi nyal thabs gan rkyal te //
NK053('i)001:4190: srin po'i rigs lho nub na yod pas mgo ni lho nub mtshams su bstan //
NK053('i)001:4191: bgegs rnams kyi gtso bo dbang ldan na yod pas rkang pa byang shar mtshams su bstan //
NK053('i)001:4192: lag pa g.yas pa'i mkhrig ma la //
NK053('i)001:4193: khra dang 'ug pa spyang ki gnas //
NK053('i)001:4194: lag pa g.yon pa'i mkhrig ma la //
NK053('i)001:4195: kang+ka bya rgod sre mo wa //
NK053('i)001:4196: rngam khro sha chen za zhing gnas //
NK053('i)001:4197: zhes 'byung bas de lta bsgoms te /
NK053('i)001:4198: de dag thams cad kyang shin tu rngams shing khros pa'i tshul du gnas pas /
NK053('i)001:4199: sha chen la zur mig bzlog cing za bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:4201: ta ki zhabs ni g.yas pa yis //
NK053('i)001:4202: gyad kyi dor stabs tshul gyis mnan //
NK053('i)001:4203: mthar byed chen po'i 'gying stabs kyis //
NK053('i)001:4204: rngams rdzig chen pos 'di skad gsungs //
NK053('i)001:4205: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka tri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:4207: ma tram gi steng du mchongs la /
NK053('i)001:4208: snying kha dang mgo dang gsang gnas su zhabs kyis bardzisa te /
NK053('i)001:4210: brgyad pa ma tram khog pa sgo'i tshul du phye bar bstan pa /
NK053('i)001:4213: gnas kyi sgo 'di su yis bcad //
NK053('i)001:4214: sems kyi bdag pos bcad dam ci //
NK053('i)001:4215: gzung 'dzin rkang lag bsnol ba'i sgo //
NK053('i)001:4216: yul las 'das pa zhabs kyis dbye //
NK053('i)001:4217: ma tram kha ru tra tha ra na phye b+h+r+aum kha ta pra ra na phye /
NK053('i)001:4219: zhabs g.yas pa'i mthe bong las lcags kyur sprul te /
NK053('i)001:4220: rkang pa bsnol ba g.yas kyis g.yon mnan pa de kha phye ste phyi sgo phye bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:4221: dgu pa khog pa dngos kha phye ba /
NK053('i)001:4223: dregs pa ma rungs lha chen khyod //
NK053('i)001:4224: rdo rje 'bar ba'i spu gri yis //
NK053('i)001:4225: lus sems sgo kun phye nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:4226: gzung 'dzin sems kyi bdag po bzung bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4227: pradz+ny+aa ke sha tsit+ta dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:4228: ma nu d+harma to sha b+h+yo u ma badz+ra ma h+aa sa ma ya ma tram kha h'u /
NK053('i)001:4230: ma rig pa'i sbubs sgo dral te khog pa kha dabye'o //
NK053('i)001:4231: ting nges kyang snang sgo phye bar bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:4232: bcu pa sras su bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:4234: khams gsum nas byung sems can khyod //
NK053('i)001:4235: rdo rje sku yi gnyis med du /
NK053('i)001:4237: 'od zer tshul du spro bsdu yis //
NK053('i)001:4238: de dag bdag gis ma tram gzugs la bzud //
NK053('i)001:4239: sku dang ye shes mchog tu bsgral //
NK053('i)001:4241: bdag gi thugs ka'i a dkar po las /
NK053('i)001:4242: a phra mo 'od zer dang bcas par spros pas /
NK053('i)001:4243: ma tram gyi rnam par shes pa trir gnas pa
NK053('i)001:4244: la phog pas bsregs sbyangs nas 'od du gyur pa
NK053('i)001:4245: las / slar yang a dkar la 'tsher ba gcig tu gyur to //
NK053('i)001:4246: de'i thugs ka'i h'u dmar po de las 'od 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:4247: a de ye shes kyi 'od zer gyi tshur bsdus te /
NK053('i)001:4248: dang po'i a la thim pa las /
NK053('i)001:4251: h'u de srog dag pa'i gsang lung du brgyud nas /
NK053('i)001:4252: bdag gi byang chub kyi sems dang 'dres nas /
NK053('i)001:4253: gsang ba'i rdo rje'i lam du byung nas /
NK053('i)001:4254: yum gyi mkha' la bab pa las /
NK053('i)001:4255: yum gyi byang chub kyi sems dang yang 'dres par gyur te /
NK053('i)001:4256: yi ge h'u du gsal ba las /
NK053('i)001:4257: ma h+aa de ba ru tra dzahdzahmh'u /
NK053('i)001:4261: yab yum gyi mkha' gsang nas phyir bton te /
NK053('i)001:4262: bdag gi mdun du sras kyi dam par bskyed nas nyi zla'i gdan la bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:4263: bcu gcig pa khog pa la gzhal yas khang du bya ba /
NK053('i)001:4264: de ltar btul nas khog pa gzha' yas khang du bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:4265: bdag gi thugs ka'am smin mtshams nas /
NK053('i)001:4266: h'u nyung 'bru tsam ma tram gyi khog pa la 'phrog pas /
NK053('i)001:4268: rdzas dang sa gzhi brtags pa der //
NK053('i)001:4272: ma lus snying rjes khyab byas te //
NK053('i)001:4273: re zhing ngom pa'i tshul du dgongs //
NK053('i)001:4275: dur khrod sa ru brtag par bya //
NK053('i)001:4276: smug nag zla gam gzhal yas shar //
NK053('i)001:4277: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK053('i)001:4279: ma tram gi phyi'i pags pa las rin po che'i gzhal yas khang du gyur /
NK053('i)001:4280: rtsib ma dang sgal tshigs las dur khrod kyi gzhal yas khang /
NK053('i)001:4281: rgya nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam zhing /
NK053('i)001:4282: dpangs srid pa'i rtse mo las 'das pa /
NK053('i)001:4283: dbyibs zla gam dbang gi dkyil 'khor du gyur par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:4284: bar gyi sha khrag las dug gsum gyi dkyil 'khor /
NK053('i)001:4287: keng rus kyi ri rab tu gyur par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:4288: bcu gnyis pa gtor ma byin la sgo srung du gnyer bsgo ba /
NK053('i)001:4289: de nas ma tram sras kyi dam par bskyed pa de la gtor ma byin par dam bsres te /
NK053('i)001:4290: e h+ye hi +aa ral+li i dam badz+ra ba ling+ta pra t+aits+tsha dzahmh'u bam hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:4292: sngar sgo byang gi dus su chos kyi rgyal por
NK053('i)001:4293: bskyed pa la gnyis su med par bstim la bzhag
NK053('i)001:4296: sgrub gnas sgo srung lha khyod kyis //
NK053('i)001:4297: mi zad rgyan gyi 'khor lo la //
NK053('i)001:4298: gtogs pa'i rnal 'byor ma yin pa //
NK053('i)001:4299: gzhal yas khang sgo srung du gsol //
NK053('i)001:4301: bcu gsum pa ma tram gnas spar chos rgyal la gtang rag gtong ba /
NK053('i)001:4302: nam sgrub pa thon pa'i dus na /
NK053('i)001:4303: sngar sgo byang la bstim pa ste slar la gnyis phye la /
NK053('i)001:4304: ma tram sras su bskyed pa de /
NK053('i)001:4305: gnas spar ba'i dgongs pa bya /
NK053('i)001:4306: chos kyi rgyal po la gtor ma gtang rag gtong la /
NK053('i)001:4307: chos skyong ba'i srung mar phrin las bcol te /
NK053('i)001:4308: dam tshig gi bya ra la bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:4309: bcu bzhi pa sgo 'byed gcod dang mtshams gcad pa /
NK053('i)001:4310: de nas rdo rje rgyal pos sna drangs te /
NK053('i)001:4311: phyag rgya lag pa dpung mgor bsnol nas /
NK053('i)001:4313: b+h+r+aum kha ta pra be sha phata /
NK053('i)001:4315: ma tram gi khog pa'i sgo phye la /
NK053('i)001:4320: phyir nud te sgo rbad kyis bcad /
NK053('i)001:4322: de nas rdo rje'i 'gros kyis man+da la bskor zhing /
NK053('i)001:4323: h'u h'u h'u zhes brjod pas /
NK053('i)001:4324: stong gsum thams cad h'u du me re re 'gyur /
NK053('i)001:4326: rdo rje dang me dpung gi gur du gyur par bsgom zhing /
NK053('i)001:4328: steng yang rdo rje'i bla re la //
NK053('i)001:4330: phyogs mtshams rdo rjes gtams pa la //
NK053('i)001:4331: rdo rje'i mtshams las ma 'da' shig /
NK053('i)001:4334: steng yang 'khor lo'i bla re la //
NK053('i)001:4336: phyogs mtshams 'khor los gtams pa la //
NK053('i)001:4340: steng yang ral gri'i bla re la //
NK053('i)001:4342: phyogs mtshams ral gris gtams pa la //
NK053('i)001:4343: ral gri'i mtshams las ma 'da' shig /
NK053('i)001:4344: badz+ra ka la ru pa sha h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:4346: steng yang dbyug to'i bla re la //
NK053('i)001:4348: phyogs mtshams dbyug tos gtams pa la //
NK053('i)001:4349: dbyug to'i mtshams las ma 'da' shig /
NK053('i)001:4350: badz+ra ma h+aa ro sha khang+ga h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:4352: steng yang rgya gram bla re la //
NK053('i)001:4354: phyogs mtshams rgya gram gtams pa la //
NK053('i)001:4355: rgya gram mtshams las ma 'da' shig /
NK053('i)001:4356: badz+ra karma sa t+wa ha ha h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:4358: bco lnga pa ma mo brgyas spyan drangs shing gnas srung bar bcol ba /
NK053('i)001:4361: b+h+r+aum 'od zer dang bcas pa brgyad /
NK053('i)001:4362: ma tram gyi gnas brgyad la 'phros pas //
NK053('i)001:4363: de rnams 'od du ste dpal rang byung gi mchod
NK053('i)001:4364: rten brgyad gzhal yas khang du gyur par bsgom mo
NK053('i)001:4366: ma mo brgyad spyan drangs shing gnas srung bar bcol ba /
NK053('i)001:4367: sngon tshe 'das dus dang po la //
NK053('i)001:4368: bcom ldan dpal chen he ru kas //
NK053('i)001:4369: dur khrod bdag po ma tram bsgral //
NK053('i)001:4370: bor nas sa gzhir gyur pa la //
NK053('i)001:4371: ro yi srung ma chen mo ni //
NK053('i)001:4372: ma mo chen mo brgyad bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:4373: de yi gnas rten chen po yang //
NK053('i)001:4374: mchod rten chen po gzi byin can //
NK053('i)001:4375: rang 'byung re re bzhag pa yin //
NK053('i)001:4376: de ltar sa gzhi 'di kun kyang //
NK053('i)001:4377: bkra shis ya mtshan thugs rje can //
NK053('i)001:4378: chos dang dngos grub 'byung ba'i gnas //
NK053('i)001:4380: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK053('i)001:4381: ma mo chen mo spyan 'dren no //
NK053('i)001:4382: ma tram de yi lus snying ma ga ta //
NK053('i)001:4383: dur khrod chen po bsil ba'i tshal //
NK053('i)001:4384: mchod rten bde byed rten srung ba'i //
NK053('i)001:4385: ma mo chen mo koo'u ri ma //
NK053('i)001:4386: mthu dang yon tan mkhas shing dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i snying stobs che sa nas //
NK053('i)001:4387: gang dmigs len pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK053('i)001:4388: ko'u r+ai chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:4389: ko'u r+ai chen mo gshegs nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:4390: dngos grub gsol zhing brtan par bzhugs //
NK053('i)001:4391: de yi mgo bo lho yi phyogs //
NK053('i)001:4392: dur khrod chen po sing+ga gling //
NK053('i)001:4393: mchod rten ri bo ta la srung //
NK053('i)001:4394: ma mo chen mo tso'u r+ai ma //
NK053('i)001:4395: mthong chos rnam par 'khrul sa nas //
NK053('i)001:4397: tso'u r+ai chen mo tso'u r+ai dngos grub lag pa g.yas pa shar lho mtshams //
NK053('i)001:4398: dur khrod chen po bal yul na //
NK053('i)001:4399: mchod rten aka so b+y+aa kri srung //
NK053('i)001:4400: ma mo chen mo puk+ka si //
NK053('i)001:4401: zas kyi longs spyod che sa nas //
NK053('i)001:4403: puk+ka chen mo puk+ka dngos grub lag pa g.yon pa lho nub mtshams //
NK053('i)001:4404: dur khrod chen po s+aa la'i yul //
NK053('i)001:4405: gyad yul mchod rten mgo mang srung //
NK053('i)001:4406: ma mo chen mo bee t+aa li //
NK053('i)001:4407: mthu dang dbang yang che sa nas //
NK053('i)001:4408: gsod par byed pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK053('i)001:4409: bee t+aa chen mo bee t+aa dngos grub rkang pa g.yas pa byang shar mtshams //
NK053('i)001:4410: dur khrod chen po li yi yul //
NK053('i)001:4411: mchod rten go'u the shan srung //
NK053('i)001:4412: ma mo chen mo tsan d+ha l+ai //
NK053('i)001:4413: me chu rdzu 'phrul che sa nas //
NK053('i)001:4415: tsan d+ha chen mo tsan d+ha dngos grub rkang pa g.yon pa nub byang mtshams //
NK053('i)001:4416: dur khrod chen po kha che'i yul //
NK053('i)001:4417: mchod rten ka ni ka srung ba'i //
NK053('i)001:4418: ma mo chen mo pra mo h+aa //
NK053('i)001:4419: bde skyid ldan pa'i yul dag nas //
NK053('i)001:4420: len cing zlog pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK053('i)001:4421: pra mo chen mo pra mo dngos grub pho mtshan steng gi byang phyogs na //
NK053('i)001:4422: dur khrod chen po o rgyan yul //
NK053('i)001:4424: ma mo chen mo kasma ri //
NK053('i)001:4425: dngos grub can yang de na mang //
NK053('i)001:4426: smyo bar byed pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK053('i)001:4427: kasma chen mo kasma dngos grub de yi nang rol thams cad kun //
NK053('i)001:4428: dur khrod chen po za hor yul //
NK053('i)001:4429: mchod rten bde byed gzhon nu srung //
NK053('i)001:4430: ma mo chen mo sma sha ni //
NK053('i)001:4431: 'byor pa'i longs spyod che sa nas //
NK053('i)001:4432: gsod par byed pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK053('i)001:4433: sma sha chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:4434: sma sha chen mo gshegs nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:4435: dngos grub stsol zhing brtan par bzhugs //
NK053('i)001:4436: de ltar spyan drangs bzhugs pa la /
NK053('i)001:4437: dpal chen po bdag gi phyag na gnas pa'i ye
NK053('i)001:4438: shes kyi ko'u r+ai ma brgyad kyis dbang bskur te
NK053('i)001:4439: / las dang ye shes dbyer med pa'i ma mo brgyad la /
NK053('i)001:4440: gzhal yas khang srung bar phrin las bcol te bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:4441: bcu drug pa phra men ma bsgom pa'o //
NK053('i)001:4442: de nas phra men ma brgyad dug gsum gyi dkyil 'khor la bkod pa la /
NK053('i)001:4443: sed+ha la sogs pa bzhi re re la mche ba can brgyad brgyad du sprul zhing /
NK053('i)001:4444: dgra bgegs la sogs pa gang la bya ba gsod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:4445: kri ta la sogs pa bzhi re re la gshog pa can brgyad brgyad du sprul zhing /
NK053('i)001:4446: gang la bya ba'i mig 'byin cing /
NK053('i)001:4448: gzhan yang las las grub pa'i phra men ma mang pos /
NK053('i)001:4449: dgra bgegs gang la bya ba'i sha la za /
NK053('i)001:4452: dug gsum stong par bsgom zhing /
NK053('i)001:4453: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis phra men ma'i 'jol tshul bya zhing /
NK053('i)001:4455: g.yas su blta zhing g.yon du nur //
NK053('i)001:4456: yid ma ches te phyir yang blta //
NK053('i)001:4458: gzhal yas khang gi bar sgor ram /
NK053('i)001:4459: yang na man+dala la bskor ba lan gsum bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4460: de yan chad du dur khrod kyi bdag po ru tra btul nas /
NK053('i)001:4461: khog pa gzhal yas khang du byas pa'o //
NK053('i)001:4463: 'khor yan chad dbang du bsdus te /
NK053('i)001:4464: phyis spob pa med par bya ba la /
NK053('i)001:4466: phrin las rnam pa bzhi'i sbyin bsreg dang /
NK053('i)001:4469: spyi'i phrin las rnam pa bzhi po 'dis /
NK053('i)001:4471: bgegs bye brag ril dbang du bsdu zhing brlag par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:4472: zhi zhing rgyas par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:4473: khyad par du drag po'i phrin las bya zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4474: ma tram gyi lte bar dbang gi las /
NK053('i)001:4480: snying khar rgyas pa'i las kyi sbyin sreg bya ste /
NK053('i)001:4481: e wam ma ya bzhis las bzhi mtshon pa ste /
NK053('i)001:4482: las bzhi po'i sbyin bsreg gis gdul bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4483: gnyis pa bro la yang bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:4488: de ltar ma grub na yang /
NK053('i)001:4489: gdul sbyang drag po'i bro yi phrin las kyis gdul bar bya ste /
NK053('i)001:4490: khro bo 'jigs byed kyi sku las ye shes kyi lta ba drag pos bskyod de /
NK053('i)001:4492: snang srid ril zla gam dmar po dbang gi rang bzhin du bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:4493: bdag nyid pad+ma he ru ka 'khor dang bcas pa bsgoms pas bro brdung ste /
NK053('i)001:4494: e wam ma ya bzhis las bzhi mtshon pa ste /
NK053('i)001:4495: ma tram lte bar dbang gi bro /
NK053('i)001:4496: bam gyi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:4497: lag pa lu gu rgyud du sbrel nas bsdams //
NK053('i)001:4501: ye gdod nas ma byung bdud la sogs //
NK053('i)001:4502: rgyal po de dang de dag gis //
NK053('i)001:4503: lan gcig dur khrod bcas pa'i tshe //
NK053('i)001:4504: gdug pa rnams kyi khrag za zhing //
NK053('i)001:4505: khro bo chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK053('i)001:4507: thang cig yud la drongs la shog /
NK053('i)001:4508: h+r+aimhche ge mo bam h+r+aih 'dod chags ma spangs gnas
NK053('i)001:4509: su dag pa pad+ma he ru ka skyes kyang 'dod
NK053('i)001:4512: 'dod chags las kyi ru tra khyod //
NK053('i)001:4514: rgyu zangs sam dmar po'i shing rnams la //
NK053('i)001:4515: dbyibs mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zla gam //
NK053('i)001:4516: logs la dbang gi lha bsgoms nas //
NK053('i)001:4517: khong stong byang chub sems lung bstan //
NK053('i)001:4518: btab na thams cad dbang du gyur //
NK053('i)001:4519: bam h+r+aim ma ma pa shang ku ru h+r+aih drag po'i bro bstan pa /
NK053('i)001:4520: de nas yang snang srid ril gru gsum drag po'i dkyil 'khor du bsgoms te /
NK053('i)001:4521: bdag nyid badz+ra he ru ka yab yum 'khor dang bcas pas bro brdung ste /
NK053('i)001:4522: ma tram gyi kha la drag po'i bro e yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:4523: lu gu rgyud du sbrel bas bsdams //
NK053('i)001:4524: bcings 'gyur bskyod nas phyogs bcur g.yo //
NK053('i)001:4526: gdod nas ma byung sogs tshig rkang bdun 'agre'o //
NK053('i)001:4527: h'u phata che ge mo h'u dzah zhe sdang ma
NK053('i)001:4528: spangs gnas su dag pa badz+ra he ru ka skyes
NK053('i)001:4529: kyang zhe sdang khyod las skyes //
NK053('i)001:4531: zhe sdang las kyi ru tra khyod //
NK053('i)001:4532: zhe sdang khro bo 'khor bcas kyis //
NK053('i)001:4533: lcags sam nag po'i shing rnams la //
NK053('i)001:4534: mgo bo rgya mdud rtse zur gsum //
NK053('i)001:4535: logs la drag po'i lha bsgoms nas //
NK053('i)001:4536: khong stong byang chub sems lung bstan //
NK053('i)001:4537: btab na thams cad brlag par 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:4538: h'u phata m+aa ra ya phata /
NK053('i)001:4540: de nas yang snang srid ril zlum po zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom la /
NK053('i)001:4541: bdag nyid bud+d+ha he ru ka yab yum 'khor dang bcas pas bro brdung ste /
NK053('i)001:4542: ma tram gyi spyi bor zhi ba'i bro y+aa yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:4543: lu gu rgyud du sbrel bas bsdams //
NK053('i)001:4544: 'bar ba lhan ner byin gyis khyab //
NK053('i)001:4545: thams cad g.yo ba med par byas //
NK053('i)001:4547: s+w+aa che ge mo s+w+aa dzah gti mug ma spangs
NK053('i)001:4548: gnas su dag pa bud+d+ha he ru ka skyes kyang
NK053('i)001:4551: gti mug las kyi ru tra khyod //
NK053('i)001:4552: gti mug khro bo 'khor bcas kyis //
NK053('i)001:4553: dngul lam dkar po'i shing rnams la //
NK053('i)001:4554: mgo la rgya mdung rtse zlum po //
NK053('i)001:4555: logs la zhi ba'i lha bsgoms nas //
NK053('i)001:4556: khong stong byang chub sems lung bstan //
NK053('i)001:4557: btab na thams cad zhi bar 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:4558: s+w+aa sh+ain+tam ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:4560: de nas yang snang srid ril gru bzhi rgyas pa'i dkyil 'khor du bsgom la /
NK053('i)001:4561: bdag nyid rat+na he ru ka yab yum 'khor dang bcas pas bro brdung ste /
NK053('i)001:4562: ma tram snying khar rgyas pa'i bro ma yi tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:4563: lu gu rgyud du sbrel bsdams bskyod //
NK053('i)001:4565: yid bzhin nam mkha' gang bar 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:4567: h+aa che ge mo h+aa dzah nga rgyal ma spangs
NK053('i)001:4568: gnas su dag pa rat+na he ru ka skyes kyang
NK053('i)001:4571: nga rgyal las kyi ru tra khyod //
NK053('i)001:4572: nga rgyal khro rgyal 'khor bcas kyis //
NK053('i)001:4573: gser ram ser po'i shing rnams la //
NK053('i)001:4574: mgo la rgya mdud rtse zur bzhi //
NK053('i)001:4575: logs la rgyas pa'i lha bsgoms nas //
NK053('i)001:4576: khong stong byang chub sems lung bstan //
NK053('i)001:4577: btab na thams cad rgyas par 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:4578: h+aa push+tim ku ru s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:4579: bar 'dir sgrub pa po'i tshe bkug la /
NK053('i)001:4581: bdag nyid dpal chen po'i thugs ka'i 'od zer gyis
NK053('i)001:4582: 'khor 'das kyi tshe bcud bsdus te bdag nyid rdo
NK053('i)001:4583: rje'i tshe grub par mos la /
NK053('i)001:4584: b+h+r+aum badz+ra +aa yu she b+h+r+aum +aah ci rigs bzlas la /
NK053('i)001:4586: de ltar btul ba'i dgos ched ni /
NK053('i)001:4587: sngon dpal chen pos de ltar mdzad pas /
NK053('i)001:4588: da ltar kyang sgrub pa pos pha'i las bus blangs pa lta bu dang /
NK053('i)001:4589: ma tram bsgral te khog pa la bde bar gshegs pa'i bzhugs gnas /
NK053('i)001:4590: gzhal yas khang su byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK053('i)001:4592: gshol la brgyab na glang skrag pa dang 'dra bar /
NK053('i)001:4593: dur khrod kyi bdag po ma tram ka mnan pas /
NK053('i)001:4594: bgegs phra mo gzhan gyis bar gcod mi nus shing /
NK053('i)001:4595: zil gyis gnon par 'gyur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:4596: dam sri ru tra bsgral bas rnal 'byor pa'i rig pa rtsal sbyangs nas /
NK053('i)001:4597: dam sri ru tra 'khor ba'i gnas nas bton te /
NK053('i)001:4598: sangs rgyas kyi sa la bzhag pa'i dge ba dang /
NK053('i)001:4599: ma tram mnan pa 'di lta bu phrin las zab mo 'di /
NK053('i)001:4600: skabs skabs su shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4601: dur khrod kyi bdag po ru tra 'khor dang bcas pa de /
NK053('i)001:4602: dpal he ru ka'i sku phyag rgya chen pos btul zhing bsgral nas /
NK053('i)001:4603: khog pa gzhal yas khang du byas te /
NK053('i)001:4604: phrin las rnam pa bzhi rdzogs par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4607: 3 / gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bri zhing rdzas dgod pa'i phrin las la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:4608: skabs sbyor bdun pa dkyil 'khor bri zhing rdzas bkod de mchod rdzas byin gyis brlab pa'i skabs so //
NK053('i)001:4609: lung dgu las mar me'i lung dang /
NK053('i)001:4611: dam rdzas dang mchod pa byin gyis brlabs pa'i lung zhes gsum pa de yin par snang /
NK053('i)001:4612: dkyil 'khor dgu pa gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK053('i)001:4613: bzhi pa mchod rdzas brten pa'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK053('i)001:4618: de yang dkyus gcig la zur gnyis par bstan te /
NK053('i)001:4621: zhi ba la yang lung gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:4622: rdul tshon bris te rdzas bsags nas bkod pa de bsnyen pa bya ba'i lung dang /
NK053('i)001:4623: rdul tshon bris te rdzas mchog bam la lha bkod de bsnyen pa bya ba'i lung ngo /
NK053('i)001:4625: 1 / de la rdul tshon bris te rdzas bsags nas bkod de bsnyen pa bya ba'i don la drug ste /
NK053('i)001:4626: dang po gzugs brnyan gyi man+dala bri bar bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:4627: lha dgod par bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:4628: mar me dgod par bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:4629: rdzas dgod par bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:4630: ting nge 'dzin gsal ba'i rten dgod par bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:4631: bsnyen pa'i cho ga gzhung bsrang ba'o //
NK053('i)001:4632: de la 1dang po gzugs brnyan gyi man+dala bri ba bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:4633: dkyil 'khor nub phyogs de bzhin gzhi //
NK053('i)001:4636: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bri bar bstan pa la lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:4637: dang po man+dala bya bar bstan pa /
NK053('i)001:4638: gnyis pa chag chag gdab pa /
NK053('i)001:4641: lnga pa sku gsung thugs kyi mtshan ma bstan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:4642: dang po man+dala bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:4644: dur khrod gnas kyi sa blangs la //
NK053('i)001:4645: stegs bu 'dom gang gru bzhi pa //
NK053('i)001:4646: 'phangs su khru gang pa yi tshad //
NK053('i)001:4647: bdud rtsi rnam lngas legs par bya //
NK053('i)001:4651: de la chag chag gdab pa yang /
NK053('i)001:4653: bka' gsang rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK053('i)001:4654: dam rdzas dag pa'i rang byung bdud rtsi lngas //
NK053('i)001:4655: bde gshegs rigs lnga'i dngos grub bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:4656: yang dag gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor chag chag 'debs //
NK053('i)001:4658: sarba pany+tsa a mri ta man+da la h'u /
NK053('i)001:4660: de nas thig skud gdab pa yang /
NK053('i)001:4661: dang por gzungs ma brtag pa dang /
NK053('i)001:4662: bdag dang gzungs ma byin gyis brlabs pa'ang kun 'og nas smos pa ltar shes par byas la /
NK053('i)001:4665: chos kyi dbyings las ye shes 'khrungs byed cing //
NK053('i)001:4666: rdo rje sems ma las kyi yid 'dzin ma //
NK053('i)001:4667: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'di la thig 'debs kyis //
NK053('i)001:4668: dngos grub sgrub pa'i las rnams kun gyis shig /
NK053('i)001:4670: thig skud ba su ta'am ras bal la byas te /
NK053('i)001:4672: yid kyis sbyor ba byas nas /
NK053('i)001:4673: byang chub sems dkyil 'khor steng du dkar breg gis byung bar bsam la /
NK053('i)001:4676: thabs dang shes rab ldan pa'i byin rlabs las //
NK053('i)001:4677: gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor chen po 'dir //
NK053('i)001:4678: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi thig 'debs kyis //
NK053('i)001:4679: ye shes gzhal yas pho brang lhun gyis grub //
NK053('i)001:4680: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man+da la b+h+r+aum /
NK053('i)001:4682: gnam thig shar nub dang lho byang du /
NK053('i)001:4684: steng gi phyogs su rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor du gyur par bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:4685: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor de mi shes rmongs pa la /
NK053('i)001:4687: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la thig gdab ste /
NK053('i)001:4688: yab yum gnyis kyis snying po brjod cing btab pas /
NK053('i)001:4689: gzugs brnyan de nyid mkha' klong rnam par dag pa'i gzhal yas khang du bsam zhing gdab ste /
NK053('i)001:4690: dang po phyogs mtshams kyi 'gros legs par snyoms la /
NK053('i)001:4691: man+dala gyi dkyil 'khor mthar gcal ba'i tshad la cha bzhir bgos te /
NK053('i)001:4692: de la cha gcig la pho brang gi snying po bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4693: cha gcig la khyams dang rdo rje ra ba gnyis sbrel bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4695: cha gcig la rta babs bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4696: de la sgo yi mdun thig tu bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:4697: dbus kyi pho brang la cha brgyad kyi mtshan ma btab ste /
NK053('i)001:4698: dang po phyogs thig gi rtsar cha gnyis la btab pas /
NK053('i)001:4699: de ni rjo thig tu 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:4700: de nas cha gcig la btab pas sgo'i pany+tsa re khar 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:4701: de nas cha gcig la btab pas sgo thig tu 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:4702: de nas cha gcig la btab pas sgo 'khyud kyi pany+tsa re khar 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:4703: de nas bar 'khyams kyi cha la pany+tsa re kha'i chag tshad gsum gyi tshad la btab pas /
NK053('i)001:4704: gru chad kyi rdo rje ra ba'i thig tu 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:4705: de bzhin du nang gi cha la btab pas gru chad nyid du 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:4706: glo 'bur gyi thig ni sgo'i pany+tsa re kha dang mnyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:4707: khyams phyed tshad la rdo rje'i ra ba dang bcas par gud du gdab bo //
NK053('i)001:4708: de nas sgo snam la cha brgyad du bgos te /
NK053('i)001:4709: cha dang po btab pas khyams kyi pany+tsa re khar 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:4710: de nas cha gnyis brkyangs te btab pas sgor 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:4711: de nas cha gcig btab pas sgo 'khyud kyi pany+tsa re khar 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:4712: de nas cha gnyis brkyangs te btab pas sgo 'khyud du 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:4713: de nas cha gcig btab pas sgo lhad kyi pany+tsa re khar 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:4714: phyi ma'o cha gcig po ni ya phubs su zad do //
NK053('i)001:4715: sgo 'khyams kyi rgyan dang rta babs ni ci dgar bya bar zad do //
NK053('i)001:4716: de nas dbus su phur pa btab ste /
NK053('i)001:4717: pho brang zlum po rdo rje'i ra ba dang bcas pa shig bskor bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4718: de nas dbus kyi pho brang gru bzhi la 'khor lo'i lte bar bskor te /
NK053('i)001:4719: de'i phyi rol cha gsum gyi tshad la /
NK053('i)001:4720: nang gi cha gcig re mig gi char bzhag ste /
NK053('i)001:4721: cha gnyis la rtsibs bya ste /
NK053('i)001:4722: 'khor lo'i rtsibs bzhi'i thig tu bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4724: de nas sa tshon byin brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:4726: rang byung 'byung ba lnga yi khyad par las //
NK053('i)001:4727: 'og gi sa tshon ye shes lnga ru rdzogs /
NK053('i)001:4728: khams gsum thugs rjes yongs su bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:4729: dag pa dri med ye shes lnga ru bsgom //
NK053('i)001:4732: sa tshon dpa' bo 'bru lnga las /
NK053('i)001:4738: ye shes lnga'i 'od du gyur te /
NK053('i)001:4739: dkar po chos dbyings ye shes /
NK053('i)001:4744: 'od zer sna lnga las rin po che sna lnga'i gzhal yas khang du gyur par bsgom la /
NK053('i)001:4745: dbus kyi phur pa bton te /
NK053('i)001:4746: de'i shul du sa tshon sna lnga dgang ngo //
NK053('i)001:4748: tshon pra brtag phyir byang shar mtshams nas pany+tsa re kha khrid de drangs te bzhag nas /
NK053('i)001:4749: de'i kha ban+d+hasa bkab ste bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:4750: zhig na mi legs ma zhig par grib so ngam me byung na legs so //
NK053('i)001:4751: dbus kyi lte ba mthing ka /
NK053('i)001:4752: 'khor lo'i rtsibs bzhi rigs dang bstun pa'am dkar ser dmar ljang ser po gang yang rung du bya /
NK053('i)001:4754: gru chad dang glo 'bur bzhi bzhi ljang gu /
NK053('i)001:4756: sgo bzhi rigs dang bstun la /
NK053('i)001:4757: phyi rol lcags ri'i mtha' rdo rje dang me 'od kyis bskor ro //
NK053('i)001:4758: lnga pa lha yi sku gsung thugs mtshan dgod pa /
NK053('i)001:4759: de la lha so so'i h'u m+aum sogs yi ge'am /
NK053('i)001:4761: yang na thig le dgod par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4762: yang na de kun mi dgos te /
NK053('i)001:4763: 'og nas smos pa'i rdzas bkod pas chog /
NK053('i)001:4769: dkyil 'khor de la brten nas bsnyen pa byas pa'i dus na /
NK053('i)001:4770: rgyu sems can gyi las dang nyon mongs pa'i g.yengs pas bsdus pa thams cad nub nas /
NK053('i)001:4771: 'bras bu rgyal ba bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi zhing khams la phyogsa nas /
NK053('i)001:4772: gzhi gzhal yas khang de la brten te bsnyen pa bya /
NK053('i)001:4774: gnyis pa lha 2bkod pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:4778: dang po rdzas dgod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:4779: kham phor ri mo bris pa dgu //
NK053('i)001:4782: rigs lnga yab yum gyi snying po /
NK053('i)001:4783: h'u badz+ra d+h+rika la sogs byang chub sems dkar dmar gyis bri'o //
NK053('i)001:4785: sems dpa' yab yum gyi snying po k+shim hi r+aa dza sogs bri'o //
NK053('i)001:4787: kham phor ri mor bris pa dgu //
NK053('i)001:4790: tsan+dana gyi phur pa zlum po re re la snying po mu ne krung sogs bri'o //
NK053('i)001:4791: sgo bzhi khro bo yab yum ni /
NK053('i)001:4792: seng ldeng gi phur pa brgyad la snying po ya m+aan ta krita ta sogs bri'o //
NK053('i)001:4793: kun bzang yab yum gnyis ni /
NK053('i)001:4794: dbus kyi ban+d+ha la bri yang zer ro //
NK053('i)001:4795: rdo rje dang dril bu la bri yang zer ro //
NK053('i)001:4796: gnyis pa lha dgod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:4797: de nas ban+d+ha'i mtshan gsol ba byas pa lha sbyan drangs shing dgod pa /
NK053('i)001:4799: dbus nas rang byung grub pa'i lha //
NK053('i)001:4800: bcom ldan rdo rje sems dpa' dang //
NK053('i)001:4801: yum chen kun tu bzang mo gnyis //
NK053('i)001:4802: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor chen po nas /
NK053('i)001:4803: dzahmh'u bam hohs spyan drangs shing //
NK053('i)001:4805: seng chen bsnol ba'i gdan steng dang //
NK053('i)001:4806: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan stengs su //
NK053('i)001:4807: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:4808: dzahmh'u bam hoh h'u badz+ra d+hika /
NK053('i)001:4809: m+aum d+ha ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:4810: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta sa ma ya tish+tha lhan /
NK053('i)001:4812: des 'grel bar byas la dgod do //
NK053('i)001:4815: shar nas rang byung bcom ldan rnam par snang mdzad dang //
NK053('i)001:4816: yum chen sangs rgyas spyan ma glang chen bsnol ba'i gdan dzi na dzika /
NK053('i)001:4817: lam te sha ra ti s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:4824: m+aam mo ha ra ti s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:4829: pyam r+aa ga ra ti s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:4836: de bzhin dbang shes dag pa sems dpa' brgyad /
NK053('i)001:4837: yul dus dag pa sems ma brgyad /
NK053('i)001:4840: nyon mongs dag pa thub drug /
NK053('i)001:4843: rtag chad mu bzhi dag pa sgo ba bzhi /
NK053('i)001:4844: tshad med bzhi ldan sgo ma bzhi /
NK053('i)001:4847: yid chos dag pa kun bzang yab yum /
NK053('i)001:4849: rgyas bsdus ci rigs sbyar ba zhi ba snyen dang /
NK053('i)001:4850: khro sgrub la'ang 'og tu 'byung ba ltar rgyas bsdus rten mtshungs sbyar chog par sems /
NK053('i)001:4851: chos spyan ldan pas dpyad par zhu /
NK053('i)001:4852: mar 3me dgod pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:4853: snang ba'i 'od dag chas par dgram //
NK053('i)001:4855: mar me bca' ba la sogs pa 'og tu shes par byas la /
NK053('i)001:4858: skye med chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK053('i)001:4859: ye shes rol pa rmad 'byung las //
NK053('i)001:4860: ma tram gyi ni khog pa la //
NK053('i)001:4861: ye shes chen po'i gzhal yas khang //
NK053('i)001:4863: kun tu bzang mo yum gyi kong bu ru //
NK053('i)001:4864: skye med byang chub sems kyi mar gyis bltams //
NK053('i)001:4865: 'chi med thabs la mkhas pa'i sdong bu la //
NK053('i)001:4866: ye shes 'od 'phro 'bar ba'i me sbar te //
NK053('i)001:4867: gti mug mun khang 'joms pa'i gzi byin can //
NK053('i)001:4868: dug gsum gnas bsreg sku gsung thugs kyi gter //
NK053('i)001:4869: sems kyi dper bzhag ye shes rang snang ba //
NK053('i)001:4870: me long lta bu'i ye shes bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:4871: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor gnas su bsgrur par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4872: dz+ny+aa na d+ai pa sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:4873: zhes mar me lha grangs bzhin du dgod par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4874: rdzas 4dgod pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:4875: rdzas kyis mdzes par 'khor bar bzhag /
NK053('i)001:4877: rigs lnga mtshon rtags dar tshon sna lnga'i yol ba bres /
NK053('i)001:4878: sems dpa' brgyad mda' bzhi dang /
NK053('i)001:4880: sems ma brgyad ral gri bzhi dang /
NK053('i)001:4882: sgo ba yab yum rtags rin po che'i phreng ba bzhi dang /
NK053('i)001:4884: ye shes lnga'i rtags tshon skud sna lngas bskor /
NK053('i)001:4885: gzhan yang mchod rdzas la sogs pa dgod par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4886: ting nge 'dzin gsal 5 ba'i rten dgod pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:4887: mig gi rten yang mngon par bzhag /
NK053('i)001:4891: gsang ba'i sgrub pa gzhung gzugs pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:4893: dbang bskur ba'i bum pa dang /
NK053('i)001:4895: dkyil 'khor dang rdzas de la brten nas /
NK053('i)001:4896: bsnyen pa'i cho ga gzhung 6bsrang ba ni /
NK053('i)001:4897: 'og nas 'byung ba nar mar lha mnyes par bya ba'i phrin las kyis shes par bya'o /
NK053('i)001:4900: rdul tshon bris te rdzas mchog bam la brten te bsnyen pa bya ba'i lung ni /
NK053('i)001:4902: dkyil 'khor zla gam sgo gcig pa //
NK053('i)001:4903: shar du bstan par bris nas su //
NK053('i)001:4904: de steng ro ni tsog pur bzhag /
NK053('i)001:4906: gong du sta gon la gnas par byas pa'i ro sgrom nas phyungs te /
NK053('i)001:4907: 'od kyi las rim ltar khrus legs par byas nas /
NK053('i)001:4909: dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa byas te man+dala dbus su bzhag nas /
NK053('i)001:4910: de la lha dgod pa yang /
NK053('i)001:4912: ro la lha rnams dgod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:4913: bdag nyid mi bskyod pa yab yum sa bon las //
NK053('i)001:4914: ta th+aa la sogs bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK053('i)001:4915: ro yi gnas su spros pa las //
NK053('i)001:4916: yan lag lnga la bsam pa ni //
NK053('i)001:4921: rkang g.yas don grub rigs lnga yab yum bsgom par bya //
NK053('i)001:4922: mdun rgyab gnyis su bsam pa ni //
NK053('i)001:4923: a li kun tu bzang po /
NK053('i)001:4926: rnam shes mig shes sa snying /
NK053('i)001:4930: dbang po mig dbang byams pa /
NK053('i)001:4934: yul mig yul gzugs l+aa s+ye ma /
NK053('i)001:4943: sems dpa' yab yum bsgom par bya //
NK053('i)001:4944: spyi bo lha'i thub pa rgyab lha min thub /
NK053('i)001:4945: dang lce mi thub snying byol song thub /
NK053('i)001:4949: dmyal ba'i thub pa yan chad thub pa drug /
NK053('i)001:4950: lte ba gshin rje yab yum drug mdo gzhan gyis mi thub /
NK053('i)001:4953: g.yon bdud rtsi 'khyil ba yab yum mo //
NK053('i)001:4954: sgo ba yab yum bsgom par bya //
NK053('i)001:4957: chos kun rtsa ba sems yin te //
NK053('i)001:4958: sems ni snang ba gsum du shar //
NK053('i)001:4960: bdag rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor sgom pa dang /
NK053('i)001:4961: bkod pa rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor rdul tshon dang /
NK053('i)001:4962: rang bzhin lhun grub kyi dkyil 'khor gnas lugs te /
NK053('i)001:4963: de gsum ci gsal du gsal ba las /
NK053('i)001:4965: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor spyan drangs bstim //
NK053('i)001:4966: phyag 'tshal mchod de gnas pa dang //
NK053('i)001:4968: yang nas yang du sbyang bar bya //
NK053('i)001:4970: bsnyen pa'i 'phro 'du 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4971: de ltar byas pa'i yon tan yang /
NK053('i)001:4973: rnam smin zag bcas phung po la //
NK053('i)001:4974: bam lha'i phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor gsal bkod nas //
NK053('i)001:4976: gnyis don mthar phyin phyag rgyar dgrol //
NK053('i)001:4978: de dag gi phrin las bya ba'i rim pa ni /
NK053('i)001:4980: bam sgrub man ngag las shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:4981: de ltar zhi ba bsnyen pa'i dkyil 'khor la blo sbyangs /
NK053('i)001:4982: zhi ba'i bsnyen pa mthar phyungs nas /
NK053('i)001:4983: 2 khro bo sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor bstan pa la don lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:4985: lha dgod pa bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:4986: mar me dgod pa bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:4987: rdzas dgod pa bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:4988: mig gi rten bzhag par bstan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:4989: de la 1dkyil 'khor bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:4990: dkyil 'khor de bzhin nub phyogs gzhi /
NK053('i)001:4991: kham phor ri mor bris pa dgu //
NK053('i)001:4992: snang ba'i 'od dang chas par dgram //
NK053('i)001:4993: rdzas kyis mdzes par 'khor bar bzhag /
NK053('i)001:4994: mig gi rten yang mngon par bri //
NK053('i)001:4996: de la dkyil 'khor bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:4997: dkyil 'khor de bzhin nub phyogs gzhi //
NK053('i)001:5000: dkyila 'khora zhes pa'i don man+da la zhes bya ste /
NK053('i)001:5002: la ni len pa'am 'dzin pa ste /
NK053('i)001:5003: bla na med pa'i byang chub mi gnas pa'i don de len pa'am 'dzin pa'i phyir ro //
NK053('i)001:5007: chos kyi dbyings ye ji bzhin pa de ni /
NK053('i)001:5008: shes bya thams cad kyi mchog tu gyur pa de ni dkyil yin pas /
NK053('i)001:5009: de la ye shes brgyad kyis bskor ba ni 'khor zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:5011: dbus kyi gtso bo ni dkyil yin la /
NK053('i)001:5012: de la 'khor rgyas 'bring gis bskor ba la 'khor zhes bya ste /
NK053('i)001:5013: spyi'i don de bzhin gshegs pa byas la /
NK053('i)001:5014: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i gzhung gis /
NK053('i)001:5015: dngos grub dkyil 'khor la brten te sgrub pa'i phyir na dkyil 'khor /
NK053('i)001:5017: dkyil 'khor la yang gzhung gnyis las /
NK053('i)001:5022: gsang ba byang chub kyi dkyil 'khor dang bzhi /
NK053('i)001:5024: don de bzhi la brten te dngos grub bsgrub bo //
NK053('i)001:5026: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK053('i)001:5027: rdzogs pa a nu yo ga'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK053('i)001:5028: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga'i dkyil 'khor dang gsum /
NK053('i)001:5030: don de gsum la brten te dngos grub sgrub bo //
NK053('i)001:5031: de gsum yang lta spyod sgrub pa gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:5032: de yang sgrub pa ma h+aa yo ga 'di /
NK053('i)001:5033: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor la brten te sgrub par rgyud lung man ngag kun las gsungs pas /
NK053('i)001:5034: zhi ba las khro bor gnas bsgyur nas sgrub pa'i dus su /
NK053('i)001:5037: gnyis pa bdud rtsi lnga'i go ma ye /
NK053('i)001:5044: bka' gsang rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK053('i)001:5045: 'khor ba'i rgyun bcad byang chub sems kyi ngang //
NK053('i)001:5046: mkha' dbyings rnam dag yum gyi gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:5047: rak+ta gsang ba'i thig le chen por spro //
NK053('i)001:5048: ma h+aa rak+ta dz+wa la man+da la h'u /
NK053('i)001:5050: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:5051: gdod nas dag pa'i dri med byang chub sems //
NK053('i)001:5052: ye shes rang byung chen po bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:5053: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor chen po chag chag 'debs //
NK053('i)001:5054: ma h+aa bo b+hi tsit+ta man+dala h'u /
NK053('i)001:5055: zhes yab yum gnyis kyi byang chub sems dkar dmar gyis chag chag gdab bo //
NK053('i)001:5057: de nas bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga yis chag chag go ma ye btang ste /
NK053('i)001:5059: dug lnga rnam dag sku lngar lhun gyis grub //
NK053('i)001:5060: gdod nas dag pa'i bdud rtsi go ma ye //
NK053('i)001:5061: shes rab yum gyi mkha' la rgyur ltar gsal //
NK053('i)001:5062: dur khrod gsang ba'i bzhugs gnas thig ler shar //
NK053('i)001:5063: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta man+da la h'u /
NK053('i)001:5066: de nas thig gdab par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:5068: dkyil 'khor thig gdab shes rab can //
NK053('i)001:5069: phyogs kun mnyam pa nyid bsgrub cing //
NK053('i)001:5070: don gyi dkyil 'khor yang dag ji lta bar //
NK053('i)001:5071: don rab tu brtag pa su zhig nus //
NK053('i)001:5072: rang gis lha yi rang bzhin gyi //
NK053('i)001:5073: gnyis med don gyi dkyil 'khor brtag pa grub par 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:5076: don dam par phyogs kun mnyam pa nyid du dmigs la /
NK053('i)001:5077: don dam la dkyil 'khor cho ga rdzogs par sus nus te /
NK053('i)001:5078: rang gi lha'i rnal 'byor du zhugs na /
NK053('i)001:5079: dkyil 'khor gyi cho ga rnams 'grub par 'gyur te /
NK053('i)001:5080: dper na lha'i bu la khang pa brtsigs pa med par rang grub tu yod pa lta bu'o //
NK053('i)001:5081: kun rdzob tu thig g.yog gzungs ma ste /
NK053('i)001:5082: byin gyis brlabs pa byas te /
NK053('i)001:5083: yab kyis yum la brjod pa /
NK053('i)001:5084: bkra shis mtshan ldan gsang ba'i yum //
NK053('i)001:5085: zhal nas ut+pala ngad ldan zhing //
NK053('i)001:5086: skad kyang ngang pa gzhon nu 'dra //
NK053('i)001:5087: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can //
NK053('i)001:5088: zla gsang dkar dmar skung khang lci //
NK053('i)001:5089: gzhan gyis kha 'drong mi gtub pa //
NK053('i)001:5090: rdo rje'i las kyi don 'grub ma //
NK053('i)001:5091: gnyis med sbyor ba'i byin rlabs las //
NK053('i)001:5093: sgrub pa'i las rnams kun gyis shig /
NK053('i)001:5099: zla gam dmar po gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK053('i)001:5100: dur khrod bdag po dregs pa'i tshogs bsgral ste //
NK053('i)001:5101: rgyu 'phreng khrag dang bcas pa'i thig 'debs kyis //
NK053('i)001:5102: thabs dang shes rab 'du 'bral med pa yi //
NK053('i)001:5103: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi thig chen 'dis //
NK053('i)001:5104: steng 'og thams cad dur khrod brdal bar shar //
NK053('i)001:5106: stong gsum thams cad khrag gi rgya mtsho la //
NK053('i)001:5107: gsang ba byang chub sems kyi thig btab pas //
NK053('i)001:5108: dur khrood gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor lhun gyis grub /
NK053('i)001:5109: khams gsum ma lus dug lnga'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK053('i)001:5110: bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga yi thig btab pa //
NK053('i)001:5111: ye shes lnga yi gzhal yas lhun gyis grub //
NK053('i)001:5112: b+h+r+aum bi shwa b+hi shud+d+he ma h+aa tsan+t+ra man+da la h'u /
NK053('i)001:5113: zhes brjod de thig gdab bo //
NK053('i)001:5114: de yang dang po phyogs mtshams kyi 'gros mnyam pa dang /
NK053('i)001:5115: thig gi cha bgo ba la sogs pa kun gong du bstan pa ltar bya ste /
NK053('i)001:5116: bzhi pa dkyil 'khor bri ba la /
NK053('i)001:5117: de la dbus kyi pho brang lte ba zlum por byas pa la /
NK053('i)001:5121: de la rdo rje bzhad pa'i gzhung gis /
NK053('i)001:5125: lho nas byang du gsum du bgos pa'i nub phyogs ngos kyi cha gnyis po la /
NK053('i)001:5126: sum gnyis zla gam sgo gcig la kha shar du bltas par byas te /
NK053('i)001:5127: de la thig bzhi btab pas le'u tshe dgu pa'i thig btab la /
NK053('i)001:5128: gzhi ma rak+tasa dmar por byugs la /
NK053('i)001:5129: dbus kyi le'u tshe la zla gam kha shar du blta bar bya /
NK053('i)001:5130: le'u tshe brgyad la zla gam chung ngu brgyad kha nang du bstan par bya /
NK053('i)001:5131: re kha rangs pa thal chen gyis btab ste /
NK053('i)001:5132: shar phyogs zla gam dkar por bya /
NK053('i)001:5133: zlum po la me ri'i thod phreng gis bskor //
NK053('i)001:5135: 'dod yon snam bu dang po dmar por bya /
NK053('i)001:5137: bar der thig la man ngag spyad /
NK053('i)001:5138: mtha' lcags ri nag por byas te /
NK053('i)001:5139: rak+ta'i pad+ma la thal chen gyis b+h+yo zhes bri'o //
NK053('i)001:5140: gnyis pa don rtags bshad pa de la gnyis /
NK053('i)001:5141: gzugs brnyan de ltar bris pa de la don gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:5142: mtshan ma'i dbyibs kyi bshad pa dang /
NK053('i)001:5143: rtsa ba'i nges tshig bshad pa'o //
NK053('i)001:5144: de la mtshan ma'i dbyibs kyi bshad par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:5145: phyi zla ba tshes bcu drug pa ltar zlum por gyur pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5146: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten kun las zlum po'i thig
NK053('i)001:5147: le spros pa med pa'i dbyings de nyid dur khrod
NK053('i)001:5148: chen po'i gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK053('i)001:5149: de'i lho nas byang du bcad pa'i nub phyogs zla gam dmar po sgo gcig tu gyur pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5150: chos kyi dbyings spros pa med pa'i ngang der /
NK053('i)001:5151: ril dbang du gyur pas zla gam du bstan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5152: de las kun 'byung kun 'jug pas sgo gcig tu bstan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:5153: nang gi zla gam brgyad ni /
NK053('i)001:5154: bcud kyi 'jig rten gyi sems ril ye shes brgyad du shar ba'i rtags so //
NK053('i)001:5156: ril chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes su lhun gyis grub pa'i phyir ro //
NK053('i)001:5157: rtsa ba'i nges tshig gis bshad na /
NK053('i)001:5158: phyi zla ba tshes bcu drug pa ltar byas pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5159: chos ril chos nyid thig le nyag gcig tu gyur pa la /
NK053('i)001:5160: bgrang ba'i tha snyad dang bral ba'i rtags so //
NK053('i)001:5161: nub phyogs zla gam dmar por byas pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5162: yum gyi mkha' pad+ma ge sar gyi klong /
NK053('i)001:5163: zla gam dmar po gzhal yas khang du gsal ba la /
NK053('i)001:5164: de la sgo gcig tu byas pa la ni /
NK053('i)001:5165: sangs rgyas dang sems can ril 'byung ba'i gnas su gyur pa'o //
NK053('i)001:5166: nang gi zla gam brgyad ni /
NK053('i)001:5167: byang chub kyi sems las ye shes kyi phyag rgya
NK053('i)001:5168: sna tshogs yum gyi mkha' las byung ba'i rtags so
NK053('i)001:5169: // dbus kyi lte ba zla gam du byas pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5170: dbyings ma 'gas pa'i ye shes kyi bye brag thugs rjer 'char ba'i phyir ro //
NK053('i)001:5171: de ltar gsal ba de bzhina ye shes lha'i pho brang yin pas /
NK053('i)001:5174: de la shar phyogs zla gam dkar por byas pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5175: chos ril dam tshig tu 'dus te /
NK053('i)001:5176: dam tshig de yang logs nas cang ma yin te /
NK053('i)001:5177: bdag dam tshig sems dpa'i sems rnam par dag pa'i rtags so //
NK053('i)001:5178: zlum po la thod pa'i phreng bas bskor ba ni /
NK053('i)001:5179: ye shes rnam pa lnga las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang yin la /
NK053('i)001:5180: de la me ris bskor ba ni /
NK053('i)001:5181: las dang nyon mongs pa'i bag chags ril ye shes chen po'i klong du bsreg cing 'joms pa'o //
NK053('i)001:5182: sgo khyams la sogs pa'i don 'og tu bshad do //
NK053('i)001:5184: slob dpon h'u k+aa ra'i gzhung gis kyang gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:5186: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi don rtags so //
NK053('i)001:5188: dkyil 'khor nub phyogs de bzhin gzhi //
NK053('i)001:5190: dbus kyi pho brang zlum por bskor te /
NK053('i)001:5191: lho nas byang du bcad pa'i shar phyogs zla gam
NK053('i)001:5192: dmar po kha nub tu bstan pa gnam sgo gcig
NK053('i)001:5193: pa / de la rak+tasa dmar por byug pa la /
NK053('i)001:5194: byang chub sems dkar dmar bsres pa'i thig le dgu dang bcas pa'i bri'o //
NK053('i)001:5195: nub phyogs thal chen gyis dkar por byug la /
NK053('i)001:5196: tha ma rdo rje ra bas bskor ba gcig thal chen gyis bri'o //
NK053('i)001:5198: gzhan yang gang dag kha cig tu //
NK053('i)001:5199: ri mo gcig pa de bzhin bya //
NK053('i)001:5200: thar byed gang dag bshad pa ni //
NK053('i)001:5201: de dag thams cad ri mo gcig /
NK053('i)001:5203: de la gru chad gzhi ljang ku /
NK053('i)001:5204: de'i phyi rim gru bzhi'i snam bu dmar po /
NK053('i)001:5205: de'i phyi rim du sgo bzhi sgo 'khyud dang rta babs bcas par bri /
NK053('i)001:5206: tha ma lcags ri rdo rje me 'od kyi phreng bas bskor bar byas la /
NK053('i)001:5207: sgo bzhi la ma tram gyi yan lag dang pags pa'i tshul du bcas par dri'o //
NK053('i)001:5209: de la phyi nang gsang bar sbyar te bshad na /
NK053('i)001:5210: phyi sbyar na dur khrod chen po ma tram gyi khog pa las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK053('i)001:5211: nang du gzugs kyi phung po dur khrod 'bar ba las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang /
NK053('i)001:5212: gsang ba yum gyi b+ha ga'i gzhal yas khang ngo //
NK053('i)001:5213: gsang ba kun gzhi'i byang chub sems rang byung gcig gi ngang ngo //
NK053('i)001:5214: de yang dbye bas kyi bshad na /
NK053('i)001:5215: phyi kun nas zlum pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5216: kun gzhi byang chub sems thig le gcig par gyur pa yin la /
NK053('i)001:5217: de la shar phyogs zla gam dmar por byas pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5218: byang chub sems thig le gcig gi ngang du ril dbang du gyur pa yin la /
NK053('i)001:5219: de la sgo gcig tu gyur pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5220: thig le byang chub sems las kun 'byung zhing der 'du ba'o //
NK053('i)001:5221: nub phyogs zla gam dkar por byas pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5222: thig le byang chub sems la nyes pa'i skyon gang gis kyang ma gos /
NK053('i)001:5224: thig le byang chub sems de 'dus ma byas shing /
NK053('i)001:5225: 'pho 'gyur med pa'i byang chub sems so //
NK053('i)001:5229: che ba'i yon tan rgyas pa'o //
NK053('i)001:5232: de la ma tram gyi lnga phung yan lag tu phyung ba ni /
NK053('i)001:5233: 'khor ba'i chos ril dur khrod chen po 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang du gyur pa ste /
NK053('i)001:5234: mtha' lcags ri dang rdo rje me 'od kyi phreng bas 'khrigs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5235: bdud dang mu stegs gang gis kyang mi tshugs par 'joms pa'i rtags so //
NK053('i)001:5236: de ltar gyur pa'i man+dala de ni /
NK053('i)001:5237: dpal chen po thig le gcig pa'i sgrub pa yin la /
NK053('i)001:5238: de la byang chub sems dkar dmar bsres pa'i thig le dgur byung ba ni /
NK053('i)001:5239: thig le byang chub sems gcig las che ba'i yon tan ye shes brgyad du shar bas /
NK053('i)001:5240: 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa'i rtags su lha mo koo'u
NK053('i)001:5241: r+ai ma brgyad dang bcas par gsal ba'i rtags de
NK053('i)001:5242: / yang dag grub pa'i don gyi lha dgur gsal ba'i man+dala lo //
NK053('i)001:5245: dkyil 'khora kyang de bzhina du bya /
NK053('i)001:5249: zhi bsnyen mthar dbyung nas tha ma'i nub la sgrub pa chen po brtsam ste /
NK053('i)001:5250: zla gam dmar po nub tu byas la lha'i pho brang bca' /
NK053('i)001:5252: de ltar dkyil 'khor bris pa dang /
NK053('i)001:5254: slob dpon rdo rje bzhad pa'i gzhung gis /
NK053('i)001:5255: dkyil 'khor bris pa de nyid gzhal yas khang du gyur pa yin pas /
NK053('i)001:5256: b+han+d+ha dang mar me bsdebs la /
NK053('i)001:5257: rang bzhin grub pa'i lha rnams spyan drangs shing dgod /
NK053('i)001:5259: slob dpon h'u k+aa ra'i gzhung gis /
NK053('i)001:5260: skabs 'dir yang mtshams bcad pa dang /
NK053('i)001:5261: dur khrod kyi bdag po mnan pa gong du bstan pa ltar skabs 'dir yang shes par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:5262: ma tram bsgral ba'i khog pa dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas khang du gsal ba der /
NK053('i)001:5263: lha dgod par bstan 3pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:5264: lha dgod par bstan pa la don dgu ste /
NK053('i)001:5265: dang po rigs brtag cing gsog /
NK053('i)001:5266: gnyis pa dbus kyi b+han+d+ha mtshan gsol /
NK053('i)001:5267: gsum pa rdo rje dril bu dgod /
NK053('i)001:5269: lnga pa koo'u r+ai ma brgyad bzhugs gsol /
NK053('i)001:5273: dgu pa gsang ba'i ma mo dgod pa'o //
NK053('i)001:5274: dang po rigs brtag cing bsags pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5275: kham phor ri mor bris pa dgu //
NK053('i)001:5278: dbus su rgyal rigs thod pa dum bu gcig pa dang //
NK053('i)001:5279: phyogs bzhir bram ze be ta l+ai rgyal rigs koo'u r+ai dang //
NK053('i)001:5281: dmangs rigs phra mo he bzhi la bya //
NK053('i)001:5282: mtshams bzhir khrus mkhan puk+ka s+ai gar mkhan g+hasma r+ai dang //
NK053('i)001:5284: btso brlag mkhan tsan d+ha l+ai rnams la //
NK053('i)001:5285: mi yi khrag la snag tsha bya //
NK053('i)001:5286: mchog gi rkang gi smyug gu yis //
NK053('i)001:5287: gtso bo yab yum dang ko'u r+ai sogs /
NK053('i)001:5288: lha dgu so so'i snying po bri //
NK053('i)001:5289: b+han+d+ha'i mtshan gsol bzhugs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5291: b+han+d+ha rnams so sor bsags shing /
NK053('i)001:5292: so so'i rang rang gi snying po bris la /
NK053('i)001:5293: sgrub pa po kun gyis phyag tu bzhes la /
NK053('i)001:5294: kun gyis dbyangs blangs la 'di skad do //
NK053('i)001:5295: gnyis pa dbus kyi b+han+d+ha mtshan gsol zhing dbus su dgod pa /
NK053('i)001:5296: dpal gyi gnam zhal mtshan dang ldan pa /
NK053('i)001:5297: thod pa rang gis smras pa /
NK053('i)001:5298: zhal bu k+aa pa la yi mtshan gsol ba //
NK053('i)001:5299: 'phrul zhal yid bzhin nor bu 'dra phra men rgyan gyis klubs //
NK053('i)001:5301: thod pa mtshan ldan sa la sbas kyang nam mkhar
NK053('i)001:5302: song bas rkang med mkha' la 'gro ba rkan sgra
NK053('i)001:5303: tog tog can // sngon gyi skyes mchog sgrub po'i rdzas yin te //
NK053('i)001:5304: dpal chen sngags kyis bkugs pas mchog thun dngos grub
NK053('i)001:5305: thob pas su zhig dngos grub 'dod pas sid+d+hi b+han+d+ha
NK053('i)001:5306: nga las longs // gang zhig bka' ltar mi byed dam la mi gnas pa //
NK053('i)001:5307: nga yi gzugs mthong tsam gyis tshig pa dang //
NK053('i)001:5308: nga yi sgra thos tsam gyis brlag par 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:5309: thod pa skam po chos sku mtshon te /
NK053('i)001:5310: dkar po zang yag 'tsher ba ni //
NK053('i)001:5313: chos kyi sku dang rab ldan pas //
NK053('i)001:5314: 'gro ba'i don la de bzhin gshegs //
NK053('i)001:5315: rlon pa lcang lor 'khyil ba ni //
NK053('i)001:5316: longs sku ye shes sgyu ma mtshon /
NK053('i)001:5317: da ltar bzhugs pa'i bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:5318: longs spyod rdzogs sku rab ldan pas //
NK053('i)001:5319: 'gro ba'i don la de bzhin gshegs //
NK053('i)001:5320: dmar po ra rir chags pa ni //
NK053('i)001:5321: dbang lnga tshang mngon lnga ldan sprul sku'i 'gro don mtshon /
NK053('i)001:5322: slad kyi byon pa'i bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:5323: sprul pa'i sku dag rab ldan pas //
NK053('i)001:5324: 'gro ba'i don la de bzhin gshegs //
NK053('i)001:5327: dbus nas rang byung grub pa'i lha //
NK053('i)001:5328: thugs mchog badz+ra he ru kah /
NK053('i)001:5329: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri gnyis //
NK053('i)001:5330: rang bzhin dkyil 'khor chen po nas //
NK053('i)001:5331: dzahmh'u bam hohs spyan drangs shing //
NK053('i)001:5332: dur khrod chen po'i gnas mchog dang //
NK053('i)001:5334: lha chen ru tra pho mo bsnol ba'i gdan steng du //
NK053('i)001:5335: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5336: sku gsum bdag nyid dpal chen he ru ka thabs kyi rgyal po yin pas /
NK053('i)001:5337: thabs kyi rgyal po dpal chen nyid kyi gnas //
NK053('i)001:5338: rgyal po'i pho brang gzhal yas khyad par byas pa
NK053('i)001:5339: ltar pho brang rtags dang ldan pa snod bcud rgyan
NK053('i)001:5340: du che // sprul pa lcang lo mang po'i kha bad can //
NK053('i)001:5341: dbang po rnam lnga snod bcud rgyan bkram nas //
NK053('i)001:5342: dngos po dang mtshan ma'i mtha' la mi gnas dbyings
NK053('i)001:5343: ye thabs shes dpal chen yab yum bzhugs pa'i rten
NK053('i)001:5344: du 'bul // badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka dpal rdo rje khrag 'thung /
NK053('i)001:5345: badz+ra kro t+ai shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:5351: b+han+d+ha kha nub tu bstan la kha sbub la bzhag ste /
NK053('i)001:5352: dpal chen yab yum gnyis thabs dang shes rab zung du 'khril te bzhugs par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:5353: gsum pa rdo rje dril bu dgod pa /
NK053('i)001:5354: rdo rje rigs mchog chen po ste //
NK053('i)001:5355: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK053('i)001:5356: thabs dang shes rab gnyis su ldan //
NK053('i)001:5357: rtags kyi phyag rgyar bzhugs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5358: bid+y+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra h'u sa ma ya tish+tha lhan /
NK053('i)001:5359: d+harma d+ha tu g+han+de hohs ma ya tish+tha lhan /
NK053('i)001:5360: zhes gser gyi rdo rje dang dril bu g.yas dang g.yon du bzhag /
NK053('i)001:5362: snying gi snying po sgrub thabs yang snying 'di //
NK053('i)001:5363: snying dang 'dra ba'i yang snying thugs la sbyin //
NK053('i)001:5364: thugs kyi snying po yin pas snying bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:5366: tsit+ta srog rtsa dang ma bral bar bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:5367: lnga pa ko'u r+ai bzhugs su gsol ba /
NK053('i)001:5368: de nas lha mo koo'u r+ai ma brgyad drangs shing bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK053('i)001:5370: dur khrod gnas brgyad 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK053('i)001:5371: ma chen 'bar ma rnam brgyad gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5373: ma mo chen mo me 'bar ma //
NK053('i)001:5374: ba spu'i bu ga nas me 'bar ba'o //
NK053('i)001:5375: shar du dkar mo koo'u r+ai chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5376: mthing nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can /
NK053('i)001:5377: sngon tshe dpal chen pos ru tra bsgral ba' dus su ye shes bsnyen cing bsgrubs //
NK053('i)001:5378: sngon gyi thugs dam da lta rnal 'byor sgrub pa po bdag dang gcig /
NK053('i)001:5379: gnas dur khrod chen po'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK053('i)001:5380: gdan bam chung mchog phran bsnol ba'i gdan steng du //
NK053('i)001:5381: tshul dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5382: badz+ra koo'u r+ai ha sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5384: ma mo chen mo me 'bar ma //
NK053('i)001:5385: lhor rkun mo tso'u r+ai chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5386: ser nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK053('i)001:5387: sngon tshe sngon gyi dur khrod mchog phran dgyes shing badz+ra tso'u r+au ha sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5389: ma mo chen mo me 'bar ma //
NK053('i)001:5390: nub tu rmongs mo pra mo chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5391: dmar nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK053('i)001:5392: sngon tshe sngon gyi dur khrod mchog phran dgyes shing
NK053('i)001:5393: badz+ra pra mo he ha sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra
NK053('i)001:5395: ma mo chen mo me 'bar ma //
NK053('i)001:5396: byang du thal byed be ta chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5397: mthing nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK053('i)001:5398: sngon tshe sngon gyi dur khrod mchog phran dgyes shing
