NK053('i)001:5399: badz+ra be ta li ha sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra
NK053('i)001:5401: ma mo chen mo me 'bar ma //
NK053('i)001:5402: shar lho sbos mo puk+ka chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5403: dmar ser 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK053('i)001:5405: badz+ra puk+ka si ha sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5407: ma mo chen mo me 'bar ma //
NK053('i)001:5408: lho nub 'tshogs ma gasma chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5409: ljang ser 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK053('i)001:5411: badz+ra g+hasma r+ai ha sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5413: ma mo chen mo me 'bar ma //
NK053('i)001:5414: nub byang rmongs mo sma sha chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5415: mthing nag 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK053('i)001:5417: badz+ra sma sha n+ai ha sa ha ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5419: ma mo chen mo me 'bar ma //
NK053('i)001:5420: byang shar gtum mo tsan+d+ha chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5421: ser skya 'bar ba'i ral pa can //
NK053('i)001:5423: badz+ra tsan+d+ha l+ai ha sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5425: b+han+d+ha brgyad dbus kyi b+han+d+ha la rim pas bskor te /
NK053('i)001:5427: de nas rtsa ba la dgu las ma smos kyang /
NK053('i)001:5428: drug pa sid+ha ma brgyad dgod pa /
NK053('i)001:5429: don gyis phra men ma brgyad kyang tshal du re re la snying po bris pa'am /
NK053('i)001:5430: yang na sku tsaka li gang rung ba dgod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5431: lus lha la mgo brnyan du byung bas phra men no //
NK053('i)001:5433: phra men chen mo rab 'bar ma //
NK053('i)001:5434: sid+ha chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5435: gser mdog chen mo seng mo'i mgo //
NK053('i)001:5437: sngon tshe ye shes bsnyen cing bsgrubs //
NK053('i)001:5438: sngon gyi thugs dam bdag dang gcig /
NK053('i)001:5440: zhing rkyang bkram pa'i gdan steng du //
NK053('i)001:5441: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5442: badz+ra sed+ha mu ka he sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5444: phra men chen mo rab 'bar ma //
NK053('i)001:5445: b+y+aa g+h+ri chen mo gshegs dmar mo chen mo stag gi mgo //
NK053('i)001:5448: badz+ra b+h+aa g+h+ri mu ka he sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5450: phra men chen mo rab 'bar ma //
NK053('i)001:5451: sri la chen mo dmar nag chen mo wa yi mgo //
NK053('i)001:5454: badz+ra sri la mu ka he sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5456: phra men chen mo rab shwa na chen mo mthing nag chen mo spyang mo'i mgo //
NK053('i)001:5459: badz+ra shwa na mu ka he sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5461: phra men chen mo rab kri ta chen mo dkar ser chen mo bya rgod mgo //
NK053('i)001:5464: badz+ra kri ta mu ka he sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5466: phra men chen mo rab kang ka chen mo dmar mo chen mo dur bya'i mgo //
NK053('i)001:5469: badz+ra kang ka mu ka he sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5471: phra men chen mo rab khwa khwa chen mo nag mo chen mo bya rog nub byang /
NK053('i)001:5474: badz+ra khwa khwa mu ka he sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5476: phra men chen mo rab 'bar ma //
NK053('i)001:5477: hu lu chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5478: sna tshogs mdog la 'ug pa'i mgo //
NK053('i)001:5479: yang na mthing byang shar du dgod /
NK053('i)001:5481: badz+ra hu lu mu ka he sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5484: de nas tshal bu bzhi la sgo ma bzhi'i snying po bris pa dgod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5486: bskal byed rdo rje ang+ku sha /
NK053('i)001:5487: rta gdong chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5488: dkar 'gugs byed chen mo lcags kyu can //
NK053('i)001:5489: sngon tshe ye shes bsnyen cing bsgrub //
NK053('i)001:5490: sngon gyi thugs dam bdag dang gcig /
NK053('i)001:5491: dur khrod chen po'i shar sgo ru //
NK053('i)001:5492: zhing rkyang sbram pa'i gdan steng du //
NK053('i)001:5493: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5494: badz+ra +aar+ya te dza te nga dzahs ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5496: bskul ba'i rdo rje p+aa sha h'u //
NK053('i)001:5497: phag gdong chen mo gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5499: 'chings byed chen mo zhags pa ma //
NK053('i)001:5500: sngon tshe sngon gyi dur khrod chen po'i lho sgo ru //
NK053('i)001:5501: zhing rkyang dgyes shing badz+ra a mu khe h'u sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5503: bskul ba'i rdo rje s+pho ta bam //
NK053('i)001:5504: seng gdong chen mo bsdam byed dmar mo lcags sgrog can //
NK053('i)001:5505: sngon tshe sngon gyi dur khrod chen po'i nub sgo ru //
NK053('i)001:5506: zhing rkyang dgyes shing badz+ra lo ka bam sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5508: bskul ba'i rdo rje gan+d+he hoh /
NK053('i)001:5510: thal byed chen mo dril 'khrol dgyes //
NK053('i)001:5511: sngon tshe sngon gyi dur khrod chen po'i byang sgo ru //
NK053('i)001:5512: zhing rkyang dgyes shing badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba tu hoh sa ma ya tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:5514: brgyad pa dbang mo dgod pa /
NK053('i)001:5516: skyer pa'i rtsangs nyi shu rtsa brgyad la dbang phyug ma'i snying po bris la dgod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5518: mi srin g.yag dang tshangs ma sbrul //
NK053('i)001:5519: khro mo gzigs dang khyab 'jug sre //
NK053('i)001:5520: gzhon nu pha wang 'phar ma dred //
NK053('i)001:5521: nag mo khu gdong lcags kyu ma //
NK053('i)001:5522: sngon tshe dpal chen po'i spyan snga ru /
NK053('i)001:5524: dam tshig tshul bzhin rjes su dgongs nas /
NK053('i)001:5526: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas 'dir //
NK053('i)001:5527: dar gyi rlod stan gdan zhing skam po'i steng du //
NK053('i)001:5528: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5531: dmar mo dom dang chu srin bum //
NK053('i)001:5532: zhi ba sdig dang be con khra //
NK053('i)001:5533: srin mo wa dang za byed seng //
NK053('i)001:5534: ser mo ra gdang zhags pa ma //
NK053('i)001:5535: sngon tshe sogs tshig rkang lnga 'gre /
NK053('i)001:5538: dga' byed rgod dang khrag 'thung rta //
NK053('i)001:5539: gcig spyod lding dang yid 'phrog khyi //
NK053('i)001:5540: grub pa shud dang rlung mo sha /
NK053('i)001:5541: bum sna dmar mo lcags sgrog ma //
NK053('i)001:5545: gsod byed spang dang mi mo skyin //
NK053('i)001:5546: ljang ser phag dang dmar mo khwa //
NK053('i)001:5547: sna chen glang dang klu mo sbrul //
NK053('i)001:5548: gsus 'dzin ljang nag dril chen skeg /
NK053('i)001:5553: dgu pa gsang ba'i ma mo dgod pa /
NK053('i)001:5554: de nas phyogs bzhir ban+d+ha'i bzed phor bzhi dgram zhing /
NK053('i)001:5556: dkar mo nyi ma'i mig gcig ma //
NK053('i)001:5557: ser mo glog gi bang can ma //
NK053('i)001:5558: sngon mo glog gi thul can ma //
NK053('i)001:5559: sti ra nag mo klu 'dul ma //
NK053('i)001:5560: gsang ba'i ma mo mched bzhi yang //
NK053('i)001:5561: sngon tshe dam tshig dur khrod dar gyi dgyes shing de ltar lha dgod pa yang /
NK053('i)001:5562: rtsa ba'i lha yang dag grub pa /
NK053('i)001:5563: dpal chen po gcig pu nyid la /
NK053('i)001:5564: de'i yon tan du byung bas /
NK053('i)001:5565: lha mo brgyad du bstan la /
NK053('i)001:5567: kham phor ri mo bris pa dgu //
NK053('i)001:5569: sid+ha man gzhan ma rnams skyobs kyi lha'am /
NK053('i)001:5570: mgron gyi lhar shes par bya /
NK053('i)001:5572: de la mar me dgod 3par bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:5573: snang ba'i 'od dang chas par dgram //
NK053('i)001:5575: mar me dgod pa la yang don bdun te /
NK053('i)001:5582: bdun pa ye shes dang sbyar te dgod par bstan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:5583: dang po snod bstan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5584: de yang mar me ji ltar bya zhe na /
NK053('i)001:5585: 'jig rten pa dag lta ba dman pa theg pa 'og ma ltar ma yin /
NK053('i)001:5588: thod tshal skyon med pa zla gam gyi dbyibs su byas la /
NK053('i)001:5589: ri mo pad+ma bris pa'i ze'u 'bru 'byon dmar las byas pa'i mtho bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:5592: gong ltar 'bras bu lnga bsgral ba'i tshil bu dang /
NK053('i)001:5598: mar dkar la sbyar bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:5601: yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje'i shar bu skam pa la /
NK053('i)001:5602: yum gyi pad+ma'i ze'u 'bru dkris te skam la /
NK053('i)001:5603: de la dur khrod kyi ras kyis dkris pas bya'o //
NK053('i)001:5605: de la rdul mo ngar lcags dang rdo tsa mkhar gong las byung ba'i mes bsgron la /
NK053('i)001:5606: de yang spyi dang khyad par du sbyar na /
NK053('i)001:5611: sdong bu ni chos kyi sku /
NK053('i)001:5612: me ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku //
NK053('i)001:5614: snod bcud ril sku gsung lhun gyis grub pa'i rtags so //
NK053('i)001:5616: khyad par gyi dbang du sbyar na /
NK053('i)001:5617: kong bu ni yum gyi mkha' /
NK053('i)001:5618: sdong bu ni yab kyi mkha' /
NK053('i)001:5619: mar yab yum gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems las ye shes kyi 'od zer byung nas /
NK053('i)001:5620: 'khor ba dang ngan song thams cad kyi ma rig pa'i mun pa sel zhing /
NK053('i)001:5621: ye shes kyi snang ba bskyed pa'i rtags so //
NK053('i)001:5623: de la ye shes su sbyar na /
NK053('i)001:5624: rgyu byang chub kyi sems rnam par shes pa'i tshogs dgu dang /
NK053('i)001:5625: 'bras bu ye shes chen po dgur sbyar te dgod pa yang /
NK053('i)001:5626: he ru ka'i gal po las /
NK053('i)001:5627: skye med chos kyi dbyings nyid las //
NK053('i)001:5628: bde skyid dga' ldan lha yul du'am //
NK053('i)001:5629: lcang lo can gyi pho brang du //
NK053('i)001:5630: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas khang //
NK053('i)001:5632: ma tram bsgral ba'i khog pa las //
NK053('i)001:5634: ye shes dgu pa'i snang ba gsal //
NK053('i)001:5635: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyis //
NK053('i)001:5636: snod bcud ye shes kun la khyab //
NK053('i)001:5637: khyab pa'i ye shes chen po yis //
NK053('i)001:5638: 'khor ba dang ni byang chub kun //
NK053('i)001:5639: mi gnas pa yi tshul gyis ni //
NK053('i)001:5640: thugs rje dbus kyi gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:5641: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5642: dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:5643: gti mug 'thib pa'i mun rum bsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:5644: me long lta bu'i ye shes kyis //
NK053('i)001:5645: skye med byang chub sems nyid 'di //
NK053('i)001:5646: sku gsung thugs su nges par rtogs //
NK053('i)001:5647: gnyis su med pa'i tshul gyis ni //
NK053('i)001:5648: rtogs pa chen po dung gi gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:5650: dgyes shing brtan dgyes shing zhe sdang 'bar ba'i mun pa bsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:5651: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis //
NK053('i)001:5652: snod bcud kun gyi 'jig rten dang //
NK053('i)001:5653: 'khor ba dang ni byang chub kun //
NK053('i)001:5654: thams cad mnyam pa nyid du rtogs //
NK053('i)001:5655: mi dmigs pa yi tshul gyis ni //
NK053('i)001:5656: rgyas pa chen po gser gyi gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:5658: dgyes shing dgyes shing nga rgyal 'bar ba'i mun pa bsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:5659: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK053('i)001:5660: rang dang spyi yi mtshan nyid rnams //
NK053('i)001:5661: ma 'dres so sor gsal bar rtogs //
NK053('i)001:5662: gnas pa chen po tshul gyis ni //
NK053('i)001:5663: dbang sdud chen po byi ru'i gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:5665: dgyes shing dgyes shing 'dod chags zhen pa'i mun pa bsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:5666: bya ba nan tan ye shes kyis //
NK053('i)001:5667: bdag don sku gsum lhun gyis grub //
NK053('i)001:5668: gzhan don 'og min gnas su sbyor //
NK053('i)001:5669: ci yang ma yin tshul gyis ni //
NK053('i)001:5670: mthar phyin chen po g.yu yi gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:5672: dgyes shing brtan dgyes shing phrag dog 'bar ba'i mun pa bsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:5673: stong pa nyid kyi ye shes kyis //
NK053('i)001:5674: stod bcud kun gyi 'jig brten dang //
NK053('i)001:5675: 'khor ba dang ni byang chub kun //
NK053('i)001:5676: thams cad stong nyid bdag yod de //
NK053('i)001:5677: stong pa nyid kyi tshul gyis ni //
NK053('i)001:5678: byams pa chen po'i shel gyi gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:5679: dgyes shis brtan dgyes shing 'khor ba'i mun nag chen po bsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:5680: 'da' dka' thugs kyi ye shes kyis //
NK053('i)001:5681: rtogs pas mnyam pa nyid du bzhag /
NK053('i)001:5682: ting 'dzin gyis ni sku gsum rdzogs //
NK053('i)001:5683: mi 'da' ba yi tshul gyis ni //
NK053('i)001:5684: snying rje chen po'i rin chen gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:5686: ting 'dzin rmongs pa'i mun nag bsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:5687: dbyings su sgrol ba'i ye shes kyis //
NK053('i)001:5689: sku gsung thugs su lhun gyis sgrol //
NK053('i)001:5690: pha rol phyin pa'i tshul gyis ni //
NK053('i)001:5691: dga' ba chen po bswe yi gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:5692: dgyes shing dgyes shing ma rtogs so sor 'dzin pa'i mun pa bsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:5693: klong du gyur pa'i ye shes kyis //
NK053('i)001:5694: snod kyi 'jig rten dur khrod gzhal yas khang //
NK053('i)001:5695: bcud kyi 'jig rten khrag 'thung phyag rgya'i tshogs //
NK053('i)001:5696: ye shes lhun gyis grub pa'i tshul gyis ni //
NK053('i)001:5697: btang snyoms chen po rdo rje'i gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:5698: dgyes shing brtan dgyes shing phyin ci log gi mun pa bsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:5699: bdag cag skal ldan rigs kyi bu //
NK053('i)001:5700: longs spyod dur khrod rdzas la brten //
NK053('i)001:5701: kong bu yum gyi gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:5702: sdong bu rdo rje zhing chen ras //
NK053('i)001:5703: 'bras bu lnga yi mar khu rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK053('i)001:5704: ye shes dgu yi mar me 'od zer 'phro //
NK053('i)001:5705: skal ldan can gyis 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK053('i)001:5707: so so'i gnas su dgod do //
NK053('i)001:5708: de yan chad du gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bstan pa ste /
NK053('i)001:5709: de yang gzugs brnyan sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK053('i)001:5711: zla gam dkyil 'khor yum gyi mkha' //
NK053('i)001:5712: b+han+d+ha bder gshegs sku yi sku //
NK053('i)001:5713: yig 'bru bder gshegs gsung gi gsung //
NK053('i)001:5714: mar me bder gshegs thugs kyi thugs //
NK053('i)001:5717: sku bkod pa ni b+han+d+ha dagu'o //
NK053('i)001:5718: gzugs brnyan gsung gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:5720: ha brgyad h'u dang snying po dagu'o //
NK053('i)001:5721: gzugs brnyan thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du /
NK053('i)001:5723: snang ba'i mar me dgu pa ste ye shes chen po dagu'o //
NK053('i)001:5724: de yang ye shes chen po dgu ni /
NK053('i)001:5725: chos nyid la ye shes kyis zin pa zhes bya ste /
NK053('i)001:5726: gang du yang ma g.yos pa chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes dang /
NK053('i)001:5727: ma 'gags par rang gsal ba me long lta bu'i ye shes dang /
NK053('i)001:5728: gnyis su med par mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK053('i)001:5729: rang rtogs su byung bas so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang /
NK053('i)001:5730: mthar phyin pas bya ba grub pa'i ye shes dang /
NK053('i)001:5731: spros pa med pa'i ngang spyod pas stong pa nyid kyi ye shes dang /
NK053('i)001:5732: bde ba chen po la snyoms par 'jug pas 'da' dka' thugs kyi ye shes dang /
NK053('i)001:5733: thams cad bdag nyid chen por gsal bas klong du gyur pa'i ye shes dang /
NK053('i)001:5734: 'khor ba thams cad ye shes chen por gsal bas dbyings su sgrol ba'i ye shes dang dagu'o //
NK053('i)001:5735: de ltar na gzugs brnyan sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du bstan pa yin no //
NK053('i)001:5736: rdzas 4dgod par bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:5737: rdzas kyis mdzes par 'khor bar bzhag /
NK053('i)001:5743: gong du zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor la rdzas bam mtshan dang ldan pa la bsnyen pa byas nas /
NK053('i)001:5744: zhi ba'i lha dang 'dzab kyis sbyangs pa'i rdzas de /
NK053('i)001:5745: man+dala gyi phyogs bzhir bro bzhis sbyangs la /
NK053('i)001:5746: shar du ngan song gnas sbyangs kyi bro /
NK053('i)001:5747: lhor rgyu drug sgrol ba'i bro /
NK053('i)001:5748: nub tu rta gdong zhal gyi bro /
NK053('i)001:5749: byang du bu mo drug gi bro /
NK053('i)001:5752: snga ma las ni gnas 'gyur te //
NK053('i)001:5754: phung po gdos bcas bem po de //
NK053('i)001:5755: phyogs bzhis bro bzhis sbyong bar bya //
NK053('i)001:5756: ye shes lha dang mkha' 'gro ma //
NK053('i)001:5757: thugs dam bskul zhing thugs dam bskang //
NK053('i)001:5759: de nas byang shar mtshams su rdzas su dgram ste /
NK053('i)001:5761: bshig nas dpal khrag 'thung gi lha rnams kyi rdzas su dgram pa yang /
NK053('i)001:5762: rgyud las 'di skad du byung ste /
NK053('i)001:5763: ro yi bsha' thabs rgyab nas bsha' //
NK053('i)001:5764: sog sprag nas sbug gu thung ngu gcig gdab /
NK053('i)001:5765: sbug gu thung ngu nas rkang pa g.yas pa'i rting par thig gcig /
NK053('i)001:5767: lag pa g.yas g.yon la thig re re btab la /
NK053('i)001:5768: khrag 'thung lha tshogs rdzas su ste //
NK053('i)001:5769: glo snying dpal chen yab yum gyi //
NK053('i)001:5770: rdzas mig bud+d+ha'i dang rna ba rat+na'i sna pad+ma'i dang lce //
NK053('i)001:5771: karma'i rigs bzhi khrag 'thung yab yum rdzas //
NK053('i)001:5772: mchin pa ko'u r+ai mkhal ma tso'u r+ai mtsher pa pra mo snod //
NK053('i)001:5773: be ta 'bras bu puk+ka s+ai mtshan ma gasma sog pa sma sha dpyi //
NK053('i)001:5774: tsan d+ha khro mo ko'u r+ai brgyad kyi rdzas //
NK053('i)001:5777: snying dpal chen dang bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga //
NK053('i)001:5779: dpung pa g.yas tso'u r+ai g.yon pra mo bzhag sha be ta dang //
NK053('i)001:5780: rgyu puk+ka mchin gasma mgo sha sma sha gsang dbang tsan d+ha rnams //
NK053('i)001:5781: rtsa ba'i lha dgu'i rdzas su bzhag /
NK053('i)001:5783: shes par byas la dgod do //
NK053('i)001:5785: go ro tsa na sed+ha rgyus pa b+y+aa g+h+ri dang //
NK053('i)001:5786: rkang sri la dang tshil bu shwa na sha krit+ta
NK053('i)001:5787: dang khrag kang+ka srog rtsa kha khwa mkhris pa hu
NK053('i)001:5789: mu ka phra men brgyad kyi rdzas //
NK053('i)001:5790: yan lag dbar thar rkang lag sor mo med pa'i mthil ldum bzhi rnams ni //
NK053('i)001:5791: ye shes sgo ma bzhi yi rdzas //
NK053('i)001:5792: sgal tshigs phrugs su bsdebs pa ni //
NK053('i)001:5793: dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad kyi rdzas //
NK053('i)001:5794: ne'u tsheg che phra sbrag pa ni //
NK053('i)001:5795: ye shes khro bo bcu yi rdzas //
NK053('i)001:5796: sha khrag rus pa rkang dang tshil //
NK053('i)001:5797: mkha' 'gro la sogs kun gyi rdzas //
NK053('i)001:5799: rang rang so so'i gnas su dgod /
NK053('i)001:5801: 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad dam yang na le'u tshe brgyad la ko'u r+ai ma brgyad kyi /
NK053('i)001:5802: bar khyams su sed+ha ma brgyad kyi /
NK053('i)001:5804: lcags ri nag po la sgal rtsibs bcas /
NK053('i)001:5806: lcang lor bcas pa'i b+han+d+hara bcad //
NK053('i)001:5807: mtshan brtags byas pa'i b+han+d+ha de //
NK053('i)001:5808: dpal chen bzhugs pa'i rten yang yin //
NK053('i)001:5810: de la dpal chen po yab yum gyi lha sku'am snying po bris la dbus su bzhag pa'am /
NK053('i)001:5811: dngos grub sgrub pa'i snod kyang yin //
NK053('i)001:5813: de'i nang du blugs bya la yang go ro tsa na klad pa dri chen dang //
NK053('i)001:5814: snying ngam srog rtsa'i khrag dang ni //
NK053('i)001:5815: m+aam sa mkhris pa dri chu dang //
NK053('i)001:5816: so dang dbang po sna lnga dang //
NK053('i)001:5817: de rnams cha ni mnyam pa dang //
NK053('i)001:5818: tshil chen bzhu ba dang sbyar nas //
NK053('i)001:5819: snying po lnga dang sbyar ba yi //
NK053('i)001:5820: b+han+d+ha gang ni dngos grub rdzas //
NK053('i)001:5822: zla gam dkar po la bzhag par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:5824: b+han+d+ha mtshan dang ldan pa'i nang du tshal bu re
NK053('i)001:5825: re la sgrub po du yod kyi gsang mtshan dang
NK053('i)001:5826: / dngos grub kyi gsol byang rdo rje che ge la dngos grub gsol /
NK053('i)001:5830: shar sgor dngos grub gsol byang dang //
NK053('i)001:5831: rdo rje dang ni dril bu dang //
NK053('i)001:5832: bdud rtsi'i bum pa dngos grub rdzas //
NK053('i)001:5833: de bzhin dbang gi bum pa bzhag /
NK053('i)001:5835: dbang bskur ba'i bum pa gong du sta gon la gnas par byas pa'i zhi ba'i bum pa'am /
NK053('i)001:5836: yang na khro bo'i lha la bum pa bcas pa dbus su bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:5838: rang byung gi ni bum pa de //
NK053('i)001:5839: byin brlabs rdzas dang kha rgyan can //
NK053('i)001:5840: des ni dbang bskur rtag tu bya //
NK053('i)001:5842: byin gyis brlabs la dal gyi dbus su bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:5843: las kyi bum pa yang dkyil 'khor gyi grwa la bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:5844: dkyil 'khor de'i phyogs bzhir mchog phur bzhi /
NK053('i)001:5846: steng 'og tu seng ldeng gi phur pa gnyis te bcu /
NK053('i)001:5847: khro bo bcur mnga' gsol dgod de /
NK053('i)001:5848: ba su ta'i zhags pas bskor ro //
NK053('i)001:5850: ba su ta yi rgyu zhags kyis //
NK053('i)001:5851: thig gdab man+dala bskor ba dang /
NK053('i)001:5852: byi na ya ga bcings pa'i rdzas //
NK053('i)001:5855: h'u dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:5856: thugs rje'i thabs dang ldan pa'i rgyu zhags kyis //
NK053('i)001:5857: rgyu drug 'khor ba'i dbyings su drangs pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:5858: thabs kyi zhags pa rgyu phreng phyag rgyar drangs //
NK053('i)001:5861: shun chen zhing gi g.yang gzhi ni //
NK053('i)001:5862: bla brer bres dang rnal 'byor chas //
NK053('i)001:5864: zhing gi g.yang gzhi la rak+ta'i thig le lha grangs bzhin byas la /
NK053('i)001:5868: gtso 'khor dgu ma sogs skabs su gang bab bya /
NK053('i)001:5869: dkyil 'khor gyi bla brer bres pa yang /
NK053('i)001:5871: srid pa gsum gyi gdug pa kun bsgral te //
NK053('i)001:5872: shes rab zab mo yum gyi mkha' dbyings su //
NK053('i)001:5873: mtha' dang dbus med dkyil 'khor rang bzhin te //
NK053('i)001:5874: phyi dang nang med lhun gyis grub pa'i rdzas //
NK053('i)001:5875: yid bzhin longs spyod 'dod dgu 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK053('i)001:5876: ye shes chen po bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags //
NK053('i)001:5877: phrag dog ma spangs gnas dag /
NK053('i)001:5879: dkyil 'khor chen po'i bla brer dgram par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:5881: gzhan yang dkyil gyi phyi rol du /
NK053('i)001:5888: rigs lnga'i mtshon cha rnam pa lnga la sogs kyang bskor te bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:5889: khyad par du dri chab kyi cha snod du bram ze mo'i b+han+d+hara sbyar la bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:5891: bla rkang gnyis dang rje ngar rkang //
NK053('i)001:5892: dung chen 'bud pa'i gling bu bya //
NK053('i)001:5893: dpung pa'i rkang rus gnyis po la //
NK053('i)001:5894: rak+ta sbreng ba'i gzar bu bya //
NK053('i)001:5896: byang shar mtshams su bar chad byed pa'i nyams len bzlog pa dang /
NK053('i)001:5898: b+han+d+ha mtshan ngan la ri rab gling phran bcu gnyis
NK053('i)001:5899: dang bcas par bris pa'i nang du dgra bgegs gang
NK053('i)001:5900: la bya ba'i gzugs ling+ga bris la gzhug pa dang
NK053('i)001:5903: ya mkhal ma mkhal gnyis po de /
NK053('i)001:5904: kha tham bya ba'i rdas kyang yin //
NK053('i)001:5905: de dang sog pa ma mod la //
NK053('i)001:5908: ya ma dam sri mnan pa'i rdzas //
NK053('i)001:5910: gnyis pa mchod rdzas dgram pa /
NK053('i)001:5911: de nas mchod rdzas dgram pa ni /
NK053('i)001:5917: khyad par du zlog chung dpal bshos zla gam la
NK053('i)001:5918: rak+ta'i thig le dgu btab pa re re drang ngo
NK053('i)001:5919: // d+aa ma ru la sogs pa'i rnga dung sil snyan sgra dang /
NK053('i)001:5920: dam rdzas zhal zas sna tshogs la sogs pa'i gtor ma /
NK053('i)001:5921: kha sprin chen zhal kheb snying shun dang bcas pa'i gcig drang ngo //
NK053('i)001:5922: bdud rtsi a mri ta stsal ba'i snod dang /
NK053('i)001:5923: 'bras bu lnga bsgral ba'i rak+ta'i snod gang dang /
NK053('i)001:5924: chang phud dza gad dang tshe la sogs pa'i 'byor
NK053('i)001:5925: bshams tshogs la sogs pa'i rdzas kyis mdzes par bskor
NK053('i)001:5927: mig gi rten yang bzhag par 5bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:5928: mig gi rten yang mngon par bzhag /
NK053('i)001:5930: dpal he ru la gtso bo /
NK053('i)001:5931: 'khor lha mo'i tshogs kyis bskor ba'i sku gzugs lugs ma'am /
NK053('i)001:5932: bris sku yang nub phyogs su bzhag ste /
NK053('i)001:5933: lha gshegs pa'i rten dang mtshan mar brtag pa'i phyi bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:5934: thabs dang shes rab 'brel bas sgrub phyir na /
NK053('i)001:5941: phal skad du chung ma zhes kyang bya /
NK053('i)001:5942: mtshan dang yon tan ldan pa yang //
NK053('i)001:5943: skye ba med pa'i yum du mnga' gsol to //
NK053('i)001:5944: rnal 'byor pa'i g.yon du bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:5946: ting 'dzin ye shes gsal ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:5947: mig gi rten yang mngon par bri //
NK053('i)001:5948: de la rten bcas bris 'bur gang rung /
NK053('i)001:5950: 'dod chags ye shes gsal ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:5951: shes rab ma mig gi rten yang g.yon du bzhag /
NK053('i)001:5953: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bris te /
NK053('i)001:5954: lha dang mar me rdzas bkod la /
NK053('i)001:5956: mig gi mthong yul rten la mngon par bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:5959: 4 / thams cad tshul bzhin byin gyis brlabs pa'i phrin las la lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:5960: mnyam pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis chos thams
NK053('i)001:5961: cad gnyis su med par byin gyis brlabs pa dang
NK053('i)001:5962: / dbang sgyur thabs kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis gnas byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:5963: shes rab dang snying rje'i ting nge 'dzin gyis yum
NK053('i)001:5964: dang rgyu dang sgrub rdzas gsum byin gyis brlabs pa
NK053('i)001:5965: dang / phyag rgya chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrub pa po byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:5966: tshogs chen rdzogs pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrub rdzas dang yo byad byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK053('i)001:5967: de la 1mnyam pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis
NK053('i)001:5968: chos thams cad gnyis su med par byin gyis brlabs
NK053('i)001:5970: mi dmigs chos la blo brtan zhing //
NK053('i)001:5971: ye shes can gyi byin stobs kyis //
NK053('i)001:5973: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos ril ni sems su snang la /
NK053('i)001:5974: sems gang du'ang ma g.yos pa la sems nyid nam mkha' dwangs pa ltar sa le /
NK053('i)001:5978: gang gis kyang ma bslad par bzhag nas gsal la rtog pa med par ma yengs par 'dug na /
NK053('i)001:5979: chos thams cad kyi chos nyid /
NK053('i)001:5980: de bzhin nyid dmigs su med pa'i ting nge 'dzin klong du gyur pa yin te /
NK053('i)001:5981: zhi gnas las su rung bas rnam par mi rtog
NK053('i)001:5982: pa'i don mthil du phebs pas blo brtan zhing 'dug
NK053('i)001:5983: na / thams cad gnyis su med par byin gyis brlabs pa yin no //
NK053('i)001:5984: de ltar chos thams cad mnyam pa nyid las su rung bas /
NK053('i)001:5985: sngar spyad pas ye shes mchog tu gyur pa'i chos nyid can des /
NK053('i)001:5987: chos nyid ci yang ma yin pa las /
NK053('i)001:5988: cir yang snang ba'i cho 'phrul yi ge h'u du gsal bar spro bsdu bya ste rdo rjer gyur /
NK053('i)001:5989: rdo rje las 'od zer spro bsdu byas te 'od kyi gong bur gsal ba las /
NK053('i)001:5994: badz+ra kro t+ai shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:5995: zhi khro gang sgom gyi lha'i snying po brjod pas /
NK053('i)001:5996: zhi ba dpal rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum mam /
NK053('i)001:5997: khro bo dpal chen po yab yum gang rung du bsgom pa'ang /
NK053('i)001:5998: ye shes sgyu ma'i cho 'phrul du gsal bas /
NK053('i)001:5999: ting nge 'dzin gyis goms pa'i mthu byin dang /
NK053('i)001:6000: rang rig ye shes kyi cho 'phrul du mnga' ba'i stobs kyis /
NK053('i)001:6003: yum dang rgyu dang sgrub rdzas dang /
NK053('i)001:6004: yo byad la sogs pa thams cad bskyed rdzogs pa rnam pa gsum ma h+aa /
NK053('i)001:6007: du byin brlabs pa'i phyir na /
NK053('i)001:6008: thams cad tshul bzhin byin gyis brlabs //
NK053('i)001:6010: de yang tshul ji ltar byin gyis brlabs zhe na /
NK053('i)001:6011: dbang 2sgyur thabs kyi ting nge 'dzin gyis gnas byin gyis brlabs pa la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:6012: dang po rig pa dbang sgyur ye shes sprul pa'i ting 'dzin gyis /
NK053('i)001:6013: gnas chos kyi dbyings su byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6014: bdag gi sems kyi cho 'phrul las /
NK053('i)001:6017: bsregs gtor bkrus dag nas stong pa nyid du bsgom pa'o //
NK053('i)001:6018: de la gnyis pa che bas dbang sgyur dregs pa gzir ba'i ting 'dzin gyis /
NK053('i)001:6019: thugs rje'i gnas khams gsum gyi sems can byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6020: bdag gtso bo yab yum du bsgom pa'i 'od zer gyi gnas dang /
NK053('i)001:6022: khams gsum gyi sems can la phogs pas las dang nyon mongs pa'i bag chags bsregs sbyangs nas /
NK053('i)001:6023: h'u gis bsdu zhing bdag la bstims pas /
NK053('i)001:6024: gnyis su med par gyur te /
NK053('i)001:6025: ye shes kyi skur gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:6026: gsum pa thabs kyi dbang sgyur 'khor ba bzlog pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK053('i)001:6027: sgrub pa'i gnas dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas khang du byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6030: e yam ram bam kem ram b+h+r+aum rnams 'phros pa las /
NK053('i)001:6031: snyigs ma'i 'byung ba lnga so sor sbyangs te /
NK053('i)001:6032: dwangs ma'i 'byung ba lnga rim brtsegs yum lnga'i mkha' gsal te /
NK053('i)001:6033: e las chos kyi dbyings kyi nam mkha' chos 'byung gru gsum /
NK053('i)001:6034: yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma /
NK053('i)001:6035: de steng yam las rlung gi dal /
NK053('i)001:6039: bam las zhing chen gyi sa gzhi /
NK053('i)001:6041: kem las kem rus kyi ri rab /
NK053('i)001:6042: ram las ye shes kyi me /
NK053('i)001:6044: b+h+r+aum las gzhal yas khang ni /
NK053('i)001:6045: de'i steng du ye shes lnga las grub pa'i phyogs
NK053('i)001:6046: bzhi dkar ser dmar ljang dbus mthing ye shes lnga
NK053('i)001:6047: ldan gzhal yas khang zla gam dbang gi dkyil 'khor
NK053('i)001:6048: snga ma dang dbyer med par gyur pa'o //
NK053('i)001:6049: de nas shes rab 3dang snying rje'i ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK053('i)001:6052: sgrub rdzas byin gyis brlabs pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:6053: sgrub 1 rdzas kham phor dang mar me byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6054: bdag gi thugs ka'am gsang gnas nas /
NK053('i)001:6058: sgo ma'i rdzas lcags phur ram dpal thar bzhi la /
NK053('i)001:6060: kham phor rnams la thim pa las /
NK053('i)001:6061: yig 'bru h'u ha he phata so sor gsal ba las /
NK053('i)001:6062: h'u bzhis h'u dang pos 'od zer spro bsdu /
NK053('i)001:6063: h'u gnyis pas gsung yig 'brur gyur /
NK053('i)001:6064: h'u gsum pas 'od spro bsdus thugs phyag 'tshal du gyur /
NK053('i)001:6065: h'u bzhi pas sku yongs rdzogs he ru ka'i skur bskyed /
NK053('i)001:6067: koo seng sgo ma yongs rdzogs bskyed /
NK053('i)001:6068: sku gsung thugs su dbang bskur ba re re dang bcas par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:6069: de la ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing bstim pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6070: bzhugs su gsol ba yan chad bya ste /
NK053('i)001:6072: sgrub rdzas bam la brten te byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6073: gong 'og gi man ngag las shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:6074: rgyu 2dang yum byin brlabs pa yang /
NK053('i)001:6076: rgyu bsgral ba'i skabs nas 'byung ba bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:6077: de nas 4phyag rgya chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrub po byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6079: dang po tshogs nas sngar ma 'dres pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6081: gong du sta gon gyi skabs su bsre bsnan bya ba bstan pa bzhin du bya ste /
NK053('i)001:6084: mtha' mar dbang bskur ba man chad du /
NK053('i)001:6085: rdo rje slob dpon phyag rgya chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gsal ba la ma g.yengs pa de /
NK053('i)001:6086: sgrub pa po rnams rang rang gi yi dam gyi lhar byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6087: dbang bskur sgrub pa 'i don nam khyed ka kho na bya'o //
NK053('i)001:6088: de yang sgrub pa po rnams dkyil 'khor du 'jug par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:6091: byin gyis brlab tu gsol ba /
NK053('i)001:6101: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK053('i)001:6102: ma tram bsgral ba'i khog pa la //
NK053('i)001:6103: smug nag zla gam gzhal yas shar //
NK053('i)001:6104: phrin las rnam bzhi rdzogs mdzad pa'i //
NK053('i)001:6105: shar lho nub byang phyogs bzhi nas //
NK053('i)001:6106: ye shes chen po sgo phyes shig /
NK053('i)001:6109: skye med gdod nas dag pa'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK053('i)001:6110: ye shes rang snang 'od kyi thugs rjer shar //
NK053('i)001:6111: ye shes thabs la mkhas pa'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK053('i)001:6112: gar gyi dbang phyug chen por byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK053('i)001:6115: gsang sngags yang dag zab mo'i zhing //
NK053('i)001:6116: zhi khro'i tshogs chen dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:6117: lha dang slob dpon blo ldan la //
NK053('i)001:6118: brda' dang gar gyis phyag bgyid do //
NK053('i)001:6120: gong du brjod pa'i phyag 'tshal ba de yang brjod /
NK053('i)001:6122: rdo rje slob dpon dang mched dang lcam dral la hoh /
NK053('i)001:6123: mkha' 'gro ma tshogs rdo rje dam can la hoh /
NK053('i)001:6125: sngon dus su mar me mdzad kyis brkyang phyag mdzad pa bzhin 'dir rnal 'byor pas kyang bya zhing /
NK053('i)001:6126: rang rang gi lha dang snying po dang gsang mtshan
NK053('i)001:6127: bla mas gnang ba dang gsum bla ma la dbul
NK053('i)001:6129: rnal 'byor pa so sor gsang mtshan las byung ba de rnams /
NK053('i)001:6130: rdo rje'i gral du dgod par gnang la /
NK053('i)001:6131: yid dam gyi lha sgom snying po bzlas par gnang //
NK053('i)001:6135: bka' gsang rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:6136: sgrub po skal ldan dbang phyug rgyal ba'i sras //
NK053('i)001:6137: lha dang slob dpon mi gnyis 'dun pas me tog 'bul lags na //
NK053('i)001:6138: bla med sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub gsol //
NK053('i)001:6141: hoh mi gnas dpal chen rdo rje la //
NK053('i)001:6142: ji ltar bsnyen cing bsgrub pa ltar //
NK053('i)001:6143: rdo rje'i rigs mchog bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:6144: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:6145: hoh mi gnas rdo rje mkha' 'gro ma //
NK053('i)001:6146: ji ltar bsnyen cing bsgrubs pa ltar //
NK053('i)001:6147: rdo rje mkha' 'gro'i dngos grub bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:6148: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:6150: de nas 7rgyan gzungs bsdeb pa'i phrin las bya ste /
NK053('i)001:6151: slob ma kun la bla ma rdo rje slob dpon gyis /
NK053('i)001:6152: bdud rtsi blangs la sku gsung thugs kyi dbang sbyin pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6153: zhi ba'i dus na zhi ba'i rgyan rtags kyis mtshan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6154: khro bo'i dus na khro bo'i rgyan dang rtags kyis mtshan pa kun /
NK053('i)001:6155: 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin skabs 'dir yang blangs la bya'o //
NK053('i)001:6156: de nas 8mched pho mo thabs shes spel mar bzhugs la dam bca' ba /
NK053('i)001:6157: slob dpon gyis 'di skad ces basgo'o //
NK053('i)001:6159: chos nyid don dam pa 'du 'bral med pa'i gzungs thag la //
NK053('i)001:6160: rig pa srog gis bsdus pa'i lu gu rgyud //
NK053('i)001:6161: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:6162: skye ba ji srid bar du ma btang zhig /
NK053('i)001:6163: ngas kyang de ltar bsgom gyis /
NK053('i)001:6164: slob ma khyed kyis nam sku gsung thugs kyi dngos
NK053('i)001:6165: grub ma thob kyi bar du ma btang shig pa'o
NK053('i)001:6166: // de la rdo rje'i mched rnams kyis kyang dam bca' ba ni /
NK053('i)001:6168: skye ba ji srid par du mi btang ngo //
NK053('i)001:6170: nam sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub ma thob kyi bar du mi btang bar dam bca' 'o //
NK053('i)001:6171: de nas 9spos chen gyi dud pa btang ste byin dbab pa /
NK053('i)001:6174: nam mkha' mtha' dang mnyam pa'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK053('i)001:6175: rnal 'byor dbang phyug rigs kyi yum dang bcas //
NK053('i)001:6176: rgyal ba 'khor bcas srung ma dam tshig can //
NK053('i)001:6177: mchod gnas bla ma rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:6178: bdag cag rnams ni sems can dman pa la //
NK053('i)001:6179: gnyen bshes mthu dpung gzhan na ma mchis na //
NK053('i)001:6180: bde bar gshegs pa'i thugs rje chen po chu rgyun ltar la dbri ste dma' ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6181: bskol ste gang nas lud pa lta bu /
NK053('i)001:6183: gdul bya 'dul ba'i dus las mi 'da' thugs rje dam tshig can //
NK053('i)001:6184: skyabs las mi g.yel yal gam sngon gyi dam bca' gcig tu dgongs //
NK053('i)001:6185: ye shes rgyal ba'i rlabs las ma g.yos kyang //
NK053('i)001:6186: dam tshig sems nyid rab tu mngon rtogs shing //
NK053('i)001:6187: byin rlabs chen po dus 'dir stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:6188: a la la hoh b+ha ga w+aan /
NK053('i)001:6189: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:6191: dkyil 'khor gzung ba'i dus la bab //
NK053('i)001:6192: byin chen dbab pa'i dus la bab //
NK053('i)001:6193: dbang chen bskur ba'i dus la bab //
NK053('i)001:6194: mthu rtsal dbyung ba'i dus la bab //
NK053('i)001:6195: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab //
NK053('i)001:6196: byin chen byin phob bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:6197: dbang chen dbang bskur bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:6198: mthu chen mthu stsol bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:6199: rtags dang mtshan ma brtan pa dang //
NK053('i)001:6200: bdag gi bsam pa grub par mdzod //
NK053('i)001:6203: lha mo ko'u ri ma brgyad kyang spyan drang shing byin dbab /
NK053('i)001:6207: rdzas dang yo byad byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6209: spyad pa yo byad kyi rdzas byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6210: mchod pa'i rdzas byin gyis brlab pa dang //
NK053('i)001:6211: stong pa nyid du byin gyis brlabs pa'o /
NK053('i)001:6213: 1 / spyad pa yo byad kyi rdzas la /
NK053('i)001:6217: gsum pa gu gul gyis bdug /
NK053('i)001:6220: drug pa byin brlabs dngos so //
NK053('i)001:6222: de rnams gsol kha bas 'byor bshams su sbyar nas /
NK053('i)001:6224: hoh phyogs bcu mtha' klas pa'i rab 'byams bsam gyis
NK053('i)001:6225: mi khyab pa'i sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams ma lus
NK053('i)001:6226: pa kun nas 'dus shing byon pa'i /
NK053('i)001:6227: rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen po dang /
NK053('i)001:6228: grub pa mched lcam dral rgyal ba rgya mtsho dang bcas /
NK053('i)001:6229: thogs pa mi mnga' bar mkhyen cing gzigs pa thugs
NK053('i)001:6230: rje chen po'i ngang du gyur cing 'gro ba'i mgon
NK053('i)001:6231: skyabs la sta gon du gnas pas /
NK053('i)001:6232: dam tshig gi mchog gsang ba'i sgor zhal gyis bzhes shing /
NK053('i)001:6233: thugs dam gyi dbang gis dkyil 'khor 'dir 'du ba
NK053('i)001:6234: la sogs pa ma lus pa thams cad dgongs su
NK053('i)001:6236: deng dus chen byin gyis brlabs pa 'dir /
NK053('i)001:6237: bdag cag rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis /
NK053('i)001:6238: 'byor ldan tshogs kyi yo byad 'byor ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6240: rgyu bzang spus gtsang bas rigs shing 'thad pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6241: rjes su mthun par dus bzhir 'byung ba'i khams dang mthun pa'i zhal zas rnams /
NK053('i)001:6242: sgyu ma mchis par bsogs nas /
NK053('i)001:6243: srid pa'i longs spyod chos kyi mnga' thang dang mthun par bshams te /
NK053('i)001:6244: 'di tsam zhig nam mkha'i rgyan skar tshogs ltar bkram //
NK053('i)001:6245: sa gzhi'i rgyan rtsi shing dang nags tshal ltar skye zhing 'thon /
NK053('i)001:6246: rgya mtsho'i rgyan rba rlabs ltar 'khyil ba /
NK053('i)001:6247: bar snang gi rgyan sprin ltar gtibs nas /
NK053('i)001:6249: sna tshogs yid kyis sprul nas /
NK053('i)001:6251: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa rig pa 'dzin pa rnams kyi /
NK053('i)001:6252: thugs dam bskang ba'i phyir 'bul zhing mchis na /
NK053('i)001:6253: thugs rjes dgongs nas bzhes su gsol //
NK053('i)001:6256: de la slob dpon gyis lan stsal ba /
NK053('i)001:6257: hoh rnal 'byor pa rnams kyis sgyu med pa'i dad pas ni bsags /
NK053('i)001:6259: phyogs bcu'i rnal 'byor pa'i snyan du ni gdags /
NK053('i)001:6260: dbang phyug chen po rnams kyi spyan gyis ni gzigs /
NK053('i)001:6261: thugs kyis kyang 'thad pas bzhes su gnang /
NK053('i)001:6264: de nas spyad pa yo byad kyi rdzas ril bla'i spyan sngar spungs la /
NK053('i)001:6265: gu gul gyi dud pas bdug /
NK053('i)001:6266: bzhi pa nyungs kar gtor ba /
NK053('i)001:6267: nyungs kar la rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi sngags ring bzlas te gtor nas /
NK053('i)001:6272: drug pa spyad pa yo byad kyi rdzas byin gyis brlab pa dngos /
NK053('i)001:6274: gtor ma'am yo byad kyi snod b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro 'du las /
NK053('i)001:6275: rin po che'i gzhal med khang du dmigs la /
NK053('i)001:6277: ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor du gyur pa'i dbus su yo byad rnams dmigs pa las /
NK053('i)001:6278: bdag dpal chen gi thugs kar nas h'u mthing ka'i
NK053('i)001:6279: 'phro 'dus rnam par rtog pa thams cad bsregs nas
NK053('i)001:6280: stong pa nyid du bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:6282: a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du gyur pa'i dbus su /
NK053('i)001:6283: +aahdamara po las 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros pas snod
NK053('i)001:6284: bcud kyi bdud rtsi thams cad slar zla ba'i steng
NK053('i)001:6285: du bsdus pas bdud rtsir dkar ltem gyis gyur par
NK053('i)001:6287: dkar po'i 'phro 'du las sku lnga ye shes lnga
NK053('i)001:6288: dang tha mi dad pa'i 'dod pa'i yon tan drug
NK053('i)001:6290: gzugs kyi lha mo dkar me long thogs pa ma dang /
NK053('i)001:6291: sgra'i lha mo ser pi wam ma dang /
NK053('i)001:6292: dri'i lha mo ljang spos me ma dang /
NK053('i)001:6293: ro'i lha mo dmar bdud rtsi'i gzhong pa ma dang /
NK053('i)001:6294: reg bya'i lha mo dkar 'khyud tshul can dang /
NK053('i)001:6295: chos dbyings lha mo mthing ga rdo rje dril bu can du gyur par bsam /
NK053('i)001:6296: de nas mang zhing rgya che bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:6297: sngags 'di lan bdun nam nyi shu rtsa gcig tu brjod par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:6299: ba lim ta te dz+wa ba ling ta ba la ba ti gu h+ya sa ma ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:6301: mchod pa'i lha mo re re las kyang dpag tu
NK053('i)001:6302: med pa spel zhing nam mkha'i khams dang mnyam par
NK053('i)001:6304: de nas mchod rdzas byin gyis brlab pa la drug ste /
NK053('i)001:6305: dza gad byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6306: bdud rtsi byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6307: gtor ma byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6308: rak+ta byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6309: dpal bshos byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6312: chang dza gad 1 byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6313: snod kyi steng du yi ge b+h+r+aum gyi 'phro 'du las /
NK053('i)001:6314: rin po che'i gzhal yas khang du gyur par bsam /
NK053('i)001:6316: ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor du gyur pa'i dbus su h'u bsam te de'i 'phro 'du las /
NK053('i)001:6317: dngos po bsregs nas stong par gyur par bsam /
NK053('i)001:6320: bcom ldan 'das mi bskyod pa sa gnon gyi phyag rgya can du gyur par bsam /
NK053('i)001:6321: dang po rdo rje'i phyag rgya bstan pas /
NK053('i)001:6322: phyag rgya las yum dkar sham mo //
NK053('i)001:6323: dbu la rigs lngas brgyan pa zhig byung bas /
NK053('i)001:6324: mi bskyod pa la mchod de /
NK053('i)001:6325: de gnyis rol pa las byang chub sems kyi rang
NK053('i)001:6326: bzhin mu tig dkar po dri ma med pa ltar
NK053('i)001:6327: gyur nas / snod gang zhing 'phel bar gyur to //
NK053('i)001:6328: dza gad de'i dkyil na yang nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su /
NK053('i)001:6330: yum m+aa ma k+ai dkar mo bdud rtsi'i bum pa
NK053('i)001:6331: thogs pa bsam gyis mi khyab pa phyogs bcur 'phros
NK053('i)001:6332: pas / chu thams cad kyi bcud bsdus nas /
NK053('i)001:6333: slar snod kyi nang du gshegs pas yum m+aa ma
NK053('i)001:6334: k+ai mang po byang chub sems la thim par bsam
NK053('i)001:6335: zhing / m+aa ma ki ri ki ri a d+hi tish+tha swa m+aam //
NK053('i)001:6337: pad+ma b+han+d+ha la sogs pa'i snod gang bar dkar lhud lhud gyur par bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:6338: de nas tsho bzhir bcad de /
NK053('i)001:6339: tsho gcig dza gad kyi snod yod tshad du khyab par stsol /
NK053('i)001:6340: tsho gcig yang phud du bcad do //
NK053('i)001:6341: tsho gcig la gu h+ya gsang ba lag gi phyag
NK053('i)001:6342: rgyas mtheb gung srin gsum gyi byang chub sems de
NK053('i)001:6343: m+aam dang bcas par blangs te /
NK053('i)001:6344: lce la rdo rje 'bar ba nas tsam gcig bsams te /
NK053('i)001:6345: lan gsum du dam tshig k+aa ya sid+d+hi /
NK053('i)001:6348: lag pa gnyis pad+ma'i phyag rgya bcas la /
NK053('i)001:6349: de las rgod pa'i khar byas te snod bzung nas btung ngo //
NK053('i)001:6350: de yang rang la nus pa ma rnyed dam mtshan ma ma thon na ni /
NK053('i)001:6351: gong du lha la mchod nas gdod dam tshig blang zhing btung ngo //
NK053('i)001:6352: de nas tsho gcig la phyi mas bslad de sgrub
NK053('i)001:6353: pa po kun la snod re re sbyin cing 'thung
NK053('i)001:6354: du stsol // de nas 3rnal 'byor sgrub pa po
NK053('i)001:6355: kun gyis rang rang gi dam tshig nyams chag skong
NK053('i)001:6356: du stsol // ba'i phyir / sngar sgrub pa'i rdzas bdud rtsi a mri ta snod nas phyung ste /
NK053('i)001:6357: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon la phul bas /
NK053('i)001:6358: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon gyis yang phud nang
NK053('i)001:6359: du bdud rtsi stsal nas sman phud de bdud rtsir
NK053('i)001:6361: kun gyis dgongs pa dril te bdud rtsi'i snod nyid b+h+r+aum dkar po 'phro 'du las /
NK053('i)001:6362: b+han+d+ha 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang gi nang du /
NK053('i)001:6363: 'og nyi ma steng zla ba ga'u kha sbyar ba'i
NK053('i)001:6364: nang du bdud rtsi dngos gzhi rnam pa lnga dbus
NK053('i)001:6365: dang phyogs bzhir dbus su byang sems dkar po h+aum
NK053('i)001:6366: / shar du dri chen ser po /
NK053('i)001:6367: lhor m+aam sa ser po s+w+aa /
NK053('i)001:6368: nub tu rak+ta dmar po +aah byang du dri chu ljang gu h+aah'o //
NK053('i)001:6369: gsal ba'i steng du yi ge dpa' bo 'bru lngas mnan par bsams te /
NK053('i)001:6370: 'bru lnga las rang gi thugs ka'i h'u las lag
NK053('i)001:6371: pa g.yon pa'i srin lag bkug la sor mo gzhan
NK053('i)001:6372: brkyang la / sbom po dang dbang mo rtse sprad pa las /
NK053('i)001:6373: nyi zla gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor ga'u kha sbyar gyi dbus su /
NK053('i)001:6375: dpal rta mgrin du gyur par dmigs te /
NK053('i)001:6376: de la bde ba rgyas 'debs ma /
NK053('i)001:6379: za byed ma ste gsang ba'i yum bzhis bskor bar
NK053('i)001:6380: bsgom pa'i phyag rgya bdud rtsi'i snod la gtug la
NK053('i)001:6381: / +aahmh'u badz+ra a mri ta h'u h+r+ai th+aa /
NK053('i)001:6383: bdag gi thugs ka'i h'u las ye shes kyi 'od zer byung nas /
NK053('i)001:6384: mtheb srin rta mgrin yab yum la 'phros /
NK053('i)001:6386: ma chags thabs kyis sbyor ba mdzad /
NK053('i)001:6387: sbyor mtshams nas byang chub sems las 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:6388: dpa' bo 'bru lnga la phog pas /
NK053('i)001:6389: ye shes kyi 'od du 'bar bas bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga bzhu btul /
NK053('i)001:6390: de las kyang dpa' bo 'bru lnga las 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:6391: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas la phog pas /
NK053('i)001:6392: thugs dam gyis rjes su dgongs nas byin gyis rlob cing dngos grub bsdus /
NK053('i)001:6393: sems can rnams la phog pas nyon mongs pa'i rtog pa sbyangs nas /
NK053('i)001:6394: tshe dang dbang thang spel te bkrag dang gzi mdangs bdag la bsdus /
NK053('i)001:6395: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten la phog pas dngos po bsregs nas /
NK053('i)001:6396: 'jig rten dag pa'i bdud rtsi dang bcud du gyur
NK053('i)001:6397: pa kun bsdus nas mu tig dkar po dri ma
NK053('i)001:6398: med pa bzhin du bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:6399: de nas bdud rtsi lnga dang /
NK053('i)001:6400: dpa' bo 'bru lnga dang ril dbyer med par gyur pa'i dbus na /
NK053('i)001:6403: h'u mthing ka gsum brtsegs mar gnas pa las /
NK053('i)001:6404: ye shes kyi 'od zer tshur byung ste /
NK053('i)001:6405: mtheb srin rta mgrin yab yum la thim /
NK053('i)001:6406: de las bdag la thim pas rtog sgrib bsregs sbyangs tshe dang dbang thang spel /
NK053('i)001:6407: bdag las 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:6408: 'phags pa la phog pas mchod pa phul nas byin gyis brlabs bsdus /
NK053('i)001:6409: sems can la phog pas rtog sgrib bsregs nas bkrag mdangs bsdus /
NK053('i)001:6410: snod kyi 'jig rten la phog nas /
NK053('i)001:6412: 'jig rten gyi bdud rtsi bcud ril bsdus nas bdag
NK053('i)001:6413: la thim pas bdag gis dngos grub thob cing tshe
NK053('i)001:6414: dang ye shes bkrag dang gzi mdangs rgyas /
NK053('i)001:6415: bdag la ye shes kyi bdud rtsi 'od zer dang bcas par byung nas /
NK053('i)001:6416: rta mgrin yab yum la thim /
NK053('i)001:6417: rta mgrin yab yum gnyis su med pa'i byang chub
NK053('i)001:6418: sems dang 'dres nas dkar tsa ra ra byung ste
NK053('i)001:6419: / bdud rtsi'i snod du bab pas /
NK053('i)001:6420: 'o ma thab tu lud pa lta bur khol zhing /
NK053('i)001:6421: mu tig dkar po dri ma med pa ltar bsam zhing dgu pa'i 'dzab bzlas pa bya ste /
NK053('i)001:6422: 'phags pa dang dkyil 'khor gyi lha mchod pa'i bdud rtsi byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6423: rnal 'byor pa'i dngos grub sgrub pa'i bdud rtsi'i bum
NK053('i)001:6424: pa gnyis ka de ltar byin gyis brlab par bya'o
NK053('i)001:6425: // de nas 3gtor ma byin brlab pa ni gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:6431: gtor gzhong b+h+r+aum las zla gam dmar po dbang gi gzhal yas khang du gtor ma'i rdzas la /
NK053('i)001:6435: dpal chen po yab yum 'khor dang bcas par gyur te /
NK053('i)001:6436: dpal gyi pho brang du bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:6437: mchod bstabs thams cad kyi gnas te /
NK053('i)001:6438: sgrub pa la dngos grub ma blangs bar du 'dzin gtor mi gtang ngo //
NK053('i)001:6439: mchod sbyin gyi gtor ma dang /
NK053('i)001:6440: tshogs dang kun byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6441: yo byad byin gyis brlabs pa'i skabs su bstan pa de nyid ltar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:6444: gnas skabs mang du dbyer yod par shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:6445: de nas 4rak+ta byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6447: b+h+r+aum b+han+d+ha ka p+aa la b+h+r+aum /
NK053('i)001:6449: snod b+han+d+ha'i gzhal yas khang 'jig rten gyi gtos tsam du gyur par bsam /
NK053('i)001:6450: rak+ta la yi ge ra dmar po gcig bsam /
NK053('i)001:6451: de la sngags 'dis byin gyis brlabs te /
NK053('i)001:6452: +aahmh'u rak+ta mu la rak+ta h'u h+r+ai th+aa /
NK053('i)001:6454: thugs ka'i h'u las 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:6456: ye shes kyi 'od zer dmar po 'bar bas /
NK053('i)001:6457: dngos po'i log rtog sbyangs nas /
NK053('i)001:6458: bdud rtsi'i rak+tara gyur ngo bo bdud rtsi rnam pa rak+ta yin pa las /
NK053('i)001:6459: gzar bu h'u las rdo rjer gyur pas dkrugs pas /
NK053('i)001:6460: rak+ta'i rba rlabs dang zer ma re re las kyang /
NK053('i)001:6461: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i lha mo'i sprin 'phro bar byin gyis brlab bo //
NK053('i)001:6462: dpal 5bshos byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6463: dpal bshos la yi ge s+w+aa las /
NK053('i)001:6466: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po cher gyur pa las /
NK053('i)001:6467: de las mchod pa'i sprin rgyun mi chad par byin gyis brlab bo //
NK053('i)001:6469: gzhan yang spos dang me tog la sogs pa zhi ba'i skabs su rigs par bya'o /
NK053('i)001:6471: 3 / de la thams cad stong pa nyid du byin gyis brlab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6472: thun mong mchod pa byin gyis brlab pa ste /
NK053('i)001:6474: phyi ltar bdud rtsi'i chu rgyun /
NK053('i)001:6476: gsang ba yab yum byang sems su brlab /
NK053('i)001:6478: phyi ltar kha dog sna tshogs pas stong gsum gang ba /
NK053('i)001:6479: nang ltar mdzes pa'i lha mo /
NK053('i)001:6480: gsang ba rnam shes tshogs brgyad du brlab /
NK053('i)001:6483: phyi ltar dri'i lha mo phyag na spos kong thogs pa mang po /
NK053('i)001:6484: nang ltar tshil chen dud pa /
NK053('i)001:6485: gsang ba dri chen ngad bsung bar brlab /
NK053('i)001:6486: badz+ra a lo ke hrihzhesa pas /
NK053('i)001:6487: phyi ltar kong bu stong gsum tsam mam rgya mtsho tsam /
NK053('i)001:6488: me lce'i 'od kyis srid gsum khyab par brlab /
NK053('i)001:6489: nang ltar snod dur khrod gzhal yas khang la /
NK053('i)001:6490: mar zhi gnas tshil chen rgya mtsho tsam /
NK053('i)001:6491: me lce lhag mthong ye shes lnga'i 'od 'phro ba /
NK053('i)001:6492: gsang ba bdag gi byang chub kyi sems ye shes kyi me mar stong 'char bar brlab bo //
NK053('i)001:6494: phyi ltar lha mo dung phor thogs pa mang pos nyon mongs pa'i ljan ljan dag par brlab /
NK053('i)001:6495: nang ltar lha mo mang pos tsan+da lde gus myug cing mchod /
NK053('i)001:6496: gsang ba zhi gnas kyi rlan lhag mthong gi byang sems su dag par bsgom /
NK053('i)001:6497: badz+ra n+aee bi d+ya zhes pas /
NK053('i)001:6498: phyi ltar lha bshos ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa ri rab bas che bar brlab /
NK053('i)001:6499: nang ltar 'dod yon lha mo lngar /
NK053('i)001:6500: gsang bar byang chub sems 'od kyi thig le rin po che 'bar ba gcig bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:6502: sangs rgyas kun gyi ting nge 'dzin //
NK053('i)001:6503: stong pa nyid ces rgyal bas gsungs //
NK053('i)001:6504: de bas rnam pa thams cad kun //
NK053('i)001:6505: stong pa nyid du dran par bya //
NK053('i)001:6506: zhes 'byung bas don dam par chos thams cad stong pa nyid du bsgom zhing /
NK053('i)001:6507: des thams cad byin brlab bo //
NK053('i)001:6510: 5 / slob ma la dbang bskur ba'i phrin las la /
NK053('i)001:6511: skabs sbyor brgyad pa slob dpon mnyes par bya zhing dbang nod pa'i phyir yon dbul ba'i skabs /
NK053('i)001:6512: lung dgu las dam tshig dbang gi lung /
NK053('i)001:6513: dkyil 'khor dgu las dbang bskur dkyil 'khor /
NK053('i)001:6514: mtha' drug las goms pa dbang ngo //
NK053('i)001:6517: dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa'i phrin las kyi rim pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6519: dbang bskur ba dngos kyi rim pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6521: khyad par can gyi dam tshig bsrung ba'i rim pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6522: sgrub pa po rnams khyad par gyi chas kyis mdzes par bya ba'i rim pa'o //
NK053('i)001:6523: phyi ma 'di gnyis sa bcad gcig tu bsdus pas gsum mo /
NK053('i)001:6525: 1 / de la slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa'i phrin las kyi rim pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:6526: rtogs pa'i blo can de dag gis //
NK053('i)001:6527: srog lus man chad rdzas rnams kyis //
NK053('i)001:6528: bla ma mnyes par bya phyir dbul //
NK053('i)001:6529: dngos grub 'dod par gsol ba gdab //
NK053('i)001:6530: zhes bya ba gsungs pa la don lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:6531: dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa'i slob ma dang /
NK053('i)001:6532: yon dbul ba'i dngos po dang /
NK053('i)001:6534: yon dbul ba'i dgos ched dang /
NK053('i)001:6535: gsol ba gdab pa'i rim pa'o //
NK053('i)001:6537: dkyil 1'khor du gzhug pa'i slob ma gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:6538: rtogs pa'i blo can de dag gis //
NK053('i)001:6540: de la dbang nod pa'i slob ma de yang /
NK053('i)001:6541: nges par brtag pa bzhi byas pa'i slob ma /
NK053('i)001:6546: bla na med pa'i byang chub la yid ches pa'i rtogs pa byung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6547: dad pa skye bar gyur te /
NK053('i)001:6548: sems kyi nges pa rnyed pa'i blo gros can /
NK053('i)001:6549: sgrub pa po skyon drug spangs shing /
NK053('i)001:6550: mi phyed pa bdun dang ldan pa /
NK053('i)001:6552: gsang sngags zab mo la blo zhugs shing dad pa can de dag gis bya /
NK053('i)001:6555: yon 2dbul ba'i dngos po gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:6556: srog lus man chad rdzas rnams kyis //
NK053('i)001:6558: de la dbang thob pa'i rgyu yon yin te /
NK053('i)001:6559: de yang rab 'bring tha ma gsum mo //
NK053('i)001:6560: rab rang gi srog phul te ci tsam ri ba'i yon gyis bslu ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6563: gzhan yang bu dang chung ma dang sring mo nor gyis brgyan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:6564: tha ma rdzas kyi rnam pa rang gang 'phangs shing gces pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6566: bla ma gang la dgyes pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6569: skyes bu rtogs pa'i blo gros can //
NK053('i)001:6570: dad pa'i sems dang ldan pa yis //
NK053('i)001:6571: srog lus ma lus rdzas bcas rnams //
NK053('i)001:6572: ser sna med pa'i sems kyis dbul //
NK053('i)001:6575: kun tu sna tshogs dgos 'dod 'byung ba'i bla ma la //
NK053('i)001:6576: yon mchog dag ni rab tu dbul //
NK053('i)001:6577: gang la yongs su gtong dka' ba //
NK053('i)001:6578: de ni mchog tu bshad pa yin //
NK053('i)001:6581: rgyal srid dang ni rang gi lus //
NK053('i)001:6582: bu dang chung ma nor gyi dbyig /
NK053('i)001:6585: rang sems 'phreng ba rab tu gces dang yid 'thad dbul //
NK053('i)001:6587: yon 3dbul ba'i gnas gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:6588: bla ma zhes bya bas bstan te /
NK053('i)001:6589: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon de yang dpal rdo rje sems dpa' dang mi gnyis par gyur pa /
NK053('i)001:6590: tshul dgu dang ldan pa ste /
NK053('i)001:6591: tshul btsun zhing gdung rgyud rigs bzang ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6592: blo yangs shing rgyud bzang ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6593: mi khom ya ma barlara ma gyur pa ste gtug cing barlinga ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6594: mi chos dang lha chos mkhas shing barlinga ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6595: dge chos nyams su lon zhing bstun pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6596: gnas dben pa la dga' zhing 'jig rten la 'dzin zhen chags pa chung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6597: zhi zhing rang rgyud dul ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6598: dge chos la brtson 'grus che zhing thugs rjes zhing khams mi gtong ba'o //
NK053('i)001:6599: de rnams dang mi ldan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6600: dbang bskur ba'i slob dpon ma yin te /
NK053('i)001:6602: tshul dgu ldan pa'i bla ma yis //
NK053('i)001:6603: rtag tu dbang bskur slob dpon bya //
NK053('i)001:6606: dbang thob par byas nas dam tshig la gnas pa /
NK053('i)001:6607: shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin du 'brel ba /
NK053('i)001:6608: bsnyen sgrub zab mo la blo sbyangs pa /
NK053('i)001:6609: bsnyen pa rdzogs par byas pa /
NK053('i)001:6610: chags pa chung zhing dge ba nyams bag tu spyod pa /
NK053('i)001:6611: dbang dang gdams ngag gi rgyun lam ma chad cing /
NK053('i)001:6612: sems can la snying rje che ba des /
NK053('i)001:6613: slob ma la dbang bskur na tshe 'di kho na la sgrib pa sbyong bar byed cing /
NK053('i)001:6614: sangs rgyas kyi sa la 'dzeg pa yin pas /
NK053('i)001:6615: de la yon dbul ba'i gnas yin no //
NK053('i)001:6616: de lta bu dang mi ldan pa la ni ma yin no //
NK053('i)001:6617: yon dbul 4ba'i dgos ched gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:6620: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon mnyes par bya ba yang /
NK053('i)001:6621: rab bla mas chos ci bstan go ba shes pa shes rab kyis mnyes par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6622: 'bring rang rgyud bzang bas bsnyen bkur ba rang rgyud kyis mnyes pa bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6623: tha ma zas nor bdog rgus mnyes pa /
NK053('i)001:6624: zang zing gis mnyes par byed pa ste /
NK053('i)001:6625: de gsum gyis bla ma mnyes par gyur na /
NK053('i)001:6626: dbang dang dngos grub 'byung nges pa'i rgyu yin pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:6627: dad pa dang mos pa'i sems kyis /
NK053('i)001:6628: yon gsum po de dbul bar bya /
NK053('i)001:6630: de la gsol ba 5gdab pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:6631: dngos grub 'dod pas gsol ba gdab //
NK053('i)001:6633: thun mong dang mchog gis bsdus pa'i dngos grub thob
NK053('i)001:6634: par 'dod pa'i slob bus yon dbul zhing gsol ba'i
NK053('i)001:6635: dus su / 'dir ngag don don tshan nyer bdun gyis bstan te /
NK053('i)001:6636: dang po dpon slob 'dug stangs bstan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6637: man+dala chen po'i nub phyogs su seng khri bcas te /
NK053('i)001:6638: der bla ma zhal shar du gzigs nas bzhugs su gsol la /
NK053('i)001:6639: slob ma rnams shar phyogs su tshar du dngar du sgrig stsal nas /
NK053('i)001:6641: bar du yol bas bcad de /
NK053('i)001:6642: slob ma rnams der ras kyi stod g.yogs dang smad dkris kyis mdzes par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6643: dar ras gang yang rung ba la sgom bzhi'i sngags
NK053('i)001:6644: btab pa yis re re'i gdong la g.yogs par byas
NK053('i)001:6645: nas mig dgab pa byas la /
NK053('i)001:6646: gnyis pa slob mas zhu ba phul ba /
NK053('i)001:6649: dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa 'khor dang bcas pa /
NK053('i)001:6650: rigs drug gi rigs lnga dang kun 'dus pa lha tshogs ma lus pa 'khor dang bcas pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6651: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon la /
NK053('i)001:6653: rdo rje'i theg pa gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir 'jug cing /
NK053('i)001:6654: dbang dang dngos grub dam pa zhig nod par 'dod pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:6655: bdag ming 'di zhes bgyi ba'i lus ngag yid gsum bran du 'bul ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6656: bu dang chung ma sring mo la sogs pa 'khor
NK053('i)001:6657: dang longs spyod la sogs pa 'bul bar mchis na
NK053('i)001:6658: bdag thugs rjes bzung zhing byin gyis brlabs par mdzad
NK053('i)001:6661: gsum pa slob dpon gyis nus sam dri ba /
NK053('i)001:6662: de la slob dpon gyis 'di skad dri'o //
NK053('i)001:6664: rdo rje theg pa gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir 'jug cing dbang nod par 'dod na /
NK053('i)001:6665: khyed nyid kyi sha dang rus pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6670: longs spyod kyi bya ba thams cad /
NK053('i)001:6671: chos don du gnyer ba'i don du dbul dgos na /
NK053('i)001:6672: 'jungs pa med pa'i dad pas 'bul bar nus sam /
NK053('i)001:6678: lnga pa mi dga' ba med cing gnang ba thob sam dri ba /
NK053('i)001:6682: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bstan pa dang spyod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6687: dri zar bcas pa gang gis kyang bslu zhing brid par bya ba ma yin no //
NK053('i)001:6688: rigs kyi bu khyod rgyal ba'i bstan pa la 'jug
NK053('i)001:6689: pa'i skal pa dang mi ldan pa'i kha na ma
NK053('i)001:6690: tho ba dang bcas pa'i gang zag gam /
NK053('i)001:6693: pha dang ma las gnang ba ma thob par 'ongs pa'am /
NK053('i)001:6695: de dag gi khrims dang 'gal zhing thugs dkrugs pa'am /
NK053('i)001:6697: zlas bdas shing tshe 'di'i khengs dregs tsam 'dod pa'i phyir 'jug pa ma yin nam /
NK053('i)001:6700: de ni cang ma lags so //
NK053('i)001:6702: bdun pa myang 'das pa 'dod dam nan gyis dri ba /
NK053('i)001:6704: 'o na khyod de bzhin gshegs pa'i gdung 'tshob cing /
NK053('i)001:6705: rdo rje theg pa'i nye lam gi snying por zhugs nas /
NK053('i)001:6706: thun mong gi dngos grub 'jig rten pa'i 'byor pa mchog thob par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6707: mchog gi dngos grub mtshan ma rnam par dag pa
NK053('i)001:6708: phyag rgya chen po'i sku mngon du thob par bya
NK053('i)001:6709: ba dang / mtshan ma med pa'i chos nyid ye
NK053('i)001:6710: dag pa rang byung gi ye shes ngo shes shing
NK053('i)001:6711: 'jug pa'i thar pa chen po'i don thob par 'dod
NK053('i)001:6717: dgu pa g.yang sa dang bcas pas nyes che bar dri ba /
NK053('i)001:6720: 'jig rten pa'i srung ma dam tshig dang ldan pas
NK053('i)001:6721: 'khor srung ma'i tshogs bgrang bar mi nus pa dang
NK053('i)001:6722: / nam mkha' la bzhugs pa'i rig 'dzin ji snyed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6723: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i 'phags pa mkhyen pa dang ldan pa /
NK053('i)001:6724: ye shes kyi spyan dang ldan zhing ma 'gags par gzigs pa /
NK053('i)001:6725: ci la'ang mi rtog pa'i thugs kyis thogs pa med
NK053('i)001:6726: par mkhyen pa rnams la mkhyen par gzu dpang du
NK053('i)001:6727: gsol nas / dam tshig gnyen po nod par spro'am /
NK053('i)001:6728: khyod kyis gal te yang dag par ma yin cing /
NK053('i)001:6729: bslu zhing nyams blangs pa tsam gyi phyir byas na ni /
NK053('i)001:6732: sha za zhing khrag 'thung ba la dga' ba dang /
NK053('i)001:6736: sder mo can gyi tshogs ji snyed pas /
NK053('i)001:6737: gang dam las 'das na brlag par mdzad pa de dag la tshad gzugs dgos pas /
NK053('i)001:6739: zhes bla mas dris pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6743: bcu gcig pa dam bcas pa khur nus sam dri ba /
NK053('i)001:6746: 'o na khyod kyis dus 'di nas bzung nas /
NK053('i)001:6747: nam snying po byang chub la ma phyin gyi bar
NK053('i)001:6748: du dam bcas pa'i khur chen po mi 'dor bar
NK053('i)001:6749: khur nus sam / zhes dris pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6750: bcu gnyis pa khas blangs shing zhu ba dang bcas pa /
NK053('i)001:6751: de kho na ltar rdo thog go //
NK053('i)001:6753: de nas yang slob mas 'di skad brjod do //
NK053('i)001:6754: byang chub rdo rje sangs rgyas la //
NK053('i)001:6755: ji ltar mchod chen bgyis pa ltar //
NK053('i)001:6756: bdag kyang rab tu bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:6757: nam mkha'i rdo rje ste skye shi 'pho 'gyur med pa de ltar bdag la stsol //
NK053('i)001:6759: bcu gsum pa yang dri ba dang dris lan gsol ba /
NK053('i)001:6761: bu khyod dga' ba ci la dga' //
NK053('i)001:6764: bdag ni skal chen bde chen la //
NK053('i)001:6765: rab dgyes 'phrul la bdag dga' ste //
NK053('i)001:6766: mchog tu dga' la bdag daga'o //
NK053('i)001:6768: bcu bzhi pa me tog sbyin zhing sgo bzhir khrid pa /
NK053('i)001:6771: sangs rgyas rnams ni thams cad kyi //
NK053('i)001:6772: rdo rje gsang ba gsum las byung /
NK053('i)001:6773: khams gsum kun gyis phyag byas pa //
NK053('i)001:6774: rdo rje'i dbang bskur chen po sbyin //
NK053('i)001:6776: slob ma'i lag tu me tog byin la /
NK053('i)001:6779: nyon mongs zhe sdang chen po yis //
NK053('i)001:6780: thog med dus nas bcad lags na //
NK053('i)001:6781: thugs rje thabs kyis sprul pa yi //
NK053('i)001:6782: rdo rje lcags kyu'i phyag rgya yis //
NK053('i)001:6783: de ring thabs sgo dbye ru gsol //
NK053('i)001:6784: badz+ra ang+ku sha dzahdzah pra be sha phata /
NK053('i)001:6786: nyon mongs nga rgyal chen po yis //
NK053('i)001:6787: thog med dus nas bcad lags na //
NK053('i)001:6788: thugs rje thabs kyis sprul pa yi //
NK053('i)001:6789: rdo rje zhags pa'i phyag rgya yis //
NK053('i)001:6790: de ring thabs sgo dbye ru gsol //
NK053('i)001:6791: badz+ra pa sha h'u pra be sha ya phata /
NK053('i)001:6793: nyon mongs 'dod chags chen po yis //
NK053('i)001:6794: thog med dus nas bcad lags na //
NK053('i)001:6795: thugs rje thabs kyis sprul pa yi /
NK053('i)001:6796: rdo rje lcags sgrog phyag rgya yis //
NK053('i)001:6797: de ring thabs sgo dbye ru gsol //
NK053('i)001:6798: badz+ra s+pho ta bam pra be sha phata /
NK053('i)001:6800: nyon mongs phrag dog chen po yis //
NK053('i)001:6801: thog med dus nas bcad lags na //
NK053('i)001:6802: thugs rje thabs kyis sprul pa yi //
NK053('i)001:6803: rdo rje dril bu'i phyag rgya yis //
NK053('i)001:6804: de ring thabs sgo dbye ru gsol //
NK053('i)001:6805: badz+ra g+han+de hohpra be sha ya phata /
NK053('i)001:6807: bco lnga pa bgegs skrad cing gzhung tshig brjod pa /
NK053('i)001:6808: bla ma gu rus nyungs kar la sum+b+ha ni'am rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi sngags ring bzlas te /
NK053('i)001:6811: rdo rje'i ye shes thob byed pa //
NK053('i)001:6812: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi //
NK053('i)001:6814: bdag gis slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK053('i)001:6816: bcu drug pa me tog dor ba /
NK053('i)001:6817: slob ma rnams shar phyogs su bkug nas /
NK053('i)001:6818: me tog gi phreng ba dor du stsal nas /
NK053('i)001:6819: dpal gyi dngos grub thob bya'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:6820: 'gro ba phan phyir tho rgyal gyis //
NK053('i)001:6821: bdag la thugs brtsir dgongs nas ni //
NK053('i)001:6822: sman par dgongs te bzhes su gsol //
NK053('i)001:6823: rin chen me tog la sogs pa //
NK053('i)001:6824: gang la bab pa rigs kyi lha //
NK053('i)001:6825: gtso bo'i rigs de bsgrub na ni //
NK053('i)001:6826: dngos grub myur te the tshom med //
NK053('i)001:6827: sngon tshe tshe rabs grangs med nas //
NK053('i)001:6828: dge ba'i las kyis bsten pa'i lha //
NK053('i)001:6830: lhag pa'i lha ni gang yin pa //
NK053('i)001:6831: da lta nyid du 'bab par shog /
NK053('i)001:6832: badz+ra pra te gri ha na h'u /
NK053('i)001:6837: bcu bdun pa rigs brtag pa /
NK053('i)001:6839: me tog lha gang la bab pa brtag par byas la /
NK053('i)001:6840: bco brgyad pa mig dbye ba /
NK053('i)001:6841: de nas mig dbye ba'i cho ga bya ste /
NK053('i)001:6842: gser gyi thur ma'i rtse la /
NK053('i)001:6843: yi ge pra ser po gcig bsam la /
NK053('i)001:6845: sngon gyi mig mkhan rgyal po yis //
NK053('i)001:6846: gse gyi thur ma thogs nas ni //
NK053('i)001:6847: 'jig rten ling thog bsal ba ltar //
NK053('i)001:6848: bu khyod mi shes rmongs pa yi //
NK053('i)001:6849: ling thog rgyal ba rnams kyis bsal //
NK053('i)001:6850: badz+ra ne tra a ba ha ra phata li h+r+ai /
NK053('i)001:6851: zhes brjod nas ling thog bsal ba'i tshul du byas te /
NK053('i)001:6852: shes bya'i sgrib pa bsal nas shes rab kyi mig dbye bar bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:6853: bcu dgu pa ci mthong dri zhing gdong g.yogs dkrol ba /
NK053('i)001:6854: de nas ci mthong dri ma'i gtam bya ste /
NK053('i)001:6855: ji ltar mthong ba'i rim pa shes pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6857: badz+ra tsak+shu ka ma la ya sarba su ra ta s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:6859: nyi shu pa dal bstan pa /
NK053('i)001:6862: kun rdzob gzugs su bstan pa yis //
NK053('i)001:6863: 'di la dad pa rab tu bskyed //
NK053('i)001:6865: dad dang brtson 'grus byas pa dang //
NK053('i)001:6866: shes rab snying rjer ldan pa yis //
NK053('i)001:6867: dngos grub ma lus mngon du gyur //
NK053('i)001:6869: de phyir 'di la brtson par byos //
NK053('i)001:6871: nyer gcig pa bgegs bskrad pa /
NK053('i)001:6872: de nas gu rus bden pa bdar te /
NK053('i)001:6873: nyungs kar la rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi sngags ring
NK053('i)001:6874: na mo rat+na tra y+aa ya sogs bzlas nas bgegs
NK053('i)001:6876: nyer gnyis pa khrus bya ba /
NK053('i)001:6877: de nas las kyi bum pa blangs la /
NK053('i)001:6878: slob ma'i mgo lus dag par bkru zhing /
NK053('i)001:6879: khong du yang 'thung du gzhug go //
NK053('i)001:6880: sngags ni gong du bstan pa de nyid /
NK053('i)001:6881: badz+ra yak+sha big+h+n+aana ta kri ta phata /
NK053('i)001:6883: nyer gsum pa dam tshig bsgrag cing dam chu blud pa /
NK053('i)001:6884: de nas dung chen po'i nang du bdud rtsis bkang ba thogs la /
NK053('i)001:6885: ye shes kyi bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs la /
NK053('i)001:6886: dbang gi sngon 'gro dam tshig len du gzhug te /
NK053('i)001:6887: slob dpon gyis rgyud las 'byung ba 'di nyid brjod par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:6888: gzhi 'dzin dam tshig snum 'dra rin po che //
NK053('i)001:6889: ma rig tha rgod ko khengs lta bu btul //
NK053('i)001:6890: yang dag don rtogs sems dang chos su 'dre //
NK053('i)001:6891: lus dang srog gi phyir yang dam tshig mchog mi spong //
NK053('i)001:6892: de la gnas na rnal 'byor dbang phyug chen por 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:6893: dam tshig mchog ni 'dir gzung ba //
NK053('i)001:6894: bla ma spun grogs lha srung dang //
NK053('i)001:6895: sngags dang phyag rgya gsang tshig rnams //
NK053('i)001:6896: bkur dang mi spong byams pa dang //
NK053('i)001:6897: rgyun mi bcad cing spel mi gtong //
NK053('i)001:6898: 'di ni rtsa ba'i dam tshig yin //
NK053('i)001:6899: yan lag gi dam tshig ni /
NK053('i)001:6900: mi spang ba dang dang du blangs //
NK053('i)001:6901: spyad par bya dang shes par bya //
NK053('i)001:6902: sgrub par bya ba'i dam tshig lnga //
NK053('i)001:6903: sems dang chos su 'dres pa na //
NK053('i)001:6904: med pa dang ni phyal ba dang //
NK053('i)001:6905: gcig pu dang ni lhun gyis grub //
NK053('i)001:6906: de las mi 'da' dam tshig yin //
NK053('i)001:6907: zhes rgyud las 'byung ba 'di bsgrags te /
NK053('i)001:6908: de rnams kyi bsrung thabs dang /
NK053('i)001:6909: ma bsrungs pa'i skyon srung ba'i phan yon bshad nas /
NK053('i)001:6911: 'di ni khyod kyi dmyal ba'i chu //
NK053('i)001:6912: dam tshig nyams na sreg par byed //
NK053('i)001:6913: dam tshig bsrung na dngos grub ni //
NK053('i)001:6915: badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya h'u tha /
NK053('i)001:6917: sarba ba tee h+r+ai da yu h'u h+r+aih tha /
NK053('i)001:6919: bdud rtsi lan gsum du rdo rjes slob ma'i lce la bzhag cing /
NK053('i)001:6921: gsum du bsgom pa'i 'od zer gyis /
NK053('i)001:6922: lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgrib pa sbyang zhing /
NK053('i)001:6923: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6925: slob ma'i snying gar ye shes sems dpa' tshon gang
NK053('i)001:6926: ba gcig yi ge h'u gis kho'i shes pa byin
NK053('i)001:6927: gyis brlab cing shin tu gsal bar bskyed la bzhag
NK053('i)001:6928: ste / nyer bzhi pa skyon yon tan /
NK053('i)001:6931: rigs kyi bu de ring phan chad khyod kyi phyag na rdo rje ni nga yin te /
NK053('i)001:6932: da phyin chad ngas ji skad smras pa khyod kyis de bzhin du byos shig /
NK053('i)001:6933: nga yi bka' las 'da' bar ma byed cig /
NK053('i)001:6934: gal te 'das na khyod dus ma yin par shi
NK053('i)001:6935: nas phyi ma dmyal bar skyes te 'gro nges pa
NK053('i)001:6936: yin no // nga yi bka' bzhin du bsrung na ni /
NK053('i)001:6937: dus 'dir tshe ring zhing bsam pa 'grub pa dang /
NK053('i)001:6938: srid pa bar do'i gnas nas sangs rgyas kyi rigs su skyes te sangs rgyas dngos su 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:6940: nyer lnga pa dal bstan pa /
NK053('i)001:6941: de nas dkyil 'khor bstan par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:6943: dkyil 'khor zla gam zhes gsungs te //
NK053('i)001:6944: mchog ni yid kyi dkyil 'khor ro //
NK053('i)001:6945: gzhal yas khang brtsegs ye shes te //
NK053('i)001:6947: sgo bzhi dran pa nyer bzhag bzhi //
NK053('i)001:6948: rnam thar brgya ldan rta babs so //
NK053('i)001:6949: rin chen sgo ste thugs rje'i ngang //
NK053('i)001:6950: yang dag spong bzhi t+wa ra na //
NK053('i)001:6951: dran pa nyer bzhag sgo khyud dang //
NK053('i)001:6952: rdzu 'phrul rkang bzhi'i sgo khyams ldan //
NK053('i)001:6953: phreng ba byang chub yan lag bdun //
NK053('i)001:6954: 'phags lam brgyad kyi rkang brgyad mdzes //
NK053('i)001:6955: lam gyi ye shes rnga yab dang //
NK053('i)001:6956: nyon mongs gcod 'joms mu tig phreng //
NK053('i)001:6957: dril bu ba dan rlung bskyod pa //
NK053('i)001:6958: shes rab chos sgra sgrogs pa dang //
NK053('i)001:6959: che ba'i yon tan 'dus pa'i rtags //
NK053('i)001:6960: bdud bzhi 'joms pa'i rgyal mtshan dang //
NK053('i)001:6961: rten 'brel mtshon pa'i me long dang //
NK053('i)001:6962: ye shes lnga yi mtshon rtsir ldan //
NK053('i)001:6963: thod phreng sku gsum thob pa'i rtags //
NK053('i)001:6964: gzhal yas khang mchog brgyan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:6966: de la pho brang gi don yang gong du bshad pa bzhin 'dir yang bshad cing bstan par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:6967: nyer drug pa lha dang rtogs tshogs sbyar ba /
NK053('i)001:6968: da ni de la bzhugs pa'i lha bstan par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:6969: rigs kyi bu don dam par chos thams cad skye 'gags med pa las /
NK053('i)001:6970: kun rdzob tu srid pa thams cad ye shes rol pa'i phyag rgyar snang ste /
NK053('i)001:6972: de la kun gzhi rnam par shes pa ni /
NK053('i)001:6973: dpal he ru ka'i rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:6975: de'i yul yum kro ti shwa ri ma'i rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:6976: mig dang rna ba dang sna dang lce bzhi'i rnam par shes pa bzhi ni /
NK053('i)001:6977: lha mo ko'u r+ai ma dang /
NK053('i)001:6980: bee ta l+ai dang bzhi'i rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:6981: mig dang rna ba sna lce'i dbang po bzhi ni /
NK053('i)001:6985: tsan+d+ha l+ai bzhi'i rang bzhin no //
NK053('i)001:6987: mig dang rna ba sna lce bzhi'i yul bzhi ni /
NK053('i)001:6989: sed+ha la sogs pa b+y+aa kri /
NK053('i)001:6991: shwa na ma bzhi yin la /
NK053('i)001:6993: kri ta la sogs pa ste 'das pa kri ta ma /
NK053('i)001:6996: dus bzhi mnyam pa nyid hu lu ma dang bzhi'o //
NK053('i)001:7001: sgo ma bzhi'i rang bzhin ste rta gdong /
NK053('i)001:7005: bdag dang bdag gir 'dzin pa ni /
NK053('i)001:7006: dbang phyug ma'i rang bzhin te /
NK053('i)001:7008: lus khams skye gnas kyi zag pa dang bcas pa'i phung po ril /
NK053('i)001:7009: zag pa med pa'i lha'i dkyil 'khor du shes par gyis shig /
NK053('i)001:7010: ces brjod de lha rtogs tshogs dang sbyar nas bstan no //
NK053('i)001:7011: lha bstan pa yang don man ngag gi rgyas 'bring du shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:7012: nyer bdun pa blo rab 'bring tha gsum gzhug cing dbang bskur ba ni /
NK053('i)001:7013: de la slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa yang /
NK053('i)001:7014: slob ma'i blo rab 'bring tha gsum dang sbyar te /
NK053('i)001:7015: de yang he ru ka'i gal po las /
NK053('i)001:7017: rang bzhin lhun grub ye ji bzhin pa'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:7018: slob ma rab gzhung dbang bskur te //
NK053('i)001:7019: bya bral ye rdzogs man ngag bstan //
NK053('i)001:7021: slob ma 'bring gzhug dbang bskur te //
NK053('i)001:7022: bskyed rdzogs grub pa'i man ngag ma h+aa /
NK053('i)001:7026: gzugs brnyan bsnyen sgrub dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:7027: tha ma'i slob gzhug dbang bskur te //
NK053('i)001:7028: rim gyis blo sbyong man ngag bstan //
NK053('i)001:7032: lha mo dag dang gar byed cing //
NK053('i)001:7033: de ni rab dgyes bdag pos khrid //
NK053('i)001:7034: pho brang dga' byed rab dgyes che //
NK053('i)001:7035: rab dgyes bdag po bde thob ldan //
NK053('i)001:7036: seng ge'i gdan rab dpe seng ges gcan gzan gzhan
NK053('i)001:7037: zil gyis gnon pa ltar lhan skyes bde bas rnam
NK053('i)001:7039: dga' ba bzhi dang bzhi yi mchog nyid kyis //
NK053('i)001:7040: rdo rje pad+mora sbyor ba yis //
NK053('i)001:7041: de khrid pas na dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:7044: nam mkha'i dbyings kyi dbus gnas par //
NK053('i)001:7045: dam tshig gi dal bskyed cing de ltar dmigs pa de yang /
NK053('i)001:7046: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor gyi skur sbyor pa can des bya ba yis //
NK053('i)001:7047: 'khor lo can slob ma nyid rdo rje sems dpar gyur dbang bskur te /
NK053('i)001:7048: rang gi gnas dal gyi tshul du shes par bya /
NK053('i)001:7049: sangs rgyas ni slob dpon du shes par bya /
NK053('i)001:7050: yum bzhis bum pa thogs nas dbang bskur ba las slob tu shes par bya /
NK053('i)001:7051: spyi bo nas chu blugs pa bum chus dbang bskur bar shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:7054: mchod pa yang ni de nyid kyis //
NK053('i)001:7055: blo dang ldan pas rtag tu bya //
NK053('i)001:7056: slob dpon slob ma'i snying gar bsgoms nas ni //
NK053('i)001:7057: dbang bskur ba ni rtag tu bya'o //
NK053('i)001:7060: yi ge gdan nam snying po'am //
NK053('i)001:7061: phyag rgya sku gsung thugs ldan par //
NK053('i)001:7062: byin rlabs ya mtshan rmad po che //
NK053('i)001:7064: kun byas dbang phyug rim pas 'jug /
NK053('i)001:7065: de ru slob ma gzhug par bya //
NK053('i)001:7067: sgrub thabs 'di nyid kyi dbang du byas na yang /
NK053('i)001:7069: gnas lugs rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK053('i)001:7070: bsgom pa ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK053('i)001:7071: bzhengs pa rdul tshon gyi dkyil 'khor dang /
NK053('i)001:7072: mkha' gsang gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor ste /
NK053('i)001:7073: 'og nas 'byung ba bzhin dkyus la ngos bzung zhing man ngag shes pas /
NK053('i)001:7074: slob ma der gzhug cing dbang bskur te byin gyis brlabs pa bya'o //
NK053('i)001:7075: de la dbang bskur ba'i rim pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:7079: zhes bya ba yan chad kyis bstan pa la //
NK053('i)001:7080: gnyis pa bar du dbang bskur ba dngos kyi rim pa ni /
NK053('i)001:7082: slob dpon dang slob ma ji ltar gnas pa'i tshul bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7083: dbang bskur ba'i thabs dang rim pa bstan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:7086: slob ma ji ltar gnas pa'i tshul gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:7087: dang po slob dpon gnas tshul ni /
NK053('i)001:7088: slob dpon ji bzhin stan bder gnas //
NK053('i)001:7090: de la bla ma rdo rje slob dpon nub phyogs nas shar phyogs su byung la /
NK053('i)001:7091: slob dpon nyid dkyil 'khor du 'jug par bya ste bdag 'jug ces kyang bya //
NK053('i)001:7092: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK053('i)001:7093: thugs rje khros pas rngam pa'i tshogs //
NK053('i)001:7094: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK053('i)001:7095: de nyid du ni bdag la stsol //
NK053('i)001:7096: zhes brjod nas rig pa'i me tog dor la /
NK053('i)001:7097: de blangs nas bdag gi spyi gtsug tu bzhag pas
NK053('i)001:7098: lha rnams bdag la gnyis su med par bstim mo
NK053('i)001:7099: // de nas rgyal thebs rang karmasa /
NK053('i)001:7100: ma dal de'i steng du ras kha tshar ma nyams pa'i steng du r+ts+wa ku sha bting la /
NK053('i)001:7102: ras dar dmar po dang dkar po gnyis bting ba'i steng du /
NK053('i)001:7103: nyi zla pad+ma bris pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7104: gzungs ma mtshan dang ldan pa dang bcas te /
NK053('i)001:7105: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon la dbul bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:7106: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon gyis kyang /
NK053('i)001:7107: dpal khrag 'thung chen po he ru ka ji bzhin du gsang ba'i yum dang bcas par bsgoms la /
NK053('i)001:7108: phyi 'i stan ras bal gyi khong tshang can /
NK053('i)001:7109: nang gi stan zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi /
NK053('i)001:7110: gsang ba'i stan yum mtshan dang ldan ma gsum gyi stan la bde bar gnas par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:7111: gnyis pa slob ma'i gnas tshul ni /
NK053('i)001:7112: de nas dam nod pa'i slob ma yang /
NK053('i)001:7113: nub phyogs kyi sgor gdan la pad+ma bris pa'i steng du gnas par byas la /
NK053('i)001:7114: dbyangs snyan pa dang bcas pas /
NK053('i)001:7115: lha dang slob dpon mi gnyis par bltas te /
NK053('i)001:7116: phyag btsal zhing phyi nang gi mchod pas mnyes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:7117: de la dbang bskur ba'i thabs dang rim pa la don gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:7118: dbang rang gi ngo bo 1 dang /
NK053('i)001:7121: de la skabs bcu pa slob dpon gyis slob ma
NK053('i)001:7122: snod dang ldan pa la phyi nang gsang ba gsum
NK053('i)001:7124: lung dgu las lnga pa dam tshig dbang gi lung /
NK053('i)001:7125: dal dgu las lnga pa dbang bskur ba'i dkyil 'khor /
NK053('i)001:7126: mtha' drug las dbang yo byad gnyis ka'o //
NK053('i)001:7128: 1 dbang rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK053('i)001:7130: byang chub kyi sems chos skur /
NK053('i)001:7131: shes pas nus pa khyad par can yod pa'o /
NK053('i)001:7134: shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin te /
NK053('i)001:7135: slob dpon dang slob ma gnyis ka la ldan pa la /
NK053('i)001:7136: gsang sngags kyi tshul gyis bskur ba rags las pa yin te /
NK053('i)001:7137: de yang bla ma'i blo la shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin khyad par can yod pa de /
NK053('i)001:7138: slob ma'i rgyud la bsgos la btang ba ni dbang bskur zhes bya'o /
NK053('i)001:7144: gsang ba'i dbang dang rdzogs pa'i dbang bzhi'o //
NK053('i)001:7145: de la ni sku'i dbang dang /
