NK053('i)001:7148: rdzogs pa'i dbang zhes kyang bshad /
NK053('i)001:7150: nus pa'i dbang zhes kyang bshad do /
NK053('i)001:7152: 1 / de la dang po phyi'i dbang bskur ba la don bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:7153: dang po dbang ji ltar babs pa'i gleng gzhi dang /
NK053('i)001:7154: tshul ji ltar byung ba'i tshul du dbang bskur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:7155: dbang thob pa'i yon tan dang /
NK053('i)001:7156: dbang ma thob pa'i skyon no /
NK053('i)001:7158: 1 / de la dbang dang po ji ltar babs pa'i gleng gzhi ni gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:7159: rdo rje'i tshul du dbang dag sbyin //
NK053('i)001:7161: de gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i tshul du dbang dag par byin pa'i /
NK053('i)001:7162: dbang dang po ji ltar babs pa'i tshul lam gleng gzhi ni /
NK053('i)001:7164: bcom ldan 'das rnam par snang mdzad /
NK053('i)001:7165: sangs rgyas kyi zhing rdul phra mo snyed kyi de
NK053('i)001:7166: bzhin gshegs pa nam mkha'i dbyings dang mnyam pa'i de
NK053('i)001:7167: bzhin gshegs pas / btsun mo'i b+ha ga la dam
NK053('i)001:7168: tshig chen po'i dkyil 'khor gru bzhir byin gyis brlabs
NK053('i)001:7169: bzhin gshegs pas / pa'i / bcom ldan 'das de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis /
NK053('i)001:7170: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang gsung dang thugs kyi bdag po de /
NK053('i)001:7171: dbang gis yongs su mnyes par bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:7172: nyid kyi sku bud med kyi gzugs su sprul nas gnas par gyur to //
NK053('i)001:7173: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung thugs kyi bdag po de /
NK053('i)001:7174: de bzhin gshes pa thams cad kyis dkyil 'khor gyi dbus su bzhag pa gyur to //
NK053('i)001:7175: de nas bcom ldan 'das mi bskyod pa la sogs pa rigs lnga /
NK053('i)001:7176: byang chub kyi sems rdo rje de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi thugs la zhugs so //
NK053('i)001:7177: de'i tshe nam mkha'i dbyings thams cad rdo rje'i ngo bor gnas par gyur to //
NK053('i)001:7178: de nas bcom ldan 'das byang chub kyi sems rdo
NK053('i)001:7179: rje de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku gsung
NK053('i)001:7180: thugs mnyam pa nyid 'byung ba zhes bya ba'i ting
NK053('i)001:7181: nge 'dzin la snyoms par zhugs nas /
NK053('i)001:7182: rig pa'i skyes bu chen po'i gzugs /
NK053('i)001:7183: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi bdag po 'di byin gyis brlabs so //
NK053('i)001:7184: byin gyis brlabs ma thag tu /
NK053('i)001:7185: byang chub kyi sems rdo rje de bzhin gshegs pa zhal gsum phyag drug pa lta bur /
NK053('i)001:7186: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis gzigs par gyur to //
NK053('i)001:7187: de'i tshe nam mkha'i dbyings na gnas pa'i sems can ji snyed pa dag /
NK053('i)001:7188: byang chub kyi sems rdo rjes byin gyis brlabs kyis
NK053('i)001:7189: bde ba dang yid bde ba thob par gyur to
NK053('i)001:7190: // de nas bcom ldan 'das rdo rje mi bskyod
NK053('i)001:7191: pa la sogs de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad ngo
NK053('i)001:7192: // mtshar che ste / gsang ba byang chub sems kyi dbang la ngam zhing bstod do //
NK053('i)001:7194: tshul de bzhin du rgyal bu don thams cad grub pa la yang dbang bskur te /
NK053('i)001:7196: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad 'dus te /
NK053('i)001:7197: byang chub sems dpa' don thams cad rab tu grub pa zhes bya ba /
NK053('i)001:7198: byang chub kyi snying por zhugs pa ga na ba der gshegs te /
NK053('i)001:7199: byang chub sems dpa' de la ched du /
NK053('i)001:7200: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i skur bstan nas /
NK053('i)001:7202: rigs kyi bu khyod gang gi phyir /
NK053('i)001:7203: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi de kho na nyid rtogs bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:7204: dka' ba sna tshogs spyad par spro ba bskyed cing /
NK053('i)001:7205: ji ltar bla na med pa yang dag par rdzogs pa'i byang chub par bya snyam /
NK053('i)001:7207: de nas byang chub sems dpa' don thams cad grub pa'i rgyal bu de /
NK053('i)001:7208: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyis dbang bskur ba rig nas /
NK053('i)001:7209: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:7212: bcom ldan 'das kyis byang chub sems dpa' phyag na
NK053('i)001:7213: rdo rje lho phyogs kyi shing sa la'i drung gyad
NK053('i)001:7214: kyi yul stobs can du dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:7215: byang chub sems dpa' phyag na rdo rjes dbang gsum du gyes par gyur te /
NK053('i)001:7216: za hor gyi yul ri me ri 'bar ba'i rtser /
NK053('i)001:7217: za hor gyi rgyal po in+t+ra bu ti dang /
NK053('i)001:7219: rgyal po u ru sha ne la phyi nang gsang ba'i tshul du dbang bskur /
NK053('i)001:7220: ri gnam lcags ma la ya'i rtser /
NK053('i)001:7223: khyi'i mkhan po ku ku r+aa tsa la sku gsung thugs kyi tshul du dbang bskur /
NK053('i)001:7224: rgya gar gyi yul chu bo 'ga' 'ag'i gang+ga'i 'gram du /
NK053('i)001:7226: dge slong so kya de ba dang /
NK053('i)001:7227: bal mo mang+ga la si ta la sku gsung thugs kyi tshul du dbang bskur te /
NK053('i)001:7228: slob dpon de rnams kyis rgya gar gyi yul ma
NK053('i)001:7229: gtad slob dpon h'u kar la dbang rdzogs par bskur
NK053('i)001:7230: ro // de nas slob dpon h'u ka ra dang /
NK053('i)001:7231: rdo rje bzhad pa gnyis kyis /
NK053('i)001:7232: rgya gar gyi yul sh+ai len n+aa len 'drar /
NK053('i)001:7233: dar slob dpon pad+ma sam+b+ha la dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:7235: slob dpon h'u ka ra sa gnas de nya da du /
NK053('i)001:7236: gnubs nam mkha'i snying po la sogs pa'i dge slong mi lnga ru gyong bid+yara tsa /
NK053('i)001:7238: gru gu e bag sha rlangs dpal gyi seng ge la dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:7240: mching phu bre gu dge'u ru /
NK053('i)001:7241: rje 'bangs nyi shu rtsa lnga la phyi nang gsang ba'i lugs su dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:7242: rje 'bangs nyi shu rtsa lnga la /
NK053('i)001:7245: gsang mtshan tshangs pa lha'i me tog /
NK053('i)001:7254: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku ma ra /
NK053('i)001:7258: b+ha mang so rje lha legs /
NK053('i)001:7262: 'gos khri bzang yab lhag grub pa rtsal /
NK053('i)001:7266: shud bu dpal gyi seng ge /
NK053('i)001:7268: glang chen dpal gyi seng ge /
NK053('i)001:7274: mkhar chen dpal gyi dbang phyug rdo rje grub pa rtsal /
NK053('i)001:7277: ngan lam rgyal ba mchog dbyangs /
NK053('i)001:7279: spa gor bee ro tsa na /
NK053('i)001:7285: khams gsum dbang sdud rdo rje mos pa rtsal /
NK053('i)001:7286: sna nam bza' nam mkha'i lha mo /
NK053('i)001:7288: shel dkar bza' rdo rje mtsho /
NK053('i)001:7294: seng mgo bza' dpal gyi sgron ma /
NK053('i)001:7301: gnyags gnya' na ku m+aa ra la dbang bskur /
NK053('i)001:7303: nam mkha'i snying pos dbang bskur ba'i /
NK053('i)001:7305: mkhar chen bza' mtsho rgyal gyis /
NK053('i)001:7306: slob dpon gnya' na la dbang bskur /
NK053('i)001:7307: gnya' na la dbang gi bka' bzhi babs so //
NK053('i)001:7309: sog po lha dpal gyi ye shes la dbang bskur /
NK053('i)001:7310: des bdag sangs rgyas ye shes rin po che la dbang bskur /
NK053('i)001:7311: bdag gis slad nas kyang bal yul du /
NK053('i)001:7312: bal po ba su d+ha ra la dbang zhus /
NK053('i)001:7313: dbang dang man ngag thag bcad do //
NK053('i)001:7314: dbang babs pa dang brgyud pa'i rim pa'o //
NK053('i)001:7316: 'di bar gyi dkyus yig chen rnams gnubs chen sangs
NK053('i)001:7317: rgyas ye shes kyis zhal skong mdzad par mngon no
NK053('i)001:7319: gnubs sangs rgyas ye shes kyis /
NK053('i)001:7321: gzhan su la yang ma gnang bar /
NK053('i)001:7322: phyis khab tu bzhes pa'i jo mo 'bro mo rin chen sgron ma la chos 'di gnang /
NK053('i)001:7324: des sras mchog rab grags la /
NK053('i)001:7326: des khyung po ye shes rgyal mtshan /
NK053('i)001:7327: des gru gu blo gros bzang po la /
NK053('i)001:7328: des zla shes rab bzang po la /
NK053('i)001:7329: des thod pa rgya 'brug grags pa la /
NK053('i)001:7330: des phyag ston rdo rje rga la /
NK053('i)001:7332: des sras khu 'dzi tshes rgyal mtshan la /
NK053('i)001:7334: des sras slung nam mkha' rtog med la dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:7335: des sras slung ban rat+na la /
NK053('i)001:7336: des sras slung ban kro d+ha la /
NK053('i)001:7337: des bdag rang slung gi ban+de bsam 'grub 'bum zhes
NK053('i)001:7338: bya ba rat+na'i tsha bo la phan pa'i dbang dang
NK053('i)001:7339: nus pa'i dbang lnga dang bcas pa ma lus pa
NK053('i)001:7340: zhal dbang dang zhabs dbang yang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:7341: 'di'i mchan rnying rnams bsam 'grub 'bum gyi yin 'dra snyam /
NK053('i)001:7342: 2 tshul ci lta bu'i tshul du dbang bskur ba la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:7343: phyag na rdo rje'i tshul du dbang bskur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:7344: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal po'i tshul du dbang bskur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:7345: gsang sngags thabs kyi rdo rje theg pa'i tshul du dbang bskur ba'o //
NK053('i)001:7346: de la der gsang sngags thabs kyi rdo rje theg pa'i tshul du dbang bskur ba 'byung ste /
NK053('i)001:7347: de yang gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:7348: rdo rje'i tshul du dbang dag sbyin //
NK053('i)001:7350: gsang ba'i rgyud mtha' dag las /
NK053('i)001:7351: bum pa'i dbang dang por bskur ba 'byung ste /
NK053('i)001:7355: dang po rig pa'i me tog dor ba'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:7356: sku gsung thugs rdo rje ltar byin gyis brlabs pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:7359: me tog gi 'phreng ba'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:7362: rdo rje dril bu'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:7363: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:7364: bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:7365: sha rnam pa lnga'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:7366: rdo rje ming gi dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:7367: bsgrub rdzas lha cha lnga'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:7369: rdo rje phur bu'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:7371: rgyal po'i bka' rtags kyi dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:7372: bcu bdun gyis bskur bar 'byung ste /
NK053('i)001:7374: sngon du 'gro bas byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7376: de la dbang 'di rnams bskur ba'i tshe /
NK053('i)001:7380: bsang gtor byas pa de la lus la spos dri zhim po dang /
NK053('i)001:7381: sman bzang pos byug ba dang /
NK053('i)001:7382: dar dang ras la sogs pa gsar ba yugs ma nyams pas lus bskon te /
NK053('i)001:7383: bla ma rdo rje rgyal po yab yum dang /
NK053('i)001:7385: gar mas rang bzhin lhun grub gyis nam mkha'i khams gang bar bsams la /
NK053('i)001:7386: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa /
NK053('i)001:7387: zhi khro 'bar ba'i lha tshogs kyis /
NK053('i)001:7388: bdag dang slob mar bcas pa la /
NK053('i)001:7389: ye shes bla na med pa'i dbang bskur du gsol //
NK053('i)001:7392: rnga dang cang te'u brdung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:7393: cha lang dang pheg brdab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7395: pi wam sbreng ba la sogs pa bya ste /
NK053('i)001:7397: glu drug gis gzi byin bskyed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7398: ye shes kyi lha tshogs thugs rje chen po dang ldan pa rnams /
NK053('i)001:7399: sngon gyi thugs dam gyi dbang gis byon pa rnams /
NK053('i)001:7400: bdag slob mar bcas pa la bkra shis par mdzad du gsol /
NK053('i)001:7401: legs so rgyal bar gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:7404: de nas slob ma de'i rgyud byin gyis brlabs pa yang /
NK053('i)001:7405: sngar yi dam gyi lha yod na yang /
NK053('i)001:7406: de'i yig 'bru phyag rgya la spros te snying gar bstims la /
NK053('i)001:7407: de nas sngags brjod pas lha'i skur byin gyis brlabs so //
NK053('i)001:7408: de med na me tog dor ba'i lha gang la bab pa'am /
NK053('i)001:7411: dpal khrag 'thung chen po'i rang bzhin du byin gyis brlabs pa yang /
NK053('i)001:7414: shes pa'i rgyud dag par sbyangs pa'i rig pa ci yang ma yin pa de /
NK053('i)001:7415: yi ge h'u gi rang bzhin du sa ler gsal ba las /
NK053('i)001:7416: ye shes sems dpa' tshon gang bar bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:7417: gnyis pa dbang bskur ba dngos ni /
NK053('i)001:7418: de las zhi khro gang 'dod kyi rtsa ba'i sngags kyis /
NK053('i)001:7419: sku phyag rgya chen por lhag gis bskyed do /
NK053('i)001:7421: 1 / de nas gang du me tog dor ba de /
NK053('i)001:7422: lha gang la bab pa brtags la /
NK053('i)001:7423: de lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas blangs la /
NK053('i)001:7426: sngon tshe tshe rabs grangs med nas //
NK053('i)001:7427: dge ba'i las kyis bsten pa'i lha //
NK053('i)001:7428: lhag pa'i lha ni gang yin pa //
NK053('i)001:7429: da lta nyid du khyod la dbab //
NK053('i)001:7432: lha de nyid kyi sngags dang phyag rgyas bstims pas /
NK053('i)001:7433: lha de nyid slob ma zhugs par gyur te /
NK053('i)001:7435: 'di ni rig pa'i me tog dor ba'i dbang ste /
NK053('i)001:7436: ye shes kyi lha dbang zhes bya'o /
NK053('i)001:7438: 2 / de nas sku gsung thugs rdo rje ltar byin gyis brlabs pa'i dbang ni /
NK053('i)001:7445: dpal ldan rdo rje sku 'chang ba //
NK053('i)001:7446: rdo rje mi phyed gsum bsgoms nas //
NK053('i)001:7447: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK053('i)001:7448: rdo rje sku yis mdzad du gsol //
NK053('i)001:7450: klad pa dung khang gi gzhal yas khang du /
NK053('i)001:7454: rnam par snang mdzad bskyed de /
NK053('i)001:7455: thugs ka na chos kyi 'khor lo dang bcas par bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:7456: de la ye shes dbab pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:7457: dbyangs 'dis gsol ba gdab par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:7459: / phyogs bcur bzhugs pa'i bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:7460: rdo rje mi phyed du sku bsgoms nas //
NK053('i)001:7461: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK053('i)001:7462: rdo rje sku yis mdzad du gsol //
NK053('i)001:7464: sku'i rigs thams cad ye shes kyi 'od zer du gyur nas /
NK053('i)001:7465: spyi bo tshangs pa'i bu ga nas mar babs te /
NK053('i)001:7466: rnam par snang mdzad la dbang bskur /
NK053('i)001:7467: de las ye shes kyi 'od zer byung bas /
NK053('i)001:7468: lus mgo mjug la khyabs te /
NK053('i)001:7469: lus ngan pa'i bag chags dag nas /
NK053('i)001:7470: ye shes kyi skur gsal bar bsgom zhing /
NK053('i)001:7471: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:7474: slob ma khyod la sku'i dbang bskur bas /
NK053('i)001:7475: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs thams cad khyod la zhugs par gyur te /
NK053('i)001:7476: lus ngan pa'i bag chags byang zhing dag nas /
NK053('i)001:7477: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mtshan bzang po sum cu rtsa gnyis dang /
NK053('i)001:7478: dpe byad bzang po brgyad cus brgyan pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:7479: ces ngag tu brjod cing ting nges kyang bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:7480: de nas gsung gi dbang bskur te /
NK053('i)001:7482: chos kyi ngag lam dpal dang ldan //
NK053('i)001:7483: rdo rje mi phyed gsum bsgoms nas //
NK053('i)001:7484: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK053('i)001:7485: rdo rje gsung gis mdzad du gsol //
NK053('i)001:7488: a mi d+he ba h+r+aih zhes brjod pas /
NK053('i)001:7489: snang ba mtha' yas bskyed de /
NK053('i)001:7490: snang mtha'i thugs ka na chos kyi 'khor lo dang bcas par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:7491: de la ye shes dbab pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:7492: dbyangs 'dis gsol ba gdab par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:7494: / phyogs bcur bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK053('i)001:7495: rdo rje mi phyed gsung bsgoms nas //
NK053('i)001:7496: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK053('i)001:7497: rdo rje gsung gis mdzad du gsol //
NK053('i)001:7499: gsung gi rigs thams cad phyogs bcu nas 'dus shing 'od zer du gyur nas /
NK053('i)001:7500: lce steng nas mgrin par thim ste snang ba mtha' yas la dbang bskur /
NK053('i)001:7501: de las ye shes kyi 'od zer byung bas /
NK053('i)001:7502: ngag ngan pa'i bag chags byang zhing dag nas /
NK053('i)001:7503: ye shes kyi gsung dang ldan par bsgoms te /
NK053('i)001:7504: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aak+ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:7506: slob ma khyod la gsung gi dbang bskur bas /
NK053('i)001:7507: pad+ma'i rigs thams cad khyod la zhugs par gyur te /
NK053('i)001:7508: ngag ngan pa'i bag chags byang zhing dag nas /
NK053('i)001:7509: gsung dbyangs yan lag drug cu dang ldan pas /
NK053('i)001:7510: 'gro ba thams cad la so so'i skad du chos sgrogs shing ston nus pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7511: bzlas brjod byed pa'i dbang dang ldan pas gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:7512: ces ngag gis brjod bsam par bya /
NK053('i)001:7513: de nas thugs kyi dbang bskur te /
NK053('i)001:7515: dpal ldan rdo rje thugs 'chang ba //
NK053('i)001:7516: rdo rje mi phyed gsum bsgoms pas //
NK053('i)001:7517: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK053('i)001:7518: rdo rje thugs kyis mdzad du gsol //
NK053('i)001:7520: snying ga'i h'u mthing ka las /
NK053('i)001:7523: tsit+ta rin po che'i gzhal yas khang du /
NK053('i)001:7524: rdo rje sems dpas kyang bya /
NK053('i)001:7525: ye shes sems dpas kyang bya /
NK053('i)001:7526: rang byung rig pa'i dpal zhes kyang bya ba bskyed de /
NK053('i)001:7527: de'i thugs ka na yang chos kyi 'khor lo dang bcas pa bskyed de /
NK053('i)001:7528: de la ye shes dbab pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:7529: dbyangs 'dis gsol ba gdab par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:7531: phyogs bcur bzhugs pa'i sangs rgyas rnams //
NK053('i)001:7532: rdo rje mi phyed thugs bsgoms pas //
NK053('i)001:7533: deng bdag byin gyis brlabs nas su //
NK053('i)001:7534: rdo rje thugs kyis mdzad du gsol //
NK053('i)001:7536: thugs kyi rigs thams cad phyogs bcu nas 'dus shing 'od zer du gyur nas /
NK053('i)001:7537: snying gar thim ste ye shes sems dpa' la dbang bskur /
NK053('i)001:7538: de las ye shes kyi 'od zer byung ste /
NK053('i)001:7539: yid ngan pa'i bag chags dag nas /
NK053('i)001:7540: thugs ye shes lnga dang ldan par bsgom zhing /
NK053('i)001:7541: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:7545: thugs ye shes su dbang bskur bas /
NK053('i)001:7546: rdo rje'i rigs thams cad khyod la zhugs par gyur te /
NK053('i)001:7547: khyod kyi yid ngan pa'i bag chags byang zhing dag nas /
NK053('i)001:7548: thugs ye shes lnga dang ldan pas /
NK053('i)001:7549: ji ltar bsam pa bzhin grub pa'i dbang dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:7550: ces ngag tu brjod cing ting nges kyang bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:7552: dbang thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro ba yin te /
NK053('i)001:7553: phyi'i dus su ni +aahmh'u gsum re re bris pa'i ri mo tsaka li la brten te bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:7554: nang gi dus su ni bdud rtsi a mri ta la brten te bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:7555: gsang ba'i dus su ni gsang ba'i byang chub sems
NK053('i)001:7556: dngos sam dkar dmar ril bu la brten te bskur
NK053('i)001:7558: de nas bum pa'i dbang bskur ba ste /
NK053('i)001:7559: gong du bsnyen pa byas pa'i zhi khro gnyis kyi
NK053('i)001:7560: bum pa res mos blangs shing bskur bar bya ste
NK053('i)001:7563: chos dbyings yum gyi bum pa na //
NK053('i)001:7564: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor pho brang bzhugs //
NK053('i)001:7565: gnyis med byang chub sems rtags chus //
NK053('i)001:7566: phyi nas gtibs shing dbang bskur bas //
NK053('i)001:7567: khyod kyi bag chags byang gyur nas //
NK053('i)001:7568: lus la sangs rgyas bltams par shog /
NK053('i)001:7570: zhi khro lha so so'i snying po la /
NK053('i)001:7571: k+aa la sha a be sha a /
NK053('i)001:7573: lha rnams so sor byang chub sems kyi 'od zer du zhu nas /
NK053('i)001:7574: slob ma'i spyi gtsug nas mar thim zhing /
NK053('i)001:7575: nye bar len pa'i phung po zag pa dang bcas pa'i bag chags dag ste /
NK053('i)001:7576: ye shes kyi sku la nag nog gi dri ma bral nas /
NK053('i)001:7577: shes sgong phyis pa ltar gyur te /
NK053('i)001:7578: zag pa med pa'i sku dang ldan par byin gyis brlab bo //
NK053('i)001:7579: smon lam yang de bzhin du gdab po /
NK053('i)001:7581: 4 / de nas rigs lnga dbu rgyan gyi dbang bskur te /
NK053('i)001:7583: khro bo'i thod pa'i phreng ba'i dbu rgyan dang //
NK053('i)001:7584: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas gtsug gi nor bu can //
NK053('i)001:7585: kun nas nyon mongs 'jig rten dbang //
NK053('i)001:7586: mi mjed la sogs de grub pas //
NK053('i)001:7587: ye shes lnga ldan dbu rgyan 'di //
NK053('i)001:7588: khyod la dbang mchog bskur bar bya //
NK053('i)001:7589: ma h+aa shu nya t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:7590: ma h+aa a dar+sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:7591: ma h+aa sa ma t+aa dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+ha lwa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:7592: ma h+aa pra t+ya be k+sha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra s+w+aa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:7593: ma h+aa kri t+ya nush+tha na dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:7595: sku lnga'i ye shes lnga 'od zer gyis /
NK053('i)001:7596: dug lnga'i nyes pa byang zhing dag nas /
NK053('i)001:7597: 'gro ba kun gyi dpal mgon du gyur par bsam zhing /
NK053('i)001:7598: smon lam yang de ltar gdab bo //
NK053('i)001:7599: de nas cod pan gyis dbang bskur te /
NK053('i)001:7601: bag chags nyes pa'i skyon bral zhing //
NK053('i)001:7602: 'khor ba'i nyes pa ma gos pa'i //
NK053('i)001:7603: ye shes lnga ldan cod pan 'di //
NK053('i)001:7604: khyod la dbang mchog bskur ba bya //
NK053('i)001:7605: badz+ra sa t+wa lam ba na a b+hi shiny+tsa h+r+aih zhes brjod de /
NK053('i)001:7606: zhi gnas dang lhag mthong zung du 'brel cing /
NK053('i)001:7607: shes bya la thogs pa med pa'i dbang dang ldan par bsam zhing /
NK053('i)001:7608: smon lam yang de ltar gdab bo /
NK053('i)001:7610: 5 / de nas me tog gi phreng ba'i dbang bskur te /
NK053('i)001:7612: 'di ni rin chen phreng ba ste //
NK053('i)001:7613: rin chen rgyu las byas pa yi //
NK053('i)001:7614: byang chub yan lag phreng ba 'dis //
NK053('i)001:7616: bsam pa yid bzhin grub pa dang //
NK053('i)001:7617: lam la bar chad med par dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:7618: badz+ra rat+na ma le a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK053('i)001:7622: bsam pa yid bzhin bsgrub pa la /
NK053('i)001:7624: byang chub kyi yan lag bdun gyi ngo bor gyur cing dbang thob par bsam la /
NK053('i)001:7625: smon lam yang de ltar gdab bo /
NK053('i)001:7627: 6 / de nas phyag rgya'i dbang bskur bar bya ste /
NK053('i)001:7629: 'di ni phyag rgya'i dbang mchog ste //
NK053('i)001:7630: lha'i sku chos rnams sku gsung thugs kyi dbang //
NK053('i)001:7631: phyag rgya chen chen po'i rang bzhin du //
NK053('i)001:7632: rtag tu bsgom zhing bsgrub par gyis //
NK053('i)001:7634: rigs lnga spyi yi phyag rgyas bcings nas /
NK053('i)001:7635: bud+d+ha mu dra a b+hi shiny+tsa /
NK053('i)001:7636: zhes bya ba la sogs pa /
NK053('i)001:7638: h'u badz+ra mu dra a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u /
NK053('i)001:7639: s+w+aa rat+na mu dra a b+hi shiny+tsa s+w+aa /
NK053('i)001:7640: +aamhpad+ma mu dra a b+hi shiny+tsa amh h+aa karma mu dra a b+hi shiny+tsa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:7642: sku lnga ye shes lnga'i thugs ka nas /
NK053('i)001:7643: rang rang gi lha sku'i phyag rgya gsal te /
NK053('i)001:7644: de las ye shes kyi 'od zer byung bas /
NK053('i)001:7645: slob ma'i sgrib pa'i d+r+wa ba rgyun bcad nas /
NK053('i)001:7646: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i phyag rgya dang ldan par bsam zhing /
NK053('i)001:7647: smon lam yang de bzhin du gdab bo /
NK053('i)001:7649: 7 / de nas b+han+d+hasa dbang bskur te /
NK053('i)001:7650: rigs bzang gi b+han+d+ha mtshan ldan la /
NK053('i)001:7652: de las yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che bsam la /
NK053('i)001:7655: chos nyid spros bral rdo rje ka p+aa la //
NK053('i)001:7656: sku lnga lhun rdzogs rdo rje ka p+aa la //
NK053('i)001:7657: ye shes lnga ldan rdo rje ka p+aa la //
NK053('i)001:7658: sku gsum ldan pa'i rdo rje ka p+aa la //
NK053('i)001:7659: mi 'gyur g.yung drung rdo rje ka p+aa la //
NK053('i)001:7660: yid gzhin gter ldan rdo rje ka p+aa la //
NK053('i)001:7661: skal ldan khyod la dbang mchog 'di bskul bas //
NK053('i)001:7662: ci bsam 'grub pa'i dbang mchog thob par shog /
NK053('i)001:7663: badz+ra ka p+aa la rat+na tre lo kya a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah zhes brjod de /
NK053('i)001:7664: b+han+d+ha bkra shis yid bzhin gyi nor bu lta bu las ye shes kyi 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:7665: slob ma'i dri ma dag nas /
NK053('i)001:7668: b+han+d+ha nyid nor bu rin po che lta bu de snying gar bstims pas /
NK053('i)001:7669: yid la ci ltar bsam pa 'grub par 'gyur te /
NK053('i)001:7670: smon lam yang de ltar gdab bo //
NK053('i)001:7671: gzhan yang rang 'dod pa'i las bsgyur zhing dbang bskur ro /
NK053('i)001:7673: 8 / rdo rje dril bu'i dbang ni /
NK053('i)001:7675: nyon mongs 'joms pa'i rdo rje dang //
NK053('i)001:7676: chos sgra sgrogs pa'i dril bu 'dis //
NK053('i)001:7677: de ring khyod la dbang bskur bas //
NK053('i)001:7678: thabs dang shes rab 'brel bar shog /
NK053('i)001:7679: badz+ra gan+d+he a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah zhes brjod de /
NK053('i)001:7680: rdo rje h'u dang dril bu a las bskyed de byin pas /
NK053('i)001:7682: rtags thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel ba'i dbang ste /
NK053('i)001:7683: smon lam yang de bzhin du gdab po /
NK053('i)001:7685: 9 / 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i dbang ni /
NK053('i)001:7688: gzugs sogs bud med lha mo'i tshogs //
NK053('i)001:7689: 'dod pa lnga yi yon tan dag /
NK053('i)001:7690: chos nyid kyi ni rgyan yin pas //
NK053('i)001:7691: dga' mgur spyod pa'i dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:7692: na mo ha ra gu na pany+tsa a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah zhes brjod de /
NK053('i)001:7693: theg pa 'og ma pas bkag pa yang /
NK053('i)001:7694: gsang sngags kyis dang du blangs te /
NK053('i)001:7695: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i lha mor dmigs nas spyad pas /
NK053('i)001:7696: ye shes chen po chos kyi dbyings la 'jug pa'i dbang ste /
NK053('i)001:7697: smon lam yang de ltar gdab bo /
NK053('i)001:7699: 10 / de nas bdud rtsi lnga'i dbang ni /
NK053('i)001:7701: b+han+d+ha bcud yangs zab pa na //
NK053('i)001:7702: khor yug gtogs pa'i snod bcud kun //
NK053('i)001:7703: bdud rtsi lnga yi rang bzhin pas //
NK053('i)001:7704: rtag tu za byed zhal du bstim //
NK053('i)001:7705: +aahmh'u sarba pany+tsa a mri ta a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah zhes brjod de /
NK053('i)001:7706: dpa' bo 'bru +aahmh'u s+w+aah+aa lngas byin gyis brlabs te phul bas /
NK053('i)001:7707: bdag gzhan gyi rnam par rtog pa sbyong zhing /
NK053('i)001:7708: mchog dang thun mong gis bsdus pa'i dngos grub bsgrub pa'i gzhi ma bdud rtsi lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:7709: smon lam yang de ltar gdab bo //
NK053('i)001:7710: so so'i yon tan yang brjod cing sbyin no //
NK053('i)001:7716: rigs lnga so so'i yon tan brjod do /
NK053('i)001:7718: 11 / sha rnam pa lnga'i dbang ni /
NK053('i)001:7721: mngon shes lnga la sogs pa yi //
NK053('i)001:7722: thun mong dngos grub ji snyed dang //
NK053('i)001:7723: rig 'dzin gtso bor bsgrub pa yi //
NK053('i)001:7724: dngos grub 'grub byed rdzas lcags kyu lta bu lnga yis dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:7725: sha lnga bdud rtsi lnga la sgron ma lnga dang
NK053('i)001:7726: lcags kyu lnga'i ming gsal 'dus las kyang bshad do
NK053('i)001:7727: // +aahmh'u ma h+aa m+aam sa a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah zhes brjod de /
NK053('i)001:7728: yum lnga'i yig 'bru m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam /
NK053('i)001:7729: lngas byin gyis brlabs te byin pas /
NK053('i)001:7733: rig 'dzin gyi gtso bor bsgub pa'i dbang ste /
NK053('i)001:7734: smon lam yang de ltar gdab bo /
NK053('i)001:7736: 12 / bsgrub rdzas lha cha lnga'i dbang ni /
NK053('i)001:7737: rgyud las 'byung ba bzhin du bskur ro /
NK053('i)001:7740: 14pa rtsa t+wang rtsa'i dbang gi don mtshon byed /
NK053('i)001:7743: rdo rje kha tram 'di byin pas //
NK053('i)001:7744: rtsa gsum gyis rtsa dbu rkyang ro gsum sku gsung mtshon /
NK053('i)001:7745: dril bu'i sgra ni gsol ba yis //
NK053('i)001:7746: chos dbyings skye med ming dbang mtshon /
NK053('i)001:7747: thams cad phab nas slar yang ni /
NK053('i)001:7748: khams gsum dag kyang 'tsho bar byed //
NK053('i)001:7749: +aahmh'u kha tram ga gan d+ha a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah zhes brjod de byin pas /
NK053('i)001:7751: sku gsum du slar 'tsho bar byed pa'i dbang ste /
NK053('i)001:7752: smon lam yang de ltar gdab bo /
NK053('i)001:7754: 15 / de nas phur bu'i dbang ni /
NK053('i)001:7755: bsnyen pa rdzogs pa'i phur pa blangs la /
NK053('i)001:7757: khro rgyal 'dus pa sras kyi mchog /
NK053('i)001:7758: sku gsung thugs su byin brlabs te //
NK053('i)001:7759: dgra bgegs 'joms pa'i mthu mnga' ba'i //
NK053('i)001:7760: phur bu 'di yis dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:7761: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba big nan bam h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:7762: a b+hi shiny+tsa h'u +aah zhes brjod de /
NK053('i)001:7763: rmad du byung ba'i phrin las kyis /
NK053('i)001:7764: gdug pa can gtan 'pho bar byed cing /
NK053('i)001:7765: khams gsum sgrol ba'i dbang ste /
NK053('i)001:7766: smon lam yang de ltar gdab bo /
NK053('i)001:7768: 16 / de nas tshe dbang bskur ba ni /
NK053('i)001:7770: sangs rgyas kun gyi bdag nyid kyi //
NK053('i)001:7771: rdo rje sems dpa'i tshe dang gzhon //
NK053('i)001:7772: de ring khyod la bskur bar bya //
NK053('i)001:7773: nad med bde mchog grub par shog /
NK053('i)001:7774: badz+ra a yu she punye punye ma h+aa punye ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:7776: tshes ni rgas rgud kyi sdug bsngal sel te /
NK053('i)001:7777: tshe dbang phun sum tshogs pa'i dbang ngo //
NK053('i)001:7778: smon lam yang de ltar gdab bo //
NK053('i)001:7779: dbang de rnams ni rgyud lung man ngag kun las
NK053('i)001:7780: btus shing dbang thams cad kyi sngon du 'gro bar
NK053('i)001:7782: de nas rgyal po bka' rtags kyi dbang bskur ba la bdun te /
NK053('i)001:7788: rin po che sna bdun dang /
NK053('i)001:7789: bkra shis kyi rdzas brgyad kyi dbang ngo //
NK053('i)001:7790: de rnams kyis bskur ba ni /
NK053('i)001:7791: rgyas par spros shes par byas la bskur ro /
NK053('i)001:7793: 3 / dbang 'di rnams thob pa'i yon tan ni /
NK053('i)001:7794: lus kyi dri ma dag nas /
NK053('i)001:7795: sa brgyad pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dang skal pa mnyam pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7796: lha bskyed pa'i rim pa la dbang thob cing /
NK053('i)001:7797: phrin las dang gsang sngags kyi bya ba la ma rmongs par 'jug pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7798: zhugs pas bdag don grub la gzhan la phan par nus pas /
NK053('i)001:7800: phyi'i dbang dang sku'i dbang zhes kyang bya'o /
NK053('i)001:7802: 4 / dbang 'di rnams ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK053('i)001:7803: gong ma'i don las bzlog ste mi 'grub pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7804: 'bras bu med cing 'khor ba'i gnas su sdug bsngal
NK053('i)001:7805: ba dang yun ring du thar bar mi 'gyur ro
NK053('i)001:7807: phyi nang gsang ba gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:7808: dbang rdzas rim par tshogs par byas te dbang bskur ba ni phyi'i 'o //
NK053('i)001:7809: de rnams ting nge 'dzin gyis bskur ba ni nang gi'o //
NK053('i)001:7810: de rnams kyi don shes shing blo la bsgom pa ni gsang ba'i dbang ngo //
NK053('i)001:7811: slob ma dkyil 'khor du bcug ste phyi'i dbang bskur ba zhes bya ba'i don to /
NK053('i)001:7813: 2 / de nas slob ma la nang gi dbang bskur ba la don bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:7814: yum shes rab ma brtag cing byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7815: gnyis su med pa'i sbyor ba brtsam pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7816: byang chub sems kyis dbang bskur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:7817: dbang 'di thob pa'i yon tan dang /
NK053('i)001:7818: ma thob pa'i skyon bstan pa'o /
NK053('i)001:7820: 1 / de la yum shes rab ma brtag cing byin gyis brlabs pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:7821: yum shes rab ma brtag cing dngos grub 'dod par gsol ba gdab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7822: bla mas bdag dang shes rab ma byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK053('i)001:7823: don de gnyis bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:7824: skabs sbyor dgu pa rigs kyi yum byin gyis brlab pa'i skabs /
NK053('i)001:7825: g.yon phyogs gnas la tshul bzhin du //
NK053('i)001:7826: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du sbyar //
NK053('i)001:7827: gar mkhan tshul 'dra sgyu ma'i rgya //
NK053('i)001:7828: de la 'ja' tshon bzhin du gsal //
NK053('i)001:7829: 'dod chags ye shes gsal ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:7831: thabs shes rgyal mor byin gyis brlab //
NK053('i)001:7833: de la 1yum shes rab ma de brtag cing slob
NK053('i)001:7834: mas dngos grub 'dod par gsol ba gdab pa gang
NK053('i)001:7835: snyam pa la / g.yon phyogs gnas la tshul bzhin du //
NK053('i)001:7837: yum shes rab ma de brtag pa yang /
NK053('i)001:7838: rtogs pa'i blo can slob ma des brtag par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:7840: yid 'ong bkra shis rigs kyi yum //
NK053('i)001:7841: zhes smos pa la bshad pa ltar brtags la /
NK053('i)001:7843: lus kyi mtshan nyid rtags dang ldan pa /
NK053('i)001:7844: ngag gi mtshan nyid dbyangs snyan /
NK053('i)001:7845: sems kyi mtshan nyid re dogs med /
NK053('i)001:7852: yon tan brgyad dang ldan pa'i bla ma de la dbul te /
NK053('i)001:7853: de yang bsgrub pa chen po'i dus su /
NK053('i)001:7854: shar phyogs su khri stan bde ba'i khar bla ma bzhugs /
NK053('i)001:7855: de'i g.yon phyogs su yum shes rab ma de dbul lo //
NK053('i)001:7856: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon gyis kyang /
NK053('i)001:7857: yum shes rab ma de la chos rgyu 'bras mi bslu ba'i gdams ngag nges par bshad de /
NK053('i)001:7858: ngag mnyan par gyur pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7859: gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor du bcug pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7860: sbyor thabs kyi gtsug lag la mkhas par gyis shig /
NK053('i)001:7862: gong du bsdad pa ltar phyi nang gi stan bde ba la yab yum gnas pa'i spyan sngar /
NK053('i)001:7863: slob mas dngos grub kyi don 'dod par byas pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:7865: gser dang g.yu la sogs pa'i me tog thogs la /
NK053('i)001:7867: ji ltar dus gsum rgyal ba yis //
NK053('i)001:7868: dam chos bdud rtsi'i char phab pas //
NK053('i)001:7869: skal ldan 'gro ba'i rgyud sbyangs shing //
NK053('i)001:7870: skal med kun gyi skyabs mdzad ltar //
NK053('i)001:7871: de ring rdo rje slob dpon gyi //
NK053('i)001:7872: zhabs la btud de zhu ba ni //
NK053('i)001:7873: bdag gi rgyud rnams sbyang ba dang //
NK053('i)001:7874: 'gro ba rnams la phan don du //
NK053('i)001:7875: sngon gyi rgyal bas mdzad pa bzhin //
NK053('i)001:7876: gsang ba'i dbang mchog bskur du gsol //
NK053('i)001:7878: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon gyis kyang /
NK053('i)001:7879: khyod nyid brtse bas gzung ba dang //
NK053('i)001:7880: 'gro kun byang chub thob bya'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:7881: dpal ldan bla ma bdag nyid kyis //
NK053('i)001:7882: khyod la dbang mchog sbyin par bya //
NK053('i)001:7885: shes rab ma de nyid lus khrus legs par byas la /
NK053('i)001:7886: dri zhim pos lus la byugs nas /
NK053('i)001:7887: zhi rtags rgyan gyis mdzes byas nas //
NK053('i)001:7889: lus la dar gos rgyan legs par byas te /
NK053('i)001:7892: thabs ni g.yas kyi phyogs su ste //
NK053('i)001:7893: de bzhin shes rab g.yon du'o //
NK053('i)001:7898: rnal 'byor nang pa'i lugs kyis phrin las rnam pa bzhi la /
NK053('i)001:7899: zhi rgyas dbang drag 'dug stangs kyi tshul re re yod pa las /
NK053('i)001:7900: 'dir sems bde ba la 'bebs pa yin pas /
NK053('i)001:7901: zhi ba'i tshul bzhin du 'dug par bya ba yin no //
NK053('i)001:7902: bla mas 2bdag dang yum shes rab ma gnyis byin gyis brlabs pa la gsum te /
NK053('i)001:7903: tha mal pa lha'i skur byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7904: lus la lha bkod de byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7905: ye shes kyi byin rlabs bsdus te byin gyis brlabs pa'o /
NK053('i)001:7907: 1 / de la tha mal pa lha'i skur byin gyis brlabs pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:7908: ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du sbyar //
NK053('i)001:7910: zhi ba la bdag nyid rdo rje sems dpa' 'am /
NK053('i)001:7911: khro bo la dpal chen po gang rung du bsgom pa'i g.yon na /
NK053('i)001:7912: mi yid du 'ong ba mo de /
NK053('i)001:7913: ji ltar 'dod pa'i yum kun tu bzang mo'am /
NK053('i)001:7914: kro ti shwa ri ma'i rang bzhin du /
NK053('i)001:7915: tha mal pa las lha'i skur sbyang zhing byin gyis brlab par bya ba yang /
NK053('i)001:7916: yum de'i rang bzhin gyis chos kyi dbyings mnyam pa nyid yin pa'i rtags su /
NK053('i)001:7917: de'i snying khar yi ge a dkar po gcig bsam la /
NK053('i)001:7918: de las 'od 'phros pas de'i nye bar len pa'i phung po bsregs sbyangs nas /
NK053('i)001:7920: a gcig pur gnas pa las /
NK053('i)001:7921: a de yang je chung je chung la mjug tu sgra tsam mo //
NK053('i)001:7922: sgra de yang mthar stong ste ci yang dmigs su med pa'i ngang du bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:7925: h'u mthing nag tshon gang ba gcig tu gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:7928: yum kro ti shwa ri ma'i rang bzhin du byin gyis brlabs bo /
NK053('i)001:7930: 2 / lus lha bkod de byin gyis brlabs pa la /
NK053('i)001:7932: zhi ba'i lha dgod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7934: de yang dkyus gcig la zur gnyis par bstan te /
NK053('i)001:7935: zhi ba'i lha bkod de byin gyis brlabs pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:7936: gar mkhan tshul 'dra sgyu ma'i rgya //
NK053('i)001:7937: de la 'ja' tshon bzhin du gsal //
NK053('i)001:7939: de la yab thabs kyi bdag nyid dpal rdo rje sems dpar gsal ba'i /
NK053('i)001:7940: spyi bor las rnam par snang mdzad la rigs bzhi'i sangs rgyas phyogs bzhir rdor sems /
NK053('i)001:7945: lce steng du am las snang ba mtha' yas la pad+ma'i rigs kyi sems dpa' chos kyi sems dpa' /
NK053('i)001:7949: bzhis bskor bar bsam pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7950: snying khar h'u las rdo rje sems dpa' la /
NK053('i)001:7951: rdo rje'i rigs kyi sems dpa' rdo rjes sems pa /
NK053('i)001:7955: bzhis bskor bar bsam pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7956: lte bar s+w+aa las rin po che 'byung ldan la /
NK053('i)001:7957: rin po che'i rigs kyi sems dpa' rdo rje rin chen /
NK053('i)001:7961: bzhis bskor bar bsam pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7962: gsang bar h+aa las don yod grub pa la /
NK053('i)001:7963: las kyi rigs kyi sems dpa' rdo rje las /
NK053('i)001:7967: bzhis bskor bar bsam pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7968: yan lag bzhi la h'u las khro bo bzhir lag g.yas gshin rje gshed /
NK053('i)001:7973: rigs so so'i snying pos byin gyis brlabs par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:7975: thabs kyi bdag nyid gnas lnga ru //
NK053('i)001:7976: dpa' bo 'bru lnga'i snying po la //
NK053('i)001:7977: rgyas btab byin brlabs dbang bskur nas //
NK053('i)001:7978: bde gshegs yab lnga'i dkyil 'khor gsal //
NK053('i)001:7980: de la yum shes rab ma kun tu bzang mor gsal ba de'i gnas lnga ru yang /
NK053('i)001:7982: sems ma bcu drug so sor bkod de bsgom pa dang /
NK053('i)001:7983: ni m+aum l+aam m+aam p+aam t+aam /
NK053('i)001:7985: spyi bor sangs rgyas spyan ma la yum chen bzhis bskor ba /
NK053('i)001:7987: snying khar rdo rje dbyings phyug ma /
NK053('i)001:7989: gsang bar dam tshig sgrol ma bcas yum re re la sems ma bzhi bzhis bskor ba'o //
NK053('i)001:7990: yan lag bzhi la sgo ma bzhi lag g.yas lcags kyu /
NK053('i)001:7994: de rnas rigs so so'i snying pos byin gyis brlabs par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:7996: de yi gzugs kyi phung po la //
NK053('i)001:7997: bde bar gshegs pa'i sa bon lnga //
NK053('i)001:7999: rgyas btab byin brlabs dbang bskur na //
NK053('i)001:8000: bder gshegs yum lnga'i dkyil 'khor gsal //
NK053('i)001:8003: spyi bo'i gtsug dang lce yi steng //
NK053('i)001:8004: nu ma'i bar dang lte ba'i steng //
NK053('i)001:8005: gsang gnas yan lag rnams su ni //
NK053('i)001:8006: yum lnga sems ma sgo ma dgod //
NK053('i)001:8008: de ltar byin gyis brlabs pa'i yab yum de'i spyod pa yang /
NK053('i)001:8009: gar mkhan gyi tshul dang 'dra bar /
NK053('i)001:8010: yab yum gcig la gcig mnyes par byed pa'i thabs sna tshogs stsol ba la mkhas pa /
NK053('i)001:8011: sgyu ma lta bu snang la rang bzhin med pa'i sku phyag rgyar bsgom pa de la /
NK053('i)001:8012: rigs lnga tshom bu lnga'i dkyil 'khor gcig la gcig mi bsgrib par /
NK053('i)001:8013: so so'i rang rang gi sku mdog dang phyag mtshan so sor gsal ba'i dpe ni /
NK053('i)001:8014: nam mkha'i 'ja' tshon bzhin du gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:8015: de la khro bo'i lha bkod de byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:8016: gar mkhan tshul 'dra sgyu ma'i rgya //
NK053('i)001:8017: de la 'ja' tshon bzhin du gsal //
NK053('i)001:8019: yab yum de gnyis tha mal pa las /
NK053('i)001:8020: lus sems gar yang bsgyur du btub pa'i dpe ni /
NK053('i)001:8021: gar mkhan gyi tshul ji lta ba dang 'dra ste /
NK053('i)001:8024: lha'i skur byin gyis brlabs pa de /
NK053('i)001:8025: gdos pa can ma yin zhing /
NK053('i)001:8026: sems kyi cho 'phrul du shar ba'i dpe ni sgyu ma dang 'dra la /
NK053('i)001:8027: de la bdag dpal chen por gsal ba'i /
NK053('i)001:8029: dpral bar rnam par rgyal pa /
NK053('i)001:8032: lte bar gshin rje gshed po /
NK053('i)001:8033: lag pa g.yas pa la khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba /
NK053('i)001:8035: rkang pa g.yas pa la gzhan gyis mi thub pa /
NK053('i)001:8037: gsang gnas su stobs po che /
NK053('i)001:8038: ba spu'i bu ga thams cad nas khro chung tshon gang ba mang pos gtams par bsgoms te /
NK053('i)001:8039: yum yang kro ti shwa ri mar gsal ba'i /
NK053('i)001:8042: lce stengs su pra mo ha /
NK053('i)001:8044: phrag pa g.yas pa la puk+ka si /
NK053('i)001:8045: phrag pa g.yon pa la kas ma ri /
NK053('i)001:8046: sta zur g.yas pa la sma sha ni /
NK053('i)001:8047: sta zur g.yon pa la tsan+d+ha li /
NK053('i)001:8048: dpung pa g.yas la sid+ha mu ka /
NK053('i)001:8049: dpung pa g.yon la b+y+aa g+h+ri mu ka /
NK053('i)001:8050: barla g.yas pa la sri la mu ka /
NK053('i)001:8051: barla g.yon pa la shwo na mu ka /
NK053('i)001:8052: lag ngar g.yas pa la kri ta mu ka /
NK053('i)001:8053: lag ngar g.yon pa la kang+ga mu ka /
NK053('i)001:8054: rje ngar g.yas pa la khwa khwa mu ka /
NK053('i)001:8055: rje ngar g.yon pa la hu lu mu ka /
NK053('i)001:8056: mkhrig ma g.yas pa la rta gdong ma /
NK053('i)001:8057: mkhrig ma g.yon pa la phag gdong ma /
NK053('i)001:8058: rkang bol g.yas pa la lcags sgrog ma /
NK053('i)001:8059: rkang bol g.yon pa la dril bu ma /
NK053('i)001:8060: sgal tshigs nas mar la dbang phyug ma /
NK053('i)001:8061: de ltar yab yum gyi sku re re la /
NK053('i)001:8062: ye shes kyi bye brag gi sku mang po shar ba'i dpe ni /
NK053('i)001:8063: nam mkha'i 'ja' tshon bzhin du snang la rang bzhin med pa /
NK053('i)001:8064: gsal la gdos pa med par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:8065: de ltar byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK053('i)001:8066: 3 ye shes kyi byin rlabs bsdus te byin gyis brlabs pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:8067: 'dod chags ye shes gsal ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:8069: thim pas rgyal mor byin gyis brlabs //
NK053('i)001:8071: de yang phyin ci log gi 'dod chags ma spangs par dngos su spyad pas /
NK053('i)001:8072: 'dod chags rang dag tu zad par byas te /
NK053('i)001:8073: yang dag pa'i ye shes su gsal ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:8074: yab yum gyi sku las ye shes rol pa'i skur shar ba'i sku so so las /
NK053('i)001:8075: stag rgod 'dzum pa'i mdangs dang ldan pa de rnams /
NK053('i)001:8076: thugs rje ye shes kyi 'od zer 'bar ba dang /
NK053('i)001:8079: cha lugs sna tshogs pa kun 'khrigs pa'i 'od /
NK053('i)001:8081: lha rnams so sor bltas pa'am /
NK053('i)001:8085: sku'i gnas dang lhag pa byang chub sems las /
NK053('i)001:8086: ye shes kyi 'od zer kha dog lnga lnga nyi shu rtsa lnga 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:8087: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa zhi khro'i lha tshogs thugs dam bskul zhing /
NK053('i)001:8088: ye shes kyi 'od zer gyis spyan drangs nas /
NK053('i)001:8089: mdun gyi nam mkha' la bzhugs par bsam zhing /
NK053('i)001:8090: zhi khro'i phrin las las 'byung ba bzhin /
NK053('i)001:8091: ye shes pa'i dal spyan drangs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8096: dbyer med par yab yum gnyis la /
NK053('i)001:8098: yum la lha mo thim par bsgom pa ni /
NK053('i)001:8101: dkyil 'khor spyan drangs mchod bstod nas //
NK053('i)001:8102: phab ste thim pas yab yum gnyis //
NK053('i)001:8103: rgyal po rgyal mor byin gyis brlabs //
NK053('i)001:8105: de la rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor yab yum la thim par gyur pa de /
NK053('i)001:8106: yab ni rdo rje rgyal po yin la /
NK053('i)001:8107: de'i yum rdo rje rgyal mo yin pas /
NK053('i)001:8108: yum yang ye shes kyi yum kun tu bzang mo'am /
NK053('i)001:8109: kro ti shwa ri ma kho nar bsgom zhing byin gyis brlab bo //
NK053('i)001:8112: 2 / gnyis su med pa'i sbyor ba brtsam pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:8113: yab yum gnyis med sbyor ba yis //
NK053('i)001:8115: de la skabs 'dir rtsol bas dngos su sbyor bar bya ste /
NK053('i)001:8117: ye shes dam tshig chen po yi //
NK053('i)001:8118: pad+mo rin chen ldan byas nas //
NK053('i)001:8119: bde mchog sgyu ma'i brdas mtshon te //
NK053('i)001:8120: dbyings kyi bde chen 'byung ba ni //
NK053('i)001:8121: rang rig ye shes de las 'od //
NK053('i)001:8122: ji bzhin mkha' la gsal ba dag /
NK053('i)001:8124: byang chub sems 'di kun tu dag /
NK053('i)001:8125: khams gsum rab tu 'das nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:8126: ma lus snying rjes khyab byas te //
NK053('i)001:8127: 'dod par bya ba rab tu mnyes //
NK053('i)001:8129: ces pa'i tshig rkang bcu gnyis po 'dir sbyo bar bya ste /
NK053('i)001:8130: de la yab ye shes chen po'i bdag nyid dang /
NK053('i)001:8131: yum gzungs ma dam tshig ma gnyis /
NK053('i)001:8132: phyag rgya chen po bzhi dang ldan pa de'i mkha' rnam gnyis byin gyis brlabs par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:8133: yab kyi thugs ka nas yi ge b+h+r+aum gcig yum gyi mkha' la 'phros pa las /
NK053('i)001:8134: mkha' de nyid zla gam dmar po dbang gi gzhal med khang pad+ma'i gdan dang ldan pa la /
NK053('i)001:8135: yum gyi byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin am dmar la dwangs pa gcig gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:8136: yum gyi thugs ka nas yi ge h'u gcig yab kyi mkha' la 'phros pa las /
NK053('i)001:8137: rdo rje rtse lnga pa gyur pa'i steng /
NK053('i)001:8138: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor de'i steng du yab kyi byang
NK053('i)001:8139: chub kyi sems rin po che'i rang bzhin dkar po
NK053('i)001:8141: de ltar yab yum gyi mkha' gsang pad+ma dang rin po che dang ldan par byas te /
NK053('i)001:8143: de'i dus su sbyor ba'i brdas bskul ba yang /
NK053('i)001:8144: nyan thos dang 'jig rten pa la ltos na lhan
NK053('i)001:8145: skyes bde ba dang mchog tu gyur pa'i sbyor ba
NK053('i)001:8146: mdzad pa'i phyir / sgyu ma lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas nas /
NK053('i)001:8148: zhes dus la bab ces yum gyis bskul /
NK053('i)001:8149: sa ma ya hohs dus yin no zhes lan byin /
NK053('i)001:8150: r+aa ga ya hohs bdag chags so zhes bskul /
NK053('i)001:8152: sa chags par bagyi'o zhes lan sbyin /
NK053('i)001:8153: zhes pas sbyor ba'i brdas bsnol mar bskul zhing mtshon te /
NK053('i)001:8154: dzah zhes lcags kyu'i phyag rgyas lus kyi cha rnams reg /
NK053('i)001:8155: h'u zhes zhags pa'i phyag rgyas stod smad nas 'khyud /
NK053('i)001:8156: bam zhes lcags sgrog phyag rgyas mkha' gsang dam du sprad /
NK053('i)001:8157: hoh zhes dril bu'i phyag rgyas yab kyis gsor yum gyis bskyod pa sogs bya'o //
NK053('i)001:8159: zhes pas phyag rgya bzhis 'du ba mdzad de /
NK053('i)001:8160: pad+ma sa ma yo gi pra be sha phata kyis yum gyi pad+ma zum pa kha phral te /
NK053('i)001:8162: zhes rig pa dbyings su 'jug pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:8164: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a nu r+aa ga dz+ny+aa
NK053('i)001:8165: na badz+ra na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham
NK053('i)001:8167: yab kyi byang chub kyi sems lus kyi gnas thams cad nas gyis bsdus shing h'u gis bskyod pas /
NK053('i)001:8168: chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin byang chub sems bde ba chen po bskul nas /
NK053('i)001:8169: phata kyis yum gyi mkha' la babs par gyur pa na /
NK053('i)001:8170: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo lhag pa'i
NK053('i)001:8171: byang chub kyi sems la zla blta bur gnas pa
NK053('i)001:8172: de las 'od zer 'phro ba de ji lta bu'i
NK053('i)001:8173: rang bzhin du / gsang ba'i mkha' la gsal zhing dag par gyur pa ni /
NK053('i)001:8174: dper na sgrib g.yogs kyi dri ma med pa'i nam mkha' dang ba la /
NK053('i)001:8175: nyi ma shar ba'i 'od kyis gsal ba 'tsher te /
NK053('i)001:8176: des ni dus dang gnas skabs kun tu gzung 'dzin gyi dri ma dag go //
NK053('i)001:8178: 'dod chags ye shes kyis gsal ba'i phyir ro //
NK053('i)001:8179: de lta bu'i 'od zer 'phros pas phyi snod kyi 'jig rten la phog pas /
NK053('i)001:8180: dngos po thams cad bsregs sbyangs te /
NK053('i)001:8181: sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag par gyur to //
NK053('i)001:8182: nang bcud kyi 'jig rten khams gsum na gnas pa'i sems can la phog pas /
NK053('i)001:8183: las dang nyon mongs pa'i rtog sgrib bsregs sbyangs te /
NK053('i)001:8184: sangs rgyas kyi sa la bkod /
NK053('i)001:8185: de nas phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams na /
NK053('i)001:8186: nam mkha' mthas gtugs pa'i chos kyi dbyings kyi mtha' klas pa thams cad du 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:8187: de na gnas pa'i sems can thams cad byang chub
NK053('i)001:8188: sems snying rje chen po'i rlan dang bcas par khyab
NK053('i)001:8189: pa byas nas / gang dang gang la mos shing thob par 'dod pa de dag la /
NK053('i)001:8190: re ba bskangs shing phan btags pas /
NK053('i)001:8191: dga' ba bskyed pa'i sgo nas sangs rgyas kyi sa la bkod do //
NK053('i)001:8192: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi de bzhin gshegs pa gzhan
NK053('i)001:8193: gyis bsgrub cing thob par 'dod pa 'khor dang bcas
NK053('i)001:8195: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi mchod pa phul te /
NK053('i)001:8196: de dag rab tu mnyes par byas te /
NK053('i)001:8197: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bsdus nas /
NK053('i)001:8198: 'od zer de dag slar thog ma'i gzugs kyi mkha' la 'dus te btsud pas /
NK053('i)001:8199: byang chub kyi sems gzugs brnyan de yang rab tu gsal bar gyur par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:8201: shes rab thabs kyi phyag rgya las //
NK053('i)001:8202: bde ba'i 'bru tshogs gsal ba'i rgyun //
NK053('i)001:8206: 3 / de la byang chub sems kyi dbang bskur ba la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:8209: byin gyis brlabs pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:8210: tha mal pa byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8211: lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs rdo rje ltar byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK053('i)001:8213: yab yum gnyis med sbyor ba yi //
NK053('i)001:8214: byang chub sems de blangs nas ni //
NK053('i)001:8216: he ru ka'i gal po las //
NK053('i)001:8217: rgyal po yab yum gnyis med sbyor //
NK053('i)001:8218: rang rig bde 'byung gsal ba'i rgyun //
NK053('i)001:8220: slob ma byin brlab dbang bskur bya //
NK053('i)001:8223: slob mas rig pa'i me tog thogs nas /
NK053('i)001:8224: gsol ba gang skad btabs pas /
NK053('i)001:8225: slob dpon gyis kyang lan gang skad brjod nas /
NK053('i)001:8226: slob ma 'og phyogs sam mdun phyogs su 'dug la /
NK053('i)001:8227: de yang ting nge 'dzin gyis nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng na 'dug par bsam la /
NK053('i)001:8228: yab yum gyi byang chub sems /
NK053('i)001:8229: gnyis su med pa'i byang chub kyi sems /
NK053('i)001:8230: mkha' gsang na ltem zhing 'khyil ba de las /
NK053('i)001:8231: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer lan gcig spyi bo nas gtims pas /
NK053('i)001:8232: lus ngag yid gsum gyi rtog sgrib sbyangs nas /
NK053('i)001:8233: yi ge h'u dkar po zhig tu gyur /
NK053('i)001:8235: de las yi dam gyi lha'i skur bskyed la /
NK053('i)001:8237: rdo rje ming gi dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:8238: de nas yab yam gnyis su med pa'i byang chub kyi sems de /
NK053('i)001:8239: de bzhin gshegs pa'i thugs ye shes dbyer med pa /
NK053('i)001:8240: chos kyi sku'i ngo bor gnas pa yin te /
NK053('i)001:8241: dngos grub thams cad kyi nang na yang mchog chen po yin pas /
NK053('i)001:8242: yum nyid kha sbub nas me long yu ba can gyi theb tu gtigs te /
NK053('i)001:8244: dam rdzas bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga'i khu ba dang /
NK053('i)001:8246: byang chub sems su sbyar nas /
NK053('i)001:8249: yi ge +aahmh'u gsum du byin gyis brlabs te /
NK053('i)001:8250: gsang ba'i sa bon dang dbyer med par bsgom pa de /
NK053('i)001:8251: 'gu ya lag gi mtheb srin sbyor ba phyag rgya nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor du gyur pas blangs te /
NK053('i)001:8252: sku gsung thugs rdo rje ltar byin gyis brlab pa ni gong du smos pa ltar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:8253: de nas dbu rgyan gyis kyang byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK053('i)001:8254: de nas byang chub sems tsho gnyis kyis dbang bskur ba la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:8255: nub pa'i dbang lnga bskur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:8256: khyad par du bsgrub pa'i dbang bskur ba ste /
NK053('i)001:8257: de bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:8258: de dag dngos grub chen po bas //
NK053('i)001:8259: ji ltar 'dod par nan tan bya //
NK053('i)001:8261: de la dang po nus pa'i dbang lnga la /
NK053('i)001:8262: ngag don du nyer drug gis bstan te /
NK053('i)001:8264: da la gang du dbang bskur /
NK053('i)001:8271: mtshungs ldan gyis rgyu rkyen gang gis thob /
NK053('i)001:8274: gnas gang du sgrib pa gang 'dag /
NK053('i)001:8285: sngon 'byung gi lo rgyus ji lta bu /
NK053('i)001:8289: de la nus pa'i dbang lnga ni /
NK053('i)001:8294: rdo rje slob dpon gyi dbang dang lnga /
NK053('i)001:8295: dngos grub bsgrub pa'i cho ga chen po yin pas /
NK053('i)001:8296: slob ma ji ltar 'dod pa bzhin du /
NK053('i)001:8297: slob dpon gyis nan tan du byas te dbang bskur ba yang /
NK053('i)001:8299: he ru ka'i gal po dang /
NK053('i)001:8300: sgyu 'phrul gnyis tshig don mthun par 'byung ste /
NK053('i)001:8301: de la slob ma chos nyan par 'dod na /
NK053('i)001:8302: nyan pa'i dbang rna bar bskur ba la /
NK053('i)001:8304: rin chen 'byung ldan gyis rab gnas byas pa yis /
NK053('i)001:8306: nyan byed 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:8307: gsang ba'i thig le ngo bo nyid //
NK053('i)001:8308: t+r+aam gyi phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog las //
NK053('i)001:8309: rin chen dkyil 'khor gsal spro thim //
NK053('i)001:8311: slob ma'i rna ba'i nang du /
NK053('i)001:8313: b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i gzhal yas khang rgyan dang bcas pa /
NK053('i)001:8314: de'i nang du 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi lte ba dang bcas pa la /
NK053('i)001:8315: nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan dang ldan pa'i steng du /
NK053('i)001:8317: gsang ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid las /
NK053('i)001:8318: yi ge t+r+aam mthing ga lngar gyur par bsam /
NK053('i)001:8320: rin po che 'od 'bar ba lngar gyur par bsam /
NK053('i)001:8322: badz+ra rat+na swa b+h+aa wa t+r+aam /
NK053('i)001:8325: rin po che 'byung ldan yab yum gyi skur gyur par bsam /
NK053('i)001:8326: de'i rtsibs bzhi la rin po che'i rigs kyi sems dpa' yab yum bzhi /
NK053('i)001:8331: sgo bzhir khro bo bzhi yang btsun mo dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:8332: de nas yum gyi mkha' chos kyi dbyings su thim pa las /
NK053('i)001:8333: rin chen sems pa'i sku phyag rgya chen po phyag mtshan dang ldan par bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:8334: de la rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing bstims la /
NK053('i)001:8335: slob dpon gyis dbang bskur ba'i cho ga bsgrag pa /
NK053('i)001:8337: gsang ba gsang chen gsang mchog gang //
NK053('i)001:8338: ma h+aa a nu a ti /
NK053('i)001:8341: gsang ba kun la mnyan par bya //
NK053('i)001:8342: gsang ba'i don nyid brtags pa las //
NK053('i)001:8343: gzhan du smra bar bya ba min //
NK053('i)001:8344: de ni nyan du gnang ba'i dbang ngo //
NK053('i)001:8345: de la slob ma sgrub pa'i dbang nod par 'dod na /
NK053('i)001:8346: dbang rdzas phreng ba yi dam lha'i rab gnas byas pa /
NK053('i)001:8348: snying kha 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:8349: gsang ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid //
NK053('i)001:8350: yi ge phreng ba'i tshogs mchog las //
NK053('i)001:8351: rigs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal spro thim //
NK053('i)001:8352: zhes gsungs pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:8354: khyad par sgrub pa'i dbang ngo /
NK053('i)001:8355: de la spyir 1sgrub pa'i dbang ni /
NK053('i)001:8356: slob ma'i snying gi dkyil du /
NK053('i)001:8357: b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i gzhal yas khang /
NK053('i)001:8358: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud dang bcas par /
NK053('i)001:8359: gdan dang bcas par bsam pa la /
NK053('i)001:8360: de'i steng du gsang ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid las /
NK053('i)001:8361: h'u dkar po sbrel ma lngar gyur pa las /
NK053('i)001:8366: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum la /
NK053('i)001:8367: rdo rje rigs kyi sems dpa' yab yum sa yi snying po /
NK053('i)001:8372: sgo bzhi'i khro bo yab yum dang bcas par bskyed la /
NK053('i)001:8373: de nas yum gyi mkha' chos kyi dbyings su thim pa las /
NK053('i)001:8374: rdo rje sems dpa'i sku phyag rgya chen po phyag mtshan dang ldan par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:8375: de la rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs bstims la /
NK053('i)001:8376: slob dpon gyis dbang bskur ba'i tshig /
NK053('i)001:8378: dus gsum rgyal ba'i sras chen po //
NK053('i)001:8379: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje zungs //
NK053('i)001:8380: rgyal ba thams cad mnyes mchod la //
NK053('i)001:8381: rgyal ba kun dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK053('i)001:8383: rdo rje dang dril bu yang sbyin no //
NK053('i)001:8384: mtshan ma med pa chos nyid rang ngo sprad pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8385: mtshan ma dang bcas pa'i gdams ngag bar 'dir sbyin no //
NK053('i)001:8386: dbang 'di thob na 'phags pa gang yang bsgrub tu gnang ngo //
NK053('i)001:8388: slob ma de nyid lha gang la mos pa'i dbang du bskur te /
NK053('i)001:8391: gang bsgrub pa'i cha rkyen gyis kyang bar 'dir dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:8392: de la slob mas las kyi dbang nod par 'dod na /
NK053('i)001:8393: dbang rdzas rdo rje rgya gram /
NK053('i)001:8394: don yod grub pa'i rab gnas so //
NK053('i)001:8396: b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i gzhal yas khang 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi /
NK053('i)001:8397: sgo bzhi dang gdan dang bcas par bsam la /
NK053('i)001:8398: de'i steng du gsang ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid las /
NK053('i)001:8401: badz+ra a mo ga sid+d+hi h+aa /
NK053('i)001:8402: badz+ra sa ma ya da ra h+aa /
NK053('i)001:8404: don yod grub pa yab yum la /
NK053('i)001:8405: las kyi rigs kyi sems dpa' yab yum phyag na rdo rje /
NK053('i)001:8409: sgo ba yab yum dang bcas pas bskor bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:8412: lag pa 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:8413: gsang ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid //
NK053('i)001:8414: h+aahyi phyag rgya'i tshogs mchog las //
NK053('i)001:8415: las kyi dkyil 'khor gsal spro thim //
NK053('i)001:8417: de nas yum gyi mkha' chos kyi dbyings su thim pa las /
NK053('i)001:8418: las kyi sems dpa'i sku phyag rgya chen po phyag mtshan dang ldan par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:8419: de las rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing bstims la /
NK053('i)001:8421: khyod ni rdo rje las yin te //
NK053('i)001:8422: phrin las rnam bzhi'i las rnams ma lus kun gyis shig /
NK053('i)001:8424: khyod kyi dgos pa byed pa yin //
NK053('i)001:8426: de bzhin gshegs pa'i mdzad spyod la spyod par gnang ba'i dbang ngo //
NK053('i)001:8427: de nas slob mas 'chad pa'i dbang nod par 'dod na /
NK053('i)001:8428: dbang rdzas 'khor lo 'od dpag med kyi rab gnas so //
NK053('i)001:8430: smra byed 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:8431: gsang ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid //
NK053('i)001:8432: h+r+aihyi phyag rgya tshogs mchog las //
NK053('i)001:8433: chos kyi 'khor lo gsal spro thim //
NK053('i)001:8436: b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i gzhal yas khang /
NK053('i)001:8437: grub bzhi sgo bzhi dang bcas pa /
NK053('i)001:8438: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud dang bcas pa /
NK053('i)001:8439: 'khor lo'i steng du nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan steng du gsang ba'i thig le las /
NK053('i)001:8440: yi ge h+r+aihdamara po sgril ma lnga /
NK053('i)001:8441: de las pad+ma sgril ma lnga /
NK053('i)001:8442: de las snang ba mtha' yas yab yum la /
NK053('i)001:8443: pad+ma'i rigs kyi sems dpa' yab yum spyan ras gzigs /
NK053('i)001:8446: mar me ma dang bcas par bskyed pa ni /
NK053('i)001:8447: badz+ra a mi d+he wa h+r+aih badz+ra b+han+d+ha ma ra
NK053('i)001:8448: sid+d+hi hoh zhe bya ba la sogs pa brjod pas
NK053('i)001:8449: / sgo bzhi'i khro bo yab yum dang bcas par bsam la /
NK053('i)001:8450: de nas yum gi mkha' chos kyi dbyings su thim pa las /
NK053('i)001:8451: rdo rje chos smra ba'i sku phyag rgya chen po phyag mtshan dang ldan par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:8452: de la phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas thams cad spyan drangs shing bstims la /
NK053('i)001:8454: chos kyi bdud rtsi bla na med //
NK053('i)001:8455: dad ldan skyes bu mos par byos //
NK053('i)001:8456: rab 'bring tha ma'i blo can la //
NK053('i)001:8457: mthun par gsang bsgrags gzhan du min //
NK053('i)001:8459: dbang 'di thob nas blo yi rim pa dang sbyar nas 'chad par gnang ngo //
NK053('i)001:8461: slob dpon gyi dbang nod par 'dod na /
NK053('i)001:8462: dbang rdzas rdo rje dang dril bu la kun bzang yab yum gyis rab gnas bya'o //
NK053('i)001:8464: bskyod chen 'khor lo'i gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:8465: gsang ba'i thig le'i ngo bo nyid //
NK053('i)001:8467: yan lag lnga la dkyil 'khor lnga dang khro phreng bsgom //
NK053('i)001:8469: slob ma'i yan lag lnga la /
NK053('i)001:8470: b+h+r+aum las rin po che'i gzhal yas khang rgyan dang bcas pa /
NK053('i)001:8471: 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud dang bcas pa re re /
NK053('i)001:8472: de'i steng du nyi zla pad+ma gdan re re /
NK053('i)001:8474: gsang ba'i byang chub sems thig le'i ngo bo nyid las /
NK053('i)001:8480: ral gri dang lngar gyur te /
NK053('i)001:8481: de las rigs lnga yab yum gyi snying po brjod pas /
NK053('i)001:8482: lag g.yas su rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum dang /
NK053('i)001:8483: spyi bor rnam par snang mdzad dang /
NK053('i)001:8484: lag g.yon du rin chen 'byung ldan dang /
NK053('i)001:8485: rkang g.yas snang ba mtha' yas dang /
NK053('i)001:8486: rkang g.yon don yod grub pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8487: rigs lnga yab yum dang bcas par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:8488: slob ma de'i lus kyi gnas bcu'am /
NK053('i)001:8489: yang na rigs lnga'i 'khor du khro bo chen po bcu yab yum dang bcas pa bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:8490: de nas yum gyi mkha' chos kyi dbyings su thim pa las /
NK053('i)001:8491: rigs gang la 'thad pa'i phyag rgya chen po phyag mtshan dang ldan par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:8492: de yang phyogs bcu dus bzhi'i sangs rgyas thams cad spyan drangs shing bstims la /
NK053('i)001:8494: slob ma slob dpon du dbang bskur ba'i tshig la //
NK053('i)001:8495: phyogs bcu dus bzhi thams cad kyi //
NK053('i)001:8496: sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rje che //
NK053('i)001:8497: dkyil 'khor kun gyi byed pa po //
NK053('i)001:8498: dkyil 'khor kun gyi sbyin pa spyod //
NK053('i)001:8500: dbang 'di thob nas dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs
NK053('i)001:8501: pa'i dkyil 'khor thams cad byed pa la dbang ngo
NK053('i)001:8503: slob dpon byas nas slob ma dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8505: dbang bskur byed pa la dbang ngo //
NK053('i)001:8507: khyad 2 par du bsgrub pa'i dbang bskur ba la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:8508: lha rgyan gcig pa bsgrub pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8509: tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa'i dbang ngo //
NK053('i)001:8510: de yang byang chub sems tsho gcig gis slob ma dbang gang 'dod de bskur te /
NK053('i)001:8511: de la 1lha rgyan gcig pa bsgrub pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:8512: spyir zhi khro'i lha gang la mos pa yin la /
NK053('i)001:8513: khyad par du dngos grub shin tu nye ba dpal chen po yin pas /
NK053('i)001:8514: dbang bskur ba'i gnas snying kha /
NK053('i)001:8515: bskur ba'i thabs dang tshig gong ma /
NK053('i)001:8517: slob ma nub phyogs kyi sgor zla gam dbang gi dkyil 'khor bris pa'i steng du bzhag la /
NK053('i)001:8518: de'i tsit+ta rin po che'i gzhal yas khang du dpal chen po yab yum bskyed la /
NK053('i)001:8519: de yum gyi mkha' chos kyi dbyings su thim pa las /
NK053('i)001:8520: dpal chen por gsal bar bsgoms te /
NK053('i)001:8521: de la ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing bstims pa'i dus su /
NK053('i)001:8522: b+han+d+ha dang mar me rdo rje dril bu gsum gyis kyang dbang bskur la /
NK053('i)001:8523: de la phyi nang gi mchod pa dang bstod pa yan chad byas la /
NK053('i)001:8524: dbang bskur ba'i tshig rnams kyang brjod /
NK053('i)001:8526: de la tshom 2bu'i dkyil 'khor bsgrub pa'i dbang la lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:8527: rdo rje rgyal po sa 'dzin gyi dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8529: sbyor sgrol ging gi dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8531: dkyil 'khor gyi rgyan mched lcam dral gyi dbang ngo //
NK053('i)001:8532: rdo rje 1rgyal po'i dbang la bcu ste /
NK053('i)001:8533: ye shes lha rnams nye bas bgegs chen 'dul ba'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8534: ma sring srung ma 'khor bas gsang ba'i dkyil 'khor skyong ba'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8535: lung rab dgongs pa byin pas yan lag nyams chag skong ba'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8536: ting nge 'dzin las su rung bas a b+hi tsa ra sgrol ba'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8537: mngon par shes pa lnga dang ldan pas rgyu drug stob pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8538: blo dang rim par ldan pas bdud rtsi bum pa bsgrub pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8539: bslab pa'i chos mthar phyin pas phyi nang gsang ba 'chad pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8540: theg pa rim pa dgu la mkhas pas slob ma rim gyis gzhugs pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8541: gsang ba'i man ngag dang ldan pas zhing bcu'i tshogs la rol pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8542: mtshan ma'i cho 'phrul mthong bas gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor 'bri ba'i dbang ngo //
NK053('i)001:8543: rgyal 2thebs kyi dbang la yang lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:8544: dkyil 'khor drug 'bri zhing 'chad pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8545: tshogs lnga la rol pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8546: phrin las drod kyi dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8548: dza gad byin gyis barloba pa'i dbang ngo //
NK053('i)001:8549: sbyor sgrol ging gi 3dbang la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:8553: sgrol ging gi dbang la lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:8554: khro bo bcu lus la 'god pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8555: snying po phyag mtshan 'debs pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8556: tsit+ta zhal du stob pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8557: rnam shes dbyings su 'dren pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8559: las 4kyi karma'i dbang la yang lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:8560: ye shes lha tshogs phyag rgyas bsdus pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8561: thabs kyi dbye tshogs rim par 'byed pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8562: shes rab rol tshogs dgyes par sbyor ba'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8563: thugs rje rol tshogs gnas su stob pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8564: dag pa'i 'byor tshogs mnyes par 'bul ba'i dbang ngo //
NK053('i)001:8565: dkyil 5'khor gyi rgyan mched lcam gral gyi dbang la yang lnga ste /
NK053('i)001:8566: rdo rje'i gral du mchis pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8567: yi dam gyi lha bsgom zhing mchod pa'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8568: phyi nang gi rgyud sde nyan du gnang ba'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8569: byin gyis brlabs pa'i zhal zas la rol du gnang ba'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:8570: pany+tsa a mri ta lus la 'chang ba'i dbang ngo //
NK053('i)001:8572: slob ma gang dbang 'dod pa de rnams zla gam dbang gi dkyil 'khor du bzhag nas /
NK053('i)001:8574: dbang rdzas byang chub sems kyi ril bu tsho gcig dang /
NK053('i)001:8575: rdo rje dril bu thogs la /
NK053('i)001:8578: thabs dang shes rab dbang chen te //
NK053('i)001:8579: rdo rje dril bu rig pa 'dzin //
NK053('i)001:8581: chos la 'dod bzhin dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:8583: slob ma dbang gang 'dod pa de la /
NK053('i)001:8585: byang chub sems lce la bzhag /
NK053('i)001:8586: rdo rje dril bu lag tu gtad nas /
NK053('i)001:8587: dbang gang 'dod pa de'i ming nas brjod de /
NK053('i)001:8588: dbang 'di rnams khyod kyis thob par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:8590: las kyang de bzhin du basgo'o //
NK053('i)001:8591: byang chub sems la brten nas bla ma'i zhal dbang bskur ba'i rim pa'o /
NK053('i)001:8593: 4 / de la dbang 'di rnams thob pa'i yon tan ni /
NK053('i)001:8594: ngag gi dri ma dag nas /
NK053('i)001:8595: sa bcu la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' dang skal ba mnyam pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8596: sems can sgyu ma lta bu las /
NK053('i)001:8597: lha sgyu ma lta bu ste /
NK053('i)001:8598: rigs rnam pa lngar gyur pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8599: de las kyang dpal chen por gyur te /
NK053('i)001:8600: rigs drug gi sku thob nas /
NK053('i)001:8601: 'gro ba'i don byed nus pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8606: rdo rje slob dpon du sa 'dzin nus pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8607: tshom bu bsgrub pa la sogs pa nus pas /
NK053('i)001:8610: 5 / dbang 'di rnams ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK053('i)001:8611: gong ma'i don las bzlog ste mi nus pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8612: 'bras bu med cing rang rgyud 'tshig pa'i nyen che bas /
NK053('i)001:8613: nang dbang ngag la bskur bas gsung gi dbang zhes gsungs /
NK053('i)001:8614: slob dpon dang slob ma gnyis kas nan tan du bya ba ste /
NK053('i)001:8615: dbang zhu ba dang bskur ba gnyis gzabs te bya'o //
NK053('i)001:8618: 3 / do nas slob ma la gsang ba'i dbang bskur ba la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:8619: shes rab ma brtag cing byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8620: bu la gtad nas dbang bskur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:8621: man ngag zab mo sbyin pa'o //
NK053('i)001:8622: de la 1shes rab ma brtag cing byin gyis brlabs pa la gnyis te //
NK053('i)001:8624: yid 'ong bkra shis rigs kyi yum //
NK053('i)001:8626: de yang gsang sngags kyi lam sbyor sgrol gnyis la brten te bsgrub pa yin pas /
NK053('i)001:8627: de yid du mi 'ong zhing mtshan dang mi ldan na /
NK053('i)001:8629: bsgrub po'i sems mi zin par bar chad du 'gyur pas /
NK053('i)001:8630: yid du 'ong zhing mtshan brtag pa yang /
NK053('i)001:8631: he ru ka'i gal po las 'di skad du 'byung ste /
NK053('i)001:8632: rigs kyi yum lnga'i gzungs ma ni //
NK053('i)001:8633: dmar ser mnyam pa'i phyag rgya can //
NK053('i)001:8634: spyan 'phang dma' la gzi byin can //
NK053('i)001:8636: dpung 'go mtho zhing spyi bo ring //
NK053('i)001:8637: de bzhin rigs kyi gzungs mar shis //
NK053('i)001:8638: dkar gsal dung mdog sgeg mo'i gzugs //
NK053('i)001:8639: sha rus 'dril la rdo rje'i dbyibs //
NK053('i)001:8641: dung can ma yi rigs mchog ste //
NK053('i)001:8642: rdo rje'i rigs kyi gzungs mar shis //
NK053('i)001:8645: shes rab che zhing blo stobs che //
NK053('i)001:8646: blo gros zad med sems la 'chang //
NK053('i)001:8647: rin chen rigs kyi gzungs mar shis //
NK053('i)001:8648: dkar la dmar chags pad+ma'i mdog /
NK053('i)001:8649: chags pa che zhing yid gzhungs pa //
NK053('i)001:8651: mig rtsa dmar zhing mdangs 'phrogs pa //
NK053('i)001:8652: pad+ma'i rigs kyi gzungs mar shis //
NK053('i)001:8653: dmar ljang 'khrug pa'i ngo bo can //
NK053('i)001:8654: khro brtson las rab don la brtson //
NK053('i)001:8655: sha rgyas chu zheng gab par 'dug /
NK053('i)001:8656: lag mthil rdo rje rgya gram 'chang //
NK053('i)001:8657: las kyi rigs kyi gzungs mar shis //
NK053('i)001:8660: bkra shis mtshan ldan gsang ba'i yum //
NK053('i)001:8661: zhal nas ut+pala ngad ldang zhing //
NK053('i)001:8662: skad kyang ngang pa gzhon nu 'dra //
NK053('i)001:8663: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can //
NK053('i)001:8664: zla gsang dkar dmar rlung dkar lci //
NK053('i)001:8666: shes rab ma de ltar brtags pa de yang /
NK053('i)001:8667: slob ma rigs lnga'am drug po de /
NK053('i)001:8668: yi dam gyi lha gang yin pa de dang bstun la /
NK053('i)001:8669: byin gyis brlabs par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:8670: byin gyis brlabs pa'i thabs gong 'og tu rgyas par bshad pa las rig par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:8671: slob ma 2la shes rab ma de lta bu gtad nas dbang bskur na /
NK053('i)001:8672: dngos grub kyi 'bras bu myur du 'byung ste /
NK053('i)001:8673: de yang bu la gtad nas dbang bskur ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:8677: de nas shes rab ye shes dbang //
NK053('i)001:8678: slob ma mchog la sbyin par bya //
NK053('i)001:8679: gzungs ma de yi bdag nyid la //
NK053('i)001:8680: bla ma nyid kyis byin brlabs te //
NK053('i)001:8681: dngos grub 'bras bu myur thob phyir //
NK053('i)001:8682: slob ma bu la sbyin par bya //
NK053('i)001:8685: dang po yum bu la gtad pa /
NK053('i)001:8686: gnyis pa rol zhing dbang dngos /
NK053('i)001:8687: gsum pa dbang 'di thob pa'i yon tan /
NK053('i)001:8688: bzhi pa ma thob pa'i skyon /
NK053('i)001:8690: drug pa dbang bskur zhing dam tshig bsgrag pa'o //
NK053('i)001:8693: slob ma dang gzungs ma gnyis byin gyis brlabs pa /
NK053('i)001:8694: de gnyis lag pa nas bzung la /
NK053('i)001:8696: legs par nyon cig rigs kyi bu //
NK053('i)001:8697: bde chen kun bzang go 'phang bsgrub pa la //
NK053('i)001:8698: shin tu dad pas shes rab ma //
NK053('i)001:8699: khyod kyi grogs kyi dam par sbyin //
NK053('i)001:8701: gnyis pa rol zhing rig pa brtul zhugs kyi dbang /
NK053('i)001:8702: stan bde ba la rol pa rtsom du gzhug ste /
NK053('i)001:8703: slob mas kyang sbyor thabs kyi man ngag gong 'og
NK053('i)001:8704: tu bstan pa ltar rig par byas la brtsam mo
NK053('i)001:8706: rigs kyi bu rig ma 'di dang rtag tu mi 'bral bar gyis shig /
NK053('i)001:8708: de nas bde ba rnyed cing byang chub sems phebs nas /
NK053('i)001:8709: me long ngam shel phor gyi nang du blangs la /
NK053('i)001:8711: gcig la gcig kyang bstab cing /
NK053('i)001:8713: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub du blangs la baza'o //
NK053('i)001:8714: 'di ni rig pa brtul zhugs kyi dbang ste /
NK053('i)001:8716: spyod pa de ltar spyod tsam nyid na yang /
NK053('i)001:8717: chos ril gnyis su med pa'i shes rab dang /
NK053('i)001:8718: rnam pa mi rtog pa'i ye shes su lhang gis gyur nas /
NK053('i)001:8719: skye 'gag med pa'i klong na 'dug pa ni kun tu bzang mo'i dbang thob pa yin la /
NK053('i)001:8720: shes rab rig ma dang ye shes lhag pa'i byang
NK053('i)001:8721: chub sems la longs spyod pa ni kun tu bzang
NK053('i)001:8722: po'i dbang thob pa yin la /
NK053('i)001:8723: de gnyis rtag tu mi 'bral bar 'grogs pa ni gnyis med shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ngo //
NK053('i)001:8724: slob dpon gyis ngo sprod gsang tshig de slob ma'i shes rab la bgos pa ni dbang bskur ba'o //
NK053('i)001:8725: slob mas nyams su myong ba ni dbang thob pa'o //
NK053('i)001:8727: dbang 'di thob pa'i yon tan ni /
NK053('i)001:8728: sems kyi dri ma dag nas /
NK053('i)001:8729: sangs rgyas kun dang skal pa mnyam zhing bde ba chen po la longs spyod pa'o //
NK053('i)001:8731: dbang ma thob pa'i skyon ni /
NK053('i)001:8732: don gong ma rnams las bzlog pa'o //
NK053('i)001:8734: de nas slob mas me tog thogs la /
NK053('i)001:8736: ston mchog rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
NK053('i)001:8737: bdag gzhan kun la phan pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:8738: bla med dam tshig mchog nyid kyi //
NK053('i)001:8739: bka' yi lung bstan gnang bar mdzod //
NK053('i)001:8741: drug pa dbang bskur zhing dam bsgrag pa /
NK053('i)001:8742: bla ma rdo rje slob dpon gyis /
NK053('i)001:8743: slob ma'i lce la byang chub sems bzhag la /
NK053('i)001:8745: khyod kyis srog chags bsad par bya //
NK053('i)001:8747: brdzun gyi tshig kyang smra bar byed //
NK053('i)001:8748: sgra ji bzhin min pa sna tshogs /
NK053('i)001:8749: ma byin par yang khyod kyis longs //
NK053('i)001:8750: gzhan phan thabs mkhas spyod pa /
NK053('i)001:8751: bud med dag kyang bsten par bya //
NK053('i)001:8752: dbang gong ma'i ye shes myong ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:8753: rdo rje'i las ni 'di dag gis //
NK053('i)001:8754: sems can thams cad bskul bar bya //
NK053('i)001:8755: gsang sngags la gzud par bya /
NK053('i)001:8756: 'og ma'i dka' thub kyis ni gzer mi bya //
NK053('i)001:8757: ji bde bas ni bde ba spyad //
NK053('i)001:8758: bde chen ye shes la rol /
NK053('i)001:8759: 'di ni sangs rgyas bde spyod yin //
NK053('i)001:8760: rnal 'byor longs spyod 'dod yon ma spangs dug lnga lam khyer /
NK053('i)001:8762: cis kyang ma 'jigs spyod par gyis //
NK053('i)001:8763: sdig pa med kyis khyod ma 'jigs //
NK053('i)001:8765: gzhan yang dam tshig nyams pa dang //
NK053('i)001:8766: skye bo gang dag dam la gnod //
NK053('i)001:8767: brtul zhugs khyod kyis de drongs la //
NK053('i)001:8768: khrag chen po ni 'thung bar gyis //
NK053('i)001:8769: skal ngan 'jig rten pa dang nyan thos la //
NK053('i)001:8770: nam yang dga' bar mi bya ste //
NK053('i)001:8771: bskal bzang rdo rje sems dpa' gtso //
NK053('i)001:8772: khyod kyis rtag tu bsgrub par gyis //
NK053('i)001:8773: zhes rgyud las 'byung ba de bsgrags so //
NK053('i)001:8774: de la man ngag 3zab mo sbyin pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:8776: zhes bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:8777: bsgom lung bka'i man ngag sbyin pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8778: snying po don gyi man ngag sbyin pa ste /
NK053('i)001:8779: de gnyis ni don man ngag gis bsgrub pa zhes bya'o /
NK053('i)001:8781: 1 / de la bsgom lung bka'i man ngag sbyin pa la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:8782: bka' khog don gyi ma gzhi sbyin pa dang //
NK053('i)001:8783: lung man ngag gi gdams pa sbyin pa dang //
NK053('i)001:8784: man ngag zab mo rna bar gshib pa'o //
NK053('i)001:8785: de la 1bka' khog don gyi ma gzhi ni /
NK053('i)001:8786: bsgrub pa'i rgyal po rgyal ba kun gyi thugs //
NK053('i)001:8788: yang dag grub pa gcig pu nyid ni /
NK053('i)001:8789: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa'i gsung 'di dang /
NK053('i)001:8790: des gsungs pa'i byang sems rnam pa lnga po /
NK053('i)001:8798: slob dpon grub thob gong ma mkhas pa rnams kyis
NK053('i)001:8799: lung man ngag mtha' dag dril nas man ngag tu
NK053('i)001:8800: bsdus pa'o // lta ba'i rdzong spyod pa'i 'phrang gnyis su bsdus pa'i man ngag /
NK053('i)001:8802: slob dpon grub pa thob pa'i nyams kyi man ngag sangs rgyas lag bcangs ma sbyin pa'o //
NK053('i)001:8803: de kho na rdzogs 3par gdams te sbyin pa ni /
NK053('i)001:8804: man ngag zab mo rna bar gshib pa'o //
NK053('i)001:8805: 'di rnams gdams pa'i man ngag yin pas sems la bslan cing nyams bag tu blang bar bya'o /
NK053('i)001:8807: 2 / snying po sngags kyi man ngag sbyin pa ni /
NK053('i)001:8808: bsgom dbyangs yi ge 'bru brgyad de /
NK053('i)001:8809: 'og nas 'byung ba nas mar rig par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:8810: de yang man ngag dbang gis sbyin dgos pa yin pas /
NK053('i)001:8811: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang rdzogs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8813: man ngag rdzogs par bstan pa la rdzogs pa'i dbang zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:8814: de la sgom lung bka' man ngag ni /
NK053('i)001:8815: mtshan ma med pa gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:8819: 'khor 'das kyi chos ril sems su thag bcad la /
NK053('i)001:8820: sems rgyu ba med cing g.yo ba med pa /
NK053('i)001:8821: nam mkha' dwangs pa ltar gsal la rtog pa med pa de /
NK053('i)001:8822: rnam rtog gang gis kyang ma bslad par bzhag nas /
NK053('i)001:8823: gsal la ma yengs pa de ni dngos chos kyi sku skye ba med pa 'o //
NK053('i)001:8825: rol pa ma 'gags pa dpal chen po yab yum
NK053('i)001:8826: ye shes kyi skur rtsol ba med par shar te
NK053('i)001:8827: / yab yum gnyis bde ba rgyun mi chad par bzhugs pa ni longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku ste /
NK053('i)001:8828: de las thugs rje'i bye brag dang sangs rgyas kyi mdzad spyod phrin las rnam bzhi sogs /
NK053('i)001:8829: rgyun mi chad par kun la khyab par 'byung ba ni sprul pa'i sku ste /
NK053('i)001:8831: rnal 'byor zab mo sku gsum rdzogs //
NK053('i)001:8833: 'di kho na phyag rgya chen pi'i dbang ste /
NK053('i)001:8834: bla mas rigs kyi bu de ltar byos shig pa ni /
NK053('i)001:8838: de ni yang dag pa'i sangs rgyas dang mnyam pa yin pas /
NK053('i)001:8839: sangs rgyas bde chen kun 'dus pa //
NK053('i)001:8841: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas /
NK053('i)001:8843: mi rtog pa'i ye shes su rgyasa /
NK053('i)001:8844: dpe nam mkha' dwangs pa lta bu'o //
NK053('i)001:8845: bkag pa med pa'i sku dpal chen po'o //
NK053('i)001:8846: sgyu ma'i phung po zag bcas sangas /
NK053('i)001:8847: zag pa med pa'i sku sgyu ma'i cho 'phrul du rgyasa /
NK053('i)001:8849: de gnyis don du grub pa ste /
NK053('i)001:8850: snang stong dbyer med ngo bo nyid /
NK053('i)001:8851: chos kyi dbyings su rnam par dag pa de la /
NK053('i)001:8852: gang gis kyang mi bsgrib cing gsal ba de la /
NK053('i)001:8853: rig pa gding du gyur nas gsal la ma yengs pa de la /
NK053('i)001:8854: yang dag grub pa gcig pu nyid do //
NK053('i)001:8855: gleng bral 'di la gnas pa yi //
NK053('i)001:8856: rnal 'byor de ni skal ba bzang //
NK053('i)001:8857: bdag dang gzhan don mi 'byed pa //
NK053('i)001:8858: sgyu ma lhun grub yul la rol //
NK053('i)001:8861: rang gi mthu yis rig pa las //
NK053('i)001:8866: gcig ste rnam pa yongs kyis med //
NK053('i)001:8867: rnal 'byor nam mkha'i bya lam gnas //
NK053('i)001:8868: ma byung ma skyes snying po la //
NK053('i)001:8869: sgros btags chos kun ga la yod //
NK053('i)001:8870: ces nam mkha' che las gsungs so //
NK053('i)001:8872: mi g.yo ba ni sku yi rgyan //
NK053('i)001:8873: mi bskyod pa ni ye shes te //
NK053('i)001:8874: mi 'dor tshig bral mnyam nyid do //
NK053('i)001:8875: gang dang gang gis gang du yang //
NK053('i)001:8876: kun 'khol kun spyod bdag las byung //
NK053('i)001:8878: thag lta bas bcad pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8879: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang ba 'o /
NK053('i)001:8883: khyad par gyi dam tshig srung du gzhug pa'i rim pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:8884: skabs sbyor bcu gcig pa slob ma sgrub pa'i dam
NK053('i)001:8885: tshig la gnas shing bsnyen bsgrub gzhung bzhin du bya
NK053('i)001:8886: ba'i skabs so // lung dgu las dam tshig dbang gi lung /
NK053('i)001:8887: mtha' drug las dam tshig go //
NK053('i)001:8888: dbang thob mdzes pa de dag gis //
NK053('i)001:8889: dul ba'i sems su bzhag nas ni //
NK053('i)001:8890: dam tshig chen pos bde bar gnas //
NK053('i)001:8892: dper na skyes bu la rgyan sna tshogs kyis brgyan
NK053('i)001:8893: na shin tu yang mdzes par 'gyur ba bzhin du
NK053('i)001:8894: / snod dang ldan pa'i sgrub pa po la /
NK053('i)001:8895: yon tan dang ldan pa'i slob dpon gyis /
NK053('i)001:8897: rdzogs pa'i dbang dang bzhi bskur te thob pa ni de dang 'dra ba'i //
NK053('i)001:8898: dbang thob pa'i sgrub po de dag gis /
NK053('i)001:8900: yun du nyon mongs pa'i dbang du mi gtang bar /
NK053('i)001:8901: spyod lam shin tu yang dul zhing /
NK053('i)001:8902: khrel 'dzem che bar sems pa bzhag nas /
