NK053('i)001:8903: bsgrub pa'i dus su khyad par gyi dam tshig chen po brgyad phogs la srungs shig pa ni /
NK053('i)001:8905: bsgrub pa 'di'i dus su le lo dang gnyid dang chang dad dbang du mi gtong ba dang 1 /
NK053('i)001:8906: rdo rje slob dpon gyi bka' dang dam tshig bden par bya ba dang 2 /
NK053('i)001:8907: rkyen ci byung yang spyod lam yangs shing tshig gi mtshon ma shor bar bya ba dang 3 /
NK053('i)001:8908: dam rdzas thams cad la blo'i 'khu 'phrig med cing dang du blang ba dang 4 /
NK053('i)001:8909: yi dam gyi lha dang snying po la ma yengs shig bar chad med par bya ba dang 5 /
NK053('i)001:8910: sbyor sgrol zab mo la brtul zhugs cher spyad pa dang 6 /
NK053('i)001:8911: khams gsum yongs sgrol du srid gsum dbang du bsdu
NK053('i)001:8912: ba'i phyir glu bro mang po brdung ba dang 7
NK053('i)001:8913: / de yang ru lu'i dbyangs drug dang /
NK053('i)001:8914: mgo la lang+ka mnan pa'i bro /
NK053('i)001:8916: la sogs pa brdung bar bya /
NK053('i)001:8917: ye dag pa chos nyid byang chub sems las ma g.yos par bya'o8 //
NK053('i)001:8918: de ltar dam tshig chen po brgyad la bde bar gnas te bsrung ngo //
NK053('i)001:8920: khyad par dam tshig brtan par bya ba dbang bskur ba'i phrin las /
NK053('i)001:8921: dbang brtan par bya ba'i dam tshig bstan pa /
NK053('i)001:8924: khyad par gyi chas kyis mdzes par bya ba ni
NK053('i)001:8925: gong du yon 'bul zhing gsol ba gdab pa'i skabs
NK053('i)001:8926: su bstan no // lha 6mnyes par bya ba'i phrin las la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:8927: zhi ba'i lha mnyes par bya ba'i phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:8928: khro bo'i lha mnyes par bya ba'i phrin las so /
NK053('i)001:8931: zhi ba la skabs sbyor bcu gnyis pa nye ba'i bsnyen pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:8932: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor ting nge 'dzin gsum la sogs
NK053('i)001:8933: pas bskyed rdzogs kyi cho ga bya ba'i skabs so
NK053('i)001:8934: // lung dgu las yi ge 'khor lo bsnyen pa'i lung ngo //
NK053('i)001:8935: dkyil 'khor dgu las ting nge 'dzin gyi da la'o //
NK053('i)001:8936: mtha' drug las ting nge 'dzin gyi mtha'o //
NK053('i)001:8939: dmigs par bya ba'i yul dang /
NK053('i)001:8940: bsgrub par bya ba'i thabs so /
NK053('i)001:8942: 1 / de la dmigs par bya ba'i yul ni /
NK053('i)001:8943: sangs rgyas tshe 'dir bsgrub pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:8944: sku gsum sa la goms par bya //
NK053('i)001:8946: de la theg pa 'og ma pa rnams kyis yun ring por bsgrubs nas /
NK053('i)001:8947: phyis sangs rgyas su 'grub par lta bu ma yin te /
NK053('i)001:8949: mthong ba'i chos tshe 'di kho na la sangs rgyas su bsgrub pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:8951: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK053('i)001:8955: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa dang gsum /
NK053('i)001:8958: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin dang gsum bsgoms pa la goms par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:8961: bskal pa bye bar rnyed dka' ba //
NK053('i)001:8962: phyag rgya 'di yi cho ga yis //
NK053('i)001:8966: 2 / bsgrub pa bya ba'i thabs la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:8967: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom par bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8968: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs zhing mchod pa'i phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:8969: bsnyen pa dbul ba'i phrin las so //
NK053('i)001:8970: de la ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bsgom par bstan pa la yang gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:8971: ting nge 'dzin spyi khog bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8972: lha bskyed pa'i rim pa bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8974: de la ting nge 'dzin gyi spyi khog bstan pa lang yang /
NK053('i)001:8977: 'byung ba rim brtsegs bsgom pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8978: rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8980: dang po ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa la /
NK053('i)001:8986: 1 / de la de bzhin kyi ting nge 'dzin ci ltar bsgom snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:8987: dang po chos kyi dbyings nyid la //
NK053('i)001:8988: dmigs pa med pa'i don gyis bsgom //
NK053('i)001:8990: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa la don rnam pa bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:8991: dang por bsgom pa'i dgos ched dang /
NK053('i)001:8995: de la 1dang por bsgom pa'i dgos ched la yang gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:8996: sems can rnams ni thog ma med pa'i dus nas /
NK053('i)001:8997: bdag tu rtog pa'i dbang gis khams gsum du 'khor ba yin la /
NK053('i)001:8998: bdag tu rtog pa'i gnyen po dang por de bzhin nyid bsgom pa dang /
NK053('i)001:8999: gsang sngags ni 'bras bu'i chos yin la /
NK053('i)001:9000: 'bras bu ni sku gsum yin te /
NK053('i)001:9001: de bzhin nyid chos kyi sku'i ngang las gzugs kyi sku gnyis 'byung ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:9002: dang por chos nyid bsgom par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:9004: chos rnams kyi de bzhin nyid la blo bzhag pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:9005: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:9007: 'khor 'das kyi chos thams cad ni rang gi sems su 'dus la /
NK053('i)001:9008: sems kyi rang bzhin ni mtshan nyid thams cad dang bral ba /
NK053('i)001:9009: ji lta bu'i dngos po mdog dbyibs che chung grub pa ma yin pas /
NK053('i)001:9010: sems kyis btags pa'i chos thams cad kyang dngos po med de /
NK053('i)001:9011: ngo bo nyid kyi stong zhing dag pa /
NK053('i)001:9012: nam mkha' lta bur gsal zhing dag pa'i dus na /
NK053('i)001:9013: chos dbyings nyid las ye shes skyes //
NK053('i)001:9015: don de'i ngang las ma g.yos par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:9016: yang ji ltar bsgom zhe na /
NK053('i)001:9019: bsgrub med yum gyi b+ha ga la //
NK053('i)001:9020: brjod med sems kyi ngang du gsal //
NK053('i)001:9023: rnam pa mi rtog pa'i dmigs su med pa'i snying po sems kyi rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:9024: yi ge a dkar po gcig bsgoms te /
NK053('i)001:9025: de yang sems kyi rgyud gsal bar byas te /
NK053('i)001:9028: sems nyid ar gsal ba snying gar bzung ste /
NK053('i)001:9029: rgyu ba med cing g.yo ba med pa'i ngang du ci gsal du bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:9030: de gsal bar gyur pa dang /
NK053('i)001:9034: bdag nyid kyang bsregs te a gcig pur gnas pa las /
NK053('i)001:9035: de yang je chung je phra ste /
NK053('i)001:9037: de yang sgra mthar stong ste /
NK053('i)001:9039: jir yang mi dmigs pa'i ngang du gyur pa ni /
NK053('i)001:9040: don chos nyid kyi ngang du bsgom pa zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:9042: mi dmigs chos nyid de bzhin nyid //
NK053('i)001:9048: 2 / de nas kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin ci ltar bsgom snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:9049: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes kyis //
NK053('i)001:9050: thams cad kun la khyab par bya //
NK053('i)001:9052: de la kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin la yang /
NK053('i)001:9060: de bzhin nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi rol mi chags pa dang /
NK053('i)001:9061: sgyu ma'i cho 'phrul 'byung bar sla ba dang /
NK053('i)001:9062: gzhal yas khang du lha dgod par bde ba'o //
NK053('i)001:9064: chos thams cad skye 'gags med pa'i ngang du gsal /
NK053('i)001:9065: sems can rnams kyis skye ba med pa'i ngang ma rtogs pa la /
NK053('i)001:9066: khyab pa'i snying rje chen po bskyed de /
NK053('i)001:9067: mtshan ma dang mtshan ma med pa'i ting nge 'dzin gnyis bsgoms pas /
NK053('i)001:9068: kun tu snang gi ting nge 'dzin ces bya'o //
NK053('i)001:9070: rang gi rig pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK053('i)001:9071: chos thams cad skye 'gags med pa la /
NK053('i)001:9072: sems can rnams kyis skye ba med pa'i ngang ma rtogs pa la /
NK053('i)001:9073: snying rje chen por bskyed pa ni 'di ltar bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:9075: brtsol med ma bsgrubs ji bzhin las //
NK053('i)001:9076: kun snang nam mkha'i ngang nyid 'byung //
NK053('i)001:9077: tsit+ta pra be s+pha ra na phata /
NK053('i)001:9079: stong pa nyid kyi ting nge 'dzin gyi ngang la langs nas /
NK053('i)001:9080: chos thams cad gdod ma nas ma skyes shing /
NK053('i)001:9081: dngos po med pa yin na /
NK053('i)001:9082: sems can rnams kyis de ltar ma rtogs te /
NK053('i)001:9083: dngos po la mngon par zhen pas /
NK053('i)001:9084: khams gsum du mngon par 'khor ba 'di rnams snying re rje snyam du /
NK053('i)001:9085: snying rje chen po bskyed pa'i rtags su /
NK053('i)001:9086: 'od dkar po tshon gang ba gcig tu gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:9087: de nam gsal bar gyur pa dang /
NK053('i)001:9088: tsit+ta pra be s+pha ra na phata /
NK053('i)001:9089: ces bya ba'i sgra byung bas /
NK053('i)001:9090: snang srid ril 'od du bdal bas ril bsregs /
NK053('i)001:9092: 'od gazhi'o la 'dus te shin tu gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:9094: rang bzhin 'od gsal kun tu snang //
NK053('i)001:9097: sku gsum char thob pa'i grogs byed de /
NK053('i)001:9098: de yang rang rig pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK053('i)001:9099: chos kyi dbyings kyi don rtogs te /
NK053('i)001:9100: rtogs pa'i ngang las ma g.yos pas ni /
NK053('i)001:9101: chos kyi sku thob pa'i grogs byed do //
NK053('i)001:9102: de ltar ma rtogs pa rnams la snying rje chen po bskyed pas ni /
NK053('i)001:9103: gzugs kyi sku rnam gnyis thob pa'i grogs byed do //
NK053('i)001:9106: 3 / de nas rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin ci ltar bsgom snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:9107: med pa'i rgyu las mngon gsal ba'i //
NK053('i)001:9108: sems kyi rang bzhin ye shes gsal //
NK053('i)001:9110: rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin bsgom pa la yang don bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:9116: gang zag la bdag med par rtogs par bya ba'i phyir ro //
NK053('i)001:9118: gzugs kyi sku rnam gnyis thob pa'i rgyur gyur pa'i phyir rgyu'i ting nge 'dzin zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:9121: dam pa'i yi ge a las ni //
NK053('i)001:9122: ye shes sems dpa' gsal bar shar //
NK053('i)001:9125: gong 'og gi 'od de las sems kyi rang bzhin
NK053('i)001:9126: yi ge a dkar po gcig tu gyur par bsgom
NK053('i)001:9130: ye shes sems dpa' sku mdog dkar po tshon gang ba /
NK053('i)001:9131: rgyan dang cha lugs spangs pa gcig tu gsal bar gyur par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:9133: 'og tu lha bskyed pa'i rjes su bsdoms te 'byung ngo //
NK053('i)001:9134: de nas sku de nyid h'u yam /
NK053('i)001:9135: zhes pas ye shes kyi rlung gis bskyod nas /
NK053('i)001:9136: nam mkha'i dbyings na gsal ba'i thugs ka nas /
NK053('i)001:9137: gnyis pa 'byung ba rim brtsegs bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:9138: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten dang bstun nas /
NK053('i)001:9139: dbang chen yum lnga'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa yang /
NK053('i)001:9141: e las nam mkha' mtha' dbus med //
NK053('i)001:9142: yam las rlung gi dkyil 'khor te //
NK053('i)001:9143: bam las chu yi rba klong 'khyil //
NK053('i)001:9144: sum las gser gyi sa gzhi chags //
NK053('i)001:9145: lam las rin chen ri rab ste //
NK053('i)001:9148: de yang ye shes sems dpa'i thugs ka nas /
NK053('i)001:9149: e yam bam sum lam ram /
NK053('i)001:9150: zhes bya ba'i yi ge 'bru rnams 'thon te 'phros pa las /
NK053('i)001:9152: dwangs ma'i 'byung ba lngar yum gyi dkyil 'khor du bskyed de /
NK053('i)001:9154: e a ka sha ma d+ha la /
NK053('i)001:9156: nam mkha' chos kyi 'byung gnas gru gsum pa /
NK053('i)001:9157: yum kun tu bzang mo'i rang bzhin du bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:9158: de'i nang du yam las yam karma rak+sha ham /
NK053('i)001:9160: thams cad brten nus pa rlung gi dkyil 'khor rdo rje rgya gram /
NK053('i)001:9162: yum dam tshig sgrol ma'i rang bzhin du bsam /
NK053('i)001:9164: bam ma ma ki ri ma d+ha la /
NK053('i)001:9165: zhes brjod pas bdud rtsi'i rgya mtsho chen po zlum po /
NK053('i)001:9166: yum m+aa ma k+ai'i rang bzhin du bsam /
NK053('i)001:9170: gser gyi sa gzhi b+h+r+aum bzhi pa yum sangs rgyas spyan gyi rang bzhin du gyur par bsam /
NK053('i)001:9172: lam ti ta ma d+ha la /
NK053('i)001:9174: rin po che sna bzhi las grub pa'i ri rab rgya khyon dpag tu med pa gcig bsam /
NK053('i)001:9176: ram dz+wa la ma d+ha la /
NK053('i)001:9178: ye shes kyi me 'od 'bar bas 'byung ba lnga spyi'i drod bsnyoms te /
NK053('i)001:9179: yum na bza' dkar mo'i rang bzhin 'od 'ja' tshon bzhin du gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:9182: mkha' dbyings rnam dag dkyil 'khor ni //
NK053('i)001:9183: ma bcos lhun grub yum gyi mkha' //
NK053('i)001:9184: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i bzhugs gnas rten //
NK053('i)001:9186: gsum pa rten gzhal yas khang bsgom pa /
NK053('i)001:9187: de la gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i snying po dang 'phro 'du ji ltar bya snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:9190: ma lus snying rjes khyab byas te //
NK053('i)001:9191: re zhing ngam pa'i tshul du dgongs //
NK053('i)001:9194: gong gi ye shes sems dpa' ph+y+wa mkhan gyi tshul du snang ba'i thugs ka'am smin mtshams nas /
NK053('i)001:9195: rang gi ngang gis yi ge b+h+r+aum smug nag 'od du 'bar ba gcig gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:9199: de la yi ge b+h+r+aum ni /
NK053('i)001:9200: stong pa nyid kyi snying por yang 'gyur /
NK053('i)001:9202: mtshon cha lnga'i snying por yang 'gyur /
NK053('i)001:9203: bcom ldan 'das gtsug tor 'khor los sgyur ba'i snying por yang 'gyur /
NK053('i)001:9204: gzhal yas khang bskyed pa'i snying por yang 'gyur bas /
NK053('i)001:9209: b+h+r+aum de las b+h+r+aum s+pha ra na phata /
NK053('i)001:9211: b+h+r+aum phra mo yungs 'bru tsam grangs med par 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:9212: phyi nang snod bcud ma lus par ye shes kyi 'od zer gyis sbyangs te /
NK053('i)001:9213: ma lus snying rjes khyab byas te //
NK053('i)001:9215: snying rje'i gzugs kyiis mtha' dbus med par khyab pa'i rtags su /
NK053('i)001:9216: 'od zer smug nag tu chi le gsal ba des /
NK053('i)001:9219: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro ma la phog pas /
NK053('i)001:9220: rigs kyi gtso bor mthong nas re /
NK053('i)001:9223: byang chub sems dpa' rnams la phog pas spun dang grogs por mthong nas ngam /
NK053('i)001:9224: dus gsum gyi rgyal ba la phogs pas /
NK053('i)001:9225: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyis mchod pa phul te /
NK053('i)001:9226: sku gsung thugs kyi rgyud mnyes par byas nas /
NK053('i)001:9229: sras kyi dam par dgongs so //
NK053('i)001:9235: b+h+r+aum bzhi po yang 'od du lham gyis zhu nas /
NK053('i)001:9236: de las yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che tshon gang bar gyur /
NK053('i)001:9237: de nas 'phro 'du gong dang mthun par byas pas /
NK053('i)001:9238: de las gzhal yas khang ji ltar bskyed snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:9239: rin chen las mdzes gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:9243: badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra ma d+ha la b+h+r+aum /
NK053('i)001:9245: gzhal yas khang rin chen mdzes pa sna lnga las grub pa ste /
NK053('i)001:9246: shar phyogs shel kang ka re dkar po /
NK053('i)001:9247: lho phyogs bee d+aur+ya sngon po /
NK053('i)001:9248: nub phyogs pad+ma r+aa ga dmar po /
NK053('i)001:9249: byang phyogs in+t+ra ni la ljang gu /
NK053('i)001:9250: dbus su sha ra ga ser po las grub pa /
NK053('i)001:9251: dbyibs gru bzhi mchod rten gyi tshul du gnas pa /
NK053('i)001:9252: phyi nang shin tu mi sgrib pa gsal ba /
NK053('i)001:9253: rgya nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa /
NK053('i)001:9254: rin po che sna lnga las grub pa 'i gzhal yas khang gru bzhi pa de la /
NK053('i)001:9261: de'i dbus su gser gyi 'khor lo rtsibs bzhi mu khyud dang bcas pa /
NK053('i)001:9265: gzugs brnyan dkyil 'khor la yang de bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:9267: de la dbus kyi lte ba la /
NK053('i)001:9277: de rnams la yang rin po che sna tshogs kyi khri stegs dang /
NK053('i)001:9281: glo 'bur dang gru chad la nyi zla pad+ma sum brtsegs /
NK053('i)001:9283: sgo bzhir yang rdo rje'i brag dang nyi ma'o //
NK053('i)001:9284: gzhal yas khang de'i rgyan yang /
NK053('i)001:9290: dril bu rlung gis bskyod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:9293: d+r+wa ba dang d+r+wa ba phyed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:9302: sgo bzhir ta la'i skyed shing dang /
NK053('i)001:9303: cang shes kyi bya sna tshogs dang /
NK053('i)001:9309: chos dbyings kyi lha mo rnams sna tshogs su 'dod snam la snang zhing /
NK053('i)001:9310: mi 'grib pa rang byung bas brgyan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:9312: rin chen 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang //
NK053('i)001:9313: mtha' dang dbus med nam mkha'i rgya //
NK053('i)001:9314: phyi dang nang med kun tu nang //
NK053('i)001:9315: rig pa'i gdan dang ye shes rgyan //
NK053('i)001:9318: ye shes 'bar ba'i gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:9319: seng ge glang rta rma bya khyung //
NK053('i)001:9320: nyi zla pad+ma rin po che //
NK053('i)001:9321: gtso dang 'khor bcas rim par gsal //
NK053('i)001:9324: 2 / de nas lha bskyed pa'i rim pa bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:9325: rdo rje sems dpa' la sogs pa'i //
NK053('i)001:9326: thugs rje che dang ldan pa yi //
NK053('i)001:9335: man ngag he ru ka'i gal po dang /
NK053('i)001:9336: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i gzhung dang gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:9338: man ngag gi rgyud he ru ka'i gal po dang /
NK053('i)001:9339: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i mdo dang gnyis kyi gzhung du bya na /
NK053('i)001:9340: lha bskyed pa'i rim pa la yang gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:9341: gtso bo yab yum bskyed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:9344: de la 1gtso bo yab yum bskyed pa ni /
NK053('i)001:9346: nam mkha'i dkyil nas ye shes shar //
NK053('i)001:9347: nges pa las ni rdo rje che //
NK053('i)001:9348: de las bcom ldan rdo rje sems //
NK053('i)001:9349: gsang ba'i yum dang gnyis med 'khril //
NK053('i)001:9351: de yang gong gi nam mkha'i dbyings na gsal ba'i ye shes sems dpa' de /
NK053('i)001:9352: badz+ra tsit+ta a be sha ya a /
NK053('i)001:9354: dbus kyi gdan stengs su dkar lhag gis babs pa las /
NK053('i)001:9355: 'od du 'bar nas yi ge h'u du gyur /
NK053('i)001:9366: rdo rje rtse lnga par gyur /
NK053('i)001:9370: rigs thams cad kyi bdag nyid /
NK053('i)001:9371: bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa' zhes bya ba /
NK053('i)001:9375: zhabs gnyis mnyam pa'i skyil mo krung du bzhugs pa /
NK053('i)001:9376: sku zhi ba'i tshul dang ldan zhing /
NK053('i)001:9377: rin po che'i rgyan gyis sbud pa /
NK053('i)001:9379: sku gsung thugs mnga' bdag ye shes lnga'i dbu rgyan dang ldan par bsgom pa la /
NK053('i)001:9384: bdag nyid de ltar gsal ba'i thugs ka nas yi ge m+aum 'phros shing 'dus pa las /
NK053('i)001:9389: yum rdo rje dbyings phyug ma g.yon du bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:9390: de yang sku mdog dang phyag mtshan ci lta bu zhe na /
NK053('i)001:9392: gtso bo mi bskyod mthing ka dkar dmar zhal //
NK053('i)001:9393: rdo rje 'khor lo rin chen g.yas //
NK053('i)001:9394: dril bu pad+ma ral gri g.yon //
NK053('i)001:9395: dbyings phyug ma g.yas yab la brten g.yon dril sngo //
NK053('i)001:9397: de nas 2'khor bskyed pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:9398: thugs rje che dang ldan pa yi //
NK053('i)001:9402: dang po mkha' gsang byin gyis brlab cing yig 'bru dang mkhar lha bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:9403: gnyis pa phyir rigs bzhi bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:9404: gsum pa phyi nang gi sems dpa' yab yum bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:9405: bzhi pa kun bzang yab yum bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:9406: lnga pa thub pa drug bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:9407: drug pa sgo ba yab yum bskyed pa'o //
NK053('i)001:9408: dang po mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:9409: yab ye shes lnga'i bdag nyid thugs rje chen po'i mnga' bdag /
NK053('i)001:9410: sku phyag rgya chen por gsal ba dang /
NK053('i)001:9411: yum mi 'bral ba'i gzungs ma dam tshig gi phyag rgyar ldan gnyis las bskyed par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:9412: de yang yab kyi thugs ka nas /
NK053('i)001:9414: yum gyi mkha'i dngos po sbyangs 'od du zhu ba las /
NK053('i)001:9418: yum gyi mkha' nyid rin po che'i gzhal yas khang /
NK053('i)001:9419: pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa'i lte ba la /
NK053('i)001:9420: am dmar la dwangs par bsgom pa dang /
NK053('i)001:9421: yum gyi thugs ka nas h'u dkar po yab kyi mkha' la 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:9422: mkha'i dngos po sbyangs 'od du zhu ba dang /
NK053('i)001:9425: yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa /
NK053('i)001:9426: sked sgor rin po che'i phreng ba dang ldan pa'i /
NK053('i)001:9427: rtse mor nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du dkar
NK053('i)001:9428: po gcig gsal bar bsgom pa ni chos kyi phyag
NK053('i)001:9429: rgya'o // de nas las kyi phyag rgya la 'jug par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:9430: de yang rig pa dbyings la 'jug pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:9433: de nas yab yum gyi brda' so sor bskul te /
NK053('i)001:9434: sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:9437: zhes yab yum so sor chags pa bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:9438: dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes pa ni /
NK053('i)001:9439: yum gyi thugs ka nas gzung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:9442: dgyes pa bskyed pas byang chub sems sad nas /
NK053('i)001:9445: phata gyis mkha' la phab ste /
NK053('i)001:9446: tsit+ta e kre ma d+ha la /
NK053('i)001:9448: yum gyi mkha' la byang chub sems kyi chag chag bor /
NK053('i)001:9449: tig btab pa dang byang chub sems kyi thig le so sor gsal ba ni /
NK053('i)001:9450: gsang ba'i sa bon zhes bya ste /
NK053('i)001:9452: bo d+hi tsit+ta p+au tsa s+pha ra na phata /
NK053('i)001:9454: byang chub sems thig le las 'od 'phros /
NK053('i)001:9458: slar 'dus pa las gnyis su med par gyur te /
NK053('i)001:9459: de las gsung yig 'brur gyur pa ni ye shes kyi sa bon zhes bya ste /
NK053('i)001:9460: gsang ba'i sa bon dang ye shes kyi sa bon gnyis su med par gyur pa las /
NK053('i)001:9461: gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams bskyed pa'i sa bon du shes par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:9463: ye shes dam tshig chen po dag /
NK053('i)001:9464: pad+ma rin chen ldan byas nas //
NK053('i)001:9465: bde mchog sgyu ma'i brdas mtshon te //
NK053('i)001:9466: dbyings kyi bde chen 'byung ba de //
NK053('i)001:9467: rang rig ye shes de la 'od //
NK053('i)001:9468: ji bzhin mkha' la gsal ba dag /
NK053('i)001:9470: byang chub sems las yig 'bru'i sku //
NK053('i)001:9484: nam mkha'i snying po tram tram /
NK053('i)001:9497: kun tu bzang po h'u a /
NK053('i)001:9527: lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis gsal bar bskyed //
NK053('i)001:9528: gnyis pa phyi rigs lnga bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:9529: de las phyi'i dkyil 'khor so so'i gdan stengs su gdon pa ni /
NK053('i)001:9533: dbus mi bskyod pa yab yum bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:9535: yum gyi gsang ba'i gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:9536: byang chub sems las skur gsal ba //
NK053('i)001:9537: rdo rje sems dpal yab yum gnyis /
NK053('i)001:9538: spro zhing rang la thim par bya //
NK053('i)001:9542: snang mdzad dkar sngo dmar ba'i zhal //
NK053('i)001:9543: 'khor lo rdo rje rin chen g.yas //
NK053('i)001:9544: dril bu pad+ma ral gri g.yon //
NK053('i)001:9545: spyan ma g.yas brten g.yon dril dkar //
NK053('i)001:9549: rin chen ser sngo dmar ba'i zhal //
NK053('i)001:9550: rin chen rdo rje 'khor lo g.yas //
NK053('i)001:9551: dril bu pad+ma ral gri g.yon //
NK053('i)001:9552: ma ma g.yas brten g.yon dril ser //
NK053('i)001:9556: mtha' yas dmar sngo dkar ba'i zhal //
NK053('i)001:9558: dril bu rin chen pad+ma ral gri g.yon //
NK053('i)001:9559: gos dkar g.yas brten g.yon dril dmar //
NK053('i)001:9563: don grub ljang dkar dmar ba'i zhal //
NK053('i)001:9564: ral gri rdo rje 'khor lo g.yas //
NK053('i)001:9565: dril bu yid bzhin pad+ma g.yon //
NK053('i)001:9566: sgrol ma g.yas brten g.yon dril ljang //
NK053('i)001:9569: nang sems yab yum bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:9572: sems ma h'u la s+ye sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:9573: lho dang po'i tram a gar ba ya /
NK053('i)001:9574: tram ma l+ye sa ma ya hoh nub dang po'i hri ha h'u pad+ma pa da ma /
NK053('i)001:9576: byang dang po'i dzim ku ru pa ni ya hoh a nirti ra ga ya mye /
NK053('i)001:9577: sa snying dkar gsal myu gu dril //
NK053('i)001:9578: gzugs ni la s+ye me long dkar //
NK053('i)001:9579: nam snying mthing ga ral gri dril //
NK053('i)001:9580: sgra ni ma l+ye phreng ba sngo //
NK053('i)001:9581: spyan ras dmar skya pad+ma dril //
NK053('i)001:9582: dri ni g+airti pi wam dmar //
NK053('i)001:9583: rdo rje ljang ku rdo rje dril //
NK053('i)001:9585: phyi sems yab yum bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:9586: shar gnyis pa'i sems dpa' me da ra ni s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:9587: sems ma dzahd+hup+pe pra we sha /
NK053('i)001:9589: thim sa ram pa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:9592: h'u s+w+aa ra tsa ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:9593: bam d+hi pam su ki ri /
NK053('i)001:9595: mum sh+ri a ram ga ya s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:9597: byams dkar klu shing g.yon na dril //
NK053('i)001:9598: d+hup+pe dkar mo spos phor bsnams //
NK053('i)001:9599: sgrib sel sngon po po ti dril //
NK053('i)001:9600: push+pe sngon mo me tog bsnams //
NK053('i)001:9601: kun bzang snye ma dril bu dmar //
NK053('i)001:9602: a lo dmar mo mar me gsal //
NK053('i)001:9604: gan+de ljang ku dri chab bsnams //
NK053('i)001:9605: bzhi pa kun bzang yab yum bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:9607: a a a badz+ra b+ha dra sa man+ta /
NK053('i)001:9609: kun bzang mnyam bzhag ye shes 'phro //
NK053('i)001:9611: lnga pa thub drug bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:9617: shar lhor mu ne srum s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:9619: nub stod du mu ne brem s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:9621: byang shar mu ne k+sham s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:9626: lha dbang phyag na pi wam bsnams //
NK053('i)001:9627: lha min thub pa go cha bsnams //
NK053('i)001:9628: sh+aakya thub pa gseg par bsnams //
NK053('i)001:9629: sh+aakya seng ge po ti bsnams //
NK053('i)001:9630: yi dwags thub pa rin chen sgrom //
NK053('i)001:9631: chos kyi rgyal po me chu bsnams //
NK053('i)001:9633: drug pa sgo ba yab yum bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:9636: badz+ra d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri dzahphata /
NK053('i)001:9639: rat+na d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:9642: pad+ma d+har ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri bam phata /
NK053('i)001:9645: karma d+ha ra ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri hohphata /
NK053('i)001:9646: phyogs mdog gam gshin rje gshed po thod dbyug bsnams /
NK053('i)001:9648: dza dza dkar mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK053('i)001:9649: gzhan gyis mi thub rdo rje bsnams //
NK053('i)001:9650: a lo ser nag zhags pa bsnams //
NK053('i)001:9651: rta mgrin dmar nag thod sbrul bsnams //
NK053('i)001:9652: lo ka dmar mo lcags sgrog bsnams //
NK053('i)001:9653: bdud rtsi ljang nag rgya gram bsnams //
NK053('i)001:9654: g+hasma ljang nag dril bu bsnams //
NK053('i)001:9655: zhes he ru ka'i gal po las 'byung bas /
NK053('i)001:9657: de ltar sku las chos dam phyag rgya chen po bzhi dang ldan pas /
NK053('i)001:9658: dkyil 'khor bskyed pa de'i gtso bo dpal rdo rje sems dpas bya bar gsungs la /
NK053('i)001:9661: rnam par snang mdzad la sogs pa'i /
NK053('i)001:9664: rigs lnga la sogs pa'i lha dag kun kyang sku
NK053('i)001:9665: lnga ye shes lnga dang ldan pa'i thugs rje che
NK053('i)001:9668: dkyil 3'khor gyi dbye ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:9674: spyir 1ni dkyil 'khor gyi lha de dag kun la yang /
NK053('i)001:9675: dkyil 'khor lnga dang ldan par dgos pas na dkyil 'khor lnga /
NK053('i)001:9678: yab thabs kyi sku phyag rgyar lhag lhag gsal ba ni /
NK053('i)001:9680: de'i g.yon du yum dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang mi 'bral ba ni /
NK053('i)001:9682: kun la rang rang gi dbu rgyan dang /
NK053('i)001:9683: ljags rdo rje rtse gsum rtse mor pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa dang /
NK053('i)001:9684: so so'i thugs ka na rang rang gi ye shes
NK053('i)001:9685: sems dpa' la thugs phyag mtshan gsung yig 'bru dang
NK053('i)001:9687: byin rlabs sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK053('i)001:9688: kun gyi sku la so so'i rgyan cha lugs so sor gsal ba ni /
NK053('i)001:9690: mkha'i dbyings rdo rje dang pad+ma ldan zhing yab yum 'khril 'khyud du bzhugs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:9691: mkha' gsang sbyor ba'i dkyil 'khor ro //
NK053('i)001:9696: thugs rje che dang ldan pa yi //
NK053('i)001:9698: sku phyag rgyar gsal ba de dag gi so so'i /
NK053('i)001:9699: ye shes kyi thugs ka dang /
NK053('i)001:9702: smin mtshams la sogs pa'i gnas nas /
NK053('i)001:9703: ye shes kyi 'od zer kha dog lnga lnga nyi shu rtsa lnga 'od zer du 'phro zhing /
NK053('i)001:9704: thugs rjes kun la khyab par mdzad de /
NK053('i)001:9705: spyir ni sems can kun gyi las dang nyon mongs pa'i bag chags sbyang zhing dag par mdzad la /
NK053('i)001:9706: khyad par du rnal 'byor pa'i phrin las rnam pa bzhi lhun gyis grub par mdzad pa'o //
NK053('i)001:9709: nyon mongs pa lnga ser sna dag drug las bsags pa'i 'gro ba ris drug ste /
NK053('i)001:9712: thub pa chen po drug la gong gi don dal lnga de dag dang mi ldan zhing /
NK053('i)001:9713: 'gro ba rigs drug gi gtso bo'i thabs su snang zhing /
NK053('i)001:9714: lha rnams kyi 'khor du snang bas na /
NK053('i)001:9717: rdo rje sems dpa' sangs rgyas kun gyi gtso //
NK053('i)001:9718: rdo rje dbyings phyug mkha' klong dag pa nas //
NK053('i)001:9719: rgyal ba rigs lnga sems dpa' sems ma sras bcas dkyil 'khor lnga dang ldan //
NK053('i)001:9720: thugs rje kun la khyab par don mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:9721: ris drug gtso bo'i g.yog 'khor ma lus rnams //
NK053('i)001:9722: bdag gzhan bsgom sgrub drangs bzhugs bkod nas sbyangs //
NK053('i)001:9727: rnam par snang mdzad la thub pa chen po drug gi 'khor gyis bskor la /
NK053('i)001:9728: rdo rjee sems dpa' la sa snying byams pa gshed po yab yum drug gi 'khor gyis bskor /
NK053('i)001:9729: rin chen 'byung ldan la nam snying sgrib sel stobs chen yab yum drug gi 'khor gyis bskor /
NK053('i)001:9730: snang ba mtha' yas la spyan ras gzigs kun bzang rta mgrin yab yum drug gi 'khor gyis bskor /
NK053('i)001:9731: don yod grub pa la phyag na rdo rjee 'jam
NK053('i)001:9732: dpal bdud rtsi yab yum drug gi 'khor gyis bskor
NK053('i)001:9737: mkha' 'gro sum cu rtsa gnyis kyis bskor te /
NK053('i)001:9738: rdo rje sems dpa' la brgyad /
NK053('i)001:9740: spyi bzhis bskor te gnas so //
NK053('i)001:9743: tshom bu drug pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK053('i)001:9746: de ltar bskyed pa'i rim pa de yang /
NK053('i)001:9747: khungs dag pa gang gis gsungs shing /
NK053('i)001:9748: lung gang las 'byung snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:9749: grub pas bstan pa'i lung bzhin du //
NK053('i)001:9751: de la sku gsum lhun gyis grub pa'i dpal rdo rje sems dpas bstan pa'i lung /
NK053('i)001:9753: he ru ka'i gal po las /
NK053('i)001:9754: ji skad du 'byung ba bzhin du /
NK053('i)001:9755: zhi khro gnyis kyi dkyil 'khor 'dir bkod pa'o //
NK053('i)001:9756: de yang tshul ji ltar snang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:9757: sku mdog so sor gsal ba yi //
NK053('i)001:9758: phyag rgya'i rgyan dang cha lugs dag /
NK053('i)001:9760: de yang rgyud ma h+aa yo ga dang sbyar ba yin te /
NK053('i)001:9761: cho ga rnam pa gsum gsung yig 'bru /
NK053('i)001:9764: rim gyis bskyed pa'i lha rnams kyis sku mdog ces pa de yang ji lta bu zhe na /
NK053('i)001:9766: mthing ka dkar po ser le brgan //
NK053('i)001:9767: ljang ku la sogs sna tshogs mtshan //
NK053('i)001:9769: rigs rnam pa lnga'i kha dog so sor gsal ba
NK053('i)001:9770: yi tshul las gzhan du 'gyur ba ni ma yin
NK053('i)001:9772: zhes pa la don bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:9773: yab rnams ni sku phyag rgya chen po /
NK053('i)001:9774: so sor thugs ka ngang mkha' dbyings rdo rje dang
NK053('i)001:9775: pad+ma la gsung yig 'brus mtshan pa ni chos kyi
NK053('i)001:9776: phyag rgya / de dag kun kyang phyag rgya bzhis
NK053('i)001:9777: 'du ba mdzad cing bsgul bskyod mdzad pas dam tshig
NK053('i)001:9778: phyag rgya / gi phyag rgya / rtag tu bde
NK053('i)001:9779: ba dang mi 'bral bar bzhugs pa ni las kyi
NK053('i)001:9780: phyag rgya / gi phyag rgya / phyag rgya'o // rgyan dang /
NK053('i)001:9783: rin po che'i dbu rgyan dang /
NK053('i)001:9787: mu tig gi se mo do dang /
NK053('i)001:9791: gzhan yang gtso bo rnams la ni /
NK053('i)001:9793: sku'i chas sku stod dar dkar gser gyi ngang ris kyis stod g.yogs byas te /
NK053('i)001:9794: gsung gi chas pa ti smug po'i smad dkris dang /
NK053('i)001:9795: thugs kyi cod pan nam zi lding dang /
NK053('i)001:9796: yon tan gyi chos gos dang /
NK053('i)001:9797: phrin las kyi phyag rgya'i phu rung dang ldan pa bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:9798: sems dpa' rnams la rin po che'i rgyan dang smad dkris las med par bshad do //
NK053('i)001:9799: thub pa drug la dar dkar gser gyi ngang ris can gyis stod g.yogs byas te /
NK053('i)001:9800: pa ti ser po se gdar ris kyis sham thabs su mdzad pa las /
NK053('i)001:9802: sgo bzhi'i khro bo la ni dpal gyi chas brgyad kyis brgyan par bgo ba'i gos gsum /
NK053('i)001:9808: sku ji ltar snang ba'i tshul lo //
NK053('i)001:9810: gtso bo dang gtso mo rnams ni rdzogs pa'i skyil krung du bzhugs so //
NK053('i)001:9811: sems dpa' dang sems ma rnams ni phyed skyil du bzhugs so //
NK053('i)001:9812: thub pa rnams ni 'greng bur bzhugs so //
NK053('i)001:9813: kun bzang yab yum yang rdzogs pa'i skyil krung du bzhugs so //
NK053('i)001:9814: sgo bzhi'i khro bo dang khro mo rnams kyi gyad kyi 'dor stabs su bzhugs so //
NK053('i)001:9815: de la sku ji ltar snang ba'i tshul ni dgu ste /
NK053('i)001:9820: gzi byin dang ldan par bzhugs so //
NK053('i)001:9826: gzhon tshul can du bzhugs so //
NK053('i)001:9827: thub pa rnams ni rab tu byung ba'i tshul can du bzhugs so //
NK053('i)001:9828: sgo bzhi'i khro bo yab yum rnams ni /
NK053('i)001:9829: khro khro dang gtum gtum ltar bzhugs so //
NK053('i)001:9830: de la sku'i 'od zer ji ltar snang ba ni /
NK053('i)001:9831: rigs lnga yab yum sras kun bzang yab yum ni 'od 'ja' tshon sna lnga'i nang na bzhugs so //
NK053('i)001:9832: sems dpa' yab yum dang thub pa rnams ni 'od sna gsum gyi nang na bzhugs so //
NK053('i)001:9833: khro bo dang khro mo rnams ni bskal pa'i me
NK053('i)001:9834: 'bar ba'i phreng ba 'khrigs pa'i nang na bzhugs so
NK053('i)001:9838: ye shes rol pa'i bye brag tu so sor bstan pa de yang /
NK053('i)001:9839: rnal 'byor pa'i spyod yul nag nog dang ra ri ma yin pa /
NK053('i)001:9840: ye shes gsal bkrar shar bar bsgom //
NK053('i)001:9842: de ltar bsgoms pa'i 'bras bu ni /
NK053('i)001:9843: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen gyi sa non /
NK053('i)001:9844: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku dang /
NK053('i)001:9847: ging gi rgyu ting 'bras bu'ang 'di yin no //
NK053('i)001:9848: de dag ni bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga'i lugs te brtan cha thob nas /
NK053('i)001:9850: 3 / rdzogs pa'i rim pa bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:9851: bskyed rdzogs grub pa'i lha dag bsgom //
NK053('i)001:9853: de yang lung man ngag gnyis las /
NK053('i)001:9855: bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga ltar ma yin /
NK053('i)001:9856: a nu yo ga'i rdzogs pa'i tshul du ste /
NK053('i)001:9857: don dam par chos nyid skye 'gag med pa las /
NK053('i)001:9858: kun rdzob tu dngos po thams cad lha dang lha
NK053('i)001:9859: mo'i dkyil 'khor du rang snang bar rtogs pa bya
NK053('i)001:9860: ste / nyams bag tu yang rnal 'byor pas /
NK053('i)001:9861: don dam par chos nyid skye 'gag med pa'i ngang las mi g.yo la /
NK053('i)001:9862: kun rdzob tu snying po brjod pa tsam gyis snang
NK053('i)001:9863: zhing srid pas bsdus pa ril lha'i dkyil 'khor du
NK053('i)001:9865: man 2ngag rdzogs pa chen po'i gzhung gis /
NK053('i)001:9866: rgyud dang lung gnyis kyi dgongs pa des kyang so so na yod pa ma yin te /
NK053('i)001:9867: chos thams cad kyi grub pa'i lugs //
NK053('i)001:9868: bden pa gnyis dbyer med pas /
NK053('i)001:9869: thams cad sku gsung thugs phyag rgya chen po lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis su /
NK053('i)001:9870: ye bka' phyi mo nas dag par bsgom zhes te /
NK053('i)001:9871: de yang ji ltar bsgom zhe na /
NK053('i)001:9872: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos thams cad /
NK053('i)001:9873: chos nyid ma skyes pa'i rang bzhin la /
NK053('i)001:9874: bya ba byed nus pa'i sgyu ma /
NK053('i)001:9875: bde bar gshegs pa yab yum bcu la sogs pa'i rang bzhin ye nas yin pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:9876: chos thams cad rang bzhin gyis mya ngan las 'das pa ste /
NK053('i)001:9877: de yang ji lta bu zhe na /
NK053('i)001:9878: phung po lnga ni rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas lnga'o //
NK053('i)001:9879: 'byung ba chen po lnga ni yum lnga'i rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:9880: rnam par shes pa bzhi ni byang chub sems dpa' bzhi'i rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:9881: yul bzhi ni mdzes pa'i lha mo bzhi'i rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:9882: dbang po bzhi ni byang chub sems dpa' bzhi yi rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:9883: dus bzhi ni mchod pa'i lha mo bzhi'i rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:9884: phyin ci log drug ni thub pa chen po drug gi rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:9888: de las byung ba'i byang chub kyi sems ni khro bo bzhi'i rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:9889: rtag chad mu bzhi khro mo bzhi'i rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:9890: yid kyi rnam par shes pa ni byang chub kyi sems kun tu bzang po'i rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:9891: de'i yul chos 'dus byas dang 'dus ma byas ni kun tu bzang mo'i rang bzhin te /
NK053('i)001:9892: de dag kyang ye nas mngon par sangs rgyas pa'i rang bzhin yin gyi /
NK053('i)001:9893: da lam gyis bsgrub pa ni ma yin no //
NK053('i)001:9896: 2 / de la rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs zhing /
NK053('i)001:9897: mchod pa'i phrin las gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:9898: zhi ba'i mchod pas mnyes pa dag /
NK053('i)001:9900: de la dang po spyan drangs pa la /
NK053('i)001:9902: rang bzhin gyi gnas nas spyan drangs pa /
NK053('i)001:9903: mdun gyi nam mkha' la spyan drangs pa /
NK053('i)001:9904: gzhal yas khang gi nang du spyan drangs pa /
NK053('i)001:9905: rig pa'i me tog dor ba /
NK053('i)001:9906: dam ye dbyer med bstim pa /
NK053('i)001:9907: brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba'o //
NK053('i)001:9908: gnyis pa mchod pa'i phrin las la /
NK053('i)001:9911: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa /
NK053('i)001:9917: bzod gsol dang smon lam bya ba'o //
NK053('i)001:9918: snga ma drug gi dang po rang bzhin gnas nas spyan drangs pa /
NK053('i)001:9920: rig pa dbyings la 'jug cing thugs rje'i rol pas /
NK053('i)001:9921: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub mngon du thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:9922: rang bzhin phrin las kyi bye brag bstan pa la /
NK053('i)001:9923: 'dir man ngag tu bsdus te bstan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:9924: phyag rgya dpung mgor bsnol nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:9925: rdo rje se gol bsnol mar brdab //
NK053('i)001:9926: sangs rgyas thams cad bsdu bar bya //
NK053('i)001:9927: badz+ra sa m+aa dzah zhes brjod nas /
NK053('i)001:9928: rang nyid kyi thugs ka dang /
NK053('i)001:9929: gsang ba'i mkha' las 'od zer lcags kyu lta bu bsam gyis mi khyab pa spro zhing /
NK053('i)001:9931: se gol las kyang 'od ze sgra dang bcas par 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:9932: bskul ba'i 'od zer gsum byung bas /
NK053('i)001:9933: gcig gis rang bzhin chos sku gcig gi ngang las gzugs skur bzhengs su gsol /
NK053('i)001:9934: gcig gis phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi mchod pa phul /
NK053('i)001:9935: gcig gis sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub nod pa'i sgra byung bas /
NK053('i)001:9936: chos nyid las ye shes kyi sku thugs rje nyer bsdogs su rong nge gnas pa las /
NK053('i)001:9937: gnyis pa mdun mkhar spyan drangs ba /
NK053('i)001:9939: dmigs med mkha' ltar dag pas khyab pa'i sku //
NK053('i)001:9940: spyan drangs gshegs su gsol bar mi dmigs kyang //
NK053('i)001:9941: thugs rje'i ngang nyid chos sku dag pa las //
NK053('i)001:9942: ye shes sgyu mas rol cing gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:9943: e h+ya hi b+ha ga wan /
NK053('i)001:9944: ma h+aa ka ru ni ka dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:9945: dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes brjod pas /
NK053('i)001:9947: zhing khams so so nas til gyi gang bu bzhin du bsam gyis mi khyab cing /
NK053('i)001:9948: 'od zer 'khrigs shing 'bar bar thims se mngon du byon nas /
NK053('i)001:9949: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor dang 'od phung 'dab 'dres tsam du bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:9950: gsum pa gzhal yas khang du spyan drang ba /
NK053('i)001:9951: de nas phyag rgya bzhis spyan drangs te /
NK053('i)001:9952: thugs rje'i lcags kyus thugs dam rgyud skul zhing //
NK053('i)001:9953: byams pa'i zhags pas gnas nas spyan 'dren gyis //
NK053('i)001:9954: bka' yi pho nya lcags sgrog mas ni gnas stobs la //
NK053('i)001:9955: bde gshegs dril bu mas ni rnam grol dgyes pa bskyed //
NK053('i)001:9958: zhes bya ba la sogs pa bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis kyi sngags brjod pas /
NK053('i)001:9959: yab yum gyi thugs ka dang gsang ba'i mkha' las
NK053('i)001:9960: phyag rgya bzhi 'od zer gyi tshul du 'phros pas
NK053('i)001:9961: / gzhal yas khang gi nang du spyan drangs te /
NK053('i)001:9964: 'od phung khrug gis 'dres par bsgoms la //
NK053('i)001:9965: bzhi pa rig me dor ba /
NK053('i)001:9966: lha gang yin pa bdag yin /
NK053('i)001:9967: bdag gang yin pa lha yin te /
NK053('i)001:9968: don dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med par rtogs na /
NK053('i)001:9969: rtags rig pa'i me tog bor zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:9970: lnga pa dbyer med bstim pa /
NK053('i)001:9971: de nas dbyings rig pa la thim zhing /
NK053('i)001:9972: rig pa dbyings la zhugs pa'i rtags su /
NK053('i)001:9973: dbyer med par bstim pa ni /
NK053('i)001:9975: rang snang dbyer med dkyil 'khor la //
NK053('i)001:9976: thugs rje'i mgon gyur ma lus rnams //
NK053('i)001:9978: bdag la dgyes nas thim par bzhugs //
NK053('i)001:9984: bye ma la mar thim pa'am /
NK053('i)001:9985: ba mo la kha ba bab pa ltar dbyer med par thim par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:9986: drug pa brtan par bzhug pa /
NK053('i)001:9987: de nyid byang chub sems dngos po mi 'gyur ba'i ngang las /
NK053('i)001:9988: ye shes kyi dngos por grub cing cir yang snang ba thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:9989: brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba ni /
NK053('i)001:9990: rgyal ba'i sku la bzhengs bzhugs mi mnga' yang //
NK053('i)001:9991: ye shes gnyis med dbyings su thim pas na /
NK053('i)001:9992: thabs dang shes rab ting 'dzin dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK053('i)001:9993: mi g.yo dgyes shing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:9994: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta s+t+wam badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:9996: gnyis pa mchod pa'i ngag don la brgyad las /
NK053('i)001:9997: dang po phyag gi mchod pa /
NK053('i)001:9998: de nas ye shes sprul pa'i sku mngon du shar
NK053('i)001:9999: ba la gnyis su med par rtogs pas dgyes pa'i
NK053('i)001:10002: dbyings kun rang bzhin rnam par dag pa las //
NK053('i)001:10003: thugs rje'i dbang gis sprul pa'i skur bzhengs pa //
NK053('i)001:10004: rdo rje'i dbyings kyi lha tshogs bzhi bcu gnyis //
NK053('i)001:10005: rang snang lha tshogs rnams la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:10006: a ti pu hoh pra ti pu hoh gnyis pa phyag rgya'i mchod pa /
NK053('i)001:10007: dbyings kyi don mtshon cing ye shes rol pa'i mchod pa dbul ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:10008: gar phyag rgya'i mchod pa bya ste /
NK053('i)001:10010: rtsa bar gyur pa'i phyag rgya ni //
NK053('i)001:10011: g.yas pa thabs kyi rang bzhin la //
NK053('i)001:10012: g.yon pa shes rab yum gyi ngang //
NK053('i)001:10013: thams dang shes rab ldan gyur na //
NK053('i)001:10014: sbyor ba'i phyag rgya 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK053('i)001:10015: yab kyi rdo rje la h'u /
NK053('i)001:10016: yum gyi pad+ma la am bsam pa'am /
NK053('i)001:10018: g.yon yum gyi 'bru lnga gsal ba'i /
NK053('i)001:10019: 'bru rnams bsnol te rtse sprad pa //
NK053('i)001:10020: bde ba chen po spyi yi rgya //
NK053('i)001:10021: rnam par grol ba mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:10022: mi bskyod pa rdo rje rnam snang 'khor lo rin 'byung rin po che //
NK053('i)001:10023: snang mtha' pad+ma don grub ral gri yum rnams dril bu 'bar //
NK053('i)001:10024: sa snying rin chen myu gu nam snying ral gri 'bar //
NK053('i)001:10025: spyan gzigs pad+ma dkar po phyag rdor rdo rje 'bar //
NK053('i)001:10026: la s+ye gzugs mdzes ma l+ye rin chen phreng ba dang //
NK053('i)001:10027: g+airti pi wam n+airti gar mkhan mchog nyid de //
NK053('i)001:10028: byams pa klu shing sgrib sel chos kyi 'khor lo dang //
NK053('i)001:10029: kun bzang rin chen snye dang 'jam dpal ud+pala la //
NK053('i)001:10030: push+pe me tog phreng dang d+hup+pe spos mchog ma //
NK053('i)001:10031: +aa lo ke mar me g+han+d+he byug pa la sogs pa'i //
NK053('i)001:10032: kun bzang mnyam bzhag ye shes 'phro //
NK053('i)001:10033: bzang mo yum 'gyur mnyam rdzogs pad+mo'i skyil //
NK053('i)001:10034: lha'i thub pa pi wam dang ni mi thub seg par dang //
NK053('i)001:10035: lha min go cha byol song po ti yi dwags rin chen sgrom //
NK053('i)001:10036: dmyal thub me dang chur ni rab tu bstan //
NK053('i)001:10037: gshin rje gshed n+ri mgo gdengs dang stobs po che rdo rjes gnon //
NK053('i)001:10038: rta mgrin thod sbrul chen po gdengs pa dang //
NK053('i)001:10039: bdud rtsi 'khyil pa rdo rje rgya gram las gyis gnon //
NK053('i)001:10040: sgom bzhi lcags kyu zhags pa s+pho ta lcags sgrog hoh /
NK053('i)001:10042: lag pa gar dang mgrin pa dbyangs kyi mchong pa 'di 'bul gyis //
NK053('i)001:10043: chos nyid dag pas dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK053('i)001:10044: gsum pa dbyings kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa /
NK053('i)001:10045: de nas thams cad spang blang gi stong pa dang
NK053('i)001:10046: bral zhing gnyis med du stong la mchod pa'i rgyu
NK053('i)001:10047: yin pa'i phyir / kun tu bzang po dbye ba med pa'i mchod pa bya ste /
NK053('i)001:10048: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:10049: rgyal ba rgya mtsho ye shes kyis //
NK053('i)001:10050: srid pa rgya mtsho mtha' yas kun //
NK053('i)001:10051: kun bzang mchod sprin mchog tu rol //
NK053('i)001:10052: na mahsarba ta th+aa ga te b+h+yo bi sha mu she b+h+ya /
NK053('i)001:10053: sarba tad+kham ud+ga te s+pha ra na hi mam ga ga na kham swa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:10054: bzhi pa mchod pa bdun dbul ba /
NK053('i)001:10055: phyi nang gi bka' rgyud mtha' dag dang mi 'gal bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:10056: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyis bsdus pa'i mchod pa /
NK053('i)001:10057: ar+g+ham me tog spos ma me mi dri chab zhal zas sgra'i bdun gyis mchod pa bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:10059: ar+g+ham me tog bdug spos dang //
NK053('i)001:10060: mar me dri chab bshos dang sgra //
NK053('i)001:10061: phyi nang gsang bar sbyar ba rnams //
NK053('i)001:10062: bdag dang mnyam pa'i tshogs la dbul //
NK053('i)001:10064: de yang dang po la mchod pa rnams spyi la byin gyis brlabs shing dbul ba ni /
NK053('i)001:10071: sarba ta th+aa ga ta si te'u /
NK053('i)001:10072: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi dngos grub /
NK053('i)001:10075: sarba ma h+aa su kha si de'u /
NK053('i)001:10076: thams cad bde ba chen po dam pa grub par mdzod /
NK053('i)001:10080: yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che lta bu las /
NK053('i)001:10081: ji ltar dmigs pa'i mchod pa 'phro bar bsgoms te /
NK053('i)001:10083: srid gsum dbyings su shar ba'i mchod rdzas te //
NK053('i)001:10084: de nyid ma bcos yum gyi thig ler shar //
NK053('i)001:10085: chags yul bde bas 'od dpung dmar la 'khyil //
NK053('i)001:10086: nyon mongs dbying su bstim phyir ar+g+ham bzhes //
NK053('i)001:10088: rak+ta tsit+ta shwa ta ni s+w+aa h+aa //
NK053('i)001:10091: de yang snod yum gyi b+ha ga mtha' dbus med pa na /
NK053('i)001:10092: phyir bstan pas bdud rtsi'i rgyun 'o gar dmigs te dbul /
NK053('i)001:10093: nang ltar rak+tasa snang srid thams cad phyam gyis mchod par dmigs /
NK053('i)001:10094: gsang bar yab yum gyi lhag pa byang chub sems dkar dmar gyis mchod par dmigs /
NK053('i)001:10097: 'byung lnga dbyings las ye shes bcud shar ba //
NK053('i)001:10098: snang srid mdangs bsdus rang byung me tog gsal //
NK053('i)001:10099: gnyis med ngang las kha dog cir yang shar //
NK053('i)001:10100: 'bras bu bcud ldan 'od phung med tog 'bul //
NK053('i)001:10102: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga push+pe pus /
NK053('i)001:10104: zhes brjod de me tog gis mchod la /
NK053('i)001:10107: me tog gi mchod pa mdzes shing kha dog rnam pa sna tshogs pas stong gsum gang bar bsam /
NK053('i)001:10108: nang du mdzes pa'i lha mo mang pos mchod par bsam /
NK053('i)001:10109: gsang ba bdag gi rnams par shes pa tshogs brgyad ye shes su shar bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10111: h'u ma bcos rang byung dam rdzas spos mchos 'di /
NK053('i)001:10112: kha dog dbyibs gsal dbang po tshim byed pa'i /
NK053('i)001:10113: stong gsum gang ba'i dri bsung bdug pa 'di //
NK053('i)001:10114: 'bar ba'i sha ngas su mchod pas mnyes gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:10116: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga d+h+aup+pe d+h+au spos me ma sngo /
NK053('i)001:10120: dri'i lha mo lag na spos kong thos pa mang
NK053('i)001:10121: po spos kyi dud pa sprin tsam du 'phro bas
NK053('i)001:10123: nang du tshil chen gyi dud pa dang zhing chen gyi ngad bsung bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10124: gsang bar byang chub sems kyi dri ngad bsung bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10127: snod bcud gnyis med yab yum dag pa las /
NK053('i)001:10128: 'bras bu rang byung ye shes mer shar nas //
NK053('i)001:10129: mtha' dbus med par gsal ba'i 'od 'bar 'di //
NK053('i)001:10130: 'khor ba'i mun khang gzhom phyir bzhegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:10132: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga a lo ke h+r+aih mar me ma dmar skya /
NK053('i)001:10136: kong bu stong gsum tsam la mar khu rgya mtsho tsam /
NK053('i)001:10137: me lce'i 'od kyis srid pa gsum khyab par bsgom /
NK053('i)001:10138: nang du snod dur khrod 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang la /
NK053('i)001:10139: mar ni zhi gnas te tshil chen rgya mtsho tsam la /
NK053('i)001:10140: me lce lhag mthong ye shes lnga'i 'od 'phro bar bsgom /
NK053('i)001:10141: gsang bar bdag gi byang chub sems kyis ye shes
NK053('i)001:10142: kyi me mar stong 'char ba'i rtsa bar bsgom mo
NK053('i)001:10145: gnyis med mkha' dbyings dag pa'i pho brang du //
NK053('i)001:10146: nyon mongs skyon bral dag pa'i byang chub sems //
NK053('i)001:10147: cir yang 'char phyir dri yi 'od phung 'bul //
NK053('i)001:10148: zhal gyi dbyings su thim nas mnyes gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:10150: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga gan+d+he gan /
NK053('i)001:10155: lha mo dung phor thogs pa mang pos tsan+dana gyi 'de gus byug cing mchod par bsam /
NK053('i)001:10156: nang ltar byang chub sems kyi rlan gyis nyon mongs
NK053('i)001:10157: pa'i ljan ljin mang po gnas su dag par bsgom
NK053('i)001:10158: / gsang bar zhi gnas kyi rlan lhag pa'i byang chub sems su dag par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10161: nam mkha' kun bzang dbyings nas cir yang 'byung //
NK053('i)001:10162: 'byung ba'i 'bras bu 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga //
NK053('i)001:10163: lha bshos yid bzhin rin chen longs spyod 'di //
NK053('i)001:10164: sku gsung thugs kyi ngang du thim par bzhes //
NK053('i)001:10166: sh+ri badz+ra r+aa ga ne wi te kha kha kh+aa hi /
NK053('i)001:10170: phyi ltar zhal zas ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa ri rab bas che bar bsgom /
NK053('i)001:10171: nang du 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i lha mor bsgom /
NK053('i)001:10172: gsang ba byang chub kyi sems kyi thig le rin po che 'bar ba gcig bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10175: sgra yi dngos por snang ba yang //
NK053('i)001:10176: yod pa ma yin shin tu grag /
NK053('i)001:10177: sgra yis rab tu tshim 'gyur yang //
NK053('i)001:10178: sgra nyid rang bzhin gang yang med //
NK053('i)001:10180: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK053('i)001:10182: sh+ri badz+ra r+aa ga girti hri hri /
NK053('i)001:10190: sil snyan la sogs pa'i sgra dbyangs sna tshogs pas mchod par bsgoms la /
NK053('i)001:10191: nang du lha mo pi wam ma mang pos chos kyi sgra sgrogs pa dang mchod par bsgom /
NK053('i)001:10192: gsang bar byang chub sems gnyis su med pa se gol gyi sgras mchod par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10194: de nas bdud rtsi'i mchod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:10195: ngag don rnam pa gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:10199: de la yin pa 1la rnam pa gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:10200: bdag nyid rdo rje sems dpa' rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor yin pa des /
NK053('i)001:10201: sman rang byung bdud rtsi'i dkyil 'khor yin pa de byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:10204: snod yum gyi mkha' dbyings dag pa na nyi zla'i steng du /
NK053('i)001:10205: rdzas nyid bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga dang /
NK053('i)001:10206: sha lnga lcags kyu'i rnam pa lngar gsal ba'i gsang 'dus nas kyang bshad do //
NK053('i)001:10208: dpa' bo 'bru lnga gsal bar dmigs te /
NK053('i)001:10212: 'bru lnga las 'od 'phros pas bdud rtsi lnga'i skyon dag par byas /
NK053('i)001:10214: snang zhing srid pas bsdus pa'i rnam rtog bzhu btul /
NK053('i)001:10215: phyi nang snod bcud kyi rtsi bcud dang /
NK053('i)001:10216: ye shes kyi bdud rtsi kun bsdus te slar 'dus pa las /
NK053('i)001:10217: dpa' bo 'bru lnga yang 'od du zhu nas /
NK053('i)001:10218: dngos grub kyi rdzas dang dbyer med par gyur te /
NK053('i)001:10219: lhag pa sku gsung thugs kyi rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:10221: bdud rtsi byang chub kyi sems dkar lteng lteng gsal bar bsgom /
NK053('i)001:10222: de la rang bzhin grub pa'i gnas na rdo rje
NK053('i)001:10223: dbyings kyi lha tshogs bzhugs pa 'gro ba 'dul ba'i
NK053('i)001:10225: bdag rtsa ba'i dkyil 'khor gyis mchod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:10226: don skye shi 'du 'bral med pa'i ngang du lha rnams gnas pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:10227: rtags bdud rtsi byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin la ye shes kyi thigs pas mchod par bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:10228: che ba'i yon tan brjod pa /
NK053('i)001:10230: rang byung gdod nas dag pa'i rdzas //
NK053('i)001:10231: rtsa brgyad stong las sbyar ba'i sman //
NK053('i)001:10232: ra sa ya na la sogs rdzas //
NK053('i)001:10233: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK053('i)001:10234: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK053('i)001:10235: rgyu drug sems can kun sgrol phyir //
NK053('i)001:10236: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK053('i)001:10237: bcom ldan rigs lnga yab yum dang //
NK053('i)001:10238: byang chub sems dpa' lcam dral dang //
NK053('i)001:10239: kun bzang yab yum thub drug dang //
NK053('i)001:10240: sgo skyong yab yum mkha' 'gor 'khor bcas la //
NK053('i)001:10241: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK053('i)001:10242: thugs rjes bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK053('i)001:10243: tshangs pa 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:10244: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra ti dza hoh kha ram kha ram kha ram kh+aa hi //
NK053('i)001:10246: kha ram dang pos snang srid kyi chos thams cad kyang /
NK053('i)001:10247: bdud rtsi chen po'i rang bzhin du gyur par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10249: de nyid bsdus te lhag pa byang chub sems kyi
NK053('i)001:10250: rang bzhin rdzas la gnyis su med par bsgom mo
NK053('i)001:10252: mthe bong a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor dang /
NK053('i)001:10253: srin lag ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor /
NK053('i)001:10254: nyi zla ga'u gnyis kyis bdud rtsi blangs te /
NK053('i)001:10255: lha gang la mchod pa'i ljags kyi dbang po la lhan lhan thim par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10257: zhes pas sku gsung thugs kyi dgyes pa chen po bskyed par bsgoms la /
NK053('i)001:10258: h'u badz+ra d+h+rika rdo rje 'dzin pa /
NK053('i)001:10263: bdud rtsi thob pa kun la yang mchod par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:10264: zhes lha bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis tshang ma'i sngags mchod sbyar ro //
NK053('i)001:10265: mchod 'os gzhan la'ang sbyar rung ngo //
NK053('i)001:10266: sku gsung thugs dang lus ngag yid gsum dbyer med
NK053('i)001:10267: par rtogs par bya ba'i phyir dngos grub blangs te
NK053('i)001:10268: / lce yi dam tshig rdo rje la //
NK053('i)001:10270: rtse mor pad+ma 'dab bzhi pa rdo rje can gyi lte bar h'u bsgoms te //
NK053('i)001:10271: mthe bong dang ni srin lag rtses //
NK053('i)001:10272: thabs dang shes rab 'brel ba yi //
NK053('i)001:10273: myangs pas byang chub gsum thob 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:10276: gnas gsum du dngos grub blang ngo //
NK053('i)001:10280: h'u mthing ka gsum rim pas blangs te /
NK053('i)001:10281: 'phro 'du dkar dmar gyis kyang rim pas sbyangs la /
NK053('i)001:10282: ye shes sku gsung thugs su gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10285: bdud rtsi nyid ye shes kyi 'od zer sna lngas stong gsum khyab par dmigs la mchod de /
NK053('i)001:10286: dri med rnam dag nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK053('i)001:10287: log rtog mtshan ma mang po sprin phung bzhin //
NK053('i)001:10288: ye shes nyi zer 'od kyis rab bsal phyir //
NK053('i)001:10289: dag pa'i don du rtogs nas mchod par bgyi //
NK053('i)001:10296: dag pa'i don la dngos grub stsol /
NK053('i)001:10301: pra ti dza hoh kh+aa hi kh+aa hi //
NK053('i)001:10303: de ltar mchod pa'i dus na /
NK053('i)001:10304: sems can thams cad kyang don gong ma lta bu'i rang bzhin du mi gnyis par gcig pas /
NK053('i)001:10306: bdag nyid chen pos mchod byas pas //
NK053('i)001:10307: phyogs bcu'i sangs rgyas thams cad mnyes //
NK053('i)001:10308: srid gsum ma lus thams cad kyang //
NK053('i)001:10309: dga' ba chen pos khyab par 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:10311: rang bzhin gcig par rtogs nas 'chod pas /
NK053('i)001:10313: bdag gis kyang dngos grub thob /
NK053('i)001:10314: sems can thams cad kyang des tshim ste //
NK053('i)001:10316: phan 2yon la yang rnam pa gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:10317: rnam rtog rang bzhan med pa'i ngang du sbyangs pa'i bdud rtsi'i mchod pa des /
NK053('i)001:10318: mchod sbyin gyi dam pa yin pas /
NK053('i)001:10319: mu ge'i bskal pa las thar ba'i phan yon dang /
NK053('i)001:10320: mtshon gyi bskal pa ni sems can gyi rnam par
NK053('i)001:10321: rtog pa tsher ma lta bu las byung ba yin
NK053('i)001:10322: te / bdud rtsi chen po'i rang bzhin gyis mi rtog pa'i ngang du sbyangs pas /
NK053('i)001:10323: mtshon gyi bskal pa las thar pa'i phan yon dang /
NK053('i)001:10324: nad thams cad kyi rgyu ni /
NK053('i)001:10325: nyon mongs pa lnga la sogs pa yin la /
NK053('i)001:10326: de nyid mi rtog pa'i ngang du sbyangs pas /
NK053('i)001:10327: nad kyi bskal pa las thar bar 'gyur ba'i phan yon yod pa dang gsum mo //
NK053('i)001:10328: dgos 3 ched la yang bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:10330: mya ngan las 'das pa'i rtsi sbyar bas /
NK053('i)001:10331: 'khor ba nyid mya ngan las 'das par 'gyur ba'i dgos ched 1dang /
NK053('i)001:10332: rnam rtog bdud kyi steng du mi rtog pa ye shes kyi rtsi sbyar bas /
NK053('i)001:10333: rang byung gi ye shes chen por 'gyur ba'i dgos ched 2dang /
NK053('i)001:10334: 'chi bdag bdud kyi steng du 'chi med ye shes kyi rtsi sbyar bas /
NK053('i)001:10335: skye shi med pa'i dngos grub thob pa'i dgos ched 3 dang /
NK053('i)001:10336: sdug bsngal nad kyi steng du phan byed sman gyi rtsi sbyar bas /
NK053('i)001:10337: sdug bsngal gyi gtan gzhi phung po lnga'i nyon mongs
NK053('i)001:10338: pa'i zag pa zad pas 'khor bar gnas kyang mi
NK053('i)001:10339: skye zhing / nam mkha' la 'phur ba la sogs
NK053('i)001:10340: pa'i thun mong gi dngos grub thob pa'i dgos ched
NK053('i)001:10341: skye zhing / 4dang bzhi'o // de lta bas na /
NK053('i)001:10342: bdud rtsi chen po'i mchod pa byas na /
NK053('i)001:10343: mchod pa thams cad pas kyang 'di khyad par che ba yin pas /
NK053('i)001:10344: rnal 'byor pas dang du blang bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:10346: de nas gtor ma nyid ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor
NK053('i)001:10347: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i lha mo la sogs pa
NK053('i)001:10348: bsam gyis mi khyab pas mchod cing mnyes par bsam
NK053('i)001:10350: rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dang //
NK053('i)001:10351: 'dod pa'i longs spyod rnam lnga po //
NK053('i)001:10352: chos nyid skye ba med dbyings las //
NK053('i)001:10353: ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'bul //
NK053('i)001:10356: de nas gzhan yang mchod pa'i bye brag dang rim pa ni /
NK053('i)001:10357: dus dang gnas skabs kyis rgyas 'bring gi rim par shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:10360: dug lnga ye shes lnga'i mchod pa sogs ci rigs bya'o //
NK053('i)001:10362: de nas sku gsung thugs yon tan phrin las kyi
NK053('i)001:10363: bdag nyid la bstod pa glu'i mchod pas mnyes par
NK053('i)001:10364: bya ba ni / mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes la bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:10366: mnyam nyid mi g.yo mnyam nyid mchog gi chos nyid can /
NK053('i)001:10367: thugs rje'i bdag nyid 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal sel bar byed //
NK053('i)001:10368: yon tan mtha' yas dngos grub rnam gnyis sbyin mdzad pa //
NK053('i)001:10369: ma rig dri med mi g.yo mnyam pa'i mchog chos can //
NK053('i)001:10370: me long lta bu'i ye shes la bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:10371: yon tan shin tu phra ba'i cha la tshad med de //
NK053('i)001:10372: dpe ni nam mkha' dang yang bskrun du yod ma yin //
NK053('i)001:10373: dngos grub mtha' yas mnyam med dpe dang bral ba rnams //
NK053('i)001:10374: sems can rnams la dngos grub mchog rnams nges par gsol //
NK053('i)001:10375: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes la bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:10376: rtag tu dri ma med pa thugs rje'i shugs las byung //
NK053('i)001:10377: smon lam grub pa 'gag pa med pa'i chos nyid can //
NK053('i)001:10378: 'gro ba'i don grub rab tu brtson par mtha' yas pa //
NK053('i)001:10379: thugs rje chen po'i bdag nyid rtag tu rnam par snang //
NK053('i)001:10380: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes la bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:10381: tshad med tshad dang bral ba'i shin tu yongs rdzogs pa'i //
NK053('i)001:10382: bde ba gshegs pa'i go 'phang dam pa mnyes gyur yang /
NK053('i)001:10383: khams gsum rnams la dngos grub mchog tu stsol mdzad pa'i //
NK053('i)001:10384: thugs rje'i spyod pas mi g.yo 'gag par yang mi 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:10385: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes la bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:10386: e ma hoh shin tu bzang po'i chos nyid mchog dang ldan //
NK053('i)001:10387: mchog sbyin rnams kyi nang na go 'phang mchog rnyed pas /
NK053('i)001:10388: khams gsum kun la rtag tu dngos grub mchog stsol mdzad //
NK053('i)001:10389: mgon po dus gsum sgrib pa med par rab mkhyen pa //
NK053('i)001:10390: dam tshig mchog gsum dam pa bdag la stsol //
NK053('i)001:10392: 'di ni sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK053('i)001:10393: yang dag yon tan rgya chen te //
NK053('i)001:10394: lan gcig tsam ni brjod pas kyang //
NK053('i)001:10398: chos sku skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin las //
NK053('i)001:10399: gzugs sku sgyu mar skye ba'i skur bstan nas //
NK053('i)001:10400: thugs rjes kun la khyab par don mdzad pa //
NK053('i)001:10401: rgyal ba bzhi bcu'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK053('i)001:10404: de nas smon lam gdab pa yan chad bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:10406: mchod pas mnyes par bya ba'i don to /
NK053('i)001:10408: 3 / de la bsnyen pa dbul ba'i phrin las gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:10409: bsnyen pa'i don du 'di dag bya //
NK053('i)001:10411: de la bsnyen pa la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:10415: de la 1rang gi ngo bo ni /
NK053('i)001:10416: rang gi sems nyid byang chub kyi sems su ngo shes pa'o //
NK053('i)001:10419: mya ngan las 'das pa la bsnyen pa'o //
NK053('i)001:10429: lha bsgom zhing 'dzab dbul ba dang /
NK053('i)001:10430: 'dod yod kyi mchod pa 'bul zhing lha so so la bstod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:10433: dang po lha bsgom pa ni /
NK053('i)001:10435: gzhan don gnyis ka'i skabs su /
NK053('i)001:10438: bdag nyid kyi thugs tsit+ta rin po che 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang du /
NK053('i)001:10439: ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor rgya long bzur ba tsam gyi steng du /
NK053('i)001:10442: ye shes sems dpa' sku tshon gang ba /
NK053('i)001:10443: sku mdog dkar po ral pa'i thor tshugs can gcig bsgom /
NK053('i)001:10445: a las zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du /
NK053('i)001:10446: rdo rje nas tsam gyi rnam snang la 'khor lo sogs rigs lnga la 'gre /
NK053('i)001:10456: yum gyi thugs kyang tsit+ta rin po che'i gzhal yas khang du /
NK053('i)001:10457: nyi ma'i steng du ye shes sems ma /
NK053('i)001:10458: de'i thugs kar yang zla ba /
NK053('i)001:10459: de'i steng du dril bu'i bum pa la /
NK053('i)001:10462: m+aum d+ha du shwa ris bskor bar bsgom /
NK053('i)001:10467: de nas bdag nyid kyi smin mtshams nas /
NK053('i)001:10471: gong gi gzhal yas khang ci 'dra ba gcig mdun gyi nam mkha' la gsal /
NK053('i)001:10473: der rtsa ba'i sngags h'u badz+ra d+h+rika /
NK053('i)001:10476: bskyed pa'i dkyil 'khor las gnyis su phye ste /
NK053('i)001:10477: dper na sprin las sprin bye ba'am /
NK053('i)001:10478: mar me gcig las gnyis su phye ba'i tshul du /
NK053('i)001:10479: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams rdzogs par bton la /
NK053('i)001:10483: 'dzab mi drag mi zhan par dbul te /
NK053('i)001:10485: m+aum d+ha du shwa ri s+w+aa h+aa //
NK053('i)001:10487: thugs ka rnam gnyis nas 'od zer dkar dmar gser gyi ba thag gzigs pa bzhin du 'phros te /
NK053('i)001:10488: dngos po dang mtshan mar snang ba ril sbyangs nas /
NK053('i)001:10490: rnam par shes pa'i phung po dang /
NK053('i)001:10491: 'byung ba nam mkhar 'dzin pa'i rtog pa sbyangs nas /
NK053('i)001:10492: rnam snang la gzugs phung dang /
NK053('i)001:10493: 'byung ba sar 'dzin rtog pa sbyong ba 'agre'o //
NK053('i)001:10494: mdun gyi nam mkha' la dbyings phyug ma'i thugs kar phog las /
NK053('i)001:10498: mnyes rab kyi phul du gyur te /
NK053('i)001:10499: mdun gyi nam mkha' la byang chub kyi sems 'od zer sprin phung bzhin du 'dus te /
NK053('i)001:10500: bdag la phog pas nyes dmigs kyi sgrib pa sbyangs /
NK053('i)001:10501: sku gsung thugs kyi dbyig thob ste /
NK053('i)001:10502: da ci bas kyang ye shes kyi sku gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10503: de bzhin du rigs bzhi la yang /
NK053('i)001:10504: rang rang gi snying po'i bsgom lugs dang /
NK053('i)001:10505: nyon mongs pa sbyang lugs gong gis 'gre /
NK053('i)001:10506: sems dpa' rnams kyi thugs kar yang /
NK053('i)001:10507: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor steng du 'od tshon gang ba re re /
NK053('i)001:10508: de'i rtse la rang re'i yig 'bu la snying pos bskor ba'o //
NK053('i)001:10509: thub pa rnams kyi thugs kar yang pad+ma'i gdan re re /
NK053('i)001:10510: de'i steng du yang 'od tshon gang ba re re'i rtse la /
NK053('i)001:10511: yig 'bru kha dog ser po re re la rang re'i snying pos bskor ba'o //
NK053('i)001:10512: sgo ba rnams kyi thugs kar yang /
NK053('i)001:10513: nyi ma'i steng du 'od mthing ka tshon gang ba re re /
NK053('i)001:10514: de'i rtse la yang yig 'bru re re la so so'i snying pos bskor bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10515: de la rang re'i bzlas pa dang /
NK053('i)001:10518: dngos grub dang por lha gang bskyed pa de'i dngos grub thob bo //
NK053('i)001:10519: 'dzab ni grangs kyi bsnyen pa'i sgo nas 'dzab thon pa dang /
NK053('i)001:10520: spyi 'dzab rtsa ba'i rgyud las gsungs pa /
NK053('i)001:10522: b+ho d+hi tsit+ta byang chub sems /
NK053('i)001:10523: ma h+aa su ka bde ba chen po /
NK053('i)001:10526: zhes bya ba 'di lha rnams kyi snying po dril ba yin par shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:10527: gnyis pa 'dod yon gyi mchod pa 'bul zhing lha so sor bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:10528: de nas tshogs bsags pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:10529: snang ba gzugs mdzes kyi mchod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:10530: grags pa sgra snyan gyi mchod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:10531: dri 'byung ye shes kyi mchod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:10532: sna tshogs ro ldan gyi mchod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:10533: reg dgyes thugs la bstar ba'i mchod pa bya'o //
NK053('i)001:10534: de nas lha so so la bstod pa bya ste /
NK053('i)001:10537: de nas dngos grub kyi gegs bsal ba'i phyir bshags pa bya ste /
NK053('i)001:10539: ye shes mnyam nyid chos skur dag pa la //
NK053('i)001:10540: ma rig dbang gis 'gro don sku sprul te //
NK053('i)001:10541: de bzlog don phyir rgyal ba'i dam mnos pas //
NK053('i)001:10542: rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor thugs dang ci 'gal ba //
NK053('i)001:10543: thugs rje che mnga' khyed la bzod par gsol //
NK053('i)001:10545: dam tshig gi bshags pa dang /
NK053('i)001:10546: yi ge brgya pa brjod nas //
NK053('i)001:10549: ye shes rgyal po sku gsung thugs //
NK053('i)001:10550: yon tan phrin las rmad po che //
NK053('i)001:10551: de nyid du ni mnyam sbyor bas //
NK053('i)001:10552: de nyid du ni bdag la stsol //
NK053('i)001:10554: yab yum gyi thugs ka rnam gnyis nas /
NK053('i)001:10556: dza las lcags kyur gyur te /
NK053('i)001:10557: lcags kyus dbus kyi mi bskyod pa yab yum thugs ka nas drangs pas /
NK053('i)001:10558: rgyal po bskyod pas 'khor dbang med par g.yo ba dang 'dra ba /
NK053('i)001:10559: mi bskyod pa bskul bas mdun gyi lha gzhal yas
NK053('i)001:10560: khang dang bcas pa 'od du lam gyis gyur nas
NK053('i)001:10562: bdag nyid sku phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor shin tu gsal zhing 'od 'phro bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10563: de ltar gsal zhing ting nge 'dzin brtan por gyur na /
NK053('i)001:10566: dngos grub kho na yang de yin /
NK053('i)001:10569: rgyud sarba bud+d+ha ltar ma yin /
NK053('i)001:10570: lung zhags pa ltar ma yin /
NK053('i)001:10572: man ngag he ru ka'i galpo dang /
NK053('i)001:10573: 'jig rten 'das pa'i mdo ltar bkod nas /
NK053('i)001:10574: de la zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor la dgos pa ci yod snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:10575: dpal chen po'i dngos grub la bsnyen pa'i don du /
NK053('i)001:10576: gong du bstan pa de dag la blo sbyong bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:10580: 2 / khro bo'i lha mnyes par bya ba'i phrin las la /
NK053('i)001:10582: skabs sbyor bcu gsum pa sgrub pa byed pa'i phyir
NK053('i)001:10583: khro bo'i lha bskyed pa'i thabs khyad par du bstan
NK053('i)001:10584: pa'i skabs / dal dgu las thugs rje'i phrin las kyi dal /
NK053('i)001:10585: mtha' drug las nyams su ting nge 'dzin /
NK053('i)001:10587: lung dgu las mdzad pa phrin las kyi lung ngo //
NK053('i)001:10589: zhi ba las khro bo gnas bsgyur ba'i phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:10590: spyan drangs shing mchod pa'i phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:10591: bsnyen pa dbul ba'i phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:10592: thugs dam bskul zhing mnyes pa'i phrin las dang /
NK053('i)001:10593: sbyor ba dang sgrol ba'i mchod pas mnyes par bya ba'i phrin las so /
NK053('i)001:10595: 1 / de la zhi ba las khro bor gnas bsgyur ba'i phrin las gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:10598: de la gnas bsgyur ba'i 'brel dgos gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:10599: dngos grub dam shes blang ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:10602: sngar zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor la blo sbyangs pas /
NK053('i)001:10605: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor la bsgrub pa byas pas /
NK053('i)001:10606: shin tu nye ba'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngosa grub dama pa zhig /
NK053('i)001:10607: rnal 'byor pa'i shesa rab dam pa zhig gi rtsal
NK053('i)001:10608: gyis de ma thag tu blang ba'i phyir dgos pa
NK053('i)001:10609: yod pa'o // de la gnas 2 bsgyur ba'i thabs la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:10610: rnal 'byor sgrub pa po'i rgyan rtags bsgyur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:10611: zhi ba las khro bor gnas bsgyur ba'o //
NK053('i)001:10612: de la 1rnal 'byor sgrub pa po'i rgyan rtags bsgyur ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:10613: lhag pa'i rtags kyis mtshan nas //
NK053('i)001:10615: de yang rnal 'byor sgrub pa po rnams /
NK053('i)001:10616: ye shes kyi lha dpal khrag 'thung gi lha rnams dang rjes su mthun par bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:10617: thabs dang shes rab spel mar zhugs nas /
NK053('i)001:10618: theg pa 'og ma dag las lhag par gyur pa'i
NK053('i)001:10619: lhag pa'i rtagsa rnam pa brgyad kyis kun mtshan cing
NK053('i)001:10621: de la lhag pa'i rtags brgyad ni /
NK053('i)001:10622: glang po che'i ko rlon dang /
NK053('i)001:10623: zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi dang /
NK053('i)001:10628: thal chen gyi thig le dang /
NK053('i)001:10637: thugs rjes sems can mi gtong ba dang /
NK053('i)001:10638: byang chub sems dbang du bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:10641: rdo rje rgyal po'i sku la dpal gyi chas brgyad gsol te /
NK053('i)001:10642: de yang he ru ka'i gal po las /
NK053('i)001:10643: glang chen gyi stod g.yogs sku la gsol ba ni 'di skad do //
NK053('i)001:10645: bdud 'dul stobs chen theg pa mchog gi rgyan 'di ni //
NK053('i)001:10646: stobs bcus pha rol bdud dpung 'dul ba'i rtags //
NK053('i)001:10647: smad pa'i mchog rnams don gyi phyag rgyar gsal //
NK053('i)001:10648: lta ba gzhung tshugs bden pa mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK053('i)001:10649: de nas zhing chen gyi stod g.yogs sku la gsol ba ni 'di skad du /
NK053('i)001:10650: zhing chen rlon pa'i g.yang gzhi'i stong g.yogs 'di //
NK053('i)001:10651: tshul khrims gos chen g.yang gzhir brjod pa ste //
NK053('i)001:10652: yan lag rnam lnga snod lnga yum gyi dbang //
NK053('i)001:10653: mi 'khor byang chub sems kyi rgyan du bstan /
NK053('i)001:10654: de nas stag gi sham thabs gsol ba 'di skad du /
NK053('i)001:10655: dpal brtul za byed stag gi smad g.yogs 'di //
NK053('i)001:10656: bsnyengs pa mi mnga' mtha' gnyis rdzogs las 'das //
NK053('i)001:10657: yal bar mi 'dor ye shes thugs rjes sdud //
NK053('i)001:10658: gdod mtha' med par sgrol zhing za bar byed //
NK053('i)001:10659: de nas sbrul gyi chun pos sku la brgyan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:10660: dpa' brjid gnyen lcug sbrul gyi chun po 'di //
NK053('i)001:10661: dpal brjid che bas bdud dpung zil gyis gnon //
NK053('i)001:10662: gnyen lcug yan lag 'khril bas yum gyi tshul //
NK053('i)001:10663: dug lnga dbang du mdzad cing 'jigs tshul rgyan du bstan //
NK053('i)001:10664: de nas thod pa'i phreng bas sku la brgyan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:10665: thod pa skam dang rlon pa ra ri dang //
NK053('i)001:10666: khro bo'i sku gsum thob pa'i dbang rtags yin //
NK053('i)001:10667: theg pa gsum gyi chags pa'i dngos gzhi ste //
NK053('i)001:10668: dug gsum sems can ma lus sgrol ba'i dbang //
NK053('i)001:10669: de nas rak+ta'i thig les sku la brgyan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:10671: chags pa'i tshul 'dzin khrag gi thig le 'di //
NK053('i)001:10672: rgyu la rol pas don du sku la bzhag /
NK053('i)001:10673: ma chags pad+ma spyan gyi sa mnan te //
NK053('i)001:10674: de phyir thugs rje chags pa'i rgyan du bstan //
NK053('i)001:10675: de nas thal chen gyi thig les sku la brgyan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:10676: 'dul byed phrin las rgyan gyis btang ba ni //
NK053('i)001:10677: 'jigs par byed pa'i phrin las rgyan du bstan //
NK053('i)001:10678: yi ge 'khor lo tshogs chen sa mnan te //
NK053('i)001:10679: 'khor lo cho 'phrul spyod pa'i sa yang yin //
NK053('i)001:10680: de nas zhag gi zo ris kyis brgyan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:10681: gzi brjid don dam bcud kyi rgyan 'di ni //
NK053('i)001:10682: bcud du gyur nas yon tan gzi brjid 'bar //
NK053('i)001:10683: rgyan du bzhag pas sku la rgyan du che //
NK053('i)001:10684: kun tu 'od kyi sa ni mnan pa'i rtags //
NK053('i)001:10686: kro ta ni la ka a bi shiny+tsa ma h+aa a /
NK053('i)001:10687: zhes kun la brjod cing mnga' gsol lo //
NK053('i)001:10688: de nas rdo rje rgyal pos kyang /
NK053('i)001:10689: sgrub pa po kun la chas brgyad kyis dbang bskur zhing byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:10690: de ltar sgrub pa po kun lhag pa'i rtags kyis matshana nas /
NK053('i)001:10691: zhi ba las 2khro bor gnas bsgyur ba la yang gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:10694: de yang 1cig char bsgyur ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:10695: snga ma las ni gnas bsgyur te //
NK053('i)001:10696: dur khrod sa ru brtag par bya //
NK053('i)001:10698: bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das mi bskyod pa'i skur gsal ba de nyid las /
NK053('i)001:10699: ye shes kyi lta ba drag pos bskyed de /
NK053('i)001:10700: byang chub kyi sems ci yang ma yin pa las /
NK053('i)001:10702: dag pa'i gzhal yas khang nyid /
NK053('i)001:10703: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas khang du gyur pa'i nang du /
NK053('i)001:10704: sangs rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis las /
NK053('i)001:10705: dpal khrag 'thung gi tshogs su bsgrub cing ye shes chen po'i klong du /
NK053('i)001:10706: snang srid ye nas sangs rgyas par bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:10707: ston pa rdo rje sems dpa' nyid kyis gsungs pa 'adi'o //
NK053('i)001:10708: na ma sarba ta th+aa ga ta nan /
NK053('i)001:10710: sa ma ya pa te nan /
NK053('i)001:10713: sarba tram k+sham swa b+h+aa wa bi shud+d+ho&a ham /
NK053('i)001:10714: zhes brjod pa tsam gyis dkyil 'khor gyi lha sangs
NK053('i)001:10715: rgyas bzhi bcu rtsa gnyis 'od du lteng lteng zhu
NK053('i)001:10717: h'u ha he phata h'u b+h+yo /
NK053('i)001:10718: zhes brjod pa tsam gyis so so'i yi 'brur gyur nas so so'i go go gnas gnas na /
NK053('i)001:10719: bskal pa'i me lta bur 'bar zhing 'dug pa las /
NK053('i)001:10720: so so'i snying po las bzhi brjod pa las /
NK053('i)001:10721: rigs lnga'i sangs rgyas yab yum /
NK053('i)001:10722: rigs lnga khrag 'thung yab yum du bsgyur /
NK053('i)001:10723: sems dpa' brgyad ko'u ri la sogs pa brgyad /
NK053('i)001:10726: thub pa drug dang sgo ba bzhi khro bo bcu /
NK053('i)001:10728: yid dang chos ye shes sems dpa' dang sems ma /
NK053('i)001:10729: 'khor dbang phyug ma dang bcas par skad cig mas bsgyur te /
NK053('i)001:10730: so so'i skur gsal ba dang /
NK053('i)001:10731: dbang bskur ba dang byin gyis brlabs pa yang bya'o //
NK053('i)001:10732: de la 2rim gyis bsgyur pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:10733: snod kyi 'jig rten gzhal yas khang gnas bsgyur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:10734: bcud kyi 'jig rten lha'i dkyil 'khor du gnas bsgyur ba'o /
NK053('i)001:10736: 1 / de la snod kyi 'jig rten gzhal yas khang gnas bsgyur ba la yang gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:10739: de la dbang 1chen yum lnga gnas bsgyur ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:10740: snga ma las ni gnas bsgyur te //
NK053('i)001:10741: dur khrod sa ru brtag par bya //
NK053('i)001:10743: de yang bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das mi bskyod par
NK053('i)001:10744: gsal ba de'i thugs rje ye shes kyi spyan gyis
NK053('i)001:10745: srid pa gsum la lan gcig gzigs pas //
NK053('i)001:10746: zhi bas mi 'dul bar khro bos 'dul bar gzigs nas /
NK053('i)001:10747: snod kyi 'jig rten gdul zhing spa bkong ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:10748: nyid kyi dbugs gang gi h'u rings kyi glu blangs te /
NK053('i)001:10749: ye shes kyi thugs rjes lan gcig gzigs te /
NK053('i)001:10752: ye shes kyi 'od zer me'i 'bar ba lta bur 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:10753: gdug rtsub dug lnga me lhar 'bar ba de kun zhi nas /
NK053('i)001:10754: ye shes kyi 'od dmar smug tu je gsal lan gcig bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10756: bdag cib sa kyang gzi byin chen po 'bar zhing snod bcud la dbang bsgyur bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10757: de nas bdag nyid kyis snod kyi 'jig rten la dbang bsgyur ba'i glu 'di blangs so //
NK053('i)001:10758: h+aum e yam ra bam kem ram /
NK053('i)001:10760: thugs ka nas yi ge de rnams gsal bar thon pa las /
NK053('i)001:10761: e mthing ka 'phros shing 'dus pa las /
NK053('i)001:10763: zhe sdang dbyings gsal nam mkha' ni //
NK053('i)001:10764: yum nyid 'byung ba'i rgyu yin phyir //
NK053('i)001:10765: mthing nag b+ha ga'i dkyil 'khor nyid //
NK053('i)001:10766: gru gsum ye shes gsal 'bar shar //
NK053('i)001:10767: e kro ti shwa ri man+da la /
NK053('i)001:10769: nam mkha' gzhal shing dwang ba de /
NK053('i)001:10770: gru gsum mthing nag mtha' dbus dang bral ba /
NK053('i)001:10771: 'od zer mthing khar 'khrug cing 'khyil bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10772: yi ge yam dud kha 'phros shing 'dus pa las /
NK053('i)001:10774: rlung nag gtams pa'i rgya gram ni //
NK053('i)001:10775: phrag dog mkha' la sgrol mdzad yum //
NK053('i)001:10776: 'degs pa'i shugs ldan ye shes dang //
NK053('i)001:10777: thogs med brtan pa'i dkyil 'khor che //
NK053('i)001:10780: rlung rdo rje rgya gram las /
NK053('i)001:10781: rlung nag gi dkyil 'khor gzhu brdungs pa dang 'dra bar gyur te /
NK053('i)001:10782: dbal tsha zhing ngad ldan pa /
NK053('i)001:10783: rnam pa rgyu ba'i rang sgra dang bcas par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10784: yi ge ra dmar smug 'phros shing 'dus pa las /
NK053('i)001:10787: chags med yum ste pad+ma'i klong //
NK053('i)001:10788: dbus mtha' med pa'i rgya mtsho ni //
NK053('i)001:10789: rba klong 'phyo ba'i ye shes yin //
NK053('i)001:10790: ra rak+ta dz+wa la sa mun dza /
NK053('i)001:10793: rak+ta'i rgya mtsho rba klong 'khrug cing 'khyil bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10794: yi ge bam dmar smug 'phros shing 'dus pa las /
NK053('i)001:10796: 'khor ba dang ba'i sa gzhi ni //
NK053('i)001:10797: gti mug chos nyid gsal ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:10798: gser 'gyur mchog phran sa gzhi gdal //
NK053('i)001:10799: thams cad bskyed brten ye shes gsal //
NK053('i)001:10800: bam smig ta sha chen gyi sa gzhi /
NK053('i)001:10803: rin po che gser gyi sa gzhi las /
NK053('i)001:10804: mchog phran gyi sa gzhi gdal zhing gyur par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10805: de nas kem sngo skya 'phros shing 'dus pa las /
NK053('i)001:10807: srid rgyu ye nas dag pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:10808: rin chen ri rab kem rus gsal //
NK053('i)001:10809: tshad med rgyan ldan kha bad che //
NK053('i)001:10810: klong nas shar bas phyed nub spangs //
NK053('i)001:10811: kem ni dz+wa la man+da la /
NK053('i)001:10814: rin po che sna lnga'i ri rab las /
NK053('i)001:10815: kem rus ri rab tu gyur te /
NK053('i)001:10816: shin tu brjid cing kha khyer gyis 'jig rten gyi khams kheb par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10817: de nas yi ge ram dmar po 'phros shing 'dus pa las /
NK053('i)001:10820: nga rgyal mkha' la sgrol mdzad yum //
NK053('i)001:10821: rmongs pa'i mun nag gtan nas sel //
NK053('i)001:10822: thams cad smin cing brtas par byed //
NK053('i)001:10826: ye shes kyi me 'od dur khrod kyi me smug nag 'bar bar 'phro zhing 'tshub par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10828: gru gsum mthing nag nam mkha' la //
NK053('i)001:10831: zhing chen gtams pa'i sa gzhi la //
NK053('i)001:10832: kem rus brtsegs pa'i ri rab steng //
NK053('i)001:10833: dur khrod me dpung smug nag 'bar //
NK053('i)001:10836: gzhal 2 yas khang ji ltar bsgyur snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:10837: smug nag zla gam gzhal yas khang //
NK053('i)001:10839: yang bdag nyid kyi thugs ka'am smin mtshams nas /
NK053('i)001:10840: yi ge b+h+r+aum smug nag nyung 'bru tsam mam til
NK053('i)001:10841: 'bru tsam rin po che'i gzhal yas khang la ci
NK053('i)001:10843: 'od smug nag tu ltem ltem zhu la khad pa las /
NK053('i)001:10844: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+ha badz+ra b+han+d+ha dz+ny+aa na /
NK053('i)001:10847: dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas khang /
NK053('i)001:10849: mdog smug nag sgo gcig pa /
NK053('i)001:10850: bar khyams dang gru bzhi sgo khyud dang bcas pa gcig tu gyur te //
NK053('i)001:10851: de yang b+han+d+ha tshar gsum las phag thabs su brtsigs pa /
NK053('i)001:10852: rak+tasa sbyin thabs su sbyar ba /
NK053('i)001:10853: gnam lcags ur mo'i gzer chen gyis btab pa /
NK053('i)001:10854: gzer mgog gza' dang rgyu skar gyis brgyan pa /
NK053('i)001:10857: lcang lo las rak+ta'i zar bu 'bab pa /
