NK053('i)001:10858: nyi zla rtsibs la 'char zhing 'phyo ba /
NK053('i)001:10859: dbus thig bzhi btab pas le'u tshe dgur gyur pa'i /
NK053('i)001:10860: gtsang khang steng tshangs pa'i gdung bres pa /
NK053('i)001:10861: gdung sna brgyad las zhing smug po brgyad kyi ka bas btegs te /
NK053('i)001:10862: gza' chen po brgyad kyi ka gzhu /
NK053('i)001:10863: sa bdag phag chen po brgyad kyi ka gdan /
NK053('i)001:10866: spre'u mi rgod kyi bgas pas thog phub pa /
NK053('i)001:10868: bya khyung ka ru na'i ya spyibs la /
NK053('i)001:10869: rus sbal gyi ma them byas pa /
NK053('i)001:10870: sprul sngon po'i skyes bu byas pa /
NK053('i)001:10872: zhing pho mo'i sgo 'gebs dang ldan pa /
NK053('i)001:10873: de'i nang na zhing gi bla bre la sogs pa'i rgyan rnam pa sna tshogs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:10874: sgo bzhi na ta la'i skyed shing zung re re yod pa /
NK053('i)001:10875: de'i yal ga re re la yang 'dod yon gyi lha mo mang po gnas pa dang /
NK053('i)001:10876: shing gi rtsa ba dang bar khyams la sogs pa na /
NK053('i)001:10882: lhag ma la sogs pa la /
NK053('i)001:10885: kang+ka la sogs pa mang pos rol par bsgyur ro //
NK053('i)001:10888: u ma de wa ti ra bam /
NK053('i)001:10890: ma h+aa de ba la sogs pa'i dregs pa'i lha brgyad bsnol ba'i steng du /
NK053('i)001:10892: seng ge glang chen rta dang khyung la sogs pa lnga ni /
NK053('i)001:10893: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK053('i)001:10894: la sogs pa rnams su bsgyur /
NK053('i)001:10895: de rnams kyi steng du nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan bting ngo //
NK053('i)001:10896: gzhan yang le'u tshe rnams dang /
NK053('i)001:10902: ro skam gyi gdan du bsgyur ro //
NK053('i)001:10904: zla gam dbang chen man+dala la //
NK053('i)001:10905: dur khrod yon tan tshogs kyis brgyan //
NK053('i)001:10906: phyi dang nang med kun tu gsal //
NK053('i)001:10907: ye shes gzhal yas nam mkha'i rgya //
NK053('i)001:10908: dregs pa lha chen khyab 'jug dang //
NK053('i)001:10909: tshangs pa brgya byin khyo shug steng //
NK053('i)001:10910: khyu mchog ma he gzig dang stag /
NK053('i)001:10911: gtum pa'i dom gyis bardzisa pa'o //
NK053('i)001:10912: ma h+aa a kri ti ra bam /
NK053('i)001:10913: ti yang sur+ya tsan+d+ra pad+ma dang /
NK053('i)001:10919: bcud kyi 'jig rten lha'i dkyil 'khor du gnas bsgyur ba la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:10923: de la 1gtso bo zhi ba las khro bor bsgyur ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:10924: ye shes dam tshig chen po yis //
NK053('i)001:10927: rdo rje dbyings las dpal gyi skur bsgyur ba //
NK053('i)001:10928: dang ba'i mtsho las rlabs chen 'khrug pa bzhin //
NK053('i)001:10929: zhi ba'i sku las khro bo'i phyag rgyar bstan //
NK053('i)001:10930: 'bar ba'i rgyal po cir yang snang bar mdzad //
NK053('i)001:10932: bdag nyid bcom ldan 'das mi bskyod par gsal ba'i /
NK053('i)001:10933: thugs rje ye shes kyi spyan gyis /
NK053('i)001:10934: srid pa gsum la lan gcig gzigs pas /
NK053('i)001:10935: gdug rtsub dug lnga me ltar 'bar de zhi bas mi 'dul bar mkhyen nas /
NK053('i)001:10936: thugs rig pa'i ye shes la h'u gsal ba de /
NK053('i)001:10937: he ru ka'i sna glus h'u bzhi po khong brgyud nas drangs te /
NK053('i)001:10938: dbugs dang sgrags nas sna'i rtse mo nyi ma'i steng nas gsal ba las /
NK053('i)001:10942: h'u 'od zer dang bcas pas dug gsum gtan rgyud sbyangs /
NK053('i)001:10943: srid pa gre zlog sangs rgyas kyi zhing khams thams
NK053('i)001:10944: cad kyang 'od du gyur nas ril h'u du gsal
NK053('i)001:10946: shes pas zin pa dang ma zin pa'i sgra skad ril h'u du grags par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:10948: de dag slar ci li li h'u bzhi po la
NK053('i)001:10949: 'dus nyi ma 'bum bas gzi byin che bar gyur
NK053('i)001:10951: h'u de 'od du zhu nas bdag la thim pas /
NK053('i)001:10952: bdag nyid 'od du gsal lam lam 'bar ba las /
NK053('i)001:10953: mkha' dbyings kyi phyag rgyas bcings te /
NK053('i)001:10954: thod phreng gi phyag rgya zhes kyang bya /
NK053('i)001:10956: 'das pa'i dus na sngon byung ba'i //
NK053('i)001:10957: bdag nyid chen po brtag pa yis //
NK053('i)001:10958: de bzhin gshegs pa'i gsung rab la //
NK053('i)001:10959: 'gro ba'i tshul du sngon byung yang //
NK053('i)001:10960: de tshe sems can thams cad kun //
NK053('i)001:10961: shin tu khro zhing gtum par gyur //
NK053('i)001:10962: shin tu gdug cing khro ba yis //
NK053('i)001:10964: shin tu khro zhing gtum pa la //
NK053('i)001:10965: zhi bas phan par mi 'gyur te //
NK053('i)001:10966: shes rab thabs kyi ngo bo yis //
NK053('i)001:10967: khro bor de bzhin gshegs kun mdzad //
NK053('i)001:10968: khro bo'i tshul can khros pas kyang //
NK053('i)001:10969: 'jig rten gsum dag sreg byed na //
NK053('i)001:10970: sangs rgyas thams cad khros pa yis /
NK053('i)001:10971: khams gsum ma lus smos ci dgos //
NK053('i)001:10972: thugs rje che dang ldan pa yi //
NK053('i)001:10973: rdo rje sems dpa' de bzhin gshegs //
NK053('i)001:10974: dam tshig la sdang rnam sbyangs phyir //
NK053('i)001:10975: dur khrod gar gyi phyag rgya gsal //
NK053('i)001:10976: ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka ma h+aa kro ti shwa ri sa ma ya //
NK053('i)001:10977: de byi shwa da na sta na h'u /
NK053('i)001:10979: bdag nyid dpal he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:10981: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi pa /
NK053('i)001:10985: phyag g.yas kyi dang po ti ra'i dbyug pa /
NK053('i)001:10987: tha ma na b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba'o //
NK053('i)001:10988: g.yon gyi dang po na rgyu zhags /
NK053('i)001:10989: bar ma na khyung gi khra /
NK053('i)001:10990: tha ma na ti ra chung ngu'i khog pa nas glo snying 'dren pa'o //
NK053('i)001:10991: dur khrod kyi chas brgyad dang ldan zhing /
NK053('i)001:10992: bskal pa'i me 'bar ba'i klong na zhabs brkyang bskum gyi tshul du bzhugs pa /
NK053('i)001:10993: yum kro ti shwa ri ma dang gnyis su med par ldan pa gcig tu bsgyur ro //
NK053('i)001:10996: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+ri he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:10997: ma h+aa tsan d+ha sarba dush+tana /
NK053('i)001:10998: ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u h'u phata phata /
NK053('i)001:11000: bcom ldan 'das mi bskyod pa nyid dpal khrag 'thung chen po gyur te /
NK053('i)001:11005: dbus sku dang mthun te mthing nag /
NK053('i)001:11006: phyag g.yas kyi dang po na gser gyi rdo rje thugs kar 'dzin pa /
NK053('i)001:11007: bar pa na kha t+w+aam rtse gsum /
NK053('i)001:11008: tha ma na mi mgo'i cang te'u rnge'u rngel chung 'khrol ba /
NK053('i)001:11009: phyag g.yon gyi dang po na b+han+d+ha dmar gyis bkang ba /
NK053('i)001:11010: bar ma na rgyu ma'i zhags pa /
NK053('i)001:11011: tha ma na khyung chen po'i khra 'phyar ba'o //
NK053('i)001:11013: gnyis brkyang bskum du mdzad pa /
NK053('i)001:11014: gnyis dor thabs su bsgrad par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11015: dbu skra kham nag ral pa gyen du 'khyil ba'i rtse mo na me 'bar ba /
NK053('i)001:11016: ral pa'i rtsa ba nas rak+ta'i chu rgyun 'bab pa /
NK053('i)001:11017: thod pa tshar gsum dang nyi zla spel nas sbrul gyis brgyus te dbu skra'i thod du bcings pa /
NK053('i)001:11018: sked pa nas rlung gi 'khor lo 'od ljang nag tu 'phro bas me'i mdog 'byin pa /
NK053('i)001:11019: smin ma glog tu 'gyu zhing smin mtshams khro gnyer gyi rlabs su g.yo ba /
NK053('i)001:11020: spyan g.yas pa gsum nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK053('i)001:11022: spyan g.yon pa gsum zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la /
NK053('i)001:11024: rdzi ma lcags kyu'i 'od zer du 'bar ba /
NK053('i)001:11025: spyan dbus ma gsum sdang mig 'bru tshugs su gzigs pa'i mig sprin dmar ba /
NK053('i)001:11026: 'bras bu gding nag la gru gsum du gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11027: snyan dung gi khang seng nas 'brug stong gi sgra lding ba /
NK053('i)001:11028: shangs nas rlung nag gi 'tshub ma ldang zhing h'u gi gdangs su 'byin pa /
NK053('i)001:11029: ag tshom ser nag las dza'i 'od zer 'phro bar bsgyur ro //
NK053('i)001:11033: rngam pa'i zhal gsum gdangs nas ljags 'dril zhing rkan sgra phata du sgrogs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:11034: ye shes kyi mche ba bcu gnyis zla ba tshes pa ltar gtsigs pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11037: sku stod glang po che'i ko rlon dang /
NK053('i)001:11038: zhing chen po'i g.yang gzhi gsol ba'o //
NK053('i)001:11041: sku smad stag gi sham thabs su dkris pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11044: thod skam gyi dbu rgyan dang /
NK053('i)001:11045: thod pa tshar gsum gyi phreng bas se ral khas brgyan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11046: he rad ta ka hed nya ba /
NK053('i)001:11051: nag bkra bzhis sku dang yan lag la brgyan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11055: thal chen gyi tshom bu dang /
NK053('i)001:11056: zhag gi zo ris kyis brgyan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11057: ba su ta kun d+ha li /
NK053('i)001:11059: rgyu ma'i ske rags dang rgyan du mdzad pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11060: badz+ra rat+na bi ta sa ya /
NK053('i)001:11062: rin po che'i gshog pa dang /
NK053('i)001:11063: rdo rje'i gshog pa'i ra brag nas rdo rje phra mo'i me stag tu dmar ljib be gdengs pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11064: badz+ra dz+wa la ram ram ram /
NK053('i)001:11066: dur khrod kyi me smug nag 'bar zhing 'phro ba
NK053('i)001:11067: dang 'khyil ba'i klong na bzhugs par bsgyur zhing bsgom
NK053('i)001:11068: mo // de ltar gsal ba'i spyi gtsug tu dkar po /
NK053('i)001:11070: thugs kar h'u mthing ka gsum gsal bar bsgom te /
NK053('i)001:11073: 'byung ba lngas bsdus pa byi dor byas /
NK053('i)001:11074: rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams la phog pas sku'i byin rlabs bsdus nas /
NK053('i)001:11075: slar la thim pas 'od du 'bar ba las /
NK053('i)001:11076: sarba ta th+aa ga ta k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:11078: 'od zer gyis bdag gi lus mgo mjug tu khyab pa las /
NK053('i)001:11079: khro chung smug nag tshon gang bas lus mgo mjug tu khyab pa las /
NK053('i)001:11080: khro chung smug nag tshon gang bas lus mgo mjug tu 'khrigs shing gtams par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11083: snang srid byi dor byas shing /
NK053('i)001:11084: rgyal ba rgya mtsho rnams la phog pas gsung gi
NK053('i)001:11085: byin rlabs bsdus shing +aahl thim nas 'od du 'bar
NK053('i)001:11086: ba las / sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa w+aa ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:11088: ljags rtsa ba rdo rje rtse gsum /
NK053('i)001:11089: rtse mo pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa'i lte ba la /
NK053('i)001:11092: ru lu 'bru brgyad kyis bskor bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11096: rgyal ba rgya mtsho la phog pas thugs kyi byin rlabs bsdus nas /
NK053('i)001:11097: slar h'u la thim pas 'od du zhu ba las /
NK053('i)001:11098: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:11100: thugs tsit+ta rin po che'i gzhal yas khang zla gam sgo gcig pa'i nang na /
NK053('i)001:11101: ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor rgya long bzur ba tsam gyi steng na /
NK053('i)001:11102: ye shes sems dpa' sku mdog dmar smug tshon gang ba zhig gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11103: de'i thugs ka na zla ba'i dkyil 'khor sran chung zlum pa tsam gyi steng na /
NK053('i)001:11104: rin po che zur brgyad thel brgyad sul gsum shu bu kha gcig gsal /
NK053('i)001:11105: de'i steng du rdo rje mthing ka nas tsam zhig phyed nub tsam du gsal ba /
NK053('i)001:11106: de'i chang zung la h'u yungs 'bru tsam zhig gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11107: de'i tha mar rin po che zur brgyad kyi steng na tshur la /
NK053('i)001:11108: ru lu 'bru brgyad nyungs kar gyi phyed tshal tsam /
NK053('i)001:11109: 'od zer du 'phro zhing bklag phyogs kyi rang bzhin du 'khor bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11110: de la ni rgyud las kyang /
NK053('i)001:11111: bdag nyid sangs rgyas thams cad kyi //
NK053('i)001:11112: sku gsung thugs gyi rdo rje'i bdag /
NK053('i)001:11113: khro rgyal ye nas yin pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:11114: phyag rgya chen por mngon rdzogs shing //
NK053('i)001:11115: sku gsung thugs su rang dbang bskur //
NK053('i)001:11116: ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor gsal //
NK053('i)001:11118: ye shes lngas dbang bskur ba /
NK053('i)001:11120: de nas sna yi rtse mo la //
NK053('i)001:11121: yid ni brtan par yang dag bzung //
NK053('i)001:11122: sna yi dbugs ring drongs pa las //
NK053('i)001:11123: rgyal ba sbyor ba'i phyag rgyar gsal //
NK053('i)001:11125: bdag nyid kyi thugs ka'i h'u las /
NK053('i)001:11126: he ru ka'i sna glu h'u rings kyis drangs nas /
NK053('i)001:11127: dbugs dang sbrag nas nang nas yar la phyung ste /
NK053('i)001:11128: sna'i rtse mo la nyi ma'i steng du gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11133: rigs bzhi'i sangs rgyas la phog pas 'od du zhu /
NK053('i)001:11134: slar sam ha ra na h'u gis bsdus pa las /
NK053('i)001:11135: slar la nyi ma'i steng gi h'u la 'dus nas /
NK053('i)001:11136: h'u de dbugs dang sbrags nas srog lam du zhugs /
NK053('i)001:11137: slar thugs ka'i h'u la thim /
NK053('i)001:11138: h'u gzhi po ma nyams par h'u phra mo zhig
NK053('i)001:11139: byung ste rtsol ba'i sems kyi dbugs la zhon te
NK053('i)001:11140: / yar rgyu mar rgyu las su rung ba byas la /
NK053('i)001:11141: de nas dbugs la zhon te klad pa'i rgyas su zhugs /
NK053('i)001:11142: tshangs pa'i seng skar nas byung ste /
NK053('i)001:11143: spyi bo'i gtsug tu nyi ma'i steng du gsal ba las /
NK053('i)001:11145: yi ge b+h+r+aum 'phros pa las rin po che 'od 'bar ba'i gzhal yas khang lngar gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11147: h'u phyogs bzhir 'phros te gsal ba las /
NK053('i)001:11148: h'u badz+ra ma h+aa shu dz+ny+aa ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:11151: badz+ra he ru ka sku mthing nag gcig tu gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11152: ma h+aa a d+ha ri sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:11154: mtshog ma'i khar bud+d+ha he ru ka sku smug nag gcig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11155: ma h+aa sa man ta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:11157: rna ltag g.yas su rat+na he ru ka sku ser nag gcig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11158: ma h+aa pra ta pra be sha dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:11160: ltag khung du pad+ma he ru ka sku dmar nag gcig tu gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11161: ma h+aa kri ta a nu sta dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:11163: rna ltag g.yon du karma he ru ka sku ljang nag zhig tu gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11164: rigs lnga po de kun kyang zhal gcig la /
NK053('i)001:11165: phyag gnyis pa spyan gsum pa /
NK053('i)001:11166: dbu skra lcang lo so sor 'khril ba la /
NK053('i)001:11167: spyi gtsug na kha t+w+aam kha rtse gsum pa re
NK053('i)001:11168: re b+han+d+ha mtheb long tsam re res rgyab brten pa
NK053('i)001:11169: / mtha' ma ye shes kyi me 'od sna lngas bskor ba /
NK053('i)001:11170: dbang bskur ba'i cod pan dang ldan pa /
NK053('i)001:11171: phyag g.yas pa kun rdo rje dang 'khor lo rin po che /
NK053('i)001:11172: pad+ma dang ral gri bsnams pa /
NK053('i)001:11173: phyag g.yon kun bdud rtsi'i bum pas dbang bskur ba /
NK053('i)001:11174: zhabs kun nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor la brten par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11175: de ni ye shes lnga 'dus pa'i bdag nyid kyi phyag rgya chen po'i rang bzhin no //
NK053('i)001:11180: de bzhin nyid kyi dbyings nas ni //
NK053('i)001:11181: khro rgyal sku dang mnyam sbyor phyir //
NK053('i)001:11182: khro mo dbang phyug mngon phyung ste //
NK053('i)001:11185: yang bdag nyid kyi thugs ka'i h'u las /
NK053('i)001:11186: yi ge klong gcig dbugs dang sbrags nas byung steng na gsal ba la /
NK053('i)001:11188: ces rigs kyi yum bzhi la spros pas yum bzhi 'od du gyur /
NK053('i)001:11189: slar sam ha ra na h'u gis bsdus te /
NK053('i)001:11190: yum kun tu bzang mo'i spyi gtsug tu thim pas /
NK053('i)001:11193: klong kro ti shwa ri sa ma ya de byi sta na shwa ta ni h'u /
NK053('i)001:11196: zhal gcig la phyag gnyis pa /
NK053('i)001:11197: sku mdog mthing ka spyan gsum pa /
NK053('i)001:11198: dbu skra mthon mthing lcang lor 'khyil ba /
NK053('i)001:11200: phyag g.yon b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba gtso bo la stob pa /
NK053('i)001:11201: stag rgod 'dzum pa'i mdangs dang ldan zhing /
NK053('i)001:11202: 'od phung dang chas nas ye shes bkra gsal du bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11203: de ltar zhi ba las khro bor bsgyur ro /
NK053('i)001:11205: 2 / da ni 'khor snga ma las gnas bsgyur ba la /
NK053('i)001:11206: thabs gang gis bsgyur snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:11207: pad+mo rin chen ldan byas nas //
NK053('i)001:11214: mkha' gsang byin gyis brlab pa /
NK053('i)001:11215: yab yum brda so sor bskul ba /
NK053('i)001:11217: byang chub sems kyi mchod pa bya ba /
NK053('i)001:11218: de la 'gro ba'i don bya ba /
NK053('i)001:11220: dang po de la mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs te /
NK053('i)001:11222: mkha' dbyings pad+ma rdo rje byin brlabs pa'i //
NK053('i)001:11223: yum mkha' a las ma chags zla gam gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:11224: pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor chos sku a dang ldan //
NK053('i)001:11225: yab kyi rdo rje h'u las rtse lngar nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor //
NK053('i)001:11227: de la yab kyi thugs ka nas /
NK053('i)001:11228: yi ge b+h+r+aum zhig yum gyi mkha' la 'phros pa las /
NK053('i)001:11231: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he tsan+d+ra pad+ma dang am /
NK053('i)001:11233: mkha' de nyid zla gam dmar po'i gzhal yas khang thig bzhi btab pas le'u tshe dgur gyur pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11234: dbus kyi le'u tshe la pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi pa'i ge sar la /
NK053('i)001:11235: dmar la dwangs pa zhig gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11236: yang yum gyi thugs ka nas /
NK053('i)001:11237: yi ge h'u zhig yab kyi mkha' la 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:11238: mkha'i dngos po sbyangs 'od du zhu ba las /
NK053('i)001:11241: yab kyi gsang ba'i rdo rje rtse lnga pa las /
NK053('i)001:11242: sked sgor rin po ches mdzes par byas shing /
NK053('i)001:11243: de'i steng du nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du /
NK053('i)001:11244: dkar po zhig gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11245: de ltar mkha' dbyings pad+ma dang /
NK053('i)001:11248: dkar por ldan par byas nas byin gyis brlab par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:11251: de'i dus su sbyor ba'i brda ji ltar bskul snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:11252: bde mchog sgyu ma'i brdas mtshan te //
NK053('i)001:11254: nyan thos dang 'jig rten pa la ltos na bde
NK053('i)001:11255: ba dang mchog tu gyur pa'i sbyor ba mdzad pa'i
NK053('i)001:11256: phyir / sgyu ma lta bu'i ting nge 'dzin la gnas nas /
NK053('i)001:11257: sbyor ba'i brdas bskul ba yang /
NK053('i)001:11265: mdzes par blta zhing yid du 'ong //
NK053('i)001:11266: gcig la gcig ni chags shing 'phreng //
NK053('i)001:11267: glu dbyangs dga' ba'i mdangs dang sgyus //
NK053('i)001:11268: gnyis su med par bskul bar bya //
NK053('i)001:11271: dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes brjod do //
NK053('i)001:11272: dzahlcagasa kyu'i phyag rgyas mdun du byas shing /
NK053('i)001:11273: h'u zhags pas stod smad nas 'khyud de /
NK053('i)001:11276: thugs ka dang thugs ka sbyar /
NK053('i)001:11277: gsang ba dang gsang ba sbyar te /
NK053('i)001:11280: pad+ma ma sam yo gi pra be sha ya phata kyis yum gyi pad+ma zum pa kha phral te /
NK053('i)001:11283: zhes rig pa'i dbyings la 'jug pa'i phyir rdo rje phul lo //
NK053('i)001:11284: de ltar rol pa la zhugs nas /
NK053('i)001:11285: bar der yab yum bde ba ji ltar skyed snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:11286: dbyings kyi bde chen 'byung ba de //
NK053('i)001:11287: rang rig ye shes de las 'od //
NK053('i)001:11289: chos kyi dbyings kyi rang bzhin byang chub sems dga' ba dang bde ba 'phrad de /
NK053('i)001:11291: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a nu r+aa ga dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:11293: yab kyi byang chub kyi sems gyis bsdus shing dkar chi li li bsdus nas /
NK053('i)001:11294: go ro tsa na'i pho brang nas mar babs nas /
NK053('i)001:11296: thugs kar thim nas srog gi gsang lung du zhugs /
NK053('i)001:11297: h'u gis sgal tshigs kyi rta la brgyud /
NK053('i)001:11298: rdo rje'i lam nas byung nas /
NK053('i)001:11299: phata kyis yum gyi mkha' la bab pa de /
NK053('i)001:11300: rang rig pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bo /
NK053('i)001:11301: lhag pa byang chub kyi sems de las 'od gcig la gcig 'phro 'du bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:11303: yum 'od du dkar ldem gyis gyur /
NK053('i)001:11305: sna bug g.yas pa nas zhugs /
NK053('i)001:11306: bdag gi sna bug g.yon par thim /
NK053('i)001:11307: dgyes pa'i ro dus gcig tu bstan /
NK053('i)001:11308: yum gyi thugs ka nas byang chub sems dmar la dwangs pa srog dag pa'i gsang lung nas zhugs /
NK053('i)001:11309: sgal tshigs kyi rta la brgyud yab kyi mkha' la thim /
NK053('i)001:11310: yab 'od du dmar ltem gyis gyur /
NK053('i)001:11311: yab kyi thugs ka nas slar brgyud de /
NK053('i)001:11313: yum gyi sna g.yon du thim /
NK053('i)001:11314: mkha' la 'bab 'od du dmar ltem ltem gnas pa las /
NK053('i)001:11315: yab kyi byang chub sems yum gyi mkha' la 'od du dkar tsa ra ra bab pa las /
NK053('i)001:11316: dkar dmar krug gis 'dres te gser dngul zhi gar blugs pa bzhin du /
NK053('i)001:11317: rang rig pa'i ye shes 'od du ltem ltem gsal bar bsgom /
NK053('i)001:11320: byang chub sems des bde bar gshegs pa ji ltar mchod snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:11322: ji bzhin mkha' la gsal ba dag /
NK053('i)001:11324: sangs rgyas sprin tshogs ma lus la //
NK053('i)001:11325: dgyes mnyam mchog gi sbyin pas gtims //
NK053('i)001:11326: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa p+au dza badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:11328: bde ba ji bzhin pa'i byang chub sems de /
NK053('i)001:11329: chos nyid yum gyi mkha' la gsal zhing dag pa ni /
NK053('i)001:11330: dper na sgrib g.yogs kyi dri ma med pa'i nam
NK053('i)001:11331: mkha' dwangs pa la mun pa'i gzhi med pa'i dri
NK053('i)001:11332: med nyi ma las 'tsher ba'i 'od phyogs bcur shar
NK053('i)001:11333: bas / 'od zer gyi rtse las mchod pa'i bye brag bsam gyis mi khyab par gyur te /
NK053('i)001:11334: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa sangs rgyas yab yum sras 'khor dang bcas pa /
NK053('i)001:11335: nam mkha'i sprin tshogs lta bu gtibs pa ma lus
NK053('i)001:11336: pa kun la mchod pas dgyes pa bskyed cing mnyam
NK053('i)001:11338: sku gsung thugs kyi che ba'i byin rlabs kun bsdus nas /
NK053('i)001:11339: mchog gi dngos grub bdag la sbyin par mdzad cing /
NK053('i)001:11340: slar la ye shes kyi 'od dang /
NK053('i)001:11342: yab yum gyi mkha' la thim pas /
NK053('i)001:11343: byang chub sems snga ma dang dbyer med par gyur te /
NK053('i)001:11345: dkar la 'tsher bar gyur pa ni gsang ba'i sa
NK053('i)001:11346: bon dang ye shes kyi sa bon dbyer med pa
NK053('i)001:11347: zhes bya ste / 'dod rgyur bsgyur ba'i rin po che //
NK053('i)001:11350: des 'gro ba'i don ji ltar bya snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:11351: byang chub sems ni kun tu dag /
NK053('i)001:11352: khams gsum rab tu 'das nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:11353: ma lus snying rjes khyab byas te //
NK053('i)001:11354: 'dod pas bya ba rab tu mnyes //
NK053('i)001:11355: sarba ta th+aa ga ta bo d+hi tsit+ta ma h+aa
NK053('i)001:11356: ka ru me tri badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aat+ma ko&a
NK053('i)001:11358: byang chub sems dkar la 'tsher ba des /
NK053('i)001:11359: dus dang gnas skabs kun tu gzung 'dzin gyi dri ma rnam pa dag ste /
NK053('i)001:11360: de yang ji ltar dag ce na /
NK053('i)001:11361: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten la phog pas /
NK053('i)001:11362: dngos po ril bsregs sbyangs te sangs rgyas kyi zhing yongs su dag par bsgyur te /
NK053('i)001:11363: nang bcud kyi 'jig rten khams gsum na gnas pa'i sems can la phog pas /
NK053('i)001:11364: las dang nyon mongs pa'i rtog sgrib bsregs sbyangs te /
NK053('i)001:11365: sangs rgyas kyi sa la rab tu bkod de /
NK053('i)001:11366: de las kyang 'das te phyogs bcur 'jig rten gyi
NK053('i)001:11367: khams nas nam mkha'i mtha' gtug pa thams cad du
NK053('i)001:11368: 'phros pas / de na gnas pa'i sems can thams
NK053('i)001:11369: cad byang chub sems snying rje chen po'i rlan dang
NK053('i)001:11370: bcas pas khyab par byas nas /
NK053('i)001:11371: gang dang gang la mos shing thob par 'dod pa de dag la /
NK053('i)001:11372: re ba skong zhing phan btags pas /
NK053('i)001:11373: dga' ba bskyed pa'i sgo nas sangs rgyas kyi sa la bkod do //
NK053('i)001:11374: de la ril gyi bkrag dang gzi mdangs slar 'dus te /
NK053('i)001:11375: yum gyi mkha' la ltem zhing 'khyil bas /
NK053('i)001:11376: yum 'dod pa'i dbang mo yang rab tu mnyes par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11379: byang chub kyi sems de las khro bo 'chol ba ji ltar spro snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:11380: bskal pa'i me dpung 'khrigs pa bzhin //
NK053('i)001:11383: bde ba thugs kyi dkyil 'khor nas /
NK053('i)001:11384: byang chub sems sprin 'phros pa las //
NK053('i)001:11386: bskal ba'i me dpung 'khrigs pa bzhin //
NK053('i)001:11389: bi shwa badz+ra kro d+ha dz+wa la sna tshogs rdo rje khro bo 'bar ba /
NK053('i)001:11390: man d+ha la dkyil 'khor phata phata phata /
NK053('i)001:11392: ha la ha la ha la h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:11394: zhes brjod pas yab yum gyi gsang ba'i thugs ka
NK053('i)001:11395: nas gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems kyi 'od
NK053('i)001:11397: khro bo 'chol ba'i dkyil 'khor sprin phung lta bus
NK053('i)001:11398: stong gsum dang 'jig rten drug lhag gis gang ste
NK053('i)001:11399: / lag na mtshon cha sna tshogs pa thogs nas //
NK053('i)001:11403: sod chod rgyob gtogs zer ba'i sgra sna tshogs su sgrog pa /
NK053('i)001:11404: ri rab 'bum dus gcig la bsnyil ba skad gsungs gsungs pas /
NK053('i)001:11412: sku re re las kyang ye shes kyi me 'od
NK053('i)001:11413: bskal pa'i me dpung lta bur 'bar zhing 'khrigs par
NK053('i)001:11414: bsgom mo // khro bo 'chol ba des las ci byed snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:11415: khro bo'i sprul pas dregs pa bsgral //
NK053('i)001:11418: stong gsum phyogs bcu'i rdul phra snyed //
NK053('i)001:11419: de snyed khro bo'i dkyil 'khor thob //
NK053('i)001:11420: de dag sangs rgyas mdzad pa yis //
NK053('i)001:11421: phyogs bcu'i dregs pa ma lus bsgral //
NK053('i)001:11422: ma h+aa badz+ra a d+ha ha pa ha pa ha ha ha kha kha kha /
NK053('i)001:11425: stong gsum gang ba'i khro bo mang po de dag gis /
NK053('i)001:11426: stong gsum gyi stong 'jig rten gyi khams thams cad
NK053('i)001:11427: ras bal rlung gis btab pa bzhin du bsreg shig
NK053('i)001:11429: khyad par du 'dod khams kyi lha chen po sogs te /
NK053('i)001:11432: nar nur las dbyings la glan pa'i phyir ril mid du mdzad /
NK053('i)001:11433: khro mo u tsush+ma'i snam nas lan gsum du phyung nas /
NK053('i)001:11434: slar mi ldog pa'i sa la bkod /
NK053('i)001:11435: sprul pa'i pho nya dang las mkhan du dbang bskur nas gdan du bting ste bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:11436: de'i chung ma srin mo rnams kyis /
NK053('i)001:11437: ston pa'i zhal ni ma mthong /
NK053('i)001:11438: 'od zer dang sgra'i che ma rgyag gis rab tu dngangs te /
NK053('i)001:11439: mthu dang bal nas la la ni brgyal /
NK053('i)001:11446: rang rang gi snying po phul nas /
NK053('i)001:11447: bar snang la mgo btud de gnas par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11448: de la bdag nyid kyi thugs ka nas /
NK053('i)001:11449: yi ge b+h+yo dmar smug re spyi gtsug gam snying khar bstim pas /
NK053('i)001:11450: ye shes kyi thugs rje dang /
NK053('i)001:11451: dam tshig tu ldan par byin gyis brlabs /
NK053('i)001:11452: lag tu rdo rje byin nas ming btags /
NK053('i)001:11453: phrin las rnam pa bzhi sgrubs shig pa'i dam tshig phog /
NK053('i)001:11454: nye gnas rnam pa bzhi'i tshul dngos chun ma /
NK053('i)001:11464: ma chags thabs kyi sbyor ba byas pas /
NK053('i)001:11467: dar gyi rlod stan re re'i steng na /
NK053('i)001:11468: dbu gtsug tor re dang ldan par /
NK053('i)001:11469: pus mo rgyal btsugs nas bzhugs zhes dang /
NK053('i)001:11471: mgo btud de gnas par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11472: snang srid thams cad khro bo bskal pa'i me dpung
NK053('i)001:11473: 'khrigs pa'i dkyil 'khor gyis dregs pa can thams cad
NK053('i)001:11474: bsgral te 'khor dbang du bsdu ba /
NK053('i)001:11476: sprul pa'i khro bo de dag slar gang du bsdu snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:11480: stong khams gang ba'i khrag 'thung rnams //
NK053('i)001:11481: bsdu ba'i sbyor bas kun bsdus nas //
NK053('i)001:11483: dbyings su thim nas yig 'bru'i sku //
NK053('i)001:11486: stong gsum gang ba'i khro bo de dag slar yum
NK053('i)001:11487: gyi mkha' la 'dus pa las 'od du lam gyis
NK053('i)001:11488: 'bar nas thog ma'i byang chub sems dang dbyer med
NK053('i)001:11489: pa las gsung yig 'bru'i tshogs su gyur par byin
NK053('i)001:11494: de la zhi ba'i dus kyi 'khor rnams khro bor gnas ji ltar bsgyur snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:11497: de yang nga ga don du /
NK053('i)001:11498: rigs bzhi'i khrag 'thung dbu la rdzogs pas dal du mi bskyed par mngon /
NK053('i)001:11499: bskyed rdzogs chen po ru yang de ltar du 'dod do //
NK053('i)001:11508: dang po ke'u r+ai bskyed pa ni /
NK053('i)001:11509: yab yum gyi mkha' gsang na gnas pa'i ha brgyad ye shes kyi 'od dang bcas pas /
NK053('i)001:11510: sems dpa' brgyad kyi spyi gtsug tu thim pa las /
NK053('i)001:11511: ye shes kyi 'od zer du 'bar zhing gnas pa las /
NK053('i)001:11516: byang chub sems dpa' 'od du zhu //
NK053('i)001:11518: dkar shams dang ni rkun mo tso'u r+ai ma dang //
NK053('i)001:11519: pra mo ha rmongs mo ma dang ro langs ma //
NK053('i)001:11521: puk+ka s+ai sbos mo dang ni gtum mo kasma r+ai dang //
NK053('i)001:11522: sma sha n+ai sme sha can dang ni ma'i tsan+d+ha l+ai tshogs //
NK053('i)001:11523: so so rang rang lag cha dang //
NK053('i)001:11524: ngo mtshar chas nas rngam pa'i sku //
NK053('i)001:11526: ma mo'i 'khor rnam pa gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:11530: dbang po dang rnam shes gnas gyur te /
NK053('i)001:11531: tshogs brgyad de kho na gcig pa'i ma mo brgyad /
NK053('i)001:11532: spyad bya yul gyi zhen pa gnas gyur pa mche gshog can gyi ma mo brgyad de bcu drug /
NK053('i)001:11533: rtag chad mu bzhi'i mtha' bkag nas tshad med bzhir rgyas 'debs pa sgo ma bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:11535: don chos nyid rnal ma la rig pa'i ye shes
NK053('i)001:11536: 'byor pas na nang gi rnal 'byor ma zhes bya'o
NK053('i)001:11537: // phyi las las grub pa dang dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad ni /
NK053('i)001:11538: phyi'i grub pa mo zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:11540: de bas na nang gi grub pa mo'i rnal 'byor ma rnams bskyed pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11541: rgyu sems can gyi ldan tshul ni /
NK053('i)001:11542: rnam par shes pa bzhi dang dbang po bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:11543: rnam shes tshogs brgyad du 'dus pas na yi ge ha brgyad do //
NK053('i)001:11544: zhi khro gnas bsgyur na byang chub sems dpa' brgyad de ma mo brgyad do //
NK053('i)001:11545: 'bras bu ye shes kyi thob tshul ni /
NK053('i)001:11546: rigs kyi cha 'dzin pa'i ye shes kyi ngo bor thob pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11547: de la nang rnam shes kyi mkha' 'gro ma bzhi ni /
NK053('i)001:11552: ming gi khyad par ke'u r+ai ma sku mdog khyad par sngon mo /
NK053('i)001:11553: phyag g.yas zhing gi dbyug pa /
NK053('i)001:11554: g.yon b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba zhig /
NK053('i)001:11555: dgod gnas kyi khyad par nang ltar bdag gi snying gar gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:11556: phyi ltar mdun gyi zla gam gyi shar phyogs yang gsal bar bsgom /
NK053('i)001:11559: tso'u r+ai ma sku mdog ser mo /
NK053('i)001:11560: phyag gnyis mda' gzhu 'gengs pa zhig /
NK053('i)001:11561: bdag gi dpung pa g.yas par gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:11562: zla gam gyi lho phyogs su yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11563: khyad par gsum sogs gong ltar kun la 'agre'o //
NK053('i)001:11566: khro mo pra mo ha sku mdog dmar mo /
NK053('i)001:11567: phyag g.yas chu srin gyi rgyal mtshan 'phyar ba /
NK053('i)001:11568: g.yon b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba zhig /
NK053('i)001:11569: zla gam gyi nub phyogs su gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:11570: bdag gi sog pa'i bar du yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11573: khro mo bee ta l+ai sku mdog mthing nag /
NK053('i)001:11575: g.yon zhing chung ngu'i dbyug pas g.yob pa zhig /
NK053('i)001:11576: zla gam gyi byang phyogs su gsal tsam na //
NK053('i)001:11577: bdag gi dpung pa g.yon bar yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11578: phyi dbang po'i mkha' 'gro ma bzhi /
NK053('i)001:11581: khro mo puska s+ai sku mdog dmar ser /
NK053('i)001:11582: phyag g.yon gyis zhing chung ngu bzung nas /
NK053('i)001:11583: g.yas kyis rgyu ma 'dren cing stob pa zhig /
NK053('i)001:11584: zla gam gyi shar lhor gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:11585: bdag gi nub 'jing g.yas par gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11588: khro mo kasma r+ai sku mdog ljang gu /
NK053('i)001:11589: phyag g.yon pa b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba'i nang du /
NK053('i)001:11590: g.yas kyi rdo rjes dkrus cing gsol ba zhig zla gam gyi lho nub tu gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:11591: bdag gi sog pa g.yas par gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11594: khro mo sma sha ni sku mdog mthig nag /
NK053('i)001:11595: phyag g.yas g.yon gnyis kyis zhing bzung nas /
NK053('i)001:11596: tshems kyis sbubs dral te snying la za ba zhig /
NK053('i)001:11597: zla gam gyi nub byang du gsal tsam ni /
NK053('i)001:11598: bdag gi sog pa g.yon par yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11601: khro mo tsan+d+ha l+ai sku mdog ser skya /
NK053('i)001:11602: phyag g.yon gyis zhing bzung nas /
NK053('i)001:11603: g.yas kyis mgo bcad nas 'phyar ba zhig /
NK053('i)001:11604: zla gam gyi byang shar du gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:11605: bdag gi nu 'jing g.yon par yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11606: khro mo ke'u ri ma brgyad po de dag kun /
NK053('i)001:11607: zhabs dor stabs su bsgrad nas zhing bsgril ma'i gdan la bardzisa pa /
NK053('i)001:11608: thugs ka na nyi ma'i steng na rin po che
NK053('i)001:11609: zur brgyad pa mtheb long tsam gyi shu bu kha
NK053('i)001:11610: na / ha 'od du 'bar ba'i mtha' mar /
NK053('i)001:11611: ru lu 'bru brgyad kyis bskor bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11612: ljags pad+ma'i steng du yang ru lu 'bru rgyad kyis bskor bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11613: dbu skra'i ral pa me 'bar bas sku lte ba yan chad khebs pa /
NK053('i)001:11614: spyan sdang mig tu bgrad cing mche ba gtsigs pa /
NK053('i)001:11615: sku la zhing chen gyi g.yang gzhi dang /
NK053('i)001:11616: stag gi sham thabs su gsol ba /
NK053('i)001:11617: ba su ta'i ske rags bcings pa /
NK053('i)001:11618: thod pa'i phreng bas se ral khar brgyan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11619: de yan chad du yang dag grub pa don gyi lha dgu /
NK053('i)001:11622: rgyu sems can gyi ldan tshul ni /
NK053('i)001:11623: dbang po dang rnam shes kyi spyad bya yul du gyur pa rnams so //
NK053('i)001:11624: zhi khro gnas bsgyur ba ni /
NK053('i)001:11625: phyi nang gi sems ma brgyad do //
NK053('i)001:11626: des na yul gyi ma mo brgyad ces bya'o //
NK053('i)001:11627: 'bras bu ye shes kyi thob tshul ni /
NK053('i)001:11628: yul dag pa chos kyi dbyings yin la /
NK053('i)001:11629: de la ye shes lnga'i rol pa ma 'gags pa gnas pa thob pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11630: de nas yang yum gyi mkha' gsang na gnas pa'i
NK053('i)001:11631: he brgyad po de ye shes kyi 'od zer dang
NK053('i)001:11632: bcas par sems ma brgyad kyi spyi gtsug tu thim
NK053('i)001:11633: pa las / ye shes kyi 'od du 'bar zhing gnas pa las /
NK053('i)001:11635: de nas dgyes te he brjod pas //
NK053('i)001:11636: byang chub sems ma 'od du zhu //
NK053('i)001:11637: seng gdong chen mo la sogs te //
NK053('i)001:11638: stag dang wa dang khyi dang bzhad //
NK053('i)001:11639: kang ka dur bya 'ug gdong che //
NK053('i)001:11640: so so rang rang lag cha dang //
NK053('i)001:11641: ngo mtshar can nas rngam thon te //
NK053('i)001:11642: phyi rol shar gyi phyogs dag nas //
NK053('i)001:11644: badz+ra seng nga mu khe he /
NK053('i)001:11646: gzhan zil gyis gnon pa'i don phra men ma seng ge'i mgo can /
NK053('i)001:11648: phyag g.yas g.yon dpung mgor bsnol nas /
NK053('i)001:11649: kha na zhing chung ngu thogs pa zhig /
NK053('i)001:11650: phyi ltar dkyil 'khor gyi bar khyams shar phyogs su gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:11651: nang ltar bdag gi lte bar gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11652: badz+ra b+y+aa kri mu ka he /
NK053('i)001:11654: dpal brtul che ba'i don b+y+aa kri mu ka stag gi mgo can /
NK053('i)001:11656: lag pa g.yas g.yon bsnol te /
NK053('i)001:11657: g.yas kyis g.yon gyi steng mnan nas /
NK053('i)001:11658: mdun na zhing yod pa la 'bru tshugs su blta ba zhig /
NK053('i)001:11660: bdag gi s+t+wa zur g.yas par yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11661: badz+ra sri la mu ka he /
NK053('i)001:11663: sna rno zhing thabs la mkhas pas 'gro don mdzad pas sri la mu ka wa'i mgo can /
NK053('i)001:11665: phyag gnyis kyis zhing gi khog pa dral te snying phyung nas lces bldag pa zhig /
NK053('i)001:11667: bdag gi bcu drug mdor yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11668: badza shwa na mu ka he /
NK053('i)001:11670: rnam rtog 'joms pa shwa na mu ka spyang mo'i mgo can /
NK053('i)001:11672: phyag g.yon gyis zhing gi khog pa bzung ba g.yas kyis dral te blta zhing lces bldag pa zhig /
NK053('i)001:11674: bdag gi s+t+wa zur g.yon par yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11675: badz+ra kri ta mu ka he /
NK053('i)001:11677: shes rab la thogs pa med pa kri ta mu ka bya rgod kyi mgo can /
NK053('i)001:11679: phyag g.yon gyis zhing bzung nas /
NK053('i)001:11680: g.yas gri thogs pas khong dral te /
NK053('i)001:11681: zhing gi rgyu ma drangs nas kha na za ba zhig /
NK053('i)001:11683: bdag gi mkhal khung g.yas par yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11686: 'khor ba dang du len pa'i brdar kang ka mu ka bya kang ka'i mgo can /
NK053('i)001:11688: phyag g.yas kyis zhing phrag pa la bkal nas /
NK053('i)001:11689: g.yon gyis zhing bzung ba zhig /
NK053('i)001:11690: lho nub tu gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:11691: bdag gi dpyi g.yas par yang gsol /
NK053('i)001:11692: badz+ra khwa khwa mu ka he /
NK053('i)001:11694: 'khor 'das mnyam pa nyid du mkhyen pas khwa khwa mu ka bya rog gi mgo can /
NK053('i)001:11697: phyag g.yas kyis gri thogs shing g.yon ban+d+ha thogs pa zhig /
NK053('i)001:11698: nub byang du gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:11699: bdag gi mkhal khung g.yon du yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11700: badz+ra hu lu mu ka he /
NK053('i)001:11702: ye shes kyi spyan dang ldan pas gdul bya phra
NK053('i)001:11703: mo yal bar mi dor ba hu lu mu ka
NK053('i)001:11706: phyag g.yas rdo rje lcags kyu /
NK053('i)001:11708: bar khyams kyi byang shar du gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:11709: bdag gi mkhal khung g.yon par yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11710: phra men ma brgyad po de'i zhabs zhing rkyang re la bardzisa te /
NK053('i)001:11711: rgyan cha lugs gzhan ke'u r+ai ma'i sar brtag go //
NK053('i)001:11712: gsum pa sgo ma bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:11713: rgyu sems can gyi ldan tshul ni /
NK053('i)001:11714: lus kyi dbang po rnam pa bzhi'o //
NK053('i)001:11716: zhi ba'i sgo ma khro bo'i sgo mar gnas 'gyur ba'o //
NK053('i)001:11717: 'bras bu ye shes kyi thob tshul ni /
NK053('i)001:11718: tshad med pa bzhis mtha' bzhi bral nas ye shes mtha' bral chen po thob pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11719: las kyi dbang po las byed pa yin pas na /
NK053('i)001:11720: lha sgo ma byung ba ste /
NK053('i)001:11721: gsang ba'i lha mo bzhi zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:11722: sgo ma'i mtshan man ngag 'chugs so //
NK053('i)001:11723: yang yab yum gyi mkha' gsang na gnas pa'i phata bzhi po de /
NK053('i)001:11724: ye shes kyi 'od zer dang bcas par /
NK053('i)001:11725: sgo ma bzhi'i spyi gtsug tu thim pa las /
NK053('i)001:11726: ye shes kyi 'od du lam lam 'bar ba las /
NK053('i)001:11728: de nas dgyes te phata brjod pas //
NK053('i)001:11731: rdo rje sring 'gro ma tshogs gsang mtshan mi pham ma dang //
NK053('i)001:11732: lho'i gdong mo ral gcig ma /
NK053('i)001:11733: nub gyi 'jig rten gsum rgyal ma /
NK053('i)001:11736: so so rang rang lag cha dang //
NK053('i)001:11737: ngo mtshar chas nas 'jigs thon te //
NK053('i)001:11738: dkyil 'khor sgo bzhir rngam gzugs gnas //
NK053('i)001:11739: badz+ra ar+ya te dza te nga dzahphata /
NK053('i)001:11742: sgo ma rdo rje lcags kyu ma /
NK053('i)001:11744: rta'i mgo can du 'dod pa'ang yod /
NK053('i)001:11745: phyag g.yas b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba'i nang nas rta mgo ljang gu phyung ba /
NK053('i)001:11746: g.yon lcags kyu thogs pa zhig /
NK053('i)001:11748: bdag gi mkhrig ma g.yas par yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11749: badz+ra a mo ka h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:11751: nyon mongs pa thal bar rlog pas /
NK053('i)001:11752: sgo ma phag gdong zhags pa ma /
NK053('i)001:11754: phyag g.yas phag rgod kyi mche ba /
NK053('i)001:11755: g.yon zhags pa thogs pa zhig /
NK053('i)001:11757: bdag gi mkhrig ma g.yon par yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11761: sgo ma nyi zla lcags sgrog ma /
NK053('i)001:11762: dred dam seng ge'i mgo can /
NK053('i)001:11764: phyag g.yas g.yon gnyis lcags sgrog bsnams pa'i mig gi steng na nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor thogs pa zhig /
NK053('i)001:11766: bdag gi rkang pa g.yas par yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11767: badz+ra b+hasmi pa la ya ba ti hohphata /
NK053('i)001:11769: sems can ro dang 'dra ba la ye shes kyi dra pa bskyed pas khams gsum slar 'tsho ma /
NK053('i)001:11770: sgo ma thal byed dril bu ma /
NK053('i)001:11773: phyag g.yas b+han+d+ha rak+tasa bkang ba'i steng na snang ba mtha' yas kyi dbu phyung ba /
NK053('i)001:11774: g.yon dril bu thogs pa zhig /
NK053('i)001:11775: byang gi sgor gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:11776: bdag gi rkang pa g.yon par yang gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11778: zhing rkyang pa'i gdan la bardzisa shing /
NK053('i)001:11779: bskal pa'i me 'bar ba'i klong na khro bag gi tshul du bzhugs te /
NK053('i)001:11780: rgyan cha lugs gzhan ke'u ri ma'i sar brtag /
NK053('i)001:11781: dpal chen po la lha mo nyi shus bskor ba /
NK053('i)001:11782: de rnams la nang gi rnal 'byor ma zhes kyang bya'o //
NK053('i)001:11783: dbang mo man chad la phyi'i grub pa mo zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:11785: bzhi pa dbang mo bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:11787: phyi srin mo'i cha lugs su gnas pa dang /
NK053('i)001:11788: nang mgo brnyan gyi cha lugs dang /
NK053('i)001:11789: gsang ba khro mo'i cha lugs su gnas pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11790: dang po phyi srin mo'i cha lugs ni /
NK053('i)001:11791: srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK053('i)001:11793: he ru ka'i gal po nas bshad do //
NK053('i)001:11794: gnyis pa nang mgo brnyan gyi cha byad ni /
NK053('i)001:11795: mi srin dmar ser tri shul zhing chen g.yag /
NK053('i)001:11796: ces pa la sogs pa lta bu'o //
NK053('i)001:11797: gsum pa gsang ba khro mo'i cha lugs ni /
NK053('i)001:11798: zhal gsum phyag drug pa ste /
NK053('i)001:11799: lha mo sgyu 'phrul nas bshad do //
NK053('i)001:11800: 'dir ni byon tshul gang yang 'dra ste /
NK053('i)001:11801: ru tra 'dul ba'i dus su srin mor gnas pas khro bo 'chol ba'i dus su srin mor bya /
NK053('i)001:11802: rnal 'byor pas bsgrubs te las la mngags pa'i dus su mgo brnyan du gnas te /
NK053('i)001:11803: phra men mgo brnyan du bya /
NK053('i)001:11804: gsang ba rang sems rtogs pa'i dus na khro mo nyi shu rtsa brgyad du bya'o //
NK053('i)001:11806: dbang mo ni las las grub pa yin pas /
NK053('i)001:11807: mkha' nas mi bskyed par srog sogs b+h+yo nyer brgyad brjod pas byon par bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:11808: de nas dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad rigs dbye zhing so sor ngos bzung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:11809: sku mdog dang phyag mtshan gsal gdab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:11811: slas dang byi mo bran mo'i tshogs //
NK053('i)001:11812: bcu gnyis nyi shu dang ni brgyad kyis mdzes //
NK053('i)001:11813: rang gi stan dang lag cha dang //
NK053('i)001:11814: ci bgyi zhes ni chas te gnas //
NK053('i)001:11817: khyo'i khyad par srin po'i chung ma sku mdog gi khyad par smug nag /
NK053('i)001:11818: mgo brnyan gyi cha lugs g.yag mgo /
NK053('i)001:11819: phyag mtshan gyi khyad par g.yas rdo rje dang /
NK053('i)001:11820: thams cad la dbang rtags su yod pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11823: phyi rol gyi lcags ri nag po sgo bzhi ldan pa'i shar dang por gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11826: tshangs pa'i chung ma dmar ser dbu bzhi ma /
NK053('i)001:11827: mgo brnyan byas na sbrul mgo /
NK053('i)001:11830: phyi rol gyi shar dang po'i 'og tu gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11833: lha chen po'i chung ma dkar ljang /
NK053('i)001:11836: tshul zhi khro zhig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11839: khyab 'jug gi chung ma sngon mo //
NK053('i)001:11842: tshul zhi khro zhig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11845: gzhon nu'i chung ma dmar mo //
NK053('i)001:11848: tshul zhi khro zhig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11851: brgya byin gyi chung ma dkar ser /
NK053('i)001:11854: tshul zhi khro zhig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11855: badz+ra ma h+aa ka li b+h+yo /
NK053('i)001:11857: ma h+aa ka la'i chung ma nag mo //
NK053('i)001:11860: tshul khro bag can zhig shar phyogs kyi sgor gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11861: ma mo de mdun shar phyogs kyi sgor gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:11862: bdag gi barla g.yas phyogs kyi nang logs nas mar gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11863: yang na shar gyi ma mo de bdun sku mdog dkar mo la zhal mthing ka /
NK053('i)001:11864: phyag g.yas rdo rje rtse gsum /
NK053('i)001:11868: ma h+aa de wa'i sring mo ser mo //
NK053('i)001:11871: tshul zhi khro zhig phyi rol gyi lho dang po la gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11874: nyi ma'i chung ma dmar mo //
NK053('i)001:11877: tshul zhi khro zhig tu gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11880: zla ba'i chung ma dkar mo //
NK053('i)001:11883: tshul zhi ba zhig tu gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11886: be con gyi chung ma ljang nag /
NK053('i)001:11888: g.yon dbyug pa rdo rje can /
NK053('i)001:11889: tshul zhi khro zhig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11892: srin po'i chung ma dmar mo //
NK053('i)001:11894: g.yon b+han+d+ha dmar gyis bkang ba /
NK053('i)001:11895: khro bag ste srin mo'i tshul 'dzin pa'o //
NK053('i)001:11898: za byed kyi chung ma ljang nag /
NK053('i)001:11900: g.yon ti ra'i rgyu ma 'dren cing za ba /
NK053('i)001:11901: tshul khro bag can zhig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11904: ra mgo dmar ser gyi chung ma dmar ser /
NK053('i)001:11907: tshul khro bag zhig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11908: yang na lho'i ma mo de bdun sku mdog ser nag /
NK053('i)001:11911: ma mo de bdun dkyil 'khor phyi rol gyi lha phyogs su gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:11912: bdag gi barla g.yas kyi phyir zur nas mar gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11915: dga' byed kyi chung ma dmar mo //
NK053('i)001:11918: tshul zhi khro zhig tu gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11921: stobs bzang gi chung ma dkar mo //
NK053('i)001:11924: tshul khro bag cig tu gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11925: e ka tsa ra ma b+h+yo /
NK053('i)001:11927: gshin rje'i sring mo dmar ser /
NK053('i)001:11930: tshul zhi khro zhig tu gsol lo //
NK053('i)001:11936: tshul zhi ba zhig tu gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11939: nor srung gi chung ma dkar mo //
NK053('i)001:11942: tshul zhi khro zhig tu gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11945: rlung lha'i chung ma sngon mo //
NK053('i)001:11948: tshul zhi khro zhig tu gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11949: ku ma ba shwa ra b+h+yo /
NK053('i)001:11951: srin bum sna'i chung ma dmar mo //
NK053('i)001:11954: tshul khro bag cig nub sgor gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11955: yang na nub kyi ma mo de bdun sku mdog dmar nag /
NK053('i)001:11958: ma mo de bdun dkyil 'khor gyi nub phyogs su gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:11959: bdag gi barla g.yon gyi phyir zur nas mar gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:11960: ma h+aa m+aa ra ni b+h+yo /
NK053('i)001:11962: gsod byed kyi chung ma dmar nag /
NK053('i)001:11966: phyi rol gyi byang dang po la gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11969: me lha'i chung ma dmar mo //
NK053('i)001:11972: tshul khro bag cig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11975: phag gi chung ma nag mo //
NK053('i)001:11978: tshul zhi khro zhig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11981: gshin rje'i chung ma dmar nag /
NK053('i)001:11983: g.yon zhing chung la za ba /
NK053('i)001:11984: tshul khror bag cig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11987: dbang ldan gyi chung ma ljang nag /
NK053('i)001:11990: tshul khro ba gcig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11993: chu lha'i chung ma sngon mo //
NK053('i)001:11996: tshul zhi khro zhig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:11999: d+ha sha gri ba'i chung ma ljang nag /
NK053('i)001:12002: tshul khro bag cig byang sgor gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:12003: yang na byang gi ma mo de bdun ljang nag /
NK053('i)001:12006: ma mo de mdun dkyil 'khor gyi byang phyogs su gsal tsam na /
NK053('i)001:12007: bdag gi barla g.yon phyogs kyi nang logs nas mar gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:12008: dbang phyug ma de rnams sku mdog gong ltar so sor gsal ba dang /
NK053('i)001:12009: so so'i dbu stongs su g.yag dang sbrul la sogs
NK053('i)001:12010: pa'i so sor dbu re re byung bar bsgom pa
NK053('i)001:12011: dang / phyag g.yas kun mthun par las kyi rdo rje rtse gsum pa re re bsnams pa /
NK053('i)001:12012: g.yon rang rtags kyi phyag mtshan gong ltar bsnams pa /
NK053('i)001:12013: zhing skam po rkyang bu dang dar gyi rlod stan re re'i steng na /
NK053('i)001:12018: zhi khro'i tshul du ldan pa /
NK053('i)001:12019: dbang po lnga las me 'bar ba /
NK053('i)001:12020: dbu skra mthon mthing lcang lor 'khyil ba la /
NK053('i)001:12021: g.yu'i zar bu chung 'od stong 'bum gyis brgyan pa /
NK053('i)001:12022: de rnams kyi thugs kar yang khrag gi rgya mtsho mtheb long tsam re re'i steng du /
NK053('i)001:12023: yi ge b+h+yo smug nag re re la /
NK053('i)001:12024: ru lu 'bru brgyad kyis bskor ba /
NK053('i)001:12025: phyogs phyogs nas nye gnas rnam pa bzhi'i tshul du
NK053('i)001:12026: shar ma lho sring nub grogs byang bran khas len
NK053('i)001:12027: cing / phrin las rnam pa bzhi zhi rgyas dbang drag la thogs pa med par mdzad pa /
NK053('i)001:12028: dur khrod chen po re re'i klong na /
NK053('i)001:12029: 'khor sprul pa dang yang sprul bsam gyis mi khyab pa dang ldan pas bskor bar bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:12030: ma mo 'di rnams sngon dpal chen pos dam la btags pa yin pas /
NK053('i)001:12031: da lta yang dkyil 'khor gang gi yang mtha' bskor du mi bsgom du mi rung ngo //
NK053('i)001:12032: dpal chen po yab yum la dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad kyis bskor ba rdzogs so //
NK053('i)001:12033: lnga pa khro bo bcu bskyed pa /
NK053('i)001:12034: de nas yab yum gyi mkha' gsang nas /
NK053('i)001:12035: yi ge h'u bcu ye shes kyi 'od zer dang bcas par 'phros te /
NK053('i)001:12036: thub pa drug sgo ba bzhi la thim pas /
NK053('i)001:12038: khro bo bcu'i snying po brjod pas /
NK053('i)001:12039: phyi rol du bskal pa'i me dpung gi klong du /
NK053('i)001:12040: ye shes kyi khro bo bcur bskyed de /
NK053('i)001:12041: phyogs skyong bcu'i gdan la bzhugs nas /
NK053('i)001:12042: mtshams dang bsrung ba'i las byed par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:12043: drug pa mgron gyi lha gzhan bskyod par /
NK053('i)001:12044: rnam pa gcig tu yab yum mkha' gsang nas /
NK053('i)001:12045: yi ge dza grangs med du 'phros pa las /
NK053('i)001:12046: thub pa drug gi spyi gtsug tu thim pa las /
NK053('i)001:12054: lang ka dur khrod kyi bdag po dang /
NK053('i)001:12057: pho nya mo drug cu rtsa bzhi /
NK053('i)001:12059: sa thob cing grub mthu brnyes pa'i rig 'dzin rnams su gyur te /
NK053('i)001:12060: dkyil 'khor gyi phyi nang kun tu rgyug cing las byed pa yin no //
NK053('i)001:12061: zhes khrag 'thung rol pa'i rgyud las bshad do //
NK053('i)001:12063: gnas ma bsgyur te sgo bzhir bzhugs te sgo srung ba'i las mdzad do //
NK053('i)001:12065: yang phur skyong ba'i srung ma ni /
NK053('i)001:12068: sa ma ya a ra li la sogs pa'i tshogs /
NK053('i)001:12069: 'khor dpag tu med pas kyang chas pas bskor te
NK053('i)001:12070: srid pa rlung yang mi shor bar gtams shing zur
NK053('i)001:12075: zhi ba las khro bor bsgyur ba /
NK053('i)001:12076: rtsa ba'i lha dpal chen yab yum /
NK053('i)001:12078: 'khor gyi lha ke sing sgo ma khro bcu dang /
NK053('i)001:12081: mgron gyi lha mkha' 'gro ging lang sogs pa la sogs pa /
NK053('i)001:12082: dus dang gnas skabs kyi man ngag gis phye ste /
NK053('i)001:12084: de la lha bskyed pa yang /
NK053('i)001:12085: bsnyen pa'i dus su zhi ba'i lha bskyed de /
NK053('i)001:12086: bsgrub pa la zhi khro sbrugs te gnas 'gyur gyi cho gar shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:12088: de la rdzogs 3pa'i rim pa bstan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:12089: dkyil gong nas mar blangs te /
NK053('i)001:12090: grub pas bstan pa'i lung bzhin du //
NK053('i)001:12091: sku mdog so sor gsal ba yi //
NK053('i)001:12092: phyag rgya rgyan dang cha lugs dag /
NK053('i)001:12093: bskyed rdzogs grub pa'i lha dag bsgom //
NK053('i)001:12095: de la bskyed pa'i rim pa zhi ba las /
NK053('i)001:12096: khro bor gnas bsgyur ba de yang /
NK053('i)001:12097: khungs dag pa gang yis gsungs na /
NK053('i)001:12098: lhun gyis grub pa'i sku ston pa dpal rdo rje sems dpas gsungs /
NK053('i)001:12100: lung man ngag gi sdud pa po /
NK053('i)001:12101: ston pa dga' rab rdo rje la gsungs /
NK053('i)001:12103: o rgyan gyi yul d+ha na ko sha'i gling du gsungs /
NK053('i)001:12104: bstan pa'i chos gang gsungs na /
NK053('i)001:12106: he ru ka'i gal po gsungs /
NK053('i)001:12108: phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gyi sa non par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:12109: mchog dang thun mong gis bsdus pa'i dngos grub thob par bya ba'i phyir mdzad /
NK053('i)001:12111: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' dang dpal chen po'i dngos grub mi gnyis par thob ste /
NK053('i)001:12112: thugs kyi rig pa las shar nas /
NK053('i)001:12113: man ngag gi sdeb byang du bsdebs pa 'di /
NK053('i)001:12114: sangs rgyas rnam par gzigs kyi sprul pa rdo rje bzhad pa la bstan /
NK053('i)001:12116: yang dag phur pa tshe sgrub dang gsum gyi dgongs pa grub /
NK053('i)001:12117: des rgyal po u ru sha ne dang /
NK053('i)001:12118: klu'i bu mo rgya mtsho ma la bstan /
NK053('i)001:12119: des rgyal po in+d+ra bo d+hi la bstan /
NK053('i)001:12120: des dge slong soka kya de ba dang /
NK053('i)001:12121: bal mo mang+ga la si ti la bstan /
NK053('i)001:12122: de gnyis kyis bal po h'u ka ra la bstan /
NK053('i)001:12123: slob dpon h'u ka ra ni shin tu yang dpal chen po'i dngos grub brnyes nas /
NK053('i)001:12124: yang dag grub pa'i rtsa ba man ngag gi sdeb byang yi ge la btab pa las /
NK053('i)001:12125: slob dpon pad+ma sam+b+ha was rdo rje bzhad pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12126: h'u ka ra dang gnyis char gyi zhal mthong zhing dbang bskur man ngag bstan pa las /
NK053('i)001:12127: slob dpon h'u ka ras mdzad pa'i dpe de /
NK053('i)001:12128: 'khrug che zhing ma tshang bar gzigs nas /
NK053('i)001:12129: mchims phu bre gu dge'u ru /
NK053('i)001:12130: rje byang chub sems dpa' khri srong lde'u btsan gyi don du /
NK053('i)001:12132: ma tshang ba'i kha bskangs nas /
NK053('i)001:12133: slob dpon h'u ka ra'i rtsa 'grel dang yang bstun nas /
NK053('i)001:12134: gnubs nam mkha'i snying pos lo ts+aa ba mdzad de /
NK053('i)001:12135: rje khro srong lde'u btsan dang /
NK053('i)001:12136: mkhar chen bza' mtsho rgyal la sogs pa la sgrub
NK053('i)001:12137: thabs kyi cho ga zab cing rgya che ba 'di
NK053('i)001:12138: bstan to // grub pas bstan pa'i lung bzhin du //
NK053('i)001:12140: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' nas /
NK053('i)001:12141: pad+ma sam+b+ha wa yan chad du brgyud pa'i lung /
NK053('i)001:12143: he ru ka'i gal po las ji skad bstan pa bzhin du /
NK053('i)001:12144: dpal khrag 'thung chen po'i dkyil 'khor gyi lha rgyud kyang /
NK053('i)001:12145: lha rnams kyi sku mdog so sor gsal ba dang /
NK053('i)001:12146: phyag mtshan so sor gsal ba yang /
NK053('i)001:12147: rgyud las gsal ba bzhin du bkod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12148: de'i phyag rgya yang bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:12149: gtso bo sku'i phyag rgya dang /
NK053('i)001:12150: gzungs ma dam tshig gi phyag rgya dang /
NK053('i)001:12151: gnyis su med pa'i byin rlabs las 'khor rgyas 'bring
NK053('i)001:12152: bskyed cing phrin las kyi bya ba rdzogs par bya
NK053('i)001:12153: ba ni las kyi phyag rgya dang /
NK053('i)001:12154: thugs kar bsgom pa dang bzlas brjod rnams chos kyi phyag rgya ste /
NK053('i)001:12156: ting 'dzin gsum po brtan byas shing //
NK053('i)001:12157: rtags kyi phyag rgya snga ma gsum bcings la //
NK053('i)001:12158: chos kyi phyag rgyar sems nyid bsgom //
NK053('i)001:12160: gzhan yang dur khrod kyi rgyan dang /
NK053('i)001:12162: rgyud las ji skad du grags pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12163: ston pa dga' rab rdo rje dang /
NK053('i)001:12164: slob dpon h'u ka ras grub pa thob cing zhal ji ltar gzigs pa bzhin du /
NK053('i)001:12165: 'dir man ngag du bkod nas bzhag pa la ni /
NK053('i)001:12166: sku mdog so sor gsal ba dag /
NK053('i)001:12167: phyag rgya rgyan dang cha lugs dag /
NK053('i)001:12169: bskyed rdzogs grub pa'i lha dag bsgom //
NK053('i)001:12171: bskyed dang rdzogs dang rdzogs pa chen po ste /
NK053('i)001:12172: de la bskyed pa ni ma h+aa yo ga ste /
NK053('i)001:12173: ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum gyi sgor zhugs nas /
NK053('i)001:12174: cho ga'i yan lag rdzogs par lha'i skur bskyed /
NK053('i)001:12175: yab yum gnyis su med par sbyor ba'i byang chub sems las /
NK053('i)001:12177: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing /
NK053('i)001:12179: bzlas pa mthar phyin par byas te /
NK053('i)001:12180: bdag gzhan gyi don mthar phyin par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:12181: ma h+aa yo ga zang ma'o //
NK053('i)001:12182: de'i lta ba yang rdzogs pa a nu yo gar bstan te /
NK053('i)001:12183: don dam par chos nyid kun tu bzang mo skye 'gags med pa'i klong las /
NK053('i)001:12184: so so'i snying po brjod pa tsam gyis /
NK053('i)001:12185: kun rdzob tu srid pa'i chos thams cad kun tu bzang po skye ba'i cho 'phrul /
NK053('i)001:12186: thabs kyi phyag rgya ye shes rol pa'i bye brag tu shar ba'o //
NK053('i)001:12187: de yang zag pa dang bcas pa'i rnam rtog gi
NK053('i)001:12188: rten dang bcas pa 'di zag pa med pa'i lhar
NK053('i)001:12190: kun gzhi'i rnam pa shes pa dpal he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:12191: de'i yul yum kro ti shwa ri ma'o //
NK053('i)001:12192: mig dang rna ba dang sna dang lce'i rnam par shes pa bzhi ni /
NK053('i)001:12196: be ta l+ai bzhi rang bzhin no //
NK053('i)001:12197: mig dang rna ba dang sna dang lce'i dbang po bzhi ni /
NK053('i)001:12202: mig dang rna ba dang sna dang lce bzhi'i yul bzhi ni /
NK053('i)001:12206: shwa na mu ka dang bzhi'o //
NK053('i)001:12208: kri ta la sogs pa bzhi'o //
NK053('i)001:12214: yid kyi rnam par shes pa ni /
NK053('i)001:12219: kun gzhi'i rnam shes yul dang bcas //
NK053('i)001:12220: rnam shes dbang po yul dus dang //
NK053('i)001:12221: dbang po rnam shes reg bya rnams //
NK053('i)001:12222: rdzogs pa'i phyag rgyar ye nas grol //
NK053('i)001:12224: grub pa'i zhes pa lung a nu yang /
NK053('i)001:12225: rdzogs pa chen po a ti yo ga ste /
NK053('i)001:12226: don dam pa kho na nyid de /
NK053('i)001:12227: chos nyid spros bral ye dag pa'i ngo bo mnyam pa nyid las /
NK053('i)001:12228: sku dang ye shes la sogs pa bskyed bsgyur bya mi dgos par shar te /
NK053('i)001:12229: dper na sprin med pa'i nam mkha' dwangs pa la /
NK053('i)001:12230: nyi zla dang gza' skar gyi tshogs /
NK053('i)001:12231: btsal ba med par rang bzhin gyis shar ba ltar /
NK053('i)001:12232: chos nyid dag par rang byung gi ye shes cir yang 'char ba'i ngo bo /
NK053('i)001:12233: gzung dka' ba la ched du byas pa'i kun btags dang bral ba la /
NK053('i)001:12234: dngos rang rig pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK053('i)001:12235: ye shes rol pa'i rang bzhin dkyil 'khor du rang bzhin gyis shar te /
NK053('i)001:12236: kun tu bzang po ye shes kyi rol par sangs rgyas nas /
NK053('i)001:12237: ye lhun gyis grub pa'i rang bzhin du gsal na /
NK053('i)001:12238: de kho na nyid lha dag par bsgom pa yin no //
NK053('i)001:12240: don dam spros med byang chub snying po ni //
NK053('i)001:12241: mnyam nyid mi g.yo chos dbyings nam mkha' che //
NK053('i)001:12242: rang byung ye shes btsal med gnas pa med //
NK053('i)001:12243: gzhi rtsa med pa'i sems nyid de ltar snang //
NK053('i)001:12245: de ltar rtogs pa'i dus na spyan drangs shing mchod du yang med la /
NK053('i)001:12246: spyan drangs shing mchod na yang de nas spyan drangs shing mchod do //
NK053('i)001:12247: zhes grub pa thod pa'i gu ru gong ma rnams gsungs so /
NK053('i)001:12249: 2 / de la spyan drangs shing mchod pa'i phrin las gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:12250: ye shes dkyil 'khor spyan drangs te //
NK053('i)001:12251: bzhugs dang brtan dang mi g.yo dang //
NK053('i)001:12252: dam tshig zil gnon phyag byed dang //
NK053('i)001:12253: mchod dang bstab dang bza' ba dag /
NK053('i)001:12254: tshul rig goms pa'i blo dag gis //
NK053('i)001:12255: ci rigs su ni brtag par bya //
NK053('i)001:12258: skabs sbyor bcu bzhi pa ye shes kyi he ru
NK053('i)001:12259: ka spyan drangs shing mchod pa'i cho ga bstan pa'i
NK053('i)001:12260: skabs / mtha' drug las la dor ba spyod pa'am ting nge 'dzin /
NK053('i)001:12261: dkyil 'khor la brgyad pa thugs rje phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK053('i)001:12263: lung dgu las brgyad pa mdzad pa phrin las kyi lung ngo //
NK053('i)001:12265: don dam par chos sku'i rang bzhin dang /
NK053('i)001:12266: de bzhin gshegs pa'i ye shes kyis /
NK053('i)001:12267: thams cad kun la khyab pa'i rang bzhin du gnas pas /
NK053('i)001:12270: spyan drangs par mi dmigs na yang /
NK053('i)001:12271: ye shes lha la dbang mi bza' bar /
NK053('i)001:12273: dag pa'i zhing la tshogs rnam pa gnyis bsags pa'i sa bon gdab pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:12274: rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i dkyil 'khor spyan drangs
NK053('i)001:12275: shing mchod pa'i phrin las bstan pa la don drug
NK053('i)001:12276: ste / spyan drangs pa'i rim pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12277: mi g.yo bar bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK053('i)001:12278: thugs dam las mi 'da' bar bskul ba dang /
NK053('i)001:12281: mchod pa'i rim pa bstan to /
NK053('i)001:12283: 1 / de la spyan drangs pa'i rim pa la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:12284: dbyings las ye shes kyi skur bzhengs te snyan gsan dbab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12285: ye shes kyi sku de 'khor sprul pa dang bcas te spyan drangs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12286: lha byin dbab cing gnas par byas pa la gzi byin bskyed pa'o //
NK053('i)001:12287: de la 1 dbyings las ye shes kyi sku bzhengs te snyan gsan dbab pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:12290: dper na rgyal po gcig spyan 'dren pa la /
NK053('i)001:12291: sngon la snyam gsan 'bebs pa'i tshul du /
NK053('i)001:12293: phyag rgya dpung mgor se gol bsnol mar brdab cing /
NK053('i)001:12294: badz+ra sa ma na dzah zhes brjod pas /
NK053('i)001:12295: rang nyid kyi thugs ka dang gsang ba'i mkha' las /
NK053('i)001:12296: bskul ba'i 'od zer gsum byung ste /
NK053('i)001:12297: gcig gis chos kyi dbyings skye ba med pa las /
NK053('i)001:12298: ye shes kyi spyod yul gzugs kyi skur rong gis bzhengs pa bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:12299: gcig gis phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyis mchod pa phul /
NK053('i)001:12300: gcig las sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub nod pa'i sgra byung nas /
NK053('i)001:12301: chos nyid ye shes kyi thugs rje nyer bsdogs su rong nger gnas pa la /
NK053('i)001:12303: de yang tshig dang sngags su bcas pa ni /
NK053('i)001:12304: he ru ka'i gal po las 'di skad gsungs so //
NK053('i)001:12305: 'dir re re la yang bzhi bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:12311: gnas gang nas spyan drangs na /
NK053('i)001:12312: ye shes can gyi spyod yul nas //
NK053('i)001:12314: sems can don slad dam tshig dgongs //
NK053('i)001:12315: gnas 'dir ma lus gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:12318: mkha' dbyings kyi phyag rgya zhes kyang bya /
NK053('i)001:12319: thod phreng gi phya rgya zhes kyang bya ste /
NK053('i)001:12321: mdzub mo gnyis ni mdud par bcings //
NK053('i)001:12322: mthe bong gung mo rtse sprad brgyang //
NK053('i)001:12323: lhag ma bzhi yang 'od bzhin brkyang //
NK053('i)001:12324: dpral bar bzhag byas thod phreng rgya //
NK053('i)001:12325: zhes gsungs pa bzhin byas la /
NK053('i)001:12327: dzahmh'u bam hoh phyag rgya bzhi /
NK053('i)001:12328: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:12329: dpal rdo rje khrag 'thung chen po /
NK053('i)001:12347: rdo rje bka' nyan dbang bsdud /
NK053('i)001:12355: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:12356: dpal rdo rje khrag 'thung chen po /
NK053('i)001:12366: ye shes kyi spyod yul nas /
NK053('i)001:12367: dpal khrag 'thung chen po 'khor dang bcas pa sems can rnal 'byor pa bdag gi don du /
NK053('i)001:12368: gnas 'dir gshegs shig par snyan gsan dbab par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:12369: ye shes 2kyi sku de 'khor sprul pa dang bcas
NK053('i)001:12370: par spyan drangs par bstan pa gang snyam pa la
NK053('i)001:12373: ye shes sprul pa'i sku 'khor dang bcas pa mdun gyi nam mkha' la bzhugs nas /
NK053('i)001:12374: snyan gsan phab pa de rings par yang gshegs shig par gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:12376: bdag cag sems can gyi dad pa dang ni bde gshegs thugs rje'i dam tshig gis //
NK053('i)001:12377: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:12378: chos sku zhi ba'i ngang las kyang //
NK053('i)001:12379: gzugs sku 'jigs tshul bstan du gsol //
NK053('i)001:12380: thugs rje che la thabs mkhas pa //
NK053('i)001:12381: gdug pa 'dul phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:12382: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal dang ldan //
NK053('i)001:12383: tshogs kyi slob dpon gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:12384: ye shes rtogs pa'i khyad par las //
NK053('i)001:12385: sprul pa mang po'i tshogs dang gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:12386: e h+ye hi kye tshur spyon b+ha ga wan bcom ldan 'das /
NK053('i)001:12387: dzahmh'u bam hoh ru lu ru lu dpal chen po'i
NK053('i)001:12388: skur snang dri sh+ya hoh sa ma ya hoh sa
NK053('i)001:12389: ma ya s+t+wam / dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru
NK053('i)001:12390: ka dpal khrag 'thung e ha hi tri sha hoh
NK053('i)001:12391: ma ya s+t+wam / kye tshur spyon / sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:12392: e ar li drag po rnyog pa med hring hring hring /
NK053('i)001:12395: de nas thal mo lan gsum du brdab pas /
NK053('i)001:12396: dpal khrag 'thung chen po 'khor dang bcas pa phyag
NK053('i)001:12397: rgya rnam pa bzhis lha spyan drangs te myur bar
NK053('i)001:12398: gshegs shing / bdag gi rig pa las bskyed pa'i gzhal yas khang gi nang du /
NK053('i)001:12399: thogs pa med par sil gyis byon te /
NK053('i)001:12401: 'od phung gnyis 'dab 'dres tsam du bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:12402: byin dbab 3cing gnas par byas la gzi byin bskyed pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:12403: byon nas bzhugs su gsol ba'i tshul /
NK053('i)001:12406: gyer tshig bde gshegs pho brang dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK053('i)001:12407: 'gro ba ma lus bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:12408: don gyi dbang du dgongs nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:12410: zhes bskul nas lag pa gnyis khu tshur bcangs te mdzub mo so sor bsgreng nas /
NK053('i)001:12415: sarba dush+tana sa ma ya mu tra pra ban tsakra k+sha ka ya h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:12417: sgrib pa dral ste sgo phye nas /
NK053('i)001:12418: mkha' dbyings kyi phyag rgya smin mtshams su bcings te sngags 'di brjod do //
NK053('i)001:12419: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tana /
NK053('i)001:12420: sa ma ya mu tra bra be sha phata /
NK053('i)001:12423: dzahmh'u bam hoh badz+ra ki'u ri ha /
NK053('i)001:12425: badz+ra seng ha mu ka he /
NK053('i)001:12427: badz+ra ar+ya te dza te nga dza /
NK053('i)001:12430: zhes sogs sngags tshang bar brjod pas /
NK053('i)001:12431: ye shes kyi he ru ka 'khor dang bcas pa /
NK053('i)001:12432: dam tshig gi he ru ka 'khor dang bcas pa la /
NK053('i)001:12433: bye ma la mar thim pa'am /
NK053('i)001:12434: ba mo la kha ba babs pa bzhin du bzhugs shing thim nas /
NK053('i)001:12435: gnas shing gzi byin dang ldan par bsgom mo /
NK053('i)001:12437: 2 / de nas mi g.yo bar bzhugs su gsol ba la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:12438: brtan par bzhugs su gsol ba dang /
NK053('i)001:12439: gdug pa can bza' ba'i lung ngo //
NK053('i)001:12440: de la brtan 1par bzhugs su gsol ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:12441: bzhugs nas kyang 'di ma tshar gyi bar du brtan par bzhugs dgos bya ba lta bus /
NK053('i)001:12446: sems can don phyir nan tan mchog bskyed cing //
NK053('i)001:12447: ye shes thugs rjes bdag la dgongs nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:12448: la dang bdag mi gnyis don du dngos grub mchog gi gnas //
NK053('i)001:12449: bdag la stsol zhing brtan par bzhugs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:12451: phyag rgya sor mo snying khar bsnol te /
NK053('i)001:12452: mthe bong so sor bsgrengs la sngags 'di brjod do //
NK053('i)001:12453: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sa ma ya hi /
NK053('i)001:12454: sarba dusata&a&a&ana sa ma ya mu tra pra ban tsakra h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:12455: k+aa ya waka tsit+ta tish+tha badz+ra /
NK053('i)001:12457: sgrub pa po nam dngos grub ma thob kyi bar du /
NK053('i)001:12458: so so'i go go gnas gnas su bzhugs par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:12459: de la 2gdug pa can bza' ba'i lung gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:12460: brtan par bzhugs pa la bza' btung 'dren pa'i tshul lo //
NK053('i)001:12464: gyer tshig che mchog mnyam sbyor 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK053('i)001:12465: gdug pa 'dul mdzad khro rgyal skur sprul zhing //
NK053('i)001:12466: gsang sngags rmad byung phrin las dgongs par mdzod //
NK053('i)001:12467: mnyam pa nyid du byin gyis brlab tu gsol //
NK053('i)001:12469: de yang ye shes kyi he ru ka rol pa
NK053('i)001:12470: chen po'i phrin las lhun gyis grub par mdzad pa'i
NK053('i)001:12472: rdo rje khur tshur g.yas g.yon gyi mthe bong che ba'i steng du bzhag la /
NK053('i)001:12473: mathe'u gnyis bsgrengs te sngags 'di brjod do //
NK053('i)001:12474: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tana /
NK053('i)001:12476: a pa stam pa ya h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:12478: bar du gcod cing mi mthun pa'i phyogs zhal du gsol bar bsgom mo /
NK053('i)001:12480: 3 / de nas thugs dam las mi 'da' bar bskul ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:12483: bza' btung drangs nas bya ba 'di 'dra ba zhig byed par zhu ba'i tshul lo //
NK053('i)001:12485: gyer tshig dam tshig pa la bzhengs pa yi //
NK053('i)001:12487: dam tshig tshul bzhin mi gshegs sam //
NK053('i)001:12488: grub pa'i mchog rnams ma stsal na //
NK053('i)001:12489: sku gsung thugs dang 'gal bar gyur //
NK053('i)001:12491: lha ye shes sems dpa' dam tshig las mi 'da' zhing /
NK053('i)001:12492: sgrub pa po la dngos grub stsol bar mdzad pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:12493: dam tshig mchog gi phyag rgya /
NK053('i)001:12495: thod rlon rgya sor mo nang du bsnol /
NK053('i)001:12496: mthe bong mdzub mo'i rtse bkug la sprad /
NK053('i)001:12497: gung mo gnyis te srin lag dang mdzub mo'i nang nas phyung ba'o //
NK053('i)001:12498: thod skam ni sor mo mgo bsdus te rtse sprad mthe bong dang mdzub mo rtse sprad pa bcangs /
NK053('i)001:12500: dang gsum gyi phyag rgya rim par bcings shing /
NK053('i)001:12501: badz+ra gu h+ye tri sha gsang ba dgyes /
NK053('i)001:12504: dam tshig gi dus la babs /
NK053('i)001:12505: badz+ra gu h+ya tri sha sa ma ya hoh badz+ra gu h+ya tri sha sa ma ya phata /
NK053('i)001:12507: dam bdar bas ye shes kyi lha dpal khrag 'thung chen po 'khor dang bcas pa /
NK053('i)001:12509: thugs dam gyi dbang gis gshegs te /
NK053('i)001:12510: sgrub pa po la ci 'dod pa'i dngos grub stsol bar bsgom mo /
NK053('i)001:12512: 4 / de nas zil gyis gnan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:12515: des kyang zhus pa'i bya ba byed tshul lo //
NK053('i)001:12517: gyer tshig sku gsung thugs su bdag sbyor bas //
NK053('i)001:12518: pho brang dkyil 'khor rang las sprul //
NK053('i)001:12519: nga ni bdud kyi bdud bdag ste //
NK053('i)001:12520: mkha' 'gro'i tshogs bcas ngas bsdus pa'o //
NK053('i)001:12522: de yang dpal chen po'i 'khor dbang phyug ma la sogs pa /
NK053('i)001:12523: gdug pa can mang po zil gyis gnon cing dbang du bsdu ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:12524: zil gyis gnon pa'i phyag rgya bstan te /
NK053('i)001:12525: mthe bong gnyis lto sbyar nas /
NK053('i)001:12526: sor mo'i dpung mgo g.yas g.yon du bsnol te sngags 'di brjod do //
NK053('i)001:12527: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+t+aana sa ma ya mu tra /
NK053('i)001:12529: bdud dpung rab tu 'joms pa'i 'khor lo /
NK053('i)001:12531: gshog pa rab tu gshog ba /
NK053('i)001:12532: byi tang ba ya byi tang pa ya /
NK053('i)001:12539: tra ti shamata&a&a&a zil gyis gnon pa /
NK053('i)001:12541: ye shes kyi gshog pa las ye shes kyi 'od dang 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:12542: 'khor rnams zil gyis gnon cing dbang du 'dus par bsgom mo /
NK053('i)001:12544: 5 / de nas phyag bya ba gang snyam pa /
NK053('i)001:12547: bya ba byas pa la mgu nas phyag bya ba'i tshul lo //
NK053('i)001:12548: de yang phyag bya ba la yang gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:12549: gdul bya gnyen po'i phyag dang /
NK053('i)001:12550: rtog pa don gyi phyag go //
NK053('i)001:12551: de la 1gdul bya gnyen po'i phyag ni /
NK053('i)001:12552: gsang ba'i yum bzhi'i dgongs pa dang ldan pa ste /
NK053('i)001:12554: gyer tshig bde ba rgyas 'debs yab yum phyag rgyar gsal //
NK053('i)001:12555: bde ba'i rmongs byed gnyis su med pa'i ngang //
NK053('i)001:12556: bde ba za byed phrin las sna tshogs sgrol //
NK053('i)001:12557: bde ba tshe 'phel skye shi med pa'i don //
NK053('i)001:12559: bde ba rgyas 'debs ma'i phyag rgya /
NK053('i)001:12560: mda' gzhu 'gengs pa'i tshul du byas la /
NK053('i)001:12562: sh+r+ai badz+ra ka ra mu ka sha ra ya ya na ma /
NK053('i)001:12563: dpal gyi lha mo mda' gzhu 'gengs ma mi gtong ba'i yum de la phyag bya'o //
NK053('i)001:12565: chos kyi dbyings nas bskul bas bzhengs te /
NK053('i)001:12566: dpal chen po yab yum gyi sku phyag rgya shin tu gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:12567: bde ba rmongs byed ma'i phyag rgya /
NK053('i)001:12568: thal mo dpung pa g.yas g.yon du bsnol ma la /
NK053('i)001:12570: sh+r+ai badz+ra r+aa ga sa ma ya ya na ma /
NK053('i)001:12571: dpal gyi lha mo chags pa thugs rjes mi gtong ba'i yum la phyag bya zhes bya /
NK053('i)001:12573: dpal chen po yab yum gnyis su med par sbyor ba mdzad bde ba la snyoms par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:12574: de nas bde ba za byed ma'i phyag rgya /
NK053('i)001:12575: lag pa g.yas pa'i mthe bong gis srin lag mnan te sor mo gzhan brkyang la /
NK053('i)001:12576: lag pa g.yon pas gru mo nas bzung la 'phyar te /
NK053('i)001:12578: sh+ri badz+ra kha t+wo ra pra tsa la ya ya na ma /
NK053('i)001:12579: dpal rdo rje kha gdong bdud bzhi 'dul bas mi gtong ba'i yum la phyag bya zhes bya /
NK053('i)001:12581: yab yum sbyor ba mdzad pa'i byang chub sems las 'od zer phyogs bcu 'phros /
NK053('i)001:12582: dregs pa can ril bsgral te slar dran pa rnyed nas kun bred cing dngangs /
NK053('i)001:12583: zil gyis gnon te spa bkod nas /
NK053('i)001:12584: 'dar lcug 'bangs su mchi zhing phyag 'tshal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:12585: de nas bde ba tshe 'phel ma'i phyag rgya /
NK053('i)001:12586: dril bu'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK053('i)001:12588: sh+r+ai badz+ra gan d+he dz+wa la ya ya na ma /
NK053('i)001:12589: gsung rab rgya mtsho sgrogs pa mi gtong yum zhes bya ste de la phyag 'tshal ba'o //
NK053('i)001:12591: dregs pa can bsgral ba'i rnam par shes pa dang
NK053('i)001:12592: 'od zer dang bcas pa slar yum gyi mkhar bsdus
NK053('i)001:12593: te / de nyid yi ge h'u du gyur pa las /
NK053('i)001:12595: ye shes sems dpa' sku tshon gang ba zhig tu gyur par bsam la /
NK053('i)001:12596: des dam pa'i chos gsung rab rgya mtsho snyed 'chad
NK053('i)001:12597: cing sgrog pas sems can gyi don mdzad pa'i rtags
NK053('i)001:12598: su dril bu bsnams par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:12599: de la rtogs pa don gyi phyag ni /
NK053('i)001:12600: bdag dang dpal chen po 'khor dang bcas pa gnyis
NK053('i)001:12601: su med par rtogs par byas te phyag 'tshal ba
NK053('i)001:12602: yang / rgyud las 'di skad du 'byung ste /
NK053('i)001:12604: bdag med phyogs bral don dam thugs chud cing //
NK053('i)001:12605: byams dang snying rje dgra zin mi mnga' yang //
NK053('i)001:12606: gdug pa 'dul phyir dus la mi 'da' ba'i //
NK053('i)001:12607: 'jigs byed he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:12608: khro mo dbang phyug sku la nyer gnas shing //
NK053('i)001:12609: thabs dag shes rab 'brel ba'i dkyil 'khor nas //
NK053('i)001:12610: mkha' 'gro mi bzad 'bar ba'i sprin 'phro ba //
NK053('i)001:12611: gdug pa 'dul mdzad yum la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:12612: nam mkha'i lus can gar yang thogs med cing //
NK053('i)001:12613: 'dod dgur bsgyur ba'i gzugs can 'phrul mo che //
NK053('i)001:12614: ma sring byams ma'i tshul du grogs mdzad ma //
NK053('i)001:12615: phyi nang mkha' 'gro'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:12616: phyogs bcu sprul pa'i zhing khams na //
NK053('i)001:12617: mnyam nyid gnas pa de bzhin gshegs //
NK053('i)001:12618: rnal 'byor chen por mtshan grags pa //
NK053('i)001:12620: a ti pu hoh sarba ta th+aa ga ta b+ha na d+ha na ma kha ro ya mi /
NK053('i)001:12621: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad la mgo bos phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:12623: shin tu dgyes pa chen po /
NK053('i)001:12624: a ti pu hoh pra ti b+hu hoh zhes brjod pas /
NK053('i)001:12625: rnal 'byor pa'i lus ngag yid gsum dang /
NK053('i)001:12626: dpal chen po 'khor dang bcas pa'i sku gsung thugs
NK053('i)001:12627: mnyam zhing dbyer med pa'i rtogs nas bsgom pa de
NK053('i)001:12628: kho na nyid phyag 'tshal ba yin no /
NK053('i)001:12630: 6 / de nas mchod pa'i rim pa bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:12633: zas nor 'di tsho yang 'bul zer ba'i tshul du /
NK053('i)001:12635: phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12636: kun tu bzang po dbyer med pa'i mchod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12637: phyi nang gi mchod pa rnam pa bdun dang /
NK053('i)001:12638: bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12640: bdud rtsis kun mnyes shing khyab par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:12643: de la 1phyag rgya gar gyi mchod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:12644: snang ba gzugs mdzes kyi mchod pa zhes kyang bya ste /
NK053('i)001:12645: rnal 'byor pa kun gyis lag pa so sos gar bsgyur /
NK053('i)001:12646: rkang pa so sos stabs brdungs pas /
NK053('i)001:12647: rnal 'byor pa kun gyis lus zhing gi rdul snyed du sprul /
NK053('i)001:12648: de dag thams cad kyang lha dang lha mor gyur pas /
NK053('i)001:12649: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten gyi khams khengs par bsgom la /
NK053('i)001:12650: ye shes rol pa'i gar dbul te /
NK053('i)001:12652: gar gyi rgyu dang gar gyi gnas //
NK053('i)001:12653: gar gyi bsgyur thabs yon tan bzhi //
NK053('i)001:12654: rdo rje khu tshur gar gyi rgyu //
NK053('i)001:12655: gar gyi gnas ni mkhal khung ste /
NK053('i)001:12656: gar bsgyur thabs ni rnam pa gsum //
NK053('i)001:12657: g.yas su bsgyur dang g.yon du bsgyur //
NK053('i)001:12658: de bzhin phyogs bcur gar bsgyur ro //
NK053('i)001:12659: gar gyi yon tan sprul pa 'byung //
NK053('i)001:12660: phyogs bcur bder gshegs thams cad kyang //
NK053('i)001:12661: chos nyid kyi don la mi 'da' bas dang po dam tshig gar lags te //
NK053('i)001:12662: nam mkha' kun kyang gar gyis khengs //
NK053('i)001:12663: da lta dam tshig gar lags te //
NK053('i)001:12664: sa gzhi kun kyang gar gyis khengs //
NK053('i)001:12665: gar mkhan tshul du sangs rgyas shing //
NK053('i)001:12666: gsang gnas bde ba'i mchog ster mdzad //
NK053('i)001:12667: ngo mtshar che ba'i lha tshogs la //
NK053('i)001:12668: rnam pa grol ba mtshon pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:12669: dpal chen khrag 'thung phyag rgya ni //
NK053('i)001:12671: phyag drug ye shes drug zhabs bzhir bsgrad /
NK053('i)001:12673: g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal //
NK053('i)001:12674: rdo rje kha t+w+aam rnge'u chung g.yas //
NK053('i)001:12675: dung dmar rgyu zhags khyung khra g.yon //
NK053('i)001:12676: dpal chen ye shes thabs kyi rgya //
NK053('i)001:12677: shes rab dbyings ma'i phyag rgya ni //
NK053('i)001:12678: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku dmog mthing //
NK053('i)001:12679: g.yas pas shes rab thabs la brten //
NK053('i)001:12680: g.yon pas dung dmar gtso la stob //
NK053('i)001:12681: kro ti shwa ri dbyings kyi rgya //
NK053('i)001:12682: dpal chen khrag 'thung yab yum la //
NK053('i)001:12683: 'bar ba'i gdan las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:12685: chos nyid dag pa dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK053('i)001:12686: ko'u r+ai b+han dmar zhing dbyug sngo //
NK053('i)001:12687: tse'u r+ai mda' gzhu 'gengs ma ser //
NK053('i)001:12688: pra mo chu srin rgyal mtshan dmar //
NK053('i)001:12689: be ta byis za rdor 'phyar gnag /
NK053('i)001:12690: pus ka dmar ser byis rgyu 'dren //
NK053('i)001:12692: sma sha mthing nag byis snying za //
NK053('i)001:12694: ko'u r+ai khro mo brgyad rnams kyang //
NK053('i)001:12695: 'bar ba'i gdan las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:12697: chos nyid dag pa dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK053('i)001:12698: sid+ha kha ro bsnol ser seng //
NK053('i)001:12699: mgo b+y+aa kri gnas blta bsnol dmar stag /
NK053('i)001:12700: sri la snying bldag dmar nag wa //
NK053('i)001:12701: shwa na 'dral blta mthing ka spyang //
NK053('i)001:12702: kri ta gri dmar rgyu 'dren rgod //
NK053('i)001:12703: kang ka zhing phrag snar mchu ring /
NK053('i)001:12704: khwa khwa khar ro b+han gri gnag /
NK053('i)001:12705: hu lu mthing tshogs rdor kyu 'ug /
NK053('i)001:12706: phra men chen mo brgyad rnams kyang //
NK053('i)001:12707: 'bar ba'i gdan gar dbyangs chos nyid dag pa rta gdong dkar mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK053('i)001:12708: phag gdong sngon mo mche zhags bsnams //
NK053('i)001:12709: seng gdong spyan gsum lcags sgrog nyi zla dmar //
NK053('i)001:12710: thal byed ljang khu spyang ki'i mgo dril 'khol dgyes //
NK053('i)001:12711: ye shes sgo ma bzhi rnams kyang //
NK053('i)001:12712: 'bar ba'i gar dbyangs chos nyid dag srin mo smug nag thod rlon 'chang //
NK053('i)001:12713: tshangs ma dmar ser pad+ma bsnams //
