NK053('i)001:12714: lha chen dkar ljang tri shu la //
NK053('i)001:12716: gzhon nu dmar mo mdung thung 'phen //
NK053('i)001:12717: brgya byin dkar mo in+d+ra gdengs //
NK053('i)001:12718: shar gyi sgo ma rdo rje nag mo lcags kyu 'dzin //
NK053('i)001:12720: bdud rtsi dmar mo pad+ma bsnams //
NK053('i)001:12721: zla ba dkar mo pun d+ha ri //
NK053('i)001:12722: be con ljang nag thod dbyug 'phyar //
NK053('i)001:12723: srin mo dmar ser thod khrag 'thung //
NK053('i)001:12724: za ba ljang nag ba su 'dren //
NK053('i)001:12725: lho sgo ma rdo rje ser mo ra mgo zhags //
NK053('i)001:12726: dga' ba dmar mo ka tar 'chang //
NK053('i)001:12727: stobs chen dkar mo gshol 'dzin ma //
NK053('i)001:12728: gcig spyod dmar ser spu gri g.yon //
NK053('i)001:12730: nor srung dkar mo bum pa 'dzin //
NK053('i)001:12731: rlung lha sngon mo ba dan 'phyar //
NK053('i)001:12732: nub sgom rdo rje dmar mo lcags sgrog bsdams //
NK053('i)001:12733: gsod byed dmar nag ral gri 'dzin //
NK053('i)001:12734: me mo dmar mo gsal shing 'chang //
NK053('i)001:12735: phag mo nag mo mche zhags thogs //
NK053('i)001:12736: rgan byed dmar nag zhing chung za //
NK053('i)001:12737: sna chen ljang nag thod khrag 'thung //
NK053('i)001:12738: chu lha sngon mo sbrul zhags 'dzin //
NK053('i)001:12739: byang sgo ma rdo rje ljang nag dril 'khrol dgyes //
NK053('i)001:12740: dbang phyug chen mo nyi shu brgyad //
NK053('i)001:12741: bsam pa mya ngan 'das gyur kyang //
NK053('i)001:12742: 'jog rtog pa yi tshul ston pa //
NK053('i)001:12743: zhing skam dar rlod steng la bzhengs //
NK053('i)001:12745: mchod bzhes dam bskang mthu dang dngos grub stsol //
NK053('i)001:12746: ces he ru ka'i gal po las gsungs so //
NK053('i)001:12747: de nas 2kun tu bzang po'i mchod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12749: gong du zhi ba'i skabs su bstan pa bzhin du 'dir yang shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:12750: de la 4bdud rtsi sman gyi mchod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:12751: sna tshogs ro ldan gyi mchod pa zhes kyang bya ste /
NK053('i)001:12752: de'i don zhi ba'i skabs su bstan pa bzhin shes par byas nas /
NK053('i)001:12755: bdud rtsi la yon tan brjod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12756: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la mchod pa dbul ba dang /
NK053('i)001:12757: bdag nyid dngos grub blangs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12758: kun la khyab par mchod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12763: rnal 'byor ba ji lta bus mchod pa'i bye brag shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:12765: de la bdud rtsi la yon tan brjod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:12766: bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga rang byung gdong nas dag
NK053('i)001:12767: pa yin pas mi gtsang bar mi blta ba yi
NK053('i)001:12768: // rtsa brgyad stong las sbyor ba'i sman /
NK053('i)001:12770: sbas pa phyi'i rtsa ba bzhi /
NK053('i)001:12771: mngon pa nang gi rtsa ba bzhi ste brgyad /
NK053('i)001:12772: de'i phrag tu yan lag stong du sbyor tshul gzhan du shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:12773: rigs lnga dam tshig lnga yi dngos //
NK053('i)001:12774: rdo rje sems dpa'i dam tshig byang sems /
NK053('i)001:12778: dri chu don grub kyi bdud rtsi dam tshig go //
NK053('i)001:12779: ye shes lnga rdzogs grub pa'i rdzas //
NK053('i)001:12780: dri chen la chos dbyings ye shes rdzogs pas rnam snang gi sgrub rdzas yin /
NK053('i)001:12781: byang sems me long ye shes //
NK053('i)001:12784: dri chu bya grub ye shes so //
NK053('i)001:12785: rgyu drug sems can kun sgrol phyir //
NK053('i)001:12786: dri chen gyis gti mug byol song sgrol /
NK053('i)001:12787: byang sems kyis zhe sdang dmyal ba sgrol /
NK053('i)001:12788: sha chen gyis ser sna yi dwags /
NK053('i)001:12791: de'i ris gtogs phrag dog lha min no //
NK053('i)001:12792: dug lnga sel ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK053('i)001:12793: zhes dri chen gyis gti mug chos dbyings ye shes su sel /
NK053('i)001:12794: byang sems kyis zhe sdang me long ye shes su sel /
NK053('i)001:12795: sha chen gyis nga rgyal mnyam nyid ye shes su sel /
NK053('i)001:12796: rak+tasa 'dod chags sor rtog ye shes su sel /
NK053('i)001:12797: dri chus phrag dog bya grub ye shes su sel /
NK053('i)001:12800: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la mchod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:12801: dpal chen rigs lnga khrag 'thung yab yum dang //
NK053('i)001:12802: ke'u seng sgo ma dbang phyug 'khor bcas la //
NK053('i)001:12803: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas dgyes mchod 'bul //
NK053('i)001:12804: thugs rjes bzhes te kun tu dgyes mdzod la //
NK053('i)001:12805: tshangs pa 'phrul gyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:12806: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ar+g+ham pra ti dza hoh zhes rgyud las gsungs so //
NK053('i)001:12808: tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal chen he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:12809: 'bar ba'i rgyal po khrag 'thung yab rnams la //
NK053('i)001:12810: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK053('i)001:12811: dgyes nas thugs rjes dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK053('i)001:12812: dpal chen sku la gnyis med lhun sbyor ba //
NK053('i)001:12813: kro ti shwa ri rigs kyi yum rnams la //
NK053('i)001:12814: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK053('i)001:12815: dgyes nas thugs rjes dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK053('i)001:12816: h'u kha ram kha ram kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK053('i)001:12817: zhes rtsa ba'i sngags kyis mchod par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:12818: mthing ka mchog bsnams rdo rje gsang ba'i yum //
NK053('i)001:12819: ke'u ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams la //
NK053('i)001:12820: rnam dag dgyes nas h'u kha ram kha ram kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK053('i)001:12821: sna tshogs mgo brnyan za byed mche gshog can //
NK053('i)001:12822: sid+ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams la //
NK053('i)001:12823: rnam dag dgyes nas h'u kha ram sgo bzhir rab rngams rdo rje sring 'gro ma //
NK053('i)001:12824: gdong mo 'jig rten ro langs tshogs rnams la //
NK053('i)001:12825: rnam dag dgyes nas h'u kha ram dpal chen 'khor tshogs badz+ra a ra li //
NK053('i)001:12826: mi srin la sogs dbang phyug tshogs rnams la //
NK053('i)001:12827: rnam dag dgyes nas h+aum kha ram gzhan yang kha ram zhes pas drangs te /
NK053('i)001:12834: srung ma bzhi dang kun dpal chen po'i 'khor yin pas mchod do //
NK053('i)001:12835: gzhan yang rigs 'dzin la sogs pa bdud rtsi thob pa kun la mchod pa bya'o //
NK053('i)001:12837: de nas bdag nyid dngos grub blang ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:12838: ltar dkar la 'tsher ba'i 'od zer dang //
NK053('i)001:12839: +aahltara dmar la dwangs pa'i yon tan gsal //
NK053('i)001:12840: h'u ltar snum la 'dril ba'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK053('i)001:12841: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:12844: wa ka sid+d+hi +aah tsit+ta sid+d+hi h'u /
NK053('i)001:12845: gong gi zhi ba bzhin no //
NK053('i)001:12847: de nas kun la khyab par mchod pa zhi ba dang mthun no //
NK053('i)001:12851: rmad du byung ba'i gtor ma dang //
NK053('i)001:12852: 'dod pa'i yon tan rnam lnga po //
NK053('i)001:12853: chos nyid skye ba med dbyings nas //
NK053('i)001:12854: ji ltar dmigs pa bzhin du 'bul //
NK053('i)001:12855: sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra sarba dush+tana sa ma ya mu tra /
NK053('i)001:12856: a la sha u li chang /
NK053('i)001:12858: ta pa ti chan khur ba tshod ma shing thog sogs /
NK053('i)001:12863: kha ram yo ga ni kha hi ho /
NK053('i)001:12864: rigs lnga khrag 'thung yab yum bcu /
NK053('i)001:12867: koo seng sgo ma dbang phyug ma /
NK053('i)001:12869: de nas mchod pa bstab pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:12872: mchod pa de dag bar ma dor chud mi za zhing /
NK053('i)001:12873: yang nas yang du zhal du stob pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:12874: rdo rje gar gyi phyag rgya las /
NK053('i)001:12875: dung chen po'i phyag rgyar byas te /
NK053('i)001:12878: he ru ka yi gnas bcu dang /
NK053('i)001:12883: srin po'i skad du yul ni ro langs /
NK053('i)001:12884: dri za'i skad du nye yul rol /
NK053('i)001:12885: grul bum skad du zhing dang /
NK053('i)001:12886: gnod sbyin skad du nye ba'i zhing /
NK053('i)001:12888: gshin rje'i skad du nye ba'i 'dus dang /
NK053('i)001:12890: lto 'phye'i skad du nye ba'i tshan+d+ho'o //
NK053('i)001:12891: dur khrod chen po'i gnas brgyad nas //
NK053('i)001:12892: zhes gong ltar dpal chen khrag 'thung spyan drangs te //
NK053('i)001:12893: dur khrod chen po'i gnas 'di ru //
NK053('i)001:12894: zhing chen gsar rnying ti rar bcas //
NK053('i)001:12895: dam gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK053('i)001:12897: ma lus gshegs nas mnabs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:12898: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:12906: sh+r+ai ban kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK053('i)001:12907: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:12917: pra ti dza hoh mchod par dgyes /
NK053('i)001:12918: sh+ri ban kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK053('i)001:12921: mchod pa ril dpal chen po 'khor dang bcas pa'i
NK053('i)001:12922: sku la thim zhing zhal du gsol bar bsgom mo
NK053('i)001:12924: de nas bza' ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:12927: rnam rtog dbyings la thim zhing ye shes rol pa'i phyir bza' ba ste /
NK053('i)001:12930: nga ni za byed chen po ste /
NK053('i)001:12931: khams gsum ma lus bsgral bar bya //
NK053('i)001:12932: gdul dka' ma lus gdul ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:12933: sha rus la sogs bza' bar bya //
NK053('i)001:12934: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru ka ma h+aa badz+ra
NK053('i)001:12935: sarba dusata&a&a&ana sa ma ya mu ta ma ra ma
NK053('i)001:12936: kha kha kh+aa hi kh+aa hi /
NK053('i)001:12937: h+r+ai da ya bi pa snying po 'thung /
NK053('i)001:12940: zhal du bstab pa de nyid /
NK053('i)001:12941: gtso bo 'khor dang bcas pas rim pa bzhin du gsol bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:12943: bza' ba'i rjes su btung ba ste /
NK053('i)001:12946: nga ni khrag 'thung chen po ste //
NK053('i)001:12947: 'khor ba'i d+r+wa bas bcings pa'i rgyu //
NK053('i)001:12948: dmar chen bskyil ba'i rgya mtsho las //
NK053('i)001:12950: ma rungs 'dod la ma chags shing //
NK053('i)001:12951: dam tshig la sdang dgra chen rnams //
NK053('i)001:12952: ngo thon stobs kyis bsgral bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:12953: dzahmh'u bam hoh sh+r+ai he ru k+aa ma h+aa sa ma ya /
NK053('i)001:12968: pra ti dza hoh mchod pas dgyes /
NK053('i)001:12969: kha kha kha le le le h'u b+h+yo h'u b+h+yo h'u b+h+yo /
NK053('i)001:12971: 'khor ba'i rgyu khrag la sogs ye shes rol pa'i klong du thim zhing /
NK053('i)001:12972: sku gsung thugs dgyes pa bskyed de ril sangs rgyas par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:12975: de dag gi mjug sdud pa ste /
NK053('i)001:12976: spyan drangs pa nas bza' btung yan chad kyis /
NK053('i)001:12977: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor mnyes par byed pa'i yan lag de dag bya'o //
NK053('i)001:12980: de la rnal 'byor ji lta bus mchod pa'i bye brag shes par bya ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:12981: tshul rig goms pa'i blo dag gis //
NK053('i)001:12982: ci rigs su ni brtag par bya //
NK053('i)001:12985: dang po bla ma mnyes por byas te /
NK053('i)001:12986: phyi nang gsang ba'i dbang thob par byas nas /
NK053('i)001:12987: de'i rting thogs su bla ma'i phyag bzhes dang /
NK053('i)001:12988: phrin las rim pa yang dang yang du mthong zhing /
NK053('i)001:12989: man ngag 'khyud med par thob par byas nas /
NK053('i)001:12990: thos bsam bsgom pa gsum la sbyor te /
NK053('i)001:12991: rang gis bsgrub pa nyams bag tu blangs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12992: gdengs su gyur ba'i dus su sgrub pa po zab mo'i don snod tshul rig cing /
NK053('i)001:12993: bsgrub pa la goms pa'i rtags su phrin las la
NK053('i)001:12994: phyogs cha med pa dang thogs pa med par shes
NK053('i)001:12995: pa'i goms pa klong du gyur pa /
NK053('i)001:12996: shes rab kyi blo dang ldan pa dag gis /
NK053('i)001:12997: bsnyen bsgrub kyi rim pa dang /
NK053('i)001:12998: phrin las kyi cho ga rgyas 'bring thams cad /
NK053('i)001:13001: man ngag las ji skad du gsungs pa mtha' dag la /
NK053('i)001:13002: skabs gang dang gang du ci dang ci rigs par rang gi blos su brtag par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:13003: de yang bsnyen pa la zhi ba'i gzhung bsrang nas /
NK053('i)001:13004: bsgrub pa la khro bo'i gzhung bsrang ba spyir mthun la /
NK053('i)001:13005: mtshams sbyor gyi man ngag shes par bya ba la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:13006: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor bsdus nas chos sku thig le nyid nas bzung ste /
NK053('i)001:13007: ting nge 'dzin rnam pa gsum nas zhugs te /
NK053('i)001:13008: khro bo'i cho ga gzhung bsrang ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13009: zhi ba'i dkyil 'khor las khro bor skad cig mas bsgyur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13010: zhi ba las khro bor rim gyis bsgyur bar bya ba'o //
NK053('i)001:13011: khro bo'i cho ga rdzogs pa'i skabs su /
NK053('i)001:13013: smon lam rgyas 'bring yang lung dang man ngag las grags pa bzhin bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13014: de'i rting thogs su 'dzab dang bsnyen pa dbul ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13015: de'i rting thogs su mchod pa bya ba la lugs gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:13016: res 'ga' tshogs gtor gyi mchod pa 'ong la /
NK053('i)001:13017: res 'ga' sbyor sgrol gyi mchod pa 'ong /
NK053('i)001:13021: bar du nyams len ma bzlog pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13024: bro la sogs pa'i phrin las kun la /
NK053('i)001:13025: lta bas zin par byas te /
NK053('i)001:13026: las gnas skabs su bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:13027: rnal 'byor pa goms pa'i shugs can gyis ci rigs su ni brtag par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:13030: 3 / de la bsnyen pa dbul pa'i phrin las la bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:13031: dbang gang thob par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13033: rnal 'byor du bya ba'i thabs dang /
NK053('i)001:13034: lung ji ltar bsnyen bsgrub bya ba'o /
NK053('i)001:13036: 1 / de la dbang gang thob par bya snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:13037: bsnyen par gnang ba'i dbang thob nas //
NK053('i)001:13040: las kyi bsnyen pa gnyis la 'jug par 'dod pas /
NK053('i)001:13041: bsnyen cing bsgrub par gnang ba'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:13042: khyad par du yang gsang ba'i dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:13044: mtha' mar bla ma'i zhal dbang yan chad gong du bstan pa bzhin /
NK053('i)001:13045: slob ma dang sgrub pa po kun gyis thob par byas nas /
NK053('i)001:13048: 2 / man ngag bstan pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:13049: bsgom dbyangs yi ge 'bru brgyad bstan //
NK053('i)001:13057: bsgom pa'i mthar thug pa yi dbang //
NK053('i)001:13060: nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang //
NK053('i)001:13070: bslab pa'i dus su mtshan med kyi bsgom pa ni /
NK053('i)001:13078: ma bslad pa la thun mtshams su bzung ngo //
NK053('i)001:13084: ma g.yos ma bslad pa la thun mtshams su bzung ngo //
NK053('i)001:13085: bsgom pa chags shing brtan par gyur pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13086: gzung 'dzin mtha' grol gyi man ngag /
NK053('i)001:13090: khrom thub par gyur pa ni /
NK053('i)001:13091: gdeng du gyur pa zhes bya ste /
NK053('i)001:13092: rtags su blang dor dang bra ba'o //
NK053('i)001:13093: de yang nam mkha' che las /
NK053('i)001:13094: mi g.yo ba ni sku yi rgya //
NK053('i)001:13095: mi bskyod pa ni ye shes te //
NK053('i)001:13096: mi len pas na bdag med cing //
NK053('i)001:13097: mi 'dor tshig bral mnyam nyid do //
NK053('i)001:13100: mi gsung mnyam bzhag sngags tshig go //
NK053('i)001:13101: zhes gsungs pas don mnyam pa nyid la bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:13102: de la 2nyams su ting nge 'dzin gyis blang ba'i dus su /
NK053('i)001:13104: mtshan bcas kyi bsgom pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:13105: sna rtser sems bzung zhing thag bcad pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13106: sku gsung thugs phyag rgya'i dkyiil 'khor la dngos grub bsgrub pa'o //
NK053('i)001:13107: sna rtser 1sems bzung zhing thag bcad pa la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:13108: sems nyid sna rtser thig le la sems bzung zhing thag bcad pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13110: gsang ba'i sna rtser byang chub sems la bzung zhing thag bcad pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13112: rnam shes sna rtser dbugs la sems bzung zhing thag bcad pa ste /
NK053('i)001:13114: sna rtse gsum la brtag byas shing //
NK053('i)001:13115: nyams kyi ting 'dzin de ru sad //
NK053('i)001:13117: bla ma'i gdams ngag ngo sprod las shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:13118: de la sku 2gsung thugs phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor la dngos grub sgrub pa ni /
NK053('i)001:13119: don man ngag gi bsgrub pa /
NK053('i)001:13121: chos nyid skye ba med pa'i rang bzhin pas /
NK053('i)001:13122: skye ba'i cho 'phrul du dpal chen po 'khor dang bcas pa'i bsgom pa yang /
NK053('i)001:13126: legs par brtag cing de la bslab ste /
NK053('i)001:13127: sems la goms pa lang ba de dang 'dra bar bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:13128: de yang chos nyid kyi ma la ril gyis bskyed pa'i ting nge 'dzin gyis /
NK053('i)001:13129: dbal chen po'i ye shes kyi skur gsal ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13130: zag pa dang bcas pa'i phung po zag pa med pa'i lhar shes te /
NK053('i)001:13131: gsang ba'i yum dang gnyis su med pa'i byin gyis brlabs las /
NK053('i)001:13133: ye shes kyi sa bon gnyis su med pa las /
NK053('i)001:13134: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rgyas 'bring bskyed de gsal ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13135: ye shes kyi dkyil 'khor spyan drangs shing thim par byas la shin tu gsal bar byas te /
NK053('i)001:13136: gong du ri mo la brtag pa dang gnyis khyad
NK053('i)001:13137: par ma byung na gdeng du gyur pa yin te
NK053('i)001:13139: de yang bzlas pa la 'jug dus su bsgom par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:13140: thugs tsit+ta rin po che'i gzhal yas khang /
NK053('i)001:13141: smug nag zla gam sgo gcig pa'i nang du /
NK053('i)001:13142: ye shes lnga'i gzugs brnyan gsal bar bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:13143: dang po nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor rgya long bzur ba tsam gyi steng du /
NK053('i)001:13144: ye shes sems dpa'i sku dmog dmar smug sku tshon gang ba zhig gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:13145: de'i thugs kar zla ba'i dkyil 'khor sran chung zlum pa tsam gyi steng du /
NK053('i)001:13146: rin po che zur brgyad pa sul gsum shu'u kha gcig gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:13147: de'i dbus su rdo rje mthing ka nas tsam zhig /
NK053('i)001:13148: rin po che la phyed nub tsam du gsal ba'i
NK053('i)001:13149: rdo rje'i chang bzung gi bum pa nyi mar gsal
NK053('i)001:13150: ba'i dbus su h'u nyungs 'bru tsam zhig gsal bar
NK053('i)001:13151: bsgom mo // rin po che zur brgyad kyi steng nas tshur la /
NK053('i)001:13152: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13156: kha dog so so'i bye brag gis bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:13157: de nas lce rtsa ba rdo rje rtse gsum pa /
NK053('i)001:13158: rtse mo pad+ma 'dab ma bzhi par gyur pa'i ge sar la yang /
NK053('i)001:13159: bcom ldan 'das snang ba mtha' yas la gsang ba'i yum bzhis bskor bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:13160: de'i ljags pad+ma 'dab ma brgyad pa gyur pa'i ge sar la h'u /
NK053('i)001:13161: 'dab ma brgyad la ru lu 'bru brgyad kyis bskor bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:13164: b+h+r+aum bi shwa bi shud+d+he badz+ra dz+ny+aa na tsakra man d+ha la b+h+r+aum /
NK053('i)001:13168: lhun gyis grub pa'i gnas nas spyan drangs pa'i ye
NK053('i)001:13169: shes kyi he ru ka 'khor dang bcas pa sprin
NK053('i)001:13171: mar me gcig las gnyis su phye ba'i tshul du byas la /
NK053('i)001:13172: dkyil 'khor gnyis kyi tshul bzung ba ste /
NK053('i)001:13173: de dag gi thugs ka dang ljags steng du yang /
NK053('i)001:13174: yi ge phreng ba'i tshogs gong ltar bsgom mo /
NK053('i)001:13176: 2 / de la dbyangs kyi rim pa bstan pa la drug ste /
NK053('i)001:13177: de yang he ru ka'i gal po ru lu spros pa'i le'u las /
NK053('i)001:13178: dbyangs drug blangs pas don drug 'grub //
NK053('i)001:13180: sngags kyi yi ge sgra sgrog pas //
NK053('i)001:13181: des ni dkyil 'khor lha rnams bskyed //
NK053('i)001:13182: zab cing 'brung ltar sgra sgrogs pas //
NK053('i)001:13183: gtum po gdug par lha nyer 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:13185: khur ba dbugs kyi rlung 'byin pas //
NK053('i)001:13186: khro bo khro mo'i sprul pa 'gyed //
NK053('i)001:13188: rdo rje srin po'i ngur skad kyis //
NK053('i)001:13189: gdug pa thams cad spa yang bkod /
NK053('i)001:13191: mkhun ci gdung ba'i sgra yang 'byin //
NK053('i)001:13192: gnod sbyin ma lus rdul du rlog /
NK053('i)001:13194: tshangs pa dbyangs kyi 'dren tshul gyis //
NK053('i)001:13195: 'khor rnams thams cad dbang du sdud //
NK053('i)001:13198: re re la'ang gsum gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:13202: sngags kyi yi ge sgra sgrogs pa'i dbyings 1ni /
NK053('i)001:13206: ha cang sgra che ba yang ma yin /
NK053('i)001:13208: ngag zhan du smra zhing g.yeng ba yang ma yin te /
NK053('i)001:13211: tsheg bar ma nyams par bzlas te /
NK053('i)001:13213: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13215: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:13216: ru lu ru lu h'u byo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13218: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13219: zhes bya ba la sogs pa sngags tshang bar /
NK053('i)001:13221: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams rdzogs pa'i tshul du bskyed pa ste /
NK053('i)001:13222: gtso gzungs 'khor dang bcas pa shin tu yang gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:13223: dpe 'brug gi sgra ltar zab pa'i dbyangs 2ni /
NK053('i)001:13224: skad 'brug ltar drag la myur ba'i gdangs kyis stong khams gang ba'i sgra sgrogs pa ste /
NK053('i)001:13225: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13226: ma h+aa tsan+da sarba dusata&a&a&ana phata /
NK053('i)001:13228: ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u phata phata phata /
NK053('i)001:13231: gang gdug pa che zhing gtum khro che ba rnams zil gyis mnan cing lhan ner 'gyur ro //
NK053('i)001:13232: khur ba dbugs kyi rlung 'byin pa'i dbyangs 3ni /
NK053('i)001:13233: lce ya rkan la gtad la /
NK053('i)001:13234: dbugs sna bug tu phyung ste /
NK053('i)001:13235: bung ba'i skad ltar rgyun ring bar byas la /
NK053('i)001:13236: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13238: shangs rdo rje'i rlung sgrom nas /
NK053('i)001:13239: khro bo'i sprul pa rdul snyed thon pas /
NK053('i)001:13240: gang 'dul bar bya ba dbang du bsdus shing rdul du brlag par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:13241: rdo rje srin po'i ngur sgra'i dbyangs 4 ni /
NK053('i)001:13242: mchu btsum ste bung ba rdza mar bcug pa bzhin du /
NK053('i)001:13243: skad gdangs che la 'bru mi gsal bar byas te /
NK053('i)001:13244: srin po khros pa'i ngur sgra che bas /
NK053('i)001:13245: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13246: zhes bya ba brjod pa'i tshe /
NK053('i)001:13247: thugs rje che la thabs mkhas pa'i mdzad spyod kyis /
NK053('i)001:13248: rdo rje srin po'i cha lugs su bsgom ste bzlas pas /
NK053('i)001:13249: dur khrod kyi bdag po dregs pa khyo shug la sogs pas /
NK053('i)001:13250: 'jigs byed chen po'i cha lugs su mthong zhing /
NK053('i)001:13251: go ba med pa'i sgras gdug pa can gyi tshogs thams cad dbang du bsdus nas /
NK053('i)001:13252: spa bkong ste bzhi par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:13253: mkhun cing gdung ba'i sgra 'byin pa'i dbyangs 5ni /
NK053('i)001:13254: dper na rnga mo bu stor ba lta bya ba ste /
NK053('i)001:13255: bcom chung la mchu btsum pa ste /
NK053('i)001:13256: lce ya rkan la gtad nas bzlas brjod bsring la bya ste /
NK053('i)001:13257: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13259: mkhun cing gdung ba'i dbyangs su blangs pa'i tshe /
NK053('i)001:13260: sngon tshangs pa dung gi thor tshugs can dang /
NK053('i)001:13261: gnod sbyin rgod ma kha gnyis btul te rdul du brlag pa de bzhin du /
NK053('i)001:13262: gang gnod par byed pa rnams thal bar brlag cing rdul du gyur par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:13264: skad snyan cing phra la dkyus rings pa 'dril khugs
NK053('i)001:13265: kyi de'u dang bcas pa so bsdoms nas len pa
NK053('i)001:13266: ste / ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13268: sngon dpal chen pos ru tra bsgral te de'i 'khor
NK053('i)001:13269: ma mo dang mkha' 'gro dang pho nya dang yang
NK053('i)001:13270: bran la sogs pa rnams dbang du bsdus pa de
NK053('i)001:13271: bzhin du / da ltar yang bdag gis dbang du bsdu bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:13273: phrin las rnam pa bzhi dang sbyar te /
NK053('i)001:13276: rdo rje dbyangs kyi rjes 'gro bar /
NK053('i)001:13279: de ltar bzlas pa'i tshul de yang /
NK053('i)001:13280: man ngag gis dus bzhir rig par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:13285: de la yid la brjod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:13288: ting 'dzin bsgrub pa'i snying la gnas //
NK053('i)001:13289: yid la bsam pa'i cho ga yis //
NK053('i)001:13291: de phyir snying po yid la brjod //
NK053('i)001:13296: bsnyen pa ma thon bar dag tu //
NK053('i)001:13297: mi yengs 'dzab ni shib shib bzlas //
NK053('i)001:13298: bar bar bstod dang mchod pa bya //
NK053('i)001:13302: gong du bstan pa ltar rig par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:13304: las la sbyar ba'i dus te /
NK053('i)001:13306: rdo rje drag po gad mo che //
NK053('i)001:13307: khur ba dbugs kyi rlung 'byin cing //
NK053('i)001:13308: 'brug gi sgra ltar zab pa yis //
NK053('i)001:13310: khams gsum dag kyang rgyas 'debs shing //
NK053('i)001:13311: thar bar byed cing gsod par byed //
NK053('i)001:13312: shi ba'ang mod la 'tsho byar byed //
NK053('i)001:13315: 3 / 'bru brgyad kyi don bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:13316: ru lu yon tan du shes pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13317: ru lu bye brag tu shes pa'o //
NK053('i)001:13318: de la ru lu yon tan du shes 1pa la bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:13319: ru lu 'di ni ya mtshan che //
NK053('i)001:13320: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13321: ru lu 'di ni rtogs pa skye //
NK053('i)001:13322: ru lu ru lu b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13323: ru lu 'di ni sgrib pa spong //
NK053('i)001:13324: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13325: ru lu 'di ni dngos grub thob //
NK053('i)001:13326: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13327: zhes he ru ka'i tan+t+ra las gsungs te /
NK053('i)001:13328: de la 1ya mtshan che ba ni /
NK053('i)001:13330: las kyi ru tra ma rungs par gyur pa ste /
NK053('i)001:13331: rang gi nus pa la nga rgyal zhing /
NK053('i)001:13332: gzhan la gnod sbyor byed pa'i tshe /
NK053('i)001:13333: ro ta ma ta smra ra ra ta /
NK053('i)001:13334: zhes pas 'khor dbang du bsdu ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13335: ma h+aa ru lu ma ma rak+sha ma ma b+h+yo /
NK053('i)001:13336: zhes bya ba rang dang 'khor du bcas pa'i snying po bzlas pa las /
NK053('i)001:13337: ril dbang du sdud cing hag dngangs pa las /
NK053('i)001:13338: dpal chen pos ru tra bsgral te ru tra'i snying po 'phrogs te /
NK053('i)001:13339: ye shes kyi snying po byin gyis brlabs /
NK053('i)001:13340: lag cha kha t+w+aam kha 'phrogs te rdo rje kha t+w+aam khar byin gyis brlabs /
NK053('i)001:13341: khog sbubs 'phrogs te gzhal yas khang du byin gyis brlabs /
NK053('i)001:13342: sha khrag la sogs pa bdud rtsir byin gyis brlabs /
NK053('i)001:13343: gdug pa'i dpal bstan pa bsrung ba'i rdzas su byin gyis brlabs /
NK053('i)001:13344: kho'i shes pa'i rgyud bstan pa bsrung ba'i srung mar mgon po ma h+aa k+aa la byin gyis brlabs /
NK053('i)001:13345: ru tra'i nang gi 'khor ye shes kyi mkha' 'gro mar ke'u seng du byin gyis brlabs /
NK053('i)001:13346: phyi'i 'khor dbang phyug ma ma dang sring mo dang mdza' mo dang bran mor byin gyis brlabs te /
NK053('i)001:13347: dam tshig gi bya ra la bzhag /
NK053('i)001:13348: de ltar byas pa yang ru lu 'bru brgyad kyis grub pa yin te /
NK053('i)001:13349: de yang thugs zhi ba'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang /
NK053('i)001:13350: sku 'bar ba'i cha lugs su phyung nas don grub
NK053('i)001:13351: pa 'di ni ya mtshan che bar sngags kyi mathu'o
NK053('i)001:13353: mtshan ma can gyi skur bsgoms nas sngags mtshan ma can bzlas pas /
NK053('i)001:13354: don chos nyid skye ba med pa'i don yang 'dis skye bar byed pa yin pas /
NK053('i)001:13355: rtogs pa skye bar byed pa yang sngags kyi mathu'o //
NK053('i)001:13357: lha bsgom shing sngags bzlas pa'i mthus ni /
NK053('i)001:13358: nyon mongs pa dang shes byas bsdus pa'i sgrib pa
NK053('i)001:13359: tshe 'di nyid la sbyong bar byed pa yin no
NK053('i)001:13361: lung 'di nyid las byung ba bzhin du byas te bzlas pas /
NK053('i)001:13362: rab kyis phyag rgya chen po'i rig 'dzin gyi dngos grub thob la /
NK053('i)001:13363: 'bring gis mngon par shes pa lnga'i lha'i mig dang rna ba'i mngon shes /
NK053('i)001:13365: pha rol gyi sems shes pa /
NK053('i)001:13366: 'chi 'pho ba dang skye ba shes pa /
NK053('i)001:13369: tha mas kyang mkha' 'gro ma rnams dbang du 'du
NK053('i)001:13370: zhing las rnam pa bzhi'i zhi rgyas dbang drag dngos
NK053('i)001:13371: grub thob bo // de yang rgyud las /
NK053('i)001:13372: sngags kyi lha ni mthu byin che //
NK053('i)001:13373: bzlas pa'i yon tan bzhi dang ldan //
NK053('i)001:13376: 2 / de la ru lu bye brag tu shes pa la brgyad de /
NK053('i)001:13379: bzlas brjod du shes pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13380: phrin las su shes pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13383: dngos grub tu shes pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13386: 1 / de la dkyil 'khor la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:13387: phyi nang gsang ba gsum mo //
NK053('i)001:13388: phyi 1 snod kyi 'jig rten dur khrod chen po'i gzhal yas khang du gsal gdab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:13390: dbang chen yum lnga 'dus pa'i mkha' dbyings su //
NK053('i)001:13391: srin po ma tram bsgral ba'i khog pa la //
NK053('i)001:13392: b+han+d+ha tshar gsum brtsegs pa'i rtsig pa byas //
NK053('i)001:13393: rak+ta'i spyi sbyar gnam lcags gzer chen btab //
NK053('i)001:13394: yon tan che rgyas gru bzhi mchod rten tshul //
NK053('i)001:13395: zla gam dbang chen smug nag 'bar ba la //
NK053('i)001:13396: ka ba mchog brgyad ldan pa'i re'u tshe dgu //
NK053('i)001:13397: tshangs pa'i gdung bzhi mchog chen ka ba dang //
NK053('i)001:13398: nyi zla ka gzhu phag gi ka gdan dang //
NK053('i)001:13399: sbrul gyi skyes bu ka ru'i ya spyibs la //
NK053('i)001:13400: rus sbal ma them zhing gi sgo 'gebs te //
NK053('i)001:13402: t+aa la'i skye shing 'dod yon lha mo dang //
NK053('i)001:13403: 'bar ba'i bar khyams dur khrod gnas bcas te //
NK053('i)001:13404: rab 'jigs dur khrod chen po rgyan dang chas //
NK053('i)001:13405: mtha' dang dbus med ye shes nam mkha'i rgya //
NK053('i)001:13406: dregs pa khyo shug bsnol zhing zhing chen steng //
NK053('i)001:13407: rab gsal nyi ma'i gdan dang bcas pa 'di //
NK053('i)001:13408: rgyu 'bras ma bkag dag pa'i gzhal yas khang //
NK053('i)001:13409: dpal chen khrag 'thung tshogs kyi bzhugs gnas yin //
NK053('i)001:13410: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u //
NK053('i)001:13412: bdag gi thugs ka nas ru lu ye shes kyi 'od zer dang bcas /
NK053('i)001:13413: snod kyi 'jig rten dang gzhal yas khang la 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:13415: dwangs ma'i 'byung ba lnga 'od kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK053('i)001:13416: dbyibs dang kha dog so sor gsal ba de yang /
NK053('i)001:13417: rgyu chos nyid kun tu bzang mo skye ba med pa'i ngang las /
NK053('i)001:13418: 'bras bu thugs rje 'gengs pa'i yum lngar gsal ba'i mkha' la /
NK053('i)001:13419: rgyu chos sku skye 'gags pa med pa'i ngang las /
NK053('i)001:13420: 'bras bu ye shes lnga las grub pa'i gzhal yas khang 'gags pa med par shar te /
NK053('i)001:13421: gsal la mi bsgrib pa zhig bsgom zhing bzlas so //
NK053('i)001:13422: de las su rung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13423: nang 2bcud kyi 'jig rten khrag 'thung phyag rgya'i tshogs su gsal gdab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:13425: chos nyid skye med gdod nas dag pa la //
NK053('i)001:13426: skye ba'i cho 'phrul 'bar ba'i skur bstan pa'i //
NK053('i)001:13427: bcom ldan dpal chen khrag 'thung yab yum la //
NK053('i)001:13428: ke'u seng la sogs mkha' 'gro'i tshogs kyis bskor //
NK053('i)001:13429: ye shes skur gsal thugs rjes khyab pa'i sku //
NK053('i)001:13430: gdug pa 'dul phyir 'jigs byed skur ston pa //
NK053('i)001:13431: dur khrod rgyan mdzes gdug byed mtshon cha bsnams //
NK053('i)001:13432: bskal pa'i me 'bar dur khrod dkyil 'khor na /
NK053('i)001:13433: khams gsum stong mdzad khrag 'thung phyag rgya'i tshogs //
NK053('i)001:13434: rgyu 'bras ma bkag lha yi dkyil 'khor gsal //
NK053('i)001:13435: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13437: thugs ka nas ru lu ye shes kyi 'od zer
NK053('i)001:13438: bcud kyi 'jig rten khams gsum gyi sems can la
NK053('i)001:13439: phog pas ye shes kyi lta ba drag pos bskyod
NK053('i)001:13440: do // rgyu chos sku skye ba med pa'i ngang las /
NK053('i)001:13441: 'bras bu dpal chen po 'khor dang bcas pa'i skur gsal ba des /
NK053('i)001:13442: rgyu khams gsum gyi sems can las /
NK053('i)001:13443: 'bras bu ma bkag pa'i sangs rgyas su lhang gis bsgyur bar bsgom zhing bzlas so //
NK053('i)001:13444: de las su rung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13445: gsang 3ba'i phyi nang snod bcud gnyis kyang byang chub sems su gsal gdab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:13447: phyi nang snod bcud chos nyid chen po ni //
NK053('i)001:13448: rang bzhin rnam dag sems kyi spyod yul la //
NK053('i)001:13449: sangs rgyas sems can gnyis su ngas ma mthong //
NK053('i)001:13450: snang stong dbyer med rdo rje theg pa'i lam //
NK053('i)001:13451: go ba'i yul 'das sangs rgyas bde ba'i zhing //
NK053('i)001:13452: 'di nyid rnam dag sprul sku thug 'phrad gsal //
NK053('i)001:13453: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13455: phyi nang snod bcud kyis bsdus pa yang rang gi
NK053('i)001:13456: sems la sems kyis sems su ngo shes pa'i dus
NK053('i)001:13457: na / snang stong dbyer med kyi dgongs pa la brtag go /
NK053('i)001:13459: 2 / de la ru lu lhar shes pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:13463: ni dpal chen sku gsung thugs //
NK053('i)001:13464: ru lu gnas kyi phyag rgyar brgyad //
NK053('i)001:13465: ru lu gong ma ke'u ri /
NK053('i)001:13466: 'og ma yul gyi seng ha brgyad do //
NK053('i)001:13467: h'u ni thabs shes sgo ma bzhi //
NK053('i)001:13468: b+h+yo ni ma sring rgya mtsho'i tshogs //
NK053('i)001:13469: h'u ni ye shes sems dpa'i sku //
NK053('i)001:13470: zur brgyad steng du 'bru brgyad gsal //
NK053('i)001:13472: gsal bar bsgom zhing gsal bar brtag /
NK053('i)001:13473: brtags pas 'bru brgyad lha rnams gsal //
NK053('i)001:13474: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13477: rgyu'i gnas skabs na phung po lnga dang /
NK053('i)001:13479: 'bras bu rnam par dag pa'i dus na ni /
NK053('i)001:13480: rigs lnga khrag 'thung yab yum gyi snying po ste /
NK053('i)001:13481: de yang dpal chen po rdo rje'i snying po zag
NK053('i)001:13482: pa med pa'i 'byung ba dang bcas pa'i rang bzhin
NK053('i)001:13483: / phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor du gsal zhing sangs rgyas pa'o //
NK053('i)001:13486: kun gzhi rnam par shes pa yul dang bcas pa ste dpal chen po yab yum la /
NK053('i)001:13489: rnam pa shes pa bzhi dang yul bzhi dang brgyad kyi rang bzhin la /
NK053('i)001:13490: 'bras bu rnam par dag pa'i dus na ni /
NK053('i)001:13491: ke'u ri la sogs par gnas gyur pa'o //
NK053('i)001:13494: dbang po bzhi dang dus bzhi'i rang bzhin la /
NK053('i)001:13495: 'bras bu rnam par dag pa'i dus na /
NK053('i)001:13496: seng ha mu ka la sogs par gnas gyur pa'o //
NK053('i)001:13499: phyin ci log bzhi'i rang bzhin la /
NK053('i)001:13500: 'bras bu rnam par dag pa'i dus na /
NK053('i)001:13501: sgo ma bzhir gnas gyur pa'o //
NK053('i)001:13504: zag pa dang bcas pa'i bdag 'dzin la /
NK053('i)001:13506: dbang phyug ma'i rang bzhin las dang ye shes dbyer med pa'i ma mo yin no //
NK053('i)001:13509: nyon mongs pa'i yid bdag tu 'dzin pa la /
NK053('i)001:13510: 'bras bu rnam par dag pa'i dus na /
NK053('i)001:13511: thugs kha'i ye shes sems dpa'i rang bzhin dkyil 'khor
NK053('i)001:13512: gyi lha kun gyi che ba'i yon tan ma lus
NK053('i)001:13513: pa'i 'byung gnas su gyur par shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:13515: ni dkar mo ke'u ri ma //
NK053('i)001:13516: ru ni rkun mo tso'u ri ma //
NK053('i)001:13517: lu ni sbos mo pra mo h+aa //
NK053('i)001:13518: ru ni thal byed be te li //
NK053('i)001:13519: lu ni rgan byed puska si //
NK053('i)001:13520: h'u ni gtum mo kasma ri //
NK053('i)001:13521: b+h+yo ni sme sha sma sha ni //
NK053('i)001:13522: h'u ni ma tshogs tsan+d+ha li //
NK053('i)001:13523: kun bsdus dpal chen snying po ste //
NK053('i)001:13524: yang dag don gyi lha dgur gsal //
NK053('i)001:13525: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13527: ru lu 'bru brgyad yang dag don gyi lha dgu'i snying po ste /
NK053('i)001:13528: lus dang yan lag gi tshul du shes par bya'o /
NK053('i)001:13530: 3 / ru lu bzlas brjod du shes par bya ba la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:13538: spro ba'i dgos ched dang bzhi sbyar ro //
NK053('i)001:13541: h'u ni thabs chen shes rab yab yum /
NK053('i)001:13543: ye shes thig le thugs la shar //
NK053('i)001:13544: rin chen zur brgyad steng nas dngos po /
NK053('i)001:13546: yul khams gsum sems can sdug bsngal bsal //
NK053('i)001:13547: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i sku la thim //
NK053('i)001:13548: sngags tshig sgra yi mchod pas mnyes //
NK053('i)001:13549: tshur 'dus dang po'i gnas su thim /
NK053('i)001:13550: lus ngag yid gsum sgrib pa sbyangs //
NK053('i)001:13551: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob //
NK053('i)001:13554: gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems //
NK053('i)001:13556: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13558: ye shes sems dpa'i thugs ka'i h'u las /
NK053('i)001:13559: rang rgyud kyi sgras 'bru brgyad la bskul bas /
NK053('i)001:13560: 'bru brgyad kha dog ljang dmar ram le'u brgan du 'phros te /
NK053('i)001:13561: bskul don byas shing dngos grub thob par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:13566: gsal 'tsher thogs med kun tu khyab //
NK053('i)001:13567: phar 'phros pas ni gzhan don mdzad //
NK053('i)001:13569: rnam par spros pas bsod nams tshogs //
NK053('i)001:13570: stong par gsal bas ye shes tshogs //
NK053('i)001:13571: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pas mngon sangs rgyas //
NK053('i)001:13572: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13574: don ni brjod pas go sla'o //
NK053('i)001:13576: ngag don du dgus bstan te /
NK053('i)001:13577: dang po rigs kyi yab lnga la 'phro 'du bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:13578: dug lnga dag pas ye shes lnga brnyes te //
NK053('i)001:13579: sku lnga ldan pas rgyud lnga sgrol mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:13580: rab 'bar cha lugs 'jigs pas kun 'dul ba //
NK053('i)001:13581: ye shes khrag 'thung thabs kyi he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:13582: bsnyen mchod sngags kyi yi ge 'bru brgyad spros //
NK053('i)001:13583: dbyer med 'dud pa'i dbyangs dang gar gyis mchod //
NK053('i)001:13584: bsnyen pa bzhes la dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK053('i)001:13585: 'bar ba'i sku mchog ston la byin gyis rlobs //
NK053('i)001:13586: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13589: 'byung ba rnam lnga yum lnga'i skur snang zhing //
NK053('i)001:13590: shes rab yum lngas thabs la dgyes 'khril nas //
NK053('i)001:13591: gtso mchog thugs dam skong ba'i dam tshig can //
NK053('i)001:13592: kro ti shwa ri'i sku mchog shes rab yum //
NK053('i)001:13593: bsnyen mchod sngags dbyer med 'dud bsnyen pa bzhes 'bar
NK053('i)001:13594: ba'i sku ru lu gnyis pa ke'u ri brgyad la
NK053('i)001:13595: 'phro 'du ni / rnam shes brgyad las khro mo'i skur snang ba //
NK053('i)001:13596: phyag rgya cha lugs gcig tu ma nges kyang //
NK053('i)001:13597: thugs rjes kun la khyab pa'i don mdzad ma //
NK053('i)001:13598: ke'u ri la sogs khro mo brgyad rnams la //
NK053('i)001:13599: bsnyen mchod dbyer med bsnyen pa 'bar ba'i ru lu
NK053('i)001:13600: gsum pa sing ha brgyad la 'phro 'du bya ba
NK053('i)001:13601: / yul brgyad dag pas mu ka brgyad du snang //
NK053('i)001:13602: mgo bsnyan tshogs kyis dur khrod za mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:13603: rdo rje mche gshog mgo brnyan phra men tshogs //
NK053('i)001:13604: sing ha la sogs phra men brgyad rnams la //
NK053('i)001:13605: bsnyen mchod dbyer med bsnyen pa 'bar ba'i ru lu bzhi pa sgo ma bzhi la 'phro 'du /
NK053('i)001:13606: phyi ci log bzhi dbyings su gnas gyur te //
NK053('i)001:13607: tshad med bsdu ba rnam bzhi'i ngang tshul can //
NK053('i)001:13608: 'gugs 'ching sdom myos byed pa'i las mkhan ma //
NK053('i)001:13609: dkyil 'khor srung ba'i sgo ma bzhi rnams la //
NK053('i)001:13610: bsnyen mchod dbyer med bsnyen pa 'bar ba'i ru lu lnga pa dbang phyug ma la 'phro 'du /
NK053('i)001:13611: dpal gyi bka' nyan dam tshig gnyan bsrung zhing //
NK053('i)001:13612: ma sring rgya mtsho'i tshul gyis brtser dgos te //
NK053('i)001:13613: grogs la gdung zhing 'gal ba tshar gcod pa //
NK053('i)001:13614: rdo rje dbang phyug nyi shu rtsa brgyad la //
NK053('i)001:13615: bsnyen mchod dbyer med bsnyen pa 'bar ba'i ru lu drug pa yang phur bsrung ba'i srung ma la /
NK053('i)001:13616: cha lugs khro 'jigs spyod pas rab mdzes pa //
NK053('i)001:13617: gzhan dag bsreg mdzad gtso la mnyes stob pa //
NK053('i)001:13618: mdzad pa rnam dag pha rol sgrol mdzad ma //
NK053('i)001:13619: yang phur skyong ba'i srung ma bzhi rnams la //
NK053('i)001:13620: bsnyen mchod dbyer med bsnyen pa 'bar ba'i ru lu bdun pa pho nya la /
NK053('i)001:13621: gshegs bzhud mi mnga' gar yang thogs med cing //
NK053('i)001:13622: rtog pa kun bral thams cad sa lar mkhyen //
NK053('i)001:13623: bya rtsol med bzhin gzhan dag tshar gcod mkhas //
NK053('i)001:13624: bka' nyan mngag gzhug pho nya rdul snyed la //
NK053('i)001:13625: bsnyen mchod dbyer med bsnyen pa 'bar ba'i ru lu brgyad pa rig 'dzin /
NK053('i)001:13626: phyogs bcu'i dang nam mkha'i 'jig rten na //
NK053('i)001:13627: lha dag lha min phra rab gzugs 'chang zhing //
NK053('i)001:13628: gsang sngags rdo rji'i theg chen gnyer blangs pas //
NK053('i)001:13629: rig 'dzin sngags 'chang rnal 'byor thams cad la //
NK053('i)001:13630: bsnyen mchod dbyer med bsnyen pa 'bar ba'i ru lu dgu pa spyir bya ba ni //
NK053('i)001:13631: dpal chen khrag 'thung thugs ni rin po che //
NK053('i)001:13632: thugs rje sku mdog yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter //
NK053('i)001:13633: bdag ni bla med byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed de //
NK053('i)001:13634: rang sems gdod nas ma skyes rin po che //
NK053('i)001:13635: lha dang gnyis su med par mnyam bzhag nas //
NK053('i)001:13636: ut+pala 'dab brgyad lta bu'i ljags brkyang zhing //
NK053('i)001:13637: khur ba dbugs ring dang bcas pa yis //
NK053('i)001:13638: ru lu ru lu 'khor lo tshogs chen po //
NK053('i)001:13639: bar chad med pa'i bzlas brjod ting 'dzin gyis //
NK053('i)001:13640: sems rtog sbyong zhing dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:13641: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13643: bdag dang mdun gyi lha gnyis spro bsdu 'gal me'i 'khor lo ltar rgyun mi chad par bya'o /
NK053('i)001:13645: 4 / ru lu phrin las su shes pa ni /
NK053('i)001:13647: dang po zhi ba'i phrin las /
NK053('i)001:13648: gnas sku gsung thugs kyi gnas nas spro //
NK053('i)001:13649: dngos pos ci spro na ru lu 2'od zer dkar po dang //
NK053('i)001:13650: tshangs pa dbyangs kyi 'dren tshul gyis //
NK053('i)001:13652: zhi ba'i las rnams grub par byed //
NK053('i)001:13653: dgos ched zhi ba'i gyur nas dbyings su rol //
NK053('i)001:13654: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13656: ru lu 2'od zer ser po dang //
NK053('i)001:13657: sngags kyi yi ge sgra sgrogs pas //
NK053('i)001:13658: rgyas pa'i las rnams grub par byed //
NK053('i)001:13659: rgyas par gyur nas dbyings su rol //
NK053('i)001:13661: ru lu 3'od zer dmar po dang //
NK053('i)001:13662: zab cing 'brug gi sgra sgrogs pas //
NK053('i)001:13663: dbang gi las rnams grub par byed //
NK053('i)001:13664: dbang du bsdus nas dbyings su rol //
NK053('i)001:13665: ru lu bzhi pa drag po /
NK053('i)001:13666: ru lu 4'od zer mthing nag dang //
NK053('i)001:13667: mkhun cing gdung ba'i sgra 'byin pas //
NK053('i)001:13668: drag po'i las rnams grub par byed //
NK053('i)001:13669: rdul du brlag nas dbyings su rol //
NK053('i)001:13670: ru lu lnga pa mnan pa /
NK053('i)001:13671: ru lu 5'od zer mthing nag dang //
NK053('i)001:13672: rdo rje srin pa'i ngur sgra yis //
NK053('i)001:13673: gnan pa'i las rnams grub par byed //
NK053('i)001:13674: gnan par byas nas dbyings su rol //
NK053('i)001:13675: ru lu drug pa bzlog pa /
NK053('i)001:13676: ru lu 6'od zer dmar nag dang //
NK053('i)001:13677: khur ba dbugs kyi rlung 'byin gyis //
NK053('i)001:13678: bzlas pa'i las rnams grub par byed //
NK053('i)001:13679: bzlog par byas nas dbyings su rol //
NK053('i)001:13680: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13682: phrin las de rnams grub par shes par bya'o /
NK053('i)001:13684: 5 / ru lu mchod par shes par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:13687: phyi mchod dngos po me tog bdug spos lha bshos mar mer bcas //
NK053('i)001:13688: bla bre rgyal mtshan na bza' 'phan dang gdugs //
NK053('i)001:13689: sil snyan rnga dung rin chen mu tig phreng //
NK053('i)001:13690: nang mchod gzugs sgra dri ro reg sogs lha mo'i tshogs //
NK053('i)001:13692: bde chen byang chub sems kyi mchod sprin rnams //
NK053('i)001:13693: dngos su bshams shing sems kyis rnam sprul te //
NK053('i)001:13695: ye shes rang snang zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK053('i)001:13697: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13699: ru lu ye shes kyi 'od zer las /
NK053('i)001:13700: mchod pa'i bye brag tu sprul te dbul bar bya'o /
NK053('i)001:13702: 6 / ru lu bshags par shes par bya ba ni //
NK053('i)001:13703: ye shes lha tshogs zhi khro'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK053('i)001:13704: rig 'dzin dam can rgya mtsho dgongs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:13705: tshe rabs thog mtha' med pa'i dus mtha' nas //
NK053('i)001:13706: da lta lus 'di blangs pa phan chod du //
NK053('i)001:13707: rang sems ma rig bdag tu bzung ba yis //
NK053('i)001:13708: 'khor ba'i nyes skyon sna tshogs byung nas su //
NK053('i)001:13709: kun gzhi'i blo la bag chags bsags pa dang //
NK053('i)001:13710: bar du thugs rjes bzung nas stsol ba yis //
NK053('i)001:13711: byang chub sems bskyed thar lam sgor zhugs te //
NK053('i)001:13712: theg pa rim par bgrod cing spyod pa'i tshe //
NK053('i)001:13713: tshul khrims sdom pa phyi nang dam tshig las //
NK053('i)001:13714: zhig ral chag nyams gyur pa ci mchis dang //
NK053('i)001:13715: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i sgor zhugs nas //
NK053('i)001:13716: 'da' dka' sdom pa'i dam tshig mnos pa las //
NK053('i)001:13717: sngon du spyad pa'i goms shugs chung ba yis //
NK053('i)001:13718: nyams su ma rtogs gzhung bzhin ma spyad de //
NK053('i)001:13719: bla ma mched la sri zhu brtse gdung chung //
NK053('i)001:13720: sngags dang phyag rgya rgyun bcad gsang tshig spel //
NK053('i)001:13721: yan lag dam tshig mdzad spyod rnam lngas 'gro don lhur ma blangs //
NK053('i)001:13722: dug lnga rnam grol lam du gnas ma gyur //
NK053('i)001:13723: mnyam pa'i mchod pas lta ba thag ma chod //
NK053('i)001:13724: shes par bya ba'i spyod yul yal bar btang //
NK053('i)001:13725: grub par bya ba'i 'bras bu rgyun thag bsrings //
NK053('i)001:13726: dbang dang mi ldan chos bshad las rnams brtsams //
NK053('i)001:13727: rtogs pa'i stobs chung dge bsgom sgrub la g.yel //
NK053('i)001:13728: dam rdzas mchod rdzogs gzhung bzhin ma bstabs dang //
NK053('i)001:13729: dam bcas khas blangs bgyis kun rjes ma sobs //
NK053('i)001:13730: byang chub rigs can spyod pas thugs ma bsrungs //
NK053('i)001:13731: bar chod gnod rkyen ma bzod 'khrul sems shor //
NK053('i)001:13732: snod dang mi ldan grogs ngan grib mas phog /
NK053('i)001:13733: de la sogs te nyes sdig ci bsags pa //
NK053('i)001:13734: gnong 'gyod mthol bshags bzod par gsol lags na //
NK053('i)001:13735: byams mgon thugs rjes tshangs pa stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:13736: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13738: bdag med phyogs bral gyi don ma rtogs te /
NK053('i)001:13739: nga bdag tu bzung ba'i dbang gis /
NK053('i)001:13740: bka' phyi nang du gyur pa'i lha dang srung ma dang /
NK053('i)001:13741: bde bar gshegs pa rnams la /
NK053('i)001:13742: ru lu 'bru brgyad ye shes kyi 'od zer du 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:13743: ril ye shes kyi 'od dpung du gyur /
NK053('i)001:13744: bdag la tshur 'dus pas bdag gi nyes skyon byang zhing dag nas /
NK053('i)001:13745: ye shes kyi sku la nag nog gi dri ma dang bral nas /
NK053('i)001:13747: mu tig dkar po dri ma med pa ltar /
NK053('i)001:13748: shes pa'i rgyud la gsal zhing dwang bar bsgom mo /
NK053('i)001:13750: 7 / ru lu dngos grub tu shes par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:13752: bsgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor bsam mi khyab //
NK053('i)001:13753: zla gam dkyil 'khor rin chen dbang //
NK053('i)001:13754: nub phyogs ngos su kha bltas te //
NK053('i)001:13755: dus gsum sangs rgyas thams cad dang //
NK053('i)001:13757: tshon gang chos kyi 'khor lo las //
NK053('i)001:13759: phar 'phros pas ni ye shes lha'i //
NK053('i)001:13760: sku gsung thugs la mchod pa 'bul //
NK053('i)001:13761: slar 'dus pas ni sgrub pa pos //
NK053('i)001:13762: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thob //
NK053('i)001:13763: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13765: thugs ka nas ru lu 'bru brgyad ljang dmar du 'phro zhing /
NK053('i)001:13766: ye shes lha'i sku gsung thugs kyi gnas su thim /
NK053('i)001:13768: lha'i thugs ka nas ru lu smug nag tu tshur
NK053('i)001:13769: bsdu zhing sgrub pa po'i lus ngag yid gsum la
NK053('i)001:13770: bsdus pas / sku 'gyur ba med pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13772: thugs skye shi med pa'i dngos grub thob par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:13773: de yan chad du man ngag gis //
NK053('i)001:13774: gnas gang nas spro ba dang //
NK053('i)001:13775: dngos po ci spro ba dang //
NK053('i)001:13776: yul gang du spro ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13777: spro ba'i dgos ched dang bzhis rig par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:13778: bla ma'i man ngag gis gsung ngo //
NK053('i)001:13779: bzlas brjod de dag ril bsdus te mchod par phul la /
NK053('i)001:13781: bde bar gshegs so bcom ldan 'das //
NK053('i)001:13782: bde bar gshegs so khro rgyal tshogs //
NK053('i)001:13783: rgyal ba rgya mtsho 'khor bcas la //
NK053('i)001:13784: bzlas brjod sngags kyi 'khor lo bskor //
NK053('i)001:13785: mchod pa dam pa bla na med //
NK053('i)001:13786: bzlas brjod mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NK053('i)001:13787: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13789: sgrub pa po'i ru lu ril bsdus te /
NK053('i)001:13790: dpal chen po'i thugs kar phul te //
NK053('i)001:13791: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK053('i)001:13792: thugs rje khro dpal rngams pa'i tshogs //
NK053('i)001:13793: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK053('i)001:13794: da lta nyid du bdag la stsol //
NK053('i)001:13795: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13797: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas ril dang /
NK053('i)001:13798: dpal khrag 'thung lha ye shes las grub pa sgo ma yan chad /
NK053('i)001:13799: sku ye shes kyi 'od zer dang ldan pa ril /
NK053('i)001:13800: sgrub pa po'i lus mgo mjug la zhugs te dbyer med par gyur te /
NK053('i)001:13801: shin tu bkra gsal du gyur pa ni thun mong chen po'i dngos grub bo //
NK053('i)001:13802: las las grub pa'i mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyi sku mi bsdu bar /
NK053('i)001:13803: 'od dang yon tan bsdus pa ni thun mong chung ngu'i dngos grub bo /
NK053('i)001:13805: 8 / de nas ru lu chos nyid du shes par bya ba la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:13806: chos nyid kyis go bgo ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13807: chos nyid kyis bsrung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13808: chos nyid kyi lta ba la gnas pa'o //
NK053('i)001:13809: de la 1chos nyid kyis go bgo ba ni /
NK053('i)001:13810: cis kyang mi phyed mi shigs pa'i //
NK053('i)001:13811: stong pa'i go cha bla na med //
NK053('i)001:13812: mtshan ma'i yul kun bcom nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:13813: thams cad myur du rgyal bar gnas //
NK053('i)001:13814: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13816: ming dang mtshan mar ma grub bar //
NK053('i)001:13817: mi gnas ma bral 'dus ma byas //
NK053('i)001:13818: chos kyi dbyings kyis bsrungs pas na //
NK053('i)001:13819: sangs rgyas kyis kyang mi gzigs so //
NK053('i)001:13820: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:13821: de ni mchog gi dngos grub chung ngu'o //
NK053('i)001:13822: chos 3nyid kyi lta ba la gnas par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:13824: phyag rgya'i cha lugs tha dad kyang //
NK053('i)001:13825: dang por chos nyid ngang las 'byung //
NK053('i)001:13826: bar du spyod pa ci spyad kyang //
NK053('i)001:13827: kun bzang rol pa'i ngang du spyad //
NK053('i)001:13828: tha mar rol pa'i snang ba yang //
NK053('i)001:13829: chos nyid mnyam pa'i ngang du bsdu'o //
NK053('i)001:13830: nam mkha' rdo rje sems dpa' che //
NK053('i)001:13831: kun bzang yangs pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK053('i)001:13832: rnam dag lam chen kun bsgral phyir //
NK053('i)001:13833: mi skye mi 'gag cir mi dgongs //
NK053('i)001:13835: gong 'og tu bstan pa'i lta bas thag bcad pa la brtag go //
NK053('i)001:13836: de ni mchog gi dngos grub chen po'o /
NK053('i)001:13838: 3 / rnal 'byor du bya ba'i thabs la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:13841: de la bsgrub 1pa'i rnal 'byor du bya ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:13842: bsgom rgyud gsal bar ci nus bya //
NK053('i)001:13844: dang por mtshams bcad pa nas bzung ste /
NK053('i)001:13846: bar du zhi khro gzhung bsrang ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13848: lhag mas mkha' 'gro ma bskyang zhing mchod pa yan chod du /
NK053('i)001:13849: rnal 'byoor pa rab mtshan med mtshan bcas kyi bsgom pa nas bzung ste /
NK053('i)001:13850: rang gi shes pa'i rgyud la gsal zhing 'dris par bsgom pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13851: 'bring sngags dang bzlas brjod par mchod par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13852: tha mar lung tshig gis gsal gdab cing bskul ba ste /
NK053('i)001:13853: rnal 'byor pa'i sgo gsum g.yo sgyu med pas ci nus su mchod pa'i rim pa 'bad de bya'o //
NK053('i)001:13854: rnal 'byor pa rgod de g.yeng ba can gyis ma yin no //
NK053('i)001:13855: bsnyen 2 pa'i rnal 'byor du bya ba yang /
NK053('i)001:13856: bsgom rgyud gsal bar ci nus bya //
NK053('i)001:13858: dang por mtshan med kyi bsgom pa //
NK053('i)001:13859: chos nyid kyi ma dang 'dris par byas shing //
NK053('i)001:13860: rang gi shes pa'i rgyud dag par byas te /
NK053('i)001:13861: ye shes dag pa'i ngang du ci gsal du bsgom pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13862: de nas phyag rgya chen po'i skur bsgoms te /
NK053('i)001:13865: mchod pa la sogs pa byas te /
NK053('i)001:13866: bzlas pa'i skabs la babs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13867: bskul tshig dang dbyangs la sogs pa mi dgos te /
NK053('i)001:13869: gtsang sbra gsum pho nya'i gtsang sbra /
NK053('i)001:13871: zas gcig tu za ba'i gtsang sbra /
NK053('i)001:13876: lung ji ltar du bsnyen bsgrub bya snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:13877: bsnyen pa'i lung bzhin brtson par 'bad //
NK053('i)001:13880: zhes bya ba la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:13888: mya ngan las 'das pa la bsnyen pa'o //
NK053('i)001:13893: 1 / don gyi dbye ba la bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:13899: mi tshe gcig la sbyar ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13900: lha'i sku gcig la sbyar ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13901: dkyil 'khor rdzogs pa gcig la sbyar ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13902: sbyor ba skad cig ma gcig la sbyar ba dang bzhi'o //
NK053('i)001:13903: de la 1mi tshe gcig la sbyar ba ni /
NK053('i)001:13904: bsnyen pa lung ston nus pa'i bla ma nye bar btsal ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13906: bla ma mnyes par byas te /
NK053('i)001:13908: dbang thob par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13910: stsol ba drag por bsnyen sgrub tshar gcod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13911: dngos grub ma thob kyi bar du mi btang bar bsgrub pa'o //
NK053('i)001:13912: lha'i sku gcig la 2sbyar ba ni /
NK053('i)001:13916: phung po lhar mos pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13918: sku gsung thugs rdo rjer byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13920: dbu la rigs lngar gsal ba'o //
NK053('i)001:13921: dkyil 'khor rdzogs 3pa gcig la sbyar ba ni /
NK053('i)001:13923: byang chub kyi sems shes pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13927: g.yon du yum bskyed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13929: gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems las dkyil 'khor rgyas 'bring gi lhar bskyed pa'o //
NK053('i)001:13930: sbyor ba skad 4cig ma gcig la sbyar ba ni /
NK053('i)001:13932: yum byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13934: brdas bskul zhing 'du bar bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13936: bde ba bskyed cing khams dbab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:13938: byang chub sems las ji ltar 'dod pa lta sbyar ba'o /
NK053('i)001:13940: 2 / las kyi dbye ba la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:13944: de la 1 dus kyi bsnyen pa ni /
NK053('i)001:13945: dbyar dgun ston dpyid kyi zla ba la bya ste /
NK053('i)001:13947: rab ra ba la 4 bsnyen pa bya /
NK053('i)001:13949: tha chung la 4 phrin las bya'o //
NK053('i)001:13950: 'bring ra ba bzhi la bsnyen mchod lan re bya /
NK053('i)001:13951: tha ma yang dbyar dgun gnyis la bsnyen mchod lan re bya'o //
NK053('i)001:13953: rab rgyun du bya ste grangs med do //
NK053('i)001:13955: tha mas kyang bdun 'bum yan chad bya'o //
NK053('i)001:13957: 'og nas ston pa lta bu ma byung bar du bya'o //
NK053('i)001:13958: de ltar shes pa la bsnyen pa /
NK053('i)001:13962: rdo rje sems dpas gsungs pa'i lung /
NK053('i)001:13963: he ru ka'i gal po dang /
NK053('i)001:13964: 'jig rten las 'das pa'i mdo las ji skad du gsungs pa bzhin /
NK053('i)001:13965: man ngag tu 'dir bkod pa ste /
NK053('i)001:13968: bsnyen pa dang ni nye bsnyen po //
NK053('i)001:13969: bsgrub dang sgrub pa chen po la //
NK053('i)001:13970: man ngag sbyor shes rnal 'byor pas //
NK053('i)001:13971: dus grangs mtshan ma'i bsnyen pa bya //
NK053('i)001:13973: bsnyen pa thon nas sgrub pa la /
NK053('i)001:13974: sgrub pa thon nas bsnyen pa dang mi 'bral te /
NK053('i)001:13975: 'brel bar bya zhing brtson 'grus drag pos 'bad par bya'o /
NK053('i)001:13977: 4 / thugs dam bskul zhing mnyes pa'i phrin las la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:13979: dam tshig mchog gis mchod pa dag /
NK053('i)001:13980: bskul tshig dbyangs kyis de dag mnyes //
NK053('i)001:13982: kha t+wa mu lu'i sgras zur gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:13985: de la 1sbyor ba'i mchod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:13986: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i dam tshig /
NK053('i)001:13987: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub bsgrub pa'i rten /
NK053('i)001:13988: gsang ba'i mchod pa bla na med pa dbul ba'i thabs dam pa ste /
NK053('i)001:13992: de'i don 1man ngag shes rab spyan la blta bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:13993: rtags 2kyi sbyor ba'i dus su don bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:13994: gzungs ma ji lta bu la sbyar ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13995: thabs ji lta bus sbyar ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13996: sbyor ba'i mchod pas mnyes par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:13997: sbyor ba'i skyon yon bstan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:13999: la spyod pas dor ba zhes bya'o /
NK053('i)001:14001: 1 / gzungs ma ji lta bu la sbyar ba la yang gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:14002: rab 1ting nge 'dzin las su rung ba yin te /
NK053('i)001:14004: thams cad la sbyor bar shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:14005: 'bring 2lha grub pa'i thun mong gi dngos grub thob pas /
NK053('i)001:14006: lha mo pan tsi ka bkug te sbyor ba brtsam mo //
NK053('i)001:14007: tha 3 mas de ltar ma nus na yang gsang sngags kyi gdengs su gyur cing /
NK053('i)001:14008: bla ma'i gdams ngag dang khyad par can gyi spyod pa ma nor bas /
NK053('i)001:14010: shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin gyi khyad par can /
NK053('i)001:14011: bla ma dang gzungs ma gnyis ka la yod pas sbyor ba brtsams te /
NK053('i)001:14012: gzungs ma'i tshul brtag pa yang /
NK053('i)001:14013: rigs kyi yum lnga'i ma ste /
NK053('i)001:14014: gong du bstan pa ltar shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:14015: de yang dus ji tsam spyad na yang /
NK053('i)001:14016: ting nge 'dzin gyi nyams bag rnyed nas /
NK053('i)001:14017: bsnyen sgrub kyi sbyor ba la 'jug par bya'o /
NK053('i)001:14019: 2 / thabs ji lta bus sbyor ba ni /
NK053('i)001:14020: gzungs ma nges par brtags pa de /
NK053('i)001:14022: dri zhim pos lus la byug cing /
NK053('i)001:14023: gos dang rgyan gyis legs par brgyan te /
NK053('i)001:14026: kun rdzob kyi man ngag bstan par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:14027: nge la don dam par ni /
NK053('i)001:14029: me long g.ya' dag gi dgongs pa bstan la /
NK053('i)001:14030: kun rdzob tu yum kro ti shwa ri ma'i skur bsgom pa'i man ngag bstan te /
NK053('i)001:14031: bdag gis kyang byin gyis brlabs shing lha lus la gnas lngar yum lngar /
NK053('i)001:14034: 3 / de la sbyor ba'i mchod pas mnyes par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:14035: bskul tshig dang dbyangs su bcas pas lha rnams mnyes par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:14036: de yang chos ril thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel ba'i ngang du bskul ba ni /
NK053('i)001:14037: phyogs bcu stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK053('i)001:14038: sna tshogs snang ba thabs kyi yab //
NK053('i)001:14039: ma skyes pa nyid shes rab yum //
NK053('i)001:14040: dbyer med gcig pas zung du 'brel //
NK053('i)001:14041: dang h'u ni thabs kyi yab //
NK053('i)001:14042: b+h+yo dang ru lu shes rab yum //
NK053('i)001:14044: ji snyed brjod pa'i chos rnams kun //
NK053('i)001:14045: thabs dang shes rab rang bzhin te //
NK053('i)001:14046: ye shes lha dang dbyer med cing //
NK053('i)001:14047: 'bru brgyad sngags kyi yi ger gsungs //
NK053('i)001:14048: spros pas bla med mchod par 'bul //
NK053('i)001:14049: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:14050: zhes brjod pas don dang rtags kyi sgo nas /
NK053('i)001:14051: dpal chen po yab yum du gsal bar bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:14053: de yang rtsa ba'i lha dgu dang sbyar te bskul ba ni //
NK053('i)001:14055: ru ni mkha' 'gro tso'u ri ma //
NK053('i)001:14056: lu ni mkha' 'gro pra mo ha //
NK053('i)001:14057: ru ni mkha' 'gro be ta li //
NK053('i)001:14058: lu ni mkha' gro puska si //
NK053('i)001:14060: b+h+yo ni mkha' 'gro sma sha ni //
NK053('i)001:14062: kun bsdus dpal chen nyid kyi ngang //
NK053('i)001:14063: yang dag don gyi lha dgur gsal //
NK053('i)001:14064: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:14066: ji snyed du brjod pa'i don de dag kun ril /
NK053('i)001:14067: yang dag grub pa don gyi lha dgu'i ngo bor bsdus shing gsal bar bsgom /
NK053('i)001:14068: de yang dpal chen po yab yum du bsdus shing sbyor ba mdzad par bskul ba ni /
NK053('i)001:14069: ni stong nyid chos kyi sku //
NK053('i)001:14070: ru ni dpal chen he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:14071: lu ni kro ti shwa ri yum //
NK053('i)001:14072: ru ni dbyer med zung du 'brel //
NK053('i)001:14073: lu ni mi gtong 'dzin pa ste //
NK053('i)001:14074: h'u ni rab tu 'ching ba'i bdag /
NK053('i)001:14075: b+h+yo ni rab tu bsdams par mdzad //
NK053('i)001:14076: h'u gis bskyod nas bde chen 'bebs //
NK053('i)001:14077: 'bru brgyad sngags kyis sgrub pa mdzod //
NK053('i)001:14078: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u //
NK053('i)001:14080: dpal chen po yab yum phyag rgya rnam pa bzhis zung du 'brel zhing /
NK053('i)001:14081: gnyis su med par 'khril ba'i tshul du bzhugs pa'i ngang du phyi nang gi 'jig rten dang /
NK053('i)001:14082: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos ril 'dus shing dbyer med par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:14083: khyad pa du yang bde ba'i mchod par tshim par bskul ba ni /
NK053('i)001:14084: ni dpal chen yab yum sku //
NK053('i)001:14085: ru ni so sor bzhag pa ste //
NK053('i)001:14087: ru ni so sor 'khyud mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:14088: lu ni rdo rje pad+mora sbyor //
NK053('i)001:14089: h'u ni bskyed nas bde chen 'bebs //
NK053('i)001:14090: b+h+yos ni byang sems mkha' la phab //
NK053('i)001:14091: bde chen nyams su myong bar mdzad //
NK053('i)001:14092: h'u gis byang sems mkha' las spros //
NK053('i)001:14093: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i thugs dam bskul //
NK053('i)001:14094: 'gro ba rgya mtsho sgrol bar mdzod //
NK053('i)001:14095: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:14097: dpal chen yab yum thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel bar bzhugs nas /
NK053('i)001:14102: rdo rje pad+mora sbyor ba dang /
NK053('i)001:14104: gsang ba byang chub sems mkha' la dbab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14105: bde ba chen po nyams su myong ba dang /
NK053('i)001:14106: byang chub sems las 'od zer 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:14107: rgyal ba rnams la mchod pas mnyes shing thugs dam bskang /
NK053('i)001:14108: 'gro ba rigs drug 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las bsgral te /
NK053('i)001:14109: chos nyid kyi skam sa la bton /
NK053('i)001:14110: tshur 'dus pas ye shes kyi byin rlabs dang /
NK053('i)001:14112: gzi mdongs ril bsdus te byang chub sems la thim pas /
NK053('i)001:14113: mu tig lta bur gsal ba las /
NK053('i)001:14116: slob ma la dbang bskur ba dang gsum du shes par bya'o /
NK053('i)001:14118: 4 / sbyor ba'i skyon yon bstan pa ni /
NK053('i)001:14120: gsang ba'i mchod pa bcag pas gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i dam tshig nyams te /
NK053('i)001:14121: bde bar gshegs pa dang mkha' 'gro ma'i bka' chad 'ong ste /
NK053('i)001:14122: byung dor byed pa'i sems can gyi rigs su skyes nas /
NK053('i)001:14123: de nas kyang dmyal bar 'gro bar bshad do //
NK053('i)001:14127: mkha' 'gro mas 'go ba la sogs pa 'byung ngo //
NK053('i)001:14129: gsang sngags chen po'i sgrub pa la //
NK053('i)001:14130: brtul shugs bskyed de sbyor ba btsal //
NK053('i)001:14131: bskul tshig dbyangs kyi mchod pa yis //
NK053('i)001:14132: rgyal ba mnyes shing 'khor ba sgrol //
NK053('i)001:14133: bka' bzhin sbyor ba ma brtsams na //
NK053('i)001:14134: ma nus skyes nas dmyal bar 'gro //
NK053('i)001:14137: dam rdzas 2kyi mchod pa bya zhing ye shes lha'i thugs dam bskul ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:14138: dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa dag /
NK053('i)001:14139: bskul tshig dbyang kyis de dag mnyes //
NK053('i)001:14141: ka p+aa la mtshan dang ldan pa lcang lo can gyi nang du /
NK053('i)001:14142: gong gi dam tshig mchog gi mchod pa /
NK053('i)001:14145: rgyu lnga bsgral ba'i rak+ta dang /
NK053('i)001:14147: sha chen po la sogs pa bsres te mchod pa bya ba yang /
NK053('i)001:14149: grangs pa sgra'i mchod pa rnam pa mang pos kyang bskul /
NK053('i)001:14150: thugs dam bskul ba'i don dang ldan pa'i tshig dang /
NK053('i)001:14151: dbyangs gre 'gyur gyi de'u bcas pa rnams kyis /
NK053('i)001:14152: dkyil 'khor rnam pa gsum dbyer med par byas pa'i
NK053('i)001:14153: lha de dag mnyes shing dgyes pa bskyed par bya
NK053('i)001:14154: ste / de yang ston pa rdo rje sems dpas gsungs pa'i tshig /
NK053('i)001:14155: he ru ka'i gal po las 'di skad du /
NK053('i)001:14157: don gyis na bstod pa ste /
NK053('i)001:14158: gtso bo yab la bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:14160: ke'u ri brgyad la bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:14161: seng ha brgyad la bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:14162: sgo ma bzhi la bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:14163: dbang phyug ma la bstod pa'o //
NK053('i)001:14165: dang po yab la bstod pa ni /
NK053('i)001:14166: mi gnas ye shes chos skur dag pa las //
NK053('i)001:14167: rtogs pa 'bar ba'i ye shes phyag rgya ni //
NK053('i)001:14168: shin tu mi bzad khro bo'i tshul ston cing //
NK053('i)001:14169: gdug pa'i rgyan dang drag po'i skur snang ba //
NK053('i)001:14170: ya mtshan rmad byung khams gsum 'jigs rngams pa'i //
NK053('i)001:14171: dug gsum rnam dag khams gsum zhal du shar //
NK053('i)001:14172: thugs rje thabs kyi rgyu drug phyag drug rdzogs //
NK053('i)001:14173: 'bar ba'i klong na mkha' 'gro'i sprin tshogs rnams //
NK053('i)001:14174: gar dgu'i rgyan dang mi bzad cho 'phrul gyis //
NK053('i)001:14175: bdud tshogs yud kyis 'dul mdzad rmad po che //
NK053('i)001:14176: dug lnga ma spangs rnam grol lam du mdzad //
NK053('i)001:14177: gzhan yang thabs tshul mtha' yas rgya mtsho yis //
NK053('i)001:14178: ji ltar 'dul zhig sku gsum cir yang ston //
NK053('i)001:14179: dus gsum rgyal ba'i yab mchog chen po ste //
NK053('i)001:14180: thugs rje'i yon tan yid bzhin 'byung ba'i gter //
NK053('i)001:14181: 'gro ba rnams kyi dpal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK053('i)001:14182: gnyis pa yum la bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:14183: khro mo dbang phyug sku la nyer mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:14184: dus gsum rgyal ba kun bskyed thams cad yum //
NK053('i)001:14185: 'khor ba mi spangs mya ngan mi 'da' bas //
NK053('i)001:14186: sgyu ma lta bu'i sku mchog mnga' brnyes pas //
NK053('i)001:14187: rgyal ba rgya mtsho ma lus mkha' la bskul //
NK053('i)001:14188: rdo rje dbyings kyi dam tshig bde mchog rab //
NK053('i)001:14189: nam mkha'i spyod yul yid bzhin bsam rdzogs 'grub //
NK053('i)001:14190: srid gsum mtha' dag dbyings dang mnyam par sbyor //
NK053('i)001:14191: kro ti shwa ri phyag rgyar gsal 'bar ma //
NK053('i)001:14192: 'bar ba'i sku mchog mnyes phyir sku la 'khril //
NK053('i)001:14193: yum gyur dbyings phyug sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK053('i)001:14194: bdag gis dug gsum sgrib pa kun spangs pa'i //
NK053('i)001:14195: dug gsum ma spangs sku gsum lhun gyis grub //
NK053('i)001:14196: yang dag grub mchog bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:14197: nyid kyis zhal 'ches grub pa'i 'bras bu dang //
NK053('i)001:14198: bdag cag las kyi 'bras bu mchis par mdzod //
NK053('i)001:14199: gsum pa ke'u ri ma la bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:14200: bcom ldan khro rgyal khrag 'thung chen po yis //
NK053('i)001:14201: sku gsung thugs las sprul pa'i mkha' 'gro rnams //
NK053('i)001:14202: drag shul tshul gyis 'gro ba'i don mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:14203: gdug pa'i tshogs dang gnod sbyin cha lugs 'chang //
NK053('i)001:14204: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad zhe sdang sku //
NK053('i)001:14205: bdag rtog phung po 'joms pa'i ti ra 'phyar //
NK053('i)001:14206: byams pa'i thugs kyis gnyis med don rtogs pas //
NK053('i)001:14207: ye shes 'od stong 'bar ba'i ke'u ri ma //
NK053('i)001:14208: zhi gnas rtse gcig stong pa'i gzhu brdungs shing //
NK053('i)001:14209: lhag mthong shes rab gcod pa'i mda' bkang nas //
NK053('i)001:14210: nyon mongs bdud 'joms ye shes dbyings rum du //
NK053('i)001:14211: dug gsum 'joms mdzad thugs rje tso'u ri ma //
NK053('i)001:14212: 'dod pa'i rdul bral chags med pad+ma'i sku //
NK053('i)001:14213: dga' byed dregs pa'i bdud 'joms rgyal ba'i rtags //
NK053('i)001:14214: chos la dbang bsgyur chu srin rgyal mtshan 'phyar //
NK053('i)001:14215: rnam rtog za byed khrag 'thung pra mo ha //
NK053('i)001:14216: phrin las rnam bzhi cis 'dul btang snyoms sku //
NK053('i)001:14217: thabs kyis khro bar mdzad cing gar stabs can //
NK053('i)001:14218: 'chi bdag bdud kyi sde 'joms ye shes rdo rje 'phyar //
NK053('i)001:14219: shes rab dbyings la sbyor mdzad be ta li //
NK053('i)001:14220: ye shes nyi ma'i ma rig mun bsal phyir //
NK053('i)001:14221: nga rtog khrag mtsho 'khyil ba'i gting rum du //
NK053('i)001:14222: thar med rgyud drug 'khyams pa'i phung po lnga //
NK053('i)001:14223: bde chen dbyings su 'dren byed puk+ka si //
NK053('i)001:14224: ye shes dbyings nyid ye nas gnyis med phyir //
NK053('i)001:14225: thabs kyi rdo rjes b+han dmar dkrugs shing gsol //
NK053('i)001:14226: sprin med mkha' la nyi zla'i gzugs brnyan bzhin //
NK053('i)001:14227: ye shes 'od stong 'bar ba'i kasma ri //
NK053('i)001:14228: 'jigs byed dur khrod tshogs rnams gzhom pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:14229: thugs rje'i tshems kyis rnam rtog sgo 'byed cing //
NK053('i)001:14230: drag shul tshul dang rngams pa'i stobs kyis su //
NK053('i)001:14231: nyon mongs yid 'phrog za byed sma sha ni //
NK053('i)001:14232: log 'dren bgegs kyi tshogs rnams gshig pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:14233: thabs kyis ngag sha'i tshul du sgrol mdzad ma //
NK053('i)001:14234: ye shes spu gri 'bar ba'i tshems brdar nas //
NK053('i)001:14235: gdug byed lnga phung 'joms pa'i tsan+d+ha li //
NK053('i)001:14236: mkha' 'gro ma spyi la bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:14237: kun kyang ye shes 'bar ba'i klong dkyil nas //
NK053('i)001:14238: dgongs spyod rgya mtsho dpag gis mi lang phyir //
NK053('i)001:14239: sku mdog phyag mtshan cir yang ma nges te //
NK053('i)001:14240: phrin las rgya mtshos ji ltar 'dul ba bzhin //
NK053('i)001:14241: dur khrod 'bar ba'i gnas mchog dam pa 'dir //
NK053('i)001:14242: bdud rtsi dmar gyi ar+g+ham rgya mtshor bskyil //
NK053('i)001:14243: zhing chen gsar rnying tshogs kyi longs spyod dang //
NK053('i)001:14244: byang chub sems dang m+aam sa rak+ta dang //
NK053('i)001:14245: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba 'di bzhes la //
NK053('i)001:14246: thugs rje'i dbang gis 'dir gshegs mchod pa bzhes //
NK053('i)001:14247: bdag gis bcol ba'i las rnams grub par mdzod //
NK053('i)001:14248: bzhi pa sing ha me la bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:14249: gser mdog gzi 'phags rdo rje'i thugs las sprul //
NK053('i)001:14250: seng ge'i skad kyis bdud dpung 'joms par mdzad //
NK053('i)001:14251: drag shul tshul gyis zhing chen sprug cing gsol //
NK053('i)001:14252: 'gro drug bsgral phyir rtsal 'phags sing ha ma //
NK053('i)001:14253: dbang mchog yon tan yid bzhin sku las sprul //
NK053('i)001:14254: sku mdog dmar dwangs byin chags stag gi zhal //
NK053('i)001:14255: gsang ba'i longs spyod zhing chen nyid la gzigs //
NK053('i)001:14256: 'chi bdag bdud kyi sde 'joms b+y+aa kri ma //
NK053('i)001:14257: dri med rnam dag pad+ma'i gsung las sprul //
NK053('i)001:14258: sku mdog dmar nag byin chags wa yi gdong //
NK053('i)001:14259: gsang ba'i longs spyod zhing chen 'dral zhi za //
NK053('i)001:14260: log 'dren bgegs kyi tshogs 'joms sri la ma //
NK053('i)001:14261: don grub rdo rje las kyi rigs las sprul //
NK053('i)001:14262: sku mdog mthing nag spyang mo 'jigs pa'i zhal //
NK053('i)001:14263: drag shul rngams pas zhing chen 'dral zhing za //
NK053('i)001:14264: rdo rje'i las kun grub mdzad shwa na ma //
NK053('i)001:14265: ye shes thugs kyis phyogs bcur khyab pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:14266: bya rgod gzugs kyis rdzu 'phrul mthu dang ldan //
NK053('i)001:14267: 'khor ba mi spongs mya ngan mi 'da' ba'i //
NK053('i)001:14268: thabs kyi gri bsnams khrag 'thung kri ta ma //
NK053('i)001:14269: dur khrod spyod pas 'gro drug bsgral ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:14270: log rtog dbang po kang ka'i mchus 'byin cing //
NK053('i)001:14271: thabs kyi gri bsnams zhing chen phrag la 'gel //
NK053('i)001:14272: 'jig rten bsgral phyir phrag dog kang ka ma //
NK053('i)001:14273: zhe sdang bag chags rtsad nas bcad pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:14274: ye shes mtshon bsnams rgyud phreng khrag la mos //
NK053('i)001:14275: rnam rtog rdul gyis ma gos bya rog gdong //
NK053('i)001:14276: yon tan yid bzhin bdag nyid khwa khwa ma //
NK053('i)001:14277: don dam gnyis med nges pa'i don rtogs shing //
NK053('i)001:14278: cir yang 'gyur ba'i kha dog sna tshogs 'chang //
NK053('i)001:14279: 'gro drug bsgral phyir lcags kyu rno bsnams shing //
NK053('i)001:14280: mi bzad thod khrag 'thung ba'i hu lu ma //
NK053('i)001:14281: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba'i klong dkyil na //
NK053('i)001:14282: kun kyang mi bzad khrag 'thung rngams pa'i sku //
NK053('i)001:14283: thod rlon pags chen khrag gis sku la brgyan //
NK053('i)001:14284: phrin las rdzogs mdzad grub pa'i tshul bzhin stsol //
NK053('i)001:14285: 'gro ba'i don phyir sna tshogs skur ston cing //
NK053('i)001:14286: zhing chen gsar rnying tshogs la longs spyod ma //
NK053('i)001:14287: dur khrod chen po'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:14288: dur khrod 'bar ba'i bdud rtsi zhing chen byang chub
NK053('i)001:14289: dam rdzas thugs rje'i bdag gis lnga pa sgo ma
NK053('i)001:14290: bzhi'i bstod pa / khams gsum 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal ci 'dra bar //
NK053('i)001:14291: byams mgon khyed kyi thugs kyis gdul slad du //
NK053('i)001:14292: rnam par rtog pa'i bag chags sbyang ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:14293: myur du sgrol mdzad rta gdong lcags kyu ma //
NK053('i)001:14294: sngon gyi smon lam thugs dam che mnga' bas //
NK053('i)001:14295: 'khor bar yun ring 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal la //
NK053('i)001:14296: rtag tu grogs mdzad skyo ngal mi mnga' ste //
NK053('i)001:14297: yid bzhin re skong phag gdong zhags pa ma //
NK053('i)001:14298: thams cad mkhyen pa'i nyi zla zhal mnga' bas //
NK053('i)001:14299: rmongs pa'i mun sel bag chags bsreg pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:14300: 'khor ba'i rgyud mkhyen cis 'dul nges ston pa'o //
NK053('i)001:14301: blo gros mig byed nyi zla lcags sgrog ma //
NK053('i)001:14302: mya ngan mi 'da' 'khor ba mthar thug la //
NK053('i)001:14303: khyed kyi thugs rjes bdag la rtag tu dgongs //
NK053('i)001:14304: phrin las rgya mtshos khams gsum 'tsho mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:14305: ded dpon mchog nyid thal byed dril bu ma //
NK053('i)001:14306: rab tu mi bzad khro mo'i tshul ston cing //
NK053('i)001:14307: 'bar ba'i sku mthong tshangs pa'i gsung sgrogs shing //
NK053('i)001:14308: gnod byed bgegs kyi snying ni 'gems par byed //
NK053('i)001:14309: phrin las sgrol mdzad thugs rjes bdag la dgongs /
NK053('i)001:14310: khams gsum 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal mi bzad pas //
NK053('i)001:14311: byams mgon khyed kyi thugs rjes bdag la dgongs //
NK053('i)001:14312: dur khrod 'bar ba'i gnas bdud rtsi zhing chen byang
NK053('i)001:14313: chub dam rdzas thugs rje'i bdag gis drug pa dbang
NK053('i)001:14315: rngams pa'i tshul gyis srin mo'i gzugs 'dzin cing //
NK053('i)001:14316: thod rus gdug pa'i 'bru mar zas su za //
NK053('i)001:14317: srid pa'i sems can khrag snying khrag mtshor gsol //
NK053('i)001:14318: dbang drag las mdzad ma nu rak+sha si //
NK053('i)001:14319: sdug bsngal mya ngan 'das rtogs tshangs ma'i gzugs //
NK053('i)001:14320: tshad med bzhi rdzogs rtags kyi dbu bzhir ldan //
NK053('i)001:14321: zhal bzhi smrang 'don gling bzhi bkra shis ldan //
NK053('i)001:14322: gti mug yid bzhin rin chen pra ma ni //
NK053('i)001:14323: thams cad mnyam pa nyid rtogs rigs mchog ma //
NK053('i)001:14324: ma rig dug gsum 'joms mdzad dpal rtse bsnams //
NK053('i)001:14325: bud med chags tshul dbang mdzad dka' bzlog ma //
NK053('i)001:14326: chags pa'i skyon bral lha chen re tri ma //
NK053('i)001:14327: thams cad sgyu ma bzhin du rtogs mkhyen cing //
NK053('i)001:14328: 'brel ba'i thugs rje 'jig rten gsum la spyod //
NK053('i)001:14329: phrin las rgya mtsho sgrol ba'i bzhad chen can //
NK053('i)001:14330: 'khor ba'i rgyun gcod drag po be sna be //
NK053('i)001:14331: 'du byed mi rtag dril bu'i sgra ltar mkhyen //
NK053('i)001:14332: rtag tu gzhon tshul 'khor bar ji snyed bzhugs //
NK053('i)001:14333: nyon mongs tha ba 'bigs pa'i mdung thung 'phen //
NK053('i)001:14334: gzhon tshul chags pa'i dbang mdzad ko'u r+ai ma //
NK053('i)001:14335: rdo rje'i las mdzad skyin gyi bla na med //
NK053('i)001:14336: lha yi rgyal srid chos la dbang bsgyur zhing //
NK053('i)001:14337: chos dbyings rgyas mdzad mi dmigs sku mdog dkar //
NK053('i)001:14338: gsod byed rdo rje lce 'bebs in+d+ra ma //
NK053('i)001:14339: 'gro ba'i don mdzad mi 'gyur sku mdog gnag /
NK053('i)001:14340: srid gsum 'joms mdzad tri shul gdegs pa dang //
NK053('i)001:14341: thugs rje'i shugs kyis 'dren mdzad lcags kyu bsnams //
NK053('i)001:14342: 'khor bar thugs rje 'char phyir tsa ka ha //
NK053('i)001:14343: byams pa'i thugs rjes dbang mdzad sku dmog dmar //
NK053('i)001:14344: b+han+d+ha snod yangs bcud kyi rgya mtsho las //
NK053('i)001:14345: rngams pa'i zhal du dug gsum 'dren mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:14346: sdug bsngal dbyings su skong mdzad badz+ra ping ka la //
NK053('i)001:14347: 'jig rten 'dul mdzad khro mo mchog tu mkhyen //
NK053('i)001:14348: byams pa'i thugs rjes 'khor ba'i rgyud 'dzin cing //
NK053('i)001:14349: 'dam skyes pad ltar 'khor ba'i sku 'khrungs kyang //
NK053('i)001:14350: chags pa'i skyon bral dbang mdzad a mri tha //
NK053('i)001:14351: zhi ba'i las ni gsod pa'i mchog tu mkhyen //
NK053('i)001:14352: zla ba'i mdog ltar yon tan mthar phyin sku //
NK053('i)001:14353: gdung ba'i nad sel 'jig rten sgrol mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:14354: gdon tshogs thams cad stong mdzad so'u me //
NK053('i)001:14355: dbyug pas 'tshog pa 'dra bar gzhan med mkhyen //
NK053('i)001:14356: thabs kyis ma 'dres phrin las ljang khu'i mdog /
NK053('i)001:14357: nan dbang drag shul spyod pa'i tshul ston cing //
NK053('i)001:14358: dregs byed spyi nas 'joms byed da na ham //
NK053('i)001:14359: log par lta ba 'joms mdzad spyan gyi mchog /
NK053('i)001:14360: skye ba'i dbugs 'phrog skye 'gro'i khrag mtsho gsol //
NK053('i)001:14361: las mdzad chags tshul gser gyi sked bcings can //
NK053('i)001:14362: drag mo rngams tshul glog 'gyu rak+sha si //
NK053('i)001:14363: phreng ba rgyan gyi nang na mchog tu mdzes //
NK053('i)001:14364: rgyun gyi thugs rjes ba su rgyu zhags gsol //
NK053('i)001:14365: chags med zhing du khams gsum 'dren mdzad ma //
NK053('i)001:14366: rgyun gyi thugs rjes sgrol mdzad bak+sha si //
NK053('i)001:14367: byams pa'i zhags pas 'khor ba'i rgyud 'dzin cing //
NK053('i)001:14368: chags pa'i tshul gyis don mdzad ra mgo can //
NK053('i)001:14369: gang la ci 'dul de la der ston pa //
NK053('i)001:14370: re ba yid bzhin skong mdzad tsa ka la //
NK053('i)001:14371: mtshon cha dbyug pa mchog du mkhyen pas na //
NK053('i)001:14372: gtun bus gdug pa ma lus 'dul mdzad de //
NK053('i)001:14373: nor gyi tshogs rnass ma lus 'phrog byed cing /
NK053('i)001:14374: khams gsum nor gyis rgyas mdzad tre'u tri ma //
NK053('i)001:14375: ra ro 'dra bar dpa' bo gzhan med mkhyen //
NK053('i)001:14376: chos rnams gnyis med don rtogs rab tu myos //
NK053('i)001:14377: nyon mongs tha ba rlog pa'i gshol bsnams shing //
NK053('i)001:14378: dge ba'i lo tog bskyed mdzad ru ram ti //
NK053('i)001:14379: brtan pas gzhan pham mdzad pa'i dpal ba'i mchog /
NK053('i)001:14380: ma lus gsod byed las la 'jug mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:14381: snyems pa mi mnga' 'gro don gcig tu spyod //
NK053('i)001:14382: gsod byed drag mdzad e ka tsa ra ma //
NK053('i)001:14383: bud med chags pas 'gro ba dbang du mdzad //
NK053('i)001:14384: thams cad ma lus 'gugs byed dge ba'i las //
NK053('i)001:14386: thugs rjes zhen pa'i ma nor ha ra ma //
NK053('i)001:14387: khrag las zas gzhan med par rtogs mkhyen cing //
NK053('i)001:14388: gdon rnams bskrad pa'i las rnams rbod gtong can //
NK053('i)001:14389: mi zad mdzod ldan gser gyi bum pa bsnams //
NK053('i)001:14390: sdug bsngal re skong khrag 'thung si ti ka /
NK053('i)001:14391: reg bya'i sems ni rlung gi khams te mchog /
NK053('i)001:14392: srid gsum dbugs kyi srog sbyin tshe 'phel ma //
NK053('i)001:14393: bde gshegs dbyings su rgyu drug sgrol mdzad ma /
NK053('i)001:14394: khams gsum gnas nas skyob mdzad pa ya be //
