NK053('i)001:14395: ston pa'i bka' dang rang gi dam bcas gnyis //
NK053('i)001:14396: mi 'da' ma grub bar du brtan par bzhugs //
NK053('i)001:14397: dam tshig srog gis sems can don mdzad ma //
NK053('i)001:14398: gti mug mun sel kum b+hi shwa ra ma //
NK053('i)001:14399: snyigs ma lnga brgya dus kyi tha ma la //
NK053('i)001:14400: srid gsum 'khor ba'i sems can gdul dka' ste //
NK053('i)001:14401: gsod pa nyid na las kyis 'dul bar mdzad //
NK053('i)001:14402: sdug bsngal dbyings su sgrol mdzad ma ra na //
NK053('i)001:14403: gzi byin can ni me yi khams te mchog /
NK053('i)001:14405: 'bar ba mchog gis gdug pa ma lus bsregs //
NK053('i)001:14406: rab brjid bskal pa'i dus mtha'i tshul ston pa'i //
NK053('i)001:14407: lhag mthong ye shes 'bar 'phro ag+ne ma //
NK053('i)001:14408: skye ba dag la skye shi rtsad gcod cing //
NK053('i)001:14409: nyon mongs tha ba rlog mdzad phag gi dbu //
NK053('i)001:14410: 'og gi phyogs nas srid gsum stobs kyis spor //
NK053('i)001:14411: skye shi rtsad gcod za byed ba ra hi //
NK053('i)001:14412: 'chi bdag thams cad gnas ma 'phos pa mkhyen //
NK053('i)001:14413: thams cad ma lus dam nyams 'chi bdag mdzad //
NK053('i)001:14414: dam tshig sru ba'i 'chi bdag bzlog mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:14415: lung gi dur khrod dbang mdzad tsa mun+t+ri //
NK053('i)001:14416: 'jigs las lhag pa'i bgegs ni gzhan med mkhyen //
NK053('i)001:14417: stong phrag brgyad cu'i bgegs la mnga' mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:14418: sna chen glang snas bdud rtsi gi hang thogs //
NK053('i)001:14419: sdug bsngal nad gsod mdzang pa'i u da na //
NK053('i)001:14420: chu las lhag pa'i zas ni gzhan med mkhyen //
NK053('i)001:14421: nor gyi tshogs rnas ma lus 'phrog byed cing //
NK053('i)001:14422: gdug pa 'dul mdzad dug gdong sbrul zhags bsnams //
NK053('i)001:14423: zhi gnas ting 'dzin dbang sdud ba ru na //
NK053('i)001:14424: sku gsung thugs yon phrin las mthar gtugs te //
NK053('i)001:14425: stong pa'i sgras bskul 'gro ba'i rgyud las 'bebs //
NK053('i)001:14426: so so'i skad du chos kyi sgra sgrogs pas //
NK053('i)001:14427: bag chags spyod mdzad lam po da ra ma //
NK053('i)001:14428: dpal chen 'jigs byed 'bar ba'i dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:14429: 'jigs rten khams kyi ma mo dam la btags //
NK053('i)001:14430: dbang phyug tshogs bcas ming btags rdo rje byin //
NK053('i)001:14431: de tshe so sos khas blangs dam bcas pa //
NK053('i)001:14432: ma sring mdza' mo bran mor khas blangs shing //
NK053('i)001:14433: bla med mchog gi theg chen srung ba dang //
NK053('i)001:14434: rjes su sgrub pa'i rnal 'byor skyong ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:14435: mi mthun phyogs kyi dgra bgegs bsgral ba dang //
NK053('i)001:14436: gdug pa bzlog cing tshe dgug bsrung ngo zhes //
NK053('i)001:14437: khyed kyi khas blangs dam bcas de min nam //
NK053('i)001:14438: dam bcas bzhin du thugs dam rgyud bskul nas //
NK053('i)001:14439: bdud rtsi rak+ta dmar gyi ar+g+ham dang //
NK053('i)001:14440: sha rus la sogs zas kyi longs spyod kyis //
NK053('i)001:14441: ma tshogs dbang phyug thugs dam bskang gyur te //
NK053('i)001:14442: nongs bgyis 'gal 'khrul chag nyams mthol bshags na //
NK053('i)001:14443: grub pa'i 'bras bu dus 'dir tshul bzhin stsol //
NK053('i)001:14445: rnal 'byor pas le lo dang gnyid dang chang dbang du mi gtong bar brtson 'grus kyis /
NK053('i)001:14447: lha re rer snying po brgya brgyad dang /
NK053('i)001:14449: mchod par bcas te dbul lo //
NK053('i)001:14452: phrin las bcol ba kun bstod pa 'di las shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:14453: 'khor bcas mchod pa rdzogs nas ni //
NK053('i)001:14458: dpal khrag 'thung la ke'u seng sgo ma dang dbang phyug ma dang bcas pa kho nar zad de /
NK053('i)001:14467: yang phur skyong ba'i srung ma rnams kyang /
NK053('i)001:14468: zla gsang thig le'i rgyud dang /
NK053('i)001:14469: rtag chen g.yab mo'i rgyud la sogs pa nas 'byung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:14470: lug so so'i bskul tshig zab mos bskul zhing mchod do //
NK053('i)001:14473: mchod pa kun gyi tha mar ni /
NK053('i)001:14477: de la tshogs mchod gzhung bzhin du 'bul nas /
NK053('i)001:14478: zos pa'i lhag ma rnams bsdus te /
NK053('i)001:14479: dgong mo dmar thag chod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14482: skya rengs shar ba'i dus su /
NK053('i)001:14483: he ru ka las kyi bzlas pas dbang du bsdus la /
NK053('i)001:14484: zhes pa don gyi lhag chog byed pa'o //
NK053('i)001:14486: dbang phyug ma la sogs pa mchod de /
NK053('i)001:14491: phreng ba khro zhal du byas nas yi dam gyi lhar bsgom ste gral srung du gzhug go //
NK053('i)001:14492: 'chag pa'i dus su rgyal po'am rgyal thebs res dbang gzugs /
NK053('i)001:14493: mar 'gro ba re la bsrung ba re re bya /
NK053('i)001:14494: yar 'ong ba re la bdud rtsi 'khyil ba'i sngags kyis mtshams bcad /
NK053('i)001:14497: de nas yang mchod pa de ma thag tu bshams te /
NK053('i)001:14498: mtshams dang las rim gzhung bsrang ste /
NK053('i)001:14499: 'dzab dang mchod pa la sogs pa rdzogs par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:14501: lha mnyes par bya ba'i skabs su /
NK053('i)001:14502: 5 sbyor ba dang sgrol ba'i mchod pas lha mnyes par bya ba'i phrin las la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:14503: bdag don lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i phyir sbyor ba'i mchod pa bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14504: gzhan don lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i phyir sgrol ba'i mchod pa bstan pa'o //
NK053('i)001:14505: de gnyis re re la yang /
NK053('i)001:14506: bdag don dang gzhan don gnyis /
NK053('i)001:14507: shes rab dang ting nge 'dzin gnyis /
NK053('i)001:14508: lta ba dang spyod pa gnyis /
NK053('i)001:14509: don dang rtags rnam pa gnyis te brgyad tshang la /
NK053('i)001:14512: dmigs med stobs kyi gdengs can gyis //
NK053('i)001:14514: dngos kyang mchod pa'i rdzas su bsngo //
NK053('i)001:14515: zhes bya ba yan chad kyi tshig rkang bco lnga po 'di la /
NK053('i)001:14516: kha ta kha lu'i sgra las drangs na /
NK053('i)001:14517: dkyus gcig la zur gnyis par ston pa ste /
NK053('i)001:14518: 1 de la bdag gi don lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:14519: sbyor ba'i mchod pa bstan pa la /
NK053('i)001:14521: bdag nyid ting nge 'dzin gyis gzengs bstod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14522: yum brtag cing byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14526: bdag nyid ting nge 'dzin gyis gzengs bstod pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:14527: dmigs med stobs kyi gdengs can gyis //
NK053('i)001:14528: sku mchog 'bar ba'i tshul du bsam //
NK053('i)001:14530: don dam par dmigs su med pa'i chos nyid la /
NK053('i)001:14531: rig pa'i ye shes kyi stobs bskyed nas /
NK053('i)001:14532: yang dag pa'i don la lta ba'i gdengs yod pa can gyis /
NK053('i)001:14533: kun rdzob tu dpal chen po'i sku /
NK053('i)001:14534: theg pa kun las khyad par mchog tu gyur pa /
NK053('i)001:14535: zhal gsum la phyag drug pa zhabs bzhi pa /
NK053('i)001:14536: 'jigs byed ye shes kyi sku la dur khrod kyi rgyan gyis sgeg pa /
NK053('i)001:14537: 'dul byed ye shes kyi mtshon cha phyag na bsnams shing /
NK053('i)001:14538: ye shes kyi me dpung 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs shing /
NK053('i)001:14539: sku gsung thugs phyag rgya'i ting nge 'dzin shin tu gsal ba'i tshul ni /
NK053('i)001:14540: me long la gzugs brnyan shar ba ltar bsam par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:14541: yum 2brtag cing byin gyis brlabs pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:14542: bsgrub rdzas de dag byin gyis brlabs /
NK053('i)001:14543: khams gsum khrag tu dmigs nas ni //
NK053('i)001:14544: dur khrod kun tu khyab par bsam //
NK053('i)001:14546: de yang yum brtag pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14547: byin gyis brlab pa gnyis las /
NK053('i)001:14548: de la yum 1brtag pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:14551: de la gsang sngags ma h+aa yo ga'i bsgrub pa'i lugs 'di /
NK053('i)001:14552: bsgrub pa'i rdzas yum shes rab ma la brten te sgrub par lung las gsungs pas /
NK053('i)001:14553: lha mo gnas nas bkug te bsgrub //
NK053('i)001:14554: yang na klu yi bu mo dgug /
NK053('i)001:14555: tha na mi yi bu mo 'am //
NK053('i)001:14556: de la bsgrubs te byang sems rdzas //
NK053('i)001:14557: phab nas mchod blangs byas gyur na //
NK053('i)001:14560: de yang rnal 'byor pa ting nge 'dzin las su rung bas ni /
NK053('i)001:14562: thams cad la sbyor shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:14563: 'bring lha grub pa thun mong gi dngos grub thob pas /
NK053('i)001:14564: dga' ldan gyi gnas nas lha mo pan tsika dgug pa'am /
NK053('i)001:14565: rgya mtsho'i gting nas klu yi bu mo yid 'ong dga' dgug pa ste /
NK053('i)001:14566: de dang gnyis bsgrubs te sbyor ba brtsam mo //
NK053('i)001:14567: thams de ltar ma nus na yang /
NK053('i)001:14568: mi'i bu mo la brtag pa bya ste /
NK053('i)001:14570: rdo rje rigs kyi gzungs ma ni //
NK053('i)001:14571: zhi ba'i tshul dgu ldan pa ste //
NK053('i)001:14572: mnyen lcug 'khril ldem gzhon tshul can //
NK053('i)001:14574: dkar dmar mdangs ldan dung mo'i mdog /
NK053('i)001:14575: mdun nas bltas na dgye dgye 'dra //
NK053('i)001:14576: rgyab nas bltas na rgu rgu 'dra //
NK053('i)001:14578: smra na ngag snyan snyan par 'gro //
NK053('i)001:14580: rdo rje sems dpa'i gzungs mar shis //
NK053('i)001:14581: de ni bsgrub rdzas dam pa ste //
NK053('i)001:14582: de la rtag tu sbyor ba bya'o //
NK053('i)001:14584: de la byin gyis 2barlaba pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:14587: bdag dbang du byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14588: rgyan gyis byin gyis brlabs pa /
NK053('i)001:14589: ting nge 'dzin gyis byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK053('i)001:14590: de la bdag 1 dbang du byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:14591: mi'i bu mo gang 'dra bar btsal te brtag pa byas te /
NK053('i)001:14592: pha ma la rin gyis bslus te bdag gir bya ba'am /
NK053('i)001:14593: de brid cing kha drangs te bdag gir bya ba'o //
NK053('i)001:14594: rgyan 2 byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:14595: de'i lus khrus legs par byas te /
NK053('i)001:14602: tsan+d+hana gyis byug cing dri zhim por bya'o //
NK053('i)001:14603: de'i lus dar dang ras dang /
NK053('i)001:14604: gos legs par spud pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14605: mgo rgyan dang rke rgyan gser dang g.yus brgyan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14608: rkang gdub kyis mdzes par spras pa'o //
NK053('i)001:14609: ting 3nge 'dzin gyis byin gyis brlab pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:14610: khams gsum khrag tu dmigs nas ni //
NK053('i)001:14611: dur khrod kun tu khyab par bsam //
NK053('i)001:14613: bu mo gsum po gang yang rung ba de //
NK053('i)001:14614: bdag dpal chen po gsal ba'i g.yon du /
NK053('i)001:14615: yum kro ti shwa ri ma'i sku bskyed de /
NK053('i)001:14616: lus dang grib ma'i tshul lta bur snang ba de /
NK053('i)001:14617: lus phyag rgya mo'i sku de ni gzugs khams dang /
NK053('i)001:14618: ngag tu 'bru brgyad sgra mthar stong pa ni gzugs med pa'i khams /
NK053('i)001:14619: yid rang byung gi sems ma dang bcas pa ni 'dod pa'i khams so //
NK053('i)001:14622: bdag gis yum la dbyangs tshig 'dis bskul te //
NK053('i)001:14623: phyogs bcu stong gi 'jig rten na //
NK053('i)001:14624: sna tshogs snang ba thabs kyi yab //
NK053('i)001:14625: ma skyes pa nyid shes rab ste //
NK053('i)001:14626: ye shes lha dang gnyis med cing //
NK053('i)001:14627: 'bru brgyad sngags kyi yi ger gsungs //
NK053('i)001:14628: spros pas bla med mchod par 'bul //
NK053('i)001:14629: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:14631: don chos nyid skye 'gags med pa'i klong nas /
NK053('i)001:14632: rtags rig pa'i ye shes dpal chen po yab yum du gsal ba'i thugs ga nas /
NK053('i)001:14633: ye shes kyi 'od zer phar 'phro ba dang /
NK053('i)001:14635: yab yum so sor sgrib pa sbyangs nas /
NK053('i)001:14636: ye shes kyi skur gsal ba de /
NK053('i)001:14637: ye shes la ye shes chags pa'i rtags su /
NK053('i)001:14638: lus ngag yid gsum 'dod chags cher g.yos pas /
NK053('i)001:14640: zhes pa'i dur khrod kun tu khyab par bsam //
NK053('i)001:14642: dbyangs tshigs 'dis byin gyis brlabs te /
NK053('i)001:14644: ru ni mkha' 'gro tso'u ri ma //
NK053('i)001:14645: lu ni mkha' 'gro pra mo ha //
NK053('i)001:14646: ru ni mkha' 'gro be ta li //
NK053('i)001:14647: lu ni mkha' 'gro pu ka si //
NK053('i)001:14649: b+h+yo ni mkha' 'gro sma sha ni //
NK053('i)001:14650: h'u ni mkha' 'gro tsa n+d+ha li //
NK053('i)001:14651: kun 'dus dpal chen yab yum dang //
NK053('i)001:14652: yang dag don gyi lha dgur gsal //
NK053('i)001:14653: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:14655: yab kyi thugs ka nas ru lu 'bru brgyad yum la spros la /
NK053('i)001:14656: yum gyi gnas brgyad du ru lu ru lu 'bru
NK053('i)001:14657: brgyad las lha mo ke'u ri ma brgyad kyi skur
NK053('i)001:14658: gsal ba yang / rnam par shes pa'i tshogs brgyad ye shes rol pa'i skur shar bas /
NK053('i)001:14659: phyi nang gsang ba'i dur khrod kun khyab /
NK053('i)001:14661: sbyor ba 3brtsam pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:14662: mkha' gsang byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14663: 'phro 'dus bskul don byas te byang sems dbab pa'o //
NK053('i)001:14664: mkha' 1 gsang byin gyis brlab pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:14665: dngos ni a ru byin brlabs nas //
NK053('i)001:14666: rin chen gsal bar shar ba dang //
NK053('i)001:14670: mkha' dbyings pad+ma rdo rjer byin brlabs pa //
NK053('i)001:14671: a las ma chags zla gam gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:14672: pad+ma'i dkyil 'khor chos sku am dang ldan //
NK053('i)001:14673: h'u las rdo rje rtse lnga nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor am //
NK053('i)001:14674: h'u dang am ni mdzes par blta zhing yid du 'ong //
NK053('i)001:14675: ru lus gcig la gcig ni chags shing 'phreng //
NK053('i)001:14676: ru lus glu blangs dga' ba'i mdangs dang sgras //
NK053('i)001:14677: h'u b+h+yos gnyis su med par bskul bar bya //
NK053('i)001:14678: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:14680: yab yum gyi mkha' gsang pad+ma rdo rjer ldan zhing /
NK053('i)001:14681: sku so so nas stag rgod 'dzum mdangs dang ldan pa zhig /
NK053('i)001:14682: chos dbyings dag pa'i ngang las sgyu ma lta bu'i sku gsal bar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:14683: yab yum 2 gnyis su med pa'i 'phro 'dus byang chub sems dbab pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:14684: chos ril dpal chen po yab yum du bsdus shing sbyor ba mdzad par bskul ba dang /
NK053('i)001:14685: khyad par du yang bde ba'i mchod pas ril mnyes par bya ba'o //
NK053('i)001:14686: de la 1chos ril dpal chen po yab yum du
NK053('i)001:14687: bsdus shing sbyor ba mdzad pa gang snyam pa la
NK053('i)001:14689: mos pa'i thugs la mnyes bsam nas //
NK053('i)001:14694: ni chos nyid chos kyi sku //
NK053('i)001:14695: ru ni dpal chen he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:14696: lu ni kro ti shwa ri yum //
NK053('i)001:14697: ru ni dbyer med zung du 'brel //
NK053('i)001:14698: lu ni mi gter 'dzin pa ste //
NK053('i)001:14699: h'u ni rab tu 'ching ba'i bdag /
NK053('i)001:14700: b+h+yos ni rab tu bsdams par mdzad //
NK053('i)001:14701: h'u gis bskyod nas bde chen 'bebs //
NK053('i)001:14702: 'bru brgyad sngags kyis grub par mdzod //
NK053('i)001:14703: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:14705: dpal chen yab yum gnyis su med par bde ba
NK053('i)001:14706: la snyoms par zhugs pa'i byang chub sems kyi 'od
NK053('i)001:14707: zer dkar dmar du 'phros pa las chags pa'i lam
NK053('i)001:14708: la mos pa rnams la phog pas /
NK053('i)001:14709: so so'i sgrib pa sbyangs shing mnyes par byas /
NK053('i)001:14712: 'khor ba dang mya ngan las 'das pa'i chos can ril sgrib pa sbyangs shing mnyes par byas nas /
NK053('i)001:14713: de dag gi byin rlabs dang bkrag dang gzi mdangs 'od dang 'od zer slar 'dus te /
NK053('i)001:14714: yab yum gyi mkha' gsang bar thog ma'i byang chub sems dkar dmar la gzud cing thim par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:14717: bde ba'i mchod pas ril mnyes par bya ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:14718: phyag mtshan snying po phra mo dag /
NK053('i)001:14719: bskul ba'i rang bzhin kun 'dus pas //
NK053('i)001:14720: brtan par reg nas mkha' la bzhag /
NK053('i)001:14721: des kyang spor ba'i las rnams byed //
NK053('i)001:14724: ni dpal chen yab yum sku //
NK053('i)001:14725: ru ni so sor bzhag pa ste //
NK053('i)001:14727: ru ni so sor 'khyud mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:14728: lu ni rdo rje pad+mora sbyor //
NK053('i)001:14729: h'u gis bskyod nas bde chen bskul //
NK053('i)001:14730: b+h+yos ni byang sems mkha' la phab //
NK053('i)001:14731: h'u gis byang sem mkha' la spros //
NK053('i)001:14732: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i thugs dam bskul //
NK053('i)001:14733: 'gro ba rgya mtsho sgrol bar mdzod //
NK053('i)001:14734: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:14736: dpal chen po yab yum thabs shes rab zung du
NK053('i)001:14737: 'brel zhing phyag rgya bzhi dang ldan par bzhugs pa
NK053('i)001:14738: de / gcig la gcig bzhad pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14741: rdo rje dang pad+mora sbyor ba dang /
NK053('i)001:14742: bde ba'i ro sku nyams su bstar ba dang /
NK053('i)001:14743: gsang ba byang chub sems mkha' la dbab pa las /
NK053('i)001:14744: gsung yig 'bru snying po 'bru brgyad dang /
NK053('i)001:14745: thugs phyag mtshan so sor gsal ba dang /
NK053('i)001:14746: sku phra mo mdzub gang ba dag tu rim par spro zhing /
NK053('i)001:14747: sangs rgyas kyi sa gsum kun tu 'od /
NK053('i)001:14750: la gnas pa'i sku che ba'i gzi brjid dang /
NK053('i)001:14751: 'od zer dang byin rlabs kyi rang bzhin du kun slar 'dus pa pas /
NK053('i)001:14752: bdag la thim pas bkrag dang gzi byin bskyed /
NK053('i)001:14753: yang dbyangs tshig dang ru lu'i sgras bskul bas /
NK053('i)001:14756: sku phra mo rim par 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:14757: 'gro ba sems can thams cad kyi ngag yid lus
NK053('i)001:14758: kyi sgrib pa sbyangs shing bkrag mdangs dang rtsi bcud
NK053('i)001:14759: kun bsdus te / slar yab yum gyi mkha' dbyings su 'dus pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14760: byang chub sems su dkar ltem gyis gyur pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14761: ting nge 'dzin brtan par gyur pas yum gyi mkha' la bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:14762: de yang rab ting nge 'dzin las su rung bas /
NK053('i)001:14763: bltas pas tshim ste yid 'phrad pa'o //
NK053('i)001:14765: lag pa 'phrad pa dang 'o byed pas tshim par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:14766: tha mas ni rtsol bas dngos su sbyor bar bya ste /
NK053('i)001:14767: dgyes pa'i ro sku nyams su bstar ba'i byang chub sems dngos su rgyas pa de /
NK053('i)001:14768: yum gyi mkha' las me long gi nang du blangs la /
NK053('i)001:14769: dbyangs tshig 'dis yon tan brjod de /
NK053('i)001:14771: byang chub sems 'di ye shes rang bzhin te //
NK053('i)001:14772: dri med rin chen char bzhin 'bab pa la //
NK053('i)001:14773: 'gro ba kun bskyed yid bzhin nor bu'i tshul //
NK053('i)001:14774: gdod nas dag pa bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin pas //
NK053('i)001:14775: gnyis med sbyor bas rdo rje'i rigs su 'grub //
NK053('i)001:14776: me long ye shes de nyid dag par bshad //
NK053('i)001:14777: de nas 4mchod pa dbul ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:14778: des kyang spros pa'i las rnams byed //
NK053('i)001:14779: dngos kyang mchod pa'i rdzas su bsngo //
NK053('i)001:14782: spros med rtog bral mkha' dbyings dag pa nas //
NK053('i)001:14783: skye med rdo rje'i sku gsung thugs mnga' ba //
NK053('i)001:14784: 'gro mgon rang byung bcom ldan thugs rje'i lha //
NK053('i)001:14785: zhi khro rab 'byams ma lus 'khor dang bcas //
NK053('i)001:14786: stong nyid dbyings nas thugs dam rgyud bskul gyis //
NK053('i)001:14787: sprul pa'i dbyings nas rol cing gshegs nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:14788: ye shes rtog bral byang sems mchod pa 'di //
NK053('i)001:14789: dgongs spyod zab mo'i thugs dam 'dis bskangs la //
NK053('i)001:14790: skye med chos sku'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:14791: bo d+hi tsit+ta p+au dza a a /
NK053('i)001:14793: byang chub sems mu tig dkar po lta bu las /
NK053('i)001:14795: las 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i lha mo mang po byung nas /
NK053('i)001:14796: dkyil 'khor gyi lha 'khor dang bcas pa la mchod pas mnyes par byas /
NK053('i)001:14797: bde bar gshegs pa'i rig 'dzin mkha' 'gro ma dang bcas pa la mchod pas /
NK053('i)001:14798: thugs dam bskangs shing nyams chag sor chud /
NK053('i)001:14799: de dag gi 'od zer byin rlabs kun bsdus te byang chub sems la thim pas /
NK053('i)001:14800: yi ge a dkar po gcig tu gsal ba ni mthe bong dang srin lag gis blangs nas /
NK053('i)001:14803: dngos po dang mtshan mar 'dzin pa ril mi rtog
NK053('i)001:14804: pa chos nyid skye 'gags med pa'i klong du gyur
NK053('i)001:14806: mchog gi dngos grub blang ba'i thabs te /
NK053('i)001:14807: dus dang gnas skabs rig cing shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:14808: gnyis su na slob dpon chen po h'u ka ras man ngag tu gdams pa /
NK053('i)001:14809: bdag nyid yang dag pa'i don rtogs pa'i rnal 'byor ni gsang dbang thob pa las byung la /
NK053('i)001:14810: gsang dbang thob pa'i dus nas shes rab ye shes kyi dbang ste /
NK053('i)001:14811: dbang gi dus kyi bu mo khyad par can la
NK053('i)001:14812: brten nas bdag dang sbyor ba rgyun du bya ba
NK053('i)001:14813: ni / bu mo gang yang rung ba de yum
NK053('i)001:14814: kro ti shwa ri mar byin gyis brlabs pa dang
NK053('i)001:14815: ni / / bdag nyid gnyis su med pa'i mkha' dbyings su /
NK053('i)001:14816: 'khor ba'i chos thams cad ma skyes pa'i thig ler sbyar ba ni /
NK053('i)001:14817: kun gzhi gdal ba'i ga'u dang /
NK053('i)001:14818: ye shes gcod pa'i ga'u ste /
NK053('i)001:14819: a li dang ka li zhes bya ste /
NK053('i)001:14820: de yang bdag dang gnyis kyi spyi bo gnas su rtsa gsum gyi 'brel bar gnas te /
NK053('i)001:14821: snying kha'i tsit+ta rin po che zur brgyad pa sul gsum pa la /
NK053('i)001:14825: dbus na a wa d+h+au ti bsti gnas te /
NK053('i)001:14826: yar gyes pa mgrin pa spyi gtsug /
NK053('i)001:14827: mar gyes pa lte ba dang gsang gnas /
NK053('i)001:14828: a wa d+h+au ti byang chub sems kyi rtsa ste /
NK053('i)001:14829: kun rdzob dang don dam pa ste /
NK053('i)001:14830: kun rdzob tu rdo rje pad+mara ldan par byas pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14835: gsang ba'i rdo rje'i kha yan chad bde ba bskyed pa de /
NK053('i)001:14836: de kho na thabs dang shes rab las byung ba'i stong pa ste /
NK053('i)001:14837: sems dang chos nyid du sbyor ba yin te yang
NK053('i)001:14838: nas yang du ma shor bar yar tsan mar nur
NK053('i)001:14839: bya zhing bde ba bskyed nas nyams su myong ba
NK053('i)001:14840: byas pa ni / sangs rgyas dang zhal 'phrad pa yin no //
NK053('i)001:14841: don dam par dga' bde nyams su myong ba de la /
NK053('i)001:14843: a wa d+h+au ti stong zhing bde ba /
NK053('i)001:14844: gsal la rtog pa med pa de las /
NK053('i)001:14845: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas ril de kho na las byung ba'o //
NK053('i)001:14846: chags pa'i me chen yum mdun du bzhag la don dam pa'i byang chub sems bskyed /
NK053('i)001:14847: chags pa'i me chung na dngos sbyar la sems bskyed /
NK053('i)001:14853: gzhi sbyor ba la brten pa'i thabs //
NK053('i)001:14857: 2 / de la gzhan don lhun gyis grub par bya ba'i phyi sgrol ba'i mchod pa bstan pa /
NK053('i)001:14859: skabs sbyor bsgrub rdzas bsgral ba'i man ngag bstan pa'i skabs bco lnga pa /
NK053('i)001:14862: dkyil 'khor dgu las mchod rdzas brten pa'am thugs rje phrin las kyi dal /
NK053('i)001:14863: lung dgu las thugs rjes khams gsum bsgral ba'i lung ngo //
NK053('i)001:14865: mngon spyod kyi phrin las spyir gdams pa bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14866: bsgrub par bya ba'i rdzas thugs rje'i phrin las kyis bsgral bar bstan pa'o /
NK053('i)001:14868: 1 / de la mngon spyod kyi phrin las spyi gdams par bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:14869: rtogs pas bdag bsgral ba dang /
NK053('i)001:14871: rtogs 1pas bdag bsgral ba la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:14872: phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi tshul du sta /
NK053('i)001:14874: las dang las kyi 'bras bu yid ches pa'i sgo nas /
NK053('i)001:14875: spyod pa dang du blangs bar bya ste /
NK053('i)001:14876: lus ngag yid gsum gyi sgo nas mi dge ba
NK053('i)001:14877: bcu spong zhing dge ba bcu dang du blang ba
NK053('i)001:14878: dang / de bzhin du nyan thos kyi 'dul ba dang /
NK053('i)001:14879: byang chub sems dpa'i sdom pa la gnas shing /
NK053('i)001:14880: nyon mongs pa dang gnyen po rim pas spangs zhing /
NK053('i)001:14881: dge ba'i rim pa gong nas gong du 'phel bar byed pa'i thabs la mkhas pa'o //
NK053('i)001:14883: don dbyings dang ye shes la dmigs nas /
NK053('i)001:14884: rtags thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel bar bya ste /
NK053('i)001:14885: bsnyen bsgrub yan lag bzhi dang ldan par byas nas phyag rgya bzhis rgyas btab nas /
NK053('i)001:14886: rang gi lus ngag yid gsum sku gsung thugs rdo rje ltar sbyor zhing /
NK053('i)001:14887: phung po khams dang skye mched lha dang lha mo'i rang bzhin du gnas pa'i sgo nas /
NK053('i)001:14888: bdag gzhan gyi don byed pa'o //
NK053('i)001:14890: yum shes rab ma la brten nas /
NK053('i)001:14891: yab yum thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel ba'i sgo nas /
NK053('i)001:14892: yon tan phrin las thams cad tshang zhing rdzogs pa'i don du /
NK053('i)001:14893: sbyor ba'i cho gas bdag gzhan gyi don du nyams bag du blangs nas /
NK053('i)001:14894: spyod yul du snang bar byed pa'o //
NK053('i)001:14895: de ltar brten pa'i thabs de sus rtogs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:14896: bdag nyid 'khor ba ngan song las sgrol ba yin pas na /
NK053('i)001:14897: rtogs pas bdag bsgral ba zhes bya'o //
NK053('i)001:14898: thugs 2rjes gzhan bsgral ba la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:14900: ting nge 'dzin gyis bsgral ba dang /
NK053('i)001:14902: de la 1thabs kyis bsgral ba la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:14903: snang ba dang mi snang ba gnyis las /
NK053('i)001:14904: gang mi la sogs pa snang ba rnams la /
NK053('i)001:14905: thabs gang dang gang gis 'dul ba'i sgo nas bkri
NK053('i)001:14906: drangs bya zhing nyon mongs pa'i sar mi bzhag pa'o
NK053('i)001:14907: // gang dbang po'i spyod yul du ma gyur pa'i mi snang ba rnams la /
NK053('i)001:14908: bdag gi dad pa dang gdung sems kyis /
NK053('i)001:14909: gang dag snying rje'i yul du gyur pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14910: chos kyi dam pas ma phog pa rnams la /
NK053('i)001:14911: tshad med pa bzhi'i thugs rjes rtag tu bzung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:14912: mchod sbyin gtor mas kun la khyab par byas te /
NK053('i)001:14913: zang zing dang chos kyi sbyin pa rtag tu btang ba'o //
NK053('i)001:14914: ting 2 nge 'dzin gyis bsgral ba la yang gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:14918: dbang po'i spyod yul du mi snang yang /
NK053('i)001:14919: dur khrod kyi bdag po ma tram khas /
NK053('i)001:14920: 'dre bgegs yi dwags kyi gtso bo byas nas yid
NK053('i)001:14921: kyi gzugs can de sgrub pa po la bar du
NK053('i)001:14923: rnal 'byor sgrub pa pos lta spyod kyi gdengs dang ldan par byas la /
NK053('i)001:14924: dngos po la mi snang yang bsam pas zin par byas la /
NK053('i)001:14925: yang nas yang du spogs shing bsgral ba ste gong du bshad zin /
NK053('i)001:14927: de la rnam par shes pa med cing bem po yin yang /
NK053('i)001:14928: de'i rnam pa shes pa de ye shes kyi pho nya dang /
NK053('i)001:14929: las kyi pho nyas bkug te bstim la /
NK053('i)001:14930: de la bsgral ba'i dgongs pas zin par byas pa la gnas spar ro //
NK053('i)001:14932: bsgral ba'i zhing gi rdzas la gnyis su bstan pa las /
NK053('i)001:14933: gdul bya bsgral ba'i rdzas bsgral ba'i zhing bcu la bya ba ste /
NK053('i)001:14935: gsang ba'i drag sngags kyis bsgral ba dang /
NK053('i)001:14936: dmod pa'i drag sngags kyis bsgral ba'o //
NK053('i)001:14937: de la 1gsang ba'i drags sngags kyis bsgral ba la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:14938: phyi nang gsang ba gsum mo //
NK053('i)001:14940: dpal chen pos dam la btags pa'i srin mo ke'u ri ma brgyad la bsnyen pa phul te /
NK053('i)001:14941: drag po'i thun zor bcas nas dmod sngags kyis bsgral ba'o //
NK053('i)001:14942: gnyis su na dur khrod kyi ma mo ro ga
NK053('i)001:14943: ma bzhi la bsnyen pa phul te thun zor dang
NK053('i)001:14944: bcas te dmod sngags kyis bsgral ba'o //
NK053('i)001:14945: nang 2ltar bsgrub pa la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:14946: dpal 1 chen po yab yum la /
NK053('i)001:14947: ke'u seng gi ma mos bskor ba la bsnyen pa
NK053('i)001:14948: phul te ma mo nying 'khol gyi drag sngags kyis
NK053('i)001:14949: bsgral te mnan pa yan chad bya ba'am /
NK053('i)001:14950: gnyis su 2 na dpal chen po yab yum la khro mo koo ri ma brgyad dang /
NK053('i)001:14951: bse yi lha mo bzhis bskor ba la bsnyen pa phul te phur thun gyis bsgral ba'am /
NK053('i)001:14952: gsum 3 du na dpal chen po yab yum la
NK053('i)001:14953: dbang phyug ma nyi shu rtsa brgyad dang bcas pa
NK053('i)001:14954: la bsnyen pa phul te mdos kyis bzlog nas zor
NK053('i)001:14955: gyis bsad pa'i las bya ba'o //
NK053('i)001:14956: gsang 3ba'i bsgrub pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:14960: bsgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po la brten te /
NK053('i)001:14961: byang shar gyi mtshams su 'brub khung bcas la /
NK053('i)001:14962: der gang la bya ba'i gzugs bcas te bcug nas /
NK053('i)001:14963: sngon dmar gyis gnya' lag du gzhug /
NK053('i)001:14964: khar nag gis ske nas btags la /
NK053('i)001:14965: gshin rje gshed po'i phur pa la brtod do //
NK053('i)001:14966: shar lho'i mtshams su gdug pa can gyi shing la hom dang ling+ga bcas la bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:14967: zangs phye dang lcags phye dang rdo phye dang /
NK053('i)001:14968: dug sna tshogs dang rme khrag sna tshogs su sbyar ba'i thun zor baca'o //
NK053('i)001:14969: phur pa yang dug shing rtags phyin pa'am lcags las byas pa la /
NK053('i)001:14973: bcu gcig byin gyis brlabs byas te bzhag nas /
NK053('i)001:14974: de nas ting nge 'dzin gyi rim pa la gzhung bsrang ste /
NK053('i)001:14975: mchod pa dang bstod pa yan chad rdzogs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14976: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:14977: zhes bya ba ni bsnyen pa ste sngon du rdzogs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:14979: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:14980: ma h+aa tsan+ta sarba dush+tana ta ka ha na da ha pa tsa h'u h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:14982: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u dzah a mu kam a kar k+sha ya s+w+aa h+aa hri /
NK053('i)001:14984: ye shes las grub pa'i pho nya dang /
NK053('i)001:14985: las las grub pa'i pho nyas dgug pa ni /
NK053('i)001:14986: man ngag gis shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:14987: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u ta /
NK053('i)001:14988: a mum kam k+sho pa ya h'u hring /
NK053('i)001:14991: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:14992: a mu kam de sha ya phata phata /
NK053('i)001:14993: ces bzlas pa ni dbye ba'i las so //
NK053('i)001:14994: de gnyis kyi dus su gu gul sbyar ba'i dud pas bdug go //
NK053('i)001:14995: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:14996: ma ma a mu kam m+aa ra ya h'u h'u phata phata /
NK053('i)001:14997: ces nyungs kar la bzlas pa ni gsad pa'o //
NK053('i)001:14998: de nas phur pa gdab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:14999: g+ha g+ha g+h+aa ta ya g+h+aa ta ya /
NK053('i)001:15001: k+ai li k+ai la ya sarba p+aa pham phata phata /
NK053('i)001:15002: h'u h'u badz+ra k+ai la ya badz+ra d+ha ro ad nya pa ya ti /
NK053('i)001:15004: k+aa ya w+aa ka tsit+ta k+ai la ya h'u h'u phata phata /
NK053('i)001:15007: thun zor bsgrub pa dag brdeg pa ni /
NK053('i)001:15008: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:15009: a mu kam ba ra g+h+ri na ha na h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:15012: mtshon gyis gtub ste shar lho'i hom la me sbar nas /
NK053('i)001:15013: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:15014: a mu kam ma ra ya h'u h'u phata phata /
NK053('i)001:15015: ces brjod pa ni bsreg pa'o //
NK053('i)001:15016: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u lam /
NK053('i)001:15017: a mu kam s+t+wam ba ya h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:15019: dur khrod du mnan pa bya'o //
NK053('i)001:15020: gnas 2 sbyang ba'i dgongs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:15021: bdag nyid dpal chen po yab yum du gsal ba'i ye shes kyi thugs ka dang /
NK053('i)001:15024: khro bo dang khro mo'i tshogs 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:15025: gzas pa po de'i rnam par shes pa bkug ste /
NK053('i)001:15026: yab yum gyi bsgul bskyod gyi phyag rgyas brdungs pas /
NK053('i)001:15027: yab yum gnyis su med pa'i byang chub sems kyi 'od zer gyis /
NK053('i)001:15028: rgyu las dang nyon mongs pa'i bag chags ni sbyangs /
NK053('i)001:15029: 'bras bu sdug bsngal gyi phung po ni bcom /
NK053('i)001:15030: sems gser zhun lta bur gnas pa de yi ge h'u du gyur pa las /
NK053('i)001:15031: g+hu h+ya dz+ny+aa na he ru ka sa t+wa h'u /
NK053('i)001:15032: gsang ba ye shes khrag 'thung sems dpa' /
NK053('i)001:15034: gsang ba ye shes kyi he ru ka zhal gcig la phyag gnyis par bskyed de /
NK053('i)001:15036: yi ge b+h+r+aum gsum gyis byin brlabs la /
NK053('i)001:15037: yam las rlung gi man+dala steng du bzhag nas /
NK053('i)001:15038: phata kyis 'og min grub pa'i gnas su /
NK053('i)001:15039: rigs lnga he ru ka yab yum gyi sbyor mtshams su 'phangs la /
NK053('i)001:15040: de bzhin gshegs pa de dag gi sras su bskyed par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:15041: de la dmod pa'i drag sngags kyis bsgral ba ni /
NK053('i)001:15042: dkar mo nyi ma'i mig gcig la sogs pa'i gsang
NK053('i)001:15043: ba'i ma mo chen mo bzhi'i las myur la drag
NK053('i)001:15044: pa'i sngags / drag sngags rnon po'i /
NK053('i)001:15045: rgyu shugs sgrol gyi sngags kyis /
NK053('i)001:15046: mkha' la rlung ltar 'phyo ba dang /
NK053('i)001:15049: u ma bzhi dang 'degs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15052: bcu drug tshang ma 'khyil ba dang /
NK053('i)001:15053: sbrul tshang ma g.yu sgang bcu drug la gnang ba'o //
NK053('i)001:15054: jag rkun la pho nya bzhin du rgyugs pa la sogs pas /
NK053('i)001:15055: gzhan gyi srog la 'tshe zhing gnod pa de bsgral te /
NK053('i)001:15056: de yang snying rjes gzung zhing gnas spar ba gong ltar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:15057: de ni las man ngag kha tshar las shes pa bya'o /
NK053('i)001:15059: 2 / de la bsgrub par bya ba'i rdzas thugs rjes phrin las kyis bsgral bar bstan pa la /
NK053('i)001:15061: sgrub pa po ting nge 'dzin gyis gzengs bstod de lhag pa'i rtags kyis mtshon pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15062: bsgrub par bya ba'i rdzas de nyid thabs kyis byin gyis brlabs cing bsgral ba'o //
NK053('i)001:15063: de la 1sgrub pa po ting nge 'dzin gyis gzengs
NK053('i)001:15064: bstod cing lhag ma'i rtags kyis mtshon pa gang snyam
NK053('i)001:15065: pa la / dmigs med stobs kyi gdings can gyis //
NK053('i)001:15066: sku mchog 'bar ba'i tshul du bsam //
NK053('i)001:15068: don dam pa chos nyid dmigs su med pa'i ting
NK053('i)001:15069: nge 'dzin stobs su gyur pa'i ting nge 'dzin de
NK053('i)001:15070: bzhin nyid las su rung ba'i rnal 'byor pa bdag
NK053('i)001:15071: nyid de / thugs chos nyid zhi ba'i ngang las ma g.yos kyang /
NK053('i)001:15072: sku mchog 'bar ba dpal khrag 'thung chen po'i sku'i tshul du bsam pa ni /
NK053('i)001:15074: mi g.yo phyag rgya chen po'i ngang //
NK053('i)001:15075: chos kyi sku las bzhengs nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:15076: sems can thams cad khro ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:15077: rdo rje yang ni khro bar bya //
NK053('i)001:15078: badz+ra ma h+aa sh+r+ai he ru ka ram dz+wa la ni h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:15080: dpal chen po'i sku mdog dang /
NK053('i)001:15082: de la lha mo rnams kyis mdzes par brgyan pa /
NK053('i)001:15083: gong du bstan pa ltar bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:15084: de la dur khrod kyi rgyan gsol zhing lhag pa'i rtags kyis mtshan pa /
NK053('i)001:15085: gong du bstan pa ltar byas nas /
NK053('i)001:15086: bsgrub 2par bya ba'i rdzas de nyid thabs kyis byin
NK053('i)001:15087: gyis brlabs shing bsgral bar bstan pa la don drug
NK053('i)001:15088: ste / bsgrub par bya ba'i rdzas de dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15089: shes rab dang snying rjes zin par bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:15090: ting nge 'dzin ji lta bus bsgral ba dang /
NK053('i)001:15091: drag po'i mngon spyod kyis bsgral ba dang /
NK053('i)001:15092: gnas spar ba'i dgongs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15093: tha mar gzugs kyi phung po la phrin las ji ltar bya ba'o //
NK053('i)001:15094: de la 1bsgrub par bya ba'i rdzas de dkyil 'khor du gzhug pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:15095: sgrub rdzas de dag byin gyis brlabs //
NK053('i)001:15098: gong du smon pa'i bkra shis gtsang ma'i rdzas dang /
NK053('i)001:15100: bsgrub pa mchog gi rdzas dang /
NK053('i)001:15102: gsum po gang rnyed pa ni /
NK053('i)001:15103: 'gro ba ris drug gi gnas nas shes pa dgug cing /
NK053('i)001:15104: de rang rang gi phung po la bstim zhing /
NK053('i)001:15105: phyag rgya bzhis gnyis su med par bcings la /
NK053('i)001:15106: kho rang dngos por bsam pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15107: yang na bsgral ba zhing gi rdzas de /
NK053('i)001:15108: gang yin pa dkyil 'khor gyi rtsar dngos por dgug pa'o //
NK053('i)001:15110: mkha' 'gro la sogs sems can lnga //
NK053('i)001:15111: bsgrub pa'i rdzas su gsungs pa yang //
NK053('i)001:15112: sdig med nyen dang ma 'brel ba'i //
NK053('i)001:15113: srog med sha khrag mchod ston bya //
NK053('i)001:15116: rab tu nyen che rnam smin mi bzlog pas shin du gzab bo //
NK053('i)001:15117: de la las la mkhas pa'i karma dang /
NK053('i)001:15118: sgrol ging gis bsgrub rdzas de bzung la /
NK053('i)001:15119: rdo rje rgyal po dang rgyal thebs la mkhyen par gsol ba /
NK053('i)001:15120: hoh dpal chen ye shes sems dpa' la sogs te /
NK053('i)001:15121: 'khor tshogs rgya mtsho dang bcas pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15122: dpal chen po sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra ta ki ni 'khor rgya mtsho dang bcas pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15123: ma tshogs kyi dbang phyug ma /
NK053('i)001:15127: phyi'i grub pa mo 'khor rgya mtsho dang bcas pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15128: gzhan yang rdo rje rnal 'byor gyi dbang phyug chen
NK053('i)001:15129: po mched lcam dral 'khor tshogs rgya mtsho dang bcas
NK053('i)001:15130: pa dang / ma lus pa thams cad dgongs su gsol lo //
NK053('i)001:15131: deng ni gnas mchog dam pa 'dir /
NK053('i)001:15132: 'phags pa thams cad mchod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15133: rdo rje lcam dral phyogs bcu na bzhugs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15134: da ltar 'dir 'tshogs pa la sogs pa'i thugs dam bskong ba dang /
NK053('i)001:15135: sems can thams cad bla na med pa'i gnas su bsgral ba dang /
NK053('i)001:15136: 'gro ba ma lus pa mtha' dag gi don bgyis ba'i slad du /
NK053('i)001:15138: bkra shis gtsang ma'i rdzas mchog 'di /
NK053('i)001:15139: dag pa lha yi rdzas mchog 'di /
NK053('i)001:15140: sgrub pa mchog gi rdzas mchog 'di /
NK053('i)001:15141: bsgral ba'i zhing gi rdzas mchog 'di /
NK053('i)001:15142: tsa ra mchog bzhi pa gcig mi'o //
NK053('i)001:15144: thugs rjes gzung zhing bsgral du gsol lo //
NK053('i)001:15145: tsa ra 'di thugs rjes ma bzung ma bsgral na spyo ba mchis te /
NK053('i)001:15147: rnal 'byor gyi theg pa la zhugs kyang tshul bzhin ma bgyis te /
NK053('i)001:15148: de bzhin gshegs pa'i bka' tshad ma khyad du bsad pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15149: rdo rje slob dpon dang mched lcam dral la ngan sems dang 'phya sems skyes pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15160: rdo rje slob dpon la snying nas smad pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15161: bla ma la dbang zos pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15162: mnyam pa'i spyod yul sun phyung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:15163: sbyor sgrol mang po'i sgo bkag pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15164: dad pa can gyi tshogs bcag pa ste /
NK053('i)001:15165: gdung sems kyi rgyun bcad de /
NK053('i)001:15167: sku gsung thugs kyi gdung 'tsho ba ba'i bar chad bgyis nas /
NK053('i)001:15168: da ltar ngan song gi gnas na 'khyams shing rtog pa'i d+r+wa bas bcings /
NK053('i)001:15170: dmyal khams kyi gting brgyud pas /
NK053('i)001:15171: nges pa'i zhing bcu dang ldan pa 'di /
NK053('i)001:15172: dkon mchog gsum gyi spyi dgra /
NK053('i)001:15173: rdo rje slob dpon gyi sgos dgra /
NK053('i)001:15177: snod ngan sgrub pa'i 'du sar yong ba yongs la gnod pa chags pa lha bu /
NK053('i)001:15178: dam dgra ngan pa'i ngang tshul can phur bzlog mkhan lta bu /
NK053('i)001:15180: dam tshig tshul bzhin du bsgral du gsol lo //
NK053('i)001:15181: hoh 'di'i rnam par shes pa ni bla na med pa'i gnas su 'og min du /
NK053('i)001:15183: gnas spong bar byin gyis brlab tu gsol lo //
NK053('i)001:15184: lnga phung gi yan lag ni /
NK053('i)001:15185: kun tu bzang po'i mchod sprin du gyur nas /
NK053('i)001:15186: de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad kyi ye shes mnyam
NK053('i)001:15187: pa nyid kyi ngang du dbyer med par thim par
NK053('i)001:15190: rdo rje rgyal po dang rgyal thebs kyis /
NK053('i)001:15192: rdzas la nyi zla'i spyan zur gyis blta zhing /
NK053('i)001:15193: ngag tu thar pa'i lam 'byed dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK053('i)001:15194: brod pa can dag dga' ba'i gnas su 'gro ba ltar //
NK053('i)001:15195: skal dang ldan pa'i sems can khyod //
NK053('i)001:15197: khyod ni sems can skal par ldan //
NK053('i)001:15198: bder gshegs thugs rjes sgrol la mkhas //
NK053('i)001:15199: blo ngan sems can snying re rje //
NK053('i)001:15200: chos nyid gnyis su med par bsgral bar gnang //
NK053('i)001:15208: byin gyis brlabs par zhu ba yan chad gong nas 'byung ba bzhin du byas la /
NK053('i)001:15209: bar 'dir lan chags kyi gtor ma btang /
NK053('i)001:15210: de nas chos nyid rnam par dag pa'i sngags swa b+h+aa wa /
NK053('i)001:15212: ngan song sbyor ba'i sngags sarba durga ti /
NK053('i)001:15214: rgyu de dri chab dang bdud rtsi'i chus bakru'o //
NK053('i)001:15215: de nas rdo rje gnod sbyin gyi sngags ring na mo rat+na tra ya y+aahsogasa brjod /
NK053('i)001:15216: nyungs kar la basngagasa te mtshams drag tu bcad la /
NK053('i)001:15217: rdo rje rgyal po dang rgyal thebs kyis 'di skad du brjod par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:15219: ye shes mkha' lding sder chen gyis //
NK053('i)001:15220: 'khor bye'u phru gu blangs pas na //
NK053('i)001:15221: bu la ma mos gzan ster bzhin //
NK053('i)001:15223: ha ha ha tra me sarba sa du pra du sha /
NK053('i)001:15226: rdo rje rgyal po dang rgyal thebs kyi /
NK053('i)001:15228: mi rtog ye shes rang bzhin dkyil 'khor te /
NK053('i)001:15229: 'dus shing 'tshogs pas tshogs kyi dkyil 'khor bstan //
NK053('i)001:15230: thabs kyi rdo rje bya ba'i rnam grangs ni //
NK053('i)001:15231: chos kyi dbyings la chos nyid rab tu gnas //
NK053('i)001:15232: rdo rje dbyings kyi dkyil 'khor bzang po der //
NK053('i)001:15233: su dag phyin pa phyir mi ldog par nges //
NK053('i)001:15234: sta na tsi mo ga sha g+ha na ma na la bra du sha h'u /
NK053('i)001:15235: zhes brjod de man+dala steng du bzhag go //
NK053('i)001:15238: zhing dang spyod yul dag pa'i gnas 'di ni //
NK053('i)001:15239: thar lam grol ba'i mchog tu rab tu dgongs //
NK053('i)001:15240: lha rnams sta gon mdzad pas 'gro don rdzogs //
NK053('i)001:15241: mi rnams sta gon gnas pas sku gsung thugs //
NK053('i)001:15242: de ltar bsgrub pa brtson pa'i bsnyen pa 'di //
NK053('i)001:15243: 'phags pa rnams kyi thugs rje nyid kyis mdzod //
NK053('i)001:15244: ma thob thob pa med par sbyar lags kyis //
NK053('i)001:15245: dus 'dir thugs rjer ldan par byin gyis rlobs //
NK053('i)001:15247: des ni sgrub pa'i rdzas de dkyil 'khor du bcug nas bdag dbang bar byin gyis brlabs pa'o //
NK053('i)001:15248: de la 2snying rje dang shes rab kyis zin par bya ba la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:15249: de la rgyu de la snying rje ji ltar bskyed snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:15250: khams gsum khrag tu dmigs nas ni //
NK053('i)001:15251: dur khrod kun tu khyab par bsam //
NK053('i)001:15253: de la dper na khrag ni dmar ba yin la /
NK053('i)001:15254: dmar ba ni chags pa'i rang bzhin yin pas /
NK053('i)001:15255: de bzhin khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad la /
NK053('i)001:15256: thugs rje chen pos chags par bya ba'i yul du dmigs nas /
NK053('i)001:15257: gzhan yang dur khrod ces bya ba ni ro mang po gnas sa la bya ste /
NK053('i)001:15258: khams gsum nyid sems can gyi ro mang po'i gnas yin pas dur khrod /
NK053('i)001:15260: de la snying rje chen po 'di ltar bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:15261: yong chos thams cad gzod ma nas ma skyes shing dngos po med pa yin la /
NK053('i)001:15262: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad kyis /
NK053('i)001:15263: de ltar ma shes shing dngos por mngon pa zhen par khams gsum du 'khor nas /
NK053('i)001:15265: skye rga na 'chi bzhi nang gi bzhi /
NK053('i)001:15266: med pa btsal gyis mi rnyed /
NK053('i)001:15269: gnyen byams dang bral dog gi sdug bsngal bzhi'o //
NK053('i)001:15273: khyab pa 'du byed kyi sdug bsngal /
NK053('i)001:15274: gsum gyis gdungs nas nyon mongs pa rnams snying re rje /
NK053('i)001:15275: 'di dag sdug bsngal gyi gnas nas bsgral bar bya'o snyam du /
NK053('i)001:15276: khams gsum gyi dur khrod kun tu khyab pa'i phyogs
NK053('i)001:15277: med pa'i snying rje chen po bskyed cing bsams nas
NK053('i)001:15278: / de nas khams gsum du 'khor ba'i sems can thams cad /
NK053('i)001:15279: dmigs cing bsgral bar bya ba'i sems can de'i lus la bsdu ste /
NK053('i)001:15281: dus gcig tu bsgral ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:15285: khams gsum nas byung sems can rnams //
NK053('i)001:15286: rdo rje'i sku yi khyad par gyis //
NK053('i)001:15287: 'od zer tshul gyis bsdus nas ni //
NK053('i)001:15288: de dag bdag gi gzugs la gzud //
NK053('i)001:15289: spro bsdu rdo rje thams cad kyi //
NK053('i)001:15290: sku dang ye shes mchog tu bsgral //
NK053('i)001:15292: ru lu ye shes kyi 'od zer gyis khams gsum
NK053('i)001:15293: gyi sems can thams cad bsdus te de'i lus la
NK053('i)001:15294: btsud pa dang / yum shes rab mas 'di skad du /
NK053('i)001:15296: las la bab pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
NK053('i)001:15298: dus la bab pa'i sems can 'di //
NK053('i)001:15299: gnyis med phyag rgya chen po yis //
NK053('i)001:15300: don rtog pa dus la bab po sa ma ya //
NK053('i)001:15301: ka re ka ha tsa re /
NK053('i)001:15302: tsa ha sa ma ya s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:15306: mu mtha' med par mi 'dzin 'gog med pa'i //
NK053('i)001:15308: rnal 'byor mnyam pa nyid las thod rgal du //
NK053('i)001:15309: khro gtum rngam dang zhi mdzad la sogs pa'i //
NK053('i)001:15310: mngon spyod kyi rgyu des mya ngan las 'da' bar /
NK053('i)001:15312: sna tshogs ston yang byang chub sems las mi 'da' mi g.yo //
NK053('i)001:15313: a tsa la sa ma ya d+harma d+hartu swa b+h+aa wa +aad+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:15315: zhi ba'i ting nge 'dzin las bzhengs nas /
NK053('i)001:15316: lag pa g.yas g.yon s+t+wa zur du bstan la /
NK053('i)001:15317: phyogs mtshams bla 'og kun tu bltas nas /
NK053('i)001:15318: 'jig rten gsum po skye shi'i mtshan nyid de /
NK053('i)001:15319: thar pa'i rgyu ci yang med cing ngan song gsum gyi gting brgyud pa /
NK053('i)001:15320: de dag la snying rje khyad par can du bskyed nas /
NK053('i)001:15323: khro gtum ltar snang yang don la tshad med byams par snang //
NK053('i)001:15324: gsod chen snying rje'i bdag snying de //
NK053('i)001:15325: bsgral zhing bstab pa dga' ba'i mchog /
NK053('i)001:15326: yal bar mi 'dor btang snyoms so //
NK053('i)001:15327: ma h+aa ka ru na ma h+aa me tri swa b+h+aa wa at+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:15329: khams gsum gyi sems can thams cad kun la phyogs ris med pa'i byams pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15330: tshad med pa'i snying rje dang /
NK053('i)001:15331: 'gyod pa med pa'i dga' ba dang /
NK053('i)001:15332: dmigs pa med pa'i btang snyoms te tshad med pa'i snying rje bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:15333: de la 2shes rab kyis zin par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:15334: de nas chos thams cad ci yang ma yin pa'i
NK053('i)001:15335: ngang ji lta ba bzhin du shes rab kyis tshig
NK053('i)001:15336: tsam ma yin par rtogs la /
NK053('i)001:15337: ting nge 'dzin gyis ji ltar dmigs shing sems las su rung bar bya ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:15338: dngos ni a ru byin brlabs nas //
NK053('i)001:15339: zhes bya ba la sogs pa gsungs te /
NK053('i)001:15340: de'i drod dang dbugs dang rlan las /
NK053('i)001:15341: ram dang yam dang kham dang bsam pa las /
NK053('i)001:15342: ram yam kham gsum gyis bsregs gtor sbyangs nas /
NK053('i)001:15343: stong pa nyid du gyur te /
NK053('i)001:15345: sems nyid yi ge a'i rang bzhin du bsgom pa yang /
NK053('i)001:15347: sems can khyod kyi phung po la //
NK053('i)001:15348: lus las drod byung me ltar 'bar //
NK053('i)001:15349: me yi snying po ram zhes bya //
NK053('i)001:15350: rig pa'i ye shes me byung bas //
NK053('i)001:15351: khyod kyi dngos po bsreg par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:15354: de las me byung bas dngos po thams cad bsregs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15356: sems can khyod kyi phung po la //
NK053('i)001:15357: lus las dbugs byung rlung ltar 'phyo //
NK053('i)001:15358: rlung gi snying po yam zhes bya //
NK053('i)001:15359: rig pa'i ye shes rlung byung bas //
NK053('i)001:15360: yod kyi bag chags gtor bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:15363: de las rlung byung bas thams cad gtor ba dang /
NK053('i)001:15366: sems can khyod kyi phung po las //
NK053('i)001:15367: lus las rlan byung chu ltar 'brub //
NK053('i)001:15368: chu yi snying po kham zhes bya //
NK053('i)001:15369: rig pa'i ye shes chu byung bas //
NK053('i)001:15370: khyod kyi bag chags bkru bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:15373: de las chu byung bas thams cad bkrus te /
NK053('i)001:15375: dag nas nang stong pa'i rang bzhin du gyur pa las /
NK053('i)001:15378: lus zla ba'i dkyil 'khor du gyur //
NK053('i)001:15379: de'i steng du sems kyi rang bzhin /
NK053('i)001:15381: a dkar po gcig tu gyur par bsam zhing byin gyis brlab bo //
NK053('i)001:15383: ting nge 'dzin gyi tshad ji tsam du bya snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:15384: rin chen gsal bar shar ba dang //
NK053('i)001:15386: dper na yid bzhin gyi nor bu rin po che las /
NK053('i)001:15387: sems can gyi dgos 'dod ji ltar bsam pa ltar 'byung ba de bzhin du /
NK053('i)001:15388: sems kyi rang bzhin yi ge a de las kyang /
NK053('i)001:15389: ji ltar bsam pa bzhin du 'byung bas rin chen zhes bya ste /
NK053('i)001:15390: a de ting nge 'dzin la shin tu gsal zhing sems las su rung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:15392: mos pa'i thugs la mnyes bsams nas //
NK053('i)001:15395: byang chub sems kyi rang bzhin de las /
NK053('i)001:15398: 'od zer phyogs bcur 'phros pa las gnyis su med
NK053('i)001:15399: pa'i bde ba la mos pa'i yab yum sras 'khor
NK053('i)001:15400: dang bcas pa thams cad la phog pas /
NK053('i)001:15401: mchod cing mnyes par bsams nas /
NK053('i)001:15405: tha mal pa'i gzugs su bsam la /
NK053('i)001:15409: lha ma yin lha'i khongs su bsdus te /
NK053('i)001:15410: lam rgyud lngar skye ba'i rgyun chad cing 'byung ba'i sgo bkag pa'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:15411: snying po phyag mtshan phra mo dag /
NK053('i)001:15412: brten pa gyur nas mkha' la bzhag /
NK053('i)001:15414: de la zhe sdang ni dmyal bar skye ba'i rgyu yin te /
NK053('i)001:15415: zhe sdang la rang bzhin med par shes nas zhe sdang sems mi skye na /
NK053('i)001:15416: dmyal bar skye ba'i rgyun bcad pa yin /
NK053('i)001:15421: bsam gtan dang snyoms par 'jug pa ni /
NK053('i)001:15426: lhar skye ba'i rgyu yin la /
NK053('i)001:15427: de dag la rang bzhin med par shes shing /
NK053('i)001:15428: de dag gi sems mi skye na /
NK053('i)001:15432: lhar skye ba'i rgyun bcad pa yin no //
NK053('i)001:15433: de nas lam lngar phyir byung ba'i sgo bkag pa ni /
NK053('i)001:15434: dmigs kyis bsgral ba de la /
NK053('i)001:15435: phyis lam rgyud lngar 'byung bar sgo yod pa'i rtags su /
NK053('i)001:15436: gnas lngar rang rgyud kyi snying po lnga bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:15437: de nas lam rgyud lngar skye ba'i rgyu de la /
NK053('i)001:15438: rang bzhin med pa'i rtags su /
NK053('i)001:15439: rang rgyud kyi snying po lnga a n+ri ti pre du 'i steng du /
NK053('i)001:15440: dpa' bo 'bru +aahmh'u s+w+aa h+aa lngas mnan par bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:15441: de yang dgod pa ni yas nas dgod la /
NK053('i)001:15442: bsdu ba ni mas nas bsdu ba bya ste /
NK053('i)001:15444: sems can khyod kyi spyi gtsug na //
NK053('i)001:15445: yi ge a gcig gnas pa ni //
NK053('i)001:15446: lha ru skye ba'i rgyu yin te //
NK053('i)001:15447: rgyud drug 'khor ba rtsad bcad nas //
NK053('i)001:15448: rgyud lnga lam gyi sgo dgag phyir //
NK053('i)001:15449: zhes bya ba gsal bar bsgom //
NK053('i)001:15450: sems can khyod kyi lce steng na //
NK053('i)001:15451: yi ge n+rihgaciga gnas pa ni //
NK053('i)001:15452: mi ru skye ba'i rgyu yin te //
NK053('i)001:15453: rgyud drug 'khor ba rtsad bcad nas //
NK053('i)001:15454: rgyud lnga lam gyi sgo dgag phyir //
NK053('i)001:15456: sems can khyod kyi snying kha na //
NK053('i)001:15457: yi ge tri gcig gnas pa ni //
NK053('i)001:15458: byol song skye ba'i rgyu yin te //
NK053('i)001:15459: rgyud drug 'khor ba rtsad bcad nas //
NK053('i)001:15460: rgyud lnga lam gyi sgo dgag phyir //
NK053('i)001:15461: h'u zhes bya ba gsal bar bsgom //
NK053('i)001:15462: sems can khyod kyi lte ba na //
NK053('i)001:15463: yi ge pre gcig gnas pa ni //
NK053('i)001:15464: yi dwags skye ba'i rgyu yin te //
NK053('i)001:15465: rgyud drug 'khor ba rtsad bcad nas //
NK053('i)001:15466: rgyud lnga lam gyi sgo dgag phyir //
NK053('i)001:15467: s+w+aa zhes bya ba gsal bar bsgom //
NK053('i)001:15468: sems can khyod kyi gsang ba na //
NK053('i)001:15469: yi ge duhgaciga gnas pa ni //
NK053('i)001:15470: dmyal bar skye ba'i rgyu yin te //
NK053('i)001:15471: rgyud drug 'khor ba rtsad bcad nas //
NK053('i)001:15472: rgyu lnga lam gyi sgo dgag phyir //
NK053('i)001:15473: h+aahzhesa bya ba gsal bar bsgom //
NK053('i)001:15474: zhes pas yi ge yas bkod la /
NK053('i)001:15475: skye gnas rigs drug gzhom pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15476: rgyud lngar 'byung ba'i sgo dgag phyir /
NK053('i)001:15482: de la mas bsdu ba ni /
NK053('i)001:15484: bu khyod rgyal ba'i sras ma yin //
NK053('i)001:15485: bu khyod rgyal ba'i sras yin na //
NK053('i)001:15486: dmyal ba'i gnas su ci ste 'khor //
NK053('i)001:15487: dmyal ba'i gnas su 'khor ba na //
NK053('i)001:15488: rkang mthil yi ge h+aahbasamasa te //
NK053('i)001:15489: dmyal ba'i lam yi sgo bcad do //
NK053('i)001:15496: h+aahs+pha ra na phata kyis 'od 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:15498: 'gro ba'i don byas pa'i nang nas kyang /
NK053('i)001:15499: khyad par du dmyal ba'i yi dwags kyi /
NK053('i)001:15503: sems can dang lha gnyis su med par 'dres nas /
NK053('i)001:15506: sam ha ra na h'u gis bsdus nas /
NK053('i)001:15508: rdo rje rgya gram rin po che /
NK053('i)001:15518: zla ba'i dkyil 'khor la phogs pas /
NK053('i)001:15526: de las ye shes kyi 'od zer yang 'bar bas /
NK053('i)001:15531: spyir rigs lnga yab yum mnyes pa'i steng du /
NK053('i)001:15532: bye brag tu don yod grub pa rin chen 'byung ldan /
NK053('i)001:15537: spyir 'gro ba ris lnga stong pa'i steng du /
NK053('i)001:15538: bye brag dmyal ba'i yi dwags kyi /
NK053('i)001:15542: rigs lnga'i thugs dam skong ba'i steng du /
NK053('i)001:15543: las kyi rigs rin chen rigs //
NK053('i)001:15546: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi thugs dam skong //
NK053('i)001:15547: ye shes lnga grub pa'i steng du /
NK053('i)001:15548: bya ba nan tan gyi mnyam pa nyid kyi /
NK053('i)001:15551: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes grub pa'i rtags su /
NK053('i)001:15567: dang bcas par gsal ba las /
NK053('i)001:15568: h+aahzhesa bya ba gsal ba las //
NK053('i)001:15569: don yod grub pa yab yum bsgom //
NK053('i)001:15570: gtso bo dang ni gtso mor ldan //
NK053('i)001:15571: thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel //
NK053('i)001:15572: sbyor ba'i byang chub sems 'phros pas //
NK053('i)001:15573: mi 'gyur brtan par gser bzhin no //
NK053('i)001:15574: badz+ra a lo ka si ti a /
NK053('i)001:15575: badz+ra sa ma ya da ra h+aa /
NK053('i)001:15577: 'bras bu lnga las don yod grub pa rin chen 'byung ldan /
NK053('i)001:15580: rnam par snang mdzad yab yum gyi skur grub par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:15581: de nas yab yum gnyis su med par 'od du gyur pa las /
NK053('i)001:15588: rked pa'i s+w+aa snying ga'i h'u /
NK053('i)001:15596: man chad stong pa gnas tsam na /
NK053('i)001:15597: phyis dmyal bar yi dwags su /
NK053('i)001:15601: mi skye bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:15602: da ha da ha sarba na rag ga te he tum h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:15604: dmyal bar skye ba'i sgo bkag go //
NK053('i)001:15605: don de bzhin du phyi ma rnams la yang shes pa ra bya'o //
NK053('i)001:15607: bu khyod rgyal ba'i sras ma yin //
NK053('i)001:15608: bu khyod rgyal ba'i sras yin na //
NK053('i)001:15609: yi dwags gnas su ci ste 'khor //
NK053('i)001:15610: yi dwags gnas su 'khor ba na //
NK053('i)001:15611: lte bar yi ge s+w+aa bsgom pas //
NK053('i)001:15612: yi dwags lam gyi sgo bcad do //
NK053('i)001:15618: s+w+aa zhes bya ba gsal ba las //
NK053('i)001:15619: rin chen 'byung ldan yab yum bsgom //
NK053('i)001:15620: gtso bo dang ni gtso mor ldan //
NK053('i)001:15621: thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel //
NK053('i)001:15622: sbyor ba'i byang chub sems 'phros pas //
NK053('i)001:15623: mi 'gyur brtan pas gser bzhin no //
NK053('i)001:15624: badz+ra rat+na sam b+ha wa t+r+aam /
NK053('i)001:15627: pa tsa pa tsa sarba pre ta ga te hi tum h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:15628: yi dwags skye sgo bkag go //
NK053('i)001:15630: bu khyod rgyal ba'i sras ma yin //
NK053('i)001:15631: bu khyod rgyal ba'i sras yin na //
NK053('i)001:15632: byol song gnas su ci ste 'khor //
NK053('i)001:15633: byol song gnas su 'khor ba na //
NK053('i)001:15634: snying kar yi ge h'u bsgom pas //
NK053('i)001:15635: byol song lam gyi sgo bcad do //
NK053('i)001:15641: h'u zhes bya ba gsal ba las //
NK053('i)001:15642: rdo rje sems dpa' yab yum bsgom //
NK053('i)001:15643: gtso bo dang ni gtso mor ldan //
NK053('i)001:15644: thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel //
NK053('i)001:15645: sbyor ba'i byang chub sems 'phros pas //
NK053('i)001:15646: mi 'gyur brtan pas gser bzhin no //
NK053('i)001:15648: badz+ra te shwa ra ti h'u /
NK053('i)001:15650: ma tha ma tha sarba tir+ya ga te he tum h'u phata //
NK053('i)001:15653: bu khyod rgyal ba'i sras ma yin //
NK053('i)001:15654: bu khyod rgyal ba'i sras yin na //
NK053('i)001:15655: mi yi gnas su ci ste 'khor //
NK053('i)001:15656: mi yi gnas su 'khor ba na //
NK053('i)001:15657: lce steng yi ge +aam bsgom pas //
NK053('i)001:15658: mi ru skye ba'i sgo bcad do //
NK053('i)001:15663: +aamh +aam zhes bya ba gsal ba las //
NK053('i)001:15664: snang ba mtha' yas yab yum bsgom //
NK053('i)001:15665: gtso bo dang ni gtso mor ldan //
NK053('i)001:15666: thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel //
NK053('i)001:15667: sbyor ba'i byang chub sems 'phros pas //
NK053('i)001:15668: mi 'gyur brtan pas gser bzhin no //
NK053('i)001:15669: +aam badz+ra a mi d+he wa h+r+aih badz+ra b+han d+ha ra ba si h+r+aih +aam h'u /
NK053('i)001:15670: sarba durga sarba kle sha h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:15673: bu khyod rgyal ba'i sras ma yin //
NK053('i)001:15674: bu khyod rgyal ba'i sras yin na //
NK053('i)001:15675: lha yi gnas su ci ste 'khor //
NK053('i)001:15676: lha yi gnas su 'khor ba na //
NK053('i)001:15677: spyi bor yi ge bsgom pas //
NK053('i)001:15678: lha ru skye ba'i sgo bcad do //
NK053('i)001:15683: zhes bya ba gsal ba las //
NK053('i)001:15684: rnam par snang mdzad yab yum bsgom //
NK053('i)001:15685: gtso bo dang ni gtso mor ldan //
NK053('i)001:15686: thabs dang shes rab zung du 'brel //
NK053('i)001:15687: sbyor ba'i byang chub sems 'phos pas //
NK053('i)001:15688: mi 'gyur brtan par gser bzhin no //
NK053('i)001:15692: pa ra b+hid ta khang+ka ts+tshin+d+ha h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:15693: lhar skye ba'i sgo yang bgag go //
NK053('i)001:15694: de ltar rigs lnga yab yum la cho ga rnam pa gsum gsung yig 'bru /
NK053('i)001:15698: ting nge 'dzan mngon gsum du gsal zhing brtan par gyur nas /
NK053('i)001:15699: ting nge 'dzin gyis sgrol na yang legs /
NK053('i)001:15700: de ltar ma sgrol na yang /
NK053('i)001:15704: sha nye ring gsum btags pa'i phye ma blud cing khong gsal lo //
NK053('i)001:15705: de nas yang dag gi srung ma bzhi la phud btang la /
NK053('i)001:15706: rdo rje slob dpon gyis dgongs pa bsrang /
NK053('i)001:15707: ging gis rgyu shugs sgrol gyi sngags gong du bsnyen pa des btab la bsgral lo //
NK053('i)001:15710: rgyu'i rna lam du ngan song sbyong ba'i snying po sarba durga te /
NK053('i)001:15712: 'byung ba lnga rang bzhin med par sbyong ba'i chos bshad pa /
NK053('i)001:15714: nyon cig sems can rigs kyi bu //
NK053('i)001:15715: khyod kyi sha rus sa yin te //
NK053('i)001:15716: sa la sa yi rang bzhin med //
NK053('i)001:15717: khyod kyi khrag rlan chu yin te //
NK053('i)001:15718: chu la chu yi rang bzhin med //
NK053('i)001:15719: khyod kyi drod ni me yin te //
NK053('i)001:15720: me la me yi rang bzhin med //
NK053('i)001:15721: khyod kyi dbugs ni rlung yin te //
NK053('i)001:15722: rlung la rlung gi rang bzhin med //
NK053('i)001:15723: khyod kyi sems ni nam mkha' ste //
NK053('i)001:15724: nam mkha'i dbyings su khyab gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:15726: da ni gong dang yang mi 'dra ba'i lta ba zab mo rna bar bshi ba ste /
NK053('i)001:15727: rdo rje sems dpa' nam mkha' che //
NK053('i)001:15728: kunabazanga yangs pa chos kyi dbyings //
NK053('i)001:15729: rnam dag lam chen kun sgrol phyir //
NK053('i)001:15730: mi skye mi 'gag cir mi dgos //
NK053('i)001:15731: byams pas don ni rnam sbyang phyir //
NK053('i)001:15732: snying rje chen po cir mi mdzad //
NK053('i)001:15733: che bas che ba'i zab mo yin //
NK053('i)001:15734: yon tan cir yang basngagasa pa med //
NK053('i)001:15735: don rnams ci bzhin mi bskyod do //
NK053('i)001:15736: bya ba med pas grol bas grol //
NK053('i)001:15737: rang byung ye shes btsal med pas //
NK053('i)001:15738: grol nas grol ba'i lam yang ston //
NK053('i)001:15740: de nas 4mtshon gyis mngon sum du bsgral ba ste /
NK053('i)001:15742: ging la dbang bskur ba ste /
NK053('i)001:15743: sbyor ging la dbang gnyis bskur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:15744: sgrol ging la dbang lnga bskur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:15745: ka ta ri ral gri la lam rgyud lnga bcad pa'i ngan song sbyong ba'i /
NK053('i)001:15746: sngags bzlas pa ging la byin te 'di skad du /
NK053('i)001:15748: khyod ni pho nya ging ka ra //
NK053('i)001:15749: ka tar sngon po 'di longs la /
NK053('i)001:15750: khams gsum sgrol bar dbang bskur gyis //
NK053('i)001:15751: skye shi rtsa ba khyod kyis chod //
NK053('i)001:15753: de nas ging chen po rnams kyis 'greng la /
NK053('i)001:15754: rdo rje khu tshur dku g.yas g.yon du brten la /
NK053('i)001:15757: dur khrod chen po gdul ba dang //
NK053('i)001:15758: dbang du bsdu ba'i las brtsam gyis //
NK053('i)001:15759: sangs rgyas kun gyis byin gyis rlobs //
NK053('i)001:15760: bde gshegs mang po kun 'dus shig /
NK053('i)001:15762: mig gis phyogs bcur blta zhing /
NK053('i)001:15763: rngam brjid ldan par byas te /
NK053('i)001:15767: khams gsum thams cad bsgral ba'i zhing //
NK053('i)001:15768: ta na chen po'i las bya'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:15769: byams dang snying rje ldan pa yis //
NK053('i)001:15770: nyon mongs 'khor ba'i rgya bral lo //
NK053('i)001:15772: 'gying bag gi stabs kyis lan gcig bsdigs nas /
NK053('i)001:15773: prad nya mu sa ta ra ma /
NK053('i)001:15774: ma nu da ra ma h+aa m+aam sa da ra phata /
NK053('i)001:15776: rgyu gang yin de bskyel te gan rkyal du bzhag nas /
NK053('i)001:15777: de la khro bo bcu'i sngags dang phyag rgya bya zhing /
NK053('i)001:15778: thabs kyi zhags pa nas 'byung ba'i /
NK053('i)001:15780: bskal pa me ltar 'bar ba yi //
NK053('i)001:15782: khro bo khro mo rnams bzhugs pa //
NK053('i)001:15783: sku ni cir yang sgyur ba'i gzugs //
NK053('i)001:15785: dbu skra kham gnag ral pa can //
NK053('i)001:15787: mi mnyam khro gnyer sdang mig ni //
NK053('i)001:15788: log par lta ba 'dul ba'i mtshan //
NK053('i)001:15790: mche ba zang yag gtsigs pas ni //
NK053('i)001:15791: skye shi rtsa ba gcod pa'i tshul //
NK053('i)001:15792: sku gsung thugs kyi byin brlabs ni //
NK053('i)001:15793: phyag rgya sna tshogs cir yang snang //
NK053('i)001:15795: thugs rje'i byin rlabs sprin ltar 'khrigs //
NK053('i)001:15797: rngam pa'i sgra skad 'brug ltar sgrogs //
NK053('i)001:15798: sprul pa'i thog thog char bzhin 'bebs //
NK053('i)001:15800: sngon gyi thugs dam chen po ni //
NK053('i)001:15801: klan ka chen po bdud la tshol //
NK053('i)001:15802: kyal ka chen po bgegs la mdzad //
NK053('i)001:15803: dam tshig can la dngos grub stsol //
NK053('i)001:15805: thugs rje chen po'i byin rlabs kyis //
NK053('i)001:15806: bdag la byin gyis rlob mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:15807: bdag gis lhag pa'i bsam pa rnams //
NK053('i)001:15808: grub par byin gyis brlab du gsol //
NK053('i)001:15810: sems kyi chos pas sku mi mnga' //
NK053('i)001:15811: sgra las 'das pa'i sbyor ba ste //
NK053('i)001:15812: bsam dang bral ba'i ye shes lags //
NK053('i)001:15814: srid gsum 'joms pa'i lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:15815: mnyam nyid ngang gis khro la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:15816: khros pas longs spyod mdzad la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:15817: rdo rje 'du 'phro khro la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:15818: zhes brjod stangs stabs zil gnon gyis sgrib pa sbyangs shing dgra bgegs 'dul sbyong byas la /
NK053('i)001:15819: de nas kun gyis gcig dril du /
NK053('i)001:15821: mi 'gyur nam mkha'i rang bzhin la //
NK053('i)001:15824: ces sgo dbye zhing lag g.yas sor mo lnga zla
NK053('i)001:15825: ba'i dal re'i steng na dpal bo 'bru lnga 'od
NK053('i)001:15826: zer kha dog lnga dang ldan pas rgyu'i tsit+ta nas
NK053('i)001:15827: bzung ste phyung tsam na tsit+ta'i nang na yi ge
NK053('i)001:15828: ti du kha bcas pa phyungs te dug gsum rtsad
NK053('i)001:15829: bcad / khasama gsum gnas nas drangs par bsam pa'i
NK053('i)001:15830: ging gi dgongs nyams dang sbyar te slob dpon la
NK053('i)001:15831: bcad / phul / slob dpon gyis b+han+d+ha'i nang du
NK053('i)001:15832: bcug pa'i srog rtsa zhal du gzhibs pa'i tsit+ta'i dkyil
NK053('i)001:15833: na sems kyi rang bzhin ti dud khar gnas pa
NK053('i)001:15834: de rang gi thugs ka'i h'u gi ye shes kyi
NK053('i)001:15835: 'od zer gyis bsregs te h'u dkar po gcig tu
NK053('i)001:15837: dbugs 'phar zhing sha ma grang gi bar der kun dgongs pa gcig tu dril nas de ltar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:15838: gnas 5 spar ba'i dgongs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:15839: de nas h'u de rang gi h'u la bstim pas tshe yi mthud mar byin gyis brlabs //
NK053('i)001:15840: de nas thugs ka'i h'u las slar h'u de h'u zhes pa'i gdams kyis sna'i rtse mor drangs te /
NK053('i)001:15842: rdo rje de 'phros 'dus nas sngags brjod cing rdo
NK053('i)001:15843: rje sems dpa' dkar po zhal gcig phyag gnyis g.yas
NK053('i)001:15844: rdo rje rtse lnga g.yon dril bu bsnams pa gcig
NK053('i)001:15845: b+han+d+ha rin po che'i gzhal yas khang gi nang du
NK053('i)001:15846: zla dkyil la bzhugs su gsol te /
NK053('i)001:15847: de nas yam las rlung dkyil du gyur pas btegs
NK053('i)001:15848: nas stong tshig gi gsal 'debs dang bcas pas rang
NK053('i)001:15849: bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i gnas na zhi khro rab
NK053('i)001:15850: 'byams kyi lha tshogs bzhugs pa'i yab yum thabs shes
NK053('i)001:15851: zung du 'brel ba'i sbyor mtshams kyi mkha' la bstims
NK053('i)001:15852: nas de bzhin gshegs pa'i sras su bskyed de bzhag
NK053('i)001:15853: go // de ltar rnal 'byor pa'i shes rab dang
NK053('i)001:15854: ting nge 'dzin dang snying rje'i sgo nas gnas spor
NK053('i)001:15855: ba'i spyod pa zab mo spyad pa'i tshe na'ang /
NK053('i)001:15856: sngon rnal 'byor gyi chos spyod cing dam tshig 'di
NK053('i)001:15857: lta bu dang blang ba las grub pa'i bde bar
NK053('i)001:15858: gshegs pa dang / grub pa'i rig 'dzin rnams kyis
NK053('i)001:15859: su zhig rnam thar 'di la zhugs pa grogs bya
NK053('i)001:15860: bar thugs dam du zhal gyis bzhes pa lags pas
NK053('i)001:15861: gshegs pa dang / / 'dir gshegs nas sems can
NK053('i)001:15862: chen po 'di 'khor ba'i rgya mtsho las bsgral nas
NK053('i)001:15863: mya ngan kyi skam sar gnas spar ba'i las mdzad
NK053('i)001:15864: du gsol zhes thugs dam bskul bar bya zhing /
NK053('i)001:15865: de ltar thugs dam bskul ba'i rang bzhin can gyi
NK053('i)001:15866: dbyings nas bde gshegs 'khor bcas kun sems can de'i
NK053('i)001:15868: rnal 'byor pa ma zad bde gshegs 'khor dang bcas
NK053('i)001:15869: pa des kyang bsgral bya de 'khor ba las bsgral
NK053('i)001:15870: nas myang 'das su spro ba'am gnas spor ba'i las
NK053('i)001:15872: de dag gi mthu byin la brten nas lhag par yang gnas spor nus so //
NK053('i)001:15873: tha mar 6 gzugs phung la ji ltar bya tshul ni /
NK053('i)001:15875: bskul ba'i rang bzhin sogs man chad ru lu ye
NK053('i)001:15876: shes kyi 'od zer gyis 'phro 'du dang mngon spyod
NK053('i)001:15877: drag po'i phrin las kyis phung po tsam yang mi
NK053('i)001:15878: snang bar sbyangs ba'i phrin las la mar sbyar na
NK053('i)001:15879: / ru lu ye shes kyi 'od zer gyis thugs
NK053('i)001:15880: dam bskul ba'i mthus rang bzhin lhun gyis grub pa'i
NK053('i)001:15881: dpal khrag 'thung gi lha tshogs kun 'dus shing byon
NK053('i)001:15882: / pas na / 'dus pa des kyang bsgral bya'i
NK053('i)001:15883: gnas ngan sbyong zhing rnam par shes par rang rang
NK053('i)001:15884: gi rigs su byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK053('i)001:15885: 'khor ba nas myang 'das su gnas spor ba'i phrin
NK053('i)001:15886: las mdzad pa ni phung po mchod par phul ba
NK053('i)001:15887: bya ste / tsit+ta slar khog par bcug /
NK053('i)001:15888: dkyil 'khor gyi phyogs bzhir res mos su bzhag la /
NK053('i)001:15889: phyogs bzhir bro chen po bzhis sbyangs /
NK053('i)001:15890: mjug tu las bzhi mthar phyin pa'i phyi las bzhi'i bros sbyangs /
NK053('i)001:15891: de nas ging gis bshags sbyangs dang smon lam brjod do //
NK053('i)001:15893: sh+r+ai sha ru sogs sngags ring brjod la /
NK053('i)001:15894: snying gshags la bdud rtsis bkrus pa'i snying khrag b+han+d+ha gang /
NK053('i)001:15895: dpal khrag 'thung gi lha tshogs dang yang dag gi srung ma bzhi la bstod bskul byas te bstab /
NK053('i)001:15896: de nas rgyal po rgyal thebs kyis tsit+ta b+han+d+hara bcug ste /
NK053('i)001:15897: mchod pa dang smon lam rnams rgyas par bya ba'i
NK053('i)001:15898: sgo nas bsgral bya'i phung po'i dngos po dag kyang
NK053('i)001:15899: mchod pa'i rdzas su bsngo bar bya ste /
NK053('i)001:15900: dkyil 'khor du mchod rdzas su dgram pa dang sgrub pa po rnams kyis spyad cing bza' bar bya'o //
NK053('i)001:15901: de ltar mnyam pa nyid gdengs su gyur cing sgyu
NK053('i)001:15902: ma'i rten 'brel la blo gnad du tshud pa'i shes
NK053('i)001:15903: rab mtshungs pa med pa dang shin tu gdul daka'i
NK053('i)001:15904: 'gro ba la lhag par brtse ba'i snying rje chen
NK053('i)001:15905: po mtshungs pa med pas kun nas bslangs te /
NK053('i)001:15906: dngos gzhi chos nyid ci yang ma yin pa las
NK053('i)001:15907: cir yang 'char du rung ba'i tshul mkhyen pa'i shes
NK053('i)001:15908: rab kyis zin cing don la gnad du 'byor ba'i
NK053('i)001:15909: ting nge 'dzin gyis ji ltar dmigs shing sbyar ba
NK053('i)001:15910: ltar las su rung ba'i mthu dang sngags kyi thabs
NK053('i)001:15911: mkhas zab mo stobs su gyur pas na /
NK053('i)001:15912: gdul bya'i las ngan rgyun gcod par nges pa'i rtogs
NK053('i)001:15913: pa gdengs su gyur pa'i sgo nas bsgral bas 'bras
NK053('i)001:15914: bu 'tsheng ba gsum ldan du grub pa de ni
NK053('i)001:15915: sngags kyi spyod pa kun gyi mthar thug pa yin
NK053('i)001:15916: pas / dus la babs kyang dang du ma blang na sngags kyi dam tshig nyams /
NK053('i)001:15917: gdul bya'i las ngan rgyun mi chod /
NK053('i)001:15918: bdag gi dngos grub mi 'grub pa la sogs skyon yod la /
NK053('i)001:15919: tshul bzhin dang du blang bas lha mchog tu mnyes shing dngos grub chen po myur du thob /
NK053('i)001:15920: gdul bya'i las ngan rgyun chod /
NK053('i)001:15921: ya mtshan chen po sngags kyi grub pa'i brtul zhugs
NK053('i)001:15922: thams cad la dbang 'byor bar 'gyur bas phan yon
NK053('i)001:15923: mtha' yas so // 'di'i ma dper gong gi rtags mtshams su //
NK053('i)001:15924: 'dir mtshams chad dpe gzhan la blta /
NK053('i)001:15926: rtags bar ldeb 2'jam mgon mi pham don bsdus kyis kha skong yod /
NK053('i)001:15928: dngos grub dbang gi phrin las la don drug ste /
NK053('i)001:15929: dngos grub kyi bar chad byed pa'i bgegs bzlog pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15930: dngos grub kyi mtshan ma mthong na'ang re dogs kyi sems mi bskyed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15931: lha dang bgegs kyi mtshan ma ngo shes par byas te nyams kyi man ngag bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15932: bar chad kyi bgegs yin na mnan pa bya ba'i thabs bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15933: ston pa'i lung bzhin du dus dang rtags la brtag ste bsgrub pa chen po brtsam pa dang /
NK053('i)001:15934: dngos grub blang zhing dbang bskur ba'o /
NK053('i)001:15937: dngos grub kyi bar chad byed pa'i bgegs bzlog pa gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:15938: bar chad byed pa'i bgegs chen yang //
NK053('i)001:15939: 'jigs pa med pa'i sems kyis bzlog /
NK053('i)001:15942: bar chad kyi bgegs nyams kyi phyag rgyas bsad cing zil gyis mnan pa'i skabs te bcu drug pa /
NK053('i)001:15943: mtha' drug las la dor ba spyod pa /
NK053('i)001:15944: yo byad gnyis las thabs kyi ting nge 'dzin /
NK053('i)001:15945: dkyil 'khor dgu las thugs rje phrin las kyi dkyil 'khor /
NK053('i)001:15946: lung dgu las bgegs chen mnan pa'i lung ngo //
NK053('i)001:15947: dang po bsnyen pa nas tha ma dngos grub ma thob kyi bar du /
NK053('i)001:15948: dge ba srog dang 'dra ba'i bar du gcod pa'i bgegs chen po drug ste /
NK053('i)001:15949: de dag kyang 'jigs pa med pa skye ba med pa'i dbyings las /
NK053('i)001:15950: skye ba'i cho 'phrul sku phyag rgya chen po'i ting nge 'dzin gsal la ma g.yos pas /
NK053('i)001:15951: gzhan gyi 'jigs pa med pa'i sems la gnas nas bzlog par bya ba ste /
NK053('i)001:15952: de yang dgong mo nyi ma nyur na /
NK053('i)001:15953: nub phyogs nas srin po sha treng gseng bu'i bu mo //
NK053('i)001:15954: rdzu 'phrul bya rog skad skyur ma zhes bya ba /
NK053('i)001:15955: rkang pa g.yas pa sa la drud nas /
NK053('i)001:15956: kha nas grogs yod zer zhing bsgrub pa'i bar du gcod du 'ong ste /
NK053('i)001:15960: dgong gi ting 'dzin mi gsal na //
NK053('i)001:15961: sngon gyi dus nyul chen mo ni //
NK053('i)001:15962: grib so sdud pa'i dbang mo che //
NK053('i)001:15963: rdzu 'phrul bya rog skad sgyur ma //
NK053('i)001:15964: de yi 'dul byed skal chen mo ni /
NK053('i)001:15965: kha dog nyi ma nub kha'i dmar thag 'dra //
NK053('i)001:15966: ral ba gser sprin 'khrigs pa bzhin //
NK053('i)001:15967: ral pa sprug pa'i skra gseb nas //
NK053('i)001:15968: gza' rgod mig dmar char du 'bebs //
NK053('i)001:15969: a la la yi phyag mtshan ni //
NK053('i)001:15970: gnam lcags zhun ma'i khro chu bskor //
NK053('i)001:15971: khros nas gnyen por rbad pa'i tshe //
NK053('i)001:15972: khro chu khol ma'i skyin mdangs 'bebs //
NK053('i)001:15973: srid pa'i gnam sa grum pa skad //
NK053('i)001:15974: srin po'i 'jig rten rba la g.yeng //
NK053('i)001:15975: dam las 'das pa btso bsreg byed //
NK053('i)001:15976: khyod kyi phrin las skal phog pa //
NK053('i)001:15977: dgong gi bar cha byed pa yi //
NK053('i)001:15978: bdud bgegs thams cad thal bar lhogs //
NK053('i)001:15979: rak+sha ru tra yak+sha tshal pa kha ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:15980: de nas nam gyi srod la rlug lha phyogs skyong gi bu mo /
NK053('i)001:15981: kha thun gyi ba ra tse zhes bya ba rus sbal nag po zhon 'ongs te /
NK053('i)001:15982: sgrub pa po'i dngos grub 'phrog cing bar gcod du 'ong ste /
NK053('i)001:15986: srod kyi ting 'dzin mi gsal na //
NK053('i)001:15987: sngon gyi nyams len chen mo ni //
NK053('i)001:15988: phyogs skyong bu mo ma rungs ma //
NK053('i)001:15989: de yi 'dul byed skal chen mo ni //
NK053('i)001:15990: thogs med rlung ltar rgyu ba mo //
NK053('i)001:15991: srid pa'i rgyal mo srog gi dpal //
NK053('i)001:15992: srid bdag chen mo kun gyi rje //
NK053('i)001:15993: ye shes 'od stong 'bar ba'i rdzu 'phrul can //
NK053('i)001:15994: rtse gcig sgrub pa po yi grogs mdzad ma //
NK053('i)001:15995: khyod kyi phrin las skal phog pa //
NK053('i)001:15996: srod la bar chad byed pa yi //
NK053('i)001:15997: bdud bgegs thams cad thal bar lhogs //
NK053('i)001:15998: rak+sha ru tra yak+sha tshal pa kha ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:15999: de nas nam phyed tsam na /
NK053('i)001:16000: tshangs pa dung gi thor tshugs can gyi bu mo //
NK053('i)001:16001: pra ma na pu ting bya ba /
NK053('i)001:16002: shing dar srub med gyon nas sbyor ba'i tshul ston cing /
NK053('i)001:16004: de bzlog pa'i gnyen po 'di skad du /
NK053('i)001:16006: nam phyed bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK053('i)001:16007: dkar po'i phyogs kyi ma rungs pa //
NK053('i)001:16008: de yi 'dul skal chen mo ni //
NK053('i)001:16009: ral gri'i lus la rkang lag glog /
NK053('i)001:16011: sngags pas gdungs nas bos pa'i tshe //
NK053('i)001:16012: mchi ma thul thul char du 'bebs //
NK053('i)001:16013: thul thul thig pa re res kyang //
NK053('i)001:16014: dkar po'i bu bran mang po kun //
NK053('i)001:16015: gzhob rgod rdog pas barjisa pa bzhin //
NK053('i)001:16016: gso glags med par dmyal thag gcod //
NK053('i)001:16017: rgyal ba'i bka' nyan dam tshig can //
NK053('i)001:16018: khyed kyi phrin las skal phog pa //
NK053('i)001:16019: nam phyed bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK053('i)001:16020: thal ba bzhin du rab tu lhogs //
NK053('i)001:16021: rak+sha ru tra yak+sha tshal pa kha ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:16022: tho rangs skya rengs shar tsam na /
NK053('i)001:16023: gza' ho rton gyi bu mo /
NK053('i)001:16024: ting ting gi mar tse zhes bya ba /
NK053('i)001:16025: lcags kyi gri mchan du bcug nas bar du gcod cing dngos grub 'phrog tu 'ong ngo //
NK053('i)001:16026: de bzlog pa'i gnyen po 'di skad du /
NK053('i)001:16028: tho rangs bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK053('i)001:16029: hor ston bu mo gdug pa can //
NK053('i)001:16030: de yi 'dul skal chen po ni //
NK053('i)001:16031: mgo ni seng ge'i mgo bo la //
NK053('i)001:16032: dud mo seng ge'i nga ro sgrog /
NK053('i)001:16033: srid pa gnam sa grum pa skad //
NK053('i)001:16035: sngon gyi bskal pa dang po la //
NK053('i)001:16036: rgyal ba'i bka' nyan dam tshi can //
NK053('i)001:16037: khyod kyi phrin las skal phog pa //
NK053('i)001:16038: tho rangs bar chad byed pa'i bgegs //
NK053('i)001:16039: bdud bgegs thams cad thal bar lhogs //
NK053('i)001:16040: rak+sha ru tra yak+sha tshal pa kha ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:16041: nyi ma shar kha'i zer la /
NK053('i)001:16042: nam mkha' lding gi rgyal po gser mig can gyi bu mo //
NK053('i)001:16043: blo gros spyan gcig ma zhes bya ba /
NK053('i)001:16044: lcags kyi 'gu ya klad la bskor zhing dngos grub kyi bar du gcod cing 'phrog tu 'ong ngo //
NK053('i)001:16045: de bzlog pa'i gnyen po skad du /
NK053('i)001:16047: shar kha'i ting 'dzin mi gsal na //
NK053('i)001:16048: shar kha'i zer la bar gcod pa //
NK053('i)001:16049: srab mda' ring la zhon pa mo //
NK053('i)001:16050: de yi 'du skal chen mo ni //
NK053('i)001:16051: dung gi mgo la shel gyi lce //
NK053('i)001:16053: gnam lcags thog gi ser chen 'bebs //
NK053('i)001:16054: sngon gyi bskal pa dang po la //
NK053('i)001:16055: rgyal ba'i bka' nyan dam tshig can //
NK053('i)001:16056: khyod kyi phrin las skal phog pa //
NK053('i)001:16057: shar kha'i zer ba bar gcod pa //
NK053('i)001:16058: bdud bgegs thams cad thal bar lhogs //
NK053('i)001:16059: rak+sha dra yak+sha tshal pa kha ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:16061: nyin mo rgyu ba bzhi 'ong ste /
NK053('i)001:16062: de ni klu chen bzhi yin te /
NK053('i)001:16063: 'tshub ma chen por byas nas 'ong ngo //
NK053('i)001:16064: de bzlog pa'i gnyen po rgyud las 'di skad du /
NK053('i)001:16066: sku ni dung gi 'khor lo la //
NK053('i)001:16067: dkar nag gyon pa'i ya mtshan can //
NK053('i)001:16068: srid pa'i gnam ni gos su gyon //
NK053('i)001:16069: grags pa'i sa ni stan du bting /
NK053('i)001:16070: khams gsum 'jig rten pang na khyer //
NK053('i)001:16071: srid pa gsum ni khur du khur //
NK053('i)001:16072: nyi ma'i skyin mda' spyan la 'char //
NK053('i)001:16073: zla ba'i rma mda' zhal nas 'char //
NK053('i)001:16074: lag na ri rab rtse dgu gsor //
NK053('i)001:16075: shin tu mi bzad gtum chen mo //
NK053('i)001:16076: klu 'dul chen mo'i dus la babs //
NK053('i)001:16077: 'di ni dpal gyi pho nya ste //
NK053('i)001:16078: dus la babs po e ka ma //
NK053('i)001:16079: rak+sha ru tra yak+sha tshal pa kha ha na ha na h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:16082: man ngag des zlog par ma gyur na /
NK053('i)001:16083: bdag nyid dpal chen por ting nge 'dzin gzengs bstod pa'i /
NK053('i)001:16084: lus kyi gnas brgyad nas ha brgyad las khro mo ke'u ri ma brgyad /
NK053('i)001:16085: zhal gsum phyag drug par he ru ka gal po ltar /
NK053('i)001:16087: dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i gnyen por rbad la gtang ngo //
NK053('i)001:16088: zor kha chen po brgyad bcas la des bzlog go //
NK053('i)001:16089: dgra bgegs gang la yang de ltar shes par byas la /
NK053('i)001:16090: thabs man ngag las shes par bya'o /
NK053('i)001:16092: 2 / de la dngos grub kyi mtshan ma mthong na yang
NK053('i)001:16093: re dogs kyi sems mi bskyed pa gang snyam pa
NK053('i)001:16094: la / dngos grub sbyin pa'i gzugs can yang //
NK053('i)001:16095: re dang dogs dang dga' ba yis //
NK053('i)001:16096: ngan pa'i don gyi sems mi dbyung //
NK053('i)001:16098: dngos grub sbyin par mdzad pa'i ye shes lha'i gzugs brnyan nam /
NK053('i)001:16100: dngos grub byung na yang dngos grub yin no snyam du re ba dang /
NK053('i)001:16101: thob bo snyam du dga' ba dang /
NK053('i)001:16102: gal te ma yin no snyam pa'i dogs pa'i bsam
NK053('i)001:16103: pa ngan pa'i don dang ldan pa'i the tshom can
