NK053('i)001:16104: gyi sems de lta bu dbyung zhing bskyed par mi
NK053('i)001:16107: 3 / lha dang bgegs kyi mtshan ma ngo shes par byas
NK053('i)001:16108: te nyams kyi man ngag bstan pa gang snyam pa
NK053('i)001:16109: la / phan gnod byed pa rnam gnyis po //
NK053('i)001:16110: gzungs dang sgra dag dri dang ni //
NK053('i)001:16111: rnam pa gsum por 'byung ba na //
NK053('i)001:16112: dogs dang bcas pa'i sems spangs te //
NK053('i)001:16113: bye brag tu ni shes pa bya //
NK053('i)001:16114: nyams kyi phyag rgyas rang don sad //
NK053('i)001:16116: phan par byed pa'i lha dang /
NK053('i)001:16117: gnod par byed pa'i bgegs rnam pa gnyis po gang yin ma nges pa'i mtshan ma dag /
NK053('i)001:16120: dri bsnam pa de gsum las gang yang rung ba zhig byung bar gyur ba /
NK053('i)001:16121: bgegs kyi mtshan ma yin par dogs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:16122: lha'i mtshan ma yin par chags pa dang bcas pa'i sems spangs la //
NK053('i)001:16123: lha dang bgegs gang yin pa'i bye brag ji lta
NK053('i)001:16124: bu yin pa bzhin du ngo shes par bya dgos
NK053('i)001:16125: pa ste / de gang gis shes par bya snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:16126: nyams kyi phyag rgyas rang don sad //
NK053('i)001:16128: de yang bla ma brgyud pa'i nyams kyi man ngag
NK053('i)001:16129: rig pa'i drod tshad dang lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas
NK053('i)001:16130: te / rang gi don grub bam ma grub nyams
NK053('i)001:16131: sad la bye brag tu ngo shes par bya ste
NK053('i)001:16132: te / / de la nyams ni gnyid dbang du gyur nas /
NK053('i)001:16133: nyams la thib thib byed na /
NK053('i)001:16134: srin po 'bum sna'i bu mo 'ong ba'i snga ltas
NK053('i)001:16135: yin pas gnyen po'i pho nya gtong zhing bzlog go
NK053('i)001:16136: // dkyil 'khor byin med pa'i seng seng por song na /
NK053('i)001:16137: nub byang mtshams kyi se skya 'ong ba'i snga ltas yin la /
NK053('i)001:16138: gnyen po'i pho nya gtong zhing zlog go //
NK053('i)001:16139: sgrub po kun khro la 'tshig pa za na gaza'i bu mo yin pas /
NK053('i)001:16141: sgrub pa nyams chung zhing bying bying byed na /
NK053('i)001:16142: 'di ni sa 'og nas dam sri mna' zan yin pas /
NK053('i)001:16143: gnyen po gtong la bzlog go //
NK053('i)001:16144: sgrub po snying mi dga' zhing sgor 'gro na tshangs pa'i bu mo yin pas /
NK053('i)001:16145: gnyen po pho nya gtong la bzlog go //
NK053('i)001:16146: gal te gzhung la bab pa'i dus na nad drag
NK053('i)001:16147: pos btab pa'am snying gcu zhing na bar gyur na
NK053('i)001:16149: gnyen po'i pho nya gtong la bzlog go //
NK053('i)001:16150: gzugs bzang zhing sdug par ston pa dang /
NK053('i)001:16152: snying mi dga' bas sems rmug cing thib thib por 'dug na /
NK053('i)001:16154: de la chags sems mi bskyed cing /
NK053('i)001:16155: zlog pa dang gzir gnon gyi las bya ste /
NK053('i)001:16156: zor kha dang bro la sogs pa yang drag tu bya'o //
NK053('i)001:16157: cho 'phrul chen po dang gzugs mi sdug pa la sogs pa cir yang snang zhing 'byung la /
NK053('i)001:16159: sems gsal zhing nyams dga' na lha byin chen po phebs pa yin no //
NK053('i)001:16160: de yang nyams kyi phyag rgya yang dag par na /
NK053('i)001:16162: sku gsung thugs kyi rtags gsum 'byung ste /
NK053('i)001:16163: sku'i rtags ni lha sku zhal mthong ba dang /
NK053('i)001:16164: gsung gi rtags ni rak+ta kho ba dang ngag la nus pa 'byung /
NK053('i)001:16165: thugs kyi rtags ni mar me mi 'chi ba dang dgongs pa chos nyid du gyur ba'o //
NK053('i)001:16166: rtags ni man ngag las shes par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:16167: yon tan dang phrin las rang bzhin gyis 'byung ngo //
NK053('i)001:16170: lcags kyu'i phyag rgya bcas te /
NK053('i)001:16171: rang gi don de grub bam ma grub pa de /
NK053('i)001:16173: gung mo gnyis gshibs te bsgreng /
NK053('i)001:16174: mdzub mo g.yas pa bkug te lcags kyu ltar byas la /
NK053('i)001:16175: bdag ri rab kyi steng lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyi gnas su phyin la snyam du bsams te /
NK053('i)001:16176: mdzub mo bsgreng bas ri rab kyi steng lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyi gnas su phyin la /
NK053('i)001:16177: slar bdag nyid kyi bsgrub pa'i gnas su 'agro'o snyam du bsams te /
NK053('i)001:16178: mdzub mo bkug pas rang gi bsgrub pa'i gnas su phyin nas rang gi don 'grub pa yin no //
NK053('i)001:16179: de ltar na mtshan ma gang byung ba'i bye brag gis /
NK053('i)001:16180: phan nod kyi bye brag kyang rab 'bring tha ma gsum 'byung bar shes par bya'o /
NK053('i)001:16182: 4 / de ltar mtshan ma gsum byung ba de nyams dang
NK053('i)001:16183: phyag rgyas rang gi don grub bam ma grub sad
NK053('i)001:16184: pas / ma grub na bar gcod kyi bgegs yin te /
NK053('i)001:16185: mnan pa bya ba'i thabs gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:16186: gal te 'byung po mnan par bya //
NK053('i)001:16189: ma grub na bgegs yin pas bzlog cing mnan par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:16190: gong gi dam sri mnan pa'i thod pa dang ling+ga la /
NK053('i)001:16191: ye shes las grub pa'i pho nya dang /
NK053('i)001:16192: las las grub pa'i pho nya dang /
NK053('i)001:16193: rang dang 'brel ba'i srung ma'i pho nyas bkug ste /
NK053('i)001:16202: gdul sbyong drag po'i bros gzir ba dang /
NK053('i)001:16203: de thod tshal la mnan te /
NK053('i)001:16204: khro bo rnams spyi bo bsdus pa'i steng du /
NK053('i)001:16205: yi ge h'u mthing nag las /
NK053('i)001:16206: rdo rje ljang gu rgya gram la /
NK053('i)001:16207: me lce phreng bas bskor ba'i rgya gram gyi dkyil
NK053('i)001:16208: du yi ge su ser po gser btso ma'i kha
NK053('i)001:16211: badz+ra su me trum h'u sa ma ya sh+tam /
NK053('i)001:16213: gser gyi ri rab dpag tshad bye ba /
NK053('i)001:16214: gru bzhi pa gcig tu gyur /
NK053('i)001:16215: de'i steng du bcom ldan 'das don yod grub pa 'khor dang bcas pa'i pho brang btab pas /
NK053('i)001:16216: khro bo rnams kyang shin tu gzir zhing mi g.yo ba dang /
NK053('i)001:16217: bskal pa mtha'i bar du mnan par bsam pa dang /
NK053('i)001:16218: phrin las rnam pa bzhis gzir gnon bya'o //
NK053('i)001:16221: 5 / ston pa'i lung bzhin du dus dang rtags la brtags
NK053('i)001:16222: te bsgrub pa chen po brtsam pa gang snyam pa
NK053('i)001:16223: la / ston pas bstan pa'i lung bzhin du //
NK053('i)001:16224: zhag grangs dus ni brtag pa'am //
NK053('i)001:16225: mtshan ma brtan por byung ba na //
NK053('i)001:16226: bsgrub pa chen po brtsam par bya //
NK053('i)001:16228: de la ston pa dpal rdo rje sems dpas bstan pa'i lung /
NK053('i)001:16229: he ru ka'i gal po las 'di skad du /
NK053('i)001:16230: rnal 'byor gsum gyi dgongs pa yis //
NK053('i)001:16231: bsnyen bsgrub rnam gsum rin par sbyar //
NK053('i)001:16237: bsnyen bsgrub gsum ni mtshan ma'i bsnyen bsgrub dang /
NK053('i)001:16239: zhag grangs kyi bsnyen bsgrub ste /
NK053('i)001:16240: tha mar zhag grangs kyi dus ni /
NK053('i)001:16242: nya la bsgrub pa gdon par dam bcas te /
NK053('i)001:16243: de ltar rnal 'byor pas gong du bstan pa bzhin /
NK053('i)001:16245: sku gsung thugs kyi rtags brtag pa'am /
NK053('i)001:16246: mtshan ma brtan po dngos grub kyi rtags 'od dang sgra dang dri dang gsum 'byung ba na /
NK053('i)001:16247: bsgrub pa chen po brtsam par bya //
NK053('i)001:16249: bsgrub pa chen po 'di brtsam pa'i dus su /
NK053('i)001:16250: rigs ngan gyi bu mo gzhon nu ma mtshan dang
NK053('i)001:16251: ldan pa gnyis kyis dngos grub sgrub pa'i cho ga
NK053('i)001:16252: byas te / de yang rgyud las /
NK053('i)001:16253: sme sha can dang mthun chen gyi //
NK053('i)001:16254: bu mo lo grangs bcu bdun pa //
NK053('i)001:16255: de dag 'grogs nas sgrub pa brtsams //
NK053('i)001:16257: yab yum dang 'grogs shing thabs dang shes rab kyi
NK053('i)001:16258: pha rol phyin pa spyad cing bsgrub pa chen po
NK053('i)001:16259: brtsam par bya'o // de yang dus ji tsam na brtsam snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:16260: rdo rje nyi ma nub nas ni //
NK053('i)001:16261: skya rengs 'char ba'i bar du bsgrub //
NK053('i)001:16263: phyi nang gsang ba gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:16264: phyi ltar na rdo rje bsgrub pa'i zhag grangs tshang
NK053('i)001:16265: ba'i nyi ma dmar thag chad ma thag tu man+dala
NK053('i)001:16266: zhal bsgyur te / zla gam zhal bsgyur /
NK053('i)001:16267: sgo bzhi yang rim pas bsgyur ba dang /
NK053('i)001:16270: gzhal yas khang gsal gdab pa der /
NK053('i)001:16272: bde chen dbyings nas khrag 'thung skur bzhengs te //
NK053('i)001:16273: byams pa'i zhal bzang mngon du ston pa dang //
NK053('i)001:16274: thugs rje'i spyan gyis rtag tu bdag la gzigs //
NK053('i)001:16275: rtse gcig gdung ba'i rnal 'byor bsgrub pa la //
NK053('i)001:16276: kun la byin gyis barlobasa shing bzhugs pa dang //
NK053('i)001:16277: dbang dang dngos grub dus 'di nyid du stsol //
NK053('i)001:16278: zhes ye shes kyi lha rnams la snyan gsan dbab pa ste /
NK053('i)001:16280: bde chen dbyings nas ke'u ri skur bzhengs te /
NK053('i)001:16283: bde chen dbyings nas seng ha sku bzhengs te /
NK053('i)001:16285: bde chen dbyings nas rta gdong skur bzhengs te /
NK053('i)001:16288: b+han+d+ha dang rdzas ril go barje'o //
NK053('i)001:16289: sgrub pa po kun la rtags gdab /
NK053('i)001:16290: dngos grub kyi rdzas ci rigs kyang bsag cing dgod do //
NK053('i)001:16291: rdo rje rgyal thebs kyis dpang gzugs /
NK053('i)001:16293: rgyal pos bsgrub pa chen po'i man ngag bsgrub bo //
NK053('i)001:16294: nang par skya rengs 'char ba'i dus su dngos grub blang ngo //
NK053('i)001:16295: nang ltar na gsang ba'i gzungs ma'i lus kyi khrag
NK053('i)001:16296: chad nas nang du drod g.yos shing pad+ma ze'u 'bru
NK053('i)001:16297: rgyas pa la / rdo rje nyi ma nub /
NK053('i)001:16299: yab kyi lus stobs dang ldan te rdo rje rin
NK053('i)001:16300: po che rgyas te khu ba 'don nus pa la
NK053('i)001:16304: rnal 'byor pa rnams kyi nyon mongs pa rnams rgyun chad de nyi ma nub pa la /
NK053('i)001:16305: sku dang ye shes ting nge 'dzin gyi nyams rnyed pa la brdar /
NK053('i)001:16308: de yang ji ltar bsgrub na /
NK053('i)001:16313: byang chub kyi sems bsgrub pa brtsam zhing bsgrub bo /
NK053('i)001:16315: 6 / de la dngos grub blangs shing dbang bskur ba la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:16316: sgrub pa pos dngos grub blang ba dang /
NK053('i)001:16317: slob ma la dbang bskur ba'o /
NK053('i)001:16319: 1 / sgrub pa pos dngos grub blang ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:16320: rdzas la h'u dbyangs bstod mchod kyis //
NK053('i)001:16322: skabs sbyor bcu bdun pa dngos grub blangs shing sgrub pa chen po'i dus nges pa'i skabs /
NK053('i)001:16323: mtha' drug las rim pa dbang /
NK053('i)001:16325: dkyil 'khor dgu las dngos grub blang ba'i dkyil 'khor /
NK053('i)001:16327: lung dgu las dbang dngos grub gnyis kyi lung ngo //
NK053('i)001:16328: byang chub sems de dang bdud rtsi lngar bsgrub pa gnyis bsres pa dang /
NK053('i)001:16329: ma h+aa rak+ta zangs chen po bkang ba gnyis /
NK053('i)001:16334: h'u tha ma gsum gyi dgongs pa bstan pa bcas so //
NK053('i)001:16335: de las h'u dang po gsum gyi dgongs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:16336: khro bo'i dkyil 'khor bskyed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:16337: spyan drangs bsnyen pa mchod pa yan chad rdzogs pa'i rting la /
NK053('i)001:16338: ye shes sems dpa'i dkyil 'khor la dngos grub bskul zhing blang ba ni /
NK053('i)001:16339: ril dbyangs mthun pas 'di skad do //
NK053('i)001:16340: lta ba h'u dang po'i dgongs pa /
NK053('i)001:16342: nam mkha'i mtha' dang mnyam pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK053('i)001:16343: khyad pa chen po bsgrub pa rgyal ba'i bka'i //
NK053('i)001:16344: snang srid thams cad snang ba chen por shar ba'i sku //
NK053('i)001:16345: ye shes chen pos brgyan pa'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK053('i)001:16346: dur khrod gnas pa'i dpal chen 'khor dang bcas /
NK053('i)001:16347: khams gsum bsgral ba'i don phyir gshegs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:16350: b+han+d+ha chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang gzhal med khang du byin gyis brlabs pa'i nang na /
NK053('i)001:16351: rak+ta ye shes kyi 'od zer dang ldan pa la /
NK053('i)001:16352: bdag nyid ye shes kyi sku 'khor dang bcas par gsal bar bsgom pa des /
NK053('i)001:16355: phyi snod kyi 'jig rten zla gam dbang gi gzhal yas khang du bsgyur /
NK053('i)001:16356: nang bcud kyi skye 'gro ril dngos grub kyi rdzas su bsgyur /
NK053('i)001:16357: bde bar gshegs pa la chos nyid kyi ngang las
NK053('i)001:16358: phyag rgya ye shes kyi skur gsal bar thon nas
NK053('i)001:16359: / mdun gyi nam mkha' la til gyi gong bu bzhin du gtams nas /
NK053('i)001:16360: 'od phung 'dab 'dres shing gsal bkrar bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:16361: h'u dang po gnyis pa'i dgongs pa /
NK053('i)001:16363: byang chub sems dang m+aam sa rak+ta dang //
NK053('i)001:16364: dri chen bdud rtsi'i chu dang rnam pa lnga /
NK053('i)001:16366: sngags dang phyag rgya ting nge 'dzin //
NK053('i)001:16367: rgyu gnyis rkyen gsum sbyar ba'i bdud rtsi 'di //
NK053('i)001:16368: rgyal ba zhi khro'i tshogs la mchod pa 'bul //
NK053('i)001:16371: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa bye brag tu gyur pas mchod de phul bas mnyes par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:16373: h'u dang po gsum pa'i dgongs pa /
NK053('i)001:16375: mnyam pa dbyings kyi pho brang rab 'byams na //
NK053('i)001:16376: zhi khro ma lus rgyal ba yab yum tshogs //
NK053('i)001:16377: khyed la ci mnga' yon tan bsam mi khyab //
NK053('i)001:16378: dmigs kyis bskul zhing dngos grub gsol ba ni //
NK053('i)001:16379: rnam par mi rtog cir yang sa ler mkhyen //
NK053('i)001:16380: thams cad mkhyeen pa'i dngos grub chen po dang //
NK053('i)001:16381: spangs len med pa mnyam pa'i ngang nyid las //
NK053('i)001:16382: lhun gyis grub pa'i dngos grub chen po dang //
NK053('i)001:16383: skye shi med pa tshe yi dngos grub chen po dang //
NK053('i)001:16384: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub chen po rnams //
NK053('i)001:16385: kun rdzob sgyu ma'i tshul gyis gsol 'debs na //
NK053('i)001:16386: dus las mi 'da' rdo rje'i tha tshig can //
NK053('i)001:16387: skyabs las mi g.yel yal gam gcig pa rnams //
NK053('i)001:16388: thugs rje dbang gis dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:16391: thugs dam gyi rgyud bskul te /
NK053('i)001:16392: gnas 'di lta bu na sgrub pa po rnams /
NK053('i)001:16393: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub 'di nod pas /
NK053('i)001:16394: dngos grub stsol ba'i dus la bab pa'i sgra byung bas /
NK053('i)001:16395: thugs dam gyi dbang gis dngos grub stsol cig pa'i nyer bsdogs su gnas par bsgom la /
NK053('i)001:16396: de nas bstod cing bsnyen pa dbul te /
NK053('i)001:16397: h'u bar pa gsum gyi dgongs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:16398: bstod cing rak+ta la h'u dang po'i dgongs pa /
NK053('i)001:16400: bder gshegs thams cad mnyam nyid thugs kyi ngang //
NK053('i)001:16401: ma skyes rdo rje kun tu bzang po ni //
NK053('i)001:16402: thabs la mkhas pas khro rgyal skur ston pa //
NK053('i)001:16403: kun bzang he ru ka la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:16404: rnam dag dgyes chags dpal chen sku la sbyor //
NK053('i)001:16405: yab yum gnyis med h'u gi dbyings nas gsal //
NK053('i)001:16406: mkha' dbyings dkyil 'khor gsang ba'i yum chen ma //
NK053('i)001:16407: yum chen dpal 'bar ma phyag tshal bstod //
NK053('i)001:16408: spyi bo thugs ka ljags steng +aahmh'u la 'bru brgyad bskor byas shing //
NK053('i)001:16410: rnam gsum tshul gyi ma 'khrul bzlas brjod 'bul //
NK053('i)001:16411: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:16412: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16414: bdag gi thugs ka nas ye shes kyi 'od zer las mchod pa'i bye brag tu gyur pas /
NK053('i)001:16415: ye shes kyi lha la mchod pas mnyes par byas /
NK053('i)001:16416: lha'i thugs ka nas ye shes kyi 'od zer tshur 'dus pas /
NK053('i)001:16417: bdag gi sgrib pa sbyangs shing dngos grub kyi snod du rung bar byas so //
NK053('i)001:16419: h'u zhes rak+ta lan gcig gzengs pas /
NK053('i)001:16420: rak+ta las mchod pa'i bye brag tu gyur pas mchod de mnyes par bsam la /
NK053('i)001:16421: h'u bar pa bar ma'i dgongs pa /
NK053('i)001:16422: h'u tshogs rje tshogs bdag dpal chen he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:16423: 'bar ba'i rgyal po khrag 'thung chen po la //
NK053('i)001:16424: rnam dag bdud rtsi dam rdzas mnyes mchod 'bul //
NK053('i)001:16425: thugs rje ches dgongs dbang dang dngos grub stsol //
NK053('i)001:16426: yum yang de bzhin du brjod nas /
NK053('i)001:16428: badz+ra kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:16429: ma h+aa pany+tsa a mri ta kha hi /
NK053('i)001:16430: ma h+aa rak+ta kha ram kh+aa hi /
NK053('i)001:16432: bde chen dbyings nas khrag 'thung skur bzhengs shig /
NK053('i)001:16433: dpal chen khrag 'thung thugs ni rin po che //
NK053('i)001:16434: ru lu ru lu'i phreng bas rab bskor te /
NK053('i)001:16435: lha dang gnyis su med par bdag sbyor bas /
NK053('i)001:16436: rtse gcig bsgrub pa rnal 'byor zab mo'i mthu //
NK053('i)001:16437: deng 'di nyid du bdag la 'bab gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:16440: ye shes kyi 'od zer rtse las lcags kyu mang
NK053('i)001:16441: po 'phros pas gtso bo dang gzungs gang gi dngos
NK053('i)001:16442: grub blang bar bya ba de /
NK053('i)001:16443: mdun gyi b+han+d+ha'i rak+ta'i 'od la bstim pas /
NK053('i)001:16444: sku gsung thugs kyi dkyil 'khor 'od du zhu nas ltem me gnas pa las /
NK053('i)001:16450: h'u mthing ga gsum du gsal ba las /
NK053('i)001:16451: h'u bar pa gsum gyi tha ma'i dgongs pa /
NK053('i)001:16453: lce yi rdo rje'i dam tshig la //
NK053('i)001:16454: rdo rje can gyi h'u bsgoms te //
NK053('i)001:16455: bdud rtsi lnga yi sbyor ba yis //
NK053('i)001:16456: zos nas dngos grub gsum thob 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:16460: blangs te bstim pas sku'i 'od zer ril bdag la thim /
NK053('i)001:16462: +aahblangasa pas gsung gi 'od zer bdag la thim /
NK053('i)001:16464: h'u blangs te thugs kyi 'od zer bdag la thim ste /
NK053('i)001:16465: bdag nyid dkyil 'khor gyi lha gtso gazungangasa gang blangs
NK053('i)001:16466: pa'i sku gsung thugs phyag rgya'i dkyil 'khor du skur
NK053('i)001:16467: gsal la mngon du gyur te /
NK053('i)001:16468: bdag nyid dur khrod brdal ba chen po'i dkyil 'khor thig le rol pa'i sku /
NK053('i)001:16469: rang bzhin gyi dkyil 'khor du gyur pa de kho na dngos grub thob pa yin no //
NK053('i)001:16471: ke'u seng sgo ma yan chad la /
NK053('i)001:16472: bstod pa re dang bsnyen pa bye brag pa re /
NK053('i)001:16474: gong du bstan pa bzhin du rig par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:16476: thugs kha'i b+h+yo dang ru lur bcas pa bsdus te /
NK053('i)001:16479: dngos grub bsdus te sku gsung thugs //
NK053('i)001:16481: de ltar lha re re la /
NK053('i)001:16486: dngos grub blangs pa re re byas pa ni /
NK053('i)001:16487: ye shes lha'i dngos grub ste dang po'o //
NK053('i)001:16493: thun mong rdzas la dngos grub blang ba dang /
NK053('i)001:16494: sku dang ye shes la blangs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:16495: mar me la blangs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:16496: rdo rje dril bu la blangs ba'o //
NK053('i)001:16497: de nas kun gyis 'dzab kyi grangs dbul te /
NK053('i)001:16499: bde bar gshegs pa khro rgyal gtso //
NK053('i)001:16500: bzlas brjod mchod pa bla na med //
NK053('i)001:16501: byin gyis brlabs kyis byin rlobs shig /
NK053('i)001:16502: bzlas brjod bsnyen pa bzhes su gsol //
NK053('i)001:16503: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16504: hoh ye shes kyi bde bar gshegs pa dpal chen po 'khor dang bcas pas pa la /
NK053('i)001:16508: deng nub bsgrub pa chen po bgyis pa'i bzlas brjod kyi grangs /
NK053('i)001:16509: nyin mtshan re la sum stong sum stong thugs kyi gter du 'bul gyi bzhes su gsol /
NK053('i)001:16511: de nas sgrub po kun bzhengs la /
NK053('i)001:16512: dkyil 'khor du bkod pa'i rdzas ril yang //
NK053('i)001:16513: badz+ra a mri ta h'u h+r+ai tha /
NK053('i)001:16514: yi ge dgu pas bdud rtsi chen po'i rang bzhin du /
NK053('i)001:16515: 'dod pa'i yon tan lnga'i rang bzhin du byin gyis brlabs la /
NK053('i)001:16516: bskul byang 'dis gsol ba gdab cing /
NK053('i)001:16518: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16519: zla gam dkyil 'khor rin chen dbang //
NK053('i)001:16520: shar nas nub phyogs ngos su kha bltas te //
NK053('i)001:16523: tshon gang yid bzhin rin po che //
NK053('i)001:16525: ru lu ru lu gnas re che //
NK053('i)001:16526: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16527: dbyangs drug blangs pas don drug grub //
NK053('i)001:16532: des ni dkyil 'khor lha rnams bskyed //
NK053('i)001:16533: zab cing 'brug ltar sgra sgrogs pas //
NK053('i)001:16535: gtum po gdug pa lhan ner gyur //
NK053('i)001:16536: khur ba dbugs kyi rlung 'byin pas //
NK053('i)001:16537: khro bo khro bo'i sprul pa 'gyed //
NK053('i)001:16538: rdo rje srin po'i ngu sgra yis //
NK053('i)001:16539: gdug pa thams cad spa yang bkong //
NK053('i)001:16541: gnod byed ma lus rdul du rlog /
NK053('i)001:16542: tshangs pa dbyangs kyi 'dren tshul gyis //
NK053('i)001:16543: 'khor rnams thams cad dbang du sdud //
NK053('i)001:16544: bdag nyid dpal chen skur bsgoms te //
NK053('i)001:16545: thugs kar gsal ba'i 'bru brgyad po //
NK053('i)001:16546: spro ni phyogs bcu'i nam mkhar spro //
NK053('i)001:16547: bsdus ni bde chen dbyings su sdud //
NK053('i)001:16548: bsgrub ni dpal chen he ru bsgrub //
NK053('i)001:16549: bsnyen ni dus gsum rgyal ba bsnyen //
NK053('i)001:16550: bsten ni ma sring mkha' 'gro bsten //
NK053('i)001:16551: mi gnas ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:16552: ye shes 'od zer slar 'dus ci li li //
NK053('i)001:16553: 'phrul gyi zhags pa rnams kyang dbyangs su bsdu //
NK053('i)001:16555: gser gyi nyi ma rnams ni klong du thim //
NK053('i)001:16556: h'u dang bcas pa'i ru lu'i phreng ba 'di //
NK053('i)001:16557: thugs kyi gter du 'bul lo bzhes su gsol //
NK053('i)001:16558: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16559: zhes brjod pas phyogs bcu nas sku dang ye shes
NK053('i)001:16560: bkrag dang gzi mdangs thams cad 'dus te dngos grub
NK053('i)001:16567: ang ril sogs la thim par bsam mo //
NK053('i)001:16569: byang chub rdo rje'i sangs rgyas la //
NK053('i)001:16570: mchod chen ji ltar mdzad pa ltar //
NK053('i)001:16571: bdag kyang rab tu bsgral slad du //
NK053('i)001:16572: nam mkha'i rdo rje bdag la stsol //
NK053('i)001:16573: zhes rang re'i lha gang yin pa de la me tog dor nas /
NK053('i)001:16574: de nas gsol ba 3gdab par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:16575: hoh bcom ldan 'das dpal chan po sh+r+ai he ru ka yab yum 'khor dang bcas pa rnams la /
NK053('i)001:16576: khyed la ci mang'i dngos grub rnams bdag cag rnal
NK053('i)001:16577: 'byor sgrub pa po rnams la stsal ba'i mod nas
NK053('i)001:16580: thogs pa med pa'i shes rab /
NK053('i)001:16585: khams gsum rnam par rgyal ba'i dbang /
NK053('i)001:16588: las rnam bzhi brtsam pa tsam gyis grub pa /
NK053('i)001:16589: dbang bcu mthar phyin pa dang /
NK053('i)001:16590: rgyal mtshan gyi dpung rgyan bzhin nub pa'i dus med pa dang /
NK053('i)001:16591: rdo rje'i snying po bzhin sra zhing mkhreg pa dang /
NK053('i)001:16592: chu la mi byings pa dang /
NK053('i)001:16593: nam mkha' la yang mi ltung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:16594: brag la thogs pa med par 'gro ba dang /
NK053('i)001:16595: rig 'dzin nam mkha' la 'gro ba la sogs te /
NK053('i)001:16596: rig 'dzin byang chub kyi dngos grub rnams /
NK053('i)001:16597: dus phyis la mi bsdad par /
NK053('i)001:16598: las dang rnam smin la snyad mi gdags par dus
NK053('i)001:16599: deng nus nyid du thob par stsal du gsol lo
NK053('i)001:16600: // de skad ces phyogs phyogs nas brjod nas //
NK053('i)001:16603: shar phyogs 4kyi b+han+d+ha la gsang mtshan dang /
NK053('i)001:16604: dngos grub stsol byang bris pa der /
NK053('i)001:16605: dngos grub bsdus pa'i chang la rdo rjes dkrugs te /
NK053('i)001:16607: bkra shis mtshan ldan rdo rje ka p+aa lar //
NK053('i)001:16608: dngos grub byin bsdus dpa' bo chang gi rol phob //
NK053('i)001:16609: ye shes rtsi bcud gnyis med bdud rtsi 'di //
NK053('i)001:16610: skal ldan sgrub pa po la gnyis med bstim /
NK053('i)001:16611: +aahmh'u sid+d+hi sid+d+hi a la la hoh zhes dbub gang ngam /
NK053('i)001:16614: bsgrub pa'i sa chen rnams kyang dus 'dir bza' 'o //
NK053('i)001:16615: de yan chad du mchog gi dngos grub blangs nas //
NK053('i)001:16616: de nas thun mong gi rdzas 5la dngos grub blang ngo //
NK053('i)001:16617: de nas sku 6dang ye shes la yang dngos grub blang ba ni //
NK053('i)001:16618: khro la khros pas zhi mdzad pa //
NK053('i)001:16619: thugs rje khro dpal rngam pa'i tshogs //
NK053('i)001:16620: 'bar ba'i byin rlabs rmad po che //
NK053('i)001:16621: da lta nyid du bdag la stsol //
NK053('i)001:16623: hoh bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po sh+r+ai he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:16624: yum badz+ra kro ti shwa ri dang gnyis su med pa'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub /
NK053('i)001:16625: bdag rdo rje che ge mo la sogs pas thob /
NK053('i)001:16629: lus ngag yid gsum du bstim zhing bskor ro //
NK053('i)001:16630: de bzhin du lha so so'i ming brjod do //
NK053('i)001:16631: hoh rdo rje mkha' 'gro ke'u ri ma'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub /
NK053('i)001:16632: bdag rdo rje che ge mo bya bas rim pas brjod cing dngos grub blang ngo //
NK053('i)001:16633: de nas dbus 7kyi mar me blangs la /
NK053('i)001:16638: deng nub bsgrub pa chen po bgyis pas /
NK053('i)001:16639: bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po sh+r+ai he ru ka
NK053('i)001:16640: yab yum gyi thugs ye shes su snang ba'i dngos
NK053('i)001:16641: grub / bdag rdo rje che ge mo gsang mtshan /
NK053('i)001:16645: dz+ny+aa na d+ai pa d+ai pa sid+d+hi sid+d+hi h'u /
NK053('i)001:16646: zhes brjod de blangs shing snying khar gtugs pa dang bskor ba bya'o //
NK053('i)001:16647: de nas rdo rje dang dril bu blangs te /
NK053('i)001:16648: hoh bcom ldan 'das dpal chen po sh+r+ai he ru
NK053('i)001:16649: ka yab yum 'khor dang bcas pa bsnyen cing bsgrub
NK053('i)001:16650: pa'i don / don dbyings dang ye shes /
NK053('i)001:16652: 'bras bu sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub bdag che ge mo la sogs pas thob bo //
NK053('i)001:16655: de yan chad du sgrub pa po rnams kyi bsnyen
NK053('i)001:16656: bsgrub mthar phyung nas bsgrub pa chen po'i dus su
NK053('i)001:16658: dngos grub thob par byed pa'i thabs te /
NK053('i)001:16662: de ltar rdzas so so'i tshig gis dngos grub blang ba ni /
NK053('i)001:16663: h'u tha ma gsum gyi dgongs pa lha spyi'i sku
NK053('i)001:16664: gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rdzogs par blang ba ni
NK053('i)001:16672: dbang bskur ba bsdu ba ste /
NK053('i)001:16674: 2 / de la slob ma la dbang bskur ba gang snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:16676: zhes pas bstan pa la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:16681: slob dpon gyis nub phyogs nas /
NK053('i)001:16683: zhes rdo rje shugs kyi phyag rgya btegs pas /
NK053('i)001:16684: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams mdun gyi nam mkha' la
NK053('i)001:16685: smin mtshams yan chad 'od phung 'dab 'dres nas thibs
NK053('i)001:16688: rig pa'i rgyal po mar me dgu pa'i sgrub thabs kyi rgyal po 'di /
NK053('i)001:16689: sku gsung thugs mi zad pa'i rgyan gyi 'khor lo sangs rgyas pa'i 'bras bu lag tu gtad cing /
NK053('i)001:16690: rgyal thabs spyi blugs kyi dbang dus 'di nyid la thob par bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:16691: rnal 'byor dbang phyug las 'phro dang skal par ldan pa rnams la /
NK053('i)001:16692: bdag sgrub pa pos dbang bskur bar 'tshal gyis /
NK053('i)001:16693: bcom ldan 'das ye shes kyi gtso bo he ru ka 'khor dang bcas pa rnams kyis /
NK053('i)001:16694: de bzhin gshegs pa'i dbang rnams bdag la bskur zhing byin gyis brlab tu gsol lo //
NK053('i)001:16696: man+dala gyi dbus su many+dzi chen po'i steng du zhing lpags bting ba der gshegs la /
NK053('i)001:16697: h'u ha he phata badz+ra kro ta sa ma ya h'u /
NK053('i)001:16699: dpal chen po yab yum 'khor dang bcas pa rnams bdag la thim par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:16703: dkyil 'khor gyi lha tshogs rdzogs par bdag la bsgom ste /
NK053('i)001:16704: sgrub pa'i dngos grub dam pa'i rdzas de dang de las bdag nyid dngos grub /
NK053('i)001:16707: dpal dang ldan pa'i b+han+d+ha mchog /
NK053('i)001:16708: rang bzhin gsang ba lcang lo can //
NK053('i)001:16709: bdud rtsis bkang ba'i tshe mchog ste //
NK053('i)001:16710: thams cad dbang gi rang bzhin la //
NK053('i)001:16711: bdag nyid dbus su 'dug nas ni //
NK053('i)001:16712: rang byung ye shes lha rnams la //
NK053('i)001:16713: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub mchog /
NK053('i)001:16714: phyi ma'i dus la mi bzhes par /
NK053('i)001:16715: da lta bdag la stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:16717: bdud rtsi'i snod kha phye la /
NK053('i)001:16718: dwangs ma yi dam gyi lha dang bla ma la mchod /
NK053('i)001:16719: de nas dkyil 'khor gyi lha la mchod /
NK053('i)001:16720: de nas bdag nyid la sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub blang ngo //
NK053('i)001:16721: bdag nyid dbang dang dngos grub thob par byas nas //
NK053('i)001:16722: de nas slob ma 2gzhug par bya ba la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:16726: de la 1gsol ba gdab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:16728: dngos grub 'dod phyir gsol ba gdab //
NK053('i)001:16731: dpal chen po yab yum la gsol ba gdab pa /
NK053('i)001:16741: mchog dang thun mong gis bsdus pa'i dngos grub 'dod par bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:16742: slob ma rnams kyis ru lu gar gyi bros bskor zhing /
NK053('i)001:16743: rgyud las gsungs pa'i dbyangs tshig 'dis gsol ba gdab bo //
NK053('i)001:16744: dang po gtso bo yab yum la //
NK053('i)001:16745: chos nyid g.yung drung rdo rje bdal ba la //
NK053('i)001:16746: 'dul ba'i dbang gi dpal chen skur bstan pa //
NK053('i)001:16747: 'jigs byed chen po dbang phyug he ru ka /
NK053('i)001:16748: 'jigs byed yab yum tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:16749: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16751: drag po'i las kyis 'dul bar dbang bskur na //
NK053('i)001:16752: byang chub sems kyi rnal 'byor sku 'chang zhing //
NK053('i)001:16753: ye shes chen po brnyes pa'i thabs mnga' ba //
NK053('i)001:16754: ye shes chen po'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:16755: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16756: gsum pa ko'u ri brgyad la /
NK053('i)001:16757: bcom ldan khro rgyal khrag 'thung chen po yis //
NK053('i)001:16758: ye shes thugs las sprul pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK053('i)001:16759: khros pa'i tshul ston ye shes 'od zer 'phro //
NK053('i)001:16760: ye shes rdzogs pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:16761: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16763: srid gsum dbang du bsdud pa'i mkha' 'gro ma //
NK053('i)001:16764: sna tshogs kun nas dbang bskur mche gshog can //
NK053('i)001:16765: 'gro ba'i don la thugs rjes dgongs nas ni //
NK053('i)001:16766: lhun gyis grub pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:16767: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16769: phyogs bzhir ye shes bzhi yi don mdzad ma //
NK053('i)001:16770: phyag rgya bzhi dang ldan pa'i rtags 'chang zhing //
NK053('i)001:16771: dngos grub mchog gi phrin las rdzogs mdzad ma //
NK053('i)001:16772: phyag rgya bzhi dang ldan pa'i dngos grub stsol //
NK053('i)001:16773: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16775: ma sring rgya mtsho lta bus grogs mdzad cing //
NK053('i)001:16776: ye shes las la grub pa'i dbang phyug tshogs //
NK053('i)001:16777: thugs dam dbang gis 'khor skyong grogs mdzad ma //
NK053('i)001:16778: rdzu 'phrul myur ba'i phrin las dngos grub stsol //
NK053('i)001:16779: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16781: bdud bdul khro bo mchog gi sku sprul te //
NK053('i)001:16782: thugs rjes gzi ldan gdug pa drag pos 'dul //
NK053('i)001:16783: ye shes rtsal 'chang khro rgyal 'bar ba'i tshogs //
NK053('i)001:16784: dbang bcu rdzogs pa'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:16785: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16787: nyin mtshan rgyu ba'i pho nya'i las mdzad ma //
NK053('i)001:16788: dus bzhir bya ra mdzad cing dgra bgegs 'dul //
NK053('i)001:16789: dpal gyi bka' nyan 'jigs rten skyo mdzad ma //
NK053('i)001:16790: dgra bgegs 'dul ba'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:16791: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16793: phyogs bcu'i sa dang nam mkha'i 'jig rten na //
NK053('i)001:16794: lha dang lha min phra rags gzungs 'chang zhing //
NK053('i)001:16795: gsang sngags rdo rje'i theg chen gnyer len pa //
NK053('i)001:16796: rig 'dzin grub mthu'i dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:16797: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16799: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:16800: bang rim dmar po dag la rten bcas shing //
NK053('i)001:16803: zla gam dmar po dag las dbang nod na //
NK053('i)001:16804: mar me dgu pa dag las mdangs phyung nas //
NK053('i)001:16805: b+han+d+ha mtshan ldan rnams las tha tshig bgos //
NK053('i)001:16806: lha dag gnyis su med par mnyam sbyar nas //
NK053('i)001:16807: ru lu 'bru brgyad bar chad med par bzlas //
NK053('i)001:16808: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa rdzogs par phul //
NK053('i)001:16809: zhag grangs dam bcas bsnyen pa mthar phyin nas //
NK053('i)001:16810: ye shes lha dang rig 'dzin dam can dang //
NK053('i)001:16811: dngos grub stsal ba'i nam dus deng nub btab //
NK053('i)001:16812: ye shes lha dang rdo rje slob dpon gyis //
NK053('i)001:16813: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rab 'byams rnams //
NK053('i)001:16814: sgrub mchog bdag cag rnams la stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:16815: ru lu ru lu h'u b+h+yo h'u /
NK053('i)001:16817: de nas 2me tog dor ba la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:16818: rig pa'i me tog dor zhing byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:16819: dur khrod rdzas kyi me tog dor zhig dbang bskur ba'o //
NK053('i)001:16820: de la rig 1pa'i me tog dor ba ni /
NK053('i)001:16822: gsar ba'i me tog dor ba dang /
NK053('i)001:16825: slob ma rnams kyis me tog thogs la /
NK053('i)001:16826: ru lu brgya rtsa brgyad brjod kyis man+dala lan gsum bskor ba'i dus na /
NK053('i)001:16827: rang rang gi thugs kha nas ru lu 'bru brgyad
NK053('i)001:16828: 'od zer dang bcas par byung nas me tog la
NK053('i)001:16829: thim / de slob dpon yab yum gyi thugs kar thim nas mnyes par bsam zhing //
NK053('i)001:16830: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi bdag po ni //
NK053('i)001:16831: ye shes sku mchog rdzogs pa'i dkyil 'khor la //
NK053('i)001:16832: rig pa byang chub sems kyi me tog 'di 'bul gyis //
NK053('i)001:16833: gnyis med rig pa'i dbyings su thim nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:16834: bdag lus bem po dus 'dir sbyangs pa dang //
NK053('i)001:16835: dpal chen skur gyur dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:16838: 'dir sngar dbang thob pa dang bsgrub pa la zhugs pa yin pas /
NK053('i)001:16839: sgo dbye ba dang mig dbye ba mi dgos te /
NK053('i)001:16840: bdud rtsi thogs la 'di skad bya'o //
NK053('i)001:16841: rigs kyi bu khyod kyi yi dam gyi lha ni nga yin te /
NK053('i)001:16842: ngas ji skad du bsgo ba bzhin du khyod kyis
NK053('i)001:16843: kyis la dam tshig phog pa las ma 'da' shig
NK053('i)001:16844: / gal te dam tshig nyams na rang rgyud 'tshig te 'agro'o //
NK053('i)001:16845: ma nyams na sangs rgyas kyi sa la nges par 'gro ba yin pas khe nyen che'o //
NK053('i)001:16847: lce la bdud rtsi rtsi bzhag la dam tshig bsnan no //
NK053('i)001:16848: de la byin gyis brlabs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:16849: slob ma'i 'og tu ma las nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor bskyed la /
NK053('i)001:16850: de'i steng du slob ma bzhag ste /
NK053('i)001:16851: bdag nyid yab yum gnyis su med pa'i mkha' rnam gnyis las /
NK053('i)001:16852: ye shes kyi 'od zer mgar ba'i tsh+wa tsh+wa ltar
NK053('i)001:16853: rno la myur ba mang po slob ma'i lus la
NK053('i)001:16854: 'phros pas // nye bar len pa'i phung po bsregs /
NK053('i)001:16856: de'i sems kyi rang bzhin yi ge h'u dkar po gcig tu gsal ba las /
NK053('i)001:16857: 'phros 'dus pa las rdo rje gcig tu gyur /
NK053('i)001:16858: de 'phros shing 'dus pa las rang rang gi yi dam gyi lha'am /
NK053('i)001:16859: dpal chen po nyid du rtsa ba'i sngags kyis bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:16861: lha de nyid sngags dang phyag rgyas me tog de spyi bor bzhag cing dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:16862: dur 2khrod rdzas kyi me tog dor ba ni /
NK053('i)001:16866: dbang rdzas byin gyis brlabs pa dang /
NK053('i)001:16868: dang po me tog dor ba /
NK053('i)001:16869: slob ma rnas kyis gsol byang bris la dar du bstums pa la 'di skad brjod do //
NK053('i)001:16870: bka' gsang rmad du byung ba'i dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK053('i)001:16871: dur khrod rdzas kyi me tog 'di bor bas //
NK053('i)001:16872: sngon tshe bsgrub pa'i lha ni gang yin pa'i //
NK053('i)001:16873: sku gsang thugs kyi dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:16876: de nas slob ma'i 3lag tu rdo rje phyed byin la /
NK053('i)001:16877: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor 'dir //
NK053('i)001:16878: byang chub rdo rje'i lam du drangs nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:16879: gzhung bzhin bsgrub pa'i rnal 'byor khyed rnams la //
NK053('i)001:16880: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub sbyin par bya //
NK053('i)001:16882: gsum pa dbang rdzas byin gyis brlab pa /
NK053('i)001:16883: slob 3dpon nyid kyis b+han+d+ha dang kham phor rnams blangs te /
NK053('i)001:16887: dkyil 'khor gyi lha gsal btab nas /
NK053('i)001:16888: bdag nyid dpal chen sku bsgom ste //
NK053('i)001:16889: zhes bya ba la sogs tshig rkang bcu gsum dang ru lu brjod pas /
NK053('i)001:16890: nam mkha' la yod pa dang /
NK053('i)001:16892: thugs ka rnam gnyis nas ru lu 'bru brgyad 'od zer dang bcas par 'phros pas /
NK053('i)001:16893: phyogs bcu dus gsum gyi bde bar gshegs pa thams cad kyi sku dang ye shes dang /
NK053('i)001:16894: sems can thams cad kyi bkrag dang /
NK053('i)001:16896: rtsi bcud thams cad bsdus te /
NK053('i)001:16897: b+han+d+ha dang dbang rdzas la thim pas /
NK053('i)001:16898: b+han+d+ha dang dbang rdzas rnams la ye shes kyi byin rlabs zhugs nas /
NK053('i)001:16899: ye shes kyi sku dang 'od zer dang /
NK053('i)001:16900: gzi byin dang ldan par bsgoms la /
NK053('i)001:16901: bzhi pa dbang bskur ba dngos la /
NK053('i)001:16902: dang po bum pa'i dbang bskur te /
NK053('i)001:16903: gong du bstan pa bzhin du shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:16912: dang po dpal chen po gnas zhal gyi dbang /
NK053('i)001:16913: 'di rnams re re la yang dbang bskur ba dngos dang /
NK053('i)001:16914: gyur shog gi smon lam gnyis gnyis so //
NK053('i)001:16915: de nas b+han+d+ha kham phor rnams kyis dbang bskur te /
NK053('i)001:16917: mtshan ma'i spros bral b+han+d+ha'i rdzas mchog 'di //
NK053('i)001:16918: sngon gyi skyes mchog sgrub po'i rdzas yin te //
NK053('i)001:16919: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK053('i)001:16920: dpal chen sku gsum dngos grub thob par shog /
NK053('i)001:16921: badz+ra sh+r+ai he ru ka badz+ra kro ti shwa ri s+t+wam /
NK053('i)001:16922: badz+ra ka p+aa la d+harma k+aa ya sam b+ho k+aa ya nirma k+aa ya a b+hi shiny+tsa a /
NK053('i)001:16923: deng che ge mo khyod la /
NK053('i)001:16926: don chos nyid skye 'gags med pa'i klong nas /
NK053('i)001:16927: rtags rig pa'i ye shes dpal chen po'i skur shar nas /
NK053('i)001:16928: thugs rje'i sprul pas 'gro ba sems can gyi don
NK053('i)001:16929: bya ba la thogs pa med cing mthu dang ldan
NK053('i)001:16930: pa'i dbang thob par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:16932: gnyis su na deng che ge mo khyod la /
NK053('i)001:16933: rdo rje slob dpon ngas b+han+d+hasa dbang bskur bas /
NK053('i)001:16934: dpal chen po'i skur grub ste khro bo'i gar dgu dang /
NK053('i)001:16936: gsung grub ste ru lu 'bru brgyad dang /
NK053('i)001:16937: thugs grub ste chos nyid skye 'gags med pa'i don rtogs te /
NK053('i)001:16938: sku gsum lhun gyis grub ste rang don mthar phyin /
NK053('i)001:16939: gzhan don mthar 'byin pa la thogs pa med pa'i mthu dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:16941: bar 'dir sku gsung thugs kyi dbang dang /
NK053('i)001:16942: ye shes lnga'i dbang ni gong dang mthun par bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:16944: de nas mkha' 'gro ma'i b+han+d+ha tshal bu brgyad re re blangs zhing bskur te /
NK053('i)001:16945: mtshan ma'i spros bral b+han+d+ha'i rdzas mchog 'di //
NK053('i)001:16946: sngon gyi skyes mchog sgrub po'i rdzas yin te //
NK053('i)001:16947: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK053('i)001:16948: ke'u ri'i sku gsung dngos grub thob par shog /
NK053('i)001:16950: badz+ra ka p+aa la a b+hi shiny+tsa +aah rdo rje
NK053('i)001:16951: mkha' 'gro ko'u ri ma'i sku gsung thugs kyi dngos
NK053('i)001:16953: dbang dang byin rlabs thob pa gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:16957: seng ha ma dang sgo ma dbang mo la sogs /
NK053('i)001:16958: lha rdzogs par ri mo dang tsakli la brten nas
NK053('i)001:16959: so so'i mtshan dang yon tan brjod de dbang bskur
NK053('i)001:16961: de nas mar mes dbang bskur te /
NK053('i)001:16962: dpal chen yab yum gsang ba'i thugs bsdus pas //
NK053('i)001:16963: skye med dbyings nas ye shes mer gsal ba'i //
NK053('i)001:16964: kun gzhi gnas gyur spyan dgu'i ye shes sbyin //
NK053('i)001:16965: sgrub pa phyi bsal ye shes gsal bar shog /
NK053('i)001:16967: rdo rje slob dpon ngas mar me'i dbang bskur bas
NK053('i)001:16968: sgrib pa thams cad byang zhing dag nas dpal chen
NK053('i)001:16969: po ye shes dgu'i dbang dang dngos grub thob par
NK053('i)001:16970: gyur cig / gnyis gyur smon lam yang gdab bo //
NK053('i)001:16972: de nas rdo rje dril bu'i dbang yang gong bzhin du bskur /
NK053('i)001:16974: de nas dpal gyi chas brgyad kyi dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:16976: de nas sgrub pa'i rdzas bdud rtsi'i bum pa blangs la /
NK053('i)001:16977: bdag nyid kyi thugs ka nas yi ge h'u las /
NK053('i)001:16979: b+han+d+ha bdud rtsi la babs pas bdud rtsi lnga las dpa' bo 'bru lngar gyur /
NK053('i)001:16980: 'bru lnga las phyag mtshan lngar gyur /
NK053('i)001:16981: phyag mtshan las rigs lnga he ru ka lnga'i skur gyur te /
NK053('i)001:16982: sku tshon gang ba re re slob ma'i gnas lngar bstim zhing /
NK053('i)001:16983: rigs rnam pa lngar gyur par bsam zhing 'dis dbang bskur ro //
NK053('i)001:16984: dang po dri chen gyi dbang //
NK053('i)001:16985: zas mchog dri chen gser mdog 'dzin pa //
NK053('i)001:16986: rnam rtog nyid las ye shes bskyed pa 'dis //
NK053('i)001:16987: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK053('i)001:16988: de bzhin nyid kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK053('i)001:16989: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa k+aa ya badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aad+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:16990: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs sku rdo rje chen po'i dag pa nga'i bdag yin /
NK053('i)001:16992: rdo rje slob dpon ngas dri chen gyi dbang bskur bas /
NK053('i)001:16993: de bzhin gshegs pa'i rigs kyi dbang dang dngos grub
NK053('i)001:16994: thob nas chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes dang ldan
NK053('i)001:16995: par gyur cig / gyur shog smon lam yang 'agre'o //
NK053('i)001:16996: gnyis pa byang chub sems kyi /
NK053('i)001:16997: skye med byang chub sems kyi rdzas mchog 'di //
NK053('i)001:16998: dkar la dwangs pa gnyis med byang chub sems //
NK053('i)001:16999: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK053('i)001:17000: rdo rje rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK053('i)001:17001: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa tsit+ta badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aad+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:17004: byang chub sems kyi dbang bskur bas /
NK053('i)001:17005: rdo rje'i rigs kyi dbang dang dngos grub thob nas /
NK053('i)001:17006: me long lta bu'i ye shes dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:17008: ma rig khams gsum 'khor ba'i sems can rnams //
NK053('i)001:17009: dug gsum bsgral ba'i dam rdzas sha chen 'di //
NK053('i)001:17010: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK053('i)001:17011: rin chen rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK053('i)001:17012: sarba ta th+aa ga ta a nu r+aa ga dz+ny+aa na badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aad+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:17014: rdo rje slob dpon ngas sha chen gyis dbang bskur bas /
NK053('i)001:17015: rin po che'i rigs kyi dbang dang dngos grub thob par gyur nas /
NK053('i)001:17016: mnyam pa nyid kyi ye shes dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:17018: gsang ba mchog gi rdzas mchog rak+ta 'di //
NK053('i)001:17019: chags med bde bar byed pa'i rak+ta 'dis //
NK053('i)001:17020: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK053('i)001:17021: pad+ma rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK053('i)001:17022: sarba ta th+aa ga ta ma h+aa wak+ka badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aad+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:17024: rdo rje slob dpon ngas rak+tasa dbang bskur bas /
NK053('i)001:17025: pad+ma rigs kyi dbang dang dngos grub thob pa gyur nas /
NK053('i)001:17026: so sor rtog pa'i ye shes dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:17028: las mchog grub pa'i dam rdzas dri chu 'di //
NK053('i)001:17029: phyi nang gso mdzad bdud rtsi'i rang bzhin 'dis //
NK053('i)001:17030: skal ldan rnal 'byor 'di la dbang bskur bas //
NK053('i)001:17031: las kyi rigs kyi dngos grub thob par shog /
NK053('i)001:17032: sarba ta t+aa ga ta ma h+aa badz+ra swa b+h+aa wa +aad+ma ko&a ham /
NK053('i)001:17034: rdo rje slob dpon ngas dri chus dbang bskur bas /
NK053('i)001:17035: las kyi rigs kyi dbang dang dngos grub thob par gyur nas /
NK053('i)001:17036: bya ba grub pa'i ye shes dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:17038: de nas b+han+d+ha nas slob ma'i khar bdud rtsi mu tig dkar po lta bur blud cing /
NK053('i)001:17039: slob dpon gyis 'di skad brjod de /
NK053('i)001:17040: deng rdo rje che ge mo khyod la /
NK053('i)001:17041: rdo rje slob dpon ngas bdud rtsi rnam pa lnga'i dbang dang dngos grub byin pas /
NK053('i)001:17042: khyod kyi nyon mongs pa rnam lnga rang dag du zad nas /
NK053('i)001:17043: phung po lnga dang rnam par shes pa tshogs brgyad sku dang ye shes su gsal te /
NK053('i)001:17044: rigs lnga ye shes lnga'i dbang dngos grub thob par gyur nas /
NK053('i)001:17045: sku lnga dang gsung lnga dang thugs lnga dang yon tan lnga dang phrin las rnam pa lnga dang /
NK053('i)001:17046: zhing khams rnam par dag pa lnga thob par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:17049: de nas sha rnam pa lnga dang /
NK053('i)001:17051: 'dod pa'i yon tan rnams pa lnga la sogs pa
NK053('i)001:17052: slob ma'i rgyud dang sbyar zhing dbang ci rigs su
NK053('i)001:17053: bskur bar bya'o // rnam pa gcig tu dbang bskur thabs lnga bcu rtsa gcig gis bya'o //
NK053('i)001:17054: spyir bla ma'i mdzad phyogs dang /
NK053('i)001:17056: man ngag gi sdeb byang gsum po /
NK053('i)001:17058: slob ma byin gyis brlabs shing /
NK053('i)001:17059: ci rigs su dbang bskur bya //
NK053('i)001:17062: 8 / spyi don brgyad pa'i tha ma /
NK053('i)001:17063: las kyi lhag ma'i phrin las bstan pa la don bcu gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:17065: dkyus nyid brjod pas go bar sla ba ni /
NK053('i)001:17066: sbyin 1bsreg he ru ka'i las bzlas 2mkha' 'gro 3skyong ba //
NK053('i)001:17071: kun kyang sems can don du 12bsngo //
NK053('i)001:17073: phrin las kyi rim pa ji ltar bya ba snyam pa las /
NK053('i)001:17074: bsgrub pa chen po'i gtor ma la /
NK053('i)001:17075: ye shes lha'i pho brang bcas pa de la /
NK053('i)001:17076: sku gsung thugs kyi byin bsdus nas /
NK053('i)001:17077: dngos grub blangs pa'i rdzas lhag ma de yang /
NK053('i)001:17078: bsgrub pa'i rdzas yang dag pa yin pas /
NK053('i)001:17079: de la cha gsum du bcad de /
NK053('i)001:17080: cha 1dang po la sbyin bsreg bya bar bstan pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:17081: sbyin sreg gi phrin las kyi rim pa bstan pa dang /
NK053('i)001:17082: dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo ba bstan pa'o /
NK053('i)001:17084: 1 / de la sbyin sreg gi phrin las kyi rim pa bstan pa la ni bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:17089: de la 1me thab bca' ba'i skabs su /
NK053('i)001:17090: phrin las rnam pa bzhi gang la mos pa'am /
NK053('i)001:17091: 'dir zla gam dmar po'i dbyibs su hom khung byas pa'i dbus su /
NK053('i)001:17092: nyi ma rdo rjes mtshan pa bris te /
NK053('i)001:17093: rdo rjes lte ba la h'u gis mtshan te /
NK053('i)001:17094: hom khung gi kha khyer la rdo rje dang me ri bris te /
NK053('i)001:17095: der tsan+dana smug po'i shing rnams dbyibs thab khung ltar brtsig pa bya'o //
NK053('i)001:17096: rdzas 2 bsags pa la bzhi ste /
NK053('i)001:17098: me 'bar bar bya ba'i rdzas dang /
NK053('i)001:17099: las grub pa bya ba'i rdzas dang /
NK053('i)001:17100: thugs dam bskul ba'i rdzas so //
NK053('i)001:17101: de la 1lha mchod pa'i rdzas la gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:17102: mchod pa rnam pa lnga dang /
NK053('i)001:17103: gtor ma'i rdzas de nyid dang /
NK053('i)001:17104: dkyil 'khor du bkod pa'i rang rang gi rdzas so //
NK053('i)001:17105: me 'bar 2bar bya ba'i rdzas la ni /
NK053('i)001:17108: las 3grub par bya ba'i rdzas la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:17109: dgra bgegs gang la bya ba'i ming gzugs dang /
NK053('i)001:17110: sdig pa sbyong bar bya ba'i rdzas so //
NK053('i)001:17114: de nas 3me lha mchod pa'i rim pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:17115: dam tshig sems dpa'i me lha bskyed pa dang /
NK053('i)001:17116: ye shes sems dpa'i me lha spyan drangs shing mchod pa'i rim pa'o //
NK053('i)001:17117: de la 1dam tshig sems dpa'i me lha bskyed pa'i skabs su /
NK053('i)001:17118: yam shing la tshil gyis byugs te dbus kyi mar
NK053('i)001:17119: me las me blangs te me thab kyi nang du
NK053('i)001:17120: bcug ste / ting nge 'dzin gyis dpal chen po'i thugs ka nas /
NK053('i)001:17121: yi ge ram dmar po 'od dang bcas pa gcig byung nas thab khung du gsal ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17122: de las me'i ril ba gcig du bsam te /
NK053('i)001:17123: de las spro bsdu byas pa las /
NK053('i)001:17124: ag+ne ye dz+wa la dz+wa la h'u phata /
NK053('i)001:17126: me lha drang srong khros pa'i cha byad can /
NK053('i)001:17127: zhal gcig la phyag bzhi pa /
NK053('i)001:17128: g.yas dang po na lcags kyu /
NK053('i)001:17132: zangs kyi ra skyes la bcibs pa /
NK053('i)001:17133: dur khrod me 'bar ba'i klong na bzhugs pa gcig tu bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:17134: de nas 2ye shes sems dpa'i me lha spyan drangs shing mchod pa'i rim pa ni /
NK053('i)001:17136: dang po spyan drangs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:17138: ye shes can gyi spyod yul nas //
NK053('i)001:17139: me lha drang srong 'khor dang bcas //
NK053('i)001:17140: dad pa dang ni dam tshig gis //
NK053('i)001:17141: tshur gshegs tshur gshegs me yi lha //
NK053('i)001:17142: sems can don la dam tshig dgongs //
NK053('i)001:17144: dzahmh'u bam hoh ag+na ye dz+ny+aa na swa ta ye
NK053('i)001:17145: e h+ye hi b+ha ga w+aan ma h+aa ka ru
NK053('i)001:17146: ni ka tri sha hoh sa ma ya hoh sa
NK053('i)001:17147: ma ya s+t+wam / zhes phyag rgya rnam pa bzhis dzahmh'u bam hoh spyan drangs te /
NK053('i)001:17148: gnyis pa bzhugs shing brtan pa /
NK053('i)001:17150: gzi brjid 'bar ba me yi lha //
NK053('i)001:17151: 'dod pa thams cad rab bsgrub cing //
NK053('i)001:17152: thugs rjes sems can don mdzad pa //
NK053('i)001:17154: ag+ne ye sa ma ya tish+tha lhan /
NK053('i)001:17155: zhes dbyer med du bstim zhing bzhugs su gsol /
NK053('i)001:17157: pad+ma rigs las grub pa yi //
NK053('i)001:17158: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK053('i)001:17159: phrin las kun gyi dpang po mdzod //
NK053('i)001:17161: ag+ne ye a la la hoh a ti pu hoh pra ti pu hoh zhes phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:17163: de nas mchod pa'i rdzas bstan pa la /
NK053('i)001:17164: mchod pa rnam pa lnga dbul lo //
NK053('i)001:17165: gong du zhi ba'i skabs su bstan pa bzhin dbul lo //
NK053('i)001:17166: lnga pa tshil chen gyi mar dang gtor ma 'bul ba /
NK053('i)001:17167: gtor ma'i rdzas nyid dbul ba'i dus su /
NK053('i)001:17169: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK053('i)001:17170: ra skyes chibs ni glog bsam mgyogs //
NK053('i)001:17171: bsregs mdzad kun gyi phyag tshang mdzad //
NK053('i)001:17172: tshim byed khyed la mchod pa 'bul //
NK053('i)001:17173: na ma sa man+ta bu ta nan /
NK053('i)001:17174: bi ma la ag+ne ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:17175: zhes brjod de tshil chen gyi mar sbreng ngo //
NK053('i)001:17176: de nas gtor ma'i rdzas dbul te /
NK053('i)001:17178: me lha'i rgyal po drang srong mchog /
NK053('i)001:17179: mnyam pa'i ngang las kun snang yang //
NK053('i)001:17180: chos nyid ngang las ma g.yos pas //
NK053('i)001:17181: ye shes sku la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK053('i)001:17182: ye shes klong yangs 'khyil ba'i hom khung 'dir //
NK053('i)001:17183: dam rdzas bdud rtsi 'bar ba'i sbyin sreg 'di //
NK053('i)001:17184: drang srong me lha'i zhal du mchod pa 'bul //
NK053('i)001:17185: bdag la sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub stsol //
NK053('i)001:17186: na ma sa man+ta bu ta nan sarba pany+tsa a mri ta ba ling+ta ag+na ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:17188: de nas me 'bar bar bya ba'i rdzas bud shing dbul te /
NK053('i)001:17189: khre te ha na badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:17191: de nas sdig pa sbyong ba'i rdzas til la bzlas te /
NK053('i)001:17192: sarba p+aa pam da ha na badz+ra ye s+w+aa h+aa /
NK053('i)001:17194: bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK053('i)001:17195: mched lcam dral gsang mtshan ming gis bsdus pa rnams
NK053('i)001:17196: kyi las dang nyon mongs pa las gyur pa'i sdig
NK053('i)001:17197: sgrib pa ma lus pa thams cad sbyong du gsol
NK053('i)001:17198: lo // zhes byas te thab khung du gtor ro //
NK053('i)001:17200: de nas nyungs kar la sngags bzlas te /
NK053('i)001:17201: dgra bgegs gang la bya ba'i phyogs su gtor te /
NK053('i)001:17202: dgra bgegs bkugs la gzugs la dbab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:17203: de la phur pas btab ste /
NK053('i)001:17204: mtshon cha'i char phab nas dum bur byas te dbul bar bya ba yin no //
NK053('i)001:17206: de kun gyi mthar bstod pa bya ste /
NK053('i)001:17208: me lha'i rgyal po drag srong mchog /
NK053('i)001:17209: bdud bzhi 'joms pa'i phyag bzhi pa //
NK053('i)001:17210: zhal bzhis las bzhi grub par byed //
NK053('i)001:17211: las kun mdzad la phyag 'tshal bstod //
NK053('i)001:17213: rig pa'i rgyal po drang srong me lha chen po khyod kyis las thams cad byed pas //
NK053('i)001:17214: bsreg rdzas lha'i zhal du dbul ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17215: me nyid ye shes kyi mer byin gyis brlab pa dang /
NK053('i)001:17216: bdag cag gi phrin las thams cad grub par mdzad du gsol lo //
NK053('i)001:17218: de ltar me lha mchod pa'i skabs 'dir don man ngag gi dbye ba gsum ste /
NK053('i)001:17219: dang po me lha de nyid la gnyis su phye ste /
NK053('i)001:17220: ye shes kyi me lha shar lho'i mtshams su gshegs su gsol te dpang po lta bur bzhugs la /
NK053('i)001:17221: dam tshig gi me lha 'od du 'bar nas thabs khung ye shes kyi me 'bar ba'i klong du /
NK053('i)001:17222: dkyil 'khor gyi lha rnams der spyan drangs te mchod par bya /
NK053('i)001:17223: zhes rgyud lung kha cig las bshad do //
NK053('i)001:17225: me lha de nyid kyi thugs ka ru /
NK053('i)001:17226: bla gam dbang gi gzhal yas khang du bskyed la /
NK053('i)001:17227: der so so'i yig 'bru las lha rnams so sor bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:17228: lha rnams spyan drangs shing bstims la /
NK053('i)001:17233: ye shes kyi me lha dbyer med pa de la mchod bstod byas nas /
NK053('i)001:17237: me lha nyid thugs rje'i ye shes kyi me 'bar
NK053('i)001:17238: ba'i klong du dpal khrag 'thung gi lha rnams spyan
NK053('i)001:17240: mchod 4pa'i rdzas phul te mnyes par bya ba ni /
NK053('i)001:17241: dang po la mchod pa rnam pa lnga dbul /
NK053('i)001:17244: lha rang rang gi dkyil 'khor du bkod pa'i rdzas dbul ba ni /
NK053('i)001:17245: gong du smos pa'i bstod pa /
NK053('i)001:17246: mi gnas ye shes chos skur dag pa la //
NK053('i)001:17247: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'i mjug tu /
NK053('i)001:17249: zhes pa'i tshig bzhi pa rer bsdebs te mchod pa bya'o //
NK053('i)001:17250: de la don gyi dgongs pa ni /
NK053('i)001:17251: 'byung ba'i me ni lus lta bu /
NK053('i)001:17252: me'i lha ni dbang po lta bu /
NK053('i)001:17253: de la brten pa'i mchod pa'i lha ni rnam par shes pa lta bu'o //
NK053('i)001:17254: mchod pa'i rdzas ni khams kyi zas lta bu'o //
NK053('i)001:17255: tshul 'di lta bu'i sgo nas mchod par byas pas /
NK053('i)001:17256: ye shes kyi lha rnams mchod pas mnyes par bya ba yang yin /
NK053('i)001:17257: gtong rag gtong ba'i tshul yang yin /
NK053('i)001:17260: dngos grub brtan par bya ba'ang yin no //
NK053('i)001:17263: thab khung la bskor ba byas nas /
NK053('i)001:17266: gtum chen dus mtha'i me ltar 'bar //
NK053('i)001:17267: zhes bya ba la sogs pa'am /
NK053('i)001:17270: zhes pa la sogs pas bstod de /
NK053('i)001:17271: ting nge 'dzin gyis dkyil 'khor bsdus la thabs khung du phrin las rnam bzhi'i bro brdung ngo //
NK053('i)001:17272: bsgrub pa'i gtor ma cha bar pa la /
NK053('i)001:17273: he ru ka las 2kyi bzlas pa bya ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17274: lhag 3phud bsres te mkha' 'gro ma bskyang ba lhag ma'i cho ga rgyas bsdus bya ba /
NK053('i)001:17276: las kha tshar las shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:17277: sgrub pa'i gtor ma cha tha ma la mi zad pa'i gter sba 4ba ni /
NK053('i)001:17280: 'khor ba'i chos srid pa'i gtos su snang ba thams
NK053('i)001:17281: cad yum dbyings phyug ma'i dbyings su sbas pa dang
NK053('i)001:17283: dam rdzas bdud rtsir sba ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17285: yab kyi byang chub kyi sems yum gyi dbyings su sba ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17287: phyag rgya chen po'i dkyil 'khor lus la sba ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17289: rdzas kyi dkyil 'khor 'og min du sba ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17291: snang srid yum gyi dbyings su sba ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17293: chos thams cad chos nyid du sba ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17295: he ru ka'i zhal ye shes kyi hom du sba ba'o //
NK053('i)001:17297: de la dus gsum 'du 'bral med par smon lam gdab pa ste /
NK053('i)001:17298: he ru ka'i gal po las /
NK053('i)001:17300: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:17301: sku mchog byang chub sems su rab zhugs pa //
NK053('i)001:17302: snang srid thams cad mi rtag dus byung na //
NK053('i)001:17303: zad med mi zad gter gyi mdun nas bsus //
NK053('i)001:17304: skye shi med pa'i tshe dang 'phrad par shog /
NK053('i)001:17305: dus gsum sku gsung thugs su gter sbas pas //
NK053('i)001:17306: dus gsum rnam par dag pa sku gsum dang //
NK053('i)001:17307: sku gsum 'gyur pa med pa thig le'i gter //
NK053('i)001:17309: rdzogs pa chen po thig le bde chen klong //
NK053('i)001:17310: thig le nyag gcig bde chen klong du gter sbas pas //
NK053('i)001:17311: snang srid thams cad bde chen sa la bkod //
NK053('i)001:17312: lam gyi nang na nye lam bder rdzogs pa //
NK053('i)001:17313: thabs kyi nang na ma nor dam pa'o //
NK053('i)001:17314: zag med byang chub sems kyi gter sbas pas //
NK053('i)001:17315: dus gsum sangs rgyas sems can gnyis med de //
NK053('i)001:17316: mi zad gter gyi dngos grub thob par 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:17320: ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bsdu ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17321: gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bsdu ba dang gnyis /
NK053('i)001:17322: dang 1 po ting nge 'dzin gyi dkyil 'khor bsdu ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17330: lha rnams so so'i snying po'i sgra //
NK053('i)001:17331: h'u ha he phata ces sgra 'byin cing //
NK053('i)001:17332: byang chub sems su gcig par thim //
NK053('i)001:17335: khro bo bcu rang sgra dang chas nas /
NK053('i)001:17337: dbang mo sgo ma bzhi la thim /
NK053('i)001:17338: sgo ma bzhi rang sgra dang chas nas sing ha brgyad la thim /
NK053('i)001:17339: sing ha brgyad rang sgra dang chas nas ke'u ma brgyad la thim /
NK053('i)001:17341: yum yang yab bdag nyid la thim /
NK053('i)001:17342: bdag kyang thugs ka'i ye shes sems dpa' la thim /
NK053('i)001:17343: ye shes sems dpa' yang thugs mtshan dang h'u la thim /
NK053('i)001:17344: h'u yang mas rim gyis zhabs kyu la thim /
NK053('i)001:17348: zla tshes thig le la thim ste /
NK053('i)001:17350: rtag mtha' la mi gnas phyir /
NK053('i)001:17351: skye ba med pa chos kyi dbyings su gyur par bsgom mo //
NK053('i)001:17352: chad pa'i mtha' la mi gnas phyir /
NK053('i)001:17354: de nas snying po dran tsam gyis //
NK053('i)001:17357: de las thugs kyi phyag rgyar 'bar //
NK053('i)001:17359: de las dpal chen khrag 'thung sku //
NK053('i)001:17362: dpal chen po'i skur yang gsal bar bskyed do //
NK053('i)001:17363: de nas 2bzod par gsol ba ni /
NK053('i)001:17364: bdag cag rdo rje slob dpon mched lcam dral 'dir 'dus shing tshogs pa rnams kyis /
NK053('i)001:17365: deng phan chad du bsnyen bsgrub zab mo tshul bzhin du sbyong ba las /
NK053('i)001:17366: tshul bzhin du rngo ma thogs te /
NK053('i)001:17367: lta ba zab mo'i gting ma rtogs shing /
NK053('i)001:17368: spyod pa zab mo dang du ma longs pa /
NK053('i)001:17369: le lo dang gnyid dbang du gyur nas ting nge 'dzin ma gsal zhing /
NK053('i)001:17371: rtsa ba dang yan lag gis bsdus pa'i dam tshig nyams shing /
NK053('i)001:17372: dngos grub kyi gegs su gyur pa thams cad chos nyid kyi ngang du bzod par gsol lo //
NK053('i)001:17374: de nas 2gzugs brnyan gyi dkyil 'khor bsdu ba ni /
NK053('i)001:17375: he ru ka'i gal po las 'di skad du /
NK053('i)001:17377: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:17378: 'phrul zhal yid bzhin nor bu 'dra ba /
NK053('i)001:17380: khams gsum bsgral ba'i dam rdzas sha chen dang //
NK053('i)001:17381: ma rig mun sel mar me dgu pa gsum //
NK053('i)001:17382: 'di la brten te lha dang dngos grub bsgrub //
NK053('i)001:17383: mchod pa ci 'byor phul nas sgrib pa sbyongs //
NK053('i)001:17384: 'khor ba ngan song rnams kyang bsgral lags la //
NK053('i)001:17385: dus gsum rgyal ba rnams kyang mchod lags la //
NK053('i)001:17386: ma sring rgya mtsho rnams kyang brten lags la //
NK053('i)001:17387: mi gnas ye shes thugs kyang bsgrub lags la //
NK053('i)001:17388: dngos grub dbyig mchog rnams kyang blangs lags kyis //
NK053('i)001:17389: dngos grub mchog thob dkyil 'khor gnas 'di nas //
NK053('i)001:17390: ye shes lha dang srung ma 'khor dang bcas //
NK053('i)001:17391: dang po gnas 'og min dang chos kyi dbyings su gshegs //
NK053('i)001:17392: nam zhig bdag gi dam bcas bsgrub pa la //
NK053('i)001:17393: khyed kyi thugs dam mchog kyang de lags la //
NK053('i)001:17394: myur bar slar gshegs par yang dgongs su gsol //
NK053('i)001:17396: dkyil 'khor gyi rdzas rnams bsdu zhing sba ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17397: sa tshon rnams kyang phyag go //
NK053('i)001:17398: de nas smon lam 6gdab pa la gnyis te /
NK053('i)001:17399: yab 1 kyis b+han+d+ha phyag tu bzhes la gdab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:17400: de yang rgyud las 'di skad du 'byung ste /
NK053('i)001:17402: mi gnas ye shes thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:17403: 'gyur ba med pa lhun gyis grub pa dang //
NK053('i)001:17404: rab 'byams rgyal ba'i bka' la dbang thob nas //
NK053('i)001:17405: 'gro ba yongs kyi dpal du gyur bar shog /
NK053('i)001:17406: de lta bu yi man ngag lung ston pa'i //
NK053('i)001:17407: bka' drin chen po dge ba'i bshes gnyen dang //
NK053('i)001:17408: dam tshig srog gi bsdus pa'i mched lcam rnams 'og min lhun gyis grub pa'i gzhal yas su //
NK053('i)001:17409: dus gsum 'du 'bral med par 'grogs pa dang //
NK053('i)001:17410: gsang ba chen po thugs kyi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:17411: dus gsum 'du 'bral med par 'grogs par shog /
NK053('i)001:17413: de nas yum 2gyis mar me phyag tu bzhes la /
NK053('i)001:17414: mar me'i smon lam gdab pa ni /
NK053('i)001:17416: dur khrod gsang ba mchog gi dkyil 'khor du //
NK053('i)001:17417: rdo rje slob dpon gnyen gyis dbu bzung nas //
NK053('i)001:17418: rgyal ba'i gdung 'tshob mched dang lcam dral rnams //
NK053('i)001:17419: nam zhig byang chub lam du zhugs pa'i tshe //
NK053('i)001:17420: 'khor ba'i g.yang sa chen por mi btang zhing //
NK053('i)001:17421: dmyal ba'i zangs khar rbab tu mi btang zhing //
NK053('i)001:17422: gcong rong zab mo'i gnas su mi skye zhing //
NK053('i)001:17423: mngal gyi srin bu dag tu ma skye zhing //
NK053('i)001:17424: gcan gzan gdug pa'i sgra skad mi thos shing //
NK053('i)001:17425: mtshon rnon gdug pa'i dbal gyis mi phog cing //
NK053('i)001:17426: 'khor ba'i mun nag chen por mi btang zhing //
NK053('i)001:17427: dge ba'i bshes gnyen bka' drin byams pa'i mgon //
NK053('i)001:17428: mi 'bral srog gi 'brel ba'i mched lcam rnams //
NK053('i)001:17429: tshe rabs 'di nas tshe rgyud gar skyes kyang //
NK053('i)001:17430: mi 'bral rtse gcig 'grogs pa'i ting 'dzin gyis //
NK053('i)001:17431: sa bcu'i khyad par rim gyis bgrod gyur nas //
NK053('i)001:17432: nam zhig 'chi 'phos dus tshe byung ba na //
NK053('i)001:17433: 'khor ba'i g.yang sa chen po ltung srid pas //
NK053('i)001:17434: snang ba'i go 'byed gsal ba'i zhun mar 'dis //
NK053('i)001:17435: sgrub mchog bdag cag rnams kyi shul mtshon nas //
NK053('i)001:17436: rgyal ba rgya mtsho'i tshos kyis mdun nas bsus //
NK053('i)001:17437: yi dam rgyal ba'i lhas ni srog brten nas //
NK053('i)001:17438: ma sring rgya mtsho'i tshogs kyis shul nas bskyol //
NK053('i)001:17439: byang chub sems dpa' brgyad kyis mtha' brten te //
NK053('i)001:17440: byang chub sems ma rnams ni rol mo 'bul //
NK053('i)001:17441: lcang lo can gyi gnas su phyin pa'i tshe //
NK053('i)001:17442: rdo rje'i khro rgyal rnams kyi zhal mthong nas //
NK053('i)001:17443: rig pa'i rgyal po'i zhabs drung skyes nas kyang //
NK053('i)001:17444: bla med sku gsung thugs su grub par shog /
NK053('i)001:17448: sgrub pa po kun gyis gos bzang po gyon te /
NK053('i)001:17449: zhal zas phun sum tshogs pa thogs la /
NK053('i)001:17450: 'di skad du brjod par bya ste /
NK053('i)001:17451: byang chub sems mchog shes rab ting 'dzin gyis //
NK053('i)001:17452: nyon mongs bdag 'dzin rnam rtog kun spangs nas //
NK053('i)001:17453: bdag nyid chen po chos nyid kyi don la rab bsgom pas //
NK053('i)001:17454: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK053('i)001:17455: rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa skar ltar 'phro ba yi //
NK053('i)001:17456: za byed bdud 'dul log rtog kun btul nas //
NK053('i)001:17457: bla med byang chub mchog la bkod pa yis //
NK053('i)001:17458: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK053('i)001:17459: zhi rgyas dbang dang mngon spyod phrin kyis //
NK053('i)001:17460: rgyud drug sems can ma las kun bsgral te //
NK053('i)001:17461: bla med byang chub mchog la bkod pa yis //
NK053('i)001:17462: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK053('i)001:17463: bka' gsang sgrub pa'i dkyil 'khor chen po ru //
NK053('i)001:17464: rdo rje slob dpon mched dang lcam dral gyi //
NK053('i)001:17465: thugs dam chen po yongs su bskang ba yis //
NK053('i)001:17466: bkra shis des kyang deng 'dir bde legs shog /
NK053('i)001:17470: gong du mtshan ma med pa'i ngang du bsdus shing gshegs su gsol ba rnams /
NK053('i)001:17471: slar la brten cing de dag dga' bar bya ba'i phyir /
NK053('i)001:17472: mkha' 'gro rgya mtshos brten cing bros bskor ba la yang /
NK053('i)001:17473: he ru ka'i gal po las /
NK053('i)001:17474: mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho brten pa dang //
NK053('i)001:17475: ma sring rgya mtsho bsnyen pa'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:17476: bro dang glu dang rnga la sogs //
NK053('i)001:17477: rtsed 'jo mang po lugs bzhin bya //
NK053('i)001:17478: lta ba dran par bya ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:17480: bdud rnams rtag tu 'dul ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:17481: bro ni bar chad med par brdungs //
NK053('i)001:17482: dkyil 'khor rang la gsal ba'i phyir //
NK053('i)001:17483: tshig ni snying po 'dzab tu bzlas //
NK053('i)001:17484: de phyir glu bro rgyun mi gcad //
NK053('i)001:17486: bar 'dir ru lu glu gar gyi bro brdung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17487: glu drug blangs pa byas la /
NK053('i)001:17488: ma sring mkha' 'gro rgya mtsho rnams //
NK053('i)001:17489: gtan du gshegs pa ma lags te //
NK053('i)001:17490: slar yang sems can don du gshegs //
NK053('i)001:17491: dkyil 'khor gzhal yas bsrung du gsol //
NK053('i)001:17493: de nas 9dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo ba ni /
NK053('i)001:17494: bdag don dang gzhan don du bsngo ba /
NK053('i)001:17496: bdag gis bla na med pa'i byang chub bsgrub pa'i thabs //
NK053('i)001:17497: sku gsung thugs kyis brnag pa'i don bsdus 'di //
NK053('i)001:17498: phal gyi spyod yul thun mong ma lags te //
NK053('i)001:17499: blo zhan bdag gis mngon sum tshad mar /
NK053('i)001:17501: dgongs pa gnyis su med par /
NK053('i)001:17502: 'grel ba'i lung la brten pa'i nyams //
NK053('i)001:17503: rtse gcig rang sems dpang du btsugs nas ni //
NK053('i)001:17504: yang nas yang du sems la brlan pa dang //
NK053('i)001:17505: lus dang srog gi phyir yang mi btang zhing //
NK053('i)001:17506: bskal pa thog ma med pa tshun chad nas //
NK053('i)001:17507: da lta phan chad dge ba ci bsags pa //
NK053('i)001:17508: de dag ma lus gcig tu bsdus nas ni //
NK053('i)001:17509: bla na med pa'i byang chub mchog tu bsngo //
NK053('i)001:17510: de ltar bsngo ba'i dge ba'i rtsa ba des //
NK053('i)001:17511: 'phags pa kun la mchod pa'i sprin 'byung ste //
NK053('i)001:17512: bdag dang gzhan gyi dgongs pa mthar phyin bsngo //
NK053('i)001:17513: lam la gnas pa'i byang chub sems dpa' rnams //
NK053('i)001:17514: mngon du mi 'gyur bag chags kun byang nas //
NK053('i)001:17515: mtshan mar mi ldog mngon par rdzogs par bsngo'o //
NK053('i)001:17516: nyam thos rang rgyal chos la bdag med cing //
NK053('i)001:17517: bsti gnas sa la nges par phyin par bsngo'o //
NK053('i)001:17518: ngan song mi ldog mngon par mtho ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17519: khams gsum sems can sgrib pa kun byang ste //
NK053('i)001:17520: phan yon rgyud gzhung mdo las ji ltar 'byung ba bzhin //
NK053('i)001:17521: mtha' yas sems can rnams kyis thob par shog /
NK053('i)001:17522: de ltar bsngosa pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba de //
NK053('i)001:17523: bdag gi lus sems rgyud la yongs smin te //
NK053('i)001:17524: tshe rabs bgrangs pa'i sdig pa kun byang nas //
NK053('i)001:17525: gsang sngags sdom dang dam tshig tshul khrims dang //
NK053('i)001:17526: nyams pa bskangs shing legs par sor chud nas //
NK053('i)001:17527: bla na med pa'i byang chub mchog tu bsngo'o //
NK053('i)001:17528: de ltar bsngosa pa'i dge ba'i rtsa ba des //
NK053('i)001:17529: gal te tshe yi 'du byed gyur pa na //
NK053('i)001:17530: skye ba ngan pas bar ni mi chod cing //
NK053('i)001:17531: tshe rabs kun tu skye ba dran pa dang //
NK053('i)001:17532: bdag dang gzhan gyis don la mthun spyod pa'i //
NK053('i)001:17533: mthu dang dbang yang nges par thob gyur nas //
NK053('i)001:17534: mthar yang nges par rdzogs par sangs rgyas nas //
NK053('i)001:17535: mtha' yas sems can rnams kyi dpal du shog /
NK053('i)001:17536: de nas 10ma dag pa bshags pa ni /
NK053('i)001:17537: rdo rje slob dpon dang mched dang lcam dral gyis bshags shing gnang ba stsal te /
NK053('i)001:17539: rdo rje slob dpon la mi tshangs pas /
NK053('i)001:17540: mched tsho gnyis su chad la /
NK053('i)001:17543: thams cad ma lus mched lcam dral //
NK053('i)001:17544: rdo rje 'bar ba'i lu gu rgyud //
NK053('i)001:17545: cis kyang mi phyed 'brel ba la //
NK053('i)001:17548: thugs dam gzhung bzhin ma 'brel zhing //
NK053('i)001:17549: dkyil 'khor gcig dang bla med bsgrubs //
NK053('i)001:17550: lhan ne lhan ne 'grub par shog /
NK053('i)001:17551: rang bzhin dag pas tshangs par gsol //
NK053('i)001:17554: hoh yi dam lha ma gsal bar bsgoms sam /
NK053('i)001:17555: mched lcam dral la ngan sems sam /
NK053('i)001:17557: ma bskyed na'ang tshangs par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:17560: thams cad ma lus mched lcam dral //
NK053('i)001:17561: mnyam la mi mnyam don gcig ste //
NK053('i)001:17562: legs nongs rnam par dbyer med kyang //
NK053('i)001:17563: rnam par dag pa'i sgo tsam du //
NK053('i)001:17564: gzhung las 'gal ba ci mchis dang //
NK053('i)001:17565: thugs dang 'gal ba ci mchis pa //
NK053('i)001:17566: rnam par dag pa'i sems kyis mthol //
NK053('i)001:17567: don gyis dmigs nas tshig gis bshags //
NK053('i)001:17568: 'dzin chags med par bzod par gsol //
NK053('i)001:17569: rang bzhin dag pas tshangs pa stsol //
NK053('i)001:17570: yang gcig gis gang skad brjod de /
NK053('i)001:17571: de nas mched tsho gnyis pos /
NK053('i)001:17572: rdo rje slob dpon la bshags pa dbul te /
NK053('i)001:17573: rdo rje slob dpon dpal dang ldan //
NK053('i)001:17574: 'phags pa'i sku dang tha mi dad //
NK053('i)001:17575: zhal nas gsungs pa rgyal pa'i bka' //
NK053('i)001:17576: snyan khung brgyud pa man ngag lung //
NK053('i)001:17577: sku gsung thugs kyang rdo rjer 'gyur //
NK053('i)001:17578: 'jig rten rje dang pha ma'i tshul //
NK053('i)001:17579: khyad par rim pas 'phags pa la //
NK053('i)001:17580: bkur bsti rim gro rngo ma thogs //
NK053('i)001:17581: ltung ba'i gnas su mi 'gyur zhing //
NK053('i)001:17582: tshangs pa mod la bstsal du gsol //
NK053('i)001:17584: de nas rdo rje slob dpon gyis tshangs pa ma bstsal nas /
NK053('i)001:17585: dam tshig nyams na sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub mi thob pas /
NK053('i)001:17586: de la tshangs pa bstsal ba /
NK053('i)001:17587: hoh rigs kyi bu rnams kyis sngar nongs pa dran nam /
NK053('i)001:17589: slan chad zhugs par bsdom mam /
NK053('i)001:17592: slan chad zhugs par bsdom na /
NK053('i)001:17593: byin du sgrib pa mi mnga' na /
NK053('i)001:17594: gal te mnga' bar gyur yang ston gyi ba mo
NK053('i)001:17595: dpyid kyi nyi mas bzhub bzhin du byang zhing dag
NK053('i)001:17596: par gyur cig / de ltar gyur pa'i bden pa'i
NK053('i)001:17597: byin rlabs kyis rdo rje slob dpon yang bstan pa'i
NK053('i)001:17598: sgron me yun ring du gnas par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:17599: rdo rje'i mched lcam dral yang mi nub pa'i rgyal
NK053('i)001:17600: mtshan la mi 'gyur ba'i g.yung drung rin po che'i
NK053('i)001:17601: dpung rgyan ltar dar zhing rgyas par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:17603: de nas rdo rje slob dpon dang mched lcam dral kun gyis /
NK053('i)001:17604: dkyil 'khor gyi lha la ma bshags na dngos grub mi thob pas /
NK053('i)001:17605: kun gyis man+dala spyi bo la blangs la /
NK053('i)001:17614: chos la chags na chags pa ste /
NK053('i)001:17615: yum la chags pa chags pa'i mchog go //
NK053('i)001:17616: khro bo'i tshogs la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK053('i)001:17617: phyag na phyag rgya chen po ste //
NK053('i)001:17618: snga dam gnyan po nyams pa mthol zhing bshags //
NK053('i)001:17619: phyi dam gnyan po nod cing sdom //
NK053('i)001:17620: bdag cag g.yar dam skong gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:17621: hoh las thams cad dbang du gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:17622: dbang dngos grub tu gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:17623: lnga pa gyur shog gi smon lam /
NK053('i)001:17624: de ltar gyur pa dang gyur pa'i byin rlabs kyis /
NK053('i)001:17625: 'o skol rdo rje slob dpon dang /
NK053('i)001:17627: lus sems kyi rgyud la las dang nyon mongs pa'i
NK053('i)001:17628: bag chags thams cad ston ka'i ba mo la dpyid
NK053('i)001:17629: kyi nyi mas bzhu ba bzhin du byang zhing dag
NK053('i)001:17631: tshe dang dbang thang dpal dang gzi mdangs thams cad
NK053('i)001:17632: rin po che'i dpung rgyan ltar dar shing rgyas par
NK053('i)001:17634: rdo rje slob dpon yang ston pa'i sgron me la
NK053('i)001:17635: yun ring zhing 'gro ba'i don mdzad pa la mthu
NK053('i)001:17636: che zhing thabs la mkhas par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:17638: chos chen po 'di yang rgyal mtshan gyi rtse mo ltar nub pa'i dus med par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:17643: mi nad phyugs nad rgyun chad //
NK053('i)001:17647: bde skyid phun sum tshogs pa dang ldan par gyur cig /
NK053('i)001:17649: de nas gu ru la yon dbul zhing gtang rag gtong ngo //
NK053('i)001:17650: slob dpon h'u k+aa ra nyid ni /
NK053('i)001:17651: de nas gdod dkyil 'khor bsdu ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17653: glu bro dang gsum po de gdod bya gsungs /
NK053('i)001:17654: rdo rje bzhad pa nyid gong ltar 'thad /
NK053('i)001:17658: zhi ba rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin dang /
NK053('i)001:17659: khro bo rgyun gyi ting nge 'dzin te /
NK053('i)001:17660: man ngag kha tshar las shes par bya'o //
NK053('i)001:17661: de 12thams cad bsdus te dge ba'i rtsa ba ji ltar bsngo snyam pa la /
NK053('i)001:17662: kun kyang sems can don du bsngo //
NK053('i)001:17664: skabs sbyor bco brgyad las tha ma dge ba'i rtsa ba bsngo ba'o //
NK053('i)001:17666: 'di la brten te byung ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17667: bdag gis dge ba ci spyad pa thams cad /
NK053('i)001:17668: sems can thams cad dang thun mong du bla na med par thob par bsngo ba'o //
NK053('i)001:17669: zhes bya ba'i tha tshig go //
NK053('i)001:17670: h'u k+aa ra'i gzhung rtsa ba'i mdzad byang ni /
NK053('i)001:17671: sgrub pa chen po yang dag grub pa zhes bya ba /
NK053('i)001:17672: grub pa'i slob dpon chen po badz+ra h'u k+aa ra'i zhal snga nas mdzad pa rdzogs so //
NK053('i)001:17675: bod kyi lha btsad po khri srong lde'u btsan gyi bka' lung gis /
NK053('i)001:17676: dpal n+aa len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang du /
NK053('i)001:17677: rgya gar gyi mkhan po h'u k+aa ra de nyid dang /
NK053('i)001:17678: zhu chen gyi lo ts+aa ba gnubs nam mkha'i snying pos bsgyur cing zhus shing gtan la phab pa'o //
NK053('i)001:17682: h'u k+aa ras mdzad rgya dpe las //
NK053('i)001:17683: 'khrug bsdebs ma tshang kha bskangs nas //
NK053('i)001:17684: man ngag kun gyi tig 'grel du //
NK053('i)001:17686: sgrub thabs cho ga rgya cher byas //
NK053('i)001:17687: 'di la nyes gyur ci mchis pa //
NK053('i)001:17688: bde gshegs mkha' 'gro rnam bzhi rdo rje rin chen pad+ma las rigs la //
NK053('i)001:17689: bzod gsol dngos grub ci mnga' ba //
NK053('i)001:17690: 'di sgrub rnams kyis thob par shog /
NK053('i)001:17691: dpal khrag 'thung chen po sgrub pa'i thabs /
NK053('i)001:17692: yang dag grub pa'i gsang 'grel chen po /
NK053('i)001:17693: o rgyan gyi slob dpon chen po pad+ma sam+b+ha wa dang /
NK053('i)001:17694: zhu chen gyi lo ts+aa ba dge slong nam mkha'i snying pos /
NK053('i)001:17695: h'u k+aa ra'i skad rnying las kyang pad+mas man ngag 'khrug bsdebs te /
NK053('i)001:17696: gsang ba'i tig 'grel du bsgyur ba /
NK053('i)001:17697: yul dbus kyi chos 'khor bsam yas kyi mchims phu
NK053('i)001:17698: bre gu dge'u ru bod kyi skad gdangs dang mthun
NK053('i)001:17700: rje byang chub sems dpa' khri srong lde'u btsan gyi yi dam du gtad pa'o //
NK053('i)001:17703: dbang dang man ngag rdzogs par byas nas /
NK053('i)001:17704: bod 'bangs su la yang mi spel ba'i rgyas btab /
NK053('i)001:17705: brtan ma bcu gnyis mngon du bkug nas /
NK053('i)001:17707: su la yang mi bstan par dam bcas so //
NK053('i)001:17710: // sgrub thabs kun gyi ma gzhi /
NK053('i)001:17714: bskyed rdzogs rnam pa gsum gyi spyi khog /
NK053('i)001:17715: bka' yi tha ram chen po 'di /
NK053('i)001:17716: dus kyi tha ma la bka' ltar ni mi spyod /
NK053('i)001:17717: theg pa 'og ma pa'i tshig gi sgro skur gyis /
NK053('i)001:17718: gsang ba dam pa bslad de /
NK053('i)001:17719: dper na spyin chu la mar khus bslad pa bzhin te sbyor ba'i mthu med do //
NK053('i)001:17720: sgra dag gtad kas sngags la bkab pas gsang sngags gol te /
NK053('i)001:17721: don mi 'dus par thor nas bsgrub bya gtor te 'gro bas /
NK053('i)001:17722: gsang sngags kyi lus nor bu rin po che lta bu ni tshig gis mtha' la bskyal te btang /
NK053('i)001:17723: ldem dgongs man ngag gi tshig rna phrug brag la
NK053('i)001:17724: 'dzeg pa lta bu ni sgro skur gyis mtha' la
NK053('i)001:17725: bskyal / 'brel bar sbyor ba'i tshig bya ngang mo'i 'gros lta bu dang /
NK053('i)001:17726: rang rkyen gnyer tshig rus sbal gyi nur 'gros lta bu dang /
NK053('i)001:17727: gtar ka gegs sel gyi tshi glag gzan la 'jums pa 'dra ba'i gsang sngags kyi lus bshig ste /
NK053('i)001:17728: dngos grub sgrub pa'i rgyud gtan yal te gtan 'khyags par 'gyur bas /
NK053('i)001:17734: tha snyad kyi tshig la dga' ba dang /
NK053('i)001:17736: gsang mi thub pa rnams la ni /
NK053('i)001:17737: rang gi srog la bab kyang ma btang shig /
NK053('i)001:17738: srog lus man chad bshig nas 'bul ba /
NK053('i)001:17739: gong ma rnams las bzlog ste /
NK053('i)001:17740: brtags pa zung ya tsam la yang /
NK053('i)001:17741: yang nas yang du gdams la /
NK053('i)001:17742: sa ma ya na ra kan /
NK053('i)001:17743: zhes bya zhing sbyin pa las ma gtogs pa /
NK053('i)001:17745: sgyu ma'i zas nor la blta ba /
NK053('i)001:17747: ye shes kyi lha dang srung mas chad pa chod la tshe'i 'du byed bskums shig /
NK053('i)001:17748: ngan song gsum po las thar ba'i dus med par shog cig /
NK053('i)001:17753: sangs rgyas gnyis pas zhing 'dir rjes brtse bas //
NK053('i)001:17754: 'dzam gling chung ngu'i byang phyogs zhabs bcags te //
NK053('i)001:17755: yang le shod du yang dag thugs sgrub mdzad //
NK053('i)001:17756: phyag chen mchog dngos bsgrub pa'i tshul bstan tshe /
NK053('i)001:17758: 1 / bod 'dre gdug pa'i 'tshub slong gzhom pa'i gzer //
NK053('i)001:17759: phur rgyud skyes bu zung gi phrag khur 'dren //
NK053('i)001:17760: bdud bgegs chos srung sgyur byed yang phur gnyis //
NK053('i)001:17761: gdong dmar can gyi thog ma'i chos skal dngos /
NK053('i)001:17763: 2 / 'og min gnyis pa dpal gyi bsam yas su //
NK053('i)001:17764: gsang chen chos kyi dga' ston 'gyed pa'i dus //
NK053('i)001:17765: 'gro kun phur lnga'i dbang sgyur sems gdul phyir //
NK053('i)001:17766: gnyen po'i chos kyang thugs sgrub gtso bor sngags /
NK053('i)001:17768: 3 / de phyir snang srid 'khor 'das chos so cog /
NK053('i)001:17769: rgyal thun thugs kyi ye shes sgyu 'phrul gar //
NK053('i)001:17770: dag mnyam lha yi phyag rgyar yongs shar ba //
NK053('i)001:17771: dpal chen yang dag he ru ka zhes grags /
NK053('i)001:17773: 4 / pad+ma'i thugs dam zhal lung gad+g+aa'i rgyun //
NK053('i)001:17774: bskyed rdzogs spyi khog man ngag snying po'i bcud //
NK053('i)001:17775: bsnyen sgrub chog phrin lag len dang 'brel ba //
NK053('i)001:17776: gsang 'grel chen por grags pa'i gzhung bzang 'di /
NK053('i)001:17778: 5 / sngon dus lha sras chos rgyal nam snying sogs //
NK053('i)001:17779: skal ldan thugs sras rje 'bangs mchog bdun la //
