NK053('i)001:17780: lkog chos stsal ba'i gdangs zab zhal mjal zhing //
NK053('i)001:17781: skal bzang thob pa sngon smon bsod nams mthu /
NK053('i)001:17783: 6 / de phyir rnying bstan 'dzin pa'i skyes bu tshos //
NK053('i)001:17784: yid bzhin dbang rgyal las lhag rnyed daka'i gzhung //
NK053('i)001:17785: bsnyen bkur sri zhus dpe lung rgyun spel phyir //
NK053('i)001:17786: thugs ngal mi bskyung bstan 'gro'i don dgongs 'tshal /
NK053('i)001:17788: 7 / de yang mtha' 'khob gdong dmar can gyi rgyal khams
NK053('i)001:17789: 'di rgyal ba gzhan gyis re zhig gdul skal du
NK053('i)001:17790: ma gyur tshe kun mkhyen pad+ma ka ras gdul zhing
NK053('i)001:17791: du gzigs te / mun gling 'dir sku dngos zhabs bcags nas /
NK053('i)001:17792: 'og min gnyis pa dpal gyi bsam yas su chos kyi 'khor lo bskor ba'i dus su /
NK053('i)001:17793: zhal nas gsungs pa'i bka' yi chos sde grangs mang bzhugs mod /
NK053('i)001:17794: phal cher mi min gyi gnas su gdan drangs te rang re'i las skal du ma gyur /
NK053('i)001:17795: bod 'bangs kyi chos skal du gyur pa gu ru'i
NK053('i)001:17796: gsung bka' mang du bzhugs pa deb ther dkar chag
NK053('i)001:17797: rnams su gsal ba rim gyis nub kyang /
NK053('i)001:17798: lha sras chos rgyal khri srong lde btsan dang /
NK053('i)001:17799: gzungs ma ye shes mtsho rgyal /
NK053('i)001:17800: yang dag thugs kyi bka' bab gnubs ston nam mkha'i
NK053('i)001:17801: snying po sogs skal ldan thugs sras thu bo bdun
NK053('i)001:17802: la man ngag mnog chos su stsal te bka' rgyas
NK053('i)001:17803: btab pa'i zab chos yang dag gsang ba'i ti ka
NK053('i)001:17804: chen po rang re'i bsod nams kyi dpal du bzhugs
NK053('i)001:17805: pa 'dis ni / snga 'gyur nang rgyud sde gsum
NK053('i)001:17806: gyi bskyed rdzogs sgrub phrin dang bcas pa'i zab don
NK053('i)001:17807: man ngag gi sgo nas gsal bar ston pa ma
NK053('i)001:17808: pa 'dis ni / zad / rdo rje theg pa
NK053('i)001:17809: spyi yi mtha' drug tshul bzhi'i gab sbas kyi zab
NK053('i)001:17810: don kyang ston pa'i rgyud sde kun gyi spyi khog
NK053('i)001:17811: lta bu 'dzam gling na khyad par 'phags pa'i zab
NK053('i)001:17812: pa 'dis ni / zad / chos lags te /
NK053('i)001:17813: 'jam dpal dbyangs dngos kun mkhyen mi pham chos kyi
NK053('i)001:17815: sgrub thabs man ngag gi bshad pa yang dag gsang
NK053('i)001:17816: 'grel chen po zhes pa grub pa'i rig 'dzin kun
NK053('i)001:17817: gyi snying bcud sa steng gi rgyan gcig 'di mdzad
NK053('i)001:17819: mkhar chen bza' la sogs pa la bstan cing gsang
NK053('i)001:17820: ba'i bka' rgyas nan tan du mdzad pa yin te
NK053('i)001:17821: / zhes basngagasa pa'i gzhung 'di'i dpe sngar dus su
NK053('i)001:17822: snga 'gyur gdan sa che shos rnams su re zung
NK053('i)001:17823: / gzhugs kyang / nye sngon dus 'gyur skabs gal
NK053('i)001:17824: che'i chos dpe phal cher mi mngon dbyings su gshegs
NK053('i)001:17825: / gzhugs kyang / par gyur / 'on kyang gu
NK053('i)001:17826: ru'i gsang 'grel chen po 'di yi ma phyi gcig
NK053('i)001:17827: kho na rmugs sangs sbas gnas phyogs su bzhugs pa
NK053('i)001:17828: rang gi lag tu 'byor ba de gsar bris zhu
NK053('i)001:17829: bcos ma zin pa yin tsa na /
NK053('i)001:17830: yig phreng dang tshi rkang chad lhag mang du snang bas /
NK053('i)001:17831: dag bcos ma dpe mdo smad phyogs kun tu nan tan gyis btsal yang ma rnyed pas /
NK053('i)001:17832: lo gcig ring tsam theng grangs mjal zhing 'bru nor dang mchan gong 'og 'chug pa'i yig skyon rnams /
NK053('i)001:17833: 'jam mgon kong sprul rin po che'i sgrub khog dang /
NK053('i)001:17835: 'brel yod rnying rgyud lung sogs su gsal ba'i tshig
NK053('i)001:17836: don chad pa yig phreng du ma kha gsab byas
NK053('i)001:17837: te / gsar bris dpe tshar gcig bskrun nas dpe
NK053('i)001:17838: rgyun mi nub phyir glog spar tshar lnga bcu bskrun
NK053('i)001:17839: te / / slar yang zhu bcos khungs 'tshol dang
NK053('i)001:17840: 'brel spar gzhi tshar gcig 'di rang nyid kyis sug
NK053('i)001:17842: yig rnying gi mchan zhig 'dug pa yig skyon mang bas yid rton pher ba mi 'dug pas /
NK053('i)001:17843: dgos nges don ldan rnams rang sor bzhag /
NK053('i)001:17844: sla mchan bskyar zlos rnams nyung ru btang ste cung dag par rlom mod /
NK053('i)001:17845: bdag lta bu so skye blun rmongs la yid rton mi 'os phyir /
NK053('i)001:17846: slad phyin snga 'gyur bstan 'dzin skyes bu rnams kyis dpe btsal gnyer gnang ste /
NK053('i)001:17848: dag bcos mdzad rgyur btang snyoms su ma lus par
NK053('i)001:17849: thugs khur che bzhes gnang thub pa gsol ba 'debs
NK053('i)001:17851: zang zing yo byad nyer bsdogs ma byas shing //
NK053('i)001:17852: srog bsdom 'jigs rung rgya mtsho brgal ma dgos //
NK053('i)001:17853: bde blag nor bu thob pa'i skal bzang las //
NK053('i)001:17854: khyad 'phags rnyed daka'i chos 'phrad e ma rmad /
NK053('i)001:17856: 1 / rgyal kun bka' yi gsang mdzod bdud rtsi'i char //
NK053('i)001:17857: lo pan klu rgyal 'phags chen rdzu 'phrul dpal //
NK053('i)001:17858: zhing 'di'i tha grur 'bebs pa'i dge mtshan gyis //
NK053('i)001:17859: skye rgu nyer 'tsho'i bde skyid slar rgyas shog 2 /
NK053('i)001:17860: bdag kyang tshe rabs kun tu pad 'byung rjes //
NK053('i)001:17861: rjes bzung zab gsang lam gyis rgyud smin cing //
NK053('i)001:17862: khyod kyi chos bstan spel ba'i bsod nams mthus //
NK053('i)001:17863: mkha' khyab 'gro sgrol phrin las mthar phyin shog 3 /
NK053('i)001:17864: ces pa mjug byang ched du brjod pa 'di ni /
NK053('i)001:17865: byang phyogs b+ho ta'i ljongs kyi bstan 'gro yongs kyi phan bde'i 'byung gnas /
NK053('i)001:17866: o di ya na'i slob dpon chen po mtsho skyes
NK053('i)001:17867: rdo rje'i bstan zhabs su skyes pa dge sbyong tha
NK053('i)001:17868: shal ba rmongs rtul pad+ma kun grol ming can des
NK053('i)001:17869: / chos 'di'i ma phyi dpe bskrun bgyi skabs smon tshig bris pa'o //
